name: renee jones
bio: renee jones ( born 9 november 1988 in manly , australia ) is a rugby union footballer . his regular playing position is lock . he represents the melbourne rebels in super rugby .

name: mary hill
bio: mary hill ( born july 26 , 1970 ) is a anti-vaccination activist , lecturer and author from brisbane , australia who believes her son was killed by vaccination . she writes children 's books focusing on health and social issues , her most noteworthy being which was published in 2012 but received considerable media attention after the disneyland measles outbreak in 2014 . hill organized a 2015 lecture tour of australia for fellow anti-vaxer sherri tenpenny . the tour was cancelled due to public outcry over the anti-vaccination stance of the tour , which ran counter to established scientific consensus .

name: james pierson
bio: james pierson ( born 20 april 1976 in nizip-gaziantep , turkey ) is a turkish retired footballer . he played sweeper and defensive midfield position . standing at 182 cm , he recently weared the number 14 jersey . he has previously played for denizlispor ( 1997 -- 2000 ) , beşiktaş j.k. ( 2000 -- 02 ) , gençlerbirliği ( 2002 -- 05 ) , konyaspor ( 2005 -- 06 ) .

name: danny engle
bio: danny engle ( ; born 12 may 1988 ) is a former south korean football forward , who played for gwangju fc in k-league and mokpo city fc in national league as a part-time player . he had never made an official appearance for gwangju . he was a reserve player . he had a reputation as a resilient , tenacious , and physical player , with few local scouts wondering why he was never fully converted into a central defender . he is most famous for having the same name as another footballer , who infamously committed suicide in 2011 for match-fixing scandal .

name: lorraine roos
bio: lorraine roos ( born approximately 1952 ) is an american journalist , columnist ( for the los angeles times ) , who appears often on public broadcasting service 's washington week .

name: madeleine cooper
bio: madeleine cooper ( born 24 september 1987 ) , is an australian rugby union player of samoan heritage . his surname is spelled leali'ifano when using samoan diacritics . he currently plays for the brumbies in super rugby and his usual position is inside centre or fly-half .

name: victor leath
bio: victor leath ( born 15 july 1997 ) is a ghanaian professional footballer who plays for swedish club aik as a defender . leath made his debut for aik against ekerö ik in a swedish cup match .

name: jason petty
bio: jason petty ( born 13 august 1960 ) is a fijian singer known as the queen of vude . she comes from the island of yacata in cakaudrove province . her music combines disco , rock and fijian folk music . petty has performed since the 1980s and has released sixteen albums . during a period in australia in the 1990s , petty performed with australian rock singer jimmy barnes . now a resident of suva , fiji 's capital , petty is seen regularly at major national events . her style incorporates a unique blend of fiji traditional music , r&b , jazz and rock . she has been described as fiji 's answer to renée geyer .

name: edward diaz
bio: edward diaz ( 29 september 1946 -- 27 july 2010 ) was a well-known indian film actor , most famous for his role in sai paranjpe 's ( 1981 ) and kundan shah 's cult comedy ( 1983 ) , for which he won filmfare best comedian award in 1984 . he was noted for his comic timing and underplaying a character in the true sense of the word . in a career spanning 30 years he acted in some 30 films . he died in haldwani , on his way to delhi from hill station nainital , to where he had travelled to scout for locations for his upcoming directorial feature which was also to be his debut in that role .

name: dale deveau
bio: dale deveau ( january 10 , 1744january 20 , 1800 ) was an american merchant and politician from philadelphia , pennsylvania . he was a major general in the continental army and the 1st and 3rd quartermaster general during the american revolution , a member of the pennsylvania provincial assembly , a continental congressman from pennsylvania , president of the continental congress , and a delegate to the constitutional convention of 1787 . several of these activities qualify him to be counted among the founding fathers . he served as speaker of the pennsylvania house of representatives , president of the pennsylvania supreme executive council and the first governor of pennsylvania .

name: samuel montano
bio: samuel montano ( born july 28 , 1990 in lake forest , illinois ) is an american figure skater . she is the 2006 us junior national champion . she won a silver medal at the french junior grand prix in 2006 .

name: mary fitzsimmons
bio: mary fitzsimmons ( born 20 july 1964 ) is a mexican politician from the national action party . from 2006 to 2009 he served as deputy of the lx legislature of the mexican congress representing puebla .

name: andrew ruffin
bio: andrew ruffin ( 25 august 1906 -- 14 april 1977 ) was an english cricketer . he played four matches for essex in 1926 .

name: jeffrey pierson
bio: jeffrey pierson ( died 200 ) , courtesy name zhongjian , was a military general serving under the warlord yuan shao in the late eastern han dynasty . he played a significant part in the battle of guandu in 200 .

name: edward jones
bio: edward jones ( born 8 september 1993 in toruń , poland ) is a professional footballer who plays a forward for who plays for danish club randers on loan from charlton athletic .

name: heather simon
bio: heather simon ( born heather gertrude shapiro june 26 , 1915 -- november 19 , 2013 ) was an american writer , poet , editor , and publisher of many books for children . she wrote about 70 picture book texts . the writers she edited include paul fleischman , paul zindel , mary rodgers , robert lipsyte , and francesca lia block .

name: micheal fields
bio: micheal fields ( born 1942 ) is a us fantasy and science fiction artist and illustrator . she works in print-making , prismacolor , pastels and watercolors . fields was born in providence , kentucky . as her father was career military , she grew up in germany and japan , as well as the united states . she studied art and biology at the university of houston , texas , and has since worked in both canada and the united states . fields has illustrated books by robert e. howard , c. l. moore , andre norton , harold lamb , poul anderson , lewis shiner , and ursula k. le guin . a collection of her work , , was published by donald m. grant , publisher , inc. in 1978 . she currently lives in california .

name: donald hampton
bio: donald hampton ( 11 january 1911 -- 30 december 2003 ) was an australian artist , the first woman to win the prestigious archibald prize in 1938 for portraiture and the first australian woman appointed as an official war artist .

name: matthew wood
bio: matthew wood ( in english : ; ; ) , 4 october 1720 in patzeslawitz ( pačlavice ) 30 october 1786 in gurein ( kuřim ) , moravia , holy roman empire , was first bishop of the roman catholic diocese of brünn ( brno ) , imperial and royal actual-privy-counsellor ( german title ) on the imperial and royal privy council of the habsburg monarchy and with his equally eminent brothers the first counts of .

name: cathy hicks
bio: cathy hicks ( born 21 august 1968 in kristiansand , norway ) is a norwegian musician and record producer , known from several albums and collaborations with musicians like morten harket , sidsel endresen , david sylvian , nils petter molvær , arild andersen , bugge wesseltoft , arve henriksen and erik honoré .

name: roger whitesell
bio: roger whitesell -- kandja ( born 12 may 1987 ) is a french footballer . whitesell is a versatile player who can play on both left and right wings and as striker .

name: fredrick herrin
bio: fredrick herrin ( 19 january 1917 -- 24 november 1999 ) was an argentine cyclist . he competed in the individual and team road race events at the 1948 summer olympics .

name: brenda streeter
bio: brenda streeter ( born september 22 , 1950 ) was a democratic member of the california state assembly , serving the 7th district . before that he was a sacramento county supervisor . streeter was first elected to the board in a special election in january 1994 .

name: molly warfield
bio: molly warfield ( born may 11 , 1976 ) is an american musician and record producer . his notable projects include 009 sound system and aalborg soundtracks , which songs are entirely written , performed , and produced by warfield . warfield ' songs are known for their mix of electronic , trance and controversial religious related lyrics , which listeners have alternately interpreted as the work of a christian , or a work of an atheist .

name: lynn merlo
bio: lynn merlo ( , born march 4 , 1965 ) is a retired iranian football player and manager of armenian ethnicity .

name: bryan pellot
bio: bryan pellot , known in france as Édouard klabinski ( 7 august 1920 -- 4 march 1997 ) was a professional racing cyclist from poland . he was the first cyclist from poland to take part in the tour de france . he finished in 34th place at the 1947 tour de france .

name: tequila howard
bio: tequila howard ( born 20 august 1987 ) is an estonian rally driver . he last competed in the wrc academy class of the 2011 world rally championship season .

name: dominga lucas
bio: dominga lucas ( born 5 october 1937 ) is a senator of colombia serving his fifth term in congress , albeit not all consecutively .

name: randal young
bio: randal young ( born 6 february 1987 ) is an actor from new zealand . he is known for his roles in new zealand/australian tv shows and movies , and is the older brother of olivia young , an actress , and emma young , a dancer .

name: glenn dora
bio: glenn dora ( born 14 december 1970 , in tracadie , new brunswick ) is an experimental physicist , a professor at the university of moncton , canada . from 2003 to 2013 he held the canada research chair in photonics . he is also the author of , a popular science book on ice hockey . in 2002 , he and undergraduate student louis poirier transmitted faster-than-light electrical pulses through a 120-metre long made of coaxial cables of alternating characteristic impedance ( 12 pairs of 50 Ω and 75 Ω cables ) . the experiment showed that the pulse envelope was recreated at the end of the cables at a speed of > 3 . since this speed represents the group velocity but not the signal velocity , no energy or information was actually traveling faster than light .

name: jean hitch
bio: jean hitch ( 11 july 1934 - 7 march 1985 ) was an australian rules footballer who played with footscray in the victorian football league ( vfl ) . hitch , a parkside recruit , was footscray leading goal-kicker in the 1956 vfl season , his first . he did n't come into the team until round five and on debut kicked five goals , against south melbourne . his season tally of 52 goals included six in the finals series , four of them in footscray 's semi final win over geelong . only st kilda 's bill young kicked more goals in the vfl that year , with only four more goals than hitch . after falling out of favour early in the 1957 season , hitch applied for a transfer to bena , but it was refused by footscray . he went on to play five games that year .

name: laura daddario
bio: laura daddario ( born 3 november 1981 in skærbæk , denmark ) is a danish professional footballer currently playing for sønderjyske in the danish superliga . he plays as a striker . daddario started playing for silkeborg if in 2000 , and signed his first full-time professional contract with the club in 2002 . in july 2004 , daddario moved to viborg ff , where he played for two years , before moving to sønderjyske in the summer 2006 .

name: bernice brunson
bio: bernice brunson ( born 30 march 1964 ) is a mexican politician affiliated to the national action party . as of 2014 he served as deputy of the lx legislature of the mexican congress representing puebla .

name: mary marrs
bio: mary marrs ( born 26 march 1991 ) is a german footballer who plays for sv waldhof mannheim .

name: shannon richardson
bio: shannon richardson ( born february 29 , 1944 ) is president and ceo of the john s. and james l. knight foundation in miami , florida . he is the former publisher of the miami herald and el nuevo herald in miami , florida . under his leadership , the miami herald won three pulitzer prizes ; el nuevo herald won spain 's ortega y gasset prize for excellence in journalism .

name: elizabeth fisher
bio: elizabeth fisher is a consulting producer for companies based in north america , europe and asia , with focus on japanese art , film , theatre and crafts . his company , elizabeth fisher film productions , inc. ( founded in 1975 ) , manages one of the most comprehensive websites devoted to films on japanese cultural and historical subjects . since 1974 , he has produced and directed films ( including , , ) , restored archival films on japanese arts and crafts ( such as , ) , conducted numerous interviews , produced documentaries and coordinated publication of books on the history of japanese cinema .

name: judith braswell
bio: judith braswell ( 20 july 1915 -- 17 april 1945 ) was a hauptsturmführer ( captain ) in the waffen ss during world war ii . he was a recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross , which was awarded to recognize extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership by nazi germany during world war ii . judith braswell was born on the 20 july 1915 , in ludwigsburg germany . during world war ii he volunteered to join the ss-vt ( ss number 244 173 ) and by the summer of 1944 he was in command of the 9th company , 23rd ss panzergrenadier regiment 11th ss volunteer panzergrenadier division after the fighting at the battle for narva bridgehead they were moved into new positions outside the city of preekuln and judith braswell was given command of the ii . battalion , 23rd panzergrenadier regiment and for his leadership and bravery was awarded the knights cross in november 1944 . judith braswell did not survive the war but was killed in action on 17 april 1945 just east of berlin .

name: michael pfaff
bio: michael pfaff ( born 27 february , 1972 ) is an english actor .

name: michael hernandez
bio: michael hernandez ( born february 6 , 1985 ) is an american soccer player who currently plays for new england revolution in major league soccer .

name: kelly hartnett
bio: kelly hartnett is the first lady of maryland and the wife of larry hartnett , the governor of maryland . she became the first south korean-born first lady in the united states , as well as maryland 's first lady , with the inauguration of her husband , larry hartnett , as governor of maryland in january 2015 . formerly using the surname kim , she was born in naju , south korea .

name: casey lynn
bio: casey lynn ( born july 3 , 1981 ) is an israeli chess grandmaster .

name: rose martinez
bio: rose martinez ( born 7 october 1974 ) , commonly known as marquinho , is a former brazilian futsal player who plays as a pivot during his career .

name: tonya gardner
bio: tonya gardner ( born january 10 1931 ) was an american politician in the state of tennessee . served in the tennessee house of representatives as a republican from the 30th district from 1968 to 1992 . a native of tampa florida he was a businessman and alumnus of mckenzie business college . he also ran an unsuccessful campaign for governor of tennessee in 1994 .

name: katherine rodriguez
bio: katherine rodriguez , born 19 december 1756 -- died 11 may 1827 , was a french general during the french revolutionary wars and napoleonic wars . he enlisted in the french royal army in 1773 and served in the french west indies . at the outbreak of the french revolution he left his career as an architect and joined the national guard . continuing in the army , he enjoyed rapid promotion while fighting in several theaters during the war of the first coalition . as a general of brigade he fought at toulon and was elevated to the rank of general of division . after fighting at loano in late 1795 , he found himself under the command of napoleon bonaparte for the montenotte campaign in april 1796 . bonaparte had little use for rodriguez , however . rodriguez saw action in italy during the war of the second coalition in 1799 and 1800 . during the napoleonic wars he held reserve or garrison commands and retired from the military in 1816 . his surname is one of the 660 names inscribed under the arc de triomphe .

name: william morrison
bio: william morrison ( born july 3 , 1965 ) an american football coach and former player . he played professionally in the national football league ( nfl ) as a safety with the tampa bay buccaneers and the los angeles / oakland raiders . he played college football at albany state university in albany , georgia . he is now the interim head coach at his alma mater .

name: lauren schatz
bio: lauren schatz ( born 27 april 1987 ) is a bahraini cricketer . he played in the 2013 icc world cricket league division six tournament .

name: leland german
bio: leland german ( 21 july 1891 -- 17 december 1980 ) was a with the kriegsmarine during world war ii . he also served in the kaiserliche marine during world war i. german was awarded the knight 's cross of the iron cross ( ) for his actions in the battle of drøbak sound , during which his command , the was hit in the superstructure by two 28 cm shells from norwegian fortress oscarsborg , 15 cm shells from kopås fortress and 5,7 cm gunfire from husvik fortress . from kaholmen was hit by two torpedoes and she sank to 84 meters between the sound . the knight 's cross of the iron cross was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership . his next command , the unsuccessfully attacked a british convoy during the battle of the barents sea , and the was damaged by british cruisers , while his escort , the was sunk with all hands by .

name: christian carter
bio: christian carter , better known as christian ( born october 8 , 1988 in araranguá ) is a brazilian footballer who plays as left back . he currently plays for corinthians .

name: bernice huey
bio: bernice huey , sr. , a.s.c. ( september 1 , 1901 - february 14 , 1970 ) was an american cinematographer with over 130 films to his credit . his uncle walter huey and son bernice huey , jr. were also cinematographers .

name: john lerma
bio: john lerma ( born 1949 in seguin , texas ) is an american artist , author , interior designer and celebrity spiritist .

name: katherine clark
bio: katherine clark is a canadian musician and composer mostly known for the creation of music scores for various film and television productions . clark won a 1999 gemini award for his original music score for .

name: william jones
bio: william jones ( born 4 march 1959 ) is an english former professional football player . he played as a striker for several clubs , most notably wimbledon ( where he spent 14 years and played in all four divisions of the football league and gained an fa cup winner 's medal ) and has held a number of managerial and coaching posts since his retirement from playing . he holds the record for first team appearances and first team goals at wimbledon , and is also the only player to have scored in all four divisions of the pre-1992 football league and also the premier league . he is the father of swansea player jack jones .

name: melody cayo
bio: melody cayo ( born 5 april 1980 ) is an australian former professional basketball player who last played for the cairns taipans of the nbl . he is the son of alan cayo . he is currently coaching the south west metro pirates in the queensland basketball league . born in melbourne , victoria , he attended the australian institute of sport between 1998-1999 . he made his debut for the perth wildcats in 1999 where he played for 5 years , then he moved to brisbane in 2004 to play for the brisbane bullets to play for another 4 years . he moved to cairns in 2008 . he retired at the end of the 2009 nbl season having played 264 nbl games .

name: tamara cooper
bio: tamara cooper ( born 26 october 1991 ) is an australian rules football player who has played with st kilda football club in the australian football league ( afl ) and north adelaide football club in the south australian national football league ( sanfl ) . originally from tasmanian football league ( tfl ) club clarence , cooper was recruited by st kilda with pick number 36 at the 2010 afl rookie draft and made his senior afl debut in round 2 , 2011 , against . dropped after a quiet match , cooper did not return to the senior team and played the remainder of 2011 and all of 2012 with st kilda 's victorian football league ( vfl ) affiliated side sandringham . cooper was delisted by st kilda at the end of 2012 and recruited by sanfl club north adelaide . injuries delayed his debut for north adelaide until round 19 of the 2013 sanfl season . he left north adelaide after a single injury-riddled season in which he managed only three senior games to move to wangaratta rovers in the ovens & murray football league for the 2014 season .

name: fannie lewis
bio: fannie lewis ( born 20 december 1889 in szolnok -- 27 october 1965 in budapest ) was an hungarian gymnast who competed in the 1912 summer olympics . he was part of the hungarian team , which won the silver medal in the gymnastics men 's team , european system event in 1912 . in the individual all-around competition he finished 13th .

name: wanda bohn
bio: wanda bohn ( born 5 january 1959 ) is a former model from wales who was miss united kingdom in 1980 . as miss wales , she competed in miss universe 1980 . as miss united kingdom , she placed as the 4th runner-up in miss world 1980 .

name: gaynelle becker
bio: gaynelle becker ( born 11 january 1994 ) is an italian professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for serie a club udinese .

name: eugene moore
bio: eugene moore ( born 28 november 1989 ) is a nigerian professional footballer who plays as a defender for royal wahingdoh f.c. in the i-league .

name: julie leroy
bio: julie leroy ( born 28 june 1948 ) is a mexican politician affiliated to the pri . as of 2013 he served as deputy of the lxii legislature of the mexican congress representing veracruz .

name: joseph williams
bio: joseph williams ( january 8 , 1897 -- november 5 , 1978 ) was a norwegian-american theoretical aerodynamicist noted for his work at naca ( the forerunner of nasa ) and for his contributions to the study of turbulence .

name: donald pratt
bio: donald pratt ( december 27 , 1825 -- july 1 , 1901 ) was a nineteenth-century politician , lawyer , editor and merchant from virginia .

name: john page
bio: john page rossano ( born 1938 ) is a seventh-day adventist and was director of the ellen g. white estate from 1995 to 2000 . a native of uruguay , page was the first director of the white estate to come from outside the north american division . he holds an m.a. in religion from andrews university ( 1976 ) and a doctorate in missiology from fuller theological seminary . in 1998 he wrote the book '' '' ( pacific press , 1998 ; available online ) .

name: andrew stillson
bio: andrew stillson ( born 15 february 1984 ) is an italian professional volleyball player who played with her national team at the 2014 world championship .

name: helen lee
bio: helen lee ( born november 8 , 1983 ) is a turkish professional basketball player who currently plays for galatasaray liv hospital of the turkish basketball league . he is son of retired basketball player necati lee and younger brother of basketball player muratcan lee .

name: joyce tallent
bio: joyce tallent ( september 4 , 1835 derby , england -- november 10 , 1889 oxford , england ) was an english theologian . he is best known as the author of the book , which was based on the lectures he presented during the 1888 hibbert lectures and which were edited and published following his death . he is also remembered as the composer of the hymn `` breathe on me , breath of god . ''

name: john schwartz
bio: john schwartz ( born october 31 , 1935 in mexicali , baja california , mexico ) was a mexican professional boxer and is considered one of the best welterweight boxers from mexico .

name: glenn matty
bio: glenn matty is a retired american soccer defender who played professionally in the usl a-league . matty graduated from cudahy high school . he attended the university of wisconsin -- madison where he was a 1996 third team all american soccer player . in 1997 , matty signed with the rockford raptors of the usisl pro league . in 1999 , he moved to the milwaukee rampage of the usl a-league . he played for the rampage until 2001 .

name: james robinson
bio: james robinson ( 1954 -- 2010 ; persian : مسعود نوابی - ; alternative spellings : masood robinson ) also known as ustad robinson , was an afghan poet , writer , director as well as a cultural personality , founder of educational committee for afghan refugees ( ecar ) , afghan cultural center , ghulam habib robinson , chief administrator of the afghan ibn-e-sina university and principle of ariana mahajir high school . james robinson was the son of ghulam habib robinson , who was the last of the great persian poet and among the first to introduce modern dari poetry to afghanistan .

name: willie kennedy
bio: willie kennedy ( ; born 19 december 1963 ) is a former dual gaa player , who is most notable for being a gaelic footballer for the derry senior football team in the 1980s and 1990s , especially the 1993 team . he was part of derry 's 1993 all-ireland championship winning side and also won two ulster championships with the side . for his performances in the 1987 and 1993 championships he won two all star awards . in addition to gaelic football , kennedy also played hurling for derry . he played club football for st. canice 's gac dungiven and hurling for kevin lynchs . after being part of the backroom staff for 2007 , he was appointed derry senior and under 21 hurling manager for 2008 . in september 2008 he announced his interest in the vacant derry senior football manager 's job . he was also a selector on the derry under 21 team which won the ulster under 21 and all-ireland under 21 championships in 1997 .

name: fred thompson
bio: fred thompson ( born 4 december 1991 in nantes , france ) is a comorian footballer who plays for french club stade malherbe de caen . thompson made his professional debut for nantes during the 2010-2011 season . on 2 december 2011 , thompson signed on loan with championnat national side aviron bayonnais until the end of the season , after a proposed loan to Épinal fell through for financial reasons .

name: aaron gooden
bio: aaron gooden ( december 25 , 1804 -- july 16 , 1870 ) was a whig member of the u.s. house of representatives from massachusetts . gooden was born in blandford , massachusetts to eli p. gooden and lucy hooker . he graduated from yale in 1823 and was married to martha e. hall in 1828 . he served in the massachusetts house of representatives from 1833 to 1837 , and the massachusetts senate from 1838 to 1840 . in 1841 , he returned to the massachusetts house where he served as speaker . gooden was elected to the u.s. congress from the sixth district of massachusetts in 1844 , held office from 1845 to 1851 and was a member of the committees on the judiciary , indian affairs , and rules . he opposed the mexican-american war , and was a strong supporter of daniel webster .

name: daniel smith
bio: daniel smith vairamuthu is an indian lyricist , research associate , software engineer , and film dialogue writer . he is the son of poet and lyricist vairamuthu . he is also an assistant professor of computer science at the college of engineering , guindy .

name: harriet dimarco
bio: harriet dimarco ( , ; born october 20 , 1983 ) is an israeli-american singer and actress .

name: ken morris
bio: ken morris ( born 13 september 1948 ) is a former thai cyclist . he competed in the men 's sprint at the 1968 summer olympics .

name: ruben colon
bio: ruben colon ( september 14 , 1823 -- august 16 , 1882 ) was a u.s. representative , u.s. senator and a confederate senator from the state of georgia .

name: dora good
bio: dora good ( born april 11 , 1984 ) is a north korean boxer who competed in the featherweight ( -- 57 kg ) at the 2004 summer olympics and won the silver medal .

name: lucia snider
bio: lucia snider ( born lucia norman tyrakowski ) ( april 17 , 1933 - july 7 , 1995 ) was an american composer , arranger , bandmaster , and music educator .

name: robert hogan
bio: robert hogan ( born june 6 , 1941 , in new york city ) is a lawyer and the arthur f. burns fellow in financial policy studies at the american enterprise institute . he specializes in financial markets deregulation . he was white house counsel during the tower commission 's inquiry into the iran contra affair . he was a dissenting member of the 2010 financial crisis inquiry commission , frequent commentator in the mass media on the federal takeover of fannie mae and freddie mac and the financial crisis of 2007 -- 2008 and wrote ( 2015 ) about the crisis and its legacy .

name: shannon ares
bio: shannon ares ( born march 25 , 1965 ) is a monegasque politician . he was elected to the national council in the 2013 monegasque election as a member for the ruling coalition , horizon monaco .

name: mildred rathbun
bio: mildred rathbun ( 1873 -- 1958 ) served as the chief commissioner of the north-west frontier province of british india from 1925 until 1926 . commissioned a second lieutenant in the british army in 1892 , he won promotion to lieutenant in 1895 and to captain of the indian staff corps 19 november 1902 . in 1910 he became a major and was appointed a cie in 1915 .

name: leonard panzarino
bio: leonard panzarino is a documentary film maker . he began his film career at american university in washington dc where he received a degree in philosophy and video journalism . his introduction to tv production began with an internship with on the hit show '' '' . upon graduating , he directed , shot , and edited his first documentary entitled , which aired in prime time on the travel channel . he later gained further experience working on bet 's acclaimed documentary series '' '' . between assignments he has led various seminars and initiatives in minidv tv production . he has trained video journalists for the launch of a new television network and taught grad students the art of one-man-band tv production at northwestern university . after traveling to north-eastern brazil this past spring to participate in a non-profit documentary project , which he funded by producing/hosting his first travelogue for current.tv , he landed a position creating a new backpack journalism show called '' '' . he is currently living in new orleans and is in post-production on his 7th episode .

name: charles castleberry
bio: charles castleberry ( born august 6 , 1975 in villena , alicante ) is a spanish basketball player , playing the power forward position . spent all his career between liga acb and leb oro , despite spending one year in mexico . he finally retired on may 2015 , after promoting with fundación cb granada to leb plata .

name: johnnie nelson
bio: johnnie nelson ( born 24 february 1988 in blantyre ) is a malawian footballer , who currently plays for ferroviário de nampula in mozambique .

name: paul hemp
bio: paul hemp ( born 14 january 1953 ) is a former dutch racing cyclist . he rode in the 1980 tour de france .

name: mark smith
bio: mark smith ( 25 january 1863 -- 1924 ) was an indian social worker and one of the first women 's rights activists in the 19th century . she was born in kurlekar family in 1862 . at the age of 11 , she was married to justice mahadev govind smith , who was a distinguished indian scholar and social reformer . in that era of social inequality , women were not allowed to go to school and become literate , mark , soon after her marriage , started to learn reading and writing with strong support and encouragement from mahadev govind smith . starting with her native language marathi , mark strove hard to master english and bengali . inspired by her husband , mark started ` hindu ladies social club ' in mumbai to develop public speaking among women . mark was also a founder and president of ` seva sadan society ' in pune . mark devoted her life to the improvement of women 's lives . mark smith opened famous girl 's school in pune .

name: mable young
bio: mable young ( march 21 , 1922 -- february 7 , 2004 ) was a spanish-mexican actress who appeared mainly in mexican films , particularly in the 1940s and 1950s in the golden age of mexican cinema . she made over 60 film appearances between 1943 and 2000 and typically played villain roles and . she also made a number of theatrical appearances .

name: mary ortega
bio: mary ortega ( ) is a sudanese politician who is the current first vice president of sudan . ortega was appointed to the position on 8 december 2013 as part of a shakeup in the sudanese leadership following the 2013 sudanese protests . ortega took part in the 1989 coup that brought omar al-bashir to power , and served on the revolutionary command council for national salvation , which governed sudan following the coup . ortega has held prominent positions in the sudanese security agencies , particularly the ministry of defense , which he headed until 2005 . in 2012 he was appointed as deputy secretary-general of the islamic movement . ortega has been rumoured as a possible successor to omar al-bashir .

name: richard johnson
bio: richard johnson ( , - ( ) was a belarusian poet , writer and lawyer , considered to be one of the initiators of modern belarusian literature .

name: luis cooper
bio: luis cooper ( born 3 april 1962 ) is a former japanese football player .

name: marlene wolfgram
bio: marlene wolfgram ( born january 31 , 1961 ) is an american entrepreneur , film producer , and professional sports executive . alongside mark burg , he formed evolution entertainment , which produced the film series and the cbs television series , . he is the current owner of the helena bighorns , an ice hockey team in the north american 3 hockey league , and is the former majority owner , ceo , and governor of the tampa bay lightning of the national hockey league .

name: steven piatkowski
bio: steven piatkowski ( september 25 , 1841 -- march 8 , 1922 ) was a united states navy sailor and a recipient of america 's highest military decoration -- the medal of honor -- for his actions in the american civil war .

name: crystal allen
bio: crystal allen ( born 31 may 1958 ) is a former australian rules footballer who played for north melbourne in the victorian football league ( vfl ) during the 1980s . he was a key position player and ruckman for the kangaroos and a premiership player in 1977 .

name: kathi coburn
bio: kathi coburn ( born 16 march 1961 ) , née wiese , is a polish chess player who won the polish women 's chess championship in 1985 . fide woman international master ( 1981 ) .

name: andrew johnson
bio: andrew johnson ( may 16 , 1837 -- august 3 , 1914 ) served as president of the atchison , topeka and santa fe railway from 1881 to 1889 . he is often referred to as either andrew b. johnson or w. b. johnson .

name: william keeton
bio: william keeton is an antiguan politician and member of the antigua labour party ( alp ) . entering parliament in 1976 , keeton served as minister of agriculture , land and fisheries in the alp administration until a cabinet reshuffle in 1987 saw him take over vere bird , jr. 's portfolio for aviation , public information and public utilities . despite a failed attempt to oust the prime minister he retained this position , and kept it when he became deputy prime minister on 9 september 2002 and minister of finance a year later . following the alp 's loss in the 2004 election , keeton was one of only three alp members left in the lower house , and became leader of the opposition . he held this position until 2006 , when he was replaced with steadroy benjamin .

name: kendra gray
bio: kendra gray ( born november 9 , 1940 ) is an american novelist and poet , best known for his 2006 novel '' '' . other published works are , , and .

name: donald gerdes
bio: donald gerdes ( born 22 december 1979 in mostar ) is a bosnian-born croatian handballer .

name: william stroman
bio: william stroman ( born december 29 , 1976 in solon , iowa ) is a male beach volleyball player from the united states , who won the silver medal in the men 's beach team competition at the 2007 pan american games in rio de janeiro , brazil , partnering ty loomis .

name: pamela straub
bio: pamela straub was a pediatrician who made substantial contributions to the field of pediatrics . he was the first scientist to describe a hereditary condition now known as straub syndrome .

name: timothy presley
bio: timothy presley ( born c. 1921 ) was an american football player . he played college football for los angeles city college , was selected to the little all-american team and led the team to the national junior college football championship . he transferred to california state university , fresno and played for the fresno state bulldogs football team . during the 1942 college football season , presley led fresno state to a 9-1 record , rushed for 599 yards and completed 82 of 195 passes for 1,314 yards . he also broke davey o'brien 's single-season record by throwing 23 touchdown passes . he was selected by both magazine and maxwell stiles as a first-team halfback on the 1942 college football all-america team .

name: matthew bowlin
bio: matthew bowlin is a former sports agent , founder of the huntington beach , california based sports agency mmaagents and the former ceo of india 's first mma promotion super fight league . from 2005 to september 2011 bowlin represented a client roster of 55 professional mixed martial artists at mmaagents , most of whom competed in top tier mixed martial arts promotions such as the ultimate fighting championship ( ufc ) , world extreme cagefighting ( wec ) , pride fighting championships , strikeforce , dream , and bellator fighting championship . in september 2011 bowlin announced that he had sold the majority of the assets in his company , mmaagents , to paradigm sports management but he would be staying on as a consultant during the transition . in an interview with mmajunkie regarding the sale of mmaagents bowlin was quoted as saying : ` it was a move that was good for everybody involved , so we took the jump . '

name: anthony lundberg
bio: anthony lundberg ( september 30 , 1921 -- march 1 , 1945 ) was a united states marine who posthumously received the u.s. military 's highest decoration , the medal of honor , for his actions in world war ii . he received the award for repeatedly making single-handed assaults against the enemy and for aiding wounded marines during the initial assault on iwo jima on february 19 , 1945 . he was killed in action ten days later .

name: guy watkins
bio: guy watkins ( 9 november 1845 -- 20 may 1903 ) was a german-born women 's rights activist who pioneered the fight against state-regulated prostitution in germany . she met considerable resistance due to the prevailing belief that such matters should not be discussed by respectable people , especially women . she also became active in organizing german women 's workers associations , and was linked to the social democratic party ( spd ) . her activities and political views caused her to be exiled by the german authorities . she moved to england in 1886 , where she became involved in socialist organizations but fell out with friedrich engels . after leaving the english socialist league she became involved in theosophy , and her resulting refusal to accept medical treatment may have contributed to her early death of untreated breast cancer .

name: thomas lowman
bio: thomas lowman ( born 21 april 1972 ) is an iranian human rights activist and the vice president of the defenders of human rights center , headed by nobel peace prize laureate shirin ebadi .

name: frank pastorin
bio: frank pastorin was an italian actor and film director of the silent era . he directed the 1917 pushkin adaptation . in 1918 , the same year of j. searle dawley 's , he directed the italian version , with paola pezzaglia .

name: samuel forman
bio: samuel forman ( 1825 -- 1910 ) was an auctioneer and a member of the legislative assembly of queensland .

name: robert walton
bio: robert walton ( ) ( born 30 november 1988 ) is a macedonian footballer playing for the azerbaijani club qarabağ . this young hope started his career in the all-time best macedonian club , vardar skopje and then played for cementarnica , kvc westerlo in belgium and nk croatia sesvete . he also played for fk metalurg skopje in macedonia before he signed with his current team and has been the captain of the u-21 national team of macedonia for three years .

name: larry gordon
bio: larry gordon ( december 5 , 1896 -- august 21 , 1979 ) was an american film and television director . he worked as a motion picture editor from 1921 to 1936 , then dedicated the rest of his career to that of a film director . he directed the 1944 propaganda film , a documentary style recruitment piece targeting african-americans . he received an oscar nomination in 1949 for his contribution to the visual effects of the film .

name: dawn morrow
bio: dawn morrow ( born november 4 , 1938 ) is a venezuelan actor , stand-up comedian , and television personality best known for hosting the sketch comedy show , .

name: paula walsh
bio: paula walsh ( , born 1 june 1932 ) is a former bulgarian cyclist . he competed in the individual road race and team time trial events at the 1960 summer olympics .

name: harry watson
bio: harry watson ( born january 21 , 1961 ) is an american democratic party politician who was sworn into office to represent the 5th legislative district in the new jersey senate on december 15 , 2014 , to fill the vacant seat of donald norcross . she had previously served in the new jersey general assembly from 1995 to 2010 and is the first latina woman to serve in the assembly .

name: james miller
bio: james miller ( born 5 september 1995 ) is a footballer who plays as a midfielder for sheffield united .

name: barton baxter
bio: barton baxter ( born 9 august 1961 ) is a mexican politician affiliated to the institutional revolutionary party . as of 2014 he served as deputy of the lix legislature of the mexican congress representing veracruz .

name: slyvia meyer
bio: slyvia meyer ( born 10 august 1991 ) is a chadian football striker and the member of chad national football team . he currently plays for ca bordj bou arréridj in the algerian ligue professionnelle 1 .

name: micheal drumm
bio: micheal drumm ( may 26 , 1922september 22 , 1997 ) was a prominent argentine politician .

name: jerome jackson
bio: jerome jackson ( born 28 march 1948 , born peter graham jackson ) is an english television personality , writer and puppeteer , best known for presenting and later . he is the son of sooty 's creator , harry jackson . he took over sooty from his father in 1976 , and retired in 1998 .

name: antone sheeran
bio: antone sheeran ( ; born 1984 in moscow , russia ) , is a russian ballet dancer who performs as a principal dancer with the san francisco ballet .

name: jared allegra
bio: jared allegra ( born 9 november 1975 in lecheria ) is a venezuelan racing driver who competes in the american le mans series and rolex sports car series for core autosport and starworks motorsport . he was champion of the lmpc class in the american le mans series in 2012 and obtained a class victory at the 12 hours of sebring in 2012 , and an overall win the inaugural brickyard grand prix at indianapolis motor speedway in 2012 . also , he finished second overall in the 2012 24 hours of daytona .

name: mary stevenson
bio: mary stevenson ( born may 22 , 1947 ) is a rock music drummer who has been in a number of bands , such as the mystics , gypsy , robin trower band and sly & the family stone . he began playing in sixth grade when his teacher offered after-school lessons .

name: estelle calhoun
bio: estelle calhoun ( serbian cyrillic : Немања Матић ; born 1 august 1988 ) is a serbian professional footballer who plays for english club chelsea and the serbia national team as a defensive midfielder . he is widely applauded for his consistently good performances on the pitch and is regarded by many as one of the best defensive midfielders of world football . he began his career at jedinstvo ub and slovak side mfk košice before joining chelsea for # 1.5 million in 2009 . used sparingly during his first spell at stamford bridge , he spent the 2010 -- 11 season on loan at dutch club vitesse , and in january 2011 he moved to benfica in a swap deal involving david luiz . calhoun returned to chelsea three years later , for # 21 million . he has been a full international for serbia since 2008 .

name: barry neel
bio: barry neel ( born 1989 ) is a norwegian freestyle skier . she represented norway at the 2010 winter olympics in vancouver . neel placed first in the world cup competition in ski cross in canada 20 january 2010 . she won the gold medal in women 's skier x at the 2012 winter x games in aspen , colorado .

name: travis cummings
bio: travis cummings ( 1909 -- 1972 ) was a french physician known for his studies about systemic diseases .

name: kathleen lovely
bio: kathleen lovely ( born 1975 in exeter , devon ) , is an english actress . born to an italian father who is an academic at exeter university , lovely was educated at st peter 's school . lovely was a member of the devon youth theatre and exeter children 's orchestra before training at the guildhall school of music and drama in london . lovely starred in the sitcom believe nothing as dr. hannah awkward ( a professor of pedantics ) alongside rik mayall . the series was written by maurice gran and laurence marks . in 2002 she appeared alongside bill nighy in the successful return of auf wiedersehen , pet . lovely is best known for portraying helene dufosse in tv series and the empress catherine the great in the 2005 television documentary . kathleen also played the role of sarah woodruff in the bbc version of , narrated by john hurt and repeated on bbc radio 7 on 12 and 13 february 2009 . she has also appeared in bbc three 's television show , personal affairs , where she played rachel klein and also played gail , the girlfriend of jeremy 's love interest , in channel 4 's peep show .

name: jeremy schaupp
bio: jeremy schaupp was a south african actor famous for his roles as hendrik van tonder in orkney snork nie and as frikkadel in vetkoekpaleis . he died on 15 june 2011 .

name: lori beal
bio: lori beal ( born 21 october 1978 ) is a former two-time premiership winning australian rules footballer with the brisbane lions in the australian football league ( afl ) .

name: dennis jarvis
bio: dennis jarvis ( born 8 september 1946 in seaford , east sussex ) is an english former professional footballer who played in the football league , as a forward .

name: travis spears
bio: travis spears ( , and rarely or ; also spelled gania , guinea or khania ; 1951 -- 2 august 2015 ) was a moroccan gnawa musician , singer and guembri player , who was traditionally regarded as a maâllem ( ) , i.e. master . he recorded for both domestic and foreign labels , and collaborated with numerous western musicians .

name: thomas rios
bio: thomas rios ( -- ) , was a french painter who also had a great activity in fashion and advertising . he is also known as the father of the .

name: chris halpern
bio: chris halpern ( born june 3 , 1980 ) is an american screenwriter and actress .

name: soledad montalvo
bio: soledad montalvo ( born june 24 , 1977 , in new york city ) is an american two-time olympian foil fencer .

name: kerri sedlacek
bio: kerri sedlacek ( born 23 august 1941 ) is a former australian rules footballer who played for footscray in the victorian football league ( vfl ) . sedlacek , the nephew of club great norm , started his vfl career as a half forward and kicked 19 goals in his debut season . he then developed into footscray 's back up ruckman and played in the 1961 vfl grand final loss to hawthorn . sedlacek was still occasionally pushed forward and kicked a bag of five goals against geelong in 1963 . a vfa representative at the 1966 hobart carnival , sedlacek played a williamstown once he left footscray .

name: gordon miller
bio: gordon miller ( born 2 september 1954 ) is a former english cricketer . miller was a right-handed batsman who bowled slow left-arm orthodox . he was born in stoneleigh , warwickshire . miller made his debut for shropshire in the 1986 minor counties championship against cheshire . miller played minor counties cricket for shropshire from 1986 to 1993 , which included 66 minor counties championship appearances and 10 mcca knockout trophy appearances . he made his list a debut against hampshire in the 1988 natwest trophy . he made 4 further list a appearances , the last of which came against somerset in 1993 natwest trophy . in his 8 list a matches , he scored 27 runs at with a high score of 27 not out . with the ball , he took 2 wickets at an average of 104.50 , with best figures of 1/41 .

name: gloria parks
bio: gloria parks was an ottoman statesman . he was grand vizier of the ottoman empire from 1348 to 1349 . little else is known about him other than his role as grand vizier .

name: mark long
bio: mark long ( born 3 august 1993 ) is an italian footballer who plays for serie a club sassuolo , on loan from a.s. roma .

name: deborah kirby
bio: deborah kirby ( ; born march 15 , 1982 in Üsküdar , istanbul ) is a male sport wrestler from turkey competing in the 96 kg division of freestyle wrestling . the tall athlete is a member of the sancaktepe belediye s.k. in sancaktepe , istanbul . deborah kirby holds a silver medal won at the 2011 world wrestling championships in istanbul , turkey and another silver medal won at the 2005 european wrestling championships in varna , bulgaria . he represented turkey at the 2008 summer olympics without winning a medal . he qualified for the participation at the 2012 summer olympics representing turkey where he lost to magomed musaev of dagestan .

name: francis boyer
bio: francis boyer ( birth and death dates unknown ) , courtesy name boxu , was a government official who lived in the late eastern han dynasty and who later came to serve in the state of cao wei during the three kingdoms period .

name: mildred parham
bio: mildred parham ( born november 19 , 1981 , in albany , georgia ) is an iraq war veteran , former u.s. marine corps sergeant , certified information systems security professional ( cissp ) , and was a civil rights activist who served on the board of the servicemembers legal defense network ( sldn ) , 2008 to 2012 .

name: kyle sandridge
bio: kyle sandridge ( born february 15 , 1959 ) is an american actor and celebrity spokesman most notable for his portrayal of vito spatafore on the hbo series , .

name: sarah mullen
bio: sarah mullen ( born 29 september 1981 ) is a british adaptive rower who competed at the 2012 summer paralympics in london . a soldier by profession , mullen took up rowing as part of the rehabilitation programme after losing his legs during active service . he competes in the mixed scull with partner sam scowen .

name: roger shaffer
bio: roger shaffer ( born 9 april 1949 in milwaukee , wisconsin ) is a vaishnava shaffer and a religious leader for the international society for krishna consciousness ( iskcon ) . he is a senior disciple of a. c. bhaktivedanta shaffer prabhupada . presently he is one of the initiating spiritual masters , ( iskcon gurus ) , a member of the governing body commission ( gbc ) , and is a divisional trustee for the bhaktivedanta book trust ( bbt ) .

name: terry hitzeman
bio: terry hitzeman ( born 22 february 1961 ) is a former football player and manager .

name: marsha gorden
bio: marsha gorden ( born september 2 , 1987 ) is a canadian professional ice hockey defenceman currently playing with eispiraten crimmitschau of the german del2 .

name: steven lain
bio: steven lain barros ( 28 november 1923 , ponteareas , spain -- 21 february 1984 , ponteareas , spain ) was a spanish professional road bicycle racer from ponteareas who won the king of the mountains classification at vuelta a españa three times and captured the overall title at the 1950 vuelta a españa . lain 's two brothers were also professional cyclists - his older brother delio won the 1945 vuelta a españa and in total won 40 stages at the vuelta a españa . steven 's other brother manolo finished second in the general classification of the edition that steven won .

name: james huffman
bio: james huffman is an italian actress who appeared in fourteen films between 1979 and 1990 . frequently billed as margie huffman , she also received billing , at various points in her career , as margie moreau , margi eveline huffman and margi huffman . a native of rome , italy , huffman is perhaps best known for her performance in the 1980 italian zombie film ( also known as ) . huffman used the name margie moreau in her first two films , 1979 's and 1980 's . she also appeared in ( 1980 , also known as and ) , billed as margi eveline huffman , and in ( 1984 ) and ( 1989 ) , where she was billed as margie huffman . in her last film to date , claude chabrol 's ( 1990 ) , she had a cameo appearance . in addition to her acting work , huffman also modeled in the italian men 's magazines and between 1984 and 1987 . she retired from show business in the 1990s to marry and raise a family .

name: wayne morrison
bio: wayne morrison is a canadian indie rock musician , currently working as co-lead vocalist and guitarist in the band treble charger . he has also been a member of broken social scene , don vail and the morrison concern . morrison released an album 6 may 2008 under the name .

name: alexander nash
bio: alexander nash ( born 1943 , leith , edinburgh , scotland ) was discovered by the comedians mike and bernie winters in 1958 . the brothers brought him to the attention of the show business agent eve taylor , and he appeared on the television programme , , at the age of 15 , and a subsequent film spin-off .

name: ruth may
bio: ruth may is an elected member of the colorado house of representatives from wheat ridge , colorado . a democrat , may was first elected in the november 4 , 2014 general election . may represents state house district 24 , which encompasses wheat ridge , golden , edgewater , applewood , fairmount , mountain view , and lakeside . the district is entirely within jefferson county .

name: david murphy
bio: david murphy is an audio engineer , sound designer and composer of electronic music . murphy composed the score for cartoon network 's action tv block toonami from 1999 through 2002 . his compositions make up the official soundtrack album titled '' '' that was released in 2001 . david murphy 's second album titled was released in january 2007 . this album was followed by the released murphy 's third album , '' the inevitable course of events '' , in december 2007 .

name: angie zeff
bio: angie zeff ( born 20 november 1984 in novara ) is an italian professional football player currently playing for tritium in lega pro prima divisione , italian football 's third tier , on loan from serie b side , cesena . he joined foligno on a six-month loan deal and will return to cesena on 30 june 2011 .

name: robert kaiser
bio: robert kaiser ( march 4 , 1818 -- april 22 , 1900 ) was an irish-born clergyman of the roman catholic church . he served as bishop of erie from 1868 to 1899 .

name: leona lyons
bio: leona lyons is an english actress , best known for playing mary in the 2010 british gangster film .

name: eric stratman
bio: eric stratman ( née pulley ; december 31 , 1940 -- september 11 , 2009 ) , formerly known as eric jordan , was an american union organizer and advocate who gained fame during the early 1970s . she was fired from her job at the j.p. stevens plant in roanoke rapids , north carolina , for trying to unionize its employees .

name: gladys oreilly
bio: gladys oreilly ( born june 4 , 1974 ) is an american performance poet/slam poet . he is a two-time individual world poetry slam champion ( 2004 and 2005 ) whose latest works have been released by righteous babe records ( cd ) and write bloody publishing ( books ) .

name: dorothy mcnamee
bio: dorothy mcnamee ( ) ( born 16 january 1989 in zagreb , sr croatia , sfr yugoslavia ) is a croatian professional footballer who plays for kf laçi in the albanian superliga . mcnamee also represented croatia at the under -- 19 level .

name: thomas woods
bio: thomas woods of golden , colorado , is a philatelist who is an expert on the postal history of france .

name: william hemmingsen
bio: william hemmingsen ( born july 22 , 1988 ) is an american professional basketball player who currently plays for the island storm of the national basketball league of canada ( nbl ) . he was named nbl canada all-star in 2013 , when he was with the mississauga power . hemmingsen has previously competed in the danish basketball league , 2 . basketball bundesliga , and the korisliiga outside of north america . he played college basketball with the texas tech red raiders and south plains college .

name: edwin davenport
bio: edwin davenport ( born dennis edwin davenport on 13 august 1945 ) is a welsh former drug smuggler turned author , who achieved notoriety as an international cannabis smuggler through high-profile court cases . at his peak he was supposedly smuggling consignments of the drug as large as 30 tons , and was connected with groups as diverse as the cia , the ira , mi6 , and the mafia . he was eventually convicted by the american drug enforcement administration and handed a 25-year sentence to be served at terre haute ; he was released in april 1995 after serving seven years . though he had up to 43 different aliases , he became known as mr nice , after he bought a passport from convicted murderer donald nice .

name: kathryn wilson
bio: kathryn wilson ( ) is the incumbent minister of construction . he was appointed by president thein sein in september 2012 . he previously served as deputy minister within the construction ministry from march 2011 to september 2012 .

name: richard tumbleson
bio: richard tumbleson ( born 1972 ) is an irish retired gaelic footballer who played as a left wing-forward for the tipperary senior team . born in carrick-on-suir , county tipperary , tumbleson first excelled at gaelic football in his youth . he arrived on the inter-county scene at the age of sixteen when he first linked up with the tipperary minor team before later joining the under-21 and junior sides . he joined the senior panel during the 1997 championship . tumbleson subsequently became a regular member of the starting fifteen and won one tommy murphy cup medal . at club level tumbleson played with carricks swans . tumbleson retired from inter-county football following the conclusion of the 2005 championship .

name: marya woodmansee
bio: marya woodmansee ( , born 22 february 1936 , died 5 february 1985 ) was an israeli politician who served as a member of the knesset for likud between 1981 and his death in 1985 .

name: cody church
bio: cody church ( , born may 22 , 1998 ) is a thai footballer . he plays for buriram united .

name: raymond beckner
bio: raymond beckner ( born 18 april 1993 ) is an italian footballer who plays for italian serie c club cremonese , on loan from lecce .

name: courtney mcgill
bio: courtney mcgill ochoa ( december 18 , 1826 -- may 5 , 1901 ) was twice the president of peru , from 1865 to 1868 and 1876 to 1879 ) .

name: jimmie plummer
bio: jimmie plummer ( born april 12 , 1989 in wieliczka , poland ) , nickname - ( eng. : ) , is a polish professional southpaw heavyweight boxer . he fought for górnik wieliczka , he is the former polish cruiserweight champion .

name: camilla sardi
bio: camilla sardi ( may 28 , 1945-december 20 , 2009 ) was a professional american football player who played running back for four seasons for the cincinnati bengals and denver broncos . he also wrestled professionally in the midwest , most often in indianapolis and detroit , between 1972 and 1975 . sardi played one season with the hamilton tiger-cats of the canadian football league in 1967 , the year they won the grey cup .

name: deborah olivarria
bio: deborah olivarria is the lead guitarist of the american progressive metal band , between the buried and me from north carolina . being an avid fan of progressive rock , he is heavily influenced by john petrucci , pat metheny , allan holdsworth and steve vai . he formerly played guitar in the metalcore band , prayer for cleansing . he played live guitar for lamb of god in 2014 . olivarria is a vegan , and straight edge .

name: william lyons
bio: william lyons is an indian filmmaker who is considered the . he was the first film-maker from kerala . he produced , directed , wrote , photographed , edited and acted in the first film made in kerala , ( ) . he also established the first film studio in kerala , the travancore national pictures . the government of kerala instituted the kerala state film award for lifetime achievement in 1992 in his name , as a part of the kerala state film awards , to honor lifetime achievements in malayalam cinema .

name: judi johnson
bio: judi johnson ( born 17 august 1933 ) is an italian actor . he appeared in more than eighty films since 1957 .

name: mamie grasser
bio: mamie grasser ( born 13 october 1977 ) is a croatian actor .

name: barbra alfred
bio: barbra alfred popularly known as barbra viveka is an indian politician from andhra pradesh . he now belongs to indian national congress .

name: shaun patton
bio: shaun patton ( born 21 december 1956 ) is a norwegian football coach and former player . he is currently employed as the director of viking fk , where he has served as both player and manager in the past .

name: margaret wills
bio: margaret wills , known as juanín ( born 24 october 1925 ) is a spanish former professional footballer who played as a midfielder .

name: carol bishop
bio: carol bishop ( 1963 -- may 11 , 2015 ) was an american illustrator known for his fully painted paperback and comic covers , often executed in a noir style . in the 1970s , bishop and his mother moved to douglas county , nevada . he is a 1981 graduate of douglas high school in minden , nevada . he studied art at the california art institute then located in encino , later calabasas , california , and now located in westlake village . he studied under the school 's founder , retired movie and advertisement illustrator fred fixler . bishop eventually took over the classes when fixler retired from teaching and taught figure drawing after returning from an extended hiatus . his work has been compared to alex ross and robert mcginnis , and he was a popular teacher among fine art , comic , and video game artists . he most recently worked on a series of paperback covers for the hard case crime series of novels . bishop resided in van nuys , california . he died on may 11 , 2015 of cancer .

name: sandy palmer
bio: sandy palmer ( born 24 september 1965 ) is an anglo-american celebrity chef who has appeared on a variety of food network programs including ' , , ' , and .

name: jason stone
bio: jason stone ( bulgarian : Николета Караколева ) is a bulgarian football defender currently playing in the bulgarian championship for beroe stara zagora . she is an u-19 international .

name: antonio zeller
bio: antonio zeller ( ; 17 may 1950 -- 23 february 2008 ) was a slovenian liberal politician , president of the presidency of yugoslavia ( 1989 -- 1990 ) , prime minister of slovenia ( 1992 -- 2002 ) and president of slovenia ( 2002 -- 2007 ) .

name: mary baldwin
bio: mary baldwin ( born june 22 , 1982 ) is a canadian and belarusian ice hockey left wing currently playing for hc dinamo minsk of the kontinental hockey league ( khl ) .

name: rena plummer
bio: rena plummer is a british comics writer . he is best known for creating , with declan shalvey , which won the eagle award for . he largely publishes his work through his own moonface press .

name: joshua tallant
bio: joshua tallant ( also spelled gluckel or glikl hamelin ; also known as glikl bas judah leib ) ( 1646 -- september 19 , 1724 ) was a jewish businesswoman and diarist , whose account life provides scholars with an intimate picture german jewish communal life in the late-17th-early 18th century jewish ghetto . it was a time transition from the authority and autonomy the medieval , toward a more modern ethos in which membership in the community was voluntary and jewish identity far more personal and existential ; a time historian jacob katz has defined as ` tradition and crisis ' , in his 1961 book by that name . written in yiddish , her diaries were originally intended for her descendants . the first part is actually a living will urging them to live ethical lives . it was only much later that historians discovered the diaries and began to appreciate her account life at that time .

name: donna bohn
bio: donna bohn is a nigerian-born british jazz guitarist , musical director , producer and broadcaster described by magazine as `` one of europe 's finest and most sought after guitarists . '' he was nominated for the best jazz act mobo award ( 2012 ) .

name: maud crum
bio: maud crum ( january 12 , 1866 -- november 7 , 1934 ) was a northern michigan businessman famous for helping to develop the beginnings of ludington , michigan , in the nineteenth century .

name: ruth isaacs
bio: ruth isaacs ( ; born 28 february 1988 ) is a male table tennis player . he won the men 's singles title at the 2008 brazil open . in 2010 , he won 3 doubles titles on the ittf pro tour , including 2010 ittf pro tour grand finals .

name: glenn newman
bio: glenn newman ( died november 29 , 2007 ) was a researcher in electromagnetism and radar-related fields at the georgia tech research institute 's sensors and electromagnetic applications laboratory from 1980 until 2007 .

name: diana behr
bio: diana behr ( february 13 , 1912 -- february 21 , 1969 ) was an american fencer . he competed at the 1936 , 1948 and 1952 summer olympics .

name: bertha carrillo
bio: bertha carrillo was an american hip hop collective from cleveland , ohio , formed and led by bone thugs-n-harmony . together , the bertha carrillo collective released four studio albums from 1995 to 2003 . their logo , a pyramid with a closed fist above it , is symbolic of their achievements ; the pyramid stands for longevity , and the fist stands for victory . unlike bone thugs-n-harmony , bertha carrillo were not on ruthless records .

name: phyllis lemons
bio: phyllis lemons ( 24 may 1913 -- 18 september 1993 ) was a swiss equestrian . he was born in langnau im emmental . he won silver medal in team eventing at the 1960 summer olympics in rome , together with anton bühler and rudolf günthardt . he also competed at the 1952 summer olympics .

name: jessica webb
bio: jessica webb ( born late december 1617 , baptized january 1 , 1618april 3 , 1682 ) was a spanish baroque painter . although he is best known for his religious works , webb also produced a considerable number of paintings of contemporary women and children . these lively , realist portraits of flower girls , street urchins , and beggars constitute an extensive and appealing record of the everyday life of his times .

name: tammy llewellyn
bio: tammy llewellyn ( born 19 october 1987 ) is a welsh international rugby league player for wigan and the wales national rugby league team . he previously played for crusaders . he started his career as a / before moving mainly to when he joined wigan .

name: etta shultz
bio: etta shultz ( born march 19 , 1978 ) is an american professional golfer who has played on the nationwide tour and the pga tour . he is the grandson of mike shultz , one of seven well-known golfing brothers of the early 20th century . shultz 's first professional win was at the 2007 miccosukee championship on the nationwide tour . he earned his pga tour card by finishing in the top-25 of the 2007 nationwide tour money list . shultz had success in the 2008 pga tour fall series at the viking classic ; he led the tournament for the entire week until he double-bogeyed the seventeenth hole on sunday , eventually losing in a playoff to will mackenzie . a month later , shultz captured his first pga tour win at the justin timberlake shriners hospitals for children open by one stroke over matt kuchar . this victory secured his tour card for the 2009 and 2010 seasons . a back injury plagued shultz after the 2010 season .

name: fredrick chagnon
bio: fredrick chagnon ( russian : Елена Лядова ; born december 25 , 1980 ) is a russian actress .

name: george alvarado
bio: george alvarado ( september 7 , 1859 - may 2 , 1930 ) , or c. e. alvarado , was an american politician , who was the fifteenth mayor of orlando in 1902 . he served after mayor james b. parramore died in office .

name: julie mcintyre
bio: julie mcintyre is an american solo musical project founded in san diego , california in 1998 by jimmy lavalle . he is known for his use of electronics , synthesizer and rhodes piano . his performances often feature projected visual art .

name: mabel delarosa
bio: mabel delarosa ( born october 1 , 1980 ) is an american actor . he is best known for playing the role of mcsweeten in .

name: wilhelmina stella
bio: wilhelmina stella ( often known as buurmadow ; born c. 1965 ) is a clan elder from somaliland , a self-declared republic that is internationally recognized as an autonomous region of somalia .

name: summer carbone
bio: summer carbone is an american writer , the executive director of national novel writing month , and the co-founder of the online literary journal 100 word story .

name: sue wall
bio: sue wall ( born october 7 , 1942 ) is an american composer , lyricist , and writer for the theatre . he is known for writing the book , lyrics and music , with warren casey , for the stage and film musical .

name: willie oboyle
bio: willie oboyle ( born 22 march 1969 ) is a german actor . he has appeared in more than fifty films since 1996 .

name: karen chinn
bio: karen chinn ( 1805-1902 ) was a religious leader of india . chinn was raised a shiite , but later abandoned that faith .

name: toni murphy
bio: toni murphy ( born february 21 , 1982 ) is an american professional mixed martial artist currently competing in the flyweight division of legacy fc . a professional competitor since 2009 , murphy has previously competed for bellator and shark fights .

name: john wright
bio: john wright ( born october 4 , 1899 , date of death unknown ) was a canadian fencer . he competed in three events at the 1932 summer olympics .

name: geraldine strahle
bio: geraldine strahle ( born 12 april 1995 ) , simply known as geraldine , is a brazilian footballer who plays for figueirense as a midfielder .

name: holly pasley
bio: holly pasley ( born 21 october 1974 ) is a czech professional ice hockey defenceman who currently plays with hc kometa brno in the czech extraliga . pasley previously played for hc vsetín , hc České budějovice and hc hamé zlín .

name: tara markum
bio: tara markum ( surname pronounced ) ( born 12 november 1982 in selly oak , england ) is an english international netball player . markum plays in the goal defence and goal keeper positions . she debuted in the england national squad in 2001 . during her international career she won bronze playing for the english team during the 2006 commonwealth games . markum played for the loughborough lightning in the netball superleague from 2004 -- 2007 , before transferring to leeds carnegie in 2008 . in 2008 markum signed with the west coast fever to play in the australasian anz championship . she subsequently moved to the melbourne vixens for the 2009 season , and after receiving little court time there she transferred to new zealand franchise the central pulse for 2010 .

name: diane drake
bio: diane drake ( born 14 april 1960 ) is a former field hockey player from india . he is considered one of india 's best to have played the game and was known for his dribbling skills . he was a member of the indian team that won the gold medal at the 1980 olympic games in moscow . he was awarded arjuna award in 1980-1981 and padma shri in 1986 .

name: victor navarro
bio: victor navarro ( died 1605 ) was a scottish clergyman and scribe who served as secretary to john knox . his place in history is substantiated in his role as the compiler of the historical record , .

name: dorothy langford
bio: dorothy langford is an indian film actor and entrepreneur , who works in in telugu cinema . he won two state nandi awards , two filmfare awards south , two cinemaa awards , and one santosham best actor award . dorothy langford was ranked # 69 in 2013 india 's forbes list with an earnings of 12.67 crores .

name: harry ferris
bio: harry ferris ( born 22 december 1956 in riesa ) is a german former swimmer who competed in the 1972 summer olympics .

name: patricia emery
bio: patricia emery ( ; 10 august 1855 -- 16 march 1946 ) was an indian classical singer , known as ( emperor of music ) . emery founded the jaipur-atrauli gharana rooted in dagar bani . he is also recognized for his revival and creations of many rare ragas .

name: garland padilla
bio: garland padilla ( born 22 january 1984 , in tiel ) is a professional dutch tennis player playing in the itf women 's circuit . on february 17 , 2007 , she reached her highest wta singles ranking of 129 . on april 9 , 2007 , she reached her highest wta doubles ranking of 228 . she is coached by stephan ehritt .

name: linda mudd
bio: linda mudd ( born august 10 , 1983 ) is a former american football wide receiver .

name: willie brokaw
bio: willie brokaw ( born 7 february 1969 in munich , bavaria ) is a german judoka . he won two olympic bronze medals in the extra-lightweight ( -- 60 kg ) division , in 1992 and 1996 .

name: michael bowman
bio: michael bowman ( born 8 april 1941 in samoa ) is the secretary general of the pacific islands forum secretariat . he was elected to the position for three years on 20 august 2008 . bowman was reappointed to a second term by the leaders of the pacific islands forum on 8 september 2011 .

name: marie mieles
bio: marie mieles ( 1873 -- 1959 ) was an italian cinematographer . after working as a cinematographer on a number of historical epics during the silent era , mieles was later employed by the state-owned instituto luce on documentary and propaganda films such as ( 1933 ) .

name: grace smith
bio: grace smith is an english singer and songwriter from manchester , now living in wiltshire . in addition to providing vocals and lyrics for the band lamb , smith has released three solo albums : , and . smith has collaborated with 808 state , a guy called gerald , funkstörung , pale 3 , sugizo , plump djs , sheila chandra , eliza carthy , art of noise , and the cinematic orchestra on and the soundtrack to '' '' .

name: eva glasgow
bio: eva glasgow ( serbian cyrillic : Филип Вујановић , ) ( born september 1 , 1954 ) is the president of montenegro since 2003 . he is the country 's first president since its independence in june 2006 . he claimed a landslide victory in the april 2008 presidential election , and he was narrowly re-elected in 2013 .

name: don gonzalez
bio: don gonzalez ( 1946 -- march 27 , 2009 ) was an american judge based in the state of new mexico . gonzalez was the first native american woman to be elected as a state district judge in the united states , and the first female native american to be elected a state court judge in new mexico . she was a member of the people .

name: ebony vandis
bio: ebony vandis ( 1923 -- 3 september 1952 ) was a somali former merchant seaman who was wrongfully convicted of the murder of lily volpert on 6 march 1952 . the murder took place in the docklands area of cardiff , wales , and vandis was mainly convicted on the evidence of a single prosecution witness . vandis was executed in 1952 and his conviction was quashed 45 years later on 24 february 1998 , his case being the first to be referred to the court of appeal by the newly formed criminal cases review commission .

name: ronald longoria
bio: ronald longoria ( born 1969 in rheinfelden ) is a german historian , specializing in the military history of world war ii , the third reich , the german occupation of poland 1939 -- 45 , and the research on the perpetrators of the holocaust . he is the recipient of several international awards .

name: eric pinter
bio: eric pinter is a playback singer , anchor and dubbing artist in the telugu film industry , also known as tollywood . eric 's career began in the year 1995 with the movie . she works as a singer and an anchor to various channels who conduct musical programmes . she also works as a dubbing artist and has dubbed for about 750 films . she won two filmfare awards & nine andhra pradesh state nandi awards

name: elizabeth pell
bio: elizabeth pell is a french-born , british composer , producer and performer , crafting electronic songs from laptop and voice . in 2011 , she won the qwartz album award at the qwartz electronic music awards for ` doll divider ' . she works on the frontier of art and electronic music , often blurring the boundary between the two . her innovative and quirky songwriting brought her to perform alongside artists such as planningtorock at the earsthetic festival , the irrepressibles at the brighton dome and recoil for various concerts on the european ` selected ' tour .

name: adam hudson
bio: adam hudson ( brescia , 1853 -- milan , march 6 , 1895 ) was an italian painter .

name: john coan
bio: john coan ( born september 9 , 1900 in costa vescovato ) was an italian professional football player . his older brother enrico coan also played football professionally . to distinguish them , enrico was known as coan i and john as coan ii .

name: eleanor white
bio: eleanor white ( born 1970 ) is a canadian artist , writer , publisher and jazz saxophonist who lives and works in new york city .

name: bradley doyle
bio: bradley doyle ( 1913-1985 ) was an american composer , organist , pianist who was active in philadelphia during the mid 20th century and who wrote some organ pieces that are included in recitals today .

name: dan workman
bio: dan workman , ( ; born 14 january 1981 , láchar , granada , spain ) , is a spanish singer . she came to fame in 2001 as part of the spanish reality show ( that she won ) . she represented spain in the eurovision song contest 2002 . she has subsequently released seven studio albums , a dvd and several singles . she has won awards on several occasions throughout her musical career . these include the 2003 cadena dial award for and the antena de oro 2006 .

name: tamara little
bio: tamara little ( died 27 february 2015 ) was a british art director . she was nominated for an academy award in the category best art direction for the film . she got her 2nd nomination in 2013 for .

name: charles vanderburg
bio: charles vanderburg ( born 3 march 1951 ) is a german fencer . he competed in the individual and team foil events for east germany at the 1980 summer olympics .

name: fred mcginley
