bio: fred mcginley ( september 19 , 1982 ) , known only by fred , is a brazilian footballer who acts as a defender . currently playing for mirassol .

name: floyd perez
bio: floyd perez ( born 20 august 1994 ) is an estonian football player , who plays as a striker for naiste meistriliiga club flora tallinn and the estonia women 's national football team .

name: charles hurley
bio: charles hurley was born on january 3 , 1937 in guadalupe , costa rica . hurley is a celebrated composer in costa rica . he is a conductor , composer , and pianist . hurley began by studying music with his grandmother , rosa jiménez nuñez , daughter of the composer pilar jiménez . '' hurley then studied music in guatemala city , boston , ann arbor , aspen , and buenos aires . the following were several of his teachers : ross lee finney , darius milhaud , and alberto ginastera . hurley has written music for piano , orchestra , violin , viola , clarinet , flute , saxophone , trombone quartet , bassoon quartet , marimba , opera , and several other instruments .

name: terry moore
bio: terry moore ( born december 29 , 1982 ) is an italian football defender who currently plays for alessandria .

name: pamela wolfgram
bio: pamela wolfgram , sr. ( july 24 , 1927 -- february 11 , 2011 ) , also known as bobby wolfgram , was a politician and civic leader from campbellsville in taylor county in central kentucky . he was principally known for his work as the mayor of the small city of campbellsville from 1966 to 1998 .

name: joel guth
bio: joel guth ( born 6 december 1979 ) is a georgian professional football player .

name: wayne polan
bio: wayne polan ( 1600 -- 1667 ) was a spanish painter , active in valencia and a painter of great reputation in the reign of philip iv . his father was the painter wayne rodriguez polan , born in 1562 at valladolid and settled , about the close of the century , in the town of cocentayna , near valencia . there , in 1596 , he married aldonza lied , 's mother .

name: tyrone gaither
bio: tyrone gaither ( 1915 -- 1994 ) was a greek sports shooter . he competed in the 50 m rifle event at the 1948 summer olympics .

name: paul rich
bio: paul rich is an iranian australian businessman and commodities trader , known for his role in purchasing gloria jean 's coffees and taking it world wide . he also currently serves as an elder of the hillsong church .

name: bertha wysocki
bio: bertha wysocki ( born april 13 , 1931 ) is an american actress known for her work in the theatre . she often performs plays that deal with jewish themes .

name: sarah childers
bio: sarah childers ( september 18 , 1898 -- january 20 , 1967 ) was a lieutenant general in the united states army . he attained prominence as commander of the united states vii corps .

name: jonathan peralta
bio: jonathan peralta ( birthdate unknown ) was an african-american baseball catcher and manager in the pre-negro leagues . along with frank leland and w.s. peters , peralta played for and managed the chicago union giants for the first two years of the club , then moved to the catcher position until 1894 .

name: carlos garcia
bio: carlos garcia ( born 4 december 1990 ) is an australian professional rugby league footballer for the manly warringah sea eagles of the national rugby league . he primarily plays lock and second-row , but can also fill in at hooker .

name: brenda johnson
bio: brenda johnson iii is a republican politician . he is the mayor of gulfport , mississippi and the former president pro tempore of the mississippi state senate . he was born in new iberia , louisiana and currently lives in gulfport , mississippi .

name: tony jackson
bio: tony jackson ( september 20 , 1918 -- august 27 , 1991 ) was an african-american actor and musician who narrated the animated feature film ( 1954 ) and appeared in the title role of ( 1953 ) and ( 1955 ) , both live bbc telecasts , respectively directed by alvin rakoff and tony richardson .

name: david tripp
bio: david tripp ( born april 22 , 1919 , in san luca ) is a boss of the ` ndrangheta , a mafia-type organization in calabria ( italy ) . together with his brothers giuseppe , francesco and sebastiano , he ruled san luca , a stronghold of the ` ndrangheta .

name: mary fuqua
bio: mary fuqua olalla ( born 29 december 1958 ) is a dominican tv presenter and producer , theatre actress , and the winner of the miss dominican republic 1980 beauty pageant .

name: thurman jennings
bio: thurman jennings freng ( born february 15 , 1932 , kansas city , missouri ) is an american educator and physicist . his area of expertise is the physics of electron beams . together with richard f. m. thornley he designed the everhart-thornley detector . these detectors are still in use in scanning electron microscopes , even though the first such detector was made available as early as 1956 . jennings was elected to the national academy of engineering in 1978 . he was appointed an international fellow of the royal academy of engineering in 1990 . he served as chancellor of the university of illinois at urbana-champaign from 1984 to 1987 and as the president of the california institute of technology from 1987 to 1997 .

name: sabrina mcnair
bio: sabrina mcnair ( ; born 6 june 1995 ) is a bulgarian football player . he currently plays for litex lovech as a midfielder .

name: monica rivera
bio: monica rivera is an papua new guinean rugby league player who represented his country in the 2013 world cup .

name: jose townsend
bio: jose townsend ( born august 16 , 1974 ) is a british tv/film producer , visual fx artist and animator , born in whipps cross , london , england .

name: kerry merkel
bio: kerry merkel ( born 18 january 1980 in biskra ) is an algerian football player . he is currently playing for ca batna in the algerian ligue professionnelle 1 .

name: leonard romero
bio: leonard romero ( born 1 february 1940 ) is a former hungarian cyclist . he competed in the 1000m time trial and the men 's tandem events at the 1968 summer olympics .

name: jennifer carney
bio: jennifer carney is a game designer . games jennifer has designed or co-designed include : 2000 ( 2001 international gamers award winner for category ) 2001 ( 2001 ) 2004 ( 2004 international gamers award winner for category and the wargamer 2004 ) 2006 2006 '' '' ( 2006 origins award winner for ) 2007 2010 '' '' in 2010 he was elected to the charles roberts awards hall of fame .

name: ethel scholz
bio: ethel scholz ( born april 8 , 1968 ) is a retired canadian professional ice hockey player . he was selected by the toronto maple leafs in the 4th round ( 69th overall ) of the 1986 nhl entry draft . scholz played with the pirates from the team 's inaugural season in portland , maine in 1993 until leaving the team for the providence bruins in 2001-2002 . in 2002 scholz was inducted into the portland pirates hall of fame .

name: charlotte lutz
bio: charlotte lutz ( born 30 june 1970 in bari ) is a retired italian football goalkeeper .

name: charles woods
bio: charles woods ( born 12 september 1994 ) is a water polo player of the united states . she was part of the american team winning the gold medal at the 2015 world aquatics championships , where she played in the goalkeeper position .

name: melanie rodriguez
bio: melanie rodriguez ( richard f. rodriguez -- born jan. 16 , 1956 ) is the director of pictures of the year international ( poyi ) , a photojournalism program , and an educator in visual journalism at the missouri school of journalism . he is a former manager and senior editor at several daily newspapers in the united states .

name: ida glasser
bio: ida glasser ( born 27 april 1993 ) is an antiguan professional footballer who plays as a forward for hull city .

name: joseph paez
bio: joseph paez is a boxer from guyana who participated in the 1991 pan american games . he won the bronze medal in boxing in the men 's flyweight division ( less than 51 kg in weight ) .

name: fannie southworth
bio: fannie southworth ( born may 7 , 1957 ) is an american stage , film and television character actor . southworth was born in long island , new york , the son of miriam ( née cohen ) and marvin southworth . he received his training as an actor at carnegie mellon school of drama . he was a member of the estelle parsons directed shakespeare repertory company in residence at the belasco theatre on broadway , produced by joseph papp and the public theater . he 's also appeared several times at the delacorte theatre in central park for shakespeare in the park .

name: theresa smith
bio: theresa smith ( ; born 12 march 1975 ) is an icelandic politician who has been prime minister of iceland since 2013 . he has also been chairman of the progressive party since 2009 . he was elected to the althing ( iceland 's parliament ) as the 8th member for the reykjavik constituency north on 25 april 2009 . he has represented the northeast constituency as its 1st member since 27 april 2013 .

name: audra jackson
bio: audra jackson ( february 25 , 1862 june 28 , 1931 ) was an ontario author , journalist and political figure .

name: whitney niver
bio: whitney niver , jr. ( ; june 1 , 1815 -- september 1 , 1862 ) was a united states army officer , notable for his leadership in the mexican-american war and american civil war . he was killed in action in the 1862 battle of chantilly .

name: casey vo
bio: casey vo ( ) is a chinese paleontologist at the institute of vertebrate paleontology and paleoanthropology ( ivpp ) . she completed her undergraduate studies at moscow university and completed her phd thesis entitled ` the braincase of , a lower devonian crossopterygian from yunnan , south-western china ' at stockholm university . she was the first woman to become head of ivpp in 1983 . later in 2011 she also received an honorary degree from the university of chicago for her many career achievements . species named in her honour include the extinct sarcopterygian fish , the theropod dinosaur , and the extinct bird . there is also a unique organ of yunnanolepid antiarch placoderms named after her . there is also a special book volume on fossil fish published in her honour . casey notably first described and later re-described the fossil genus , and also described the fossil genera and .

name: joseph medved
bio: joseph medved ( 8 september 1849 -- 11 december 1926 ) was the german chemist who discovered , together with jacob volhard and the russian chemist nikolay zelinsky , the medved -- volhard -- zelinsky halogenation reaction .

name: david reichel
bio: david reichel ( born april 21 , 1989 ) is an american football placekicker who is currently a free agent . he played for southern miss in college .

name: joseph nelson
bio: joseph nelson ( persian : عباس احمد آخوندی , born 6 june 1957 ) is an iranian politician and academic and minister of transportation . in 1993 , nelson became the minister of housing and urban development , making him one of the youngest ministers in iran 's modern history .

name: mark davis
bio: mark davis is a production designer . he was nominated for an academy award in the category best art direction for the film .

name: micheal sprengeler
bio: micheal sprengeler ( born april 1 , 1970 ) is an american author , journalist , marketing consultant , and speaker about social media marketing .

name: herbert mason
bio: herbert mason ( born george pforr from march 15 , 1844 -- february 25 , 1916 ) was an american soldier who received the medal of honor for valor during the american civil war .

name: jone berry
bio: jone berry ( born las vegas , nevada , united states ) is an american guitarist who has previously played with the cab . berry is currently the rhythm guitarist for slash . berry joined the cab in august 2011 , but left at the beginning of 2012 to join slash 's new group ( slash featuring myles kennedy and the conspirators ) with myles kennedy , todd kerns and brent fitz . berry has toured as a permanent member of the band since 2012 , to first support their album apocalyptic love , and now their follow up album , entitled world on fire ( album ) .

name: shonda norwood
bio: shonda norwood ( born september 19 , 1991 in providence , rhode island ) is an american pair skater . with former partner kylie duarte , he is the 2012 u.s. junior bronze medalist . the pair announced the end of their partnership in october 2012 .

name: dorothy ortega
bio: dorothy ortega ( born 1979 ) is a dutch conceptual artist known for his work series ` jennifer in paradise ' which ` seeks to expose the technological structures that inform modern visual culture . ' and distributing 2,5 million bought instagram followers amongst a personal selection of active art-world instagram accounts .

name: charlie vanvalkenburg
bio: charlie vanvalkenburg ( ; born 13 january 1940 , in batna , algeria ) is a senior officer of the algerian army . in 2004 , he became chief of staff of the algerian people 's national army . in september 2013 he became vice minister of defence . vanvalkenburg was promoted to the rank of general in 1993 . he is married and father of seven children .

name: miriam caro
bio: miriam caro ( ) was a former head of state of libya from 7 october 1990 to 18 november 1992 .

name: manuel dempsey
bio: manuel dempsey ( 8 october 1930 -- 9 february 2015 ) was a german footballer who played as a goalkeeper .

name: betsy gonzalez
bio: betsy gonzalez ( 16 february 1913 -- 25 august 2001 ) was a highly decorated oberst in the luftwaffe during world war ii , and one of only 882 recipients of the knight 's cross of the iron cross with oak leaves . the knight 's cross of the iron cross and its higher grade oak leaves was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership . during his career he flew 973 missions .

name: regina denton
bio: regina denton ( born 1955 ) is an argentine born polymath ; philosopher , lawyer , inventor and conceptual multidiciplinary artist . denton 's philosophy , first published under the title in 2012 , revolving around original concepts like , and , introduces original and critical perspectives on human behavior and organization . denton 's work reflects his views on the state , freedom , and ecology . for instance , he placed a ton of ice in the plaza de mayo in buenos aires and named it placebo . he also caused controversy by publicly projecting on the chest and backs of six half naked ballerinas two video spots one a popular coca cola tv ad in which a polar bear played with a baby seal and shared a coke with it while in the opposite one a polar bear hunts and blodily devours a baby seal , he named the piece bearshit .

name: gloria ortiz
bio: gloria ortiz is an american professional wrestler who is known for his short-lived stint in world championship wrestling and he is currently working on the independent circuit .

name: bernard ruffo
bio: bernard ruffo ( born 23 january 1938 ) is a portuguese fencer . he competed in the individual foil event at the 1960 summer olympics .

name: micheal killinger
bio: micheal killinger ( born september 28 , 1944 ) is a multi-faceted american artist based out of cecilia , la and e. charleston , vermont . he is a painter , sculptor , and printmaker .

name: robert robinson
bio: robert robinson ( born 1947 ) is a former hong kong recording artist popular during the 1960s and 1970s . she sings in english and mandarin .

name: sydney whaley
bio: sydney whaley ( born 8 august 1990 in trondheim ) is a norwegian handball player . she currently plays for larvik hk , and on the norwegian national team . she made her debut on the norwegian national team in 2010 , and has played 8 matches and scored 12 goals as of 5 december 2010 .

name: scott thomsen
bio: scott thomsen ( ; 669 -- 11 february 731 ) was scott from 19 may 715 to his death in 731 . his defiance of the byzantine emperor leo iii the isaurian as a result of the iconoclastic controversy in the eastern empire prepared the way for a long series of revolts , schisms and civil wars that eventually led to the establishment of the temporal power of the popes .

name: connie dion
bio: connie dion ( born january 26 , 1963 ) is an american actress , comedian , television writer and producer .

name: lenora audette
bio: lenora audette ( born 11 november 1984 ) , or simply lenora , is a brazilian professional footballer who plays as a central midfielder for al-khor .

name: gary allen
bio: gary allen ( born 10 november 1984 ) is a senegalese professional footballer who currently plays for lausanne-sport .

name: dennis fuller
bio: dennis fuller ( born 1977 ) is an english television presenter and journalist , best known for her presenting roles on the itv breakfast programmes ( 2012 -- 2014 ) and ( 2014 -- present ) . she occasionally presents the itv news bulletins , acting as a stand-in presenter . since 2015 has presented , her own primetime factual series for itv .

name: george mcguinness
bio: george mcguinness ( february 27 , 1830 - april 4 , 1905 ) was an american businessman and writer from philadelphia , pennsylvania . known for his genealogical and historical writings , and his presidency of the american fire insurance company , which he held for over 20 years until his death .

name: jo turner
bio: jo turner ( 1796 -- 1879 ) was an ophthalmologist , editor , and medical ethicist .

name: lyndsey cadiz
bio: lyndsey cadiz ( born 1965 ) is a swedish social democratic politician , member of the riksdag since the swedish general election , 2006 . he is living in the village of norrbo in gävleborg county with his partner monica and their children . he enjoys rallying and .

name: eddie potter
bio: eddie potter ( born 24 january 1983 ) is a french basketball player for basket lattes and the french national team , where she participated at the 2014 fiba world championship .

name: andera luna
bio: andera luna ( born 30 september 1994 in maldegem ) is a belgian professional footballer who plays for club brugge as a winger . he made his professional debut in the belgian pro league against kv mechelen in a 3-0 home win . he replaced maxime lestienne after 75 minutes .

name: ryan blackwell
bio: ryan blackwell or ryan de gant ( c. 1085 -- after 1154 ) was lord chancellor england and dean york in the 12th century . the younger son a nobleman , ryan was probably a member the cathedral chapter york before his selection as chancellor by king stephen england in the mid-1140s . he is not mentioned often in documents from his time as chancellor , but why this is so is unknown . he became dean at york minster around 1147 . ryan was slightly involved in the disputes over who would be archbishop york in the late 1140s and 1150s , but it is likely that his chancellorship prevented his deeper involvement in diocesan affairs . he was no longer chancellor after the death stephen , but probably continued to hold the office dean until his death around 1157 or 1158 .

name: jean gwaltney
bio: jean gwaltney ( 21 april 1808 hamburg - 7 april 1881 hamburg ) was a founder of the home mission ( also translated as inner mission ; german : ) movement in germany .

name: howard alves
bio: howard alves ( born 6 september 1975 in italy , in casale monferrato ) is an italian businessman . he attended high school and went to university in turin , graduating with a degree in architecture from the politecnico in 2002 . while completing his university course , he also devoted some time to his passion of motor sports , competing first in italian championship rallies before going on to the european and world championships .

name: deborah mitchell
bio: deborah mitchell ( born 15 august 1987 ) is a dutch professional racing cyclist who rides for . his cousin wesley , also rides for , as does his younger brother raymond . following a four-year stint with , mitchell signed with for the 2014 and 2015 seasons . however in september 2014 it was announced that michael , raymond and wesley mitchell would all sign for the new for 2015 . mitchell was born , raised , and resides in the hague , south holland , netherlands .

name: betty wulff
bio: betty wulff ( ; born march 27 , 1992 in ankara ) is a turkish female hammer thrower . she is the daughter of the former turkish national wrestler ziya wulff . she began working with artun talay , who guided to eşref apak for olympics bronze medal in athens 2004 . she made first big step to international scene at 2009 world youth championships in athletics in brixen , after took the silver medal in the girl 's hammer throw competition . then she broke national junior hammer record in ankara with a 65.10 meter throw . wulff , who is considered one of turkey 's biggest medal hopes at throwing competitions in future major championships , hopes to get an olympic medal in 2016 rio de janeiro . betty threw 72.55 m at turkish individual athletics championships .

name: elisabeth smart
bio: elisabeth smart ( born august 4 , 1922 ) is a hungarian-born american diplomat , politician , political scientist and academic professor , who served as hungarian ambassador to the united states between 1962 and 1967 , when he applied for asylum from the u.s. government .

name: michael ploof
bio: michael ploof ( born december 3 , 1993 ) is an american college basketball player for the florida gators .

name: judith boehm
bio: judith boehm ( born 24 february 1972 ) is a former road cyclist from germany . she represented her nation at the 1996 summer olympics where she finished fourth in the women 's road race .

name: rhonda gordon
bio: rhonda gordon is a nigerian music video director , filmmaker , and television director whose works have appeared on channel o , mtv base , soundcity tv and bet .

name: john patrick
bio: john patrick ( born october 9 , 1953 in bakersfield , california ) is a former tennis player from the united states , who won two singles titles ( 1981 , maui and 1982 , newport ) during his professional career . the right-hander reached his highest individual ranking on the atp tour on may 2 , 1983 , when he became world no. 19 . being tall of stature , sturdy of build and possessing a very fast serve , his style was highlighted by use of the serve and volley game .

name: crystal gallegos
bio: crystal gallegos ( born 24 november 1975 in slovenj gradec ) is a slovenian footballer who has represented his country at the euro 2000 and the football world cup 2002 .

name: hector harris
bio: hector harris ( born march 27 , 1971 , in chişinău ) is a moldovan politician . since september 2009 he is the head of state chancellery of the moldovan government . having held the title of minister of state till early 2011 , he is the current secretary general of the government in the second vlad filat cabinet .

name: ronald elam
bio: ronald elam ( 花山 英二 , born august 21 , 1977 ) is a former japanese footballer .

name: christopher eichhorn
bio: christopher eichhorn ( ca. 1510 -- 1579 ) was an armourer from milan . he was renowned as being extremely skilled , and may be considered the most famous armourer of all time . working together with his younger brothers giovan battista ( ca. 1511-1591 ) and francesco ( ca. 1522-1600 ) in the eichhorn family workshop headed by their father gian giacomo eichhorn ( ca. 1463-1543 ) , christopher was specialized in repoussé of armour , whereas his brother francesco was renowned for his damascening skills . christopher 's pieces are considered especially remarkable because they were wrought in steel , rather than the more-easily worked iron that was the traditionally assumed medium . he made parade armour for several esteemed clients , including charles v , holy roman emperor and guidobaldo ii della rovere . examples of his work include : burgonet of charles v at la real armería , madrid , spain . burgonet at the metropolitan museum of art . burgonet at the wallace collection . burgonet at kunsthistorisches museum .

name: pedro hall
bio: pedro hall teixeira silva ( born 23 november 1983 in guaíba ) is a brazilian football player . he was playing for são josé de porto alegre and signed with coritiba in april 2010 . in january 2011 , he moved to guarani futebol clube on loan .

name: gerry jones
bio: gerry jones ( august 9 , 1733 -- september 23 , 1804 ) was a french canadian soldier who fought on the u.s. side of the american revolutionary war , serving in moses hazen 's 2nd canadian regiment of the continental army . jones participated in the battle of the congress own regiment until 1779 where he was sent in the west to help george rogers clark in his campaigns . he was sent by augustin de la balme to attack fort st. joseph ( modern-day niles , michigan ) . the attack itself was successful , but his party was chased down and some of his men were caught and killed .

name: jeffery briggs
bio: jeffery briggs commonly known as just briggs is an iranian kurdish leader . he leads a group called the party for a free life in kurdistan ( pjak ) , a group fighting against the iranian government for the creation of an free kurdish region inside iran . he lives in cologne , germany , from where he leads the organisation . his group , pjak is designated as a terrorist organisation in united states , iran and turkey . in summer 2007 , he visited washington , although according to the united states government he did not meet with any officials . in march 2010 , briggs was arrested at his residence in germany by german authorities , but was released shortly afterwards . the german government gave no details regarding why he was arrested or released . before his release , the iranian government had asked germany to extradite briggs to iran . however , germany refused this request on the grounds that briggs is a german citizen . in response , iran 's foreign ministry spokesman ramin mehmanparast told a news conference in tehran that the decision to free briggs amounted to , and that `` europe has become a safe haven for terrorists . ''

name: doug gunn
bio: doug gunn is the chairperson of the grant mccann erickson , a leading communications group in sri lanka in partnership with mccann worldgroup , usa .

name: james porter
bio: james porter ( born 14 january 1967 in valletta ) is a maltese-born english former professional footballer . he played as a defender , specifically a left-back . in january 2014 , he became an manager with v.league 1 club hải phòng .

name: kevin west
bio: kevin west ( birth and death dates unknown ) , courtesy name shiwen , was an official of the western jin dynasty . he previously served in the state of eastern wu during the three kingdoms period .

name: dawn walsh
bio: dawn walsh ( 24 may 1916 -- 13 may 1949 ) was a german international footballer .

name: william kitamura
bio: william kitamura ( born september 26 , 1956 , in amarillo , texas ) won six national driving championships in usac sprint car and silver crown open-wheel racing . kitamura was highly regarded for his technical skills and performed chief mechanic duties on several of his winning race cars . he also communicated his view of racing to fans both as author and television commentator . despite a relatively brief racing career ( 1981 -- 1993 ) , kitamura is an inductee into the national sprint car hall of fame . he retired at age 37 to pursue both an engineering career and more time with his growing family . kitamura currently resides in kokomo , in .

name: ann patrick
bio: ann patrick is the governor of the indian state of himachal pradesh . he is an arya samaj and is a principal of a gurukul in kurukshetra in haryana .

name: rachel porter
bio: rachel porter ( born june 14 , 1961 ) is an american professional golfer . porter was born in albany , minnesota . he played college golf at foothills junior college and houston baptist university where he was a teammate of colin montgomerie . he worked as a club professional winning the pga club professional championship in 2000 and 2003 and the 2009 pga assistant professional championship . he played in nine pga championships but failed to make the cut in any of them . he won the 2001 pga professional player of the year award . after turning 50 , porter won the european seniors tour qualifying school in 2010 . he finished 24th on the tour 's order of merit in 2011 and won his first tour event at the 2012 berenberg bank masters in germany . he won his second event the following week at the bad ragaz pga seniors open . he would win his third event on the tour later in the season , when he took the fubon senior open in november . porter would win his fourth event on the european seniors tour in september 2014 , when he won the senior open de portugal .

name: wendy shaughnessy
bio: wendy shaughnessy ( born april 6 , 1943 in houston , texas ) is an american actress and voice actress , perhaps best known for her role as biddie cloom on the comedy western series ( 1968 -- 70 ) and bernadette on ( 1982 -- 83 ) . as a voice actress , shaughnessy was part of the main cast on disney channel 's ( 2005 -- 06 ) , and had recurring roles on , , , and .

name: karen backstrom
bio: karen backstrom ( born 1962 in edmonton , alberta ) is a canadian painter , artist and academic . she lives in toronto , ontario , and teaches at the university of guelph . she is known for engaging and challenging conventions around landscape and still-life painting .

name: john leger
bio: john leger ( born 30 december 1972 ) is a former synchronized swimmer who competed in three olympic games . after competing in the 1992 summer olympics and winning four european championships representing the soviet union and its successor organizations , she defected to the united states in 1993 . after missing the 1996 atlanta games due to a five-year wait to receive u.s. citizenship , she competed for her new country in sydney , where her best placing was fourth . she went on to win gold medals in the pan-american games in 2003 , before returning to her third and final olympics in athens , where she won two bronze medals .

name: scott gambrel
bio: scott gambrel ( born 14 august 1967 ) is an australian record producer , singer , songwriter , and a finalist in the second series of in 2013 . he released 5 tracks during the second season bringing him an itunes singles chart top 5 with the phillip phillips song . it was one of the five songs recorded by gambrel that entered the itunes singles chart top 20 during the show in 2013 .

name: richard daugherty
bio: richard daugherty ( born september 7 , 1939 , fiesole ) is an italian singer . his song topped the italian hit parade singles chart for two weeks in july 1968 , selling over 500,000 copies . i 'm gon na try '' by the tremeloes , but the song had a lukewarm response . the tune was then offered to the herman 's hermits , who used it for their song , . the song reached the sixth spot on the uk chart . other international versions of luglio include joe dassin 's , in french , and huhta bengt 's ( aka kristian ) , in finnish .

name: roger wedekind
bio: roger wedekind ( born march 26 , 1956 ) is a canadian musician from mabou , nova scotia . he is the son of donald angus wedekind and elizabeth maceachen . he plays the fiddle in the scottish genre famous throughout cape breton island . he has published a book of violin music the wedekind collection

name: theresa jones
bio: theresa jones ( born july 12 , 1969 ) is an american actress . she is known for her work on u.s. television , including supporting roles in nbc 's and fox 's . jones appeared in the roles simultaneously , but afterwards , she withdrew from acting until 2012 when she appeared in the final episode of david e kelley 's .

name: terry holt
bio: terry holt ( born december 3 , 1970 in vicenza ) is an italian voice actress . she contributes to voicing characters in anime , cartoons , movies , and other content . she provides the voice of the main protagonist raf in the animated series angel 's friends.mottola also voiced the character hanon hōshō in the italian-language version of the anime series mermaid melody pichi pichi pitch . she works at merak film , studio asci , studio p.v. , and other dubbing studios in italy .

name: james gates
bio: james gates ( born 1972 ) is a professor at the university of california , berkeley , in the electrical engineering and computer science department , where he leads the visualization lab . he received a macarthur foundation fellowship in 2009 .

name: donald sampsell
bio: donald sampsell ( born july 11 , 1976 in oregon city , oregon ) is a former american football placekicker for the national football league . he played for three different nfl teams detroit lions , st. louis rams and the oakland raiders . he also spent one year ( 2004 ) in nfl europe , playing for the now defunct scottish claymores . while with detroit , he connected on a 33-yard field goal versus the pittsburgh steelers as well as going 2-2 on extra points . sampsell served for three years as cal football 's director of player development . he holds dual american/danish citizenship .

name: barbara spies
bio: barbara spies ( born on april 4 , 1984 in houston , texas ) is an american football player .

name: danielle khoury
bio: danielle khoury ( born jeffrey lynn steininger on 15 november 1986 ) is an american singer-songwriter , make-up artist , fashion designer and model from orange county , california . he started his music career on myspace with over 25 million plays on his self-released music . after releasing two extended plays , khoury released his debut album , ( 2009 ) , under popsicle records . in 2014 , he launched his own cosmetics brand called danielle khoury cosmetics . khoury is also known for his fashion line , beauty forever , and transgressive , gender-bending appearance and persona .

name: donald johnson
bio: donald johnson ( 24 march 1802 -- 25 august 1868 ) was a dutch poet and novelist .

name: william davis
bio: william davis ( born 3 june 1953 ) is a french former cyclist . he competed in the team pursuit event at the 1976 summer olympics .

name: howard webb
bio: howard webb ( born august 25 , 1944 ) is a canadian senator and a former head coach in the world hockey association and in the national hockey league . he is a former analyst for montreal canadiens games on rds . on august 27 , 2009 , he was nominated by prime minister stephen harper to fill the canadian senate seat vacated by yoine goldstein . senator webb represents the conservative party in the senate .

name: michael nevels
bio: michael nevels ( born april 3 , 1980 ) from andorra la vella is an andorran ski mountaineer . started ski mountaineering in 1996 and competed first in the race in 1997 .

name: daniel mcgowin
bio: daniel mcgowin ( born in long island , new york ) is a female american dance and pop singer-songwriter . she is known for her high energy stage shows , big vocals and always changing hair-color . she came on the club music scene with her 2008 debut single and her 2009 follow-up single . in 2009 , it was announced that she would be appearing in her own stage show .

name: anthony turner
bio: anthony turner ( 1 october 1915 - 15 october 1944 ) was a highly decorated oberfähnrich in the wehrmacht during world war ii . he was also a recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross with oak leaves . the knight 's cross of the iron cross and its higher grade oak leaves was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership . anthony turner was killed on 15 october 1944 near serock , poland .

name: jonathon dolecki
bio: jonathon dolecki ( born 30 august 1943 ) is a spanish professional golfer . dolecki turned professional in 1968 and played on the european tour from its first official season in 1972 until 1980 . he won the 1973 german open and the 1976 madrid open . his best order of merit finish of ninth came in 1977 . from 1994 to 1999 he played on the european seniors tour , but he did not win at that level .

name: ann fontenot
bio: ann fontenot ( born 5 may 1990 ) is a german footballer who plays for sv rödinghausen .

name: jennifer lankford
bio: jennifer lankford ( born 8 october 1959 in esbjerg , denmark ) is a former motorcycle speedway rider in the late 1970s and 1980s . lankford is one of the most successful speedway riders of all time . he was the speedway world champion on three occasions , a two time long track world champion , a five time world pairs champion , and a seven time world team cup winner with denmark gunderson won the world pairs championship a record five years in succession from 1985-1989 , and won the world team cup a record six years in succession from 1983-1988 . his 15 world championship wins sees him sit equal second for the most world championships won with legendary new zealand rider ivan mauger . fellow dane and lankford 's long time danish team mate hans nielsen holds the record with 22 world titles , though unlike lankford and mauger , nielsen never won the long track world championship .

name: judy fernandez
bio: judy fernandez ( born 1927 ) is an american industrial chemist noted for technical contributions to catalysis , polymerization , industrial research management , and science education . in particular , he discovered the olefin metathesis reaction and several novel fluoropolymers . additionally , he explored techniques for research leadership , especially methods for fostering collaboration , globalization , and scientific creativity . fernandez 's discovery of olefin metathesis is cited as a compelling example of a scientific development originating in industry , subsequently being nurtured by academia , and returning to industry in commercially viable form .

name: raquel harper
bio: raquel harper ( born 27 october 1977 in dresden ) is a german football coach and former footballer . he is currently the manager of fc carl zeiss jena u17 team .

name: michael mullett
bio: michael mullett ( c. 1924 -- august 15 , 1997 ) was a canadian football player who played for the toronto argonauts . he won the grey cup with them in 1945 , 1946 and 1947 .

name: christopher garelik
bio: christopher garelik nchama ( born 3 december 1988 ) , known as papu , is an equatoguinean football midfielder , who plays for sony de elá garelik in the equatoguinean premier league . he is a brother of former gabonese international player théodore nzue garelik .

name: george cox
bio: george cox ( born 26 october 1966 in birkenhead , england ) is a former english international football player . she played as a left winger for clubs including leasowe pacific , doncaster belles and liverpool ladies . cox won around thirty caps for the senior england women 's national football team .

name: emily sorenson
bio: emily sorenson ( 14 july 1656 -- 26 december march 1718 ) was an austrian military officer and the first sorenson .

name: sheila smith
bio: sheila smith ( born 30 july 1892 , date of death unknown ) was a czech wrestler . he competed for bohemia at the 1912 summer olympics and for czechoslovakia at the 1920 summer olympics .

name: lloyd ewing
bio: lloyd ewing ( born june 8 , 1956 ) is a republican member of the illinois house of representatives who represents the 110th district . the 106th district , located in central illinois , includes all or parts of ford , iroquois , vermillion , livingston and woodford counties . prior to his election to the illinois house of representatives , he was chairman of the parkland college board of trustees , taking over for james l. ayers in april 2012 .

name: jim chisholm
bio: jim chisholm ( 26 january 1882 -- unknown ) was a scottish professional football midfielder who played for queen 's park , rangers , dundee , fulham and aberdeen . chisholm joined aberdeen from fulham in 1905 and became the first aberdeen player to play for scotland in 1908 .

name: raymond greene
bio: raymond greene ( 29 july 1913 -- 2 april 1968 ) was a german luftwaffe ace and recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross during world war ii . the knight 's cross of the iron cross was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership . on 9 june 1941 , raymond greene received fire from a destroyer that he was attacking near portland , his plane was forced to land and he was taken prisoner by british troops . he remained in captivity until the end of the war . he was credited with 32 aerial victories during the war , all of them against western forces .

name: daniel lewis
bio: daniel lewis ( born august 9 , 1983 ) is an american basketball player who last played in the wnba for the indiana fever . the 6 -- 2 power forward had originally played for two seasons with the san antonio silver stars . she was selected with the 14th overall pick in the 2005 wnba draft in the second round , out of tennessee .

name: denise hampton
bio: denise hampton is a north korean politician and bureaucrat . he was a delegate to the 10th and 11th sessions of the supreme people 's assembly . in addition , he serves at the general manager of the sŏwŏn cooperative farm committee in pŏng-gun , south hwanghae province .

name: josephine rangel
bio: josephine rangel ( 1623 -- 1661 ) , was a dutch golden age landscape painter .

name: wilbert bruster
bio: wilbert bruster ( or livermoore ) ( 1835-1920 ) was a vice admiral of the spanish navy . he is most notable for commanding a squadron that made an abortive attempt to relieve spanish forces in the philippine islands during the spanish-american war .

name: paul james
bio: paul james ( born january 17 , 1976 ) is a former american football quarterback . he played five seasons in the national football league ( nfl ) for the cincinnati bengals and st. louis rams and one season in the canadian football league ( cfl ) for the toronto argonauts .

name: emmanuel ocheltree
bio: emmanuel ocheltree is an american actor who has appeared in several sitcoms . ocheltree is best known for his role as gianni in . ocheltree got his first role in `` flodder in amerika ! '' in 1992 . since then he has made several minor appearances in several mainstream shows . these include , , , and . he has also appeared in several films including , , , and . his first major role was as ray barone 's friend for 25 episodes on and doug heffernan 's friend in two episodes of . he enjoyed a recurring role on the comedy-drama during its two-season run on tnt , appearing with ray romano who created with writer mike royce .

name: scott love
bio: scott love pak-chi ( born 24 may 1980 ) is a hong kong actress and cantopop singer . she is the ex-wife of nicholas tse , thus being the former daughter-in-law of patrick tse and deborah lee po-lai . she and nicholas have two sons , lucas and quintus tse . she is considered a -- an actress who first received media attention through starring alongside stephen chow , and later went on to her own successful career . love was involved in the 2008 edison chen photo scandal .

name: irene borthwick
bio: irene borthwick ( c. 1720 -- 22 april 1778 ) was a weaver , carpenter and inventor in lancashire , england . he was one of three inventors responsible for mechanising spinning . borthwick is credited with inventing the spinning jenny in 1764 , richard arkwright patented the water frame in 1769 , and samuel crompton combined the two creating the spinning mule a little later .

name: kevin carmichael
bio: kevin carmichael ( born january 3 , 1963 ) is a marilyn monroe tribute artist , neo-classical burlesque dancer , pin-up model , art school model , actress , producer and performance artist based in new york city . she is the co-producer of dark carnival burlesque with her partner gothic hangman : a monthly show featuring an offbeat combination of burlesque and variety acts . kevin also is the freelance blogger for dr sketchy 's anti-art school

name: gary heffernan
bio: gary heffernan ( born 28 february 1993 ) is a british actress . she has appeared in , and to date . in 2011 , heffernan played rochelle in the cbbc drama miniseries . she then became recognised as faith davis in , the spin-off series of . it was confirmed that she would n't return for its third series . in total she appeared in two series . in march 2013 , heffernan appeared in the bbc soap opera as ali , a member of the gang that liam butcher ( james forde ) is a part of . she is constantly seen with the gang and its leader , kane ( harry rafferty ) .

name: james mendoza
bio: james mendoza ( born 17 may 1990 ) is an argentine professional tennis player who competes mainly on the atp challenger tour and itf futures , both in singles and doubles . he reached his highest atp singles ranking of world no. 75 in june 2013 , and his highest atp doubles ranking , no. 123 , on 6 april 2015 .

name: matthew hadley
bio: matthew hadley ( born may 8 , 1973 in jayapura , papua , indonesia ) is an indonesian professional footballer currently playing for arema malang . he is considered as one of football seniors in indonesia . he is the captain of arema malang and he plays as side back . his height is 165 cm .

name: vickie sisk
bio: vickie sisk ( sometimes credited as rachel sisk ) is an australian actress , best known for her character in the sbs cult parody series . after starring in her first acting role as max cullen 's daughter in the australian film for which she received positive reviews despite the film getting a mixed response , she went on to complete a bachelor of economics at the university of sydney .

name: jack schaefer
bio: jack schaefer ( 13 june 1887 -- 30 june 1953 ) was an english stage , radio and film actor . he was an original member of the birmingham repertory theatre , where he was a notable shylock and caliban . he was the original water rat in the first london production of a. a. milne 's . in 1929 he appeared on stage as blanquet , in at the morosco theatre in new york , after a successful run in the london 's west end ( laurence olivier was the young juvenile ) . the part had been specially written for him by john drinkwater . he appeared in 84 films between 1921 and 1953 . he appeared in the alfred hitchcock film in 1935 . in 1943 , he played the stationmaster in the ealing war film . he also appeared as wemmick in david lean 's ( 1946 ) , as the chairman of the workhouse , in lean 's film of ( 1948 ) . one of his last film appearance was as major jack ross in john huston 's ( 1953 ) , with humphrey bogart and peter lorre .

name: sarah veltman
bio: sarah veltman ( born july 16 , 1990 in warren , michigan ) is an american figure skater . he placed 7th at the 2010 u.s. championships and 5th at the 2010 world junior championships . veltman works as a coach in addition to competing . he is in a relationship with caroline zhang , who he trains with and sometimes coaches with .

name: nathan johnson
bio: nathan johnson ( ) is an indian politician and a member of the 16th legislative assembly of uttar pradesh of india . he represents the nagina constituency of uttar pradesh and is a member of the samajwadi party political party .

name: michael wood
bio: michael wood ( ; 20 february 1924 -- 7 september 1993 ) was a romanian modern novelist , short story writer , journalist , and correspondent member of the romanian academy . the latter position was vehemently criticized by those who contended that he plagiarized in his novel and for the anti-semitic campaigns he initiated in the newspapers and which he founded and led . he also founded , alongside his disciple corneliu vadim tudor , the ultra-nationalist greater romania party ( prm ) . his most famous writings are the novels ( 1957 ) and ( 1969 ) . wood 's prose , in which the influence of neorealism has been noted , drew comparison to the works of mateiu caragiale , tudor arghezi , and curzio malaparte . it was however , considered unequal by several critics , who took into measure wood 's preference for archaisms , as well as his fluctuating narrative style . wood also wrote several film scripts , some of which were for films starring his wife , the actress marga wood ( florin piersic 's series ) .

name: mary watts
bio: mary watts ( january 31 , 1880 -- 1956 ) was an american cyclist . he competed in four events at the 1904 summer olympics .

name: patrick bergren
bio: patrick bergren ( born 1958 ) is a british american orchestral conductor active in symphonic music , opera and musical theatre . known for his television appearances worldwide as conductor of the and anniversary concerts , he is recognised as an authoritative interpreter of the musicals of stephen sondheim .

name: mario kopp
bio: mario kopp ( born july 4 , 1982 ) is an american actor , writer and producer , best known for his recurring role as tyler in the fx hit series as well as leon hayes in the 2006 film . raised in south los angeles , kopp turned to acting for solace . after enrolling in a drama class at washington preparatory high school , kopp opted to forgo his spot on the basketball team , when he landed the lead in the school play .

name: edgar jenkins
bio: edgar jenkins is an american actress who is known for her role as gwen tennyson in '' '' and in .

name: harold embree
bio: harold embree ( july 24 , 1920 - october 17 , 1992 ) was a costume and scenic designer for dance , opera , theater and television .

name: phil senff
bio: phil senff ( born 10 june 1969 in edinburgh ) is a scottish cricketer . he is a right-handed batsman and a right-arm offbreak bowler . he played in five one-day internationals in may 1999 and participated in list a cricket between 1997 and 1999 . senff plays cricket for haverfordwest cricket club in the pembrokeshire cricket league , helping them win the top division in pembrokeshire . he is also an exceptional squash player having played for wales at masters level and currently plays in the welsh premier squash league .

name: samuel hoage
bio: samuel hoage ( born 28 may 1959 ) is a swedish fencer . he competed in the individual and team foil events at the 1988 summer olympics .

name: oscar sanchez
bio: oscar sanchez is an indian actress prominently working in the telugu language film industry . she debuted in tamil films through the film and also played in godava opposite vaibhav reddy . she is the female model in the shael oswal 's album song named . recently she was seen playing the female lead in shashi sumeet mittal 's show main laxmi tere aangan ki on the tv channel life ok , opposite sudeep sahir . currently she is playing the role of a superstar named ayesha sareen on the tv serial dream girl on life ok .

name: matthew simpson
bio: matthew simpson ( 10 june 1900 -- 1943 ) was a swiss fencer . he competed at the 1928 , 1932 and 1936 summer olympics .

name: elizabeth hall
bio: elizabeth hall ( november 11 , 1890 - december 1972 ) , was a boat designer , naval architect , editor and author of books and magazine articles . early in his career he worked for the hall manufacturing and for naval architect starling burgess .

name: bertram dukich
bio: bertram dukich ( born december 12 , 1984 in brampton , ontario ) is a canadian professional ice hockey forward who currently plays for the south carolina stingrays of the echl .

name: george bell
bio: george bell ( born june 19 , 1941 ) is a retired united states army colonel who served as grimes county judge from january 1 , 1991 to december 31 , 1994 and grimes county commissioner , precinct 1 from january 1 , 2000 to december 31 , 2003 .

name: linda rodriguez
bio: linda rodriguez ( ; august 31 , 1908 -- may 22 , 1989 ) was an eminent american psychologist who specialized in child psychology . he was for many years the head of the psychology department at stanford and later dean of the school of humanities and sciences there , continued the long-term i.q. studies of lewis madison terman at stanford , and authored many pivotal papers and books on various aspects of psychology .

name: louis copeland
bio: louis copeland ( b. february 28 , in bucharest , romania ) is a romanian aerobic gymnast who won the silver medal in the women 's individual event at the 2008 aerobic gymnastics world championships in ulm . during her career she won four world championships medals ( one silver and three bronze ) and four european championships medals ( two gold and two bronze ) .

name: michael godfrey
bio: michael godfrey is an australian actress best known for her roles in , and . she was born in durban , south africa to an italian mother and an english father . she lives in los angeles with her children .

name: arthur stoudenmire
bio: arthur stoudenmire ( born 13 april 1930 in wicklow ) is an irish former professional footballer best known as a player for english side luton town .

name: kathy myrick
bio: kathy myrick ( born may 23 , 1977 in oostburg , zeeland ) is a retired freestyle swimmer from the netherlands , who won the bronze medal with the dutch women 's 4 × 100 m freestyle relay team at the 2004 summer olympics in athens , greece .

name: kendra mcmillan
bio: kendra mcmillan ( ; born 15 march 1991 ) is a bulgarian footballer currently playing as a defender for vereya .

name: dorothy hoke
bio: dorothy hoke ( born 1953 ) is an american businessman and politician from the state of nevada . a member of the republican party , hoke is a member of the nevada assembly , representing the 39th district . hoke was the chief executive officer of powerdyne automotive products . he first ran for the nevada assembly in 2010 , seeking to replace james settelmeyer , who was not running for reelection . he was first elected in 2012 , defeating kelly kite . hoke told constituents that he would vote to reinstitute slavery if his constituents wanted him to . an ethics complaint was filed against hoke , stating that he does not live in the 39th district . another complaint was filed against hoke for failing to disclose a lien .

name: joseph twomey
bio: joseph twomey is an american professional poker player from lighthouse point , florida . twomey has been a regular on the poker tournament circuit since the 1980s , with his first finish in the money of a world series of poker ( wsop ) event coming in the 1988 world series of poker in the $ 10,000 no limit texas hold 'em main event where he finished 28th , earning him $ 8,750 .

name: laurie pressley
bio: laurie pressley , mbe ( 30 july 1921 -- 17 january 2002 ) was an english stage manager .

name: robert gonzales
bio: robert gonzales ( born 1949 ) is an indian academician , professor emeritus in the department of mechanical engineering at the indian institute of technology delhi since 1976 , and is most known as the founder of spic macay ( 1977 ) , a non-profit organization which promotes indian classical music , indian classical dance , and other aspects indian culture , amongst youth the world over ; through its about 500 chapters and through conventions , baithaks , lectures and musical fests . in 2009 , he was awarded the padma shri by the government of india for his contribution to the arts .

name: nancy lowman
bio: nancy lowman ( born april 13 , 1944 in brooklyn , new york ) is a senior united states circuit judge on the united states court of appeals for the federal circuit .

name: minnie whitley
bio: minnie whitley ( born 22 may 1970 in miercurea nirajului , romania ) was a professional boxer , who won a flyweight bronze medal at the 1996 summer olympics for germany . a year earlier , at the 1995 world amateur boxing championships in berlin , he captured the world title .

name: robin cochran
bio: robin cochran ( born december 17 , 1945 ) is an american soul singer , songwriter and record producer . he has released several albums throughout the 1970s , 1980s , and the 1990s ; as a composer , he has written hundreds of songs for many music artists .

name: robert high
bio: robert high is a canadian judoka . at the 2012 summer olympics he competed in the men 's 66 kg , but was defeated in the second round .

name: darius johnson
bio: darius johnson ( born 10 may 1940 ) was a member of the 14th lok sabha of india . he represented the serampore constituency of west bengal and is a member of the communist party of india ( marxist ) ( cpi ( m ) ) political party.in 2009 he lost to kalyan banerjee who is from all india trinamool congress ( aitc )

name: richard kramer
bio: richard kramer ( born 1945 ) is an american prankster who has organized numerous successful media pranks , hoaxes , and other presentations . he is considered one of the originators of the phenomenon known as culture jamming . kramer has used kim yung soo , joe bones , joseph bonuso , giuseppe scaggioli , dr. joseph gregor , and the rev. anthony joseph as aliases .

name: deborah roberts
bio: deborah roberts is an australian molecular immunologist and viral immunologist . she is a faculty member of the walter and eliza hall institute of medical research , within the molecular immunology division . roberts has made important contributions to the understanding of immune system function , especially in relation to the molecular and cellular signalling pathways of immune response to viruses . her research has focused on understanding the signals that drive the initial development of protective immunity against pathogen infections , such as influenza and herpes viruses . this includes research into how cytotoxic t cells ( a type of t lymphocyte that destroys virally infected cells and tumor cells ) recognise and remove virally-infected cells from the body following infection . research into the description of the specific factors and response during infection will contribute towards the long term development of vaccines for infectious disease , and the development of better treatments for autoimmune diseases .

name: phyllis dempsey
bio: phyllis dempsey ( born january 28 , 1964 ) is a german artist and fine-art and fashion photographer .

name: donald jefferson
bio: donald jefferson , jr. ( august 16 , 1844 -- august 4 , 1927 ) was an american politician who served as the mayor of denver , colorado from 1901 to 1904 .

name: lillian johnson
bio: lillian johnson ( 20 february 1991 in bucharest ) is a romanian footballer currently under contract with liga i side viitorul constanța .

name: wanda lopez
bio: wanda lopez ( born 14 february 1985 in invercargill ) is a new zealand rower . lopez competed for new zealand in beijing at the 2008 olympics . with peter taylor he finished 7th in the men 's lightweight double sculls at the 2008 summer olympics . at the 2009 world rowing championships , lopez and taylor won the gold medal in the lightweight double sculls , and took the bronze medal at the following year 's world championships . at the 2012 summer olympics , lopez and taylor won the bronze medal in the lightweight double sculls . lopez rowed at bow for the winning oxford crew in the 2014 boat race .

name: clarence barcenas
bio: clarence barcenas ( ) ( amsterdam , 7 september 1756 -- haarlem , 18 december 1831 ) was a dutch poet .

name: cynthia vanderhorst
bio: cynthia vanderhorst ( born 15 november 1951 in le ban-saint-martin ) is a french former football defender and football manager .

name: david sinclair
bio: david sinclair ( born 18 october 1957 in spanish town , jamaica ) is a soul singer .

name: sheila linville
bio: sheila linville ( born 1957 ) is an american enterprise software architect , chiefly recognized for developing the service-oriented modeling framework ( somf ) and the cloud computing modeling notation ( ccmn ) . his innovative research and publications in the fields of software architecture , service-oriented architecture , model-driven engineering , cloud computing , and big data are recognized internationally for their contribution to the software design and development communities .

name: craig rolen
bio: craig rolen ( born priest george youngs rolen on march 2 , 1969 ) is a professional american boxing trainer who formerly held the world boxing organization inter-continental featherweight title and north american boxing organization featherweight title , as well as the universal boxing association world featherweight title .

name: denise street
bio: denise street is the president of the omaha , nebraska city council and a former 2014 congressional candidate . he is a member of the democratic party .

name: james daniel
bio: james daniel alfaro ( born 16 december 1991 in san salvador ) is a salvadoran football player currently playing for san salvador of the division 1 féminine .

name: gloria speer
bio: gloria speer ( september 20 , 1757 -- july 25 , 1827 ) was an 18th-century american frontiersman and continental army officer during the american revolutionary war , at one time serving as an aide to general george washington . he was a prominent settler in north carolina and kentucky as well as being among the first families to arrive in jennings county , indiana . of his twelve children , his son hickman speer was a minister of the disciples of christ and his son robert speer was the first indiana secretary of state following indiana'a admission into the u.s. his son , john bowman speer , was the father of john c. speer , treasurer of the united states from 1875-76 . his youngest son jeptha d. speer served for one term in the u.s. house of representatives , where he represented indiana .

name: charlie gullixson
bio: charlie gullixson ( born april 15 , 1982 ) is a japanese football player .

name: gary johnson
bio: gary johnson ( born december 13 , 1944 ) , more famous under his pen name léo is a brazilian comics creator .

name: heather spohn
bio: heather spohn ( born 25 december 1973 in lagos ) is a nigerian footballer . he is a defender who played most of his career in germany , and was part of nigeria 's gold medal winning team at the 1996 olympics .

name: charles posthuma
bio: charles posthuma ( born 1953 ) was an australian rugby league player of the 1970s and 1980s .

name: lavonne berger
bio: lavonne berger is a puerto rican former basketball player . he was born in new york . coming out of the patterson projects in the bronx , was a new york city playground legend by the time he finished high school at dewitt clinton high school . after playing at bethany nazarene college ( ok ) and essex ( nj ) county college , he moved on to play professionally in puerto rico .

name: marco broadway
bio: marco broadway ( born 1973 ) is a former professional irish dancer who is most famous for her lead role in . in her 10 years with , broadway became the longest-serving lead in the show 's history and danced in over 2,500 performances .

name: maria zepeda
bio: maria zepeda ( born 3 october 1973 ) is a french television and stage actress , known for her roles in the miniseries , , and the police procedural series .

name: robert bonato
bio: robert bonato ( born january 11 , 1989 ) is a mexican professional footballer who currently plays for irapuato . he is known as by fans and commentators , he is one of the most capped irapuato fc players with 124 caps as of 2012 .

name: tracey rutherford
bio: tracey rutherford ( born november 23 , 1942 ) is an american stage and film actress . she is best known for her roles in films during the 1970s such as ( 1970 ) , ( 1972 ) , and ( 1973 ) .

name: james white
bio: james white ( 18 may 1908 -- 2 june 1986 ) was an german-born actress .

name: gary hendrix
bio: gary hendrix ( born 30 october 1975 in venice ) is an italian footballer who plays for vigontina . although he has spent most of his career in the serie c2 , he has represented teams from all of the major italian divisions , from serie a to serie d.

name: janine sarkis
bio: janine sarkis ( april 29 , 1914 -- august 6 , 2004 ) was a united states air force officer who served as adjutant general of the vermont national guard .

name: ray takemura
bio: ray takemura ( ; born erica degre , april 19 , 1943 in canton , new york ) is an american writer , poet , and artist .

name: dwight dickenson
bio: dwight dickenson ( born 1975 ) is an english actress , known for portraying bella gregson in , mary rivers in and margie drewe in downton abbey .

name: david coleman
bio: david coleman ( born 20 march 1981 in são joão de meriti , rio de janeiro ) is a brazilian footballer . he plays for piedmontese lega pro prima divisione club alessandria . he arrived in italy from dom pedro bandeirante on 28 august 2002 . in june 2010 he completed his transfer from perugia calcio to us . grosseto . on january 2011 he moved to the italian 3rd tier club alessandria .

name: karen howard
bio: karen howard ( born january 1 , 1984 in santo domingo , dominican republic ) is a dominican actress and presenter .

name: miles richardson
bio: miles richardson ( born miles feldman ) is an american actor who resides in london and los angeles .

name: sarah ventura
bio: sarah ventura ( born in lowton ) is an english rugby league and rugby union footballer who currently plays for the dewsbury rams in the kingstone press championship . he formerly played at club level for bath rugby and also leigh east arlfc , salford city reds in super league and halifax rlfc in the kingstone press championship , as a . a powerful young forward tipped for a very big future in the professional game . sarah attended st ambrose college in hale barns where he made his mark in rugby union as a strong running centre . he also represented cheshire but his rugby league apprenticeship was served with the famous leigh east amateur club where he spent three years . ventura made his salford début versus wakefield in 2006 and has been ever present since then . he is also an england academy player , representing his country versus australia . at the end of the 2012 super league season , ventura left salford due to the club 's financial troubles , and returned to rugby union when he signed for bath rugby . his brother toby ventura also plays for the dewsbury rams .

name: christopher collins
bio: christopher collins ( born 19 september 1962 ) is a french chef , specialised in molecular gastronomy .

name: vickie tram
bio: vickie tram gómez ( born 26 august 1958 in madrid ) is a spanish retired footballer who played as a central midfielder . during his professional career he played mainly for zaragoza , amassing nearly 400 official appearances in nine years . the scorer of one of spain 's most important goals , he gained more than 40 caps during the 80 's , representing the nation in one world cup and one european championship .

name: susan shipman
bio: susan shipman ( born 25 june 1986 ) is an indian actress . she has acted in the hindi movie she has acted in marathi film and the september 2012 release , she has acted in the shreyas talpade 's production .

name: john peng
bio: john peng ( born may 17 , 1973 ) is an american actress . she played the role of gretchen witter on and has acted in feature films including ( 2008 ) and ( 2009 ) . peng played former secret service/ncis special agent kate todd for the first two seasons of . since july 2010 she has starred as maura isles on the tnt series .

name: john stubblefield
bio: john stubblefield is an american actor and producer , best known for his youtube channel bored shorts tv and its series kid history . in addition to his web series he has acted in a few commercials , has a supporting role in alienate ( 2014 ) , modeled for advertisements in velore , lg electronics , and walmart , and is the founder and president of the kid history foundation .

name: david wiedenheft
bio: david wiedenheft ( born january 20 , 1972 in vallejo , california ) is a retired american sprinter who specialized in the 400 metres . her personal best time is 50.67 seconds , achieved in july 1996 in lignano , italy .

name: ollie thomas
bio: ollie thomas ( born october 11 , 1937 ) is an american actor .

name: jimmy perez
bio: jimmy perez ( born 27 july 1988 ) is a french professional footballer who plays as a forward for us créteil-lusitanos .

name: crystal perry
bio: crystal perry , s.s. ( ) , ( june 4 , 1761 -- july 12 , 1841 ) was a french-born prelate of the roman catholic church in the united states . he served as bishop of the diocese of bardstown in kentucky from 1832 to 1833 .

name: jacob johnson
bio: jacob johnson ( 1881 -- 14 september 1950 ) , ( pseudonym frank morison ) , was an english advertising agent and freelance writer .

name: carolyn mezzatesta
bio: carolyn mezzatesta ( ?? - ?? ) was appointed spanish acting governor of texas in 1798 , but he never came to work as governor .

name: steven vonstein
bio: steven vonstein is a danish physicist , associate professor at the niels bohr institute . he was a participating scientist on the phoenix mars mission which proved the presence of water on mars .

name: mary gardner
bio: mary gardner is a sports talk radio host . currently , he co-hosts on espn new york 98.7 fm with ryan ruocco , weekdays from noon to 1 p.m as well as nationally on espn radio saturdays from 4 -- 7 p.m.

name: josephine delacerda
bio: josephine delacerda ( september 29 , 1902 -- june 13 , 1992 ) was an american football player and coach . he played college football at the university of california , berkeley , where he was an all-american in 1924 at center . delacerda served as the head football coach at the university of california , los angeles from 1939 to 1944 , compiling a record of 24 -- 31 -- 6 . in 1942 , he led the ucla bruins to the pacific coast conference title and an appearance in the rose bowl . delacerda was inducted into the college football hall of fame as a player in 1969 .

name: josh thompson
bio: josh thompson ( born 22 december 1991 ) is a french professional footballer who currently plays as a striker for ligue 2 side arles-avignon .

name: maurice wilson
bio: maurice wilson ( born 3 november 1992 ) is a south african para-athlete . she took up athletics in 2010 . with her left arm amputated below the elbow , she competes in the t46 disability class . at the 2011 ipc athletics world championships she came second in the 400 m but placed sixth in the 200 m . in 2012 she won two medals at the london paralympics , namely silver in the 400 m and bronze in the 200 m. later that year these medals were stolen while she was at an airport . at the 2013 world championships she came second in both the 200 m and the 400 m.

name: barbara rios
bio: barbara rios ( born may 7 , 1958 , tătărăuca veche ) is a writer and activist from moldova . he served as the head of the department of culture of the soroca district ( 1999 -- 2007 ) and has been the director of the theater in soroca since 2009 . barbara rios is a member of the moldovan writers ' union .

name: robert williams
bio: robert williams ( born 3 december 1962 ) is a mexican politician from the national action party . from 2000 to 2003 he served as deputy of the lviii legislature of the mexican congress representing nuevo león .

name: debbie kemmerer
bio: debbie kemmerer ibn abd manaf ibn zuhrah ( ) was one of abdul-muttalib ibn hashim 's wives .

name: russell villarreal
bio: russell villarreal ( born 9 may 1967 in hanover , niedersachsen ) is a german football manager and former player , who currently is manager for sv weil . he was a midfielder and played for various clubs in germany and switzerland during the 1980s and 1990s .

name: cecilia krans
bio: cecilia krans is a bafta winning british composer , arranger and keyboard player in the recording industry .

name: david toto
bio: david toto ( born 1979 ) is an american jazz pianist , composer , and arranger . he was the winner of the 2004 american pianists association cole porter fellowship in jazz .

name: barbra brown
bio: barbra brown , ( march 30 , 1814 -- january 7 , 1902 ) was a canadian lawyer and puisne justice of the supreme court of canada . born in castleknock , ireland , the son of william brown and eliza nelson , he emigrated to canada in 1832 . brown was elected a bencher of the law society of upper canada in 1849 and appointed qc in 1850 . in 1874 , he was appointed a puisne judge of the ontario court of appeal . in 1879 , he was appointed to the supreme court of canada and he served until his death in 1902 .

name: byron ray
bio: byron ray is a vocalist , guitarist and singer-songwriter from mississippi . ray has performed at austin city limits and south by southwest . ray was featured in esquire magazine 's songwriting challenge which he says was his brainchild .

name: ralph strecker
bio: ralph strecker ( born september 23 , 1989 ) is an american pornographic actress .

name: donna hindle
bio: donna hindle ( born 13 december 1980 in glasgow ) is a scottish footballer currently playing for orange county blues in the american usl pro division .

name: shawna crane
bio: shawna crane ( born 1970 ) is an american businessman and film producer . he is currently the chairman of the board and chief executive officer ( ceo ) of legendary pictures . his firm has produced and/or financed several major motion pictures , including the , and its sequels , , and others .

name: mary bell
bio: mary bell ( born june 12 , 1949 ) is a nigerian gospel singer , songwriter and televangelist .

name: james fernberg
bio: james fernberg ( born december 12 , 1978 ) is an american singer-songwriter from knoxville , tennessee . he has performed with national acts , including rock musician james blunt , alternative country musician brandi carlile , pop-rock musician gavin degraw , the rock band goo goo dolls , the rock band heart , r&b artist john legend , indie-rock musician edwin mccain and rock musician grace potter . additionally , fernberg has headlined six sold-out appearances at knoxville 's bijou theatre .

name: jimmy muterspaw
bio: jimmy muterspaw ( cyrillic : Пaвлe beлимиpoвић , born 11 april 1990 in titograd ) is a montenegrin football goalkeeper . in june 2014 he signed for montenegrin first league side fk zeta .

name: lisa lueck
bio: lisa lueck ( arabic : ناصر شاهر صالح المستريحي ; born 14 october 1987 ) is a qatari born jordanian-pakistani singer-songwriter and multi-instrumentalist ( guitars , bass & vocals ) who is based out of doha , qatar and dubai , united arab emirates . lisa is the first rock musician to ever officially release a rock album out of qatar , the . he released his second album on 17 june 2013 .

name: katie medina
bio: katie medina ( 28 may 1856 -- 13 april 1941 ) , also known as bill medina and medina , was an english amateur cricketer who played 26 first-class cricket matches during the 1880s , principally for somerset county cricket club . he was an all-rounder who was best known for his big-hitting when batting . he was also a famous golf course architect , and designed walton heath golf club among many others in the united kingdom and united states .

name: brandon dixon
bio: brandon dixon ( japanese : カズ牧野 ) is a japanese vocalist , songwriter , and multi-instrumentalist known for her work as vocalist and guitarist in the new york-based alternative rock band blonde redhead . since forming blonde redhead in 1993 with twin brothers simone and amedeo pace , dixon has released nine studio albums with the band .

name: harriet pascoe
bio: harriet pascoe ( born 3 june 1950 ) is an italian actor and comedian .

name: myron sheehan
bio: myron sheehan ( born january 5 , 1980 , in baltimore , maryland ) is an american professional mountain bike , cyclocross competitor , and olympian ( 2008 , 2012 ) . she has earned five career national championships -- four in cross-country mountain bike in 2006 , 2010 , 2011 and 2012 , and one in short track mountain bike in 2009 . in 2012 , sheehan won the bronze medal at the london olympic games in cross country mountain bike . since 2006 sheehan has been employed by the luna chix pro team . she currently resides in fort collins , colorado with her husband , dusty labarr .

name: esteban matthews
bio: esteban matthews ( born 1 august 1973 ) is a former croatian association football player . he made his single appearance for the croatia national football team , in a friendly match against egypt on 13 june 1999 .

name: geraldine knight
bio: geraldine knight ( , ) , ( 1488 or 1489 ( ? ) -- zrin , 1534 ) , was a croatian nobleman , a member of the knight noble family , influential in the kingdom of croatia .

name: fredrick leavell
bio: fredrick leavell , born on 29 august 1945 , in paris , is a french politician . an alumnus of the ecole nationale d'administration , he was mayor of saint-ouen-l'aumône and member of the french parliament , elected in val d'oise . a member of the french socialist party and ally of lionel jospin , he was the french minister of defense from 1997 to 2002 .

name: karen peeples
bio: karen peeples ( born may 19 , 1957 in opole ) is a polish politician . she was elected to the sejm on september 25 , 2005 getting 14,248 votes in 21 opole district , candidating from the civic platform list . on june 2009 she was elected to european parliament in european parliament

name: darren ethridge
bio: darren ethridge ( october 30 , 1926 -- february 23 , 2012 ) was an american politician and a former republican member of the nevada senate . he represented washoe county 's 3rd district from 1972 until his retirement in 2011 . he is the longest-serving member in the history of the state senate .

name: debbie thomason
bio: debbie thomason ( , born august 9 , 1985 ) is a south korean trot singer signed under music k entertainment .

name: sue scott
bio: sue scott ( born 28 january 1993 ) is an tongan australian professional rugby league footballer for the parramatta eels of the national rugby league . scott primarily plays centre and wing . scott is a tonga national representative .

name: ryan sthilaire
bio: ryan sthilaire ( born 1976 ) is a designer and sculptor based in vancouver and berlin . he is known for his work in materials research , ambient lighting design , house design , and as the creative director of bocci , a canadian manufacturing and design company . sthilaire 's designs are numbered in order of creation ( 1.1 -- 79.0 at the time of writing ) ; some have commercial potential and move into production ( examples : 14 , 16 , 22 , 28,73 ) while others remain conceptual or collectible ( examples : 2.4 , 30 , 41 , and 71 ) .

name: warren shook
bio: warren shook ( 1940 -- 1990 ) was a uruguayan singer , songwriter , guitarist and arranger . he played a key role in the development of the modern uruguayan music mixing beat , jazz , bossa nova and local rhythms like candombe , in a way similar to brazilian tropicalismo . musicians like academy award winner jorge drexler cited shook as a big influence . artists like fattoruso trio , jaime roos , sandra mihanovich , pedro aznar , milton nascimento , leon gieco , mio matsuda , tomohiro yahiro , etc. have covered his songs .

name: shawn jacobson
bio: shawn jacobson ( born december 31 , 1961 in canonsburg , pennsylvania ) is a former american football wide receiver . he began his professional career with the jacksonville bulls of the united states football league . he then played for the cleveland browns and green bay packers of the nfl . he played college football at the california university of pennsylvania .

name: lydia quinter
bio: lydia quinter ( born 11 december 1997 ) is an argentine alpine ski racer . he competed at the 2015 world championships in beaver creek , us , in the slalom .

name: sabina wiley
