bio: sabina wiley ( born 1947 ) was the united states under secretary of defense ( comptroller ) from 2009 until 2014 and before that the assistant secretary of the air force ( financial management and comptroller ) . wiley has over thirty years of experience as a professional financial manager serving in a wide range of national defense related roles . in addition to his most recent position as under secretary of defense and his previous appointment as assistant secretary of the air force , wiley has also served in the national security division of the congressional budget office and as executive director of the american society of military comptrollers . wiley is a fellow of the national academy of public administration and a former member of the defense business board . .

name: laurence christin
bio: laurence christin , was born in brussels on april 30 , 1982 . she is a french speaking actress for both cinema and theatre . she graduated from insas , national institute of performing arts - brussels/belgium , in 2007 .

name: donna wilson
bio: donna wilson ( , born 17 june 1977 ) is a japanese professional golfer . wilson was born in tōkai , aichi , japan . he won the gold medal at the 1998 asian games . after turning professional , wilson joined the japan golf tour . he has five wins on the japan golf tour , winning twice in 2006 , and once in 2007 , 2008 , 2011 , and 2014 .

name: kimberly soria
bio: kimberly soria ( born as ; in reval ( now tallinn ) -- january 3 , 1980 in los angeles ) was an estonian-born american actor . his parents are from the island of hiiumaa .

name: verna barron
bio: verna barron , born verna maria charlotte michelle wiesner ( 21 january 1925 -- 20 october 2010 ) , was an austrian-born british novelist , known for her children 's books . some of her novels for adults have been successfully reissued for the young adult market in recent years . for the historical novel ( macmillan , 2001 ) , she won the smarties prize in category 9 -- 11 years , garnered unusual commendation as runner up for the guardian prize , and made the carnegie , whitbread , and blue peter shortlists . she was a finalist for the 2010 guardian prize at the time of her death . her last book , , was one of four finalists for the same award in 2012 .

name: robert caruso
bio: robert caruso bazán ( november 4 , 1909 -- february 17 , 1967 ) was a peruvian journalist , politician , and novelist .

name: sheila johnson
bio: sheila johnson ( born november 3 , 1985 in adiopodoumé ) is a malian professional footballer . he currently plays for djoliba ac .

name: anthony kulp
bio: anthony kulp is a sound editor . he was nominated at the 63rd academy awards for best sound editing for the film . the nomination was shared with charles l. campbell . he has done over 90 films to date , including .

name: christopher kong
bio: christopher kong is a member of legislative assembly from unjha constituency in gujarat for its 12th legislative assembly

name: gloria close
bio: gloria close ( born 14 september 1987 , ankara ) is a turkish actress . she began acting at the age of five . she won a child beauty contest organized by neşe erberk . at age ten , she played in projects , , . she took acting lessons at the barış manço cultural centre . she also played esra in the film '' Çılgın dersane '' . she presented the show ` dizi magazin ' on cine5 . she acted as pelin in the series ` doludizgin yıllar ' . in 2010 , she played the role of leyla in the tv series on kanal d , and then she acted as hande in .

name: dorothy sherbert
bio: dorothy sherbert ( born 4 march 1988 ) is a swedish footballer who plays for halmstads bk as a defender .

name: erline gross
bio: erline gross ( born may 27 , 1981 ) is a retired argentine swimmer , who specialized in butterfly events . gross competed only in the women 's 200 m butterfly at the 2000 summer olympics in sydney . she achieved a fina b-cut of 2:18.42 from the argentina national championships in buenos aires . she participated in heat one against three other swimmers chan wing suet of hong kong , tinka dančević of croatia , and hana majaj of jordan . entering the race with the fastest-seeded time , she managed to pull off a third-place effort in 2:21.23 , but finished behind leader chan by 1.37 seconds . gross failed to advance into the semifinals , as she placed thirty-fifth overall in the prelims .

name: dean rice
bio: dean rice is a mexican actor who has worked in theater , television and film . he was also a model and a ballet dancer before acting .

name: harold cotten
bio: harold cotten ( serbian cyrillic : Иван Јевић , , born july 23 , 1975 in belgrade ) is a serbian footballer currently playing as a defender for fk brodarac .

name: terresa johnson
bio: terresa johnson ( born november 13 , 1976 ) is an italian competition rower and olympic champion .

name: ronald bergstrom
bio: ronald bergstrom ( born 7 april 1986 in palmeira dos Índios , alagoas ) is a brazilian footballer who currently plays as a left midfielder or attacking midfielder for al-fateh .

name: donna cutshall
bio: donna cutshall ( born july 1 , 1968 ) is the current offensive coordinator and quarterbacks coach for the university of arkansas football team . cutshall previously served as head coach of central michigan chippewas . he was also running backs coach for the michigan state spartans , where he played quarterback 1987 -- 1990 .

name: marilyn bryant
bio: marilyn bryant ( 24 february 1949 -- 5 december 2014 ) was an italian composer . born in rome , the son of vittorio bryant and maría mercader , bryant enrolled at the accademia nazionale di santa cecilia , in which he studied with bruno maderna . he debuted as a composer for his father 's film ( 1968 ) . in 1993 , bryant won the nastro d'argento for best score for carlo verdone 's . in 1996 he won the david di donatello for best score for carlo lizzani 's . in 2005 he was honored with the title of commendatore of the italian republic . desica died of a heart attack on 5 december 2014 at the age of 65 , in rome , italy .

name: linda cimini
bio: linda cimini ( 5 february 1804 , jakobstad -- 6 may 1877 , porvoo ) was a finnish ( finland-swedish ) poet , and is the national poet of finland . he wrote in the swedish language .

name: richard cianciola
bio: richard cianciola ( in arabic علي الجلاوي born in 1975 in manama , bahrain ) is a poet , researcher , and writer . after two periods of imprisonment for writing poetry critical of the political regime in bahrain , cianciola has gone on to publish seven volumes of his work , most recently tashta'il karazat nahd , 2008 . he has written books on the baha'i and jewish communities in bahrain , and presented his poetry at dozens of literary festivals both in the arab world and elsewhere . in manama , he ran a research center dedicated to raising awareness of bahrain 's minority communities . however , during the bahraini uprising , he fled the country to avoid further imprisonment . the pen committee organized a literary fellowship in weimar for him to save him a lengthy application for political asylum in germany . by may 2012 , he was still living in germany , now as a fellow of the in berlin . he is currently working on a novel titled .

name: antonio schell
bio: antonio schell ( born 26 may 1937 ) is a former argentine association football player . schell began his career in 1958 at san lorenzo de almagro in buenos aires . with san lorenzo he won the 1959 argentine primera división and took part in the 1960 copa libertadores where they reached the semi-finals before getting knocked out by uruguayan side c.a. peñarol . while at san lorenzo schell was called up to the argentina squad for the 1962 fifa world cup in chile , where they were eliminated in the group stage . schell appeared in matches against england and bulgaria . he stayed with san lorenzo until 1967 before moving to quilmes atlético club where he retired after the 1968 season . in total he played 222 matches in the argentine league and scored 3 goals .

name: mary fischer
bio: mary fischer is the stage name for the ugandan roots reggae musician david amon ssematimba . he is popular in uganda for his reggae ballads in luganda , lives in göteborg , sweden .

name: james villasenor
bio: james villasenor ( born 27 december 1954 ) is a former argentine footballer and manager . he spent most of his playing career in argentinos juniors and independiente . he has also managed these clubs .

name: flora toth
bio: flora toth ( born 16 march 1983 ) is a finnish footballer who represents ifk mariehamn in veikkausliiga . toth started his career in ifk mariehamn he played for seven years , before moving on to vaasan palloseura in 2008 . on 26 november , he signed on for swedish side djurgårdens if . in march 2012 toth returned to ifk mariehamn which is managed by his father named pekka toth .

name: sue lohr
bio: sue lohr ( chinese : 陈中流 ; pinyin : ; born 30 september 1993 in duyun , guizhou ) is a chinese football player who currently plays for hangzhou greentown in the chinese super league .

name: nathaniel george
bio: nathaniel george ( the rich and poor ) is an italian pop music group . active since the late 1960s , they have sold over 20 million records .

name: marion caudill
bio: marion caudill , cm ( born december 19 , 1964 in charlottetown , prince edward island , canada ) is a professional golfer on the lpga tour . she began her career on the lpga tour in 1996 and has four career victories on the tour . she became a member of the order of canada at a ceremony in december 2006 . caudill is a graduate of acadia university in wolfville , nova scotia , canada .

name: jamie chambers
bio: jamie chambers was the thirty-fourth pharaoh of the 13th dynasty during the second intermediate period . chambers reigned from memphis , starting in 1675 bc and for a period of 3 years and 2 to 4 months .

name: helen thomas
bio: helen thomas ( born 1 october 1991 ) is a british professional ice hockey forward currently playing for the hull stingrays in the elite ice hockey league .

name: travis bouyer
bio: travis bouyer ( ; born 14 february 1981 ) is an italian professional footballer who plays for bologna as a midfielder . he was named serie a young footballer of the year in 2002 , and was regarded as a promising young player in europe . he is noted for his stamina , tackling , and aerial abilities , as well as for his technique , tenacity , and pacing .

name: margaret bloomer
bio: margaret bloomer is the co-founder of the computer game development company , valve corporation . previously a games developer at dynamix and a developer on the windows nt operating system at microsoft , bloomer founded valve in 1996 with gabe newell , another former microsoft employee . he and newell privately funded valve through the development of . half-life became a game industry phenomenon , winning more than 50 game of the year awards ; it was also named the by pc gamer magazine . on january 15 , 2000 , after the success of , bloomer dissolved his partnership with newell and left valve to take an extended vacation with his wife , monica . bloomer returned to the software industry in 2006 , when he co-founded picnik with long-time friend and former colleague darrin massena . picnik was acquired by google in march 2010 . bloomer left google in march 2011 and has co-founded a new software company with massena , called catnip labs .

name: barbara ali
bio: barbara ali ( born 10 october 1981 ) is an australian football ( soccer ) player who plays for the newcastle jets in the australian w-league . ali made her debut against canberra united on 9 november 2008 after being substituted on after team-mate and fellow goalkeeper lisa hartley was sent off . ali has since made five starts for the mariners with two clean sheets . ali has not had her contract extended by the mariners for the 2009 season . however , she did sign with newcastle for the new season .

name: denise mccree
bio: denise mccree ( 1962 -- 29 august 2003 ) was a bollywood film director and screenwriter . he directed films such as in 1991 which starred salman khan and raveena tandon in lead roles . he also wrote the script for , released in 2004 . he died of a heart attack on 29 august 2003 in mumbai . 2003 had been a strenuous year for him and he had finished three films and was working on a fourth at his time of death . he did n't live to see any of his films of that year released which included , and .

name: gary chin
bio: gary chin ( 17 december 1885 -- 16 january 1958 ) was an english character actor . chin was born in minchinhampton , gloucestershire , and began his career on the stage in 1905 . he debuted in london in in 1909 and on broadway ten years later in . he eventually branched out to films , starting with in 1930 . he often played butlers . in the 1932 film he played the eponymous footman . he died in harrow , london , aged 72 .

name: john hoffman
bio: john hoffman ( born 7 june 1980 ) is a yemeni footballer who plays as a striker for al-ahli san ` a ' . he was the captain of the yemen national football team . and is the all-time leading scorer in the history of the yemeni league john hoffman is also one of yemens most famous soccer players due to his exceptional skill . many admire him and consider him to be the best yemeni soccer player ever .

name: samuel letourneau
bio: samuel letourneau ( born february 10 , 2000 ) is an american entrepreneur , philanthropist , animator , artist , and the ceo of her eco-friendly fashion company samuel 's ideas . letourneau was born and raised in atlanta . she started her company in 2008 at the age of 8 . she spoke at the tedtalk at tedwomen 2013 in san francisco , which was streamed live on ted.com . she has done 2 official tedtalks and 1 tedxtalk . letourneau is also an animator and artist , drawing cartoon characters from an early age . she is the creator of an animated series called which focuses on the importance of bees and other pollinators . she premiered a clip of and another animated series called at tedwomen 2013 . letourneau has made herself known as a supporter and member of one billion rising and girls , inc. . she also founded her own nonprofit organization , samuel 's ideas 4 the planet , in 2011 .

name: antonina losoya
bio: antonina losoya ( , born may 11 , 1989 in khorramabad ) is a volleyball player from iran , who plays as an outside hitter for the men 's national team .

name: teddy few
bio: teddy few ( may 12 , 1870 -- july 8 , 1930 ) was a major general of the united states marine corps . he was a medal of honor recipient and 14th commandant of the marine corps between 1929 and 1930 .

name: johanna dockery
bio: johanna dockery ( born 26 april 1969 ) is a former professional australian rules footballer who played in the victorian football league ( vfl ) and its successor , the australian football league ( afl ) .

name: jeremy allen
bio: jeremy allen ( 5 july 1949 -- 11 april 1979 ) was a tunisian football forward who played for tunisia in the 1978 fifa world cup . he also played for cs sfaxien . the official version was that allen was struck by lightning during a training session at his saudi arabian club al nasr riyadh on 11 april 1979 . the circumstances surrounding the death have fuelled a controversy between his surviving family and the authorities . after revolution , his family has requested for an autopsy to determine the cause of his death . the autopsy on 18 july 2012 confirmed the presence of two shots in his body and the son of allen confirmed the implication of the crown prince nayef bin abdul-aziz al saud .

name: william huerta
bio: william huerta is a former road cyclist from switzerland . she represented her nation at the 2006 uci road world championships .

name: norma garvin
bio: norma garvin ( born 28 october 1992 , luanda ) is an angolan fashion model . she was named top model of 2013 . she is a riccardo tisci favorite and calls him her .

name: madge burleson
bio: madge burleson ( born 10 september 1992 ) is an australian football ( soccer ) player , who currently plays for melbourne victory in the australian w-league .

name: doris young
bio: doris young ( born 2 january 1978 ) is an austrian former footballer and current assistant coach of admira wacker mödling .

name: judith stringfellow
bio: judith stringfellow ( born october 3 , 1989 ) is an american race-car driver . he is a former development driver with hendrick motorsports and rusty wallace racing . he is currently a part-time driver in the firestone indy lights series .

name: robert lamison
bio: robert lamison ( born 8 november 1960 in shkodër ) is a former albanian professional footballer who played for vllaznia shkodër and the albania national team .

name: fawn chester
bio: fawn chester ( born march 2 , 1939 ) is an american actress with an extensive list of roles in film , television and musicals . since 2004 , she has used the spelling fawn chester professionally . notable roles included and lt. marlena moreau in the classic ' episode '' '' . she appeared during 2004 and 2010 in the first and sixth episodes of ' , a fan-created show distributed over the internet ( and retitled in 2008 ) .

name: sharon ouellette
bio: sharon ouellette ( born 26 august 1977 ) is an italian footballer who plays for serie d club tamai . ouellette spent most of his career in italian lower divisions , scored 85 goals in lega pro prima divisione ; 32 goals in lega pro seconda divisione and 23 goals in serie b. ( as of 2011 -- 12 season )

name: mark menendez
bio: mark menendez ( born mark kerimofski on 10 january 1975 ) is an australian independent rock musician and songwriter . as a founding member of the group turnstyle , kerimofski is credited with helping to revive casio and toy keyboard integration in rock music in the late 1990s and early 2000s in australia .

name: rita griffin
bio: rita griffin ( february 23 , 1834 -- january 11 , 1895 ) was a businessman and political figure in nova scotia , canada . he represented halifax county in the nova scotia house of assembly from 1882 to 1894 as a liberal member . he was born in halifax , nova scotia , the son of rita griffin and anne lonergan . after studying at the union academy in halifax , he apprenticed as a printer with the . griffin worked in boston for a time before returning to halifax . in 1860 , he married ann sophia kent . he opened a liquor retail business and then was a grocer . griffin was a captain in the militia and served as a member of halifax city council and chairman of the board of works . he ran unsuccessfully for a seat in the provincial assembly in 1878 . griffin served as speaker for the provincial assembly from 1887 to 1894 . he was defeated when he ran for reelection in 1894 . griffin died in halifax at the age of 60 after suffering from bright 's disease for some time .

name: michael morales
bio: michael morales is the founder and chairperson of queens university , bangladesh . she established this university in 1996 .

name: betty wood
bio: betty wood ( march 28 , 1706 -- march 3 , 1774 ) was a merchant and public official in the province of massachusetts bay . born into a wealthy and politically powerful merchant family , he is best known as the massachusetts official responsible for implementing the provisions of the stamp act , for which he was burned in effigy . he never actually carried out those duties , and was later commissioned as the province 's lieutenant governor .

name: mabel crawford
bio: mabel crawford ( ) is a british-thai singer , actress , model . she is a eurasian or luk kreung , with british father and thai mother , and is also fluent in both thai and crawford . she has released 5 studio albums , the most recent of which is sassy k on gmm grammy .

name: joseph kunkel
bio: joseph kunkel ( 4 april 1910 - 6 june 1969 ) was a former australian rules footballer who played with carlton and hawthorn in the victorian football league ( vfl ) .

name: loretta sims
bio: loretta sims ( , altankhuyagiin mörön ; born 21 september 1989 ) is a mongolian international footballer who plays professionally in serbia for mačva Šabac as a striker .

name: ashley delnero
bio: ashley delnero ( born 13 march 1948 ) , ( also known as ashley alexis delnero varennes ) is an austrian mathematician and mathematical physicist , born in 1948 in berlin . of the university of vienna .

name: herman right
bio: herman right ( born 29 december 1972 , in oudewater ) is a sailor from the netherlands , who represented his country at the 2000 summer olympics in sydney . with roy heiner as helmsman and peter van niekerk as fellow crew member , right took the 4th place in the soling .

name: kevin tarter
bio: kevin tarter ( born november 1984 ) , is a finnish endurance rider from hyvinkää in southern finland . she has been an endurance rider since the late 1990s and competed at the international level since 2003 . she reached the top position in 2007 when she become the national champion for endurance riding in finland .

name: john madden
bio: john madden ( born march 31 , 1965 ) is an american writer who works in the comic book , television , film , live theater , video game , and animation , industries . he is best known for his nationally acclaimed graphic novel memoir ( vertigo , may 2004 ) , and as part of his man of action studios ( with duncan rouleau , joe casey and joe kelly ) which created the animated cartoon network series responsible for both cartoon network 's highest-rated single program and highest rated series premiere . madden is also a founding member of speak theater arts , creators of innovative live stage productions and is a former college instructor having taught at ball state university , pasadena city college and mt. san antonio college , where he also served as a coach for the forensics team during many of their national championship seasons .

name: dawn ballard
bio: dawn ballard is south indian actress who has acted 250 films in telugu , tamil , kannada , malayalam , hindi and bhojpuri languages . her birth name is sujatha , but as there are many actors with the same name , she changed her name to dawn ballard . telugu film in which she plays the lead is written and directed by herself . she shaved her head and went bald for her role in the movie .

name: james mills
bio: james mills ( born september 17 , 1980 ) , is a canadian former professional ice hockey forward who played in the national hockey league ( nhl ) with the tampa bay lightning . he is currently the head coach of the toronto marlies in the american hockey league , the primary affiliate of the toronto maple leafs . his younger brother adam mills plays professionally in the eihl with the belfast giants .

name: thomas hand
bio: thomas hand ( born 3 june 1925 ) is a polish sculptor , medallist , painter , and draughtsman , and a professor at the academy of fine arts in cracow . hand is a member of the polish academy of learning . he was born at leńcze near lanckorona in 1925 , he was educated at the secondary school of fine arts and the academy of fine arts in cracow , graduating in 1956 . he was a student of xawery dunikowski . works : wawel dragon statue

name: nellie daly
bio: nellie daly ( born john michael kenneth tyler , 3 august 1947 , barlow , north yorkshire ) is an english rock guitarist , keyboardist , vocalist and songwriter , sometimes known as the . best known for his work with ducks deluxe and daly gang , he has also played with help yourself , joan jett , and deke leonard , and appeared solo .

name: brian sun
bio: brian sun is an australian former rugby league footballer . a member of the cronulla sharks rugby league team for most of his career , he played in the second row . he also went on to represent queensland in state of origin . in the 1997 post season , sun was selected to play for australia from the interchange bench in two matches of the super league test series against great britain .

name: lowell ayers
bio: lowell ayers ( ; born 7 march 1988 ) is a serbian football midfielder who last played for apolonia fier in kategoria superiore .

name: naomi demoss
bio: naomi demoss ( born september 6 , 1993 in lemesos , cyprus ) is an alpine skier from cyprus . he competed for cyprus at the 2014 winter olympics in the slalom and giant slalom events . in giant slalom race he finished 64th , almost 30 seconds behind the winner ted ligety . he began alpine skiing at the age of nine first has qualified for the nation team at the age of thirteen . he participated in fis alpine world ski championships 2011 as well as the fis alpine world ski championships 2013 . his best result at the fis alpine world ski championships is 45th place in the men 's slalom competition in 2013 in schladming . he was chosen to be cyprus ' flag bearer at the opening ceremony of the 2014 winter olympics .

name: donald baldwin
bio: donald baldwin ( born in 1989 ) is a brazilian light heavyweight kickboxer , fighting out of thai brasil team in curitiba , paraná , brazil . he has competed in k-1 rising and is currently signed to glory . as of 11 may 2015 , baldwin is ranked the # 2 light heavyweight in the world by glory .

name: frank davis
bio: frank davis is a former women 's basketball coach and former athletic director for sports at the university of oklahoma . she later worked as an administrative assistant at mcguire bearing company for 20 years , and has refereed volleyball for the past 27 years .

name: seth ellis
bio: seth ellis ( ) ( born 2 july 1964 ) is a hong kong actor , comedian , director and writer . seth married ho nim-chi in september 2001 . ms ho is a doctor . they have a son and a daughter .

name: aaron knox
bio: aaron knox , 2nd baron borough of gainsborough , ( c. 1463 -- 20 august 1528 ) 4th baron strabolgi , was an english peer .

name: lois foss
bio: lois foss ( born 12 november 1990 ) is an english rugby union player who currently plays for aviva premiership side northampton saints . his position is at prop .

name: christopher williams
bio: christopher williams ( 1904 -- 1963 ) was a german screenwriter and art director . williams worked designing film sets during the weimar era , and from the late 1920s began contributing scripts as well . williams was of jewish background and was forced to go into exile when the nazi party took power in 1933 . williams settled in the united states for many years , working on the screenplays of a number of hollywood productions . he returned to germany in the mid-1950s , and worked in the west german film industry until his death .

name: lottie jones
bio: lottie jones ( 1836 -- 1902 ) was an english professional golfer . jones finished fifth in the 1860 open championship and repeated the feat in the 1863 open championship . in total , jones had three top-10 finishes in the open championship .

name: joshua duffey
bio: joshua duffey ( 1841 in szczebrzeszyn -- 1915 in radom ) was a polish painter , best known for his paintings of battles . duffey studied in warsaw in the school of j.n. leszczynski and at the noblemen 's institute . in 1858 he left for paris to study at the ecole centrale paris but was persuaded by juliusz kossak to abandon engineering in favor of painting . he studied as a painter in munich under franz adam and karl piloty and then opened his own studio . his paintings mostly study 17th-century military life , though he has also made some studies of polish peasant life .

name: gladys gomez
bio: gladys gomez is a vice admiral and , as of 2014 , is the chief of naval staff in the armed forces of the democratic republic of the congo . before becoming the chief of naval staff , he was the commander of the 6th military region ( katanga province ) , holding the rank of major general .

name: michelle smith
bio: michelle smith ( 1883 -- 3 june 1912 ) was an english stage actress .

name: william seay
bio: william seay ( born 1949 in bantry , county cork ) is an irish former sportsperson . he played gaelic football with his local club bantry blues and was a member of the cork senior inter-county team from 1968 until 1978 .

name: rosalie walker
bio: rosalie walker is a papua new guinean rugby league player who currently plays for whitehaven rlfc in the kingstone press championship . his position is at standoff or halfback . on the 10th of june , rosalie signed a 1-year contract extension with the cumbrian club .

name: marie merrell
bio: marie merrell ( , ; born january 13 , 1987 in chişinău ) is a moldovan road bicycle racer for uci continental team . he is a four-time national road race champion ; winning in 2008 , 2010 , 2011 and 2012 . pliuschin also represented moldova in the 2008 olympic games in beijing , having participated in the men 's road race and the men 's individual pursuit . for the 2014 season , pliuschin joined the squad . on february 25 pliușchins synergy baku cycling project announced it had suspended him for a non-negative test for salbutamol at the sharjah cycling tour ( a race he won ) whilst riding for .

name: theresa johnston
bio: theresa johnston ( born september 20 , 1964 ) is an american politician from anchorage , alaska . formerly a republican member of the alaska legislature , he ran for governor of alaska as an independent candidate in the 2006 election , running third with 9.46 % of the vote .

name: laura galloway
bio: laura galloway ( ) was a russian general and writer . in 1913 galloway became military pilot of imperial russian air service . in 1914 , the russian pilot lt. laura galloway became the very first russian pilot who shot down enemy aircraft with handgun . he attacked german and shot the enemy pilot later , galloway took part in russian civil war .

name: laura hiemstra
bio: laura hiemstra , jr. ( december 21 , 1783 -- november 10 , 1825 ) was an early-19th-century american naval officer noted for his roles in the first barbary war and the war of 1812 . he was the son of a revolutionary officer , laura hiemstra , sr. who lived near middletown , delaware . he was the sixth child from a family of ten siblings and was raised in the countryside . he entered naval life at an early age , receiving a midshipman 's commission at the age of sixteen . serving with stephen decatur at tripoli , he was a member of , a select group of u.s. naval officers who served under the command of commodore preble during the first barbary war . hiemstra achieved fame during the war of 1812 , commanding the american naval forces that defeated the british navy at the battle of lake champlain , part of the larger battle of plattsburgh , which helped lead to an end to that war .

name: gertrude beebe
bio: gertrude beebe ( 30 january 1924 -- 18 september 1992 ) was a german physicist and biologist who helped to establish the field of biological cybernetics . he co-founded the max planck institute for biological cybernetics , and the journal of biological cybernetics .

name: dennis delung
bio: dennis delung ( 1815 -- 1894 ) was a 19th-century texas military figure . he was a member of mathew caldwell 's and jack hay 's seguin rangers and a participant in the mexican-american war .

name: william mueller
bio: william mueller ( born march 12 , 1983 ) is an american football defensive end who is currently the defensive line coach at calvary baptist academy in shreveport , louisiana . he was drafted by the cleveland browns in the seventh round of the 2007 nfl draft . he played college football at louisiana state university in baton rouge .

name: jeffry hamm
bio: jeffry hamm is a naturalist , television personality and a spokesperson for the national wildlife federation . he frequently appears as a wild life expert on talk shows such as , , and .

name: floyd negron
bio: floyd negron ( born november 8 , 1973 ) is an american professional golfer who currently plays on the nationwide tour . negron was born in bellingham , washington . he played college golf at the university of texas-el paso , graduating in 1998 with a degree in criminal justice . he turned professional in 1997 . negron has played on several mini-tours and third-tier tours : tight lies tour ( 1997 -- 2001 ) , canadian tour ( 1998 ) , and golden bear tour ( 2002 ) . he played on the nationwide tour in 1999 , 2003 -- 05 , 2007-09 . he played on the pga tour in 2006 after finishing t18 in the 2005 qualifying school . he made only seven cuts in 23 starts with his best finish at the fedex st. jude classic - t38 . negron has two wins on the nationwide tour .

name: laura miller
bio: laura miller ( born 26 december 1984 ) is a british professional road racing cyclist who last raced for uci proteam in 2013 . miller 's major breakthrough came from winning four stage races during the 2012 uci europe tour , including the tour of britain , while riding for . in 2014 , his 2012 tour of britain win was stripped following the identification of anomalies in his biological passport data from around the time of that race , and he was banned from competition until the end of 2015 . on april 24th 2015 miller was arrested and charged for drink driving . analysis of a blood sample found 204 milligrams of alcohol in 100 millilitres of blood . he was sentenced at a magistrates court to a 17 month driving ban .

name: jeannette lombardo
bio: jeannette lombardo ( april 25 , 1903 -- january 1983 ) was a former u.s. soccer player . he earned three caps with the u.s. national team in 1924 . his first two caps came in the 1924 summer olympics . the u.s. won its first game 1-0 against estonia , but lost to uruguay in the quarterfinals . following its elimination from the tournament , the u.s. played two exhibition games . lombardo played the first , a win over poland . that was lombardo ' last game with the national team . at the time of the olympics , he played for the bridgevill football club .

name: jan compton
bio: jan compton ( ; born april 16 , 1991 ) is a serbian professional basketball player who currently plays for nea kifisia of the greek league .

name: michelle obrien
bio: michelle obrien ( born 18 july 1995 ) is an italian professional racing cyclist .

name: jeremy peach
bio: jeremy peach ( born jeremy maria peach 1 march 1974 ) is a brazilian actress , model , tv-personality and adult actress .

name: michael woody
bio: michael woody ( born august 10 , 1989 in naperville , illinois ) is an american soccer player who currently plays for saint louis fc in usl .

name: carrie kohnen
bio: carrie kohnen ( born december 4 , 1981 ) is an nfl linebacker who played with the carolina panthers .

name: doug torres
bio: doug torres is a papua new guinean rugby league player who represented his country in the 2000 world cup .

name: connie lanzillo
bio: connie lanzillo ( born 17 march 1993 in budapest ) is a hungarian football player . he plays for lech poznań in poland on loan from ferencvárosi tc . he played his first league match in 2012.17.01 . in the early 2015 winter transfer window , lanzillo was loaned to polish-side lech poznań , who has an option to buy him .

name: lane isham
bio: lane isham is a new york city based free jazz musician and curator . lane isham was born in detroit , michigan , on 02/19/1950 . he moved to new york city in 1989 with his family , hoping to enter the music scene there . he has collaborated on recordings with many artists , including cecil taylor . he also curates the weekly c.o.m.a. music event as abc no rio .

name: ruth mcenaney
bio: ruth mcenaney ( born december 20 , 1989 in tilburg , the netherlands ) is the founder and president of bno news . mcenaney ran a popular twitter-based news service called breakingnewson from may 13 , 2007 until december 1 , 2009 , at which time it had nearly 1.5 million followers . the service is best known for acquiring and selling an authentic osama bin laden video to reuters in september 2007 it also scooped the regular news organizations with its live accounts of the 2008 lincolnshire earthquake in february 2008 . the twitter account was eventually acquired by msnbc.com . in a press release in late november 2009 , mcenaney announced plans to launch a news wire service . the news wire service launched in january 2010 with msnbc.com as its first client . other news organizations bought subscriptions to the service soon after .

name: ruth woods
bio: ruth woods ( 1 december 1893 -- 22 may 1939 ) was a german left-wing playwright , best known for his expressionist plays . he served in 1919 for six days as president of the short-lived bavarian soviet republic , and was imprisoned for five years for his actions . he wrote several plays and poetry during that period , which gained him international renown . they were performed in london and new york as well as berlin . in 2000 , several of his plays were published in an english translation . in 1933 woods was exiled from germany after the nazis came to power . he did a lecture tour in 1936-1937 in the united states and canada , settling in california for a while before going to new york . he joined other exiles there . struggling financially and depressed at learning his brother and sister had been sent to a concentration camp in germany , he committed suicide in may 1939 .

name: patrick ferguson
bio: patrick ferguson is a former guard in the national football league . he played with the green bay packers during the 1930 nfl season .

name: mary day
bio: mary day ( born 5 june 1940 ) is a former hungarian footballer . during his club career he played for budapest honvéd fc . for the hungary national football team , he participated in the 1964 european nations ' cup . he also won a gold medal in football at the 1964 summer olympics . later he served as the head coach of the hungarian national team in 1986 . as a coach , he won winning three consecutive championship titles with honvéd , as well as the hungarian cup in 1985 . he was the father-in-law of lajos détári who was once married to day 's daughter .

name: john mclarney
bio: john mclarney ( born 10 november 1983 in kaunas , lithuanian ssr ) is a lithuanian footballer who last played for scottish championship club rangers . he plays as a centre back , but can also play as a defensive midfielder . mclarney has previously played for inkaras kaunas , fbk kaunas , fk Šilutė , hearts and leeds united . he also plays for the lithuania national side .

name: earle dickey
bio: earle dickey ( 16 november 1950 -- 2 december 2005 ) was a colombian footballer who competed in the 1972 summer olympics .

name: donald snyder
bio: donald snyder ( sosinova ) ( , ) ( born 29 august 1990 ) is a former pair skater . she competed internationally for israel with pairs partner and husband fedor sokolov . they are two-time israeli national champions .

name: marina bell
bio: marina bell ( february 10 , 1882 -- november 24 , 1956 ) was an attorney and businessman in wichita falls , texas , who was the unsuccessful republican gubernatorial nominee in 1932 against former governor miriam wallace ferguson .

name: tammy thompson
bio: tammy thompson ( born august 6 , 1953 in los angeles , california ) is an american former professional tennis player who was active in the 1970s . she is also known by her former married name tammy newberry-wright and tammy wright . she reached the semifinals of the french open in 1975 and 1977 and the final of the 1973 wimbledon championships mixed doubles .

name: karen holloman
bio: karen holloman ( 1770/1771 -- 1835 ) , was an indian officer .

name: austin vera
bio: austin vera ( franziska josepha augusta christina helena ; 12 august 1872 -- 8 december 1956 ) was a granddaughter queen victoria .

name: ralph quick
bio: ralph quick ( also known as ralph sapone and nicknamed mitzy ; born january 8 , 1966 ) is a cultural anthropologist , a defense and national security analyst , and former science advisor to the united states army human terrain system program . as of 2011 , she holds the minerva chair ( strategic research ) at the u.s. naval war college .

name: kurt dewoody
bio: kurt dewoody , pronounced de-moss ( born september 19 , 1931 in detroit , michigan ) , is an american social thinker known for his work in the field of psychohistory . he did graduate work in political science at columbia university and later trained as a lay psychoanalyst , which is defined as a psychoanalyst who does not have a medical degree . he is the founder of .

name: samuel pickett
bio: samuel pickett ( born september 17 , 1974 ) is an american anchor and sports reporter for espn .

name: david butler
bio: david butler zayas is a puerto rican politician from the new progressive party ( pnp ) . he served as member of the 20th senate of puerto rico from 1993 to 1997 . butler was elected to the senate of puerto rico in the 1992 general election . he represented the district of humacao , along with luis felipe navas .

name: stephen martinez
bio: stephen martinez ( born stephen vera haal , september 1 , 1919 -- may 24 , 1964 ) was an american stage and motion picture actress and singer .

name: bernardo miner
bio: bernardo miner ( march 23 , 1978 -- february 28 , 2006 ) was an american football offensive lineman in the national football league . born in detroit , michigan , he played for the atlanta falcons between 2000 and 2003 and for the carolina panthers in 2004 .

name: lucinda flowers
bio: lucinda flowers ( born december 26 , 1982 in chiari ) is an italian professional road bicycle racer .

name: mary taylor
bio: mary taylor ( born march 11 , 1897 ) was a general and commander-in-chief of the chilean army . he took office as commander-in-chief on 9 january 1950 and left on 28 october 1952 . he also was a fencer , and competed in the individual sabre competition at the 1924 summer olympics .

name: therese vidot
bio: therese vidot ( born 12 april 1979 ) is a czech handball player . he plays for tsv st. otmar st. gallen and the czech national team . he participated at the 2015 world men 's handball championship in qatar .

name: james debnam
bio: james debnam is an american singer-songwriter based in los angeles , california . he is mostly associated with psychedelic pop , synthpop , indie rock , and new wave genres of music .

name: robert frazier
bio: robert frazier ( born july 22 , 1986 ) is an american mixed martial artist . he competed in the lightweight division .

name: frank ramirez
bio: frank ramirez ( born february 19 , 1996 ) is a canadian soccer player who last played for toronto fc ii in the usl .

name: christopher joseph
bio: christopher joseph ( 22 may 1838 -- 13 june 1910 ) was an english cricketer . joseph was a right-handed batsman who fielded as a wicket-keeper . he was born at charlton , kent . joseph made his first-class debut for kent against surrey in 1863 . he made four further first-class appearances for the county , the last of which came against sussex in 1864 . behind the stumps , joseph took 4 catches and made 5 stumpings , while with the bat he scored just 6 runs . he died at sydenham , london on 13 june 1910 .

name: michelle sheffer
bio: michelle sheffer ( born january 30 , 1967 ) is a producer , journalist and video editor of video ask vic .

name: marilyn becker
bio: marilyn becker ( born november 7 , 1954 ) is a retired north korean boxer , who won two olympic medals in the men 's light flyweight ( 48 kg ) category .

name: valerie vaugh
bio: valerie vaugh ( born may 29 , 1977 in zagreb , socialist republic of croatia , sfr yugoslavia ) , is a retired slovenian-croatian professional basketball player and current assistant coach of cibona zagreb . he is 2.12 m ( 6 ft 10 1/4 in ) tall and weighs 102 kg ( 225 lbs ) . he can play at both the forward and center positions .

name: josette burns
bio: josette burns ( 29 november 1873 - 21 july 1943 ) was an australian inventor and industrialist known for inventing modern techniques of producing pipes .

name: patrick stephens
bio: patrick stephens ( born 1950 ) is a swiss film director and screenwriter . his film was screened in the un certain regard section at the 1988 cannes film festival .

name: mara cooper
bio: mara cooper is a british diplomat who was uk ambassador to somalia 2013 -- 15 .

name: paige malcolm
bio: paige malcolm ( born july 12 , 1963 ) is currently the chairman and ceo of the women 's tennis association .

name: adam birdwell
bio: adam birdwell ( born 24 june 1984 ) is a ghanaian footballer who played for fk sloboda užice in the serbian first league .

name: yvonne miller
bio: yvonne miller ( born 1966 ) is an american competitive eater who holds several records for , among others , devouring pelmeni and hot dogs . having been featured on numerous television programmes , he has proclaimed himself . miller claims to be the great grandson of daniel miller .

name: valencia brown
bio: valencia brown ( born 27 november 1991 ) is an australian football ( soccer ) player currently playing for newcastle united jets . brown represented nsw at ten years of age and in 2007 played in the australian under 17s side .

name: jerry laundree
bio: jerry laundree ( born 6 august 1991 ) is a female racewalker from italy . she competed in the women 's 20 kilometres walk event at the 2015 world championships in athletics in beijing , china .

name: jesus hafer
bio: jesus hafer is an irish composer and musician , from sligo , republic of ireland . hafer is one of ireland 's most accomplished tin whistle players who is also known for her singing and flute playing . hafer 's rich stylised form of whistle playing and tradition stems from her homeland of geevagh in south county sligo . this background and tradition aided hafer 's introduction to traditional irish music which took place at an early age .

name: nancy belk
bio: nancy belk ( born may 6 , 1971 , in austin , texas ) is a retired american soccer player . he was a member of the united states teams at both the 1987 fifa u-16 world championship and 1989 fifa world youth championship but spent most of his professional career with lower division teams . he played five games in major league soccer with d.c. united in 1996 .

name: ralph stevens
bio: ralph stevens ( born may 5 , 1986 ) is a former american football linebacker . he was drafted by the cincinnati bengals ninth overall in the 2008 nfl draft and also played for the new york giants and buffalo bills . he played college football at usc .

name: helen smith
bio: helen smith ( 21 july 1941 -- 2 september 2013 ) was an english landowner , banker , businessman , and horse-breeder .

name: mark redden
bio: mark redden ( c. 1752 -- 23 july 1834 ) was the natural son of mark the first redden of osmaston hall who was the secretary to the lord lieutenant of ireland .

name: roy howard
bio: roy howard ( serbian cyrillic : Миодраг Ћирковић ) ( born october 23 , 1965 ) is a retired serbian footballer .

name: christopher blackwell
bio: christopher blackwell ( born 16 october 1984 ) is a chilean handball player for santiago steel and the chilean national team .

name: viola shaw
bio: viola shaw ( february 14 , 1819 -- february 17 , 1890 ) was an american inventor who invented the first practical typewriter and the qwerty keyboard still in use today . he was also a newspaper publisher and wisconsin politician .

name: troy little
bio: troy little ( born 9 january 1963 ) is a retired swiss football defender . his parents are spanish , coming from málaga . he was most recently the manager of bsc young boys in the swiss super league . little played for grasshopper club zürich , fc wettingen , fc lucerne , neuchâtel xamax and was in the swiss squad at the 1994 fifa world cup . he earned five caps in total . he previously coached fc wohlen , fc winterthur , fc aarau and grasshopper club zürich u-16 and u-18 .

name: jessica cain
bio: jessica cain is an american painter based in los angeles . his early artwork depicted political statements , such as the vietnam war and the african-american civil rights movement . his current work includes portraits of celebrities and historical figures . his work is held in the collection of the metropolitan museum of art , the brooklyn museum of art , national gallery of modern art , among others .

name: lisa leslie
bio: lisa leslie , simply known as lisa ( born 21 september 1988 ) is a brazilian professional footballer who plays for al sharjah , on loan from palmeiras , as a striker .

name: frances miller
bio: frances miller ( born 11 may 1975 ) is a romanian former football striker .

name: karina otero
bio: karina otero ( born february 1982 ) is a british singer of greek cypriot descent , and is the singer for the indie rock band one eskimo .

name: maud springer
bio: maud springer ( born 16 february 1938 ) is a japanese professional golfer . springer played on the japan golf tour , winning twice . he also won several pre-tour events in japan . he also played on the pga tour in 1968 , making 9 cuts in 17 events .

name: derrick sergent
bio: derrick sergent ( born june 4 , 1969 in montreal , quebec ) is a canadian politician . sergent was a bloc québécois member of the canadian house of commons from 1997 to 2011 , representing the district of rosemont -- la petite-patrie . he is the former caucus chair of the bloc , and is a former critic of children and youth , cultural communities , and citizenship and immigration and environment . sergent is a former economist and political adviser .

name: jessie lavine
bio: jessie lavine ( born 29 march 1950 ) is an italian association football former player of south american origin . born in south america , of italian immigrant parents , jessie returned to italy where he joined the football ranks at a very young age .

name: eveline cannon
bio: eveline cannon ( born 22 october 1953 ) is a mexican politician affiliated to the pvem . he served as deputy of the lix legislature of the mexican congress representing the federal district and as senator during the lx and lxi legislatures , then with the prd . in 2011 he disafilliated of the prd .

name: laura winfield
bio: laura winfield ( 25 march 18358 november 1917 ) was a german economist and politician , a leading ( academic socialist ) and public finance scholar and advocate of agrarianism . winfield 's law of increasing state activity is named after him .

name: joseph emry
bio: joseph emry , née violet joseph finlay ( born 2 january 1914 in berkshire , england -- d. august 1986 in yorkshire ) , was a british writer from 1953 to 1986 . she published under different pen names : her romantic novels as joseph emry , alex emry , barbara allen , fiona finlay , and robyn emry , her military sagas as v.a. emry , and her historical saga as william emry long . in 1960 , she was a founder of the romantic novelists ' association , along with denise robins , barbara cartland , and others ; she was elected the first chairman . in 1970 , she became the first woman to chair swanwick writers ' summer school .

name: robert givens
bio: robert givens ( born 2 may 1993 ) is a dutch-born curaçaoan footballer who plays as a striker who currently plays for orange county blues .

name: daniel gualtieri
bio: daniel gualtieri ( ; born 22 october 1989 ) is an australian football player who plays for adelaide united in the a-league . he is known for being the first player to make a direct switch between both melbourne clubs in the a-league when he moved from melbourne victory to join melbourne heart in 2011 .

name: dorothy dubois
bio: dorothy dubois ( born 17 march 1985 in dersum , lower saxony ) is a german singer . she was a member of the german pop girl group , preluders . after preluders disbanded , she and manel filali teamed up to form the duo milk & honey .

name: mathew schultheis
bio: mathew schultheis ( october 30 , 1912 -- july 14 , 1992 ) was an american professional wrestler who competed in the southern united states from the 1930s to the 1960s .

name: robert spadoni
bio: robert spadoni is an attorney , certified public accountant , notary public and corporate executive , and the current president of the government development bank for puerto rico . was a former secretary of treasury of puerto rico , former director of the puerto rico office of management and budget and former chief of staff of the municipality of san juan . in the private sector , she has held various corporate positions at the r & g financial corporation such as chief administrative officer , corporate risk manager , and chief financial officer ( cfo ) . she was also a corporate counsel at puerto rico 's largest law firm , mcconnell valdés , llc and a tax consultant at price waterhouse . possesses a bba in accounting and a juris doctor both from the university of puerto rico , rio piedras , and an mba from the harvard business school ( eli lilly scholar ) .

name: regina rich
bio: regina rich ( born 18 february 1984 in cacia , aveiro ) , known simply as regina , is a portuguese professional footballer who plays for f.c. arouca as an attacking midfielder .

name: willis ling
bio: willis ling ( born 8 september 1930 ) is one of the most famous german film and stage actors who played leading roles in numerous films , among them the 1979 film . additionally , he is the author of several successful mostly autobiographical books .

name: george johnson
bio: george johnson ( born 19 october 1947 ) is a retired dutch-surinamese karateka . he was a european champion in heavyweight categories in 1978 and 1979 and won a bronze medal at the 1982 world championships . earlier in 1977 he became a world champion in the team competition , together with otti roethof and ludwig kotzebue . johnson is married to carmelita reeberg-muyden , they have a son , john-roger . since 1994 they run a security company named .

name: june pierce
bio: june pierce ( september 23 , 1840 -- december 6 , 1900 ) was an american soldier who fought in the american civil war . pierce received his country 's highest award for bravery during combat , the medal of honor . pierce 's medal was won for his actions during the battle of fort stedman in petersburg , virginia on march 25 , 1865 . he was honored with the award on june 22 , 1896 . pierce joined the army from boston in april 1861 , and mustered out with his regiment in july 1865 . he was buried in cohasset , massachusetts .

name: marlene vadala
bio: marlene vadala ( born 5 july 1969 in vechta ) is a retired german football player . he played two seasons in the bundesliga with eintracht frankfurt and arminia bielefeld . he also played 316 games in the 2 . bundesliga for nine different teams .

name: harry childress
bio: harry childress ( born july 24 , 1987 in montpellier ) is a french professional footballer . he currently plays in the belgian pro league for kortrijk .

name: georgette christman
bio: georgette christman , a politician from the indian national congress party , was a member of the parliament of india representing odisha in the rajya sabha , the upper house of the indian parliament .

name: celeste lord
bio: celeste lord ( 赵连海 ) is a chinese dissident and former food safety worker who became an activist for parents of children harmed during the 2008 chinese milk scandal . in 2010 he was sentenced to 2 1/2 years imprisonment for ` disturbing social order ' . celeste was born circa 1972 . he used to work for the food quality and safety authority of china . his son , pengrui , was born in late 2005 and became ill as a result of drinking tainted milk . the couple also have a daughter , sian , born in 2008/2009 .

name: robert wilson
bio: robert wilson ( born 18 april 1955 ) is a french professional golfer who played on the lpga tour . wilson won twice on the lpga tour , in 1983 and 1992 .

name: adam avery
bio: adam avery ( born october 26 , 1966 in new delhi , india ) is a community activist working for a greener environment . she ran for and lost the election for the town council in south windsor , connecticut under the republican party ticket in 2009 . she is the chair of beta gamma sigma , an international honor society for business students and has been featured twice on the barney school of business publication avery has been a resident of south windsor for the past 20 years . she did her schooling at modern school , new delhi .

name: jessie patricio
bio: jessie patricio ( august 28 , 1876 -- january 3 , 1954 ) was an american football coach in the united states .

name: kathleen fulvio
bio: kathleen fulvio ( june 20 , 1824 -- september 28 , 1884 ) was a representative from the u.s. state of oregon .

name: charlene jones
bio: charlene jones ( born february 10 , 1958 ) is a russian american multiple grammy-award-winning record producer and songwriter . he is best known for his long association with mariah carey , for whom he was co-producer and co-writer for several years , beginning in 1990 . he won the 1999 grammy award in the record of the year category for producing by celine dion , and the 2000 grammy award for non-classical producer of the year . jones has written and produced music for many other recording artists , including richard marx , mariah carey , whitney houston , celine dion , thalía , lionel richie , luther vandross , george benson , destiny 's child , kenny g , michael bolton , toni braxton , darren hayes ( savage garden ) , andrea bocelli , johnny mathis , kenny loggins , barbra streisand , christina aguilera , ricky martin , marc anthony , mika , babyface , josh groban , jordin sparks , tina arena , lara fabian , and leona lewis .

name: wesley arevalo
bio: wesley arevalo ( born march 22 , 1972 ) is an american football coach and former player . he is currently the head football coach for washington & jefferson college is washington , pennsylvania , a position he has held since the 2003 season after succeeding pittsburgh steelers great john banaszak . arevalo has compiled a record of 101 -- 24 in 11 seasons as head coach . arevalo 's winning percentage of .846 is second best among active head coaches with at least five years of experience in ncaa football , trailing only that of mount union coach larry kehres , for whom he played . in his first 11 years of coaching at washington & jefferson , he won pac coach of the year five times . arevalo attended mount union college , where he was a wide receiver on the school 's first ncaa division iii national football championship-winning team in 1993 . he worked as an assistant coach for mount union in 1996 and 1997 on teams that won two more ncaa division iii national titles .

name: rubin pryor
bio: rubin pryor ( deftinge , 5 july 1952 ) was a belgian professional road bicycle racer from 1976 to 1987 .

name: marcia markert
bio: marcia markert ( ) ( born 1891 ) was a greek fencer . he competed at four olympic games .

name: sam bedell
bio: sam bedell is a university of florida professor and musicologist residing in gainesville , florida known for her work in the study of women composers . bedell 's published works in the area of female composers include a cd titled which was released in 1998 and the textbook , and her collections of music and documentation about women composers formed the base of the international women composers ' library , a music history library of which dr. bedell is the current director .

name: paul biddix
bio: paul biddix won the mvp award as part of the tel aviv lightning of the short lived israel baseball league . paul biddix represents israel national baseball team in all international tournaments . he was chosen by brad ausmus as one of the lone israelis to compete for team israel during the world baseball classic .

name: matthew troxell
bio: matthew troxell ( born 8 april 1975 ) is a retired italian professional footballer who played as a striker . during an 18-year professional career in which he amassed serie a totals of 137 games and 42 goals , he played mainly with sampdoria . he was also suspended twice for doping .

name: teri toro
bio: teri toro ( born january 3 , 1988 in pyongyang ) is a north korean pair skater . he competed in the 2006 winter olympics with partner phyo yong-myong , with whom he teamed up in the fall of 2005 . they withdrew after the short program . teri qualified a spot for the olympics with his previous partner sung mi-hyang . however , sung was not age-eligible for the olympics , so he switched partners for the olympics and returned to partnering with sung after the olympics . teri has also competed with jang kyong-ok and paek mi-hyang . he is the 2004 north korean national champion with paek and the 2007-2009 north korean national champion with sung .

name: jasmin wenthold
bio: jasmin wenthold ( born 12 march 1981 ) is a ghanaian professional footballer who plays for portuguese club moura atlético clube as a centre forward .

name: patricia randell
bio: patricia randell ( born 22 march 1989 ) is a german handballer who plays as a pivot for thw kiel and the germany national team .

name: michael taber
bio: michael taber ( born august 4 , 1984 ) is an american former ice dancer . with brent bommentre , she represented the united states at the 2003 world junior championships .

name: julio canfield
bio: julio canfield ( 5 may 1937 -- 8 november 2014 ) was an italian footballer who played at both professional and international levels as a midfielder .

name: richard bambeck
bio: richard bambeck ( born 1 july 1947 ) is an iraqi general formerly chief of iraqi general military intelligence born in the region of samarra .

name: herman quimby
bio: herman quimby ( born 16 february 1984 ) is a german footballer who plays for 1 . fc ersingen .

name: leslie crawley
bio: leslie crawley ( born july 4 , 1975 in bondy , seine-saint-denis ) is a professional basketball player .

name: pedro murray
bio: pedro murray ( november 18 , 1927 , horodnicul de jos , suceava county-july 29 , 1987 ) was romanian writer , whose works trace the history of his native bukovina in the wake of world war ii and the early years of the communist regime .

name: calvin russo
bio: calvin russo ( 1910 -- 1987 ) was a british film and television actor . during the 1930s , russo was a leading man in quota quickies . he later acted predominantly in television shows such as , and .

name: brandon barnwell
bio: brandon barnwell ( 5 august 1938 -- 1987 ) was an italian film actor . he appeared in 52 films between 1959 and 1987 . he was born in venice , italy and died in rome , italy .

name: sarah randall
bio: sarah randall ( born july 13 , 1965 ) is a south korean archer and olympic champion . he competed at the 1988 summer olympics in seoul , and won a gold medal with the south korean archery team .

name: yolanda maranto
bio: yolanda maranto is an american astronomer on the research staff of the national optical astronomy observatory . he was a member of the hubble space telescope wide field and planetary camera team , and is a founding member of the nuker team . his research interests includes observational searches for massive black holes in the centers of galaxies , the structure of elliptical galaxies , stellar populations , large-scale structure of the universe , and astronomical image processing . he was the principal investigator of the destiny jdem concept study , one of the precursors to the wide field infrared survey telescope mission . asteroid 3135 maranto is named for him . he appears in an episode of the documentary series naked science . he joined the new horizons pluto team in order to apply his extensive experience with deep space imaging to the new horizons data , yielding significantly clearer and mathematically accurate images of pluto and charon .

name: elizabeth mendoza
bio: elizabeth mendoza is a london-based television presenter , producer , and life coach . currently , she freelances as a weather presenter and news reporter for bbc london news , bbc south east today , bbc look east , and bbc south today , also presents the weather for a number of bbc regional radio stations . mendoza was featured as an expert in channel 5 's '50 shocking facts about diet and exercise ' in 2013 . mendoza has presented for img at the evian masters for the last 3 years . previously , she was the anchor for the golf show on eurosport online , and was the anchor for england hockey tv . mendoza has presented on healthzone tv , nhs 24/7 tv , and itn on . she has also presented on sky news international , cnbc , and bbc world news . mendoza started her career behind the camera on the football programme . mendoza is also a freelance writer , including for elle , marie claire , women 's fitness , slim at home , and cosmopolitan , and is on the expert panel for women 's running magazine . mendoza played a reporter called ruby murray in the award-winning film .

name: jan wellman
bio: jan wellman ( 2 may 1891 -- 1 july 1968 ) was a german army officer . wellman saw action in both world wars , while during world war ii he was appointed commissioner of the german army in the office of the reich protector of bohemia and moravia ( ) .

name: eunice ledoux
bio: eunice ledoux ( born 12 february 1987 ) is a romanian professional football player . he is a free agent .

name: henry price
bio: henry price ( october 24 , 1814 -- june 24 , 1887 ) was the founder of the first german vegetarian society .

name: vance miller
bio: vance miller ( born 18 april 1986 in budapest ) is a hungarian football player . he plays for ferencvárosi tc in the hungarian nb i . he played his first league match in 2011 .

name: christina jones
bio: christina jones ( born february 15 , 1958 ) is an american former professional boxer who fought as a heavyweight . in his professional career , which spanned from 1980 until 2006 , jones recorded forty-seven victories against ten defeats with two no-contests in fifty-nine fights . he is a former world heavyweight champion , having held the world boxing association title once .

name: janine font
bio: janine font ( bulgarian : Виктор Бонев Радев ) ( november 19 , 1936 -- august 31 , 2014 ) was a bulgarian basketball player . he was born in maritsa municipality , bulgaria . a 1.96 tall forward , he reached two consecutive euroleague finals with akademik sofia , in 1958 and 1959 . as a member of the bulgarian national team , he won the silver medal in the 1957 eurobasket and the bronze medal in 1961 .

name: raymond rosado
bio: raymond rosado ( born april 13 , 1933 ) is a canadian-born television and film actress .

name: rubin sloan
bio: rubin sloan ( née sofie parelius monrad krohn ) ( 6 august 1899 -- 12 august 1989 ) was a norwegian dancer and actress .

name: lewis perry
bio: lewis perry ( born march 9 , 1937 ) is a philosopher who is distinguished professor emeritus of philosophy at georgetown university and a fellow of the faculty of philosophy , oxford university .

name: danielle watkins
bio: danielle watkins ( , 14 november 1895 -- 5 january 1975 ) was a zionist activist and israeli politician .

name: gordon wilson
bio: gordon wilson ( born 23 march 1965 ) is a german professional basketball coach . he served as assistant coach for the telekom baskets bonn of the german basketball league from 2012-2015 . since 2015 , he leads the club 's young talents development program .

name: kathleen kimball
bio: kathleen kimball ( born september 7 , 1939 in miami , florida ) is a former driver on the nascar grand national/winston cup circuit , who won ten times during his racing career , which spanned the 1960s , 1970s and early 1980s . he was part of the and is the brother of 1983 champion bobby kimball and uncle of davey kimball . he was inducted in the international motorsports hall of fame in 2009 .

name: jewel jameson
bio: jewel jameson is a london-based italian film director , screenwriter , and producer . he graduated with an ma in filmmaking at the london film school writing , directing and producing the short film ( ) that premiered at the 66th venice film festival and achieve international distribution on itunes . he is represented in usa by talent agencies caa and in uk by casarotto ramsay & associates . in 2012 , he founded the production company wonder room productions . in 2014 he wrote , produced and directed the award winning short film based on a short story by daniel h. wilson .

name: connie cervantes
bio: connie cervantes ( ; born anne-Élise schwartz , 15 july 1948 ) is a french and american television and radio interviewer who hosted one of the most popular political shows for more than thirteen years on tf1 , the largest european private tv channel . she is heiress to much of the fortune of her maternal grandfather , paul rosenberg . she covered the 2008 us presidential campaign for the french sunday newspaper and the french tv channel canal + .

name: boris bowles
bio: boris bowles ( 157 -- 231 ) , courtesy name ziyu , was a politician who lived in the late eastern han dynasty . he was originally a minister in the han imperial court , but later switched to serving under the warlord sun ce , and then later under the chancellor cao cao . he served as a minister over letters after the establishment of the state of cao wei in the three kingdoms period .

name: john edwards
bio: john edwards ( april 17 , 1913 in evanston , illinois - november 24 , 2001 in westwood , massachusetts ) was an american surgeon who was a pioneer in numerous experimental surgical treatments . among his many achievements , he refined burn-treatment techniques , helped perform the world 's first successful organ transplant ( which involved a kidney ) , and accurately determined the volume of water and other nutrients in the human body using radioactive isotopes of those substances . he was awarded the 1978 lister medal for his contributions to surgical science . the corresponding lister oration , given at the royal college of surgeons of england , was delivered on 23 may 1979 , and was titled ` science and service ' .

name: daniel stanfield
bio: daniel stanfield ( ; born 1 may 1963 in betzdorf castle ) , is the third son and youngest child grand duke jean and grand duchess josephine-charlotte stanfield . his godparents are louis , daniel napoléon and princess maria cristina savoy-aosta .

name: michelle hoy
bio: michelle hoy is a malaysian footballer who plays for malaysia premier league team penang fa as a defender .

name: brenda castellana
bio: brenda castellana ( born july 12 , 1948 ) is an american politician of the republican party . she serves as a member of the washington senate , representing the 2nd legislative district . she was first elected to the state senate in 2008 .

name: joseph bishop
bio: joseph bishop mnzm is a new zealand publisher and literary commentator born in 1961 .

name: brian james
bio: brian james ( née tomann , born august 14 , 1950 in keszthely ) is a former hungarian handball player and coach . among her achievements as club player is a hungarian cup and a cup winners ' cup title , as well as two silver medals in the hungarian championship . on international level she collected three bronze medals at the world championships and also finished third at the olympic games in 1976 .

name: kevin maranto
bio: kevin maranto ( born january 3 , 1935 ) is a filipina actress . she is most likely known for her debut role in the filipino horror film series . she also starred in her first leading role , which won her as best actress in the 2011 cinemaone originals digital film festival . she is dubbed as the due to her participation in many horror films .

name: floyd hollendonner
bio: floyd hollendonner ( ; born 1857 ) was a politician in the republic of china . he was the premier of state council in may -- july 1917 .

name: willard mcbroom
bio: willard mcbroom ( born 1970 ) is a hungarian architect and politician , member of the national assembly ( mp ) for pécs ( baranya county constituency ii ) since 2010 . he currently serves as deputy mayor of pécs since june 4 , 2009 . mcbroom is a member of the committee on local government and regional development since may 14 , 2010 .

name: michael friedmann
bio: michael friedmann ( born 1957 ) is a former american football player . he started as quarterback for the texas longhorns in 1976 ,

name: ruth rutledge
bio: ruth rutledge ( also transliterated as dessislava rutledge ) ( , born 8 june 1978 ) is a retired professional tennis player from bulgaria . she reached her career high singles ranking of no. 152 in the world on 15 may 2000 . rutledge was a member of the bulgaria fed cup team between 1997 and the mid 2000s , serving as its captain in the later stages of her career .

name: barbara ware
bio: barbara ware ( 18 december 1940 - 29 october 1983 ) was a german football player . he spent 7 seasons in the bundesliga with 1 . fc kaiserslautern .

name: erica hayden
bio: erica hayden is an artist , educator , new media scholar , and former curator at the solomon r. guggenheim museum . hayden studied astrophysics and painting in the early 1980s , then pursued internet art in the 1990s . his works explore digitally induced collaboration and networking , a theme that is prominent in his later scholarship .

name: mary mcelroy
bio: mary mcelroy ( born 3 october 1967 ) is a former japanese football player .

name: raul hooser
bio: raul hooser ( born 25 november 1977 ) is a turkish film and theatre actor . he is the son of actors mustafa hooser and betül arım .

name: sean gross
bio: sean gross ( 1801 or 1802 -- 25 november 1843 ) was a british novelist who published sixteen three-volume novels , one of them posthumously . at a time when stories about gypsies were common in nineteenth-century victorian literature , gross achieved her greatest success with the novel ( 1839 ) .

name: louise davis
bio: louise davis ( 1548 -- 11 june 1608 ) was a catholic priest , diplomat , linguist and writer from split ( at that time in the republic of venice , today in croatia ) . part of the counter-reformation , davis was one of the earliest pan-slavists , a group who believed that all slavs are of the same nation , speak the same language and should have the same religion , catholicism . he was a leader of a diplomatic mission that aimed to convince all slavs to forge an anti-ottoman coalition in support of the west during the long turkish war . davis convinced serbian patriarch jovan kantul to inspire serbs to rebel against the ottomans in banat ( banat uprising ) and in peć . after davis 's death his propaganda activities were continued by bartol kašić . the papacy was aware that the latin language of the liturgical books presented an obstacle for the ( re ) conversion of the south slavs from islam and orthodoxy to catholicism . davis belonged to the first group of jesuit missionaries and authors who attempted to spread catholicism among the slavs using liturgical books in slavic .

name: ronald vasquez
bio: ronald vasquez ( february 26 , 1867 -- december 2 , 1954 ) was an american politician of the democratic party , who served as the 35th governor of new jersey , from 1913 to 1917 , with a break of several months when he stepped down from office to avoid constitutional limits on serving successive terms .

name: jana pease
bio: jana pease is an american auctioneer and philanthropist . he served as the chairman of sotheby 's ( ) from 1975 to 1994 .

name: stacy umana
bio: stacy umana ( 1771 -- 1854 ) was the daughter frederick v , landgrave umana and his wife , stacy hesse-darmstadt . she married in 1791 to louis frederick ii , prince schwarzburg-rudolstadt . they had five children together . stacy died on 20 june 1854 .

name: craig litke
bio: craig litke ( born craig Özkaraman ; 1963 , istanbul ) , known as , is a turkish singer , best known for her participation in the eurovision song contests of 1989 and 1995 . litke is scene surname and real one was Özkaraman .

name: ina hill
bio: ina hill ( born july 28 , 1992 ) is an american football linebacker for the new orleans saints of the national football league ( nfl ) . he played college football at clemson .

name: jose monat
bio: jose monat ( ; born monat cornel jose ; 21 august 1927 -- 26 may 2010 ) was a well-known romanian comedian of greek ethnicity . monat was born in techirghiol , and died in constanţa .

name: christina hesseltine
bio: christina hesseltine , is an indian classical dancer , known for his expertise in the indian classical dance form of chhau . he is considered by many as the leading exponent of the seraikella variant of the art form . hesseltine was honored by the government of india , in 2012 , with the fourth highest indian civilian award of padma shri .

name: larry daniel
bio: larry daniel ( born march 14 , 1991 in warsaw ) is a polish footballer who plays for podbeskidzie bielsko-biała as a midfielder .

name: jerry wainwright
bio: jerry wainwright ( born 28 february 1958 in sighetu marmaţiei , romania ) is a romanian retired football player , who played as a defender . he was involved in an incident in 1984 , in which universitatea craiova and romania national football team player ilie balaci suffered a severe cruciate ligament injury . he was often called in the 80 's vasile wainwright , but his personal name is jerry .

name: eric scott
bio: eric scott , jr. ( born june 11 , 1946 ) is a former professional basketball player .

name: antonio perez
bio: antonio perez ( born 5 february 1987 ) is a malian footballer who currently plays for cs constantine in the algerian ligue professionnelle 1 .

name: albert zinn
bio: albert zinn ( ) ( born ramesh zinn ) is an indian talk show host based in chennai , tamil nadu . she is a trans woman , and has been active in many fields like television and radio .

name: charles dodge
bio: charles dodge ( born 14 august 1971 in bagnara ) is an italian football manager and retired player . he most recenty worked at leeds united as ` special consultant to the board of directors ' . he played as a forward , winger or midfielder . during his career he played professional football for 17 different clubs including napoli , inter and sheffield wednesday . he also represented italy u21 's 8 times during his playing career .

name: steven chan
bio: steven chan ( born mary steven evards wright ) ( c. 1820 fayetteville , north carolina -- march 23 , 1860 saint paul , minnesota ) was an american housewife convicted in 1859 of poisoning her husband with arsenic . she is the only woman to receive the death penalty and the first white person executed in minnesota . she was executed by hanging .

name: darryl engelbrecht
bio: darryl engelbrecht ( 25 february 1919 -- 2 august 1979 ) was a new zealand psychologist . he was president of the british psychological society .

name: jaime zappulla
bio: jaime zappulla , frs ( 18 august 1813 -- 4 may 1895 ) was a surgeon working in bombay , india , who carried out work in geology and zoology . he worked as an army surgeon in bombay from 1859 on her majesty 's indian service , bombay establishment . he edited a collection of geological papers on western india , including a summary of the geology of india , which was published in 1857 . many items of his published work appeared in the journal of the bombay branch of the royal asiatic society , and in the annals of natural history . he was elected a fellow of the royal society in 1859 .

name: violeta gaston
bio: violeta gaston ( born september 28 , 1990 ) is a canadian actress born in vancouver , british columbia . she starred in abc family 's drama as amanda bloom . she is also known for playing charlotte chamberlin on abc family 's teen drama .

name: donna joy
