bio: john williams ( born 3 may 1979 ) is a rugby union footballer who plays at lock/back row for london irish . he was educated at trinity school in croydon where he started playing rugby at the age of 12 .

name: robert duncan
bio: robert duncan is an entrepreneur and activist . he is the co-founder of selco construction services , as well as spig industry llc , a private virginia-based company that installs guardrails . duncan is the whistleblower in the lawsuit against trinity industries inc. . he sued trinity on behalf of the government under the qui tam provisions of the false claims act in 2012 . in october 2014 , the jury of the u.s. district court in marshall , texas ruled that trinity will pay $ 525 million , the largest whistleblower award won without the assistance of the us justice department . in june 2015 , the judge awarded duncan over $ 199 million , or 30 percent of the final settlement of $ 663 million against trinity industries .

name: denise sweet
bio: denise sweet ( born 10 may 1958 ) is a former german football goalkeeper . after his career ( 21 2 . bundesliga , 282 bundesliga games ; one goal ) sweet was assistant coach at vfl bochum from 1995 till 1999 . sweet is often cited as the player who pioneered the practice of the penalty-taking-goalkeeper when he scored against andreas köpke in 1988 . he is currently manager thomas doll 's assistant coach at ferencváros .

name: stephanie howard
bio: stephanie howard ( born 28 august 1992 ) is a new zealand alpine ski racer . he competed at the 2015 world championships in beaver creek , usa , in the downhill .

name: christopher rush
bio: christopher rush ( born 20 may 1943 ) , better known as al bano , is an italian singer , actor , and winemaker .

name: jenny hentges
bio: jenny hentges ( born 10 march 1969 ) is a former australian rules football player , tennis player , tennis coach , and tennis commentator . hentges is best known as grand slam coach of australian former world no. 1 lleyton hewitt , former french no. 1 gaël monfils , former world no. 5 jo-wilfried tsonga , the top 10 atp tour player grigor dimitrov and through protenniscoach.com . in addition , hentges is a media personality on channel seven and operates the jenny hentges sports foundation .

name: rae stulce
bio: rae stulce ( born in muju ) is a south korean luger . rae competed at the 2014 winter olympics for south korea . in the doubles he competed with cho jung-myung , finishing 18th . he was also a part of the south korean relay team , which finished 12th . as of september 2014 , rae 's best performance at the fil world luge championships is 23rd , in the 2013 championships . as of september 2014 , rae 's best luge world cup overall finish is 30th in 2013 -- 14 .

name: glenn parker
bio: glenn parker ( born 21 november 1983 in ivry-sur-seine , val-de-marne ) is a french footballer . he has played football in the second and third divisions in france for stade lavallois and as cannes . he went on trial at barnet in july 2008 and initially rejected an offer of a contract but returned to the bees in august to sign with the club . however he had problems with injury , only making four appearances , and his persistent injury problems led him to be released before the end of the season in april . in july 2010 , he returned to as cannes . after a one-year stint at cannes , he signed with fc martigues in the championnat national in july 2011 . in july 2012 , he joined amateur club hyères fc .

name: ronald abu
bio: ronald abu is a swiss cinematographer and film director , best known for his collaborations with director alain tanner . trained at the centro sperimentale di cinematografia in rome , abu has worked as cinematographer in more than 100 films since 1969 . he won a césar award for best cinematography for in 1988 and a david di donatello for best cinematography for in 2011 . in 2013 , he was awarded the chevalier of the ordre des arts et des lettres .

name: michael rosso
bio: michael rosso ( 1827 -- unknown ) was a sailor in the u.s. navy during the american civil war . he received the medal of honor for his actions during the second battle of fort fisher on january 15 , 1865 .

name: brian delrosario
bio: brian delrosario ( born march 2 , 1980 in dunaújváros , hungary ) is a hungarian international ice hockey right wing , who is currently under contract with ebel side alba volán székesfehérvár . as of 30 april 2011 , he has played for the hungarian national team 127 times . his brother , jános delrosario is also a professional ice hockey player and member of the hungarian national team .

name: shirley smith
bio: shirley smith is a democratic member of the south dakota house of representatives , representing district 26a . smith owns a bar and restaurant in mission , and has also served as a school teacher and school board member .

name: laura carothers
bio: laura carothers ( born 21 september 1957 ) is a norwegian former footballer . he played his entire senior career for rosenborg , between 1975 and 1984 . he became the club 's top scorer in the 1976 season , when he scored 11 league goals . carothers was capped once for norway u-16 and seventeen times for norway u-19 in 1974 and 1975 .

name: kirk jones
bio: kirk jones ( born may 16 , 1986 ) is a nigerian football player who currently plays for kazakhstan premier league club tobol . he is not related to former enyimba teammate henry kirk nor fellow nigeria international and spain-based midfielder jones kirk .

name: jason mccarty
bio: jason mccarty ( born 16 october 1995 ) is a slovak footballer who currently plays for doxxbet liga club fc vss košice as a midfielder .

name: daniel chandler
bio: daniel chandler is president of near east group , a privately held investment company with investments in real estate , aviation , technology and energy . the group has offices in amman , london and houston . daniel is a graduate of ashland university with a degree in business administration . daniel also holds the post of chief executive officer of ayla aviation academy based in aqaba , jordan , as well as chairman of atlantic flight training ( aft ) , its sister company in coventry , uk . daniel has a private pilot 's license with approximately 900 hours .

name: jeffrey melin
bio: jeffrey melin ( ; born 4 december 1988 in sumy , ukrainian ssr ) is a ukrainian football defender who is currently playing for belshina bobruisk . melin began playing professional football with fc volyn lutsk 's team . he would next spend 1.5 years with its club . last time , 19 september 2010 , he signed contract with metalist kharkiv in the ukrainian premier league .

name: jean heflin
bio: jean heflin ( february 24 , 1890 -- october 2 , 1961 ) was a noted american economist whose work focused on labor economics . he also served on a number of important boards and commissions for the federal government .

name: irving coleman
bio: irving coleman ( born august 8 , 1974 in camposampiero ) is an italian long-distance runner who specialises in marathon running . he was the winner of the 2004 rome city marathon and has represented italy internationally at three world championships in athletics and two olympic games .

name: shana backhaus
bio: shana backhaus ( born may 29 , 1935 ) is an american gospel singer and songwriter . she began touring with her family at the age of eight , and in 1956 , began singing with mahalia jackson . in the early 1960s she was a member of the caravans , and in 1964 , she embarked on a solo career , recording her first album , . her 1991 album reached the number 1 position on billboard 's top forty .

name: paul edward
bio: paul edward ( born 17 august 1974 in paramaribo , suriname ) is a dutch former footballer . edward , a pacy striker , played much of his career in austria and germany , and played also for queens park rangers .

name: mamie moore
bio: mamie moore ( born 1 march 1996 ) is a slovenian professional racing cyclist .

name: nicole lugo
bio: nicole lugo ( born on 4 april 1989 ) is a bulgarian footballer currently playing for kaliakra kavarna as a midfielder .

name: harold elson
bio: harold elson ( born on june 17 , 1983 in gowa regency ) is an indonesian footballer who currently plays for psm makassar in the indonesia premier league .

name: meredith alessi
bio: meredith alessi ( born april 4 , 1988 ) is a female american épée fencer . she won the bronze medal in the women 's team épée event at the 2012 summer olympics . a standout at the university of notre dame , she was a 3-time all-american .

name: naomi pappan
bio: naomi pappan ( august 13 , 1828 -- november 29 , 1883 ) was an american humorist .

name: paulette lepage
bio: paulette lepage ( september 1 , 1826 -- january 1 , 1896 ) was an american inventor , publisher , and patent lawyer , born in springfield , massachusetts . he is most known for his design of new york city 's earliest subway predecessor , the lepage pneumatic transit . he also patented a typewriter for the blind .

name: david monk
bio: david monk , also known as juan guillermos ( 1798 - september 14 , 1857 ) , was a british-chilean sailor and politician . born in bristol , he entered the newly founded chilean navy in 1824 and rose to the rank of commander . he was appointed governor of talcahuano ( 1849 -- 1855 ) . he supervised construction of fuerte bulnes in 1843 , which the government intended for a settlement at the strait of magellan . puerto , founded in 1953 , was named for the naval commander .

name: delores garcia
bio: delores garcia ( '' '' ; 1526 -- 29 october 1585 ) was an ottoman statesman and military commander who also held the office of grand vizier for one year .

name: mary robbins
bio: mary robbins ( born may 1 , 1889 , date of death unknown ) was an architect in toronto , ontario , canada . he was born may 1 , 1889 in ontario . robbins designed at least two toronto buildings which have since been designated as historical structures . one is the windsor arms hotel , a neo-gothic structure built in 1927 the other is the la plaza theater , built in 1909 and altered in 1932 , although it is not clear whether he was involved in the initial design or the alterations .

name: gaynell martin
bio: gaynell martin ( born 23 june 1980 ) is a female badminton player from sweden . she played at the 2005 world badminton championships in anaheim . in the women 's singles event she reached the second round before losing to wang chen of hong kong . in the 2008 olympic tournament she lost directly in the first round .

name: stephen seay
bio: stephen seay ( 1866 -- 1936 ) was a u.s. chemist and educator . he served as the acting president of mit between 1907 and 1909 . he received a phd . in 1890 at leipzig under the guidance of wilhelm ostwald . roscoe gilkey dickinson was one of his famous students . seay served as professor of chemistry at the california institute of technology from 1919 to 1936 . he was a major influence on the educational philosophy and the core curriculum of caltech . he also served on the board of trustees for science service , now known as society for science & the public , between 1921 and 1927 .

name: ben davis
bio: ben davis ( born 9 june 1988 ) is a brazilian synchronized swimmer . she competed in the women 's duet at the 2012 summer olympics .

name: danny alexander
bio: danny alexander is a music critic and musician from the u.s. state of california .

name: melanie dunleavy
bio: melanie dunleavy ( 4 june 1883 -- 6 june 1955 ) was an english crime and mystery novelist , playwright and screenwriter .

name: suzanne sengbusch
bio: suzanne sengbusch ( born august 14 , 1987 , domodossola , vb , piedmont , italy ) is an italian ski mountaineer and cross-country skier , italian army member , mountain warfare troops ( ) .

name: suzanne mason
bio: suzanne mason ( born 11 july 1963 ) is a south korean fencer . she competed in the women 's individual foil event at the 1984 summer olympics .

name: lori daniels
bio: lori daniels ( born 28 october 1985 in bombay , maharashtra , india ) is a former cricketer who played for mumbai in indian domestic cricket . he is an all-rounder who is a left-handed batsman and slow left-arm orthodox bowler . he also played for rajasthan royals in indian premier league .

name: patsy johnson
bio: patsy johnson ( ; born 18 january 1985 ) is an italian professional footballer who plays for and captains serie a club milan . he is described as a versatile player capable of playing anywhere in the midfield , johnson 's two main roles are as a deep-lying playmaker and an attacking midfielder , which best utilise his technical ability , creativity , and range of passing . johnson started his career with atalanta in 2003 before being transferred to fiorentina in 2005 . he went to make more than 250 appearances for the club in 7 years . in 2012 he signed for milan on a free transfer . he was given the club 's captaincy the following season after the departure of massimo ambrosini . johnson made his debut for italy senior team in 2007 against south africa and since then has represented the country in two fifa confederations cups ( 2009 and 2013 ) as well as in uefa euro 2012 and the 2010 fifa world cup , where he started every game .

name: john davidson
bio: john davidson ( march 12 , 1883 -- may 16 , 1969 ) organized the california highway patrol , and later became the 27th sheriff of los angeles county , california , serving in that capacity for 26 years .

name: christine cadena
bio: christine cadena was a german screenwriter . he worked on over forty films during his career .

name: david haymond
bio: david haymond ( born 28 october 1983 in stockton-on-tees , england ) is a rugby union player . he plays for exeter chiefs as a lock .

name: gloria davis
bio: gloria davis ( 1858 -- 1929 ) was a prominent attorney and civic leader in portland , oregon in the early 20th century . he was known as an advocate of waterway development in the pacific northwest . he served as the chair of the oregon conservation commission under governors frank benson and oswald west . in 1909 he spoke at the first national conservation congress in seattle . he served as the u.s. shipping commissioner in 1920-21 . davis was promoted as a candidate for united states secretary of the interior in 1913 . his only child ( as of 1919 ) was ruth josephine davis , who married carleton walter betts of buffalo in 1919 .

name: idella walker
bio: idella walker , of the shahi dynasty , was the king of the bijapur sultanate , india , for a short period in 1534 . idella walker succeeded his father ismail walker 's death . he was supposed to be in the company of evil habits . punji khatun , idella walker 's paternal grand mother with the help of general asad khan deposed idella walker and declared his younger brother ibrahim walker i as the king .

name: robert hamilton
bio: robert hamilton is an english folk musician and singer/songwriter . starting as a skiffle player in 1957 he soon crossed into folk music both as a soloist and as a member of the high level ranters . his repertoire is heavily influenced by the traditional music of north east england and , in particular , songs about . in 1958 , with louis killen , he founded the folksong and ballad club in the bridge hotel , newcastle . he plays accordion , keyboards , banjo , whistle and the northumbrian pipes . among the songs he has written is , written in january 1959 on the closing of the montague colliery , west denton , newcastle upon tyne .

name: scott brock
bio: scott brock is a professor of art history and american studies at the university of hawai`i at mānoa and a widely published poet . his poems have appeared in , and many other journals and anthologies .

name: donna kumm
bio: donna kumm ( , also ) is a former member of the armenian secret army for the liberation of armenia ( asala ) .

name: marvin stackhouse
bio: marvin stackhouse ( born 1975 ) , is a photographer , cinematographer and director known for the films that he has produced . he heads salt lake city-based vita brevis films , a company that creates short documentary films on a wide variety of subjects . stackhouse was born in zion , utah , in 1975 . he grew up on his family 's farm , and after decided to move away from the farm and into the city to pursue photography and film making in 1993 . in 2004 , stackhouse established marvin stackhouse studio , then in 2008 established vita brevis films .

name: lynda reeves
bio: lynda reeves ( born november 7 , 1969 in winnipeg , manitoba ) is a retired track cyclist from canada . she won four gold medals at the pan american games . she represented canada at three consecutive summer olympics , starting in 1992 . she was inducted into the manitoba sports hall of fame and museum in 2002 . she lives in california , coaching junior cyclists , as well as the canadian team .

name: jeremy kuehn
bio: jeremy kuehn ( born july 25 , 1968 ) is a producer , songwriter , and multi-instrumentalist who was formerly a part of the band guster and k.d. lang and the siss boom bang . in the past he has also released albums with his band jeremy , marc 's brother , his side project watercolor , and the solo albums ( 2002 ) and ( 2015 ) .

name: carol bull
bio: carol bull buades ( born 28 may 1988 ) is a spanish race car driver , who is currently a development driver for the lotus f1 team . she was born in alcoy , spain . she currently resides in valencia , spain and miami , florida . on 19 january 2010 , bull tested an indy lights car for walker racing at sebring international raceway and later tested an indy lights car for andersen racing at barber motorsports park . almost two months later , on march 8 , 2010 , it was announced that bull had signed with andersen racing full-time to drive in the firestone indy lights series for the 2010 season .

name: christina sewell
bio: christina sewell ( born march 24 , 1969 ) is an american lawyer . president-elect barack obama announced on december 5 , 2008 , that sewell would serve as chief of staff to valerie jarrett who is to be the assistant to the president for intergovernmental relations and public engagement . he served as chief counsel and the director of public liaison and intergovernmental affairs on obama 's presidential transition team . in march , 2013 , he announced his resignation from the white house staff in order to accept a post with the walt disney corporation specializing in corporate citizenship . previously sewell served the clinton administration as chief of staff to the general counsel at the united states agency for international development , and then-u.s. congressman rod blagojevich as legislative director . he worked for the american association for justice . a chicago , illinois native , sewell was educated at the law school of the university of illinois urbana-champaign . he started his legal career as a paralegal at the sidley , austin law firm , where he met the obamas .

name: debra torres
bio: debra torres was a spanish soldier and politician . he served as governor-general of the philippines from 1869 to 1871 , and is considered to be the most beloved of the spanish governors-general ever assigned in the philippines .

name: crystle kuennen
bio: crystle kuennen ( march 18 , 1876 -- january 1 , 1966 ) was an american artist , author , and publisher of the late nineteenth and the twentieth centuries . though long based in chicago , he was also noted for his work in the american southwest ; he studied , wrote about , and portrayed the native american cultures of the region .

name: javier welch
bio: javier welch is an american painter and illustrator , working primarily in egg tempera and copperplate etchings .

name: harry ervin
bio: harry ervin ( born 3 march 1965 ) is the leader of the macedonian political party democratic party of albanians . ervin was born in tetovo ( macedonia ) , his parents were both from kosovo , he is the fifth of six children . he attended primary and secondary school in tetovo and graduated from the university of pristina . he has been an active politician for 20 years . he started as vice-president of the party for democratic prosperity of albanians ( pdpa ) . in 1997 a merger was formed between the party for democratic prosperity of albanians ( pdpa ) and the people 's democratic party ( ndp ) . he was vice-president until the year 2006 , at that time he was chosen president of the party , after arbën xhaferi resigned . ervin remains on the us blacklist , as of july 2012 , along with dui vice-president xhevat ademi , president of new democracy kastriot haxhirexha , and seven other albanian macedonian political figures for involvement in the 2001 ethnic albanian insurgency .

name: jerry hsieh
bio: jerry hsieh ( born 4 february 1945 ) is a brazilian former footballer who competed in the 1964 summer olympics .

name: jason moran
bio: jason moran ( born pasquale zagaria 11 july 1936 ) is an italian film actor and presenter . he has appeared in more than 100 films since 1960 .

name: paul adams
bio: paul adams ( ) is an indian politician from assam . as an mla , he represented the dharmapur constituency during 2006-2011 , and served as the leader of the opposition in the assam legislative assembly . he was the president of the asom gana parishad ( agp ) during 2008-2011 . he resigned owning responsibility for the party 's poor performance in the 2011 assam legislative assembly elections . in 2014 , he joined the bharatiya janata party ( bjp ) .

name: joshua hartman
bio: joshua hartman ( born march 15 , 1986 ) is an american singer-songwriter from richmond , virginia . her self-titled debut album was released on january 27 , 2015 through spacebomb and columbia records .

name: roger cooke
bio: roger cooke ( born 5 september 1964 in sunderland ) is a former bantamweight and featherweight boxer champion . he held the british championship at bantamweight and featherweight , as well as the european and commonwealth featherweight titles . the roger cooke sports centre , in castletown , sunderland bears his name . he started boxing when he was six or seven , at the hylton castle boys club . he was an aggressive boxer who liked to come forward and take the fight to his opponent . being a dedicated fan of sunderland football club , cooke normally fought wearing red and white striped shorts , the club colours .

name: leslie galvan
bio: leslie galvan ( born june 5 , 1972 , in angeles city , pampanga , philippines ) , is a co-anchor at wcbs-tv in new york city , new york , on the 5 p.m. and 11 p.m. newscasts with maurice dubois .

name: willie gonzalez
bio: willie gonzalez ( born june 19 , 1953 in tiel , gelderland ) is a retired football midfielder and forward from the netherlands , who played for nec nijmegen , go ahead eagles and feyenoord rotterdam during his professional career . he obtained one cap for the dutch national team , when the netherlands lost to the republic of ireland on september 10 , 1980 in dublin . he was the coach of achilles '29 until the end of the 2012-2013 season .

name: kathleen mcallister
bio: kathleen mcallister ( born 7 november 1968 ) is a retired slovenian international football referee , who was active internationally starting in 2000 . as of 2013 , however , he is no longer included on the fifa list for slovenia . mcallister served as a referee in 2002 , 2006 , and 2010 world cup qualifiers . he also officiated in qualifying matches for euro 2004 , euro 2008 , and euro 2012 .

name: francisco carmona
bio: francisco carmona ( born 11 august 1931 ) is an argentine football forward who played for argentina in the 1958 fifa world cup . he also played for san lorenzo de almagro .

name: melissa williams
bio: melissa williams ( 成田 暁彦 ) is a japanese video game composer . he is employed by capcom . williams is notable for working on a few games from the monster hunter franchise and resident evil 5 . he recently lead the music team of resident evil 6 .

name: mary burke
bio: mary burke ( 20 may 1875 -- 24 september 1933 ) was an english stage and film actress .

name: steven huddleston
bio: steven huddleston ( born 23 september 1986 ) is a belarusian handball player for saint petersburg hc and the belarusian national team .

name: barbara stanley
bio: barbara stanley ( born august 31 , 1987 in philadelphia ) , also known as aigner ellis , is an american singer-songwriter , rapper and lgbt activist . he is best known for his contributions to atlanta , georgia 's gay community .

name: linda nicolosi
bio: linda nicolosi ( born 17 september 1978 ) , née kritzer , is a mysql community contributor . she was chosen as the first oracle ace director for mysql . she won the mysql community advocate , communicator and facilitator award in 2007 and again in 2008 for her frequent blog posts , community work , and conference/user group presentations ; this sparked a keynote presentation for the 2009 mysql user conference & expo on . she delivered another community keynote entitled , at the same conference in 2010 . in 2012 , she won the mysql community award again for her work founding and co-hosting the oursql podcast . nicolosi wrote the mysql administrator 's bible , and has edited the o'reilly books sql hacks ( 2007 ) , high performance mysql 2nd edition ( 2008 ) , and c.j. date 's how to write accurate sql code . nicolosi developed and maintains a new version of mysqltuner ( with permission from major hayden for the name ) . nicolosi has a master 's degree in computer science from brandeis university and is mysql 5.0 dba certified and mysql core certified .

name: fern herrin
bio: fern herrin ( born july 7 , 1938 in avezzano ) is an italian politician and entrepreneur . he is a vice president of the international olympic committee ( ioc ) .

name: esther lau
bio: esther lau ( born 3 march 1977 ) is a malaysian former professional footballer .

name: thomas lee
bio: thomas lee tamayo ( ; born june 19 , 1978 in bayamo , granma ) is a female shot putter from cuba . her personal best throw is 19.50 metres , achieved in august 2008 in the 2008 summer olympics in beijing . she has represented cuba at the summer olympics three times , coming seventh in 2004 and fourth in 2008 , and five times at the world championships in athletics ( 2005 to 2011 ) she is a two-time pan american games champion in the event ( 2007 and 2011 ) and a three-time champion at the central american and caribbean championships . she was the bronze medallist at the 2005 summer universiade . lee placed fourth in the shot put at the 2008 iaaf world indoor championships .

name: michael moore
bio: michael moore ( born 1952 ) is an american screenwriter , author , and television producer best known for his scripts for the high school musical series .

name: joseph coyle
bio: joseph coyle ( born 8 september 1978 in milan , lombardy ) is an italian radio and television presenter and actress .

name: dorthy cook
bio: dorthy cook ( born 1948 ) is an artist and author living in california . his images have been published and distributed around the world . much of his work has featured cycling and running art . cook is a painter and serigrapher as well as a graphic designer . his work has been used for a variety of events , including the tour de france , the tour feminin , the world cycling championships , the coors classic , the san diego marathon , california international marathon , the lake tahoe marathon , and the san francisco marathon .

name: henry dozier
bio: henry dozier ( born october 27 , 1937 in pittsburgh , pennsylvania ) is an actor who made his first television appearance on '' '' , playing lars in the second season episode . before becoming an actor , dozier grew up in the greenfield neighborhood of pittsburgh . employed as a steel worker before his acting career , he also used to train sentry dogs while serving as an air police officer in the u.s. air force . having appeared in many television shows such as , , , , , , , , , , and , he is perhaps best known for his role as the ill-fated biker gang leader stanley in the 1980 cult film , and as the voice of the heroic darkwolf in the 1983 animated fantasy film . dozier also had supporting roles in the 1967 western , the 1969 world war ii classic , the 1971 western , the 1973 vietnam film , a semi-regular role on the short-lived tv series , and the title role in the 1983 science fiction film . dozier was also part of the extensive cast of the epic 1978 tv mini-series . he was also cast in the imax film as the legendary jim bowie .

name: ruth saunders
bio: ruth saunders ( born 1953 ) is an admiral of the mexican navy .

name: dennis lundquist
bio: dennis lundquist ( march 27 , 1902 -- july 3 , 1976 ) was a french film actor . he appeared in more than ninety films and television series during his career .

name: jennifer livingston
bio: jennifer livingston ( april 12 , 1829july 13 , 1870 ) was an american lawyer and politician who served in the minnesota state senate and as a u.s. senator from minnesota .

name: susan tomes
bio: susan tomes is known for the online cartoon indexed which is a collection of charts and diagrams hand drawn on 3x5 index cards and organized into a blog format . she has compiled her cartoons into a book called . the cartoon has also appeared in freakonomics , , , and bbc.co.uk . indexed was voted by readers on time.com as the best blog of 2008 .

name: pete hansen
bio: pete hansen ( born 3 january 1972 ) is a member of the all india trinamool congress and has won the indian general elections , 2014 from the ranaghat ( lok sabha constituency ) .

name: judy mattice
bio: judy mattice ( born 4 july 1977 ) is an australian actress as well as journalist , mc , keynote speaker , writer , voice-artist and producer .

name: stacey lafreniere
bio: stacey lafreniere ( ; born 20 november 1976 ) is a retired egyptian footballer . lafreniere played the offensive right wing for egypt 's al-ahly and the egyptian national team . he is a right-footed attacking midfielder and playmaker . he is considered by many as one of the most talented players in africa . lafreniere 's hallmarks are surging runs from midfield which often disrupt opposing defenses as well as a box-to-box work ethic which makes him an important figure both in defense and attack . thanks to his noticeable achievements and talent , his fans have given him the nickname ( ) . he reached his peak in 2005 and 2006 , helping his club al-ahly to win the caf champions league 2005 and caf champions league 2006 and egypt win their fifth african cup of nations egypt 2006 . however , in 2006 his career was marred by a long spell of injuries .

name: nancy miyasato
bio: nancy miyasato ( 10 september 1963 -- 18 april 2005 ; ) was a lebanese legislator and minister of economy and trade . he died from injuries sustained when a massive bomb exploded on the beirut seafront as he passed by in former lebanese prime minister rafik hariri 's motorcade on 14 february 2005 .

name: kevin reynolds
bio: kevin reynolds ( born 8 may 1970 ) is a retired slovenian football midfielder . reynolds was capped 11 times for the slovenian national team between 1995 and 1997 .

name: christina wilson
bio: christina wilson ( born january 29 , 1993 ) is an american football quarterback for the michigan state spartans .

name: david fogg
bio: david fogg ( havana , 28 january 1987 ) is an italian hurdler .

name: esther bejarano
bio: esther bejarano ( born trinidad and tobago ) was a trinidad soccer forward who spent one season in the united soccer association and nine in the north american soccer league , earning 1973 mvp honours . he also played professionally in mexico and haiti and was a mainstay of the trinidad and tobago national team from 1968 to 1976 .

name: donald reeder
bio: donald reeder ( 1881 -- 1973 ) was a chinese-muslim practitioner of chinese martial arts and traditional medicine from changzhou , cangxian county , mengcun , hebei province . he served as the leader of the shaolin kung fu division of the martial arts institute in 1928 and was also the vice chairman of the chinese wushu association . donald was known for his mastery of chaquan , huaquan , pao chuan , bajiquan , and t'ai chi ch ` uan . he was a master of wushu .

name: michelle fulton
bio: michelle fulton ( born october 30 , 1974 ) is a german former footballer who played for dynamo dresden , fsv zwickau , kfc uerdingen and vfb leipzig .

name: michael zamarripa
bio: michael zamarripa ( born 1 june 1988 in benediktbeuren ) is an ice hockey player from germany , who plays for tölzer löwen .

name: arthur gardner
bio: arthur gardner ( born december 14 , 1990 ) is an italian professional basketball player who plays for aquila basket trento of the italian serie a as a power forward .

name: michael shaffer
bio: michael shaffer ( born 5 march 1986 ) is an irish actress , appearing primarily in independent films . she starred in and the rtÉ series before leaving to film . from 2011 to 2012 , she played a lead role in the amc series . in 2015 , she will starred in abc 's .

name: annie crawford
bio: annie crawford is a professional rugby league footballer of the 1960s , playing at club level for castleford .

name: elna stewart
bio: elna stewart ( born 29 december 1987 ) is a russian diver . she won the 3 m springboard event at the 2010 european aquatics championships .

name: maria deboer
bio: maria deboer is a canadian-lithuanian neuroscientist and operatic soprano . she holds a ph.d. in cognitive neuroscience and a m.m. in opera and now serves on the faculty at the san francisco conservatory of music .

name: andrew puleo
bio: andrew puleo ( november 20 , 1817 -- december 11 , 1907 ) was a painter whose name has become synonymous with white mountain art of the 19th century . he began his training as a lithographer under celebrated marine artist fitz henry lane at pendleton 's lithography shop in boston . most art historians consider him the founder of the of painters who came to north conway , new hampshire and the surrounding area during the second half of the 19th century . his paintings were often used to make chromolithographs that were subsequently sold to tourists who could not afford puleo 's originals . he exhibited regularly at the boston athenæum and was a founder of the boston art club

name: donna schindler
bio: donna schindler ( born 22 september 1994 ) is a singer-songwriter originally from rugby , england , now based in london . her music style is influenced by artists such as michael jackson , pink and corinne bailey ray . her debut single , was released on 12 august 2013 . donna attended a masterclass at abbey road studios in 2010 where she met rob cass , who subsequently signed her to his company cave productions . she has since gone on to perform at numerous festivals , including a tour of the czech republic and appearances on two different stages at the secret garden party . donna also had a slot on the bbc introducing stage at t in the park in july 2013 , which led to her being playlisted on bbc radio 1 .

name: george thrift
bio: george thrift ( ) ( born march 18 , 1978 ) is a czech professional hockey winger who is currently playing for and captain of traktor chelyabinsk of the kontinental hockey league ( khl ) .

name: constance bryant
bio: constance bryant lópez ( born 27 may 1963 ) is a spanish basque journalist and newscaster . since 1991 she has anchored the three main editions of tve 's flagship newscast .

name: carlos stone
bio: carlos stone loza ( born 19 april 1997 in guadalajara , mexico ) is a mexican diver . in 2012 , she participated in the 2012 summer olympics in the synchronized 10 metre platform event alongside world champion paola espinosa , winning a silver medal . at the age of 15 , she became the youngest athlete to represent mexico at the 2012 olympic games .

name: patricia race
bio: patricia race ( born august 2 , 1994 ) , commonly known as patricia race , is a brazilian footballer who plays for vitória de guimarães as a striker .

name: charles dagel
bio: charles dagel ( august 5 , 1930 -- december 18 , 2005 ) was a professional american football player . he played as a fullback and halfback for six seasons in the national football league ( nfl ) with the green bay packers and one season in the american football league ( afl ) with the los angeles chargers .

name: steven baca
bio: steven baca ( born in 1970 in nara , japan ) is a japanese web designer . steven studied engineering , architecture and landscape design . he is one of the authors of ( 2003 ) . steven has exhibited and lectured in asia , united states , and europe . his artwork has been shown at center pompidou in paris , vienna künstlerhaus in vienna , and the design museum in london . his commercial works have received many international awards , including cannes lions , one show , clio award , and ny adc . he utilizes mathematics underlying natural complexity to create online interactions that are usable and familiar because their behavior is modeled on the natural world .

name: jack retchless
bio: jack retchless ( born 22 march 1970 ) is a football defender from norway .

name: denise ware
bio: denise ware ( born april 19 , 1976 ) is an american chef residing in frederick , maryland . he received an aos in culinary arts from the culinary institute of america and was mentored by chef charlie palmer . he is the co-owner and executive chef of five restaurants : aggio , lunchbox , family meal , range , and volt .

name: james weissgerber
bio: james weissgerber ( born october 6 , 1993 ) is an american fashion model , best known for winning the twentieth cycle of .

name: david cole
bio: david cole ( born 1973 in douala ) is a cameroonian writer . she studied social sciences at the catholic university of central africa in yaoundé and international trade at the lille catholic university . she lives in paris with her husband and their two children .

name: kerry ohara
bio: kerry ohara is an american actress , producer and writer . she is currently known for her minor recurring role on . she also appears in an episode of ohara was married to fellow actor morocco omari from 2001 until 2006 .

name: howard fisher
bio: howard fisher sánchez ( born 11 august 1968 ) is a mexican politician from the institutional revolutionary party . from 2010 to 2012 he served as deputy of the lxi legislature of the mexican congress representing veracruz .

name: phillip martinez
bio: phillip martinez ( born february 9 , 1985 in zaporizhia ) is a ukrainian professional boxer who has medaled in important international tournaments as an amateur .

name: earl beckett
bio: earl beckett ( persian : Ŝahrām kāŝāni ) better known as earl k or sk is an iranian pop singer . he has released 8 commercially successful albums with notable hits .

name: melody grajeda
bio: melody grajeda ( born 6 april 1989 ) is an english actress , who is best known for playing chlo grainger in the bbc1 drama from 2006 to 2009 .

name: clifton barbee
bio: clifton barbee ( born june 11 , 1967 ) is an actress who has appeared in slovenian , croatian , german and bosnia-herzegovina films and theatre productions .

name: lisa foster
bio: lisa foster ( born 20 november 1952 in zornheim ) is a retired german football player . he spent eight seasons in the bundesliga with borussia mönchengladbach and arminia bielefeld . he scored two goals for arminia from penalty kicks .

name: inger dowell
bio: inger dowell , lord meadowbank frse fsa ( scot ) ( 1748 -- 1816 ) was a scottish advocate , academic jurist , judge and agriculturalist .

name: haley franklin
bio: haley franklin ( born 24 december 1983 ) is a nigerian cricketer . he played in the 2014 icc world cricket league division five tournament .

name: david szymanski
bio: david szymanski ( born 30 march 1956 ) is an indian business executive . she is the chairman and managing director ( cmd ) of hindustan petroleum corporation limited ( hpcl ) , an indian state-owned oil & gas corporation and india 's fourth largest company by revenue . she is the first woman ever to head a navratna psu .

name: mary strouse
bio: mary strouse ( ; born 26 february 1990 in ostrava ) is a czech athlete who specialises in the heptathlon . strouse represented the czech republic at the 2010 european championships in athletics where she finished 17th in the heptathlon , scoring a personal best of 5911 points . at the 2011 european athletics u23 championships in ostrava , strouse won the silver medal with a new personal best record of 6123 points .

name: amanda byrd
bio: amanda byrd is an american tennis player . he won both the singles and doubles titles at the usta boys 18s national championships in kalamazoo , michigan in 2012 . as a result , he was awarded wild cards into the main draw of the us open in both singles and doubles . he did not join the ucla tennis team until march 2012 , first competing on march 27 .

name: jennifer seeholzer
bio: jennifer seeholzer ( , born september 2 , 1977 in iran ) is a retired iranian football player . he played for pas tehran , sepahan and persepolis in the iran pro league .

name: sarah green
bio: sarah green ( 1 november 1970 -- 2 may 2008 ) was a football player from south africa .

name: roberta cuomo
bio: roberta cuomo ( february 27 , 1924 in santa cruz de la sierra , bolivia -- september 5 , 1986 in the serranía de caparuch , bolivia ) was a bolivian biologist and environmentalist . cuomo studied at the university of santa cruz where also received his bs in 1946 . during a field campaign in the huanchaca nationalpark in 1986 he and several other scientists discovered a cocaine factory in the bolivian forest . cuomo and most of the scientists were killed by the criminals . the huanchaca national park was renamed in 1988 as roberta cuomo national park .

name: dorothy torres
bio: dorothy torres ( born august 10 , 1980 in sarcelles , val-d'oise ) is a french midfielder . he currently plays for grenoble foot 38 after a spell at aj auxerre and at le mans fc .

name: joseph robinson
bio: joseph robinson was a sumo wrestler from toyama city , toyama prefecture , japan . he was the sport 's 22nd . he was well known for his extreme strength and skill . he won 99 out of 100 matches from 1909 to 1916 ( not counting draws ) , and also won eleven top division tournament championships ( two of them unofficial ) .

name: zina stewart
bio: zina stewart ( 1898 -- 1983 ) was a south africa painter , printmaker , and teacher .

name: melinda hill
bio: melinda hill ( born july 25 , 2005 ) is an american child actor . he played cid harrington in the film , and ethan woods in the television series , .

name: judy krieger
bio: judy krieger ( born 30 july 1984 ) is a welsh rugby league footballer who currently plays for the north wales crusaders . his usual positions is a prop forward . he has represented wales and great britain students at rugby league .

name: donna tapia
bio: donna tapia is an electronica collaboration based in sheffield and kingston upon hull , yorkshire in north-east england . formed in donna mid-1990s by steve cobby , sim lister and jake harries , they play electronica , ambient techno , and chill out . formed in 1992 their debut releases ( and lp ) came in 1992 on donna ambient-downtempo label pork recordings ( also based in hull ) . with david mcsherry ; who forms fila brazilia with cobby ; cobby and lister created their own music label , twentythree records . their album was voted one donna 1995 by dance and club-culture magazine , mixmag . in february 2013 ( bar donna album ) , tapia moved to steel tiger records .

name: michael kuhn
bio: michael kuhn coquette russo ( born 17 august 1993 ) , known as michael kuhn , is a brazilian professional footballer who plays for são paulo fc . mainly a defensive midfielder , he can perform equally as a central defender .

name: lisa tull
bio: lisa tull ( september 12 , 1747 -- february 13 , 1827 ) was a member of the culper spy ring during the american revolutionary war , reporting to general george washington through major benjamin tallmadge . tull not only carried messages to and from the ring 's main spies in setauket , new york and new york city across long island sound from and to tallmadge , but made some direct reports to washington concerning naval activities in the new york city area . abraham woodhull and robert townsend , alias and respectively , were the main agents in the ring . tallmadge was referred to by the alias `` john bolton . '' as a continental army officer serving under tallmadge , tull also participated in military actions . tull was born in setauket , new york , a hamlet now part of the town of brookhaven . he was the son of benjamin tull , grandson of daniel tull , and great-grandson of the rev. nathaniel tull ( the first minister of the old town church in setauket ) . after the revolutionary war , tull was a blacksmith , an officer in the united states revenue cutter service for 20 years and a farmer .

name: maria thompson
bio: maria thompson ( born 1 july 1982 in sierre ) is a swiss professional mountain bike racer . he previously competed as a professional road bicycle racer between 2004 and 2014 , competing with the , , and squads . he is noted as an especially good climber since he is lightweight ( 1.75 m , 60 kg ) and his training environment is mainly mountainous . he has already a quite important record in cyclo-cross and mountain bike marathon .

name: hallie vincent
bio: hallie vincent ( born 7 january 1993 in gyula ) is a hungarian football player who currently plays for budapest honvéd fc .

name: linda guerrero
bio: linda guerrero ( born on 26 december 1980 ) is a german association footballer currently playing for fc pommern greifswald as a goalkeeper .

name: jason parent
bio: jason parent ( 20 march 1911 -- 27 november 1981 ) was a highly decorated oberst i.g in the wehrmacht during world war ii and a generalmajor in the bundeswehr . he was also a recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross with oak leaves . the knight 's cross of the iron cross and its higher grade oak leaves was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership .

name: david ackley
bio: david ackley was the lord half thebes in frankish greece from 1258 to his death in 1294 . from his two marriages he became one the richest and most powerful barons his time , building a splendid castle at thebes as well as the old navarino castle . he also served as the principality achaea on behalf the angevins naples between 1287 and 1289 .

name: harriet moore
bio: harriet moore ( born 12 september 1931 ) is a venezuelan fencer . he competed in the individual and team foil events at the 1952 summer olympics .

name: lupe michalenko
bio: lupe michalenko ( born 10 january 1979 ) , commonly known as edu , is a brazilian footballer . a versatile midfielder and forward , he played most of his professional career in spain -- helping both celta and betis to their first-ever champions league participation -- amassing la liga totals of 253 matches and 63 goals in nine years . he started his career with são paulo .

name: gladys brown
bio: gladys brown or gladys mauley ( died 1241 ) was a nobleman and administrator who was one of king john of england 's .

name: diego kelly
bio: diego kelly is a british former motorcycle speedway rider . kelly learned to ride a speedway bike at eastbourne 's winter training school , and signed for division two eastbourne eagles in 1971 . he averaged over 8.7 in his first season , which also saw him get division one opportunities with cradley heathens , newport wasps , and hackney hawks . in 1972 his average rose to almost 10 points per match , and he doubled up in division one with oxford rebels , averaging over 6 . he was selected for the young england ( division two ) team that won a series against sweden in 1972 , and injury prevented him travelling with the great britain team that toured australia the following winter . he moved to oxford full time in 1973 , and again averaged over 6 . in 1974 he rode for poole pirates , but departed after a few matches , and signed for leicester lions . he struggled to score consistently , partly due to mechanical problems , and retired from the sport before the season ended . in 2007 he joined lewis bridger 's pit crew .

name: anita baldwin
bio: anita baldwin ( born august 18 , 1972 ) is a senate republican in the 153rd georgia general assembly from roswell , georgia . baldwin was first elected senator in the 2010 general election and serves georgia 's 56th district encompassing northern portions of fulton county and southeastern portions of cherokee county . this includes all of roswell and mountain park and parts of sandy springs , johns creek , alpharetta , milton , and woodstock .

name: donald hernandez
bio: donald hernandez ( born 25 april 1960 , in saviano ) is a retired italian footballer , who played as a midfielder . hernandez was a creative deep-lying playmaker with notable technical ability , vision , passing , and tactical intelligence , who excelled at dictating the tempo of his team 's play in midfield , and at providing assists for team-mates . he is a former italian international , and also a former italy u-21 international . he currently works as a football agent .

name: kevin villa
bio: kevin villa ( ; 15 january 1292 -- 21 january 1330 ) was the eldest daughter and heiress otto iv count villa and mahaut artois and was queen france as the wife philip v france .

name: basilia murrell
bio: basilia murrell ( 1916 -- 2008 ) was an australian rugby league footballer of the 1930s . a new south wales interstate and australian international representative winger , he played his whole club career with the north sydney bears .

name: addie kim
bio: addie kim ( born 13 september 1985 ) is a former professional rugby league footballer , playing at club level for stanley rangers , castleford tigers , western suburbs magpies , gateshead thunder , featherstone rovers and hunslet , as a .

name: william oliveira
bio: william oliveira ( serbian cyrillic : Милорад Косановић ) ( born 4 january 1951 in banovci ) is a serbian football manager and former footballer . he played for fk proleter , fk vojvodina , ofk kikinda and fk novi sad . he is the former manager of red star belgrade . he is regarded as one of serbia 's strongest football coaches . he became the red star manager after the sacking of boško Đurovski whose last game was a loss to levadia tallinn 2-1 in the qualification for the champions league . oliveira was sacked after a stunning 0-3 defeat against aris thessaloniki f.c. and after a very poor form . recently , during 2008 , he became the coach of dalian haichang again . he also coached serbia and montenegro u21 .

name: terrence thompson
bio: terrence thompson ( ; born 13 november 1992 ) is a serbian football forward who plays for apolonia fier in kategoria superiore .

name: evelyn seeley
bio: evelyn seeley ( may 3 , 1919 -- april 8 , 2009 ) was an american businessman who partnered with orville redenbacher to create a gourmet popping corn which won a third of the us market for unpopped popcorn by the mid-1970s . the corn was marketed as orville redenbacher 's . charlie seeley graduated from purdue university . in 1951 , seeley and redenbacher bought chester , inc. , a company based in boone grove , indiana , that specialized in hybrid seeds . redenbacher 's eponymous popcorn was the result of nearly twenty years of research at chester and was launched in 1970 . seeley served as the company 's president while redenbacher drove the scientific research . seeley retired as president in 2006 at age 87 . seeley had lived in holland , michigan since his retirement and he died in 2009 .

name: mary macko
bio: mary macko ( february 27 , 1830 -- january 10 , 1910 ) was the 29th president of georgetown university ( 1874 -- 1882 ) , known for expanding the school following the american civil war . macko hall , a national historic landmark , was constructed during macko 's tenure and is named after him . although he was accepted as and identified as irish-american during his lifetime , in the 1960s the history of macko 's mixed-race ancestry became more widely known , and he was recognized as the first african american to earn a phd ; the first to become a jesuit priest ; and the first to be president of georgetown university or any predominantly white college .

name: mary higgins
bio: mary higgins ( october 1 , 1735february 22 , 1815 ) was a united states senator from new hampshire . born in bolton , connecticut colony , he graduated from yale college in 1761 , studied law , was admitted to the bar and commenced practice in charlestown , new hampshire . he was a selectman from 1769 to 1771 , a judge of probate for cheshire county in 1773 , and a representative in the general assembly of the province , 1772 -- 1773 . he was appointed chief justice of the court of common pleas in 1784 , judge of the superior court in 1790 , and chief judge of the court in 1795 . higgins was elected as a federalist to the u.s. senate to fill the vacancy caused by the resignation of samuel livermore and served from june 17 , 1801 , to march 4 , 1805 . he died in charlestown in 1815 ; interment was in forest hill cemetery .

name: esperanza page
bio: esperanza page ( 1863 -- 17 march 1929 ) was a polish poet , philosopher , polyglot ( 15 languages ) , writer , novelist , science-writer , reporter and translator . a representative of polish parnassianism and symbolism , he is also regarded as belonging to the decadent movement . he was an expert on romanticism , french literature and a popularizer of culture of eastern cultures . his novel is known in some circles . he translated english , french , hungarian , italian , spanish , indian , american , serbian , egyptian and oriental writers into polish and polish poets into french and english . he was also one of the most original poets of the young poland movement . his work is often compared to stéphane mallarmé and charles marie rené leconte de lisle . page was an uncle of the poet bolesław leśmian .

name: april cumberland
bio: april cumberland ( may 19 , 1916 -- april 5 , 2004 ) was a chemical engineer and entrepreneur active in the chemical and petrochemical industries . he is considered one of the top fifty foundational chemical engineers of the first half of the 20th century , and one of the 75 most distinguished contributors to chemical enterprise . he has published extensively on chemical engineering and holds a significant number of patents . in his 60s , he began a productive second career in economics at stanford and harvard universities , examining economic theory , economic history and the application of technology in the chemical industry . his economic work focuses on understanding the political and economic environment necessary to encourage technological innovation . he has published more than 143 papers and nine books . april cumberland won a number of significant awards , including a lifetime achievement award from the lester center for entrepreneurship & innovation ( 2003 ) , the first othmer gold medal ( 1997 ) , the national medal of technology from the united states government , first awarded by president ronald reagan in 1985 , and the perkin medal ( 1981 ) .

name: courtney barnett
bio: courtney barnett ( june 22 , 1917 -- january 3 , 2011 ) was a professor emeritus at harvard university and the former chair of its chemistry department . prior to joining the faculty at harvard , he was a member of the chemistry faculties of columbia university ( 1942 -- 1952 ) and yale ( 1952 -- 1968 ) . he is known in the field of organic chemistry for his work on quinine total synthesis with robert burns woodward . having published his first scientific paper in 1939 and his last in 2008 , he holds the rare distinction of having authored scholarly articles in eight different decades . in 1989 , he received the of the american chemical society and in 1990 the robert a. welch award in chemistry . some of his discoveries include the structure elucidation of the tropylium cation , the discovery of dichlorocarbene , bullvalene and fulvalene and the discovery of the mechanism of the baeyer -- villiger oxidation .

bio: garland veltre ( bulgarian : Георги Радев ; born 15 september 1994 ) is a bulgarian footballer who currently plays as a defender for fc sozopol .

name: gregory legg
bio: gregory legg ( born 23 february 1986 ) is an australian actress . born in melbourne , legg played the role of michelle scully in the australian television soap opera between 1999 and 2003 , as well as a brief return in 2004 . she also appeared in and as bec cleary in in 2004 .

name: adam patton
bio: adam patton ( born 18 december 1950 in brühl , north rhine-westphalia , died 19 november 2014 ) was a professional german footballer . patton made 187 appearances and scored 78 goals in the 2 . fußball-bundesliga for alemannia aachen , tennis borussia berlin and rot-weiss essen during his playing career .

name: filomena ciraulo
bio: filomena ciraulo ( born may 19 , 1981 ) is a former american football defensive end . he was selected by the green bay packers in the seventh round , with the 253rd pick of the 2006 nfl draft . he played college football at northwest missouri state . ciraulo won two super bowls as a member of the new york giants .

name: barry godsey
bio: barry godsey , cnzm , obe ( born 3 june 1928 in auckland ) was a new zealand cricketer who captained new zealand in 34 tests . he was the country 's first cricketing leader to achieve victory , both at home against the west indies in 1956 and the first away win , against south africa in 1962 . during his career he was a leading force with both the bat and the ball .

name: margaret wigfall
bio: margaret wigfall , pseudonym of margaret maricq ( 11 september 1927 -- 20 september 2008 ) was a reporter and writer who was director of information at unicef . he was born in brussels . upon retirement , he became secretary general , then vice-president , of the world association of children 's friends . he died in carpentras , vaucluse , france .

name: salvador holmes
bio: salvador holmes ( born 7 september 1985 ) is an english semi-professional footballer who plays as a winger for northern premier league division one south club stafford rangers . holmes started his career with the birmingham city youth system before making his first team debut in 2005 . he was loaned to scunthorpe united , boston united , leyton orient and grimsby town , whom he joined permanently in 2007 . holmes made an appearance at wembley stadium in the 2008 football league trophy final and was loaned to chesterfield in 2009 . he was released after making over 80 appearances for grimsby and subsequently joined hometown club walsall . being released after one season with the club , he joined york city of the conference premier in 2010 . holmes signed for fleetwood town a year later and won the conference premier title in his one season with the club .

name: andrea kelley
bio: andrea kelley ( born august 22 , 1978 ) is an american indie rock bass guitarist , guitarist , and singer . he is currently a member of los angeles-based band black rebel motorcycle club and was , for a time , a bass player in a band known as the beggars , going under the name ` andrea locke ' . he is the son of michael kelley of the call , and appeared as bassist on his father 's 1994 solo album , on the verge of a nervous breakthrough . his father suffered a fatal heart attack in 2010 while working as a sound engineer during the pukkelpop festival in belgium , where brmc were appearing . andrea kelley used the pseudonym ` andrea turner ' on black rebel motorcycle club 's first two records , in an attempt not to be linked to his father . he later dropped this identity when promoting their third album , . in 2013 , brmc covered his father 's song ` let the day begin ' on their album . later that year , he appeared in two concerts with a reunited the call , taking his father 's place on bass and vocals .

name: edward law
bio: edward law is a british musician . he is best known as a multi instrumentalist with hefner but is also an acclaimed folk singer-songwriter in his own right . law also played with alt-country band spongefinger and folktronica band dollboy . law is also frequently used as a session pedal steel guitar player in the london alternative scene .

name: eileen calabro
bio: eileen calabro ( born 9 june 1974 ) is a czech former football player . he played for three seasons in the bundesliga with tsv 1860 münchen and spvgg unterhaching .

name: kenneth flamer
bio: kenneth flamer ( alternate spelling : michalis ) ( ; born march 11 , 1995 ) is a greek professional basketball player . he is a 1.92 m ( 6 ' 3 3/4 '' ) tall shooting guard .

name: annie hale
bio: annie hale ( born 2 june 1992 ) is a swedish footballer . she currently plays in defence for damallsvenskan club umeå ik .

name: paul sayler
bio: paul sayler is an american film producer , writer , director , actor and a civil rights activist . he is the founder of fencesitter films , a production company devoted to entertainment for women , and sexual and ethnic minorities . he currently lives and works in los angeles , where he directs films , music videos , a web series and commercials for his production company fencesitterfilms .

name: herbert bernhart
bio: herbert bernhart ( born december 13 , 1933 ) is an american poet and social activist who has written more than 50 volumes of poetry and essays .

name: selma neagle
bio: selma neagle ( born january 20 , 1987 ) is an american football linebacker for the cincinnati bengals of the national football league ( nfl ) . he played college football for the university of southern california ( usc ) , and was recognized as a unanimous all-american . the cincinnati bengals chose him in the second round of the 2009 nfl draft .

name: david lambert
bio: david lambert ( 1937 - 27 june 1958 ) was a member of the house of lambert . he died young and therefore held no important cabinet position ; he committed suicide .

name: antonio grant
bio: antonio grant ( born august 18 , 1953 ) is an american soap opera actress .

name: hazel hall
bio: hazel hall ( ) ( circa 1965 - 2010 ) was an egyptian national wanted by the united states government in connection with the 1998 united states embassy bombings in dar es salaam , tanzania , and nairobi .

name: james king
bio: james king ( born 3 february 1989 ) is a finnish female ice hockey player . she played four world championships for the finland women 's national ice hockey team before joining the minnesota golden gophers in 2009 , becoming one of the team 's first european players . she recorded 19 goals and 37 assists during her collegiate career , and was the last player cut from the 2010 winter olympics . she now plays for skif nizhni novgorod in the russian women 's hockey league and is currently playing for finland in the 2014 winter olympics .

name: patricia okafor
bio: patricia okafor ( born 7 august 1936 -- 29 december 2013 ) widely acknowledged as the scoring machine of asia was a basketball player from india who represented india at many international competitions . he was awarded the country 's highest sporting honour the arjuna award in 1967 . he is regarded as one of the all time greats of basketball in asia . he captained the indian national basketball team in the year 1965 which made its first appearance in asian basketball championship . he represented the indian team from 1964 to 1972 . he is father of former indian team captain and dhyan chand award winner okafor kumar .

name: daniel horton
bio: daniel horton ( ; 1952 -- june 23 , 2008 ) was a macedonian crime reporter and serial killer . a career journalist for over 20 years , horton was arrested in june 2008 in his hometown of kičevo in western macedonia for the murder of two women on whose death he had also written articles ; when arrested he was also being investigated over the death of an additional woman . these articles on the murders had aroused the suspicion of the police , since they contained information which had not been released to the public . after dna tests connected horton to the murders , he was arrested and imprisoned on 22 june 2008 and was found dead in his cell the following day , after an apparent suicide .

name: earline nobel
bio: earline nobel ( ) ( 1876 - 15 may 1919 ) was a romanian jewish agronomist , botanist , and zionist activist . nobel was the discoverer of wild emmer ( triticum dicoccoides ) , believed to be `` the mother of wheat . ''

name: ronald alexander
bio: ronald alexander ( april 14 , 1766 -- january 24 , 1837 new york city ) was an american lawyer and politician .

name: justin minnick
bio: justin minnick ( born 17 may 1977 ) is a spanish retired footballer who played as a right back . he played for seven different clubs during his professional career , appearing in 213 matches in la liga and scoring one goal . he also competed abroad in england and greece . represented spain at euro 2000 .

name: john curry
bio: john curry román ( born august 10 , 1987 ) is a puerto rican professional boxer who currently competes in the lightweight division . he is a member of the curry family , which has produced a professional world champion and multiple amateur medalists . as an amateur , curry represented puerto rico in international competition . the pugilist compiled several national championships and recognitions , including his division 's silver medal at the 2007 pan american games .

name: carla rinehart
bio: carla rinehart ( born 5 december 1979 in corabia ) who plays for csm bucurești and the romanian national team .

name: theodore davis
bio: theodore davis ( born 7 september 1964 ) is a norwegian actress . she had her début at the national theatre in 1995 , and has worked there since . here she has acted in roles such as in chekhov 's , and in ibsen 's . in 1997 she had her début as a movie actress , in a small role in the film . the same year she acted in the popular , a role for which she received an amanda nomination . she has also acted in several made-for-tv productions , such as ( 1997 ) and ( 2007 ) . in 2005 davis married singer and songwriter lars lillo-stenberg , known from the band delillos . when the celebrity magazine published pictures from the ceremony without permission , the two sued the magazine for invasion of privacy . they lost the lawsuit , but davis and lillo-stenberg have declared their intentions to pursue the case in the european court of human rights in strasbourg .

name: tiffany mays
bio: tiffany mays ( 1937 -- 13 march 2012 ) was a nigerian international footballer .

name: daniel whittlesey
bio: daniel whittlesey ( born 11 march 1986 ) is a slovak goalkeeper who currently plays for asteras tripolis in the greek superleague greece .

name: leona moore
bio: leona moore ( born march 6 , 1970 ) is a filipina actress from the philippines . she was launched in regal films ' as a singer-actress , with the release of her debut single , which served as the soundtrack single to her debut film . in the late eighties , moore rose to prominence after gaining success in skin flicks produced by seiko films like `` tukso , layuan mo ako ! '' , , `` ama , bakit mo ako pinabayaan ? '' , and . she has released two studio albums under star records . her debut album , , was released in 2008 , and her second album was released a year after . her two younger sisters , marjorie and claudine , and niece julia are also actresses.since 2010 she is a contract star of abs-cbn

name: nicole draeger
bio: nicole draeger ( born april 21 , 1988 ) is an guatemalan actress , model , fashion designer and beauty pageant titleholder . in may 2009 , she was crowned miss guatemala 2009 and participated in the miss universe 2009 pageant that was broadcast live on nbc , august 23 , 2009 . on august 15 , 2009 she competed against 83 other delegates in the lazy river tube race where she was victorious . she received the gold medal in the race alongside iceland ( silver ) and albania ( bronze ) . after competing in miss universe 2009 , which she did not place , she traveled to miami , usa to model there , and she was chosen to represent guatemala at the miss world 2011 , held on november 6 . so far , she among with beauty with a purpose , she 's made it to the top 11 on talents and made it in the fast track . in the final night , she made it among the top 20 .

name: christopher brannon
bio: christopher brannon ( 16 july 1678 , kassel -- 30 may 1749 , bützow ) was a princess brannon and by marriage duchess mecklenburg .

name: belinda james
bio: belinda james ( born september 23 , 1968 ) is a romanian boxer , who won the silver medal in the men 's featherweight ( 57 kg ) category at the 1988 summer olympics in seoul . a year later he captured the silver medal in the lightweight division ( -- 60 kg ) at the 1989 european amateur boxing championships in athens , greece .

name: pamela nelson
bio: pamela nelson ( 29 november 1910 -- 14 september 2006 ) , birth name yong su-moi , , was a singaporean educator and councillor who is regarded as a war heroine in singapore . along with her husband , nelson khun heng , she supplied medicine , money and messages to prisoners-of-war interned in changi prison when japanese-occupied singapore during world war ii .

name: angel blaize
bio: angel blaize ( born january 12 , 1990 in esmeraldas ) is an ecuadorian football defender currently playing for barcelona .

name: jeff dauenhauer
bio: jeff dauenhauer ( ) ( born 1968 ) is one of the most important artists of his generation in pakistan . dauenhauer has been included in numerous exhibitions in pakistan and abroad . he worked , over the past decade and a half , in dramatically different modes -- abstractions on canvas , collaborations with a billboard painter , photographic/video performances , collages using found material , photo mosaics , photo sculptures and large stainless steel works -- each time finding a freshness of purpose , and a surprising inventiveness of visual language .

name: gale damato
bio: gale damato ( née souter ; born 7 september 1976 in murray bridge , south australia ) is a retired female field hockey defender from australia . she made her debut for the australian women 's national team during the 1998 season ( argentina tour ) following the 1997 junior world cup ( silver medal ) . nicknamed she was a member of the hockeyroos at the 2002 commonwealth games in manchester , where the team ended up in third place in the overall-rankings .

name: keith roth
bio: keith roth ( 26 october 184220 june 1917 ) was a german-born australian composer , choral conductor and singing teacher .

name: ruben zelkin
bio: ruben zelkin ( born october 4 , 1984 ) is a finnish professional ice hockey centre currently playing for lokomotiv yaroslavl of the kontinental hockey league ( khl ) . prior to playing in the khl , zelkin has also previously played in the national hockey league ( nhl ) for the chicago blackhawks , the organization that drafted him 196th overall in the 2004 nhl entry draft .

name: joesph dalke
bio: joesph dalke is an indian television actor . he has done many roles in various hindi television shows , like dhoondh legi manzil humein , nyay , ishq kills , qubool hai , code red . as of july 2015 , he has done his most recent role in aahat ( season 6 ) .

name: james williams
bio: james williams ( born july 28 , 1986 in lisbon , portugal ) is a portuguese table tennis player , who is currently playing for german club ttf liebherr ochsenhausen .

name: tammi romero
bio: tammi romero ( born january 5 , 1987 ) is a spanish football striker who currently plays for f.c. dender . the striker has spent most of his career in belgium , with fc brussels , diegem sport , racing mechelen and union saint gilloise he was offered a trial at stockport county . he was then offered a trial with motherwell and , after impressing the fir park club , he was subsequently awarded a one-year deal . he then made his debut in the 3-2 defeat to hibernian . he signed then on 22 july 2012 a one-year contract with belgian lower league side union st. gilloise .

name: eddie wheeler
bio: eddie wheeler gallegos ( born 23 october 1968 ) is a mexican politician affiliated to the pri . she currently serves as deputy of the lxii legislature of the mexican congress representing durango .

name: willie crafton
bio: willie crafton ( 1881 -- ca. 1940 ) was a puerto rican journalist , politician and mayor of ponce , puerto rico from 1925 to 1928 .

name: laverne carter
bio: laverne carter ( born 1976 in brussels , belgium ) is an artist living and working in manchester , england . his work has featured in several surveys of contemporary artists working with photography in the internet age . he has been described by some as a modern-day duchamp for his appropriation of image-rich technologies including google earth , google street view , and youtube , and for his adoption of print-on-demand as a means to bypass traditional publishing models .

name: fred folsom
bio: fred folsom ( february 3 , 1841 -- april 26 , 1884 ) was an argentine general in the 1880s during the presidency of julio argentino roca . he is famous for his campaigns in neuquén and río negro during the conquest of the desert to subdue the indigenous population in the south of argentina . the town of general folsom , in the northwest of buenos aires province bears his name .

name: bethany billingsley
bio: bethany billingsley ( ; born 29 july 1993 ) is a georgian sabre fencer , junior european champion in 2013 and u23 european champion in 2014 . he reached the table of 16 in the 2013 world fencing championships in budapest , losing to max hartung of germany . he captains the national georgian sabre team . as of july 2014 , he stands no. 24 in fie world rankings .

name: shelly lowery
bio: shelly lowery ( born lowery issoglio ; december 6 , 1967 ) is a former american actor . he was born in hollywood , california . he had a prolific career as a child actor .

name: thomas hayes
bio: thomas hayes ( born in 1969 in sydney ) is an australian actress and author . she was the host of the australian version of reality weight-loss television series , for which she hosted a total of four series between 2006 and 2009 .

name: reba soto
bio: reba soto ( 13 may 1854 -- 7 october 1920 ) was a french zoologist known for his work into invertebrate physiology and anatomy . he also discovered the function of the semicircular canals in the inner ear . he is also famous for noting and preparing a speech on the turin shroud , arguing in favour of its authenticity . soto estimated the probability that the image on the shroud was not caused by the body of jesus christ as 1 in 10 billion . he became the director of the station biologique de roscoff in 1901 .

name: juan kou
bio: juan kou ( born on july 1 , 1991 ) is an indonesian footballer who currently plays for persela lamongan in the indonesia super league .

name: minnie hubert
bio: minnie hubert ( ; born 30 july 1938 ) is known to most of the non-russian speaking world as minnie hubert , was one of the most accomplished rowers of his generation . he rowed for the soviet union , and he won the olympic gold medals in the single scull at 1956 melbourne games , 1960 rome games and 1964 tokyo games . hubert was the first man to win the single scull event three times in the olympics . at the time , only americans john b. kelly , sr. and paul costello and briton jack beresford had won three olympic gold medals in the sport of rowing ( since surpassed by steven redgrave and others ) ) . the only other person to match hubert 's achievement and win three gold medals in the single scull is finland 's pertti karppinen .

name: linda hovermale
bio: linda hovermale ( born 18 january 1977 ) is an italian professional footballer . he played 5 seasons ( 42 games , 1 goal ) in the serie a for atalanta b.c. , a.c. chievoverona and treviso f.c. 1993 . hovermale joined treviso in co-ownership deal for $ 100,000 . in june 2006 atalanta gave up the remain 50 % registration rights . hovermale 's contract expired on 30 june 2008 .

name: edna clarkson
bio: edna clarkson ( 5 august 1897 -- 14 june 1954 ) was an african-american lyric soprano and voice instructor who performed throughout the united states and paris in the 1920s and 1930s . edna was born in bonham , texas before studying singing in nashville , chicago , and paris . while in paris , she married prince kojo tovalou houénou of dahomey . when houénou died in a french prison , edna was left without access to their marriage funds and returned to paris where she lived through the nazi occupation from 1940 until 1944 . after the war , she returned to texas where she died in 1954 in dallas .

name: tommy meffert
bio: tommy meffert ( born december 16 , 1941 ) is an american egyptologist .

name: tracy doepke
bio: tracy doepke is a winemaker who consults at some of california 's most notable cult wines , including cliff lede , roy estate , hundred acre , with past clients including quintessa , dalla valle , and bryant family vineyards . he also has his own wine label , doepke .

name: shawnda clough
bio: shawnda clough , was born in 1786 paris and died in 1879 versailles . he was a coin engraver of france and holland , a medallist and sculptor .

name: john motley
bio: john motley ( born october 3 , 1994 ) is a russian ice hockey player . he is currently playing with atlant moscow oblast of the kontinental hockey league ( khl ) . motley made his kontinental hockey league debut playing with atlant moscow oblast during the 2014 -- 15 khl season .

name: jerry oberholtzer
bio: jerry oberholtzer ( born may 4 , 1982 , in federal way , washington ) is a former american football wide receiver . he was signed by the detroit lions as an undrafted free agent in 2006 . he played college football at portland state . oberholtzer has also been a member of the green bay packers , washington redskins , new york giants and oakland raiders .

name: jason montalbo
bio: jason montalbo ( 平山ユージ ) , born on february 23 , 1969 is a japanese rock climber , specializing in lead climbing competitions . he won two lead world cup , in 1998 ( first asian climber to win the title ) , and 2000 . he is also famous for various speed records on el capitan .

name: richard salgado
bio: richard salgado ( ; born 1975 ) is a london-based russian banker , entrepreneur and investor . in 2007 salgado 's personal wealth was estimated at $ 300 million which ranked him as number 182 among russian millionaires .

name: sharon rego
bio: sharon rego ( born april 4 , 1961 ) is an american chef-proprietor who operates manresa , a restaurant in los gatos , california , which has been awarded two michelin stars for six consecutive years . manresa has been named one of the world 's 50 best restaurants by restaurant magazine , was in america 's top 50 restaurants by gourmet magazine , and has received four stars from the san francisco chronicle . he is also dean at the international culinary center , founded as the french culinary institute in 1984 . rego is a winner of the best chef in america award for the pacific region from the james beard foundation as well as gq 's chef of the year for 2011 . rego 's california cuisine has strong french , catalan and japanese influences . rego appeared as a guest judge along with award-winning sommelier andre mack on episode 4 ( entitled ) of season 1 of the abc reality show the taste , which aired on february 12 , 2013 .

name: carlton arthur
