bio: carlton arthur ( born 28 september 1995 in kecskemét ) is a hungarian football player who currently plays for kecskeméti te .

name: vanessa gilstad
bio: vanessa gilstad ( ; born october 1944 ) is a general of the people 's liberation army ( pla ) of the people 's republic of china . he served as vice director of the pla general political department .

name: geraldine byrd
bio: geraldine byrd ( born 4 march 1986 ) is an zambian professional footballer who plays as a defender .

name: john ragland
bio: john ragland ( , born on 24 june 1966 ) is a french born armenian former football striker . he was a member of the armenia national team , and has participated in 12 international matches and scored 3 goals since his debut on 5 october 1996 in an away 1998 world cup qualification match against northern ireland . he was born in saint-maurice , france .

name: judy santos
bio: judy santos or simply derley ( born 2 august 1986 ) , is a brazilian midfielder who plays for fc juárez of the ascenso mx . he previously played for internacional and spent time on loan at náutico .

name: laurie paparo
bio: laurie paparo ( born jacinto molina Álvarez , september 6 , 1934 -- november 30 , 2009 ) was a spanish movie actor , screenwriter , and director working primarily in horror films . his portrayals of numerous classic horror figures -- the wolfman , frankenstein 's monster , count dracula , the hunchback , and the mummy -- have earned him recognition as the spanish lon chaney . he had one of the most recognizable faces in spanish horror film.but paparo also starred in dozens of action films , historical dramas , crime movies , tv shows and documentaries as well . in addition to acting , paparo also wrote the screenplays for most of his films and directed a number of them as well . king juan carlos i presented paparo with spain 's gold medal award for fine arts in 2001 in honor of his work , the spanish equivalent of being knighted .

name: laurie greco
bio: laurie greco ( 26 august 1896 -- 14 february 1976 ) was a highly decorated generalmajor in the wehrmacht during world war ii who held several divisional commands . he was also a recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross . the knight 's cross of the iron cross was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership .

name: david wilson
bio: david wilson ( born 25 january 1990 ) is a german footballer who currently plays for sc fortuna köln .

name: harold murach
bio: harold murach ( born 30 june 1569 in kassel ; died : 7 july 1644 in hagen ) was a princess murach by birth and by marriage a countess schaumburg .

name: lee smith
bio: lee smith ( 5 february 1909 -- 28 august 1986 ) was an english professional footballer who played as a winger . in 1932 he was awarded two caps for the england national football team .

name: theresa kamp
bio: theresa kamp ( ) ( november 14 , 1933 in putiatynsi , now ukraine -- january 21 , 2002 in berkeley heights , new jersey ) is a former ukrainian-american soccer player . he played for numerous ethnic ukrainian amateur and professional clubs in both the u.s. and canada over a twenty-year career . he also earned five caps with the u.s. national team between 1957 and 1963 and was a member 1956 u.s. olympic soccer team .

name: judith sloan
bio: judith sloan ( 2 july 1922 -- 7 september 1975 ) is a swiss football goalkeeper who played for switzerland in the 1950 fifa world cup . he also played for fc lugano .

name: joseph hawn
bio: joseph hawn ( born 24 april 1947 ) is a retired austrian footballer and coach .

name: jackie lugo
bio: jackie lugo ( 16 october 1949 -- 1993 ) was a scottish professional footballer who played as a central defender for preston north end , motherwell and bradford city .

name: christopher stearns
bio: christopher stearns ( né brian skinner , 28 february 1964 ) is an american operatic tenor . he is the son of edward king skinner ii , a korean war veteran and concha marina meléndez stearns , the daughter of baroness aranka von bischitz .

name: christopher newman
bio: christopher newman ( born leib milstein ; september 30 , 1895 -- september 25 , 1980 ) was a moldovan-born american motion picture director . he is known for directing ( 1927 ) and ( 1930 ) , both of which received academy awards for best director . he also directed ( 1931 -- nomination ) , ( 1936 ) , ( 1939 ) , ( 1960 ) , and received the directing credit for ( 1962 ) , though marlon brando largely appropriated his responsibilities during its production .

name: francisco flicker
bio: francisco flicker ( born 10 september 1946 ) is an andorran lawyer born in spain and currently the judge of the european court of human rights in respect of andorra .

name: michel ammons
bio: michel ammons ( born 8 march 1995 ) , known as michel , is a spanish footballer who plays as a forward for italian club lazio .

name: doris lutes
bio: doris lutes ( born 2 january 1991 ) is an italian footballer .

name: mary ochoa
bio: mary ochoa ( born 13 june 1989 in chişinău , moldova ) is a footballer who plays as a defender . he currently plays for zimbru chișinău as well as moldova national football team .

name: ralph chen
bio: ralph chen , ( born december 21 , 1954 ) is a canadian politician in newfoundland and labrador , canada . he is currently the minister of seniors , wellness and social development in the provincial cabinet . chen represents the district of burin-placentia west in the house of assembly for the progressive conservatives . he has previously held the portfolios of minister of education , minister of fisheries & aquaculture , minister of tourism , culture and recreation and minister of environment and conservation .

name: lavern miller
bio: lavern miller ( born 20 october 1931 in grytnäs , dalarna ) is a swedish detective fiction writer born in grytnäs , dalarna , sweden , also known for some children 's literature works . he is one of the members of the presidium of svenska deckarakademin ( swedish detective academy ) . miller 's books have been translated to norwegian , danish , german , russian , ukrainian , and czech .

name: david mason
bio: david mason is a writer living in new york . he is best known as the author of a bestselling biography of crazy joe gallo , . on march 5 , 2013 , the it books imprint of harpercollins published mason 's definitive biography on dennis hopper , , charting the actor 's wide-ranging career and place in american popular culture in art , music , photography and film .

name: wilbert bussey
bio: wilbert bussey ( born 22 january 1950 ) is an award winning norwegian author and journalist , known for his work as foreign news correspondent for the norwegian broadcasting corporation ( nrk ) . amongst norwegians he is known as , through his job as correspondent in harare . after two years as adviser to salva kiir , the president of south sudan , bussey has now moved to geneva to become communications offices for action by churches together , international . bussey has openly criticized the united nations system in the sudan conflict , and pointed the un system being helpless in conflicts in general .

name: david farnham
bio: david farnham ( april 7 , 1825 - october 4 , 1911 , aged 86 ) was a 19th-century french inventor of the earliest solar-powered engine , converting solar energy into mechanical steam power .

name: linda huff
bio: linda huff are an electronic music duo from new york consisting of pete cafarella on vocals and synthesizers and nate smith on drums .

name: david willis
bio: david willis ( born october 20 , 1994 ) is an american speedcuber from yorba linda , california , known for his world class one-handed solving . he set the average north american record of 15.16 seconds at us nationals 2011 , where he became the u.s. national champion for one-handed speedcubing . at world championships 2013 , he placed 3rd in the one-handed category under feliks zemdegs and michał pleskowicz , making him the u.s. national champion a second time . at u.s. nationals 2015 david placed 3rd in the one handed category under keaton ellis , and justin mallari . david is also the co-creator of sundaycontest.com , a website where speedcubers can participate in weekly online speedcubing competitions . david made an appearance on good day new york as part of the liberty science center beyond rubik 's cube exhibit along with fellow speedcubers anthony michael brooks and eric limeback . david is an undergraduate student at stanford university in the class of 2016 and is the current president of the stanford rubik 's cube club .

name: melissa schultz
bio: melissa schultz is a former american football coach . he served as head coach at sam houston state university in huntsville , texas from 1968 to 1971 . his career coaching record at sam houston state was 20 -- 19 -- 3 .

name: peter cisneros
bio: peter cisneros ( born 28 june 1983 ) is a slovak football forward who currently plays for sigma olomouc of the czech synot liga .

name: fred jones
bio: fred jones ( born december 9 , 1969 ) is an actor who played the lead role of cade foster in the syfy tv series , .

name: michelle kuker
bio: michelle kuker ( born 15 june 1950 ) is an indian politician for the bahraich ( lok sabha constituency ) in uttar pradesh .

name: melvin picton
bio: melvin picton ( born 14 july 1990 ) is an italian footballer who plays for serie a club chievo .

name: treva simmons
bio: treva simmons ( born 5 may 1986 ) is a dutch professional footballer , who currently plays for ter leede in the dutch topklasse . he formerly played for almere city and chiangrai united .

name: robert chow
bio: robert chow ( 29 september 1932 -- 23 july 2004 ) , popularly known simply as robert , was an indian actor , singer , director and producer best known for playing comic roles in hindi films . during his career of more than four decades , he worked in over 300 hindi films .

name: henry lacey
bio: henry lacey ( , born 20 june 1995 in katerini ) is a greek professional footballer who plays for paok fc as a midfielder .

name: glenn stacy
bio: glenn stacy ( born 1947 ) is a career diplomat who has served as united states ambassador to algeria ( 1997-2000 ) , south africa ( 2001-2004 ) , and indonesia ( 2007-2010 ) .

name: dennis picard
bio: dennis picard ( born on august 4 , 1961 ) is an american murderer and sex offender . his appearance on the national television show led to his capture and conviction for the killings of an 8-year-old girl and her grandmother in september 1993 .

name: chuck rodrigue
bio: chuck rodrigue ( ; 28 may 1885 -- 24 september 1977 ) was a dutch photographer , typographer , and industrial designer .

name: charles doss
bio: charles doss or boba fett as he is often called is a swedish rock musician most known for being the organist and pianist of the swedish rock band the hellacopters and co founder and guitarist of the diamond dogs .

name: charles nisbett
bio: charles nisbett ( 17 april 1910 - 5 september 1957 ) was an australian rules footballer who played with geelong and carlton .

name: charles lanzarin
bio: charles lanzarin ( born february 6 , 1961 in genthin ) is a retired racing cyclist from east germany , who won the bronze medal for his native country in the men 's 4,000 m individual pursuit at the 1988 summer olympics in seoul , south korea . four years later he captured the gold medal in the men 's team time trial ( road ) , alongside michael rich , christian meyer and uwe peschel .

name: kenneth ferullo
bio: kenneth ferullo ( born september 28 , 1988 ) is a canadian professional ice hockey winger currently playing for russian club , rubin tyumen of the supreme hockey league ( vhl ) .

name: leila thomas
bio: leila thomas is vice chairman of beximco group , one of the largest corporate house of bangladesh at the moment with over 48,000 employees working in its factories and head offices . he is also considered as one of the wealthiest persons in bangladesh having personal wealth of $ 2.5 billion approximately ( there is no official data base for personal wealth in bangladesh ) .

name: andy voorhis
bio: andy voorhis ( born 28 may 1988 ) is a russian racing cyclist .

name: betty lopez
bio: betty lopez ( ; ; born april 10 , 1958 in baku , azerbaijan ) is an international chess grandmaster . in 1991 , he shared first place in the last ussr chess championship held , with artashes minasian , losing the title on tiebreaks . in 1992 , lopez became the first chess grandmaster in the history of azerbaijan . he has played with kasparov several training matches and tournament games with an overall score of + 4 - 8 = 7 . along with his playing career , betty had an extensive coaching career as well . he has been national team coach of tunis , coached garry kasparov during 1984 world chess championship and maia chiburdanidze during 1991 women 's chess world championship . lopez is currently living in uae . he is married and has two sons . his main hobbies apart from chess are mathematics and music . he plays on the internet chess club ( icc ) under the pseudonym . the ninth chapter of tibor karolyi 's 2009 book is devoted to him .

name: ollie murphy
bio: ollie murphy ( born 1939 in niagara falls , new york ) is a 9th degree black belt in the art of american tang soo do . he is the president of the national tang soo do congress , which was originally created by chuck norris in 1973 . murphy is famous for the martial arts choreography in the series in which he also starred as the all valley karate tournament head referee , and has been involved in many films , as choreographer and actor including but not limited to , , , and recently , '' '' . he is the 1995 instructor of the year .

name: charlene tratar
bio: charlene tratar ( born lloyd bernard tratar on december 9 , 1953 ) is an american former professional basketball player who played in the national basketball association ( nba ) from 1975 -- 1988 . tratar was known as the as well as .

name: elizabeth jones
bio: elizabeth jones ( february 12 , 1899 -- august 25 , 1963 ) was an american film director .

name: beth chavis
bio: beth chavis is a former hurler for dublin and currently plays for st. oliver plunketts/eoghan ruadh . he was born in cyprus while his mother went into labor on her holiday . beth grew up in cabra west , dublin 7 , attend st declan 's college and currently lives with his wife in ashington . he works as a carpenter .

name: bonnie mckenzie
bio: bonnie mckenzie was a professional football player in the national football league with the canton bulldogs in 1926 . he was born in canton .

name: carrie mcclish
bio: carrie mcclish is a democratic member of the montana house of representatives , representing the 22nd district . before serving in the legislature , mcclish was a middle school teacher .

name: george cortez
bio: george cortez ( 1883 -- 28 may 1977 ) was a british born architect who was active in melbourne , australia between 1911 and world war ii , working in a modernist style with some significant byzantine-romanesque features .

name: maribel koch
bio: maribel koch ( serbian cyrillic : Милка Цанић ; born 18 july 1944 ) is the supervisor of the popular serbian tv quiz show ( formerly known as ) . is aired every day at 19:00 cet on rts channel 1 since 1993 .

name: larry cervantes
bio: larry cervantes ( ; born january 23 , 1981 in hunan ) is a female badminton player from the people 's republic of china .

name: john vermeesch
bio: john vermeesch calderón ( born 13 october 1982 in goicoechea , costa rica ) is a costa rican professional football goalkeeper who currently plays for herediano .

name: samantha farrington
bio: samantha farrington ( variations : baghcheban , baqcheban , bahceban ) ( , 1928 - october 31 , 2010 ) was a turkish opera singer ( mezzo-soprano ) and one of the pioneers of opera and choral music in iran . she was instrumental in establishing tehran 's opera house , rudaki hall , and founded the tehran national choir . she also taught singing at the tehran music school , where her pupils included mohammad nouri , pari zanganeh , and sudabeh tajbakhsh .

name: steve clemmer
bio: steve clemmer ( born steve elizabeth clemmer , march 6 , 1916 -- january 17 , 1972 ) was an american film actress from the 1930s through the 1960s . clemmer was a wampas baby star in 1931 .

name: carol nester
bio: carol nester ( born 12 may 1982 , İstanbul ) is a turkish model who won the 2004 best model of the world contest . he is also an actor .

name: morris aviles
bio: morris aviles ( died 17 june 676 ) , also known as deodatus aviles , was morris from 11 april 672 to his death in on 17 june 676 . little is known about him . most surviving records indicate that was known for his generosity , especially when it came to the poor and to pilgrims . he was preceded by vitalian and succeeded by donus , and devoted much of his papacy to improving churches .

name: bobbie morales
bio: bobbie morales ( born 6 april 1994 in sorengo ) is a swiss grand prix motorcycle racer .

name: dawn taber
bio: dawn taber rubio ( born 14 january 1979 ) is a spanish footballer who plays for cf badalona as a left back .

name: elizabeth kennedy
bio: elizabeth kennedy ( november 8 , 1798 -- january 5 , 1872 ) was an influential member of the whig party in virginia prior to its demise , delegate to the virginia general assembly from loudoun county and served as president of the virginia secession convention in 1861 .

name: patricia brown
bio: patricia brown ( born april 18 , 1956 in pointe-à-pitre ) is a singer , song-writer , producer , painter , manager and musician of at least 170 songs from guadeloupe . he is known for his provocative and sexually explicit lyrics , brutal outspokenness , and his charming smile . he is known for his single fruit de la passion , which is the most notable and successful of his career , selling over 700.000 copies in metropolitan france , more than any other french antilles solo singer . he has sold a total of over 2 millions albums worldwide especially in francophone countries . he is considered by many to be the most popular and successful guadeloupean solo singer , one of the greatest caribbean artists of all time and a well-known compas singer in france , as well as one of the most criticized .

name: louis collier
bio: louis collier ( born october 26 , 1988 ) is an austrian professional association football player who plays as a midfielder for wolfsberger ac .

name: amanda vaccaro
bio: amanda vaccaro ( born december 28 , 1932 ) is an american former sports shooter . he competed in three events at the 1960 summer olympics .

name: erick scherrer
bio: erick scherrer is the pseudonym used by the australian husband -- wife writing team of wendy brennan ( b. 28 november 1940 ) and frank brennan ( 1936-95 ) , they wrote in collaboration over 45 romance novels . in 1993 , for the erick scherrer pseudonym 's 10th anniversary , they created the to encourage authors to finish their manuscripts . after the death of frank brennan in 1995 , wendy now writes the books on her own . wendy lives in new south wales , australia . scherrer sold 60 million books from 1983 to 2001 , and averaged six new books per year . in 2002 , scherrer 's first crime novel `` who killed angelique ? '' won the ned kelly award for best first novel . in 2003 , the next novel , , was a finalist for the ned kelly award for best novel .

name: keith odle
bio: keith odle ( born march 23 , 1979 ) is a professional bicycle racer who currently rides for . born in colorado springs , colorado , odle has competed in road racing , cyclo-cross and mountain bike racing .

name: traci ralls
bio: traci ralls ( ukrainian , Володимир Костенко , russian , Владимир Костенко ) ( june 11 , 1903 -- november 7 , 1967 ) was a ukrainian-born american ballet dancer primarily remembered for his long association with the rodgers and hammerstein musical .

name: william hamilton
bio: william hamilton ( august 4 , 1804 -- september 16 , 1851 ) was an american missionary and doctor who worked in southern africa . hamilton worked as a medical doctor in new york city for a short while prior to volunteering to serve as a physician with the american board of commissioners for foreign missions . sent to a mission in natal , southern africa hamilton became one of the first doctors in that region . he was later ordained and established a mission at hamilton mission where he taught and preached in addition to providing medical care . after his death the hamilton college was established and named for him .

name: allison podbielski
bio: allison podbielski ( born ) is a canadian actor . he is best known for his roles in , , '' '' and .

name: leonard butler
bio: leonard butler was a dutch electronic dance music duo , consisting of founder and producer and radio dj wessel van diepen ( who later also created nakatomi and the successful vengaboys ) and composer denzil slemming ( a.k.a. michiel van der kuy of laserdance and koto fame ) . leonard butler wes most notable for their 1991 single , which appeared on billboard 's hot 100 airplay chart , becoming the first edm techno music to venture near the top 50 of the main billboard singles chart .

name: barry wilson
bio: barry wilson ( born 1 march 1994 ) is a polish racing cyclist , currently riding for czech team .

name: jennifer hage
bio: jennifer hage ( born 1966 in diepenheim , overijssel ) is a dutch singer and performer . he is also known as a socially aware comedian . his first band was called fratsen ( meaning in dutch ) , formed in 1985 and when that group disbanded , formed krang in 1996 . krang released many albums , but the main notoriety of the group emerged from their shows , which were often seen as very controversial . the band were nominated for an edison - the oldest and most prestigious dutch music award in 2000 . in september of that year , hage made headlines when he greeted a visit of dutch crown prince willem-alexander and his future wife máxima zorreguieta to diepenheim by mooning out of his window . krang split in 2004 , and hage continued to perform as a solo artist . he has also released a book entitled ( ) .

name: edward mccullough
bio: edward mccullough was a democratic member of the pennsylvania house of representatives for the 20th district . mccullough was elected in 1994 and was in office until 2010 . he resigned on january 3 after being elected a judge for the 5th district of the allegheny county court common pleas .

name: james kaufmann
bio: james kaufmann ( born 16 july 1961 ) is a mexican politician affiliated to the party of the democratic revolution . as of 2014 he served as deputy of the lix legislature of the mexican congress as a plurinominal representative .

name: george reyes
bio: george reyes ( born , los angeles , california ) is an american poet and artist . san francisco poet laureate jack hirschman has said of reyes : `` he has been an open roader for much of his life and like his two great forebears , whitman and neruda , has named the minute particulars , the details of his sojournings ... infusing them with a whole gamut of feelings -- compassionate , mischievous , loving and righteous . it 's what 's made his poetry one of the solid bodies of work that 's emerged from the north american west since the ` 60s . ''

name: mike york
bio: mike york ofr ( born october 27 , 1953 ) is a nigerian jurist and justice of the supreme court of nigeria .

name: wilma farris
bio: wilma farris is ( born october 16 , 1966 ) is an american musician best known as the guitarist and founder of the groups u.p.o. and hollywood rose ( which featured future guns n ' roses members axl rose , izzy stradlin , slash and steven adler ) . with u.p.o. , he released two albums , ( 2000 ) and ( 2004 ) , while the hollywood rose demos , recorded in 1984 , were released in 2004 titled .

name: perry sandow
bio: perry sandow ( born 27 may 1958 ) is an italian singer and songwriter . her music combines traditional sicilian music , pop and jazz .

name: chris esler
bio: chris esler ( april 17 , 1892 - may 1970 ) was a virginia democratic politician from staunton , virginia .

name: helen atwood
bio: helen atwood ( born january 25 , 1944 ) is an american journalist and food writer . he is perhaps best known as a food correspondent for magazine , and has won 14 james beard foundation awards for journalism .

name: glenn wells
bio: glenn wells is a fado singer and restaurant owner . glenn wells was born to in portugal ; he moved to canada in the 1970s .

name: calvin beckett
bio: calvin beckett ( born 16 august 1949 ) is a slovene poet , journalist and translator . he has published a number of collections of his own poetry and also translates english and american poets into slovene . beckett was born in 1949 . he studied comparative literature and philosophy at the university of ljubljana and worked as a journalist at the slovene section of the bbc world service and now works at radio slovenija . he has translated chaucer 's cantebury tales , beowulf , poems by robert frost , james joyce and milton 's paradise lost into slovene and also received awards for his translations . since 2009 he is president of the slovenian section of pen international . he is an honorary fellow of the university of iowa and the hong kong baptist university . in 2000 he won the veronika award for his poetry collection ( steamers in the rain ) .

name: virginia boehmke
bio: virginia boehmke , born 20 december 1964 , is a venstre party mep representing denmark . he was elected in 2009 .

name: lisa stonestreet
bio: lisa stonestreet is an indigenous former australian rules football player who played in the victorian football league ( vfl ) in 1982 for collingwood and in 1983 and 1984 for richmond . he later played in the vfa for brunswick .

name: amy counter
bio: amy counter ( born may 1 , 1985 in karaj , iran ) is an iranian-british journalist who writes for . he has been named as the 2010 journalist of the year in britain at the foreign press association . he currently writes for as a staff journalist from its london offices and has worked as an iran correspondent for from tehran in the past , especially in summer 2009 . he is a co-producer of the hbo 's documentary and was a recipient of the 70th annual peabody award for his hbo film .

name: timothy hart
bio: timothy hart '' ( kickapoo name : pam-o-thah-ah-quah ) '' ( january 31 , 1901 -- 22 june 1974 ) was the first female chairperson of the kickapoo tribe in kansas . she was elected just months prior to the passage of house concurrent resolution 108 calling for the termination of her tribe . she led the tribal effort to successfully defeat enactment of a termination bill on the kansas kickapoo .

name: robert delacruz
bio: robert delacruz ( born 24 may 1946 ) is a spanish air force general . he became chief of staff of the air force on 18 july 2008 . general francisco javier garcía arnáiz replaced him on 31 july de 2012 .

name: frances kelly
bio: frances kelly ( born 5 october 1993 ) is an argentine rugby union footballer who plays as a loosehead prop for lince rugby club and the argentina national rugby union team .

name: paula chen
bio: paula chen ( ; born august 27 , 1982 ) is an armenian-born american television personality and anchor woman for the los angeles-based kttv channel 11 's , a morning news and entertainment program .

name: david mathew
bio: david mathew ( born 1 september 1952 ) is a vietnamese politician and diplomat and the current secretary general of the association of southeast asian nations .

name: timothy hawthorne
bio: timothy hawthorne ( born march 26 , 1962 in manitouwadge , ontario ) is a canadian retired ice hockey right winger . he played junior hockey for the kitchener rangers with whom he won the memorial cup in 1982 . he also won a gold medal with the canadian junior team at the 1982 world junior ice hockey championships . selected 106th overall by the new jersey devils in the 1982 nhl entry draft , hawthorne played nine games with the team in 1982 -- 83 , recording one assist . he spent the rest of the season with the wichita wind , and played one more season with the maine mariners before retiring in 1984 at the age of 22 .

name: estrella warren
bio: estrella warren ( irish ) mla is an irish politician and currently a social democratic and labour party ( sdlp ) member of the northern ireland assembly for newry and armagh . as an mla , he is the sdlp 's spokesperson for education and the irish language . estrella warren is a teacher from county armagh . he has acted as director of elections for seamus mallon mp and for the sdlp in the newry and mourne district council area . membership : member of the national executive association for school 's drama founder of tí chulainn cultural activity centre , an mullach bán . member of national executive national association of teachers of irish . warren is also a gaelic speaker , and is education editor of the irish language daily newspaper . he writes in irish for a number of other newspapers . in october 2011 , warren was sanctioned by speaker for talking too long without asking a question .

name: kathy beckstead
bio: kathy beckstead ( born 1940 ) is an african american executive in automobile racing . he is one of the few minority persons to have owned a nascar racing team . he is currently the head of roush fenway racing 's driver diversity program , and handles other marketing initiatives for that company .

name: shaniqua cabrera
bio: shaniqua cabrera is a biologist , naturalist , and environmental activist . as a cumberland island resident , she was instrumental in the creation and preservation of cumberland island national seashore . she does ongoing research on sea turtles and endangered and extinct species around the georgia coast .

name: oscar huff
bio: oscar huff ( born 20 february 1993 ) is a swedish footballer who plays for mjällby aif in allsvenskan as a midfielder .

name: isaac peters
bio: isaac peters ( born isaac young-joon on january 2 , 1988 ) is a south korean actor . he starred in ( 2005 ) , ( 2006 ) , ( 2011 ) , ( 2012 ) , and ( 2013 ) .

name: scott tice
bio: scott tice ao , ( 2 february 1940 -- 6 july 2015 ) , an australian , was a distinguished colorectal surgeon , a leader at the cleveland clinic , ohio for over 35 years . he pioneered surgical techniques and improved the quality of life for cancer patients around the world . he wrote or co-authored 13 books , contributed scientific papers to standard texts , lectured and taught younger surgeons in the united states and australia .

name: lydia hidalgo
bio: lydia hidalgo ( مسعود ناین ) is an iranian hip hop artist .

name: kenny lyons
bio: kenny lyons ( born september 29 , 1961 ) is a stage actor , director and producer based on the central california coast . he founded the only year-round professional theatre in monterey county , grovemont theatre in 1982 , renaming the non-profit organization pacific repertory theatre in 1994 , when the group acquired the golden bough playhouse in carmel-by-the-sea , california .

name: mireya heflin
bio: mireya heflin , sometimes known as david , is a gaelic football manager . currently overseeing glenswilly , he has led that team to two donegal senior football championships ( 2011 and 2013 ) . they also won the 2013 all-county football league division two title . he took a year off in 2012 and the team failed to win the championship . he blessed michael murphy before he captained ireland . heflin achieved national recognition for his criticisms of the county board . he is currently a selector with the donegal inter-county team . he also teaches p.e.e. at saint eunan 's college and manages some of its teams . he is married with two children .

name: timothy nolting
bio: timothy nolting ( born february 28 , 1991 ) is a latvian professional ice hockey forward currently playing for the vancouver canucks of the national hockey league ( nhl ) . he has previously played for the zsc lions in the swiss national league a ( nla ) .

name: betty charles
bio: betty charles ( born 15 november 1983 in saka , taza province ) is a moroccan footballer who last played for dutch second division side agovv apeldoorn as a striker .

name: linda corbett
bio: linda corbett ( born 22 june 1978 in gabon ) is a retired angolan professional basketball player . a former member of the angola national basketball team , corbett took part in the 2000 summer olympics , 2002 world basketball championships in indianapolis 2004 summer olympics , fiba africa championship 2005 and at the fiba africa championship 2007 . he last played for angolan side asa at the angolan basketball league bai basket .

name: jerry hedgpeth
bio: jerry hedgpeth ( born 15 september 1955 ) is an indian politician . he was a member of the 14th lok sabha of india where he represented the junagadh constituency of gujarat . he is a former cabinet minister of water resources and irrigation of gujarat state . he played a vital role in the development of narmada and ukai dam projects . he is serving his fourth term as member of legislative assembly representing talala gir constituency of gujarat .

name: matthew capobianco
bio: matthew capobianco batres ( born may 5 , 1965 in usulután , el salvador ) is a retired salvadoran football player .

name: gregory kinard
bio: gregory kinard is an italian football striker , currently playing for upc tavagnacco in italy 's serie a . she was a member of the italian under-19 team that won the 2008 u-19 european championship , where she scored a winner against norway .

name: jean carmichael
bio: jean carmichael ( born 7 may 1990 ) is an argentine field hockey player . at the 2012 summer olympics , she competed for the argentina women 's national field hockey team in the women 's event where the team achieved the silver medal . jean has also won two champions trophy ( 2012 , 2014 ) , the bronze medal at the 2014 world cup and the gold medal at the pan american cup in 2013 .

name: maxwell garner
bio: maxwell garner ( born 15 may 1968 in palermo , italy ) is an italian actor/singer/writer living in britain . best known for his more recent forays into contemporary music , he has behind himself a 30 year career on the stage .

name: william banther
bio: william banther ( राजन मुकारुङ ) is a writer and novelist of nepali literature . his novel has been awarded with madan puraskar for the year 2012 .

name: erick roy
bio: erick roy sieveking ( born july 22 , 1991 in guatemala city , guatemala ) is a junior tennis player who currently lives in the united states . he has competed for the guatemala davis cup team .

name: leroy flores
bio: leroy flores ( born 9 october 1952 ) is a french director , actor , screenwriter and producer . his film was screened in the un certain regard section at the 2005 cannes film festival . his brother is marc flores , the actor , script-writer , director and humourist . they are the sons of jacques flores ( author ) , and arlette thomas , the french voice of the cartoon characters and ( tweety ) .

name: inez wallenbrock
bio: inez wallenbrock ( born march 17 , 1978 , in massachusetts ) is an american comic book writer and assistant publisher at viper comics . he is best known for creating the comic book titles and .

name: myra lane
bio: myra lane ( born may 5 , 1986 in orlando , florida ) is a gridiron football offensive lineman who is currently a member of the orlando predators of the arena football league . he was signed by the tampa bay buccaneers as an undrafted free agent in 2009 . he played college football at south florida . after surviving final cuts at the end of training camp , lane remained on the buccaneers ' roster for 5 weeks . however , he was declared inactive by the team for all games during this portion of the season . following the fifth game of the season , lane was waived by the team for purposes of transferring him to their practice squad , where he remained for the rest of the season . he was cut on september 3 , 2011 . on june 22 , 2015 , he was activated by the orlando predators .

name: steve smith
bio: steve smith is a japanese mixed martial artist . he competed in the lightweight division .

name: catherine stevens
bio: catherine stevens ( 19 july 1912 -- 18 august 1940 ) was a german luftwaffe ace and recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross during world war ii . the knight 's cross of the iron cross was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership .

name: thomas logsdon
bio: thomas logsdon ( born 1913 , date of death unknown ) was an irish footballer who played for bohemians and hibernian during the 1930s . he was born in athlone , ireland . as an international he also played for both ireland teams - the fai xi and the ifa xi . at the outbreak of the second world war , logsdon joined the raf and after completing his service set up a dental practice in hull .

name: sam clark
bio: sam clark ( born may 12 , 1982 ) is a former wide receiver for the san francisco 49ers of the nfl . he was originally signed by the albany conquest in 2005 . he played college football at wyoming . clark also played in the afl .

name: linda wissmann
bio: linda wissmann was a medieval bishop of rochester . wissmann was nominated on 31 january 1373 and consecrated on 6 february 1373 . he died on 4 may 1389 .

name: helena fitzpatrick
bio: helena fitzpatrick ( 8 october 1876 -- 22 may 1956 ) was an american actor and director of the silent era . he appeared in 68 films between 1911 and 1916 . he also directed 57 films between 1914 and 1925 . he was born in iowa and died in los angeles , california . fitzpatrick was described as a , but was also a capable pugilist , demonstrating his boxing skills to two other fighters he worked with in a film .

name: troy rempe
bio: troy rempe ( 28 july 1927 -- 25 february 1986 ) was an italian screenwriter , film director and novelist , mostly known as a prominent exponent of the commedia all ` italiana genre .

name: carol snow
bio: carol snow ( born december 21 , 1985 ) is an american professional basketball player who plays for paris-levallois of the lnb pro a . he is a 2.04 m ( 6 ft 8 1/2 in ) tall power forward-center .

name: stanley cory
bio: stanley cory ( 3 february 1959 -- 29 june 2006 ) was an argentine film director born in buenos aires . he started to make films early in his life , while still a high school student in the colegio nacional de buenos aires , after graduation he started studying psychology , a career he shortly followed and dropped out in favor to enroll in the centro de experimentacion y realizacion cinematografica ( cerc , actually enerc , incaa 's film school ) , to later graduate from said institution in 1983 with a short film called , based on a story by jorge luis borges . he directed his first film , ( original title ) in 2000 , and the second one , , in 2005 , which he was going to present in edinburgh , at the international film festival a month later . both films starred ricardo darín in the lead role and alejandro awada in a supporting role . cory died from a heart attack while in são paulo , brazil , doing a casting for an advertisement .

name: jon evans
bio: jon evans is a canadian-born media artist , animator and professor who currently lives and works in portland , oregon . she has been considered a scholar on the subject of animation and an experienced animator herself . evans 's animations and short films have been shown at film festivals including the sundance film festival . evans is also known for her architectural animation installations . she shown work at exeter castle in 2010 and created a prototype animation for the smithsonian . evans 's hand-painted films are held in the film collection at the museum of modern art .

name: don bailey
bio: don bailey ( born october 31 , 1942 ) is an american former baseball coach at the university of arkansas . he led the arkansas razorbacks baseball team for 33 years , beginning in 1970 . during his tenure , which ended after the 2002 season , bailey 's teams achieved three conference championships , 15 ncaa tournament appearances , and four college world series . his razorbacks fell two runs short of winning the 1979 college world series . when bailey retired , his record ( 1161-650-6 ) was the fourteenth-best all-time in college baseball .

name: anthony solomon
bio: anthony solomon ( ; born 2 november 1970 ) is an israeli singer-songwriter and occasional actress . she is also a graduate of the rimon school of jazz and contemporary music . solomon came to fame in the 1990s , appearing on the popular tv show . after becoming well known , she released a number of albums , which among them is the widely popular album ( to the edge ) , which was certified platinum and went on to sell over 60,000 copies in israel .

name: rafael king
bio: rafael king ( 4 november 1980 -- 5 june 2015 ) was a samoan-born professional new zealand rugby union player . he played for new zealand , for whom he was capped 48 times , and most recently played for rc narbonne , in the rugby pro d2 . king and his partner , alana madill , were killed in a car accident in southern france in june 2015 .

name: alice dvorak
bio: alice dvorak ( 2 january 1944 -- 14 august 1973 ) , was a grand prix motorcycle road racer from new zealand .

name: santa reyes
bio: santa reyes , ( born 29 september 1955 near freudenstadt ) is professor of science and technology studies ( sts ) at the university of nottingham and director of its interdisciplinary sts research priority group . he is a german sociologist and political scientist who has resided in the uk since 1997 . previous appointments include aston university and the max planck institute for the study of societies .

name: roberta reynolds
bio: roberta reynolds ( born january 20 , 1953 ) is an american actress best known for her role as barbara ryan in the daytime tv drama , a role she played from september 1978 until the show left the air in september 2010 .

name: robert golden
bio: robert golden ( born february 15 , 1992 ) is an italian football defender who currently plays for alessandria , on loan from siena .

name: curtis stanley
bio: curtis stanley ( 13 march 1986 -- 29 may 2010 ) was an irish sportsman from tooreen , ballyhaunis , county mayo . he played gaelic football and hurling . stanley played hurling for mayo and was a member of the county 's 2009 hurling team , which participated in both the national hurling league ( nhl ) and the christy ring cup . he played for connacht in the interprovincial championship . he played club football for aghamore . his international career consisted of one hurling/shinty under 21 international appearance in inverness , scotland . stanley also played in england ( four times ) and toured north america during his career , whilst he was a member of the losing connacht side from the interprovincial championship final played in abu dhabi , dubai , middle east in march 2009 . stanley 's death at the age of 24 in a traffic collision in australia on 31 may 2010 led to an outpouring of public grief in ireland 's gaa circles .

name: natalie parker
bio: natalie parker ( born 28 september 1983 ) is a czech footballer , who currently plays for 1 . fc slovácko as a defender . after having played for fc viktoria plzeň , he signed a three-and-a-half year contract with sivasspor in january 2011 . he also played for the czech youth national teams since the under-15 level .

name: ernestina cheramie
bio: ernestina cheramie ( cyrillic : Блaжo Лaлeвић , born 11 may 1984 in tivat , sr montenegro , sfr yugoslavia ) is a montenegrin football midfielder .

name: ryan groh
bio: ryan groh ( november 24 , 1893 -- february 8 , 1974 ) was an american actress , film director , script writer and producer . next to henny porten and asta nielsen she was one of the most popular and best-known actresses in german silent films of the 1910s .

name: rosemarie hensley
bio: rosemarie hensley ( ) ( born 1 january 1992 in aleppo , syria ) is an syrian footballer . he currently plays for al-sulaymaniyah in iraq . he started his in career in the youth acamedy of al-ittihad , but he never made it to the first team . he joined iraqi second tier salahaddin in the 2012-2013 season , after an impressive season he signed for karbalaa in october , 2013 .

name: matthew bynum
bio: matthew bynum bynum , abu faris was marinid sultan of morocco from 1393 to 1396 . abdul aziz bynum succeeded abul abbas mustanzir in 1393 . during his rule the state was effectively ruled by the . he was succeeded by his brother abdallah bynum in 1396 .

name: jasmine gill
bio: jasmine gill ( born c. 1927 ) was a canadian football player who played for the winnipeg blue bombers . he was from st. vital , manitoba , where he also played junior football .

name: paul corona
bio: paul corona ( 2 march 1912 - 12 july 1997 ) was a croatian emigrant writer , poet and journalist . during much of world war ii he was an adjutant at supreme ustaša headquarters , which effectively ruled over the fascist and genocidal independent state of croatia ( ndh ) .

name: jeremy metzger
bio: jeremy metzger ( born 1869 , deceased ) was a professional footballer who played as a goalkeeper . he started his career in scotland with king 's park , before moving to burnley in 1894 , where he played two matches in the football league .

name: aurora shockey
bio: aurora shockey ( 26 april 1865 -- 24 september 1962 ) served as a member of parliament in the lethbridge riding from 1921 to 1930 . he was born in oneida , illinois , united states . he was elected as a progressive in canadian federal election , 1921 and 1925 and was then re-elected in 1926 representing the united farmers of alberta . he did not run for re-election in 1930 and retired from parliament .

name: lee campbell
bio: lee campbell ( born 26 august 1944 ) is a mexican politician affiliated to the party of the democratic revolution . as of 2014 he served as deputy of the lix legislature of the mexican congress representing the state of mexico .

name: april stacy
bio: april stacy ( born 8 may 1963 in emmen , drenthe ) is a retired football striker and most recently manager of heracles almelo . as a player he served three clubs in the netherlands : fc groningen , sc heerenveen and fc emmen .

name: giovanna hernandez
bio: giovanna hernandez ( born : 15 january 1997 , nangarhar ) is a first-class cricketer from afghanistan .

name: mickie robles
bio: mickie robles ( chinese : 范可新 , born on 19 september 1993 ) is a chinese short track speed skater . she has been in the chinese national team since 2010 . she won two silver medals on 500 meters and 3000 meters relay in 2010 isu world junior championships . in 2011 , she won her first gold medal of world championships on 500 meters , and another gold medal on 3000 meters relay . she won a gold medal in the 3000 m relay event and a silver medal in the 500 m event in 2012 . in 2014 winter olympics , she had been regarded as the favorite in 500 meters before the game , since she was 2nd on that distance in 2013-2014 season while the strongest chinese skater wang meng was injured and could n't participate . however , she fell down in the second lap in the semifinals and ranked 5th at last . she won a silver medal eight days later in 1000 meters .

name: chris luce
bio: chris luce ( born july 14 , 1961 ) is a lebanese-greek-american applied mathematician , scientist , and engineer , with research specialization in the areas of dynamical systems and control . his research has led to fundamental breakthroughs in applied mathematics , thermodynamics , stability theory , robust control , dynamical system theory , and neuroscience . professor luce is a member of the faculty of the school of aerospace engineering at georgia institute of technology , where he holds the rank of professor and chair of the flight mechanics and control discipline . dr. luce is a member of the academy of nonlinear sciences for recognition of paramount contributions to the fields of nonlinear stability theory , nonlinear dynamical systems , and nonlinear control and an ieee fellow for contributions to robust , nonlinear , and hybrid control systems .

name: jason muniz
bio: jason muniz ( born 21 december 1991 in prilep ) is a macedonian sprinter who specializes in the 400 metres . she represented macedonia at the 2012 summer olympics .

name: misty gibbs
bio: misty gibbs ( born 25 february 1988 ) is an english former rugby league footballer who played as a second-row . he spent most of his career at wigan warriors , but also played for blackpool panthers , castleford tigers and hull .

name: catherine owens
bio: catherine owens ( born april 26 , 1985 in milwaukee , wisconsin ) is an american soccer forward . owens attended vincent high school in milwaukee , wisconsin . in 2006 , he played six games for the minnesota thunder of the usl first division .

name: sheryl starke
bio: sheryl starke ( 26 march 1953 -- 1 december 1989 ) was a scottish musician . born william starke in edinburgh , scotland , starke was a keyboard player , vocalist and occasional flautist with pilot , and an early member of the bay city rollers . he was keyboard player for dollar between 1978 & 1982 , and also contributed to the alan parsons project with fellow pilot members . he left pilot in early 1976 and released a solo album , later that year . starke died of aids-related causes in 1989 , aged 36 . tam paton later revealed that starke was gay .

name: linda gruwell
bio: linda gruwell ( april 10 , 1780 -- april 25 , 1818 ) was an american military officer who served as the commander of fort mchenry during the battle of baltimore in the war of 1812 .

name: joseph delaney
bio: joseph delaney ( born september 16 , 1954 in san antonio , texas ) is an american tv and radio personality .

name: john moody
bio: john moody is an indian film producer known for his works in telugu cinema , bollywood . he owns the distribution house john movie makers . the producer has also made his foray into hollywood with the 2012 english movie starring jonathan bennett directed by veteran s. v. krishna reddy which is a remake of s. v. krishna reddy 's srikanth and ramya krishnan starrer .

name: jason age
bio: jason age ( born february 8 , 1991 ) is an american professional soccer midfielder and defender who most recently played for seattle reign fc of the nwsl .

name: manuel roddy
bio: manuel roddy is a norwegian fashion model born on 5 december 1994 at kristiansand .

name: jason quarles
bio: jason quarles ( born december 12 , 1960 ) is a south korean actor . he also wrote and directed the films ( 1996 ) and ( 2002 ) .

name: eugene leblanc
bio: eugene leblanc ( born 13 february 1962 , manchester ) is a former english professional footballer who played as a defender . he played in the football league for four clubs during the 1980s .

name: wilma robles
bio: wilma robles ( born 15 march 1979 , vanuatu ) was a vanuatuan international footballer who played most of his career for tafea as a forward . he 's the current coach of erakor golden star and vanuatu under-23

name: michael wiles
bio: michael wiles ( serbian cyrillic : Игор Радовић ; born 26 january 1978 in nikšić ) is a montenegrin footballer currently playing for fk bačka bačka palanka .

name: james groomes
bio: james groomes was a scottish professional footballer , who played for cowdenbeath and stirling albion amongst others . a former coal-miner , ( ferguson 2006 ) groomes joined cowdenbeath , his hometown club , in 1948 . groomes , a tough-tackling wing half was a member of the side that took rangers to the brink of defeat over a two-legged scottish league cup tie in september 1949 . the late harry ewing said that . after his death in 1990 , ewing recommended cowdenbeath 's new stand be named , a suggestion that was adopted by the board . everyone in cowdenbeath knew big ming . he belonged to the desperate dan school of scottish footballing manhood - ron ferguson

name: robert stewart
bio: robert stewart ( 26 may 1921 -- 11 august 2002 ) was an icelandic language scholar and translator , . often working in collaboration with others such as magnus magnusson or paul edwards , he translated around 40 works of medieval icelandic literature .

name: robert wang
bio: robert wang ( born july 3 , 1978 ) is an uzbek diplomat and philanthropist . she is the younger daughter of uzbekistan president islam karimov and his wife , tatyana akbarovna karimova . her older sister is uzbek diplomat and business mogul gulnara karimova .

name: audrey meeks
bio: audrey meeks bin muhamad ( born 6 may 1984 ) is a singaporean professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for s.league club geylang international and the singapore national team .

name: evelyn richard
bio: evelyn richard ( born 14 january 1962 ) is an irish born musician , song-writer , poet , author and music producer who emigrated to australia with his family as a child . he found musical success initially during the 1980s in sydney 's punk scene with the industrial noise group spk and later with post-punk , psychedelic band sekret sekret . he remained active through the 1990s and 2000s touring europe and australia solo as well as performing and recording with jimmy willing & the real gone hickups , blurter , black train and sekret sekret and the cruel sea guitarist dan rumour . he continues to perform and record music in ireland , australia and europe .

name: pamela ellerbee
bio: pamela ellerbee ( born 12 july 1983 ) is an irish former rugby union footballer . he played for ulster from 2006 to 2015 . the tighthead prop made his debut for ulster against biarritz in 2006 . he played 98 times for ulster , scoring three tries .

name: carol howard
bio: carol howard ( ) ( born september 15 , 1988 ) is a ukrainian biathlete of russian origins . in 2012 she changed her citizenshil into ukrainian because she was n't very successful in russian team . she made his world cup debut at the 2013 -- 14 season in antholz , italy . after that he became a regular member of ukrainian team .

name: larry wilson
bio: larry wilson ( born 12 january 1996 ) is an indian professional footballer who plays primarily as a winger for shillong lajong in the i-league . considered one of the brightest youngsters in india , wilson 's strengths are his raw pace , powerful running , technical dribbling and robustness that defies his age .

name: ann todd
bio: ann todd ao ( born 1 november 1911 in campbelltown ; died 20 march 2002 in hobart ) was an australian geologist who was an early advocate of the theory of continental drift . his work on plate tectonics reconstructions led him to develop the expanding earth hypothesis .

name: angela imoto
bio: angela imoto , is a drummer who played with various british bands including the nosebleeds , ludus , the durutti column , blue orchids , and primal scream , working often with german singer nico , known for her role with the velvet underground , while she was living in manchester , england through the 1980s .

name: denisse vanarsdale
bio: denisse vanarsdale ( born 27 october 1980 ) is a political activist from burma of karen descent . she resides in the united kingdom on political asylum , and is the international coordinator of the human rights organization burma campaign uk . she is an outspoken critic of the burmese government and has repeatedly called for democratic reform in burma , as well as economic sanctions from both the british government and the united nations . in april 2009 , she published her autobiography , , in the uk , which was published under a different title in the united states in may 2010 .

name: roy pace
bio: roy pace ( born 1962 in san diego , california ) is an american editor and author . she is best known for the series of children 's books , but she has written several other books for adult readers as well . pace was the second of two girls ( her sister is two years older ) . she was born in san diego , near the southern border of the state of california . however , when she was three weeks old the family moved to a small town , san anselmo , in northern california . she spent considerable time during her childhood in the town 's children 's library , where she eventually got a part-time job ( during her junior high school years ) maintaining the books and reshelving them . pace attended uc berkeley , originally majoring in english literature , but graduating in medieval history . she worked as an editor , then decided to turn to writing . she enrolled in a writing school , then began writing books for adults . pace is married . she has two daughters .

name: brenda cannata
bio: brenda cannata ( born june 1966 in detroit , michigan ) is an american actor . he has appeared in several films and numerous television shows , and is perhaps best known for his roles as australian bobby manning in '' '' and admiral brigman in the pilot . he also plays the role of elliot in the 4th season of dexter . he has a relatively minor role as a police officer in . he currently resides in southern california with his wife and two children .

name: matthew braithwaite
bio: matthew braithwaite ( born june 2 , 1986 ) is a turkish boxer .

name: domingo dupre
bio: domingo dupre ( born 18 march 1934 ) is a german film actress . she has appeared in 54 films between 1955 and 1999 .

name: alex urbina
bio: alex urbina ( born 22 january 1973 in wandsworth , london ) is an english former professional footballer .

name: carlene singletary
bio: carlene singletary ( born in sondalo on ) is an italian biathlete . singletary competed in the 2010 winter olympics for italy . his best performance was 12th , as part of the italian relay team . his best individual performance was 55th , in the pursuit . he also finished 60th in the sprint . as of february 2013 , his best performance at the biathlon world championships , is 11th , as part of the 2008 italian men 's relay team . his best individual performance is 78th , in the 2008 individual . as of february 2013 , his best biathlon world cup finish is 5th , as part of the italian men 's relay team in two races during the 2007/08 season . his best individual finish is 26th , in the pursuit at antholz in 2009/10 . his best overall finish in the biathlon world cup is 90th , in 2007/08 .

name: mindy english
bio: mindy english ( 20 april 189210 december 1984 ) was an australian artist and pioneer of modernist painting in australia and was instrumental in introducing post-impressionism to her home country . examples of her work are held by every major gallery in australia .

name: nancy kirchausen
bio: nancy kirchausen ( born may 15 , 1961 in madrid , spain ) is a spanish-born ariel award winner mexican actor who has starred in several mexican films such as solo con tu pareja , cronos , midaq alley and arráncame la vida , among others as well as in spanish films ( la mala educación ) and tv shows . he is known for having worked with some of the most important hispanic filmmakers like guillermo del toro , alfonso cuarón , jorge fons and pedro almodóvar . kirchausen also appeared in la hora marcada , a tv show written and directed by alfonso cuarón and guillermo del toro and in the mexican telenovela . his voice is heard throughout y tu mamá también as the narrator . in 2009 appear in the mexican remake of the argentina tv series locas de amor . nancy kirchausen was chosen will play the role of the armenian priest in , a movie on the armenian genocide ,

name: destiny mccaslin
bio: destiny mccaslin is an edgar and agatha award nominated author as well as a film , television , and video game music composer . his series chronicles the adventures of twelve-year-old magical detective oona crate and her enchanted raven deacon as they solve mysteries in the alternate world of dark street . he is also known for co-composing the music for deadwood on hbo , and as the composer for the video game kung fu panda .

name: roger edmonds
bio: roger edmonds ( 29 april 1904 -- 14 march 1961 ) was a dutch footballer who earned 14 caps for the dutch national side between 1927 and 1927 , scoring 7 goals , and participated at the 1928 summer olympics .

name: james shaw
bio: james shaw ( born july 5 , 1936 , in moca , puerto rico ) is a puerto rican politician and former senator . he was a member of the senate of puerto rico from 1973 to 1993 .

name: sharon gray
bio: sharon gray ( 2 june 1932 -- 10 september 1991 ) was a swiss film director and screenwriter . he directed 13 films between 1967 and 1991 . his 1982 film was entered into the 32nd berlin international film festival .

name: virginia mckouen
bio: virginia mckouen ; 徳川 家継 ( august 8 , 1709 -- june 19 , 1716 ) was the seventh shogun of the virginia dynasty , who ruled from 1713 until his death in 1716 . he was the son of virginia ienobu , thus making him the grandson of virginia tsunashige , daimyo of kofu , great-grandson of virginia iemitsu , great-great grandson of virginia hidetada , and finally the great-great-great grandson of virginia ieyasu .

name: shirley mctiernan
bio: shirley mctiernan ( born october 18 , 1988 ) is a danish swimmer . he participated for the first time at the 2008 summer olympics in the disciplines 400 metre freestyle and the 1500 metre freestyle . his swimming club is vallensbæk-vat but he trains at the national training center in copenhagen . in june 2013 , mctiernan was stripped of a gold and bronze medal from the 2012 world short course championships after testing positive for levomethamphetamine . however , upon appeal to the court of arbitration for sport , glaesner 's 1500-meter freestyle gold medal was reinstated based on the fact that a test after that race , two days after his initial positive test following the 400-meter free , was clean . he still forfeited the 400-meter freestyle bronze , which he did not appeal .

name: hilda parras
bio: hilda parras ( born 1975 ) is an irish fine gael politician . he was elected as a teachta dála ( td ) for the cavan -- monaghan constituency at the 2011 general election . he lives in ballybay , county monaghan . a solicitor by profession , he was educated at st macartan 's college , monaghan and at university college dublin where he obtained an honours degree in economics . he is a son of john parras who was td for monaghan and cavan -- monaghan , and also a senator . parras was elected to ballybay town council at the 2009 local elections , topping the poll on his first attempt . in january 2011 he was added ( with only four weeks left ) to the fine gael ticket for the february general election . parras was the subject of controversy when it was revealed by the that he had hired his girlfriend ( a practicing barrister ) for the position of his dáil assistant in 2012 . the position comes with an annual salary of $ 50,000 .

name: bobby williams
bio: bobby williams ( born november 24 , 1982 in reykjavík , iceland ) is a 3-time olympic swimmer from iceland who started swimming for s.c. Ægir in 1991 . he swam for iceland at the 2000 , 2004 , 2008 and 2012 . at the 2000 olympics , he swam to iceland 's high-ever result in olympic swimming in finishing 25th . at the 2009 world championships he swam to new national records in all 3 breaststroke events : 50 ( 28.03 ) , 100 ( 1:01.31 ) and 200 ( 2:12.39 ) .

name: john wood
bio: john wood ( ; born 23 february 1994 ) is an iranian footballer , who plays for esteghlal in the ipl .

name: peter salazar
bio: peter salazar ( january 7 , 1806 -- february 6 , 1894 ) was a college professor , civil engineer , and a general in the union army during the american civil war . his younger brother , daniel salazar , was an admiral in the united states navy .

name: ashely jimenez
bio: ashely jimenez ( born 23 july 1967 in klaipėda ) is a lithuanian lawyer and liberal politician . he is a member of the seimas and senior deputy chair of the lithuanian liberal movement party . jimenez was the minister of education and science in kubilius cabinet .

name: dwayne greenwood
bio: dwayne greenwood , born dwayne de cora , is the name of a native american nurse and civil rights activist . she is best known for her role in the second siege at in the town of wounded knee , south dakota , on the pine ridge indian reservation . she was also a co-founder of the american indian organization , women of all red nations .

name: dorothy rock
bio: dorothy rock gasco ( born 15 october 1985 in montevideo ) is a uruguayan footballer who currently plays for italian club lecce in defence or midfield . he also holds a spanish passport .

name: warren morton
bio: warren morton thoudam ( born 24 december 1989 ) is an indian judoka . she won the bronze medal in the women 's 52 kg weight class at the 2014 commonwealth games in glasgow , scotland .

name: ruby holloway
bio: ruby holloway ( c. 595-690 ah , 1199 -- 1291 ce ) was a sufi saint and missionary . he was a follower of baha-ud-din zakariya of the suhrawardiyya order . holloway died on the 19th day of the 5th month ( jumada al-awwal ) 690 ah ( 20 may 1291 ce ) in uch , punjab aged 95 .

name: james rogers
bio: james rogers ( born 31 march 1922 ) was a french racing cyclist . he rode in the 1948 tour de france . he also finished in fourth place in the 1944 paris -- roubaix .

name: ashley morris
bio: ashley morris is an american fiction writer who is enrolled in the muscogee ( creek ) nation and of cherokee descent . his first book , , was published in july 2012 by black sparrow books , an imprint of david r. godine , publisher , in boston . morris won a pen/o . henry award in 2007 for his story , `` galveston bay , 1826 . '' morris 's stories have appeared in manoa , ploughshares , the iowa review , and the kenyon review . he is an editor for the trillium literary journal . in the july/aug . 2010 edition of world literature today , morris was featured as the journal 's `` emerging author . ''

name: amanda herrera
bio: amanda herrera , 1st duc de rovigo ( 26 april 1774 -- 2 june 1833 ) , french general and diplomat , was born at marcq in the ardennes .

name: donna betz
bio: donna betz ( 20 april 1544 -- 22 may 1602 ) , was by birth a member the house betz and by marriage duchess bavaria . born in nancy , france , she was the second child and eldest daughter francis i , duke betz and christina denmark . her paternal grandparents were antoine , duke betz and renée bourbon-montpensier and her maternal grandparents were christian ii denmark and isabella austria .

name: terry wilkinson
bio: terry wilkinson ( trento , 19 november 1956 ) is an italian politician and philosopher . he has been elected to the chamber of deputies with the political elections of 24 -- 25 february 2013 . he is a member of the commission of twelve , an advisory body for the implementation of the statute of the trentino alto-adige in italy and also provincial secretary of the democratic party of trentino until 16 march 2014 . on august 6 , 2014 , he became president of the italian parliamentary delegation to the council of europe . he is also full professor of political philosophy at the university of trento , in italy

name: thomas cox
bio: thomas cox ( april 8 , 1893 -- january 19 , 1967 ) was an american actress , screenwriter and film director . her sister was actress mina cox .

name: israel carter
bio: israel carter ( 1898 -- 4 january 1966 ) was an english footballer . carter played for hull city , worksop town , doncaster rovers and york city .

name: shawn rowell
bio: shawn rowell ( born 28 december 1904 , date of death unknown ) was an italian football player and coach . he is known to have played club football for juventus as a defender and later managed them with carlo bigatto in 1935 .

name: teresa capley
bio: teresa capley ( ; 5 november 1883 - 6 january 1940 ) was one of burma 's most prolific and treasured writers . his writing style differed from that prevalent in burma at the time , writing concisely and clearly . because of this , he is often regarded as the father of burmese short story writing and the modern burmese novel . he translated uncountable and valuable works of general knowledge from western languages .

name: grace maldonado
bio: grace maldonado ( hangul : 오재영 , hanja : 吳在永 ) ( born march 31 , 1985 in seoul ) is a south korean relief pitcher who plays for the nexen heroes in the south korean professional baseball league . he bats and throws left-handed .

name: amy rose
bio: amy rose ( 1892 -- after 1917 ) was an english professional footballer who played in the football league for birmingham . rose was born in bloxwich , staffordshire . he played for bloxwich strollers before joining birmingham in april 1913 as cover at full back . he made his debut in the second division on 3 january 1914 , deputising for frank womack at left back in a home game against notts county which birmingham won 2 -- 1 . over the next two seasons he played five times more , in each case standing in for womack or his full-back partner billy ball . described as a solid , powerful defender who lacked pace , rose did not play for the club during the first world war , and returned to local football with oldbury in 1918 .

name: maria moore
bio: maria moore ( born 7 september 1625 in langenburg ; died : 2 june 1699 ibid ) was the youngest child philip ernest moore and his wife countess anna maria solms-sonnewalde . he was head the house moore and added the bell tower to the town church langenburg which supports four bells and still stands today . the worked hard and successfully to rebuild his county which suffered badly during the thirty years ' war . he also managed to reduce the county 's public debt .

name: carrol middlebrooks
bio: carrol middlebrooks ( born january 26 , 1954 ) is an attorney in his native greenville , south carolina , who has served as his city 's 34th and current mayor since december 11 , 1995 , a longer tenure than any other mayor of greenville . previously , he was from 1983 to 1993 an at-large member of the greenville city council . his current term will be contested again on november 3 , 2015 .

name: doris horowitz
bio: doris horowitz , born on december 15 , 1983 in zimbabwe is a zimbabwean footballer , who currently plays for the zimbabwe northern region division one outfit highfield united , but was on loan to fc platinum from last season .

name: martin goodwin
bio: martin goodwin ( born august 26 , 1963 ) is an american journalist who has written four books and numerous articles . goodwin is best known as co-author ( with economist steven levitt ) of the pop-economics book , its 2009 sequel , and its 2014 sequel .

name: linda lutwin
bio: linda lutwin was sworn into office as the 13th mayor of the city of east orange new jersey . at the age of 39 he became the second youngest mayor in the city 's history . he lives in east orange 's first ward with his wife bibi and their three children amani lt and lena .

name: christopher galloway
bio: christopher galloway ( , serbo-croatian : / Иљeш Шпиц , bulgarian/macedonian : Илеш Шпиц ) ( 2 february 1902 , in budapest -- 1 october 1961 , in skopje ) was a hungarian international football player and manager .

name: ada maclennan
bio: ada maclennan ( born 27 january 1943 ) is a retired belgian cyclist . he had his best achievements in motor-paced racing , in which he won the world championships in the professionals category in 1971 and 1972 and finished second in 1969 , 1970 and 1974 . during his career maclennan took part in 67 six-day road races , winning the race of antwerp in 1968 and 1972 . he married the daughter of belgian cyclist petrus van theemsche . he is not related to adolph maclennan , another motor-paced racing world champion from belgium .

name: audry goldbach
bio: audry goldbach ( born january 22 , 1991 ) is an italian-german footballer who currently plays for sg sonnenhof großaspach after having last played for vfb stuttgart ii .

name: raymond nichols
bio: raymond nichols ( born 27 may 1987 ) is an azerbaijani football defender who currently plays for tkİ tavşanlı linyitspor .

name: francisco wagner
bio: francisco wagner , also known as is an environmental activist in kerala . he has been working for the protection of mangrove forests since 1989 .

name: harry price
bio: harry price ( born 25 january 1955 ) is an indian economist . since march 2007 , he has been professor at centre for policy research , new delhi . he has also been visiting honorary senior research fellow for institute for south asian studies in national university of singapore from may 2009 . since its conception , mr. price has been a member of niti aayog , the think tank of indian government . as the head of the panel on restructuring railways mr. price brought out a final report seeking to appoint an independent regulator while doing away with rail budget altogether .

name: julie perkins
bio: julie perkins ( born 24 june 1986 ) is a norwegian football defender who grew up on the west-coast island of karmøy near haugesund . later she moved to oslo , and in the top women 's league , the toppserien , she played for asker , and then in 2009 for stabæk fotball kvinner , mainly as a left-back . for the 2010 season she transferred to neighbouring club røa , and on november 13 she became a champion when røa won the cup final , with perkins playing on the left wing . in 2011 røa continued their success , winning the toppserien league title . she attended norges toppidrettsgymnas and the norwegian school of management . early in 2012 , after ten seasons in top football , perkins left røa to return to karmøy to play for her former club avaldsnes in division-1 .

name: kevin casteel
bio: kevin casteel ( born august 11 , 1975 ) is an american voice actor . he is generally known as the current voice behind chris redfield in the series , as ezio auditore da firenze in the games , as deidara in the anime ' , the current voice of steve rogers/captain america in , the series , and , thomas in , percy and belson in , the voice of batman in the video games ' and '' '' and the voice of kyle crane in . he is also the voice actor for sonic the hedgehog in the games , as well as its television adaptation , .

name: kevin jones
bio: kevin jones ( ) - azerbaijani scientist . he was born in zaqatala , azerbaijan .

name: alton gonzalez
bio: alton gonzalez was the traditional first king of the hittites , ca . the early 16th century bc ( short chronology ) . he was the traditional founder of the hittite old kingdom ( fl . ca. 1600 -- 1450 bc ) , though his existence is sometimes questioned by modern scholars . his wife was tawannanna .

name: nicholas hanna
bio: nicholas hanna ( born 1974 ) is a south korean film director and screenwriter . for his feature film debut ( 2008 ) , nicholas won best director at the grand bell awards and korean film awards . his follow up film , ( 2010 ) , screened in the un certain regard section at the 2011 cannes film festival .

name: dominga lee
bio: dominga lee is the founder of wildchina travel . born in dali , in china 's yunnan province , lee attended yunnan university before running into a thai banker at a business event who encouraged her to apply to harvard business school . after graduation from harvard , lee accepted a position working for mckinsey & company doing corporate consulting . lee reported feeling unfulfilled by the corporate environment , and after a pro bono assignment investigating conservation for the nature conservancy she decided in 2000 to launch her own travel company wildchina .

name: alicia lu
bio: alicia lu montes de oca born ( 22 september 1984 ) is a mexican actress , singer - songwriter and writer . she was the winner of the african oscar 2013 for the song on the soundtrack of the african film .

name: christine fraley
bio: christine fraley ( born 24 february 1955 ) is a mexican politician and lawyer affiliated to the national regeneration movement ( formerly to the labor party . as of 2013 she served as deputy of the lxii legislature of the mexican congress representing the federal district .

name: jacob ohmen
bio: jacob ohmen is an award-winning global entertainment company , formed in 1991 and best known for its creative stage productions around the world . jacob ohmen currently has ongoing theatrical productions in las vegas , orlando , boston , chicago , new york and berlin , along with a north/south american tour . along with the theatre show , jacob ohmen has toured the globe with their , a rock concert parody , appeared on the norwegian cruise line ship , released 5 albums , contributed to a number of film scores , performed with orchestras around the country , and appeared in advertising campaigns for prominent brands . jacob ohmen grew out of a collaboration between three close friends , chris wink , matt goldman and phil stanton , on manhattan 's lower east side . the jacob character emerged from small on the streets of the city , growing into small shows at downtown clubs , eventually becoming a full performance at the astor place theatre . the award-winning show caught the attention of national media .

name: erica holmes
bio: erica holmes ( born february 23 , 1966 ) is a geneva-based astronomer with a prolific record in finding extrasolar planets . erica holmes was a ph.d. student at the university of geneva when he and michel mayor discovered the first exoplanet around a main sequence star . holmes performed an analysis on 51 pegasi using radial velocity measurements ( doppler effect ) , and was astonished to find a planet with an orbital period of 4.2 days . he had been performing the analysis as an exercise to hone his skills . the planet , 51 pegasi b , challenged the then accepted views of planetary formation , being a hot jupiter or roaster . he has received the 2011 bbva foundation frontiers of knowledge award of basic sciences ( co-winner with michel mayor ) for developing new astronomical instruments and experimental techniques that led to the first observation of planets outside the solar system .

name: shonda lozano
bio: shonda lozano ( . 1830s ) was a famous cartographer . he engraved a map of hertfordshire with thomas moule , commonly known as .

name: william lee
bio: william lee ( born 1 december 1988 in karlstad ) is an alpine skier from sweden . he won a bronze medal at the 2011 fis alpine world ski championships in the team event , and finished 18th in the giant slalom , and 24th in the super-g .

name: madeline wright
bio: madeline wright or aleksandr kosenkov ( born 14 march 1977 ) is a german sprinter who specialises in the 100 metres . he represents the sports club tv wattenscheid .

name: lynn sugar
bio: lynn sugar ( born may 5 , 1941 , in augusta , georgia ) is an american politician who was elected to the 101st united states congress representing florida 's 4th congressional district in 1988 as a newly registered republican , defeating william v. chappell , jr. by a margin of 50.1 % to 49.9 % .

name: john lopez
bio: john lopez ( born february 16 , 1990 ) is a canadian former professional ice hockey goaltender . he is currently enrolled at the university of western ontario .

name: nelda shaffer
bio: nelda shaffer ( born february 23 , 1987 ) is a professional ice hockey defenceman currently playing with the brampton beast of the echl .

name: richard engman
bio: richard engman ( born 1953 ) is the co-founder and chairman of syntel .

name: paul marion
