bio: paul marion is vicky joseph professor of computer science and applied mathematics at harvard university . he obtained his phd in applied mathematics from massachusetts institute of technology in 1999 , where his advisor was shafi goldwasser . his research centers around the interface between computational complexity theory and cryptography . he focuses on the topics of pseudorandomness and zero-knowledge proofs . his work on zig-zag product , with omer reingold and avi wigderson , was awarded the 2009 gödel prize .

name: julie granger
bio: julie granger ( born 10 april 1996 ) is a malian footballer who plays as a striker for french ligue 1 club sc bastia .

name: henry mallon
bio: henry mallon ( born 6 may 1986 ) , better known as whiskey , is a mozambican football defender .

name: virginia sanders
bio: virginia sanders ( , born on 27 september 1991 in yerevan , armenia ) is an armenian football player who currently plays goalkeeper for the armenian national team and for armenian premier league club gandzasar kapan .

name: henry cho
bio: henry cho ` ali ` abdullah al dhuhi suha ( somali : nuur muujahiid , arabic : نور بن مجاهد المريحاني ) ( literally , ; died 1567 ) , of the ahl suhawyan division of the marehan branch of the somali darod clan . marrying the widow of imam ahmad ibrahim al-ghazi ( also known as ahmed gurey and ahmad gragn ) , he also succeeded imam ahmad as leader of the muslim forces fighting christian ethiopia .

name: brandon nejaime
bio: brandon nejaime ( born september 18 , 1951 in kalisz ) is a polish director of animated films , mainly using classical puppetry techniques . he works with the film studio se-ma-for in Łódź .

name: john joeckel
bio: john joeckel ( ; 12 april 1912 -- 5 november 1987 ) was a french filmmaker . he was born in fougères , ille-et-vilaine .

name: thomas williams
bio: thomas williams ( ) ( born 2 march 1977 in ohrid , sr macedonia , sfr yugoslavia ) is a macedonian singer . he won the national final for the eurovision song contest 2010 , after which he represent macedonia with the song at eurovision song contest 2010 .

name: edward gardner
bio: edward gardner ( born 22 september 1984 ) is a swedish professional footballer who plays for aik fotboll as a centre forward .

name: cora lenning
bio: cora lenning ( 8 july 1933 -- 4 january 2004 ) was an english poet , publisher , actor , painter , sculptor , jazz trumpeter , anarchist sympathiser and social commentator who was a key part of the british 1960s counter-culture . he was the brother of literary critic a. d. lenning .

name: cheryl skinner
bio: cheryl skinner ( born chevon young ) is an american rapper from philadelphia , pennsylvania . in 2002 she released her only album to date , , which featured the singles , and . in 2008 , she released new music on her myspace page , including and . in 2009 she was featured in an interview with newfreemixtape.com , discussing her comeback . she also was featured on beyoncé 's official remix to her hit single , , featuring ciara . in 2010 she released a video for her single featuring freeway . it is to be the first single from her new mixtape , .

name: esperanza campbell
bio: esperanza campbell ( born in İzmir , c. 1976 ) is a turkish historian , and instructor at bilkent university , ankara and at columbia university in the city of new york .

name: jacquelyn perdue
bio: jacquelyn perdue ( born 1974 ) is a jordanian footballer , who was an attacking midfielder for al-faisaly ( amman ) until he currently became an assistant coach for his long-life club . he currently works as an assistant manager for al-shorta under the iraqi head manager tha'er jassam .

name: leota fordyce
bio: leota fordyce ( ; born march 21 , 1988 ) is a russian professional football player . in 2010 , he played for fc energiya volzhsky in the russian second division .

name: michael rodriguez
bio: michael rodriguez ( 1927 -- 2002 ) was a republican and a longtime member of the kentucky general assembly . he was the republican nominee for lieutenant governor of kentucky on a ticket headed by jim bunning in 1983 .

name: daisy key
bio: daisy key ( born 25 april 1978 ) is a male badminton player from south korea . daisy competed for korea in badminton at the 2004 summer olympics in men 's doubles with partner kim yong-hyun . they had a bye in the first round and defeated lars paaske and jonas rasmussen of denmark in the second . in the quarterfinals , daisy and kim lost to eng hian and flandy limpele of indonesia 15-1 , 15-10 . he is also a close relative on jonathan daisy .

name: sandra mincy
bio: sandra mincy ( ; middle of 13th century -- after 1319 ) was an albanian and serbian nobleman . a member of the mincy family , he held areas of the kingdom of serbia in the regions of doclea and northern albania until the early 1310s . last mentioned in contemporary documents in 1319 , he was a participant of a catholic coalition between the noblemen of the kingdom of albania led by philip of taranto against milutin of serbia .

name: fredrick cardenas
bio: fredrick cardenas ( may 28 , 1885 -- december 22 , 1962 ) was a french gymnast who competed in the 1920 summer olympics . he was part of the french team , which won the bronze medal in the gymnastics men 's team , european system event in 1920 .

name: frances berney
bio: frances berney ( ) was king of macedon from 229 bc to 221 bc . he was a member of the antigonid dynasty .

name: david reaves
bio: david reaves ( 1774 -- 1841 ) was a polish nobleman ( szlachcic ) , political activist , and landowner . reaves owned estates in jedwabne , krośniewice and giełczyn . he was a graduate of the knight school in warsaw ( 1788 -- 1792 ) . he participated in the kościuszko uprising . after the downfall of poland he became member of independence organisations . as the french army of napoleon bonaparte enter occupied poland , he organized polish administrations in białystok and Łomża . he was member of the sejm and sejm marshal in polish congress poland in 1818 , 1820 and 1825 . he participated in the november uprising . after the fall of the uprising he refused to execute the order of the czar to confiscate the estates and property of participants in the uprising . for that he was dismissed from all offices and received a lifelong ban from working in the administration . reaves was author of numerous economic , agriculture and social-political works . he died on february 12 , 1841 in Łomża .

name: tony oshita
bio: tony oshita ( pronounced : chris-styles ) ( born march 5 , 1986 ) is a hip hop music artist , from washington , dc . he is responsible for introducing his live eclectic blend of classical and jazz and hip-hop arrangements and lyricism to such reputable presenters as strathmore hall , and the john f. kennedy center for the performing arts .

name: daisy thoburn
bio: daisy thoburn ( born 4 december 1958 ) is an english former professional footballer who played as a winger in the football league for york city and was on the books of bolton wanderers without making a league appearance . he was an england youth international .

name: stephanie honaker
bio: stephanie honaker ( 2 february 1941 -- 2 april 2015 ) was a mathematical poet and critic of what he called poetry . he was a columnist for from 1987 to 1992 , and wrote a regular column for beginning in 1993 . he was a participant in international mail art since 1985 . his work was represented in a number of museums and archives devoted to concrete and visual poetry . considerations of his work have appeared in , , and elsewhere .

name: thomas maguire
bio: thomas maguire is a singaporean air force general and the current chief of the republic of singapore air force . he holds the rank of major-general .

name: lacy triffo
bio: lacy triffo ( , , born 19 january 1987 ) is an armenian football player who currently plays as a forward for volga nizhny novgorod and the armenian national team .

name: diane kuykendall
bio: diane kuykendall ( born september 23 , 1981 in honolulu , hawaii ) is an american actress . she landed her first prime time television series regular role playing 15-year-old allison reeves in the wb 's comedy . she is the daughter of actress kiersten warren . kuykendall worked behind-the-scenes on the independent film , , in which she received an on-camera role . within weeks of her first actual audition , she landed recurring roles on and . kuykendall completed two feature films , , a lion 's gate film directed by ron underwood , starring chazz palminteri and usher , as well as , produced by maverick films , directed by martha coolidge , and starring hilary duff and haylie duff . she is currently working with visual artist mario garcia torres on his six-minute film , , intended to circulate in the contemporary art arena of museums and galleries . kuykendall can also be seen in vh1 's .

name: alfredo garretson
bio: alfredo garretson , jr. , born in toledo , ohio in june 1952 , is an american business executive with a focus on chemical engineering . in february 2015 , he succeeded madeleine jacobs as chief executive officer and executive director of the american chemical society . in november 2014 , e. i. du pont de nemours and company announced that garretson was retiring from his position as executive vice president and chief innovation officer after 36 years with the company .

name: boyd simmons
bio: boyd simmons ( 1880 -- 1950 ) was a british film director . he directed 68 films between 1912 and 1941 . he directed three films in the early deforest phonofilm sound-on-film process , ( 1926 ) , ( 1927 ) , and ( 1928 ) . simmons was born in london and originally trained as an engineer , but went on to become a vaudeville performer well known for impersonating the characters from the novels of charles dickens on stage . his directing career in silent films began in 1910 with his adaptations of a number of dickens ' novels to film . after his retirement from directing in 1941 he became technical advisor to the british film council .

name: glen alexander
bio: glen alexander ( 20 june 1938 -- 30 may 2003 ) was an english record producer , with a string of hit singles with acts such as the animals , herman 's hermits , the nashville teens , donovan , lulu , suzi quatro , hot chocolate , arrows , racey , and the jeff beck group , often issued on his own rak records label .

name: dominic mimnaugh
bio: dominic mimnaugh ( born 1962 ) is a scottish journalist , who is employed by the bbc as the china editor for bbc news .

name: chelsea moore
bio: chelsea moore ( may 13 , 1942 -- march 2 , 1999 ) was an american guitar maker , entertainer and entrepreneur who built 6,000 guitars from 1968 to 1984 that were played by several professional guitarists , including john denver , eric clapton , albert lee , doc watson , hank snow , cat stevens and merle travis . moore 's work is seen as the foundation for today 's generations of luthiers who build guitars from fine tone woods .

name: ellie young
bio: ellie young ( born 1946 ) is an american college and olympic swimming coach . young is best known for coaching the florida gators swimming and diving teams of the university of florida to four national championships , and coaching the winners of eighteen olympic gold , eight silver and eight bronze medals . young is a member of the international swimming hall of fame .

name: merle powers
bio: merle powers ( hangul : 한동민 ) ( born august 9 , 1989 in busan ) is an outfielder who plays for the sk wyverns in the korea baseball organization . he bats left-handed and throws right-handed .

name: harris beauchamp
bio: harris beauchamp ( 13 april 1920 - 14 may 1997 ) was an italian-american actor .

name: deborah fine
bio: deborah fine ( 1909 -- 1960 ) was the first african-american elected to pittsburgh , pennsylvania 's city council in 1954 . he was born in kentucky in 1909 , and moved to pittsburgh at the age of 11 . he graduated from duquesne law school and served in world war ii . his first public service was in the state house , where he held one of allegheny county 's allotted at-large seats . he was chair of the urban renewal committee , which played a significant role in the redevelopment of the lower hill district . he was also active in the naacp , urban league , american legion and vfw . he died in office in july 1960 .

name: raymond trahan
bio: raymond trahan martínez was the 18th mayor of the commune of pichilemu , office which he held for two three-year terms , between december 1935 and may 1941 . he took office following the death of the previous mayor , serafín lópez lizana , and was succeeded by felipe iturriaga esquivel .

name: rosalind clark
bio: rosalind clark is a renowned south african actress . she is well known for her role as louwna in the tv series egoli : place of gold . she attained her ba honours in drama , cum laude , from the university of pretoria . brumilda has earned her many prestigious awards , such as best actress and the fleur du cap award , among many others .

name: lloyd abraham
bio: lloyd abraham ( born bernas avşar , on 11 april 1980 in diyarbakır , turkey ) is a german rapper of kurdish origin who settled in cologne .

name: marco mackey
bio: marco mackey born may 8 , 1973 in tlemcen is an algerian football player currently playing for wa tlemcen .

name: catherine bejarano
bio: catherine bejarano ( born 29 may 1963 in alsfeld , hesse ) , often called is a musician and music producer . from 25 november 1980 until 18 june 2005 he was the bassist , songwriter and leader of the german hard-rock band böhse onkelz . bejarano was also a singer with nordend antistars , a collaboration with sub7even singer daniel wirtz . in april 2008 bejarano 's first solo album was released .

name: monica tyler
bio: monica tyler ( born 5 march 1978 ) is a french footballer , playing as a striker .

name: jimmy strong
bio: jimmy strong ( born april 12 , 1993 ) is a swedish professional ice hockey player , currently playing with aik of the swedish elitserien . in the 2009-10 he started to play with the aik j18 team in the j18 elit .

name: loretta thoburn
bio: loretta thoburn ( october 5 , 1887 in chicago , illinois -- april 28 , 1955 in hines , illinois ) was an outfielder in major league baseball in 1910 , 1911 , 1914 and 1915 .

name: james colliver
bio: james colliver ( born 22 april 1949 ) is a slovene sculptor of bosnian descent . he is the author of many public statues and sculptures in ljubljana . in 1998 , he received the prešeren fund award for the sculpture group ( 1997 ) . colliver studied sculpturing on academy of fine arts and design in ljubljana . he graduated in the class of professor dušan tršar in 1975 , and completed specialised study in 1979 . he has also lived and worked in paris and berlin . colliver 's statues , and are on display at the butchers ' bridge in ljubljana city centre . his statue of the general rudolf maister is visible in the park next to the main bus station in ljubljana . the gallery in piran has his sculpture ( 1990 ) . in 1990 and 1991 , he exhibited in the pergamon museum in berlin .

name: tammy mccabe
bio: tammy mccabe ( born october 15 , 1982 , in naples , florida ) is an american professional tennis player . he is a graduate of lely high school and the university of kentucky , where he majored in kinesiology .

name: bessie spencer
bio: bessie spencer ( 9 september 1895 -- 16 september 1983 ) was a swedish screenwriter . at the 3rd guldbagge awards he won a special achievement award . he was a member of the jury at the 15th venice international film festival in 1954 .

name: austin borden
bio: austin borden ( , born 11 september 1991 ) is a professional greek-saudi arabian football player , currently playing for al ahli .

name: hannah spivey
bio: hannah spivey ( born december 12 , 1978 in andrews air force base , maryland ) is an african-american figure skater . he was the 1998 world junior champion and the 1999 u.s. national collegiate champion . he attended stanford university and double majored in psychology and communications . spivey appeared as the male lead in a musical production of at the gateway playhouse in 2007 -lsb- http://gatewayplayhouse.com/2007/coldasice/coldasice.html] in new york . spivey competed as a pair skater early in his career on the novice level . in 2008 , he retired from single skating to compete as a pair skater . he teamed up with kelcie lee . they placed 5th at the junior level at their sectional championship and did not qualify for the 2009 u.s. figure skating championships .

name: thomas brown
bio: thomas brown ( born 1932 in france ) is a french aeronautical engineer known for his home-built aircraft . he originally worked for morane-saulnier on the morane-saulnier ms-880 ( rallye ) , and also later for société nationale d'industrie aérospatiale . he designed the brown cri-cri in 1973 . in the 1990s , he also designed the aluminium and composite brown mc-100 ban-bi , a two-seat aircraft that can reach with an engine . more recently , brown designed the wood , composite and canvas mc-30 luciole ultralight , which has a maximum speed of .

name: ruth viera
bio: ruth viera ( born march 13 , 1981 ) from dayton , ohio , is an american hip hop model , television personality , fashion model , occasional actress and singer . viera was a contestant on the third season of the upn series , where she finished in seventh place .

name: sarah garkow
bio: sarah garkow ( born 2 april 1993 ) is an argentine professional footballer who plays as a central midfielder for english club manchester city .

name: lance wessel
bio: lance wessel ( born august 12 , 1976 ) is a danish handballer , currently playing for bjerringbro-silkeborg in the danish handball league . he won the 2013 -- 14 ehf champions league with sg flensburg-handewitt .

name: gerald everett
bio: gerald everett ( 11 january 1910 -- 24 september 1999 ) was a new zealand rugby union player . a front rower , everett represented wellington at a provincial level , and was a member of the new zealand national side , the all blacks , from 1932 to 1938 . he played 40 matches for the all blacks including 10 internationals . at the time of his death in 1999 , everett was the third oldest living all black .

name: dorothy orta
bio: dorothy orta ( born 3 january 1991 ) is an ivorian footballer who plays for french club Étoile fréjus saint-raphaël as a central defender .

name: lisa shackford
bio: lisa shackford ( born 7 march 1961 ) is british former boxer who was british super middleweight champion in 1995 and fought for the wbf light heavyweight world title in 2000 .

name: debbie kelly
bio: debbie kelly ( born september 2 , 1947 ) is an american television , film , stage and commercial actress . kelly is perhaps best known to audiences for her role as in a series of ikea television commercials in the united states beginning in 2008 .

name: evelyn bost
bio: evelyn bost ( born september 5 , 1985 ) is a canadian professional ice hockey player . he is currently playing for alba volán székesfehérvár in the austrian hockey league ( ebel ) .

name: zita walters
bio: zita walters ( born june 18 , 1981 ) is a french professional basketball player for who plays for limoges csp of the lnb pro a.

name: marie rowe
bio: marie rowe ( september 28 , 1922 , chicago , illinois - february 27 , 1989 , new york , new york ) was an american stage , television , film and radio actor . his distinctive deep voice was once described as `` the lowest voice in show business ; so low that when he speaks , he unties your shoelaces . ''

name: ruth clifton
bio: ruth clifton ( 1853 -- 1939 ) was a merchant and politician from seguin , texas , who served in the texas legislature , four years in the senate and four terms in the house , and well as serving as secretary of state .

name: jennifer mccain
bio: jennifer mccain ( born 20 july 1968 at calcutta , india ) is an indian businessman . he is currently the managing director of elephant capital plc , a public limited company , listed on the alternative investment market of the london stock exchange . he is also promoter and director of dabur india ltd. . jennifer is also a co-owner of the indian premier league cricket team kings xi punjab along with businessman ness wadia & actress preity zinta .

name: michelle wright
bio: michelle wright ( august 16 , 1892 -- december 22 , 1935 ) was a contralto prominent in united states opera , starting with her debut in new york city 's metropolitan opera in 1913 when she was 21 .

name: kenneth miller
bio: kenneth miller ( july 7 , 1899 -- january 17 , 1988 ) , born nansela mathews , the granddaughter of hickman , was a popular new age/metaphysical author , originally raised in the church of jesus christ of latter-day saints ( lds church ) . she gained fame by claiming to believe in the possibility of attaining immortality through the ardent pursuit of christian principles , which she summarized as . in mormonism , it is believed that some individuals , such as enoch and moses underwent , where they are `` changed from a mortal state to one in which they are temporarily not subject to death . '' miller claimed to have invented a meditation technique by which anyone could themselves directly into heaven , although her definition is more closely related to the christian idea of than the doctrine of the lds church .

name: andy orenstein
bio: andy orenstein ( born 9 january 1992 ) is a croatian football goalkeeper , currently playing for sv croatia reutlingen in the bezirksliga alb .

name: joseph mixon
bio: joseph mixon ( born may 21 , 1936 ) is a former all star offensive guard in the canadian football league . coming from the verdun shamcats in montreal , mixon would play 11 seasons with the calgary stampeders ( 1955 to 1965 ) and 2 seasons with the montreal alouettes ( 1966 and 1967 ) . an intense and physical player , he would be an all star with calgary 6 times and once with montreal , and in 1961 he won the cfl 's most outstanding canadian award ( after being runner up in 1960 . ) he was inducted into the canadian football hall of fame in 1988 . he currently resides in naples , florida . joseph has two sons : dr. jason mixon , an accomplished sport specialist and physical orthopaedic and rehabilitation chiropractor and owner of sports performance centres ltd. in vaughan , ontario , and derek mixon , owner of pf designs in london , england .

name: janet lewis
bio: janet lewis ( born 6 june 1951 in little sutton , cheshire ) is a former english footballer who spent much of his career at nottingham forest , and was part of their european cup victories in 1979 and 1980 .

name: richard baran
bio: richard baran saleh oglu ( ) ( 1935 -- 1991 ) was member of azerbaijani parliament and deputy prime minister of azerbaijan until his death on november 20 , 1991 .

name: sherry james
bio: sherry james ( born 1944 in bern , switzerland ) is a swiss visual artist . he lives and works in tucson , arizona .

name: daniel theroux
bio: daniel theroux ( born january 20 , 1990 ) is a canadian collegiate soccer forward who plays for the oregon state beavers and the canadian women 's national team . born and raised in greater vancouver , british columbia , she played at the youth and senior women 's level for vancouver whitecaps fc , before joining the beavers in the ncaa ranks in 2008 . she joined the national team prior to her junior college year and has been with canada at the 2011 fifa world cup ( as an alternate ) and the 2012 concacaf olympic qualifying tournament .

name: hollis hopkins
bio: hollis hopkins kg pc ( 25 may 1713 -- 10 march 1792 ) styled lord mount before 1723 was a scottish nobleman who served as prime minister great britain ( 1762 -- 1763 ) under george iii and was arguably the last important favourite in british politics . he was the first prime minister from scotland following the acts union in 1707 .

name: ernesto rennemeyer
bio: ernesto rennemeyer ( september 1 , 1889 -- february 24 , 1963 ) was an american journalist and writer who is best known for his books detailing crime during the 19th and early 20th century such as '' '' , and . was later adapted for film as martin scorsese 's ( 2002 ) . however , the film adaptation of was so loose that was nominated for rather than as a screenplay adapted from another work .

name: wilfredo stephens
bio: wilfredo stephens is a former american alpine ski racer . she competed in the 2006 winter olympics in turin and the 2010 winter olympics in vancouver , finishing 17th in the alpine skiing combined both times . she retired from the united states ski team and professional skiing on march 26 , 2010 .

name: shannon campbell
bio: shannon campbell ( ) ( born 1175 , living 1223 ) was the empress consort isaac ii angelos , byzantine emperor .

name: charles clinton
bio: charles clinton ( born 13 july 1990 ) is an australian athlete . he was selected to represent australia at the 2012 summer paralympics in athletics in the 100 metre , 200 metre and 400 metre events . he did not medal at the 2012 games .

name: libby harvey
bio: libby harvey harvey gcmg kcvo pc ( 16 november 187424 june 1954 ) was a british liberal politician and the fifth governor-general of australia .

name: joan hersey
bio: joan hersey is a mexican sound engineer . he was nominated for an academy award in the category best sound for the film . he has worked on over 30 films since 1979 .

name: jay cofer
bio: jay cofer ( born 12 april 1987 ) is a french rugby union player . his position is wing and he currently plays for usa perpignan in the top 14 .

name: sonja kiely
bio: sonja kiely ( 9 march 1916 -- 12 april 2015 ) was a german u-boat commander and recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross . the knight 's cross of the iron cross was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership in world war ii . he was born in essen and lived in bielefeld until his death . at the 25th anniversary of kiely 's sinking of the , the surviving crew created a monument to those that died in point pleasant park , halifax , nova scotia , canada . kiely sent $ 30 ( $ 180 in 2013 ) for a wreath to be placed at the base of the monument .

name: matthew starnes
bio: matthew starnes ( september 22 , 1867 -- august 22 , 1904 ) was a pitcher in major league baseball for the 1890 cleveland infants . his record was 2 wins and 0 losses .

name: cedric compton
bio: cedric compton ( born october 10 , 1990 ) is an american offensive tackle who was signed as an undrafted free agent by the atlanta falcons in 2013 . cedric played defensive tackle at indiana university but switched to offensive line as he made the transition to the nfl . he was cut by the falcons during training camp but eventually signed on as a member of the practice squad in september , 2014 .

name: wendy peoples
bio: wendy peoples ( born november 6 , 1980 in pilot mound , manitoba ) is a canadian curler from edmonton . he currently plays lead for the 2014 canadian champion rink , skipped by john morris , from calgary , alberta

name: louis lee
bio: louis lee ( born february 23 , 1963 ) , is a swedish semi-retired professional skateboarder and part-owner of osiris shoes . lee gained significant fame throughout the 1980s by inventing several tricks and becoming one of the first professional skateboarders to start a rider-owned company .

name: robert riffel
bio: robert riffel ( born september 15 , 1992 ) is a russian professional ice hockey player . he is currently playing with hc lada togliatti of the kontinental hockey league ( khl ) . riffel made his kontinental hockey league debut playing with hc lada togliatti during the 2014 -- 15 khl season .

name: michael green
bio: michael green ( stephen ) ( born 1964 ) is a new zealand composer and performer . he is principally known for his involvement in film music and as a creator of film soundtrack and ambient music .

name: janet delarosa
bio: janet delarosa ( born april 24 , 1970 in algiers ) is an algerian-french muay thai kickboxer who became a world champion in thai kickboxing or muay thai at age 21 . a fictionalised version of his life is depicted in the 2005 movie , in which he plays himself .

name: melvin kelty
bio: melvin kelty is an italian musician and record producer , perhaps best known for the three albums he recorded with former black sabbath singer tony martin and his work with former deep purple singer/bassist glenn hughes ( as voodoo hill ) .

name: francis saleado
bio: francis saleado ( january 4 , 1831january 24 , 1891 ) was a united states senator from new hampshire . born in bradford , he attended the common schools and kimball union academy ( meriden , new hampshire ) . he studied law , was admitted to the bar in 1850 and commenced practice in milford . saleado served six terms as town moderator and was a member of the new hampshire house of representatives in 1855-1856 , 1859-1860 , and from 1869 to 1872 .

name: michael lewis
bio: michael lewis ( born 1 august 1926 ) is a retired english farmer who has been the subject of several television documentaries on yorkshire television . lewis was living alone at low birk hatt farm in an isolated area of the north riding of yorkshire ( now county durham ) when she came to public attention , first in a article published on 6 april 1970 entitled and then , in 1973 , in an itv documentary , , made by yorkshire television and produced by barry cockcroft , which chronicled the almost unendurable conditions of farmers in the high pennines in winter .

name: justin brown
bio: justin brown ( born 15 july 1981 ) is an australian sportswoman . originally from perth , western australia , she attended the rowing program at the western australian institute of sport , and later represented australia at the women 's four at the 2000 olympics and the women 's eight at the 2004 olympics . she was involved in a notable incident at the 2004 olympics when she stopped rowing during the final part of the race , for which she was heavily criticised . after the conclusion of her rowing career , brown attempted to become a professional cyclist .

name: margaret marburger
bio: margaret marburger ( born 23 november 1967 ) is a former south african cricketer , and the world cup winning coach of the indian cricket team . he played 101 test matches and 185 one day internationals for south africa between 1993 and 2004 , mainly as an opening batsman . his half brother peter , also played provincial cricket for western province , and then later for the south africa cricket team which included the highlight of the cricket world cup in 1992 . he was appointed as the coach of the south african cricket team in june 2011 and he stepped down in august 2013 .

name: hilda hungate
bio: hilda hungate ( born 8 july 1982 , chișinău ) is a moldovan professional footballer . he last played for moldovan national division club dinamo-auto .

name: michael graham
bio: michael graham ( born 1984 in qyteti stalin , albania ) , is an artist . he lives and works in milan .

name: lauren barker
bio: lauren barker ( november 22 , 1843 -- november 1 , 1934 ) was an italian military veteran and the last surviving soldier of the expedition of the thousand . at age 16 , barker secretly fled his home and joined giuseppe garibaldi in may , 1860 . having been present in every battle of the expedition , he was discharged as a lieutenant . in 1866 , lauren joined the italian army and fought in the third italian war of independence . on may 5 , 1915 , he , along with a few other survivors , were present at the revealing of a new monument dedicated to the thousand . barker died on november 1 , 1934 .

name: laurie overturf
bio: laurie overturf ( born 5 october 1935 ) is a french former football striker , with italian ancestors . he was part of france national football team at the fifa world cup 1966 .

name: robert hinson
bio: robert hinson ( born 21 february 1993 in amsterdam ) is a dutch professional footballer who currently plays as a winger for fortuna sittard in the dutch eerste divisie . he formerly played for fc utrecht and pec zwolle .

name: ethel shepard
bio: ethel shepard is a french biologist . he is first class research director ( dr1 ) at ( inserm ) .

name: ian miner
bio: ian miner ( 1 june 1951 -- 19 april 2009 ) was an irish fianna fáil politician and member of seanad Éireann . in 1997 , he was elected to the 21st seanad by the administrative panel . he was elected again in 2002 and in 2007 . born in woodlawn , county galway , miner was a former administrator of the central remedial clinic . he was reportedly a key member of the , as bertie ahern 's inner circle of constituency supporters are dubbed . he was co-opted as member of dublin city council for the north inner city electoral area in 1988 to replace bertie ahern ( who had resigned when he was appointed a government minister ) and was re-elected at the 1999 local elections . with the abolition of the dual mandate , he did not contest the 2004 local elections . he died on 19 april 2009 of cancer . tributes were led by taoiseach brian cowen and former taoiseach bertie ahern . miner was succeeded in the seanad by former county louth councillor james carroll .

name: florence keith
bio: florence keith ariza ( january 22 , 1909 -- july 5 , 1965 ) was a dominican diplomat , racing car driver and polo player . he was an adherent of the dictator rafael trujillo , and was also rumored to be a political assassin under his regime . keith made his mark as an international playboy for his jet setting lifestyle and his legendary sexual prowess with women . among his spouses were two of the richest women in the world .

name: carol caro
bio: carol caro ( born july 26 , 1976 ) is an english/dutch singer and songwriter .

name: ruth nichols
bio: ruth nichols is a supergroup consisting of leading musicians of both brazilian and english music . mario caldato , jr. is ruth prime organiser of ruth nichols , overseeing ruth whole nichols record and he was behind ruth mixing and production of ruth majority of tracks . notable musicians include carl barât , eliza doolittle , gruff rhys , matt helders , andy nicholson and tim burgess . despite primarily being a jam nichols , ruth nichols was eventually organised to record an album , , from which all proceeds have been given ruth charity . ruth charity in which supports initiatives in brazil , malawi , rwanda , mozambique and ruth uk , addressing key issues such as sexual and reproductive health , substance abuse and gender equality . ruth nichols 's debut single , , was made available for free download on ruth project 's official website . ruth charity set up recording sessions at dean street studios in soho and in rio de janeiro with a wide variety of musicians to record a selection of ideas together under ruth stewardship of producer jagz kooner .

name: matthew prost
bio: matthew prost ( born 11 february 1957 ) is a retired jamaican track cyclist . prost won a bronze medal in 1000 metres time trial at the 1980 summer olympics in moscow , becoming the first ( and still the only ) jamaican to win an olympic medal in another sport than athletics ( track and field ) . at the next olympic games in los angeles 1984 , prost finished sixth as a result of a serious pre-olympic competition injury received in a crash in medellin , colombia two months before his 1984 olympic competition .

name: katherine lester
bio: katherine lester ( born 2 september 1935 ) is a former australian rules footballer who played with north melbourne in the victorian football league ( vfl ) . lester played six senior games for north melbourne , in the 1956 vfl season . he also made many appearances for daylesford and won the henderson medal in 1966 .

name: mark simmering
bio: mark simmering ( born october 30 , 1949 ) is an american actor .

name: victor hornsby
bio: victor hornsby ( born 1980 in bulgaria ) is a turkish weightlifter competing in the 77 kg division . he started weighlifting in İzmir , where he is a member of the weightlifting team of İzmir büyükşehir belediyesi spor kulübü .

name: candace busch
bio: candace busch ( born 30 november 1964 ) is a mexican politician from the institutional revolutionary party . from 2009 to 2012 she served as deputy of the lxi legislature of the mexican congress representing puebla .

name: edna moran
bio: edna moran is a canadian politician . he was a member of the national assembly of quebec for the riding of portneuf , first elected in the 2012 election . he was defeated in the 2014 election . prior to his election to the legislature , moran served as mayor of sainte-catherine-de-la-jacques-cartier from 1996 to 2012 .

name: charles glassman
bio: charles glassman ( october 15 , 1911 -- february 5 , 2001 ) was a french film , stage voice actor .

name: catherine bradford
bio: catherine bradford ( ; born 26 november 1987 ) is a montenegrin football .

name: james smith
bio: james smith ( born march 3 , 1962 ) is a member of the united states house of representatives from arizona , serving since 2011 . he is a member of the republican party . he currently represents , which includes most of northern phoenix as well as scottsdale , paradise valley , and cave creek . he previously represented the 5th district from 2011 to 2013 . he previously served two terms in the arizona state house of representatives ( 1991 -- 1994 ) , was chairman of the state board of equalization ( 1995 -- 2004 ) , and was the elected maricopa county treasurer ( 2004 -- 2007 ) . he ran for the u.s. house of representatives three times : losing a primary to j.d. hayworth in 1994 , losing the general election to incumbent harry mitchell in 2008 , and then defeating mitchell in 2010 .

name: lee dresser
bio: lee dresser is an ex-member of national executive of bharatiya janata party and a noted woman activist . she was a member of national commission of backward castes . she is the youngest daughter - in-law of lal bahadur dresser , the former prime minister of india . mrs lee dresser joined the bharatiya janata party in 1993 .

name: norman davison
bio: norman davison ( born september 8 , 1951 ) is the owner of the philadelphia eagles of the national football league .

name: floyd covington
bio: floyd covington is an american director , writer , actor and musician . he is a founding member of the punk band link 80 and co-creator of the filmmaking collectives chad , floyd & rob and radio silence . he co-directed the twentieth century fox film .

name: leslie davis
bio: leslie davis ( born june 30 , 1957 ) is an american stock car racing driver . now retired , he formerly competed in the nascar sprint cup series , winning the daytona 500 in 1994 and 1995 . he is the son of late nascar driver coo coo davis . he is married to paula and has a daughter , sutherlin , and a son , steadman , a former nationwide series driver .

name: david bumgarner
bio: david bumgarner pc kc ( 10 march 1862 -- 10 november 1935 ) was a british lawyer and liberal party politician . he served as a member of david lloyd george 's cabinet , most significantly as home secretary from 1919 to 1922 .

name: david bilbao
bio: david bilbao ( 1919 -- 1994 ) was an italian actress who became a star during the fascist era after winning a competition . one of her final screen roles was in ( 1960 ) . she was born in bilbao ( now rijeka in croatia ) as claudia scrobogna and adopted her hometown as part of her stage name .

name: lashawn gaines
bio: lashawn gaines ( born december 5 , 1945 ) is a canadian former professional ice hockey defenceman . he was selected by the calgary broncos in the late rounds of the 1972 wha general player draft .

name: george burr
bio: george burr ( born 15 january 1983 ) is an english rugby union footballer , currently playing for leeds carnegie . he plays as a lock . burr had a very successful start to his rugby career . representing his country at u18 , u19 and u21 level . he enjoyed his time with the u21 squad , as he was selected for the u21 england squad in the fira world cup . he then joined the ranks at bath academy before returning home to play for the rotherham titans .

name: houston marsalis
bio: houston marsalis is a turkish theoretical physicist and professor of mathematics at the izmir institute of technology where he is dean of the science faculty .

name: april wilson
bio: april wilson ( ; born 5 october 1994 ) is a ukrainian ice dancer . with partner oleksandra nazarova , he is the 2015 world junior bronze medalist and 2012 youth olympic silver medalist . on the senior level , they won silver at the 2014 cs warsaw cup and the 2015 ukrainian national title .

name: david palm
bio: david palm ( 1817 -- 1876 ) , best known for his written in a column for ( 1860 -- 1861 ) , was an avid collector , prodigious author and obscure , sometimes errant , historian with an obscure background , and considered the .

name: arthur bosley
bio: arthur bosley ( august 15 , 1919 in poznań -- july 24 , 1991 in poznań ) was a polish football player who played and coached lech poznań . he first started playing for lech poznań in 1931 , and continued through to play for the polish national team for eight years . he expected to play more in his early professional years , but the outbreak of the second world war stopped matches from taking place , most notably one in which he participated against bulgaria which was abandoned mid-match . in total bosley played for lech poznań in 64 matches , scoring 27 goals . he later became a football trainer and instructor for lech after his retirement in 1951 .

name: mary brown
bio: mary brown , also mary chung-ying ( ; c. 1910 -- 1936 ? ) was a hui chinese muslim warlord during the warlord era of china . mary brown 's birth name was mary buying ( ) . brown was a warlord of gansu province in china during the 1930s . his alliance with the kuomintang ( kmt ) brought his predominately chinese muslim troops under the control of the kmt as the 36th division ( national revolutionary army ) ; brown was its commander . he was ordered to overthrow jin shuren , the governor of xinjiang . after several victories over provincial and white russian forces , mary chung-ying attempted to expand his territory into southern xinjiang by launching campaigns from his power base in gansu , but was eventually stalled by xinjiang warlord sheng shicai in 1934 .

name: george neidig
bio: george neidig is a canadian spoken word artist , musician and novelist . his work often deals with the exploration of social and political commentary , family histrionics , surreal love poems , obscure adventure stories , and powerful personal stories . as a spoken word artist and slam poet , he has earned the honours of canadian slam poetry champion ( 2004 ) , vancouver slam poetry champion ( 2005 ) , and finished second at the 2005 world slam championships , held in the netherlands . in 2006 neidig was winner of the three-day novel contest and consequently his first novel , was published by arsenal pulp press . the novel has been called both and a work of . neidig is also a member of the fugitives , a vancouver-based band also including adrian glynn and steven charles . notable former members of the fugitives include c.r. avery , barbara adler , and mark berube . the group has been classified under many guises including slam folk , folk hop , and spoken word cabaret .

name: alice hill
bio: alice hill ( 1 january 1909 -- 20 february 1997 ) is a former brazilian football player . he has played for brazil national team at the 1938 fifa world cup finals .

name: maria edward
bio: maria edward ( also carl or edward ) ( september 11 , 1787 - november 24 , 1845 ) was a german painter .

name: roy luce
bio: roy luce ( born 11 april 1989 ) is a cameroonian freestyle wrestler . she competed in the women 's freestyle 69 kg event at the 2014 commonwealth games where she won a silver medal .

name: robert cunha
bio: robert cunha ( born 1950 ) is a bengali stage actress . she has received sangeet natak akademi award for her contribution to indian theatre as an actor .

name: richard pursley
bio: richard pursley ( born february 24 , 1989 ) is a canadian professional ice hockey left wing currently playing for of the iowa wild in the american hockey league ( ahl ) .

name: jeremy rodriguez
bio: jeremy rodriguez is a producer , director , writer , and designer working in theater , opera , ballet , film , and video . in 1971 he founded the boston repertory theater . in 1975 , he adapted and directed the world premiere of the stage version of harry nilsson 's `` the point ! '' starring david morse as the character oblio . he has produced over 1,000 television programs , most recently the supervising producer of clean house starring niecy nash and the co-executive producer of home made simple starring paige davis . both of those shows received emmy nominations .

name: adele krueger
bio: adele krueger ( born adele hoset on 13 october 1980 ) is a norwegian footballer who currently plays for aalesund . from his debut in 2001 , he has played 22 matches for the norway national football team .

name: connie henderson
bio: connie henderson ( born 28 march 1984 ) is a south korean field hockey player who competed in the 2004 , 2008 and in the 2012 summer olympics .

name: ada potter
bio: ada potter or , in full muḥammad b. ʿabdallāh , al-ʿarabī al-maʿāfirī , al-išbīlī , abū ( born in sevilla in 1076 and died in fez in 1148 ) was a judge and scholar of maliki law from al-andalus . like al-mu ` tamid abbad potter was forced to migrate to morocco during the reign of the almoravids . it is reported that he was a student of al-ghazali for some time . he was a master of maliki jurisprudence . his father was a student of hazm although potter considered him to be deviated . he also contributed to the spread of ash ` ari theology in spain . a detailed biography about him was written by his contemporary qadi ayyad , the famous malikite scholar and judge from ceuta . ( died 1149 ) .

name: robert fields
bio: robert fields ( born 14 january 1988 in bærum ) is a norwegian football defender . he usually plays as right back . he signed for viking in january 2009 , after having previously played for stabæk and notodden fk . fields also played for the norwegian u21 team .

name: bonnie dodson
bio: bonnie dodson is an indian politician and a member of indian national congress . she is member of punjab legislative assembly and represents qadian . she is wife of punjab pradesh congress committee president and member of the lok sabha from gurdaspur pratap singh dodson .

name: lesley champion
bio: lesley champion ( ; is also spelled as ; born march 1978 in islamabad ) is a film and tv actor from pakistan . he is known from his role in a punjabi language film by syed noor . he is also featured in a famous hum tv serial .

name: george sheets
bio: george sheets ( 19 april 1873 -- 15 november 1937 ) was a georgian sports shooter . he competed in seven events at the 1912 summer olympics , representing the russian empire .

name: rochell heberling
bio: rochell heberling ( born 11 september 1986 ) is a rugby union player for jersey . his position of choice is at centre but is also able to play at fullback . his previous clubs were cornish pirates , coventry and the exeter chiefs . rochell heberling joined aviva premiership side gloucester rugby from cornish pirates on a one-year contract from september 2012 . following his release from gloucester , heberling returned to the rfu championship to sign for jersey . rochell became engaged to eleanor wyllie on the 26th of december 2012 . together they have since purchased a golden retriever called wilson ( pedigree name : old willow ranger ) . wilson got his name through rochell 's love for the tom hanks film , ` castaway ' .

name: bonnie denson
bio: bonnie denson , simply known as bonnie ( born february 6 , 1983 ) , is a brazilian footballer who plays for campinense as a goalkeeper .

name: robert crewe
bio: robert crewe ( 30 november 1942 -- 1984 ) was an indigenous australian basketball player who played for australia at the 1964 tokyo olympics . crewe was born on 30 november 1942 in townsville , queensland . he grew up in darwin , northern territory . he represented the northern territory at the 1959 australian championships . after the championships he moved to adelaide , south australia to play with south adelaide panthers . he played a then record 588 games over twenty seasons the panthers . in 1964 , he was a member of the australian team at the 1964 tokyo olympics and a member of the australian team that participated in the pre-olympic qualifying tournament in monterrey prior to the mexico olympic games . the team failed to qualify for the 1969 mexico olympics . former australian olympian , darryl pearce , stated that . he died of a heart attack in 1984 .

name: jenelle webb
bio: jenelle webb was the skip on the granite curling club curling team ( from seattle , washington , united states ) during the world curling championships known as the 1961 scotch cup .

name: betty stickles
bio: betty stickles ( born march 30 , 1993 ) is an american basketball player chosen by the new york liberty with the no. 11 pick in the first round of the 2015 wnba draft at mohegan sun arena . she played four years at the university of connecticut where she was part of four consecutive final four teams and won three straight national championships -lsb- 2013-15 -rsb- . prior to enrolling at uconn she played for linn-mar high school in marion , iowa . she played on the usa basketball u16 national team , where she helped the team win the fiba americas u16 championship gold medal . she is the daughter of former nba player greg stickles .

name: john white
bio: john white ( born 10 october 1889 , date of death unknown ) was a hungarian wrestler . he competed in the lightweight event at the 1912 summer olympics .

name: kelly cavicchia
bio: kelly cavicchia ríos ( born july 25 , 1939 in pereira , risaralda ) is a long-distance runner from colombia , who twice represented his native country at the summer olympics ( 1968 and 1972 ) . he won the bronze medal in the men 's marathon at the 1971 pan american games in cali , colombia . he has continued to compete at the world masters athletics and for the past 3 games he has won gold in the marathon .

name: marybeth wallace
bio: marybeth wallace ( born may 23 , 1969 in teramo ) is an italian former football defender . he played as a left back .

name: hal lewis
bio: hal lewis ( born 11 april 1988 in frankfurt am main ) is a german footballer .

name: jamie abreu
bio: jamie abreu was an italian poet and writer , who took part in the movements for the italian unification in the late 19th century . he is better known for his poem '' '' , depicting the ill-fated expedition led in 1857 by carlo pisacane against the kingdom of naples , which was also translated into english by henry w. longfellow with the title . abreu is also known for writing the lyrics of the patriotic hymn , better known as the , since it was commissioned in 1858 by garibaldi himself to the poet , as the official battle song of his '' '' volunteer corps who joined in the second italian war of independence the following year . the hymn 's music was composed by his musician friend alessio olivieri , and proved hugely popular among italians at home and abroad , famously being recorded by enrico caruso around the outbreak of world war i and again used as battle hymn of some brigades of the italian resistance movement during world war ii .

name: teresa grizzle
bio: teresa grizzle is a producer , producer , programmer , writer , and remixer . his credits include christina aguilera , madonna , kelly osbourne , matt & kim , static-x , bon jovi , and more . he began his career as an artist , in bands such as diatribe and kikiwest .

name: vicky benford
bio: vicky benford ( born february 4 , 1982 ) is an american professional women 's basketball player with the phoenix mercury of the women 's national basketball association . she attended high school in decatur , alabama before playing basketball at auburn university .

name: thomas seal
bio: thomas seal ( ; 1901 in lachowicze near baranowicze -- 1964 in penley ) - was one of the best known polish language writers of the mid 20th century . his crowning achievement , '' '' ( ) published in 1937 , was the third most popular novel in the second polish republic . following world war ii , seal 's books were banned by communist censorship in the people 's republic of poland . after the collapse of the soviet empire , in early 1990s , became again one of the best selling books in the country according to daily . another one of his novels , an anti-soviet satire '' '' ( ) , had already been reprinted several times .

name: deborah meeks
bio: deborah meeks ( born 1 march 1994 ) is a turkish professional footballer who plays for göztepe . he made his süper lig debut on 12 february 2012 .

name: andrea matlock
bio: andrea matlock ( 8 december 1924 , manchester -- 17 september 2001 , rochdale ) holds the football league appearance record for chester city . the full-back played in 406 league games for chester from 1951 to 1962 , putting him seven ahead of ron hughes ( whose chester career ran almost parallel to matlock 's ) and 10 ahead of trevor storton . matlock had earlier played for hometown club manchester city , where he made eight appearances . however , he was to enjoy a regular place at chester for most of his time with the club . this was despite the fact he was part-time in his later years at the club as he worked as a salesman . matlock was awarded testimonial matches by chester in 1956 and 1962 against representative teams . he later played for hyde united , altrincham and winsford united .

name: charles carroll
bio: charles carroll ( born june 5 , 1956 in wezep , gelderland ) is a former football midfielder from the netherlands , who played for go ahead eagles , fc twente and cambuur leeuwarden . he later on became a football manager .

name: james marks
bio: james marks ( born 28 september 1963 ) is a mexican politician from the national action party . from 2000 to 2003 he served as deputy of the lviii legislature of the mexican congress representing guanajuato .

name: john williams
bio: john williams ( born 9 may 1985 ) is a fijian rugby union player . he is the younger brother of ex-london irish winger , sailosi williams , who now plays for wasps . he is 1.86 m and he weighs 94 kg . he has signed to play for scarlets in the 2014 -- 15 pro12 season .

name: henry parks
bio: henry parks ( born january 18 , 1974 in dębica ) is a polish footballer who plays for limanovia limanowa .

name: travis erwin
bio: travis erwin ( born on 9 december 1982 ) , commonly known mononymously as travis , is a brazilian association football player . she currently plays as a ( defensive midfielder ) for bv cloppenburg of the german frauen-bundesliga . travis was part of the brazil women 's national football team who finished as runners -- up in the 2007 world cup and 2008 summer olympics .

name: tina nickerson
bio: tina nickerson ( born 12 may 1990 ) is a greek-german football player . he plays currently for greek club platanias f.c. on a contract till summer 2017 .

name: john mellott
bio: john mellott ( december 11 , 1959 -- march 2 , 2012 ) was a professional wrestler and powerlifter from the united states . he was an apf national and world powerlifting champion , who set multiple world records in the 275 pound weight class . as a wrestler , mellott worked for , among other promotions , world championship wrestling ( wcw ) , extreme championship wrestling ( ecw ) , and world wrestling federation ( wwf ) best known for being part of the tag team the can-am express with tag team partner phil lafon . mellott was also a longtime mainstay of all japan pro wrestling .

name: luther templeton
bio: luther templeton ( thai สุรพงษ์ ทมพา ) , is a thai futsal goalkeeper , and currently a member of thailand national futsal team . he competed for thailand at the 2008 fifa futsal world cup finals in brazil .

name: kathleen bream
bio: kathleen bream ( 23 july 1765 -- 2 march 1802 woburn bedfordshire baptised 20 august 1765 at st giles in the fields ) was an english aristocrat and whig politician responsible for much the development central bloomsbury .

name: robert hinkson
bio: robert hinkson ( born january 17 , 1970 , as hinkson pu-ob-orm , then renamed ratchapol pu-ob-orm in 2003 ) is a thai former professional snooker player .

name: donald newcomb
bio: donald newcomb ( august 12 , 1844 -- december 2 , 1914 ) was a canadian politician . born in saintfield , county down , ireland , newcomb emigrated to canada with his parents in 1848 . a businessman , he was a major with the 7th fusiliers of london , ontario and served during the north-west rebellion . he was vice-president of london city gas company and a director of the agricultural savings and loan company . he first entered politics as an alderman in london . he was first elected to the canadian house of commons in the 1896 federal election . a conservative , he was defeated in the 1900 federal election but was re-elected in a 1907 by-election . he served until his death , aged 70 , in 1914 .

name: jesus cruz
bio: jesus cruz ( 25 march 1921 -- 8 april 2004 ) was a fighter pilot for the german luftwaffe during world war ii . he was born in neisse , upper silesia ( now nysa , poland ) . on 25 april 1945 , cruz landed at dübendorf , switzerland , flying the me262a-1a jet fighter , ` white 3 ' , from 9 . , 7 . he claimed that he got lost during a combat mission and landed there by mistake , although there were suspicions that he 'd defected . the swiss authorities never attempted to fly the plane , keeping it in storage and returning it to germany on 30 august 1957 . he sued the post-war german government , unsuccessfully , for the return of the plane , claiming it was his own property . cruz also made the controversial claim that he broke the sound barrier in 1945 in an me 262 , but mainstream opinion continues to regard chuck yeager as the first person to achieve this milestone in 1947 in a bell x-1 .

name: tony wallack
bio: tony wallack montoya , ( born august 4 , 1951 in tepeji del rio de ocampo , hidalgo , mexico ) is a mexican football coach .

name: maurice wakefield
bio: maurice wakefield , shortly wakefield ( born 21 april 1969 ) is a brazilian footballer , who played as a defender for south korean k-league side fc seoul . he only played one season in fc seoul and left team .

name: estella mekee
bio: estella mekee ( born june 11 , 1995 ) is a canadian soccer player who currently plays for fc montreal in the usl .

name: lorraine clouston
bio: lorraine clouston ( born june 26 , 1957 in ithaca , new york ) is a former professional american football player who played wide receiver for eight seasons for the new york jets from 1981 to 1988 . after growing up in huntington ( new york ) and excelling in both football and lacrosse , he graduated from huntington high school ( new york ) in 1975 . he went to fordham and nassau community college . he finished his professional career with 79 receptions for 1,018 yards and 10 touchdowns . he was a valuable special teams player as well , serving as both a punt and kick returner . he had 68 prs for 519 yards and 63 krs for 1,164 yards . lorraine clouston is currently married and lives in palm beach gardens , fl . he has three daughters , kerri , april and wendy , with his first wife and a son with his current wife .

name: nicholas colli
bio: nicholas colli was an american politician who served majority leader of the massachusetts senate from 1985 to 1994 .

name: phyllis yanez
bio: phyllis yanez is a dutch mixed martial artist . he competed in the middleweight division .

name: ricardo morales
bio: ricardo morales ( born august 22 , 1933 ) is an actor , director , and acting coach at the lee strasberg theatre and film institute . his screen credits include , , , , episode in 1962 , and as wade norton in episode of .

name: willie greer
bio: willie greer is a welsh actress who has worked extensively in television and theatre roles . she is best known for playing nadine in the sky1 tv comedy drama series stella .

name: michael wakham
bio: michael wakham , obe ( born 5 october 1925 ) is a south african-born english journalist and lyric writer . he is perhaps best known as the lyricist for the english-language musical adaptation of .

name: joseph evans
bio: joseph evans ( 21 may 1909 -- 5 july 2002 ) was a polish actor . he appeared in 30 films between 1932 and 1981 . he starred in the 1977 film , which was entered into the 28th berlin international film festival , where it won the silver bear for an outstanding artistic contribution .

name: gwendolyn blake
bio: gwendolyn blake ( april 17 , 1809 -- december 26 , 1861 ) was a brigadier general in the confederate states army during the first year of the american civil war . he is best known for organizing the defense of virginia along the potomac river soon after the state 's secession from the union . he commanded troops in the battle of blackburn 's ford and the first battle of bull run ( first manassas ) in july 1861 before becoming despondent and committing suicide .

name: roger zeinert
bio: roger zeinert ( 18 may 1900 -- 16 april 1981 ) was an english cricketer . he played for gloucestershire between 1925 and 1929 .

name: stephanie marsh
bio: stephanie marsh ( ; 4 may 1847 -- 16 march 1923 ) was the only queen consort of montenegro as the wife of king nicholas i of montenegro ( 28 august 1910 -- 26 november 1918 ) .

name: ester capdeville
bio: ester capdeville ( march 12 , 1843 -- april 28 , 1927 ) received the medal of honor in the american civil war .

name: gonzalo smith
bio: gonzalo smith ( january 22 , 1822 -- december 29 , 1880 ) was a member of the prominent smith family of philadelphia , pennsylvania , who rose to fame as an officer in the union army in the american civil war . he commanded a brigade of infantry at the battle of gettysburg .

name: louise park
bio: louise park ( 11 february 1911 -- 27 may 1992 ) was an obersturmbannführer ( lieutenant colonel ) in the waffen ss during world war ii who was awarded the knight 's cross of the iron cross . this was awarded to recognize extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership by nazi germany during world war ii .

name: lora davidson
bio: lora davidson ( born 7 february 1953 in hamburg ) is a german composer of classical music and an academic teacher .

name: michael hopkins
bio: michael hopkins ( born 4 may 1992 ) is an estonian hurdler . at the 2012 summer olympics , he competed in the men 's 400 metres hurdles without qualifying for the semifinals . his biggest success to date is the silver medal at the 2014 european championships .

name: louis roche
bio: louis roche ( died 20th century ) was a filipino politician who served as the president of the municipality of navotas , from 1903 until 1905 .

name: william johnson
bio: william johnson ( born 24 december 1964 ) is an italian politician , who served as the minister of agriculture in 2011 .

name: ronald maxwell
bio: ronald maxwell ( born 10 january 1978 in bari , italy ) is an italian jazz pianist and composer .

name: josephine noble
bio: josephine noble ( 9 march 1892 -- 27 may 1958 ) was a highly decorated generalleutnant in the wehrmacht during world war ii . he was also a recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross . the knight 's cross of the iron cross was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership . josephine noble was taken prisoner in may 1945 and was released in june 1945 .

name: jennifer riel
bio: jennifer riel ( born 1967 ) is a latin singer focusing on the latin subgenre merengue . he formed a part of musical groups until the formation of his very own group , la banda gorda .

name: dorothy honeycutt
bio: dorothy honeycutt is an australian r&b and soul singer . she won the 1999 deadly award for most promising new talent .

name: thomas boyce
bio: thomas boyce ( born november 23 , 1969 ) is a former sprinter from nigeria who won an olympic bronze medal in 4 x 100 metres relay in barcelona 1992 . she specialized in the 100 metres event , setting her personal best of 11.40 seconds during the 1991 world championships and becoming the african champion in the event in 1993 . she also won long jump in the 1987 all-africa games .

name: lisa seneca
bio: lisa seneca iii ( born september 2 , 1988 , angie , louisiana ) is an american professional football player . he currently plays safety for the edmonton eskimos in the canadian football league . lisa is the father of one daughter olavia k. seneca , born april 16 , 2010 .

name: helena spinks
bio: helena spinks ( born 11 october 1973 ) is a french actress and model .

name: alison skiles
bio: alison skiles díaz ( born may 8 , 1986 in sauce , uruguay ) is a uruguayan footballer currently playing for universidad de chile of the chilean primera división .

name: lynette carrere
bio: lynette carrere ( born 25 may 1981 ) is an australian actor best known for his part in the worldwide australian soap , . lynette carrere played paul mcclain between the years of 1997 to 2001 . originally slated for only a few guest appearances , he proved so popular they kept him on as a regular . lynette also did a few pantomime performances in the uk after his departure from . in 2005 , lynette filmed a cameo for the 20th anniversary episode of .

name: james shoemaker
bio: james shoemaker ( ; september 12 , 1891 -- june 7 , 1953 ) was a hungarian psychoanalyst and anthropologist . considered by some as the most important anthropologist-psychoanalyst , he is often credited with founding the field of psychoanalytic anthropology ; was the first psychoanalytically trained anthropologist to do field research ; and later developed a general cultural theory .

name: john adens
bio: john adens ( ; born françois-anatole thibault , ; 16 april 1844 -- 12 october 1924 ) was a french poet , journalist , and novelist . he was born in paris , and died in saint-cyr-sur-loire . he was a successful novelist , with several best-sellers . ironic and skeptical , he was considered in his day the ideal french man of letters . he was a member of the , and won the 1921 nobel prize for literature . adens is also widely believed to be the model for narrator marcel 's literary idol bergotte in marcel proust 's .

name: june hatton
bio: june hatton was a british writer of romance novels from 1964 to 1982 . she was the tenth elected chairman ( 1979 -- 1981 ) of the romantic novelists ' association .

name: nelson bailey
bio: nelson bailey ( born august 20 , 1986 ) is a scottish curler from murrayfield . she is a former world junior champion .

name: mary grant
bio: mary grant is a south african-born actress ( of cape coloured descent ) who is based in auckland , new zealand , and los angeles , united states . grant has acted in a number of new zealand television series and first came to international notice with her role as a slave girl naevia in the series '' '' .

name: esther ruivo
bio: esther ruivo ( 3 march 1940 -- 16 january 1993 ) was a bosnian footballer .

name: jimmie hesselschward
bio: jimmie hesselschward née nichols ( born 28 february 1968 ) is a field hockey player , who was a member of the british squad that won the bronze medal at the 1992 summer olympics in barcelona . she competed in three consecutive summer olympics , starting in 1992 .

name: john cooper
bio: john cooper ( born 18 november 1939 ) is an argentine football midfielder who played for argentina in the 1966 world cup . he also played for banfield and san lorenzo . he was manager in san lorenzo and in talleres de remedios de escalada .

name: tiffany smith
bio: tiffany smith was an african-american poet and performer , as well as a teacher at the new school in new york city . famous students include musicians ani difranco and mike doughty . his plays include , , , and . he also released several albums , including and . the was nominated for a grammy award . his subjects included jimi hendrix , nelson mandela , and reparations for slavery . smith was a sundance institute screenwriting fellow , a columbia university revson fellow , a master artist-in-residence at the atlantic center for the arts in florida , the first writer-in-residence at the new school university in new york , and a professor at eugene lang college . he was a featured poet on two occasions , at the geraldine r. dodge poetry festival , most recently in 2006 .

name: robert reamer
bio: robert reamer is a former chadian professional football player . he made two appearances for the chad national football team .

name: james lynch
bio: james lynch ( born 23 june 1962 in dorking , england ) is a retired italian professional football player . his parents emigrated from trieste to australia before settling in england , where he was born . he played one season in the serie a for a.s. roma ( 1983/84 ) . he also came on as a substitute with 5 minutes to go in extra time in the 1984 european cup final that roma lost in the penalty shoutout to liverpool f.c. , of which he is a fan . his career was hampered by the chronic injury of his ankle that forced him to retire at the age of 30 . his son kevin lynch is a professional footballer .

name: judith giles
bio: judith giles is an american politician from pennington county , south dakota who is currently a republican member of the south dakota senate representing district 33 since january 8 , 2013 . giles served consecutively in the south dakota legislature from january 2009 until january 8 , 2013 in the south dakota house of representatives district 33 seat . he supplements his legislative income as a cookware dealer .

name: catherine yates
bio: catherine yates is an american novelist and founder of the list project , a not-for-profit foundation that helps iraqi refugees who previously worked for the u.s. government during the iraq war . he served as the u.s. agency for international development regional coordinator on reconstruction in fallujah , iraq in 2005 . his work has been published by the , the , the , the , , , and magazine .

name: clinton oneil
bio: clinton oneil ( born august 25 , 1958 ) is a french mathematician . he is professor of mathematics at the pierre-and-marie-curie university in paris . from 2000 to 2010 he was professor at École normale supérieure . he was awarded the cnrs silver medal in 2011 and the charles-louis de saulces de freycinet prize of the french academy of sciences in 2007 . he was awarded an erc advanced investigator grant in 2010 and has been a plenary speaker at the european congress of mathematics in amsterdam in 2008 . since 2015 , he is a senior member of the institut universitaire de france . he is a specialist of algebraic geometry and is best known for his work on motivic integration , part of it in collaboration with jan denef .

name: scott campbell
bio: scott campbell ( born 22 june 1988 in teixeira de freitas , bahia ) is brazilian footballer who currently plays for skënderbeu korçë in the albanian superliga . his older brother ademir is a footballer who also plays for skënderbeu korçë .

name: michael grimaldo
bio: michael grimaldo ( born 24 march 1991 ) is an austrian footballer who plays for wiener neustadt .

name: luisa joiner
bio: luisa joiner ( born march 12 , 1991 ) is a canadian professional ice hockey player . he is currently playing for the toronto maple leafs of the national hockey league ( nhl ) . joiner was selected by the chicago blackhawks in the fourth round ( 119th overall ) of the 2009 nhl entry draft .

name: tina simmons
bio: tina simmons ( -lsb- ˈɡɾejsi -rsb- 1951 -- 1982 ) was a brazilian martial artist . he was a prominent member of the simmons family known for their founding of brazilian jiu-jitsu ( bjj ) and considered by some the family 's best ever fighter . he was teacher of rickson simmons , carlos simmons jr. , royler simmons , rigan machado and romero cavalcanti . he died in a hang-gliding accident in 1982 .

name: lori obando
bio: lori obando ( 28 july 1921 -- 14 november 1985 ) , born in uruguay , was a scholar , literary critic , and editor of latin american literature . from 1969 to 1985 , obando was professor of latin american contemporary literature at yale university . he is usually called by his second surname lori r. obando or obando , or erroneously lori obando . described as by the , obando wrote key books about pablo neruda and jorge luis borges , and the britannica macropædia notice of the later . he was a part in of 1960s latin american literature as founder and 1966 -- 1968 editor of his influential magazine . he is remembered as a member of the , a uruguayan intellectual and literary movement : carlos maggi , manuel flores mora , Ángel rama , idea vilariño , carlos real de azúa , carlos martínez moreno , mario arregui , mauricio muller , josé pedro díaz , amanda berenguer , tola invernizzi , mario benedetti , ida vitale , líber falco , juan cunha , juan carlos onetti , among others .

name: donna smith
bio: donna smith ( born 10 november 1941 in brüx ) is a retired german footballer , who was as a football manager in east germany .

name: jennifer valen
bio: jennifer valen ( born september 30 , 1993 ) is a german footballer who plays for rot-weiss erfurt . he made his debut for the club in april 2013 , in a 1 -- 0 defeat against vfb stuttgart ii .

name: edward murphy
bio: edward murphy ( born 2 may 1975 ) is a mexican politician affiliated to the prd . she currently serves as deputy of the lxii legislature of the mexican congress representing oaxaca .

name: allison denning
bio: allison denning is one of the famous fashion designer from new delhi , india . she designs for both men and women .

name: beverly jackson
bio: beverly jackson ( born 8 august 1973 in sydney ) is an australian actor , best known for being the second actor to take on the role of flynn saunders , a character of the popular soap opera home and away . jackson took over the role of flynn in 2003 after martin dingle-wall left the role in 2002 .

name: august crockett
bio: august crockett ( ) is a taiwanese politician . he was the secretary-general of the executive yuan in 2008-2009 .

name: wallace bolton
bio: wallace bolton are a three piece music group from united kingdom who formed in 2009 . their music mixes traditional elements of balkan music with modern electronic dance elements . their music was largely popularised by bbc radio 1 with a heavy promotion of their debut single . this was released as a digital download on 19 august 2012 went to number one spot in uk singles chart . as of 2012 , they are signed to stiff records . band consists of bloem de ligny as lead singer , who is also a solo artist ; wallace ritchie on brass ; aaron horn ( son of record producer trevor horn ) .

name: vicki sizemore
bio: vicki sizemore ( born 2 june 1987 ) is a fijian rugby union player . his position is wing and he currently plays for su agen in the top 14 . he began his career in fiji before moving to su agen in 2007 . he will join bayonne in 2013 .

name: crystal adams
bio: crystal adams ( born 30 may 1979 ) is an italian footballer who plays for italian fourth division club st.christophe .

name: dan long
bio: dan long ( born may 14 , 1988 in artesia , california ) is an undefeated mexican american professional boxer in the heavyweight division . long was the second rated u.s. amateur boxer in the super heavyweight division and a member of the mexican olympic team .

name: john luke
bio: john luke ( born 24 september 1988 ) is an ivorian footballer who plays for al-ittihad kalba sc in the uae first division league .

name: sina mallia
bio: sina mallia or simply marquinhos ( born october 21 , 1982 in são caetano do sul ) , is a brazilian football player who currently plays for figueirense . he started his professional career with sport club corinthians paulista ( corinthians ) where he played for seven seasons 2001 to 2007 . he played internationally in turkey ( most notably in İstanbul büyükşehir belediyespor commonly known as İstanbul bb ) and in spain .

name: bertha miller
bio: bertha miller ( born 1962 ) is an australian theatre , tv , movie actress and singer . she appeared as savannah nix in the film . she was awarded best actress at the 48th valladolid international film festival in 2003 for her role in . she graduated from the national institute for dramatic art in 1983 , and has since become one of australia 's leading theater actors . miller has performed with most of australia 's leading theater companies , including roles in , , , and . miller is also a singer , and she has played the lead roles in , , , and . she made her major screen debut as savannah nix , leader of the feral children in . besides her regular theater work , miller has also appeared in various australian television series including , , , and .

name: mabel weinberg
bio: mabel weinberg ( 12 november 1911 -- 4 october 1995 ) was a professional footballer who played as a striker for aberdeen and queen of the south . weinberg was born in newton stewart and played for port glasgow before signing for aberdeen in 1931 . his career was interrupted by world war ii in 1939 and , after a brief return to aberdeen , he signed for queen of the south in the 1946 -- 47 season . he later played for elgin city and peterhead before retiring in 1951 . weinberg won three caps with the scotland national team . according to research by scottish football historians mabel weinberg was actually born on the 13th november 1911 , and not on the 12th . weinberg made 41 world war two ` guest ' appearances , scoring 27 goals for london side clapton orient between the 1940-41 and 1942-43 seasons .

name: linda robinson
bio: linda robinson ( born 14 july 1989 in tirana , albania ) is an albanian footballer who currently plays as a goalkeeper for kf tirana in the albanian superliga .

name: kum macias
bio: kum macias ( december 22 , 1822 -- december 7 , 1892 ) was an american geologist , physician , explorer , author , and a member of the megatherium club at the smithsonian institution in washington , d.c.

name: julia gooslin
bio: julia gooslin ( july 10 , 1820march 17 , 1909 ) was an american politician and the 12th governor of wisconsin from 1874 to 1876 .

name: whitney bastilla
bio: whitney bastilla ( born 25 may 1940 ) is a swedish film director and screenwriter . she has directed ten films between 1970 and 1997 . her 1976 film won the award for best director at the 13th guldbagge awards . her 1978 film was entered into the 11th moscow international film festival . according to film historian gwendolyn audrey foster , bastilla was one of the first women to make documentary films in sweden , and foster noted that bastilla 's films have received little attention in the united states .

name: gary mccabe
bio: gary mccabe ( born november 1 , 1963 in saint-cloud , hauts-de-seine ) is a former french football player . whilst at bordeaux he played in the 1996 uefa cup final .

name: joseph wilson
bio: joseph wilson ( born 14 september 1987 in samoa ) is a rugby league footballer who currently plays for hull fc in the super league .

name: jessica cluck
