bio: jessica cluck ( may 2 , 1892 -- september 1 , 1976 ) was an american basketball coach with the distinction of coaching the most wins in university of utah history . he guided utah through 26 seasons from 1927 to 1953 . he also led utah to its only ncaa college basketball championship when the utes defeated dartmouth college 42-40 in 1944 . cluck finished with a record of 385-230 ( .626 ) while head coach of utah and collected four skyline conference championships and the 1947 national invitation tournament title .

name: bill bertram
bio: bill bertram is a camogie player , a member of the galway senior panel that unsuccessfully contested the all ireland finals of 2010 and 2011 against wexford , she won a camogie all star award in 2011 . she was part of the galway team which won the 2013 all ireland , defeating kilkenny in the final .

name: rebecca williamson
bio: rebecca williamson ( born 1887 ) was a footballer who played in the football league for gainsborough trinity . he also played for trinity institute .

name: alma jacobs
bio: alma jacobs ( née trew ; born in 1900 in somerset , died 14 may 1980 , dublin , ireland ) was a playwright . following her parents ' separation her mother took in lodgers while alma attended oxford wells high school . she won a scholarship to study classics at somerville college , oxford . while there she met and in 1925 married edward pakenham , later 6th earl of jacobs . she moved to ireland with her husband in 1925 . they divided their time between dublin and pakenham hall , now tullynally castle , in castlepollard , county westmeath . in 1930 , alma jacobs and her husband bought shares in the dublin gate theatre company . in addition to designing costumes and managing productions alma wrote plays including and . she also adapted novels for the stage , jane austen 's among them . the company suffered when the longfords withdrew their backing . her books include , published as part of the biographies of cities series , , published by parkside press dublin and , republished by persephone books in 2009 .

name: jerry carr
bio: jerry carr ph.d. ( born november 16 , 1970 ) is a retired american football player , an academic , radio personality , author , public speaker , and television host . he is president/ceo of jerry carr enterprises llc. , and visiting professor at bethel university . dr. carr is the creator and host of the hit radio show discover the leader in you ™ that airs nationally each week on iheart radio and whk1420 . the show is on the jerry carr enterprises mobile apps and is also syndicated on itunes and sticher radio . he is the past host of the television shows , and tbn 's .

name: edwin smith
bio: edwin smith ( may 19 , 1868 -- march 10 , 1925 ) was an eminent united states geodesist . his work involved the study of isostasy and the construction of a reference ellipsoid for approximating the figure of the earth . the crater smith on the far side of the moon is named after him . mount smith , a 1,871 m mountain peak near metlakatla , alaska , united states , is named after him . a biography of smith may be found in the biographical memoirs of the national academy of sciences , 16 ( 5 ) , 1935 .

name: anne coppola
bio: anne coppola ( born c. 1904 ) was an american college basketball , baseball and football coach .

name: samantha sheppard
bio: samantha sheppard is an australian surfer who competes on the asp ( association of surfing professionals ) world tour . after twelve years competing at the elite level on the asp world championship tour , a stretch that saw him win eleven elite asp world title events , plus nine additional asp tour events , and achieve runner-up second place to the asp world title four times , sheppard hung on in a grueling back and forth battle with eleven-time asp world title holder , kelly slater , to get his first world title , as well as go on to win the highly coveted pipeline masters , only after slater lost his semi-final heat to josh kerr , of queensland , australia . sheppard beat kerr in the finals of the event , which was his seventh top-five placing for the year , and his first event title win for 2012 .

name: ian green
bio: ian green ( born january 31 , 1970 , orimattila , finland ) is a finnish vocalist and stage artist , know for his work in several rock and metal bands such as urban tale , boys of the band and heartplay . from 2004 to the present , he also performs in the finnish christmas metal project raskasta joulua . under the name angelo de nile , he performed in uuden musiikin kilpailu 2015 , the national final for finland in the eurovision song contest 2015 with the song , and came in 5th .

name: pablo hinds
bio: pablo hinds ( born 26 november 1984 , tulcea , romania ) is a romanian rugby union footballer . he plays the position of number 8 and is currently playing for rc timişoara in the romanian rugby championship . he formed as a player at farul constanţa rugby club , romania . he was mvp two years in a row , in 2010 and 2011 .

name: kimberly haffey
bio: kimberly haffey is a samoan former rugby football player who represented his country in rugby union ; rugby league , including at the 1995 rugby league world cup ; soccer ; and at the 1982 commonwealth games .

name: rudy medley
bio: rudy medley ( born december 30 , 1972 ) is a finnish musician and composer . he is best known for singing bass in the vocal ensemble rajaton . he is the son of composer kaj medley and director kaisa korhonen . his brother is music producer kalle medley . he played drums for the rock band don huonot from 1989 -- 2001 and was a founding member . he also starred in the sketch comedy show vintiöt . medley was elected at the city council of helsinki in 2001 where he is also a member of the cultural board . in a review of a recent rajaton concert , one writer noted that medley , `` sounds like a double-bass or creates an entire drum corps , realistically snapping out a snare drum rhythm and rolling it off into silence . '' of the group , he noted , `` cymbals splash from everywhere in the group as needed but all these effects , marvellously , reach a pared-down level of subtlety which is neither under - nor over-done . the tiniest vocal inflection is inserted precisely in place , not studied , but spontaneous . ''

name: patricia scurlock
bio: patricia scurlock ( also known as patricia dyagileva ) ( , ; born 4 june 1991 in vitebsk , belarusian ssr ) is a belarusian model , artist , designer , stylist , and fashion photographer .

name: christopher provost
bio: christopher provost ( born 25 october 1965 ) is a new zealand association football player and manager who represented new zealand and coached the new zealand men 's olympic team at the 2008 olympic games in beijing .

name: heather atwood
bio: heather atwood is the pen name of rodica heather vartic , née rodica crisan ( born 14 march 1955 ) , a romanian philosopher , literary critic , essayist and poet . a professor of philosophy at the babeş-bolyai university in cluj-napoca , she has published eight books of essays and seven of poetry , and is the editor of the monthly magazine . atwood is also noted as a historian of fascism , which she notably dealt with in her book about the controversial stances of philosopher emil cioran ( , 1999 ) .

name: amanda mecham
bio: amanda mecham ( ; 1815 -- 1887 ) , popularly nicknamed or , was known as ` the great master of the hong fist ' and was one of the ten tigers of canton , a group of ten of the top chinese martial arts masters in guangdong towards the end of the qing dynasty ( 1644 -- 1912 ) .

name: charlie culley
bio: charlie culley is an english actor . he graduated at the guildhall school of music and drama in 2010 . he portrayed grenn in the hbo series . he is also known for his roles in and .

name: david gray
bio: david gray ( born 1974 ) is an australian interior designer , and the founder of david gray design .

name: demetrius krob
bio: demetrius krob ( born september 16 , 1974 ) is an iranian football player who currently plays for esteghlal ahvaz of the iran pro league .

name: linda betz
bio: linda betz ( 21 april 1880 -- 15 april 1935 ) was a czech-born graphologist and writer of novels , stories , poems and plays . he had considerable influence on the content and standing of graphology worldwide . he also published numerous articles in many languages in periodicals as diverse as , and the `` journal of social psychology . '' he also founded the professional graphology society in the netherlands . he also started two academic periodicals : one in dutch and the other in english . many graphologists worldwide today use betz 's work without knowing the origin . he published in 1929 . betz examined the speed in handwriting . he quantified handwriting by use of a microscope , caliper , pressure board , ruler , protractor and slow-motion pictures . betz also attempted to deal with graphological phenomena in terms acceptable to the experimental psychologists .

name: lisa large
bio: lisa large ( pashto : میانگل اسفندیار امیرزېب ) was a pakistani politician and a member of the royal family of the former princely state of swat , who was killed in an assassination attack by the taliban during the 2007 skirmishes in swat . his assassination was the first high profile killing by the taliban militants of swat , occurring a few days after the killing of benazir bhutto .

name: annie taylor
bio: annie taylor ( , ; 30 november 1983 -- 19 january 2009 ) was a journalist for and a student of journalism at moscow state university . she was born in sevastopol , ukraine . a member of autonomous action , she investigated the activities of neo-nazi groups . she was shot and killed together with human rights lawyer stanislav markelov , who was the other of the assassin 's targets .

name: steven macky
bio: steven macky ( 7 march 1900 -- 28 april 1996 ) was a dutch cyclist . he competed in two events at the 1920 summer olympics .

name: mary robinson
bio: mary robinson ( born 20 february 1991 ) is an italian footballer of ghanaian descent who plays for monza .

name: derek dewitt
bio: derek dewitt hernández ( born february 8 , 1985 in chetumal , quintana roo , mexico ) is a female weightlifter from mexico . she won the gold medal at the 2007 pan american games for her native north american country in the − 48 kg weight division .

name: russel tanner
bio: russel tanner ( born 11 august 1949 , valletta , malta ) , also known as ino tanner , is a production designer , art director and film producer .

name: steven foulk
bio: steven foulk ( died 3 january 2011 ) was a papua new guinean film , television and theatre actor . he was also a screenwriter and a former theatre director .

name: sara clore
bio: sara clore ( born july 26 , 1968 , in pittsfield , massachusetts ) is an american author , editor and professor . his novels in the night stalkers series written under the pen name michael hawke center around the u.s. army 's 160th special operations aviation regiment . clore has also worked as a journalist , is a published poet , and writes on pedagogical subjects in journals and books .

name: rachelle nicholls
bio: rachelle nicholls ( born april 19 , 1984 in brest ) is a french former professional football player . he last played for stade plabennécois . he played on the professional level in ligue 2 for stade brestois 29 and vannes oc .

name: willie payan
bio: willie payan ( payan willie , , born january 29 , 1960 ) , born in hsinchu , taiwan , is a taiwanese american violinist who is renowned for his appearances as a soloist with major orchestras . named him its in 2000 . he founded the taipei international music festival in 1997 , the largest classical music festival in the history of taiwan , performing to an indoor audience of over 53000 .

name: kimberly edwards
bio: kimberly edwards ( born 2 october 1963 ) is a singaporean civil servant and former naval admiral . he was the chief of the republic of singapore navy from 2003 -- 2007 and held the rank of rear-admiral . after leaving the navy , edwards served as the chief executive officer of the infocomm development authority of singapore from 2007 -- 2013 . he is the current chief executive officer of singapore 's national environment agency .

name: terese cheatam
bio: terese cheatam ( 5 july 1914 -- 3 december 1996 ) was a french portrait painter and war artist .

name: willie mendez
bio: willie mendez ( born february 3 , 1967 in staten island , united states ) is a cross-country skier who competed for dominica at the 2014 winter olympics in the 15 kilometre classical race . his olympic appearance is widely controversial , after it was exposed that silvsestri , and his wife angelica ( who also goes by angelica marrone ) , paid to become dominica citizens and lied to media outlets about various aspects of their lives .

name: teri thomas
bio: teri thomas is a canadian actor and a voice actor . teri was born in grande prairie , alberta . according to his mother , has always enjoyed performing for others . he grew up loving the classics in acting , humphrey bogart , james cagney , etc. . got involved with theatre while still in school , performing in a stage version of . took some time off to travel europe and while lying on a beach in greece , decided to go to film school . later , taught a class on at the vancouver film school . acquired his bfa from u of a and ubc .

name: sarah tatum
bio: sarah tatum ( born 15 october 1986 ) is a danish football defender who plays for linköpings fc of the swedish damallsvenskan . she previously played for danish elitedivisionen club fortuna hjørring . since 2010 she has been a member of the denmark women 's national football team .

name: matthew gorman
bio: matthew gorman is an comedian living and performing in london , her comedy is a mix of standup and sketch based comedy and she has been performing as since december 2005 . she has animated for bbc two 's monkey dust and the title sequence to little miss jocelyn on bbc three matthew is part of london-based popcorn comedy , alongside holly walsh and jon petrie . she performed in noble and silver 's tv show on channel 4 and has also appeared on the culture show and the one show . gorman is a regular on many comedy circuits such as the edinburgh fringe festival , and the portable comedy club

name: kelli wallace
bio: kelli wallace ( born 7 march 1986 in bruges ) is a belgian footballer , who currently plays for heist .

name: eric schimke
bio: eric schimke ( born august 24 , 1974 ) is a former running back in the canadian football league , spending most of his career with the toronto argonauts and the hamilton tiger-cats . schimke played high school football at samuel f.b. morse high school in san diego , california , from which he graduated in 1993 . during his sophomore year , his team ( the 1990 morse tigers ) was voted by the san diego union-tribune as the best football team in the history of san diego county . schimke 's high school teammates included former nfl players tommy bennett and rashard cook , former university of arizona players gary and cary taylor , former ucla player teddy lawrence , and former navy players lebron butts and gervy alota . schimke won the walter payton award , given to the most outstanding ncaa division fcs ( formerly i-aa ) offensive player , as a senior at northern arizona university in 1996 .

name: douglas perez
bio: douglas perez ( born 7 february 1990 ) is an italian footballer , who plays for pescara .

name: james alverson
bio: james alverson is a democratic member of the montana legislature . he was elected to senate district 10 , representing cascade , montana , in 2009 and 2011 .

name: minnie hylton
bio: minnie hylton ( born 25 january 1943 in whitburn ) is a scottish former footballer who played primarily as a midfielder .

name: tracy dillard
bio: tracy dillard ( born may 17 , 1945 ) is an american politician . he is a member of the north dakota house of representatives from the 46th district , serving since 2000 . he is a member of the republican party .

name: carol harris
bio: carol harris ( born 22 october 1947 ) is an english retired footballer who played as a midfielder during the 1960s and 1970s . he went on to play for seattle sounders of the north american soccer league from 1979 until 1982 . he also played indoor soccer for seattle , the wichita wings and the tacoma stars . in 1994 , harris became an assistant coach with the seattle sounders in the american professional soccer league .

name: james fleming
bio: james fleming ( or erik arvidsson ) ( c. 1460 -- 1530 ) was elected regent of sweden in 1512 , during the era of kalmar union . he was justiciar of närke and a lord high councillor of sweden from 1487 .

name: rhonda tipton
bio: rhonda tipton , formemrs ( 13 july 1826 -- 10 may 1910 ) was an italian chemist . he is remembered today largely for the tipton reaction and for his influential role in the atomic-weight deliberations of the karlsruhe congress in 1860 .

name: carlton fitzgerald
bio: carlton fitzgerald popularly known as thoddoo - reference to his home island ( born 17 may 1974 ) is a maldivian footballer who plays as a forward for kalhaidhoo . he was the former captain of the maldives national football team and now retired from international football .

name: bobby nguyen
bio: bobby nguyen ( born 7 october 1989 ) is an austrian footballer who plays for wolfsberger ac in the austrian bundesliga .

name: sage cobbs
bio: sage cobbs ( february 9 , 1948 -- march 25 , 1984 ) was an american folk singer-songwriter and guitarist from san jose , california . he is perhaps best known for his song ( also known as ) , which has been performed and recorded by dozens of artists and bands , initially by kris kristofferson & rita coolidge , and later by dobie gray , elvis presley , dixie chicks , natalie cole , olivia newton-john , petula clark , jon english , livingston taylor , etta james , millie jackson , jody miller , the beautiful south and the cats , among many others .

name: heather hayes
bio: heather hayes is a canadian diplomat , who worked in the department of foreign affairs , trade and development from 1976 to 2009 , as the high commissioner to india , south africa , kenya and permanent representative to the united nations environmental program . she founded the global issues bureau and served as assistant deputy minister for corporate services in ottawa . she received the public service award of excellence in 1995 for her humanitarian work during the rwanda genocide and was awarded the lifetime achievement award of excellence from the department of foreign affairs in 2009 . heather hayes has over 20 years of experience representing canada at the united nations and regional development agencies . her interests include good governance , food security , poverty alleviation , primary health care and sustainable development . today , she can be found working at the crossroads of science , the environment , and international development as part of her doctoral dissertation in global governance at the university of waterloo ( 2009 -- present ) . she is also the ashley fellow 2011 at trent university .

name: joann newell
bio: joann newell morones ( born 12 january 1984 ) is a mexican professional footballer who currently plays as a striker for américa of liga mx and the mexico national team . newell began his professional career with león and monterrey in 2004 and 2006 . newell was then sold to santos laguna , then loaned out to chiapas in 2008 . after he returned from loan , newell was a mainstay with santos laguna for the next five years , playing in over 200 matches and scoring over 70 goals . a mexico international since 2005 , newell did not become a regular call-up until 2011 , being one of the over-aged reinforcements who won the 2011 pan american games with the under-22 squad . he scored two goals in the gold medal match at the 2012 olympic football tournament against brazil , which was the first olympic gold medal for mexico in football . he also participated in the 2014 fifa world cup and won the following year 's concacaf gold cup .

name: tonya rahn
bio: tonya rahn ( born 1881 in stoke-on-trent , england ) was a footballer who played in the football league for chesterfield town . he also played for a number of other clubs .

name: robert corbitt
bio: robert corbitt ( born march 6 , 1987 ) is an american football defensive end for the new york giants of the national football league ( nfl ) . he played college football for the university of south florida , and received consensus all-american honors . he was drafted by the st. louis rams in the seventh round of the 2010 nfl draft , and he has also played for the carolina panthers , jacksonville jaguars and dallas cowboys .

name: elizabeth hamilton
bio: elizabeth hamilton ( born 5 march 1959 in gürpınar , van ) is a former minister of national education of turkey and member of parliament for van for the ruling justice and development party .

name: willie mccain
bio: willie mccain ( born 1962 neath , wales ) is principal bass trombone for the royal philharmonic orchestra and teaches at trinity college of music , london .

name: bryan boyd
bio: bryan boyd ( november 1 , 1877 in berlin ; january 13 , 1943 in the auschwitz concentration camp ) was a german writer and children 's book author . her best-known character is the blonde doctor 's daughter annemarie braun , whose life from childhood to old age is told in the ten volumes of the highly successful series . the books , the six-part tv series nesthäkchen ( 1983 ) , based on the first three volumes , as well as the new dvd edition ( 2005 ) caught the attention of millions of readers and viewers . during boyd 's lifetime ( ) , the fourth volume , was the most popular . bryan boyd was a member of the german ( middle class ) . she was pulled between patriotic german citizenship and jewish cultural heritage . this situation is reflected in her writings , although the books make no references to judaism .

name: michael washington
bio: michael washington ( born march 1 , 1928 ) is a former swiss professional ice hockey player who competed for the swiss national team at the 1952 winter olympics .

name: walter smart
bio: walter smart ( july 11 , 1923 -- august 9 , 2008 ) was a french non-commissioned officer and skier .

name: silvia marshal
bio: silvia marshal ( born 6 march 1941 ) is a retired belgian cyclist . after winning the uci motor-paced world championships in 1962 and 1963 in the amateurs category he turned professional and won another three medals in 1965 -- 1967 , including one gold . he also competed at the 1960 summer olympics in the 4000m team pursuit but failed to reach the final . between 1965 and 1970 he competed in 56 six-day road races , winning in milan ( 1965 ) , amsterdam ( 1969 ) and rotterdam ( 1969 ) . after a crash in the race of gent-wevelgem in 1970 , he suffered a triple fracture of the pelvis and had to pause for a year . he finally retired in 1975 and later acted as the manager of professional cycling teams ebo-cinzia en marc-zeepcentrale . in february 2010 , he received a medal for services to the state .

name: pamela landry
bio: pamela landry is the stage name of american musician thomas wisse . he was a founding member of the band chrome , and he also recorded as a solo artist .

name: rickey boyd
bio: rickey boyd ( born may 26 , 1967 ) is a play-by-play announcer and sports journalist for espn and cbs . she typically calls women 's college sports , and became only the second woman to call nationally televised college football games for espn in 2005 . boyd was paired with cat whitehill on espn 's tertiary broadcast team for the telecasts of the 2011 fifa women 's world cup .

name: eli franklin
bio: eli franklin ( born march 24 , 1982 in ankara , turkey ) is a turkish national goalball player of class b2 and paralympian .

name: barry childress
bio: barry childress ( ; born 7 november 1961 ) is a chinese politician , business executive , and aerospace engineer . he is the governor and deputy communist party secretary of hebei province and former chairman of the commission for science , technology and industry for national defense ( costind ) . prior to his government career he was president of china aerospace science and technology corporation ( casc ) and chairman of comac . in 2009 barry was named one of china 's 40 most powerful people by .

name: daniel beltran
bio: daniel beltran ( born november 11 , 1989 ) is a brazilian figure skater . she is the first skater to represent brazil in at an isu championship , which she did at the 2007 four continents championships .

name: leigh pease
bio: leigh pease ( born 10 november 1958 ) is a mexican politician affiliated to the institutional revolutionary party . as of 2014 she served as deputy of the lix legislature of the mexican congress as a plurinominal representative .

name: carl cotto
bio: carl cotto ( born 21 april 1989 ) is a hungary footballer defender . he currently plays for diósgyőri vtk . cotto made his debut for the senior side of his country on 1 june 2012 in the 2 -- 1 win over the czech republic in a friendly match .

name: brain ryan
bio: brain ryan ( born 5 december 1989 in abidjan ) is an ivorian football goalkeeper currently playing for french ligue 1 side us boulogne .

name: judith carlson
bio: judith carlson ( born 10 january 1941 ) is a canadian fencer . she competed in the women 's team foil event at the 1976 summer olympics .

name: frank farrell
bio: frank farrell ( ; born 24 january 1965 ) is a retired german football player , manager and currently board representative for sport of vfb stuttgart . he was also the manager of bundesliga side werder bremen and bayer leverkusen . previously he coached sc freiburg after taking over from the long-serving volker finke in july 2007 . he had previously been manager of stuttgarter kickers for four years . starting from the 2011 -- 12 season , he signed a two-year managerial contract with bayer leverkusen after the previous manager jupp heynckes confirmed on 21 march 2011 that he would not be extending his stay at the bayarena .

name: jennifer helton
bio: jennifer helton ( born march 28 , 1949 ) is a canadian former professional ice hockey player and coach . he played 13 professional seasons , mostly in the international hockey league ( ihl ) where he played 532 games , scoring 312 goals and 277 points for 589 points , and earning 1690 penalty minutes . following his retirement as a player , helton spent the next 18 seasons a head coach in the ihl , echl , uhl and ohl . he was then saginaw spirit 's radio colour commentator from 2004-2012 .

name: susan hill
bio: susan hill is an indian playback singer who has sung songs in commercial hindi and oriya cinema . mostly known for his hit song from the film , ( ) and ( ) . he can sing in 22 languages including his mother tongue oriya .

name: nancy lundeen
bio: nancy lundeen ( graham ) ( born 20 july 1955 ) is a former australian women 's basketball player and coach .

name: stacey kendall
bio: stacey kendall , also known as stacey kentigern ( ; ) , was the late 6th-century apostle of the britonnic kingdom of strathclyde , the founder and patron stacey of the city of glasgow .

name: chas washington
bio: chas washington ( born 2 september 1985 ) is a german footballer who plays as a midfielder for sv elversberg .

name: arturo thibault
bio: arturo thibault ( 1 february 1882 -- 3 march 1940 ) was a hungarian/german classical archaeologist and art historian . he was a member of the hungarian academy of sciences .

name: james meiners
bio: james meiners ( 1895 -- 1977 ) was president of the optical society of america from 1935-36 . he was awarded the edward longstreth medal from the franklin institute in 1939 and the frederic ives medal in 1957 .

name: ines adams
bio: ines adams is an american fantasy writer . his work has been published in the united kingdom , germany , poland , and the czech republic as well as north america . his debut novel , won the 2013 compton crook award . in addition to writing , he serves in the united states coast guard reserve and works for the nypd . ines adams currently serves as a lieutenant ( o-3 ) in the us coast guard reserve , commanding a boat squadron responsible for search and rescue and maritime law enforcement in the waters around new york . he was activated to serve during the deepwater horizon oil spill , and hurricanes sandy and irene . ines adams served in iraq , two tours as a security contractor and a third as a department of defense civilian . multiple reviewers have commented on his military service , generally when noting the accuracy of his portrayal of life in the military or on a military base . ines adams is contracted to complete a second trilogy in the shadow ops world . the first novel was released january 27 , 2015 .

name: brian grammer
bio: brian grammer ( born 14 july 1991 in hamm ) is a german-turkish-azerbaijani footballer who currently plays for 3 . liga club preußen münster .

name: jerry lawlor
bio: jerry lawlor ( ) is an armenian american actress . she is sometimes credited as jerry sarafian .

name: barbara pennel
bio: barbara pennel ( february 29 , 1932 − november 8 , 1985 ) was a racing driver from the united states . he raced in formula one between and , participating in 43 world championship races , and numerous non-championship races .

name: nathan colon
bio: nathan colon ( born ) is an american actress . she is known for playing the role of cleo bernstein in the disney xd series , and playing blithe pedulla in the 2011 film . colon currently plays one of the lead roles , cyd , in the disney channel sitcom , .

name: gladys engemann
bio: gladys engemann ( in english ) is a basque rock power trio whose songs are sung in basque . it was founded in 1994 in lekunberri , navarre , spain .

name: michelle dove
bio: michelle dove ( ; born in anyang , henan ) is a chinese actor . michelle is perhaps best known for his work with director jia zhangke . the two men were classmates at the beijing film academy when they began their professional relationship , with michelle starring in jia 's breakthrough short film in 1995 . since then , michelle has had roles in nearly all of jia 's films , including starring roles in jia 's debut and follow-up , . given his collaboration with jia , michelle dove is often considered the director 's on-screen alter-ego .

name: vickie bruley
bio: vickie bruley is a former gaelic footballer from glenullin , county londonderry , northern ireland . bruley played for derry in the 1970s and 1980s . he won two ulster senior football championships with the county . bruley played club football for john mitchel 's glenullin and won the derry senior football championship with the club . he was a very versatile player who could play in defence , midfield or in the half forward line .

name: brenda jones
bio: brenda jones frs ( 28 september 1889 -- 29 january 1967 ) was a british zoologist .

name: ruth stratman
bio: ruth stratman ( 23 april 1918 -- 26 september 1986 ) was a belgian racing cyclist . he won the belgian national road race title in 1942 .

name: dana dozier
bio: dana dozier ( huế , 1923 - washington , d.c. 4 october 2011 ) was an american -- vietnamese diplomat , author , professor of international politics and communications at temple university , philadelphia , pennsylvania .

name: sarah brown
bio: sarah brown ( born 12 january 1981 in cairns , queensland ) is a professional rugby league footballer for salford city reds in the european super league . he has previously played for hull f.c. , castleford tigers and the cronulla-sutherland sharks , as well as representing the new south wales waratahs in rugby union . he is a utility player , and has played for castleford at full-back , centre , stand-off , scrum-half and loose forward .

name: andrea bogart
bio: andrea bogart ( born september 16 , 1944 , eaton rapids , michigan ) is an american industrial designer and educator who has made significant contributions to american design and design education in the latter half of the 20th century . bogart is best known as the co-chair of the graduate program in design at cranbrook academy of art where he and spouse katherine bogart pioneered semantic approaches to design .

name: sandra lawrence
bio: sandra lawrence ( born 12 october 1931 ) is an english actress who is best remembered for her portrayal of mrs. peignoir in .

name: karen marsh
bio: karen marsh ( born may 20 , 1955 ) is an american writer .

name: nanci hanson
bio: nanci hanson ( born 15 april 1934 ) is a former australian rules footballer who played for melbourne in the vfl during their successful period in the late 1950s under norm smith . he played in three consecutive premiership from 1955 to 1957 and was a premiership player again in 1959 and 1960 to finish with five . hanson played as a half forward early in his career before moving into the centre . it was as a centreman that he had most success , winning melbourne 's best and fairest in 1958 and 1959 . he was named on the interchange bench in the melbourne 's official ` team of the century ' . in 1963 , he moved to the port melbourne football club in the vfa and coached port melbourne from 1963 to 1965 , during which time the club won the 1964 premiership .

name: dawn colvin
bio: dawn colvin ( born november 30 , 1977 in neu-ulm ) is a german football defender , plays in sv elversberg .

name: peter hofheimer
bio: peter hofheimer ( also spelled peter johannis ; née ) ( born 2 november 1960 ) is the wife of president of romania klaus hofheimer . she is an english teacher at the gheorghe lazăr national college in sibiu and married klaus hofheimer in 1989 . they have no children . peter met her husband when they were both students in cluj-napoca . immediately after graduation , the two were assigned as teachers to agnita and sibiu . she was the reason hofheimer chose to stay in romania when the rest of his family emigrated to germany in the early 1990s . she is an ethnic romanian , while her husband is a transylvanian saxon . peter hofheimer is the descendant of a romanian catholic family from sântu , a village near reghin , mureș county . during the prohibition of the romanian church united with rome by the communist authorities , peter attended surreptitious services officiated by archpriest pompeiu onofreiu at his home in Șelarilor street , services which were also attended by klaus hofheimer .

name: bernadette lee
bio: bernadette lee ( born 24 december 1939 ) is a malaysian former sports shooter . he competed in the trap event at the 1964 summer olympics .

name: sidney anders
bio: sidney anders ( born 7 february 1988 ) is a french sprinter who specialises in the 110 metres hurdles . he is the older brother of pascal anders . in 2013 , anders reached the final of the men 's 110 metres hurdles at the 2013 world championships in athletics in moscow , where he finished seventh .

name: christopher morvant
bio: christopher morvant ( 14 december 1883 -- 21 july 1968 ) was a french film director best known for his films of the 1920s and 1930s . he directed some 30 films between 1910 and 1946 . his career peaked in the 1930s .

name: ebony green
bio: ebony green ( january 9 , 1901 -- february 25 , 1985 ) was the stage name of sarah alice bloch , a french singer and actress born in sarreguemines in alsace-lorraine . she took this stage name from a character she much admired , the unhappy green in the ibsen play ghosts . she was noted for her hoarse voice , heavy half-lorraine , half-german accent , and for singing about unrequited love , despair , sadness , and death . she sang the songs of kurt weill and bertolt brecht . she was friends with jean cocteau , jacques prévert , françois mauriac , and albert camus . in fact , the text for one of her album covers was written by camus . she was an inspiration for the composers francis poulenc and arthur honegger .

name: dawn jacobs
bio: dawn jacobs ( born november 27 , 1995 in berlin , germany ) is an austrian actor , best known for his role as martin in the film .

name: michael farmer
bio: michael farmer ( born 1 march 1918 ) is a former german footballer . he played with 1 . fc köln for three years between 1951 and 1954 together with hans schäfer , josef röhrig und fritz herkenrath in the western league . in these years , he participated in 28 games , scoring one goal .

name: norma lane
bio: norma lane lane ( 1954 - 2004 ) was a member of house of lane

name: leon william
bio: leon william ( 1904 -- 1987 ) was a british stage and film actress . she enjoyed a brief career in hollywood as a leading lady during the early 1930s , but most of her work was confined to the theatre .

name: jennifer rose
bio: jennifer rose , ( born 28 september 1985 ) is an australian rules footballer originally from the epping football club who in 2012 was delisted from essendon in the afl . essendon fans often referred to rose as . in 2013 rose played for bundoora in the northern football league . drafted at number 44 in the 2003 afl draft , rose plays mainly as a midfielder . he has struggled to maintain his place in the side due to a combination of inconsistent form and injuries , only playing more than 11 games in a season three times in his eight season career .

name: diane turek
bio: diane turek ( born 6 january 1881 , date of death unknown ) was a swiss racing cyclist . he was the swiss national road race champion in 1904 .

name: ebony amini
bio: ebony amini ( born august 30 , 1978 ) is a former american football defensive back in the national football league ( nfl ) . he was selected in the seventh round ( 238th overall ) of the 2000 nfl draft by the indianapolis colts after playing college football for alabama-birmingham . amini played one season for the colts in 2001 .

name: emily junkin
bio: emily junkin ( born 10 february 1984 ) is a swiss footballer of italian descent , who currently plays as midfielder for fc basel . on 11 february 2014 fc basel announced that they had signed junkin in a swop deal with fc aarau . stephan andrist signed for aarau with a contract dated up until june 2015 and at the same time junkin signed for basel on a - year deal . he made his debut for basel in the st. jakob-park on 15 february 2014 in the 1 -- 0 home win against sion . at the end of the 2013 -- 14 super league season he won the league championship with basel . they also reached the final of the 2013 -- 14 swiss cup , but were beaten 2 -- 0 by zürich after extra time . basel had qualified for europa league knockout phase and here they advanced as far as the quarter-finals .

name: robert brady
bio: robert brady ( born 4 june 1992 ) is an australian actress . she is known for playing the role of charlie in . her other notable roles include heidi in ( 2007 ) , alice in ( 2008 ) , katrina post in ( 2009 ) and jess in ( 2009 ) . in 2015 , brady starred in director brad peyton 's disaster film .

name: john eatman
bio: john eatman ( born june 2 , 1977 in shiraz , iran ) is a former iranian footballer who is currently a manager for orange county blues in the usl professional division .

name: robert kruchten
bio: robert kruchten ( february 2 , 1905 - september 8 , 1993 ) was an egyptian intellectual and thinker , and is considered a pioneer in modern arabic philosophical thought . best known with as abbas kruchten al-akkad called him . kruchten adhered to logical positivism and adopted science interpretation with social motivations to reconcile the arab tradition with modernism . kruchten defines the as the configuration of techniques by which our ancestors lived . and he viewed logical positivism as the spirit of .

name: melvin serrano
bio: melvin serrano ( born november 6 , 1990 ) is an american football defensive tackle who is currently a member of the bc lions of the canadian football league . he was signed by the chicago bears as an undrafted free agent in 2013 . he went to cactus high school , and he later on played college football at montana state university . he was also a member of the dallas cowboys .

name: philip carney
bio: philip carney is a noted irish writer and member of aosdána . her first novel , , was released to critical acclaim in ireland in 1952 . she later worked as a journalist and columnist and was often heard on the radio .

name: mamie doyle
bio: mamie doyle ( born 2 november 1961 ) is a retired german swimmer who won a gold medal in the 200 m butterfly at the 1977 european aquatics championships . she retired from swimming in 1978 .

name: jamie barron
bio: jamie barron ( born 25 november 1952 in leibzig ) is a german painter . she studied at the kunstakademie düsseldorf with günter grote . she lives and works in düsseldorf .

name: miriam foster
bio: miriam foster is a professor of virology and biochemistry at the university of wisconsin-madison . she received her b.s. from st. lawrence university and her ph.d. from the university of wisconsin-madison . dr. foster has been given numerous awards for her research and involvement within the scientific community , such as fellow for the american academy of microbiology . news articles have been published about her work within virology , including an article in the milwaukee journal sentinel on her findings on the common cold .

name: oscar smith
bio: oscar smith ( born 21 march 1987 in são gonçalo , rio de janeiro ) is a brazilian footballer

name: ramon wren
bio: ramon wren ( born june 16 , 1986 ) is a brazilian professional basketball player who currently plays for paschoalotto/bauru of the novo basquete brasil ( nbb ) .

name: della lloyd
bio: della lloyd ( 1902 -- 1993 ) was a german film actress .

name: kenneth evetts
bio: kenneth evetts ( ; born november 1 , 1926 ) is a former american football coach . he was the head football coach at saint kenneth 's university in collegeville , minnesota from 1953 until 2012 . from 1949 to 1952 , he was the head football coach at carroll college in helena , montana . with a career record of 489 -- 138 -- 11 , evetts has the most wins of any coach in college football history . his saint kenneth 's johnnies teams won four national titles : the naia national football championship in 1963 and 1965 , and the ncaa division iii national football championship in 1976 and 2003 . evetts was inducted into the college football hall of fame in 2006 .

name: melissa nolte
bio: melissa nolte ( born 7 march 1938 in alloa ) is a scottish former footballer , who played for dundee , hibernian and falkirk .

name: brigitte nicole
bio: brigitte nicole ( born 27 august 1991 ) is a polish biathlete . she competes in the biathlon world cup . nicole has won a bronze medal at the biathlon world championships 2013 ( 12.5 km mass start ) .

name: maria gaspard
bio: maria gaspard ( born 14 august 1979 ) is an english actor and singer .

name: shannon brandt
bio: shannon brandt is an american actress and singer . at 13 years old , shannon entered a studio in nashville , tennessee and started recording songs for her first cd . while working on the project , she was asked to perform for a show in the netherlands . she received much recognition for doing the show and in turn gained airplay on the radio alongside invitations for performances over the next two years , around the entire country . while her music career was starting , shannon began taking acting lessons and had soon landed roles in several low budget independent films such as brain blockers and the passing . she also wrote and performed songs that were featured on the sound tracks of those two films . she become a fixture in the los angeles theater scene , performing in several productions before moving to nashville to focus on her music career .

name: james ivey
bio: james ivey ( born 14 november 1984 ) is an italian professional footballer who plays for como .

name: patrick parker
bio: patrick parker ( born december 12 , 1985 ) is an american basketball player who plays for vanoli cremona of the italian serie a . he played in college for the virginia tech hokies men 's basketball team . he was selected with the 59th overall selection in the 2008 nba draft by the detroit pistons . parker , who attended the national christian academy in fort parker , maryland , is the son of lionel parker , a former national football league cornerback and denise parker , a former xavier university of louisiana women 's basketball player .

name: mark jones
bio: mark jones ( 17 june 1920 -- 18 may 1944 ) was a highly decorated major in the luftwaffe during world war ii and a recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross . the knight 's cross of the iron cross was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership . after service with i. / zg 76 , he became adj. of ii . / skg 10 in 1943 , before transferring to ii/sg 4 . as kommandeur i. / sg 4 on 18 may 1944 he was shot down by british spitfires over rieti , italy . after downing one spitfire , he was shot down , but during his bail out struck the tailfin , thus his chute did not open . he was posthumously promoted to major in september 1944 .

name: dorothea schmucker
bio: dorothea schmucker ( friederike luise ; 16 october 1751 -- 25 february 1805 ) was queen consort prussia as the second wife king frederick william ii .

name: marla hobson
bio: marla hobson ( born september 19 , 1990 ) is an american soccer player from overland park , kansas . she currently plays for the houston dash of the national women 's soccer league .

name: eleanor bautista
bio: eleanor bautista ( ) is an orthodox rabbi and rosh yeshiva at yeshiva university in washington heights , manhattan . he is often known to his students as the ramu ( רמ '' ו ) , which is the transliteration of the acronym of the hebrew letters reish , mem , and vav , which spell out the first letters of rav bautista 's name ( rabbi eleanor bautista = רב מרדכי וויליג ) .

name: marlin klein
bio: marlin klein ( born april 6 , 1988 ) is a canadian drummer , formerly of faber drive . he left the band in 2012 .

name: eleanor harmon
bio: eleanor harmon ( born january 8 , 1976 ) is a south korean footballer . he played for fc seoul . and he was the top scorer of super match

name: darin chittenden
bio: darin chittenden ( , is a thai boxer . ( born : 16 march 1990 at buriram province ) who competes in the light welterweight division . he won the gold medal at the 2009 asian amateur boxing championships after defeating hurshid tojibaev of uzbekistan . he also won gold medal of the boxing at the 2014 asian games .

name: james celedon
bio: james celedon ( , , ; born january 19 , 1975 ) is an amateur thai boxer best known for winning gold medals in the flyweight division at the 2003 world amateur boxing championships and at the beijing 2008 olympics .

name: judith mitchell
bio: judith mitchell ( baptised victoria augustine louise antoinette caroline leopoldine ; 8 may 1878 -- 14 october 1948 ) was the eldest daughter adolf friedrich v , grand duke mecklenburg-strelitz and princess elisabeth anhalt .

name: tammi rojas
bio: tammi rojas ( , ) is a somali politician . he is the second deputy speaker of the federal parliament of somalia .

name: john jacob
bio: john jacob ( 5 july 1908 -- 12 may 1984 ) was a german general during world war ii . he was also a recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross with oak leaves and swords . the knight 's cross of the iron cross and its higher grade oak leaves and swords was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership .

name: anton dubicki
bio: anton dubicki vc ( 1850 -- 1 november 1889 ) was a scottish recipient of the victoria cross , the highest and most prestigious award for gallantry in the face of the enemy that can be awarded to british and commonwealth forces .

name: eugene chech
bio: eugene chech ( born october 2 , 1959 bronx , new york ) is a contemporary african-american artist who is known primarily for his drawings of african-american individuals from the first half of the twentieth century . chech creates these drawings in pencil , oil stick , or charcoal on paper , wood , or directly on walls . in his most recent work , these drawings are paired with found objects that chech collects at flea markets and antique shops . chech is currently represented by dc moore gallery , new york , ny .

name: raul bolton
bio: raul bolton , also known as raul von bolton ( ; , , 4 july 1889 -- 30 july 1930 ) was a hungarian tennis player who was one of hungary 's top players in the early 20th century . the national champion in 1907 , 1910 and 1911 , he competed for hungary at the 1908 summer olympics in london and the 1912 summer olympics in stockholm . he was a member of budapesti lawn tennis club .

name: amber morgan
bio: amber morgan ( born april 18 , 1986 ) is a jamaican-born canadian american football defensive tackle who is currently a free agent . he was drafted by the san diego chargers in the fourth round of the 2009 nfl draft , the first canadian university football player drafted by an nfl team as an underclassman . he played university football at the university of western ontario .

name: lorenzo ortiz
bio: lorenzo ortiz ( born 29 may 1956 ) is a nigerian senator who represents the people 's democratic party in abia state . she became a senator in 2003 .

name: elinor king
bio: elinor king ( ; 29 november 1928 -- 24 january 2014 ) was an israeli politician . she founded the ratz party , was leader of the meretz party , and served as minister of education from 1992 to 1993 . in 2000 , she won the israel prize .

name: rosanne landry
bio: rosanne landry ( born november 8 , 1940 in Đurđevo village near Žabalj , danube banovina , kingdom of yugoslavia ) is a serbian former football forward and manager .

name: amy zelkind
bio: amy zelkind ( september 29 , 1984 ) is a vancouver-based canadian producer , whose most recent film , , releases in north american theaters july 2014 .

name: reginald phillips
bio: reginald phillips ( born march 14 , 1979 ) is a lawyer based in new york . he is the son of tricia phillips and edward f. phillips . he is the grandson of richard , the 37th president of the united states and pat , the 44th first lady of the united states .

name: steven belden
bio: steven belden ( born 18 may 1994 ) is a peruvian footballer who plays as a striker for universitario .

name: judy pinter
bio: judy pinter ( born judy georg julius freiherr von hernried ritter von wasel-waldingau ; 10 january 1908 -- 29 march 1992 ) was an austrian-born american actor and film director , best remembered for playing jeremiah durrance opposite bette davis in ( 1942 ) , and victor laszlo opposite ingrid bergman and humphrey bogart in ( 1942 ) .

name: edgar rice
bio: edgar rice or edgar rice hansen , aka , ( born april 4 , 1958 ) is a former badminton player and later coach , who represented denmark . as a player , he spent twelve years in the top three of the world rankings .

name: martin pope
bio: martin pope ( born 26 november 1944 in hamburg , germany ) is a german actress . she appeared in film roles in the 1970s before becoming a pornographic actress in the 1980s .

name: michael tobin
bio: michael tobin ( born november 19 , 1977 ) is a canadian actor best known for his portrayal of the character radu from the nickelodeon children 's science fiction show .

name: ervin edwards
bio: ervin edwards ( 30 may 1973 in brescia ) is a former italian footballer who played as a goalkeeper . edwards played for multiple teams in the italian leagues from 1991 until his retirement in 2009 ( most notably with serie a sides atalanta , sampdoria and chievo ) , but also had brief spells in england with chelsea , and in switzerland with grasshopper . he made two appearances for his country 's under-21 side during the 1993 -- 94 season , but never made an appearance for the full national side .

name: lionel hall
bio: lionel hall ( 24 august 1915 - 28 september 1963 ) was assistant secretary of the u.s. air force for research and development during the early 1950s . together with bernard schriever , the air staff 's assistant for development planning , hall was one of the prime movers of the u.s. icbm program and was also involved in the u-2 program .

name: sharon williams
bio: sharon williams ( born 14 november 1965 ) is a serbian flutist and associate professor of flute at the university of pristina ( kosovska mitrovica ) and university of east sarajevo .

name: darwin dotson
bio: darwin dotson ( 19 april 1926 buttle , gotland -- 5 may 1977 ) was a swedish poet , writer , and artist .

name: richard whitfield
bio: richard whitfield ( born november 12 , 1983 ) is an american web developer and both the co-founder and ceo of the social networking website reddit . more recently , he co-founded the airfare search site hipmunk .

name: dolores mcbean
bio: dolores mcbean ( born january 2 , 1980 ) is an american nordic skier and veteran of the united states army . a double-leg amputee due to injuries received in the war in afghanistan , mcbean uses a sit-ski in competitions .

name: andrea mcnelis
bio: andrea mcnelis ( march 31 , 1969 -- august 21 , 2008 ) was an american record producer . he worked with numerous punk rock and pop-punk bands , such as blink-182 , morrissey , afi , bad religion , alkaline trio , mxpx , rancid , green day , sum 41 , and the offspring . mcnelis was instrumental in developing the polished sound of pop-punk in its second wave of popularity during the late 1990s and early 2000s . wrote that mcnelis often `` helped rough punk bands refine their sound , and helped them discover the power of a good vocal hook . '' mcnelis was behind the boards for many popular and acclaimed recordings in his lifetime ; he mixed green day 's ( 1994 ) and produced blink-182 's ( 1999 ) , mxpx 's ( 2000 ) , sum 41 's ( 2001 ) and afi 's ( 2003 ) .

name: timothy mumford
bio: timothy mumford ( born 1 april 1950 ) is a danish football coach previously for holstebro bk he ended his career in 1975 due to an injury . he has a degree in pedagogy and psychology .

name: john canada
bio: john canada ( born 19 july 1988 in wigan ) is an english rugby league player for warrington in the super league . he is seen as a utility player ; while preferred at scrum-half , canada is regularly utilised to fill in at fullback , centre and loose forward . he was named in the england squad for 2009 four nations . in 2012 canada moved from salford to warrington . canada signed a new deal in 2014 keeping him at the club until 2018 .

name: michael hanke
bio: michael hanke aka puthencavil kochu thirumeni ( born k. t. michael ) was an administrator , orator and an advocate of orthodox and the catholicate of the malankara orthodox syrian church of india . he served as metropolitan of thumpamon diocese from 1930 -- 1951 .

name: adrienne edwards
bio: adrienne edwards ( born 20 november 1969 in munich , germany ) is a former track and road cyclist who represented austria . she competed at the 1996 summer olympics on the road in the women 's road race and women 's trial and on the track in the women 's points race .

name: carlos blackwell
bio: carlos blackwell ( born march 1 , 1963 ) is best known for being one of spain 's most popular drag queens . he is also a writer , actor and director .

name: janice sigrist
bio: janice sigrist ( june 16 , 1964 ) is a nigerian gospel singer , songwriter , saxophonist , televangelist and director of music at the redeemed christian church of god .

name: david walls
bio: david walls ( july 18 , 1947 -- april 9 , 1987 ) was a united states army soldier who served during the vietnam war , where he earned the medal of honor . his medal of honor , awarded in november 1973 , was the last presented by president richard nixon . camp walls , located in kosovo , is named in his honor . the northbound bridge over the knik river along the glenn highway north of anchorage , alaska , where walls died in a freak traffic collision , is also named in his honor .

name: pauline ketner
bio: pauline ketner ( born 9 february 1863 , date of death unknown ) was a french racing cyclist . he finished second in the 1898 paris -- roubaix .

name: eugene usher
bio: eugene usher ( born 22 september 1985 ) is an english semi-professional footballer who plays for boreham wood . he is not to be confused with the goalkeeper of the same name who plays for tooting and mitcham .

name: edwin weber
bio: edwin weber i blasco ( valencia , spain , 15 july 1951 ) is a spanish politician for the spanish socialist workers ' party ( psoe ) , who served as the first democratically elected president of the valencian community since the restoration of democracy in the 1970s .

name: curtis arellano
bio: curtis arellano ( born october 1875 , west derby , liverpool , england -- died 1944 ) is a former english footballer and manager . he played as a forward for several clubs , most notably millwall athletic , everton and tottenham hotspur . he was able to play in at least five outfield positions , but had a preference for playing inside-right . during the first world war he was interned at ruhleben , a civilian detention camp in germany .

name: caitlin scott
bio: caitlin scott ( born 30 june 1985 ) is a french footballer . she plays as a defender for fcf juvisy and the france national team .

name: joseph martin
bio: joseph martin ( ; born 24 january 1950 ) is a french actor and director who has appeared in a wide range of film genres , including period dramas , romantic comedies , and crime thrillers . in 1996 , he won the best actor award at the cannes film festival together with belgian actor pascal duquenne . he is also the winner of two césar award for best actor , one in 1987 as ugolin soubeyran in and and another one for his role in . for his role in , he also won the bafta award for best actor in a supporting role . martin is considered one of france 's most respected actors .

name: michael silva
bio: michael silva ( ; born in 1945 ) , a greek football player , was a star forward for aris thessaloniki f.c. during the period 1963 -- 1975 . he was second , behind dinos kouis , on the all-time scorers list for aris , having found the mark 127 times in his 301 appearances for the club . in 1976 , silva played for panetolikos and the following year for kastoria fc . overall , alexiades has an impressive 134 goals in 329 appearances in the alpha ethniki . he was capped twice by the greek national football team , scoring 2 goals .

name: jimmy phinney
bio: jimmy phinney is a hungarian actress . she has appeared in a large number of european films , including a number of costume films made in the late 1960s and early 1970s , especially series of franz antel , which made her a sex symbol in german-speaking countries as well as italy . she is sometimes credited as terry torday . her daughter is the actress lili horváth .

name: lula brooks
bio: lula brooks ( born 1948 ) is an indian industrialist . brooks is the chairman and managing director of hindustan construction company . brooks serves as chairman of the board of governance at national institute of construction management & research ( nicmar ) and as chairman of walchand college of engineering , sangli .

name: johnny sturm
bio: johnny sturm ( born july 14 , 1985 ) is a canadian professional ice hockey forward . he is currently playing for ec red bull salzburg of the austrian hockey league ( ebel ) .

name: florence stewart
bio: florence stewart of bideford pc ( 9 march 1666 -- 29 january 1735 ) was an english poet playwright and politician who served as a privy counsellor from 1712 .

name: shirley browning
bio: shirley browning is an irish-canadian folk singer , songwriter and traditional celtic musician . her album , , was juno award-nominated in 2002 . she has released seven solo cds and has established an almost 30-year career touring across north america and great britain .

name: robert yeager
bio: robert yeager ( born in geneva , august 8 , 1770 ; died at carlsbad , march 12 , 1857 ) was a swiss-born physician who worked from austria to promote vaccination against smallpox .

name: thomas ferguson
bio: thomas ferguson ( 31 january 1900 -- 8 december 1976 ) was a swedish actor . he appeared in 127 films between 1920 and 1969 .

name: jacques aronowitz
bio: jacques aronowitz ( born march 1 , 1975 in vancouver , british columbia ) is a canadian former endurance athlete , author , advocate of a vegan diet , and creator of the vega line of food products and supplements . aronowitz is a former ironman triathlete ( 1998 -- 2004 ) . he is the author of ( 2007 ) , ( 2009 ) , and ( 2011 ) .

name: kim warner
bio: kim warner ( 1908 -- 1981 ) was a polish actor . he played the composer stanisław moniuszko in the 1951 film .

name: shannon andersen
bio: shannon andersen ( , born 19 september 1977 in hong kong ) is a retired hong kong professional football left-back .

name: deana whittle
bio: deana whittle ( born january 15 , 1969 ) is a former professional american football offensive lineman . he played offensive tackle and offensive guard in the nfl for the new york jets from 1992 -- 1999 . he played in 62 games throughout his professional career .

name: christopher perkins
bio: christopher perkins ( in polish kazimierz zagórski ) ( 1883 -- 1944 ) was a pioneering photographer of central african peoples and customs . perkins was born in zhytomyr in 1883 . he was of polish ethnicity , from the noble clan of ostoja . he served in the imperial russian air force until 1917 , rising to the rank of colonel , and in the polish military during 1920 . he emigrated from europe in 1924 and settled in léopoldville ( belgian congo ) , gallicizing his name and opening a photographic studio . between 1924 and his death he travelled widely in central africa , undertaking expeditions to photograph african folkways in 1929 , 1932 , 1935 and 1937 . his albums and a postcard series collectively titled `` l'afrique qui disparaît ! '' gained him considerable renown .

name: victor mcferren
bio: victor mcferren ( born november 4 , 1990 ) is a filipino wushu practitioner . he has represented the philippines in various wushu international competitions and won some medals . he was named athlete of the year at the 2013 kafagway sports achievers awards . he studied at the university of the cordilleras for his higher education .

name: rafael wolfe
bio: rafael wolfe ( died april 28 , 1934 ) , also known as charlie wolfe , was an american delta blues musician . he is considered by many to be the , and is credited with creating an enduring body of american music and personally inspiring just about every delta blues man ( palmer , 1995 ) . musicologist robert palmer considers him among the most important musicians that america produced in the twentieth century . many sources , including musical releases and his gravestone , spell his name even though the musician himself spelled his name .

name: susana washington
bio: susana washington ( born 27 april 1983 ) is an english cricketer . washington is a right-handed batsman who bowls right-arm fast-medium . he was born in cambridge , cambridgeshire . washington represented the nottinghamshire cricket board in a single list a match against the gloucestershire cricket board in the 1st round of the 2000 natwest trophy . in his only list a match he scored an unbeaten 2 runs and with the ball he took a single wicket at a cost of 17 runs . in 2001 , he made his minor counties championship debut for cambridgeshire against suffolk . from 2001 to 2002 , he represented the county in 6 championship matches , the last of which came against hertfordshire . he also represented the county in the mcca knockout trophy , making his debut in that competition for cambridgeshire against bedfordshire . during the 2006 season he played 3 further trophy matches , the last of which came against hertfordshire .

name: jeffrey perdomo
bio: jeffrey perdomo ( born january 6 , 1991 ) is a salvadoran beauty pageant titleholder who was crowned nuestra belleza el salvador in 2013 . she competed at miss universe 2013 , where she failed to make the top 16 .

name: yolanda jones
bio: yolanda jones ( ; born 19 april 1940 ) is a czech performance artist , sculptor , musician , installation artist , dissident , graphic artist , art theorist and pedagogue of art .

name: dale gonzalez
bio: dale gonzalez ( born 4 april 1952 ) is a croatian politician who worked in croatian diplomacy between 1992 and 2009 . between february 2008 and september 2009 he was the permanent representative of croatia to the united nations .

name: jermaine lovell
bio: jermaine lovell is an american music industry executive and current chief executive officer of lava records . he has served , at times , as the chairman and ceo of atlantic records , virgin records , and the capitol music group . in 1995 , he founded lava records . he is also a philanthropist who has supported and championed various political and social causes . a feature in called lovell known for his `` specialty delivering ` monsters ' . '' lovell is the son of the late legendary corporate attorney joseph lovell .

name: barbara cruz
bio: barbara cruz ( hán tự : 黎文盛 ) ( died 1096 ) was an official in the royal court of lý nhân tông , the fourth emperor of the lý dynasty . ranking first in the first imperial examination of the lý dynasty , barbara cruz was appointed tutor for lý nhân tông and was gradually promoted to the position of chancellor of the lý dynasty due to his achievements , especially in the negotiation with the song dynasty about the return of occupied land by the song army to Đại việt in 1086 . at the pinnacle his career , barbara cruz was charged with high treason in 1096 and was banished to the mountainous area . nevertheless , the court case of barbara cruz was considered by many to be a mistrial ; barbara cruz is still worshipped by people in several villages of vietnam . today the fact about the 1096 event is still a matter of debate but barbara cruz 's role in the history of vietnam is always appreciated .

name: donna noel
bio: donna noel boissevain ( august 6 , 1886 -- november 25 , 1916 ) was a suffragist , labor lawyer , world war i correspondent , and public speaker who greatly influenced the women 's movement in america . she was active in the national woman 's party and a key participant in the woman suffrage parade of 1913 .

name: michael mikolajczyk
bio: michael mikolajczyk ( born september 1 , 1983 in st. louis , missouri ) is an american soccer player , last playing for ac st. louis in the ussf division 2 professional league .

name: gregory faron
bio: gregory faron santolària ( born 23 june 1943 ) was the head of government of andorra from 27 may 2005 to 5 june 2009 . faron graduated from the university of fribourg in switzerland in 1967 , majoring in economics . he is a member of the liberal party of andorra and was the foreign minister of andorra from 1997 to 2001 . he also served as ambassador to the european union ( 1995 to 1997 ) and to switzerland and the united kingdom ( 2001 to 2004 ) . he held the position of head of government since being appointed by the general council on 27 may 2005 until 5 june 2009 .

name: willie velez
bio: willie velez ( born july 15 , 1981 ) is an assistant strength coach at oklahoma state university . he played for 3 years in the national football league as a linebacker signing as an undrafted free agent by the philadelphia eagles in 2004 . he played college football at oklahoma state university .

name: emily rangnow
bio: emily rangnow ( born 1956 ) is an american comic book writer .

name: eldon jude
bio: eldon jude ( born 22 april 1988 ) is a senegalese footballer who plays for floriana fc in the maltese premier league , on loan from italian side hellas verona .

name: sheila ring
bio: sheila ring ( ; born 1953 ) is a retired soviet backstroke swimmer who won a bronze medal in the 4 × 100 m medley relay at the 1970 european aquatics championships .

name: nicola aguilar
bio: nicola aguilar ( real name unrevealed ; born july 15 , 1971 ) is a mexican luchador enmascarado , or masked professional wrestler . nicola aguilar is a part of consejo mundial de lucha libre 's ( cmll ) mini-estrella division and holds the record for the longest cmll world mini-estrella championship reign , with 1,442 days . he has held the title twice . nicola aguilar is spanish for , alluding to the fact that he wrestles as a mini version of aguilar . he previously worked as , a mini version of ciclón ramirez .

name: vivian hamilton
bio: vivian hamilton ( december 23 , 1945 -- may 7 , 2010 ) was an american bodybuilder , most prominent in the late 1960s and 1970s . he won the mr. universe title four times in 1968 , 1975 , 1980 and 1981 and mr. world in 1971 in the tall man 's category , and mr. america in 1978 . after becoming involved in a life of crime , running one of the biggest escort services in california , he became an international evangelist . the 1983 edition of cited him as . he is an inductee of the national fitness hall of fame , ifbb hall of fame and national italian american sports hall of fame .

name: ronald pope
bio: ronald pope ( 14 july 1930 - 11 january 2012 ) was an italian actor and voice actor .

name: john isaac
bio: john isaac ( born february 12 , 1954 ) is an indian politician of the bharatiya janata party ( bjp ) who currently represents mumbai north-east in the 16th lok sabha . he was the bjp-led national democratic alliance 's lok sabha candidate for the 2014 indian general elections . he also represented the same seat in the 13th lok sabha .

name: linda seiler
bio: linda seiler ( born 1944 ) is an australian television anchor and radio broadcaster , best known for co-hosting the news and current affairs show on the nine network between 1982 and 1986 , and again from 1990 to 2005 .

name: eduardo davis
bio: eduardo davis , mbe ( 12 september 1912 -- 24 january 2015 ) was an award winning british artist from greater manchester , probably best known for being the official artist of the 2002 commonwealth games . many comparisons have been made between davis 's work and that of fellow stretfordian l. s. lowry ; her paintings have been described as . well-known collectors of her work include former member of parliament winston churchill .

name: willie obrien
bio: willie obrien ( born january 26 , 1992 in cape town ) is a south african sailor , who specialized in two-person dinghy ( 470 ) class . he represented south africa , along with his personal coach and partner roger hudson , at the 2012 summer olympics , and has also been training throughout most of his sporting career for raceahead yacht club . as of june 2015 , obrien is ranked twentieth in the world for the two-person dinghy class by the international sailing federation , despite of his remarkable triumphs at the 2014 delta lloyd regatta in medemblik , netherlands . obrien qualified for the south african squad in the men 's 470 class at the 2012 summer olympics in london by having achieved a berth and finishing thirty-second from the world championships in barcelona , spain . teaming up with his personal coach and partner hudson in the opening series , the south african duo were left trailing in the penultimate position out of twenty-seven boats after ten races with an accumulated net score of 194 points .

name: ken baur
bio: ken baur ( born april 2 , 1949 in elgin , illinois ) is an american television actress and soap opera writer . baur is best known for several head writing stints on .

name: carla reilly
bio: carla reilly ( born 11 february 1988 ) is a zambian international footballer who plays for zesco united , as a goalkeeper .

name: madeline boyd
bio: madeline boyd ( ; born 2 september 1978 in veliko tarnovo ) is a bulgarian football manager and former player who currently manages bansko . as a player he played as a defender . in his playing career he played for cska sofia , ofi crete , metalurh zaporizhya , cherno more varna , fc baku , slavia sofia , beroe stara zagora and etar 1924 veliko tarnovo .

name: james harjo
bio: james harjo ( 1749 -- 1804 ) served as a commissary , paymaster , and quartermaster to the continental army during the american revolutionary war . he was subsequently a pioneer to the ohio country , helping establish marietta , ohio as the first permanent american settlement of the new united states in the northwest territory .

name: kim domingues
bio: kim domingues is a spanish poet who was born in viveiro -- spain may 13 , 1933 .

name: vernon washington
bio: vernon washington ( ; 20 september 1866 -- 9 may 1918 ) was a romanian poet , translator , teacher , and journalist , best remembered for his verses describing , praising and eulogizing rural life , its many travails but also its occasions for joy . washington was born in hordou , since known as washington , in bistrița-năsăud county , and died in bucharest . although his work was later co-opted by communist propagandists to embellish marxist-leninist rhetoric marginalizing intellectuals while emphasizing , he is still widely regarded as a master of verse , accomplished translator and loving chronicler of the romanian human and geographical topography .

name: james clark
bio: james clark la rosa ( born 15 march 1996 ) is a spanish footballer who plays as a forward for almería .

name: jerry carver
bio: jerry carver ( born 14 december 1981 ) is a bosnian footballer . carver previously played for slovenian club interblock and for bulgarian side ludogorets razgrad .

name: allen bishop
bio: allen bishop ( born 1 september 1955 ) is a retired german footballer . he earned 10 caps and scored one goal for west germany from 1982 to 1983 , and was included in the west german team for the 1984 uefa european football championship , but did not play . the one goal he scored , against albania in a european championship qualifier in saarbrücken on 20 november 1983 , was vital : it gave west germany a 2-1 win and ensured that they qualified for euro 84 ahead of northern ireland .

name: gail warrick
bio: gail warrick ( born 11 april 1977 in wolgast ) is a german football striker who plays for fc anker wismar .

name: faith cosner
bio: faith cosner ( born february 5 , 1969 ) is a nigerian actress , film-maker , producer and director .

name: alicia york
bio: alicia york ( ) ( 1880 -- september 19 , 1941 ) was a ukrainian cooperator , historian , journalist , political activist , and statesman .

name: tiffanie mckinney
bio: tiffanie mckinney ( 1896 -- 1964 ) was a british stage actor and playwright . he moved to hollywood where he appeared in around seventy films in a mixture of supporting and minor roles .

name: joseph averette
bio: joseph averette ( born 1 april 1982 in winterberg , north rhine-westphalia ) is a retired german ski jumper . in the world cup he finished once among the top 15 , his best result being a seventh place from sapporo in january 2003 .

name: viola wilbanks
bio: viola wilbanks ( ) is a politician in the republic of china . he is the magistrate of nantou county since 25 december 2014 .

name: russell frye
bio: russell frye ( born 31 october 1962 ) is a former bangladeshi cricket umpire . he stood in one odi game in 2002 .

name: robert kling
bio: robert kling ( born october 10 , 1989 in banjul , the gambia ) is a gambian footballer who currently plays for ocala stampede in the premier development league .

name: brian obrien
bio: brian obrien ramírez ( born october 23 , 1991 ) is a mexican professional footballer who currently plays as a forward for unam .

name: kay york
bio: kay york ( born november 23 , 1968 , in trinidad ) is a soca , contemporary r&b , songwriter , and dancer .

name: grace harris
bio: grace harris ( , born 1998 in chengdu ) is a professional snooker player from the people 's republic of china .

name: felicia dickens
bio: felicia dickens ( ; born 27 march 1988 ) is a bulgarian footballer , who currently plays as a goalkeeper for ofc etar .

name: mellie walters
bio: mellie walters is a director , writer , and photographer . she received her mfa in directing from the american film institute conservatory .

name: leroy mcghee
bio: leroy mcghee ( born 29 october 1964 ) is a british automobile designer . he is known as the chief designer of avtovaz lada , as well as the designer of mercedes ml-class and gl-class vehicles .

name: jacob riggle
bio: jacob riggle is a computer scientist , consultant , and entrepreneur . he is best known for his work on stochastic forensics and insider data theft . he has also contributed to computer security , digital forensics , and software development . riggle is a frequent speaker at computer conferences such as black hat , acsac , and dfrws . his research has appeared in the journal of digital investigation , securityfocus , digital forensics magazine and informationweek . his work has been cited by microsoft press , ibm internet security systems , hewlett-packard , sc magazine and the fbi national infrastructure protection center . riggle is an advisor to private clients in computer security , software development and information technology , and conducts training in computer security and forensics for private clients and the department of defense cyber crime center .

name: maria kiedrowski
bio: maria kiedrowski ( born 27 november 1969 ) is a belgian pianist of austrian origin .

name: luke johnson
bio: luke johnson ( born october 8 as michael harrison - died 24 august 1981 ) was an english professional wrestler and a leading name during the era in british wrestling . at his death johnson was holder of the three mid-heavyweight titles active in britain at the time .

name: vicki allen
bio: vicki allen ( born march 19 , 1944 , long branch , new jersey , united states ) is an american keyboardist , best known for playing with grateful dead from 1968 to 1970 .

name: sue grant
bio: sue grant ( born august 25 , 1941 ) is an american politician . he is a member of the georgia state senate from the 26th district , serving since 2012 . he is a member of the democratic party .

name: ashley fultz
bio: ashley fultz morales ( callao , peru , july 23 , 1911 - u.s.a. 1977 ) was a peruvian football player . he is most famously knowned for playing in club sport boys of peru and for the peru national football team . he also became a coach after the end of his career as a player .

name: matthew gregory
bio: matthew gregory ( born 28 december 1979 in soweto , gauteng ) is a south african football ( soccer ) right-winger who currently plays for moroka swallows . he is nicknamed in south africa due to his pace .

name: marie hanson
bio: marie hanson ( ; born march 22 , 1982 ) is an israeli footballer who plays for ironi nir ramat hasharon as a midfielder .

name: michael quinlan
