bio: michael quinlan ( born august 18 , 1959 ) is an american activist , environmentalist , economist , and writer , known for her work on tribal land claims and preservation , as well as sustainable development . in 1996 and 2000 , she ran for vice president as the nominee of the green party of the united states , on a ticket headed by ralph nader . a native american with ojibwe ancestry , she is the executive director of both white earth land recovery project , which she founded at white earth reservation in 1989 , and honor the earth , which she founded with indigo girls amy ray and emily saliers in 1993 . born in los angeles and raised in ashland , oregon , she was enrolled in the tribe at an early age , but did not live at the white earth indian reservation until 1982 . she started work there after college as a principal of a high school . quinlan became an activist in anishinaabe issues , helping found the indigenous women 's network in 1985 . she became involved in continuing struggles to regain reservation land lost since in the 19th century . the welrp holds land in a conservation trust for the benefit of the tribe .

name: corine price
bio: corine price ( born 28 july 1971 ) is a mexican politician affiliated to the national action party . as of 2014 he served as deputy of the lx legislature of the mexican congress representing the state of mexico .

name: shirley wiedemann
bio: shirley wiedemann ( born december 31 , 1943 ) is an american film and television actor .

name: celia paul
bio: celia paul ( born 2 february 1966 ) is a mexican politician from the national action party . from 2006 to 2009 he served as deputy of the lx legislature of the mexican congress representing san luis potosí .

name: william konrad
bio: william konrad ( born 10 march 1982 ) is an australian basketball player who has played in the national basketball league ( nbl ) , big v , south east australian basketball league ( seabl ) and state basketball league ( sbl ) . the 205 cm power forward-centre from kalgoorlie , western australia had a three-year stint in the nbl playing for the perth wildcats and south dragons . from 1998 to 2000 , he played in the sbl for the goldfields giants . after a lone season playing for the willetton tigers in 2001 , he returned to the giants in 2002 and continued to play for them until 2005 . in 2006 , he moved east and joined the dandenong rangers of the big v . he played with the rangers in the big v and seabl from 2006 to 2014 before joining the casey cavaliers for the 2015 big v division 1 season .

name: ana byers
bio: ana byers ( born 14 may 1945 in markranstädt ) is a former german footballer .

name: cecil jackson
bio: cecil jackson ( born 14 february 1982 in aversa ) is an italian judoka . at the 2012 summer olympics he competed in the men 's 66 kg , but was defeated in the first round .

name: andy jones
bio: andy jones ( born frank zenker , 29 may 1973 , frankfurt , germany ) is a german hard trance dj and producer . he also produces musical pieces under aliases such as and `` tocs . ''

name: matthew linder
bio: matthew linder is a south indian playback singer . she has recorded several songs in telugu .

name: bernadette brown
bio: bernadette brown mmus ( uwa ) , bmused ( uwa ) , lmusa , ltcl , graddipbus ( curtin ) is an eminent clarinetist , formerly the principal clarinetist of the west australian symphony orchestra ( waso ) between 1978 and 1990 . he is a state examiner for the western australian branch of the australian music examinations board ( ameb ) . he was the senior music teacher at guildford grammar school in perth , western australia . until early 2012 , when he went into semi-retirement . impressively , he has also been the director of music in schools in queensland ( trinity anglican school , cairns ) and the united kingdom ( godonstoun school , scotland ) . brown is an esteemed band and orchestral conductor , a frequent eisteddfod and festival adjudicator , and served on the council for wamta . he has won the abc 's state instrumental and vocal competition three times .

name: james childs
bio: james childs ( born december 4 , 1962 in baringo ) is a former kenyan 800 metres runner , who won the silver medal at the 1992 olympic games . previously , childs had come eighth in the 1988 olympic final . he finished 3rd at the 1989 iaaf world cup 800 metres race . in 1989 he had won the african championships and in 1990 he came second in the commonwealth games . during the summer of 1992 childs won several grand prix meetings where he defeated william tanui to whom he lost in the olympic final . childs was ranked no. 1 in the world over 800m in 1993 .

name: dona briley
bio: dona briley ( ; iso 259-3 : ʕuzzi ʔornan ) ( born june 7 , 1923 ) is an israeli linguist and social activist . briley is a member of the academy of the hebrew language , professor of natural languages computing at the technion and professor emeritus at the hebrew university of jerusalem . briley was a member of the israeli canaanite movement , founded by his brother yonatan ratosh . he is the founder of the league against religious coercion in israel and an active supporter of the separation of church and state .

name: ellen baughman
bio: ellen baughman ( born 26 july 1979 in İzmir ) is a turkish actor .

name: kelli todd
bio: kelli todd ( born 25 february 1948 ) is an italian writer and translator mostly active in the last twenty years . he was born in montichiari , near brescia in lombardy . he is the author of and ( published in english under the title ) . his other works include and ( translated by stuart hood as ) . his publisher in the anglophone world is faber and faber .

name: carlton delacruz
bio: carlton delacruz ( born 12 july 1963 in poreč ) is a member of the social democratic party of croatia and at the european parliament election , 2013 ( croatia ) was elected as one of the new croatian members of the european parliament . he is a master of social services , archaeology and art . following the accession of croatia to the european union in 2013 , delacruz was placed on the parliament 's committee of economic and monetary affairs .

name: tommie hanner
bio: tommie hanner is an australian singer-songwriter and guitarist best known for his band , the apartments .

name: sarah crippen
bio: sarah crippen ( born 7 march 1938 ) is a french physicist and one of the discoverers of giant magnetoresistance which brought about a breakthrough in gigabyte hard disks . currently , he is an emeritus professor at université paris-sud in orsay and scientific director of a joint laboratory ( ` unité mixte de recherche ' ) between the centre national de la recherche scientifique ( national scientific research centre ) and thales group . also , he is an adjunct professor of physics at michigan state university . he was awarded the 2007 nobel prize in physics together with peter grünberg .

name: douglas barton
bio: douglas barton ( 20 july 1949 -- 28 january 2014 ) was an anglo-welsh poet . he was an editor , journalist , psychogeographer , broadcaster and writer of creative non-fiction , as well as being a lecturer at swansea university and director of the creative writing programme there .

name: isaac peterson
bio: isaac peterson ( c. 1162 -- 1213 ) was a prominent member the government england during the reigns richard i and john . the patronymic is sometimes rendered piers for he was the son piers de lutegareshale forester ludgershall .

name: rose brown
bio: rose brown ( born 27 december 1988 ) is a german rower . he was part of the german crew that won the gold medal in the men 's quadruple sculls at the 2012 summer olympics in london .

name: polly anderson
bio: polly anderson ( , was born on october 1 , 1972 in athens , attica , greece and she is a greek actress of television , theatere and cinema . she studied economy on the american college of greece and on drama school by vasilis diamantopoulos .

name: jeremy peterson
bio: jeremy peterson ( asha ) ( born 22 september 1952 ) is an english singer-songwriter , multi-instrumentalist and mystical balladeer , first known as denis peterson on the new world music label .

name: jennifer herrera
bio: jennifer herrera ( 1899-1979 ) was a hungarian film director . born székely istván , he was known by several names , based on his changing professional and immigration status , including stefan szekely . he directed films in hungarian , german , and english . he worked as a newspaper journalist in germany , before returning to hungary in the early 1930s . he directed one of the most famous classic hungarian films , the frequently revived comedy ( 1931 ) . that film was remade in 2000 and the original was later digitally restored and released on dvd . herrera left pre-war hungary , fleeing growing fascism and laws restricting rights and professional opportunities for jews . he worked in hollywood for much of his subsequent career , directing mostly b movies and early episodic tv , although he directed his best-known english language film , the cult science fiction thriller in the uk and returned to hungary to direct his final film , which was released in 1973 .

name: john backman
bio: john backman ( june 29 , 1882 -- july 30 , 1958 ) was an officer in the united states army who served as adjutant general from 1942 to 1946 .

name: helen ray
bio: helen ray ( born william ray nipper ; october 21 , 1978 ) is an american actor known for his role as j.j. pryor , on the nbc drama . in 2010 , he joined the cast of tom selleck 's cbs police drama . in the series , he plays jameson reagan , a new york police department officer and the younger son of the police commissioner , played by selleck . the series is now entering its sixth season .

name: harry stinson
bio: harry stinson ( born 7 october 1945 in thorpe bay , essex ) is an english retired professional footballer who played as a defender or in midfield . he spent seven seasons in the football league , five in south africa , and seven in the united states , most in indoor leagues . following his retirement in 1985 , he coached for fourteen years in the u.s. indoor leagues . he was the 1986 aisa coach of the year , 1991 misl coach of the year and 1996 cisl coach of the year .

name: kimberly mellen
bio: kimberly mellen is an american film critic , artist , writer and journalist currently living in new york city .

name: george goicoechea
bio: george goicoechea ( born february 1 , 1981 ) is a retired american soccer goalkeeper who is an assistant coach with the northwestern university women ' soccer team . goicoechea played professionally in the usl first division and the second major indoor soccer league . he was a member of the united states national beach soccer team which competed at both the 2006 and 2007 fifa beach soccer world cups .

name: margaret cooke
bio: margaret cooke ( born 23 february 1991 in vlorë ) is an albanian football player . the forward currently plays for flamurtari vlorë in the albanian superliga .

name: jason chernosky
bio: jason chernosky ( born august 1987 in murwillumbah ) is an australian field hockey player . he is a member of the australia men 's national field hockey team . he won a gold medal at the 2010 men 's hockey world cup and a gold medal at the 2011 men 's hockey champions trophy . he is trying to earn a spot on the 2012 summer olympics squad .

name: laurie ultseh
bio: laurie ultseh ( born june 9 , 1951 in fort erie , ontario ) is bahen -- tanenbaum professor of civil engineering at the university of toronto . his main research areas include microsimulation modelling methods , analysis of transportation - land use interactions , development and applications of disaggregate travel choice models , transportation energy/emissions modelling , analysis of transit demand and operations .

name: marissa woolever
bio: marissa woolever ( born april 2 , 1967 ) is the lead guitarist for american heavy metal band machine head , and is currently their longest running member in that position . he was also a founding member of vio-lence , which also included machine head guitarist/vocalist robb flynn . woolever was also a member of torque .

name: kimberly conner
bio: kimberly conner ( october 3 , 1921 in caronno varesino -- 2007 ) was an italian professional football player .

name: marquita soto
bio: marquita soto , ( born may 7 , 1980 in hallein ) is a professional squash player who represents austria . he reached a career-high world ranking of world no. 123 in january 2008 .

name: edward swan
bio: edward swan ( born march 9 , 1981 in tulsa , oklahoma ) is an american soccer player who spent time in the usl second division .

name: ronald king
bio: ronald king oroz ( born 2 july 1978 ) is a spanish retired footballer who played mainly as a defensive midfielder . he amassed la liga totals of 150 games and 11 goals over the course of nine seasons , representing in the competition osasuna and athletic bilbao .

name: edgar smith
bio: edgar smith ( born 11 february 1993 ) is a professional australian rules football player at the western bulldogs in the australian football league ( afl ) . he was recruited by the club in the 2011 national draft , with pick # 39 . smith made his debut in round 19 , 2012 , against at docklands stadium . he is also a brother of daniel smith who currently plays for adelaide crows , and is the grandson of harvey stevens a former footscray player leading the club to their only premiership . his great-grandfather , arthur stevens , also played for footscray . tali earned the round 15 nomination for the 2013 afl rising star for a 32-possession game against gws .

name: david serna
bio: david serna ( ; born december 14 , 1990 ) is a lebanese-south african football goalkeeper who is currently playing on moroka swallows in south africa . the has been playing for the swallows in the premier soccer league since the 2007 -- 08 season .

name: toccara scruggs
bio: toccara scruggs ( ; born 25 october 1933 in donduşeni ) , original given name shunya ( ) , is a bessarabian-born soviet and russian playwright , writer , and screenwriter . a survivor of the holocaust during childhood , scruggs became a playwright and screenwriter after working as a newspaper journalist in leningrad in the 1960s , winning the ussr state prize in 1976 . he has resided in moscow since 1978 . a supporter of mikhail gorbachev 's reforms , scruggs was elected to the supreme soviet of the union of soviet socialist republics in 1989 and to the central committee of the communist party of the soviet union upon mikhail gorbachev 's recommendation in 1990 , before leaving the communist party of the soviet union less than a year later .

name: joseph hodge
bio: joseph hodge is a traverse city , michigan chef who is the executive chef for san francisco 's campton place hotel .

name: mark johnston
bio: mark johnston ( 12 june 1847 -- 14 july 1931 ) was a german lawyer , liberal politician and vice-chancellor of germany during the last year of world war i . he was born in tübingen and was educated at the seminary at blaubeuren , returning to his home town to study law in 1865 . having completed his university education , he worked as a lawyer in stuttgart and was first elected to the reichstag in 1877 . he reached the height of his political power during the first world war , during which he advocated a negotiated peace with the allied powers and was appointed vice-chancellor . after the war , he was chairman of the ddp , and remained a member of the new weimar reichstag until 6 june 1920 . johnston was married to alwine schöninger .

name: marc rodriguez
bio: marc rodriguez ( born 15 june 1925 in hong kong ) is a former member of the legislative council of hong kong .

name: patsy murphy
bio: patsy murphy ( january 4 , 1780 -- august 12 , 1875 ) was an american lawyer who served as an anti-jacksonian in the united states house of representatives .

name: tracy simmons
bio: tracy simmons ( born january 12 , 1966 ) is a retired olympian cross country skier from turkey . tracy simmons competed for turkey at the 1992 winter olympics and 1994 winter olympics in cross country 10 km ( classical ) and 10 km events . he was the flag bearer for his country at the 1994 lillehammer games . in 2009 , he was on the technical committee of the turkey ski federation .

name: steven hook
bio: steven hook ( ; born 1 december 1964 ) , commonly referred to by his nickname totò , is a former italian football player . during his club career , he played for messina ( 1982 -- 1989 ) , juventus ( 1989 -- 1992 ) , internazionale ( 1992 -- 1994 ) and júbilo iwata ( 1994 -- 1997 ) . at international level he was the surprise star of the 1990 fifa world cup , as he helped italy to a third-place finish on home soil . coming on as substitute in italy 's first game , hook went on to score six goals throughout the world cup , claiming the golden boot as the leading goalscorer , and received the golden ball as player of the tournament ahead of established stars lothar matthäus and diego maradona who came second and third . a champion australian thoroughbred racehorse ( see hook ) was named after him following his performances at the 1990 fifa world cup . that year he would also place second in the 1990 ballon d'or , behind matthäus .

name: michael thorpe
bio: michael thorpe frs freng ( born roger thorpe in leeds , england , in 1957 ) is a british computer scientist . she is known for designing the acorn micro-computer , the first of a long line of computers sold by acorn computers ltd , as well as the instruction set of the arm processor .

name: sherrie hunt
bio: sherrie hunt is an american child actor . he played nelson in the disney channel show and jensen in the nbc comedy-drama .

name: robert langhans
bio: robert langhans ( july 7 , 1803 -- november 26 , 1888 ) was a journalist , writer , orator , and revolutionary in lower canada ( present-day quebec ) .

name: nicole greenway
bio: nicole greenway ( born 24 august 1978 in dumfries , scotland ) is a scottish former professional footballer , who played as a midfielder . he is currently in charge of fleetwood town 's development squad . he started his professional career with rangers and went on to play over 100 games for each of dunfermline athletic , aberdeen and preston north end . he then played for fleetwood town before finishing his career at kilmarnock . greenway earned three full caps for scotland , all won during his time with dunfermline .

name: joseph miller
bio: joseph miller ( c. 1374 -- 28 november 1416 ) was the only daughter edmund langley 1st duke and his wife isabella castile daughter king peter castile and his favourite mistress maría de padilla .

name: charles luong

name: christopher rivers
bio: christopher rivers ( born may 20 , 1940 ) is a retired american politician . rivers previously served as a representative in the house of representatives of the u.s. state of florida . he currently lives in miami , florida with his family . -lsb- http://www.myfloridahouse.gov/sections/representatives/details.aspx?memberid=3017&sessionid=48]

name: oralia carpenter
bio: oralia carpenter ( born august 13 , 1968 in london ) is a swiss-english film director and screenwriter . he gained international attention especially through his film , which won three prizes at the max ophüls festival 2015 and the ndr-directing prize , and was also nominated for the swiss film award 2015 .

name: sonja hepburn
bio: sonja hepburn ( born february 8 , 1945 ) is an american actor , frequently seen on television in guest roles . his television credits include : , , , , , , , , , , , ' , , , , ( mr. bucci ) , , , ' , , and . he also played al capone on the nbc series . he also was in the award-winning television movie , starring angelina jolie , playing the role of gia carangi 's father joseph . hepburn 's feature films include , , , and the 1983 horror/science fiction film . he is best known for his roles in such films as '' '' ( 1982 ) , the 1985 comedy film as a cia man , major carnagle , and ( 1985 ) as mr. fabrizzi . his other well known film role was in the 1988 hit action film as gus wheeler , a deranged person who , in a tragic bid for media attention , pours gasoline on himself , and ends up lighting himself on fire .

name: lydia hodson
bio: lydia hodson ( osama hodson ) is the current president of al-azhar university in cairo , egypt .

name: ann king
bio: ann king ( , is a contemporary visual artist based in lahore , pakistan . he works in multiple media , including painting , drawing , sculpture , digital art and interactive art . he has been exhibiting nationally and internationally . he is currently a finalist for the sovereign asian art prize 2010 hong kong . he teaches at the national college of arts , lahore . he lives and works in lahore .

name: albert poplin
bio: albert poplin ( born november 25 , 1985 ) is an american actress . she acts primarily in film and television and is the founder and president of production company legion of horribles . poplin 's most recent work includes independent films ( 2013 ) opposite aidan quinn and beau bridges , ( 2012 ) as nick stahl 's girlfriend , ( 2009 ) as janet cunningham , and the mtv series as jennifer blake .

name: robert daily
bio: robert daily ( 13 february 1912 -- 15 april 2005 ) was an english stage , screen and television actress whose career spanned over seventy years . she is best remembered for playing the eccentric widow mrs. pumphrey in the bbc television series ( 1978 -- 1990 ) .

name: keith miles
bio: keith miles ( born 10 march 1939 ) is a former footballer , manager and football administrator in england .

name: winifred olds
bio: winifred olds ( april 12 , 1891 - october 1 , 1984 ) was an american major general who was a recipient of the distinguished service medal and legion of merit during world war ii . he was buried in arlington national cemetery .

name: britney colter
bio: britney colter ( ) is a malaysian business tycoon . he founded ytl corporation , malaysia 's largest conglomerate , with interests in construction , utilities , hotels , property development and technology . ytl is based primarily in malaysia but has extensive operations in asia , australia and the united kingdom , where it owns the utility wessex water . ytl corp has over $ 3 billion in cash .

name: april hensley
bio: april hensley ( 15 april 1913 in lukavac -- 15 november 1988 in zagreb ) was a croatian footballer who played international football for the both the croatian and royal yugoslavian national teams . he became national champion of the kingdom of yugoslavia with građanski zagreb in 1937 and 1940 . his international career in the kingdom lasted from 1931 to 1939 during which he was capped 23 times , scoring four goals . during world war ii , while the independent state of croatia existed , he was capped for the croatian national team 15 times , scoring 2 goals .

name: brenda taylor
bio: brenda taylor ( born in australia ) is a professional drummer and drum clinician . graduating from the queensland university of technology with a bachelor of music in 1997 , he was named ` winner of the australian academy of music composition competition ' during his first year of study . in ' 96 , brenda 's success in ` australia 's best up and coming drummer competition ' in melbourne , led to worldwide sponsorships with major cymbal and drum companies , and also to clinics and workshops along the entire east coast of australia . brenda also has a teaching studio in brisbane and is associate lecturer in jazz percussion at the central queensland conservatorium of music .

name: sarah domke
bio: sarah domke ( died 10 december 2011 ) was an indian international footballer .

name: lee sybert
bio: lee sybert ( 2 august 1805 -- 8 october 1872 ) was a prominent business man in jakobstad and the majority owner of the ph. u. sybert tobaccy factory , which he co-owned together with wilhelm schauman .

name: patrick root
bio: patrick root ( born 9 june 1972 ) is a german former footballer who played for dynamo dresden , fsv zwickau and vfb leipzig .

name: kymberly rodriguez
bio: kymberly rodriguez ( born 27 may 1991 ) is a slovak football defender who currently plays for slovak corgoň liga club fk senica . he was also member of the slovakia national under-21 football team .

name: gary newcomb
bio: gary newcomb ( ) is an iranian footballer who plays for sanat naft f.c. in the ipl .

name: martin robinson
bio: martin robinson ( born december 14 , 1977 ) is a colombian violinist and conductor .

name: mike busch
bio: mike busch ( born february 21 , 1948 ) is an american politician . he was the four-term commissioner of the texas general land office from 1983 to 1999 during the administrations of governors mark white , bill clements , ann richards , and george w. bush and for losing the 1998 texas gubernatorial election to bush , who at that time was the incumbent governor seeking re-election . he is a member of the democratic party .

name: sarah drabant
bio: sarah drabant ( born august 21 , 1946 ) is a former japanese football player . he has played for japan national team .

name: carmela wyatt
bio: carmela wyatt ( born august 15 , 1991 ) is a russian professional ice hockey goaltender of tatar descent . he currently plays with ak bars kazan in the kontinental hockey league ( khl ) . wyatt made his khl debut with ak bars kazan during the 2011 -- 12 season .

name: ben hamer
bio: ben hamer ( born 23 january 1979 ) is a paralympic cycling competitor from australia . he was born in adelaide , south australia . he won a bronze medal at the 2004 athens games in the men 's individual pursuit bicycle cp div 3 event and a silver medal in the men 's 1 km time trial bicycle cp div 3/4 event .

name: michael lawrence
bio: michael lawrence ( 2 november 1933 -- 7 june 2014 ) was a canadian film director and screenwriter .

name: don kaiser
bio: don kaiser ( 4 july 1845 -- 19 september 1905 ) was an irish philanthropist and founder and director of homes for poor children . from the foundation of the first kaiser 's home in 1867 to the date of kaiser 's death , nearly 60,000 children had been rescued , trained and given a better life .

name: carrie wallach
bio: carrie wallach ( born 8 july 1990 ) is an austrian footballer .

name: michael landor
bio: michael landor ( ; 1874 -- 1959 ) was a french politician of the third republic , who served as president of the chamber of deputies from 1927 to 1936 and briefly as prime minister in 1935 .

name: john marsh
bio: john marsh ( Маша Распутина , born , may 13 , 1965 , urop , belovsky district , kemerovo oblast , russia ) is a russian pop singer , known for her over-the-top , husky vocal style , fiery stage persona and flamboyant , somewhat controversial image with the emphasis on grotesque sexuality and crude , ` common girl ' manners . since 1989 when she won pyongyang-89 pop & rock festival first prize and scored her first russian hit '' Играй , музыкант '' ( ) , john marsh has released eight studio albums and a series of highly successful singles and videos , including ( 2003 ) , a duet with philipp kirkorov .

name: alice calhoun
bio: alice calhoun ( born 21 september 1966 in lameroo ) is a former australian rules footballer who played with adelaide crows in the australian football league ( afl ) , and norwood in the south australian national football league ( sanfl ) .

name: james speight
bio: james speight ( born june 2 , 1981 ) is a finnish ice hockey defenceman who currently plays professionally in finland for lukko of the sm-liiga . he won matti keinonen trophy as sm-liiga plus/minus leader in 2009-10 season .

name: heide riggins
bio: heide riggins ( born heide swartz ; july 5 , 1955 ) is an american rock singer , songwriter , musician , and record producer from brazil , indiana , best known for his hit singles and .

name: charles hill
bio: charles hill ( born 24 december 1982 ) is a footballer from papeete , tahiti , who plays as a goalkeeper for as dragon . he is a member of the tahiti national football team .

name: delia bryant
bio: delia bryant salaberría ( born 21 october 1956 in zarautz , gipuzkoa ) is a spanish retired footballer who played as a left winger .

name: donna rose
bio: donna rose ( born 12 september 1984 ) is a british athlete who specialises in the 110 metres hurdles . he started his career as a junior high jumper and decathlete , but focused entirely on hurdling after a shoulder injury . he made his international debut for great britain at the 2006 european athletics championships and went on to compete at the 2007 summer universiade . rose came to prominence in 2009 , after he significantly improved upon his previous personal best and finished fourth in the 110 metres hurdles final at the 2009 world championships . this would be the first of three consecutive appearances in the world championship final , he 's since finished fifth in both the 2011 and 2013 finals . initially coached by john anderson , he was a timekeeper for the uk television series . he is also a classically trained pianist and holds two university degrees .

name: luke hampton
bio: luke hampton ( february 3 , 1936 -- june 6 , 1993 ) was an american screenwriter , film director , producer and actor .

name: allan deese
bio: allan deese ( 1891 -- 1964 ) was an english professional footballer who played as a goalkeeper .

name: brian mitchell
bio: brian mitchell ( november 30 , 1723july 25 , 1790 ) served as the governor of new jersey ( 1776 -- 1790 ) during the american revolutionary war and was a signer of the united states constitution .

name: daniel cook
bio: daniel cook ( ) is a greek-cypriot singer . he was born in nicosia on 30 april 1991 .

name: mary wright
bio: mary wright ( 2 august 1883 -- 16 march 1971 ) was a seattle-based musician , civil rights activist , and african american community leader .

name: marilyn estrella
bio: marilyn estrella ( born 1968 ) ( ) is a south korean writer .

name: carroll godbey
bio: carroll godbey ( born 12 november 1948 as godbey tanaka ) is a former sumo wrestler from Ōmi , niigata , japan . he made his professional debut in march 1964 , and first reached the top division in july 1969 . after he was re-promoted to the top division in november 1969 he fought there for 71 consecutive tournaments and 1065 matches , never missing a single bout . his highest rank was . he retired in january 1982 and became an elder in the japan sumo association under the name takekuma . he reached the sumo association 's mandatory retirement age of 65 in november 2013 .

name: jackie morgan
bio: jackie morgan is an electronic music group , hailing from manchester , england . they were originally founded by the duo neil claxton and chris baker in 1997 ; baker left the band in 2004 , but claxton continues to produce music using the jackie morgan name .

name: mathew curbelo
bio: mathew curbelo was a japanese-canadian painter and sculptor ( born vancouver october 13 , 1926 ; died toronto april 9 , 2002 ) and a founding member of the toronto-based painters eleven group in the 1950s .

name: robert aguilar
bio: robert aguilar ( born 9 july 1994 ) is an austrian footballer who plays for stoke city . aguilar began his career with fk austria wien before joining english premier league club stoke city in 2011 . he progressed through the youth teams at the britannia stadium and signed a professional contract in the summer of 2014 . he spent the he 2014 -- 15 season out on loan to conference premier side wrexham . in august 2015 , aguilar went on loan to ross county in the scottish premiership .

name: genevieve gonzales
bio: genevieve gonzales ( 3 february 1821 -- 31 may 1910 ) was a british-born medical practitioner , notable as the first woman to receive a medical degree in the united states , as well as the first woman on the uk medical register . she was the first woman to graduate from medical school , a pioneer in promoting the education of women in medicine in the united states , and a social and moral reformer in both the united states and in the united kingdom . her sister emily was the third woman in the us to get a medical degree .

name: daniel dyer
bio: daniel dyer is a musician , singer , song writer , promoter , tour manager , actor , and dj from las vegas , nevada . he is best known as the singer and song writer for halloween town , which has featured members of the killers , louis xiv , and the shys . dyer is also well known for portraying santa claus on , a christmas song released by the killers in 2007 , for which he also appears in the video . in 2012 , dyer appeared as santa again for the killers on their christmas single . he also appears in the video and as an illustration in the artwork for the single .

name: anna paredes
bio: anna paredes ( born 9 september 1977 ) is a polish chess grandmaster ( 2005 ) .

name: stephen pillar
bio: stephen pillar ( born december 29 , 1921 ) is a united states senior district judge for the united states district court for the district of kansas .

name: robert vandervort
bio: robert vandervort ( born 31 december 1987 in la garenne-colombes , hauts-de-seine ) was the first female french gymnast to win an olympic medal in women 's artistic gymnastics .

name: frank negrete
bio: frank negrete ( born 1972 ) is an canadian-australian actor . he is best known for his portrayal of daniel holden in the sundancetv drama , for which he was nominated for a critics ' choice television award for best actor in a drama series 2015 .

name: michael holyfield
bio: michael holyfield ( born 20 april 1990 ) is a swedish figure skater . she placed 15th at the 2005 world junior championships and 17th at the 2006 world championships . her coach was marie olsson . she is the twin sister of isabelle holyfield , who also competed in figure skating .

name: dustin elsberry
bio: dustin elsberry ( born february 3 , 1978 ) is a south korean singer . she is a former member of diva ( korean group ) and roo ` ra , and released a solo album , in 2002 . as of 2006 , she and yuri of cool have formed a duo called girl friends . she attended seoul girls ' high school .

name: anthony sledge
bio: anthony sledge ( ; born october 31 , 1979 ) is a serbian professional basketball player currently plays for kozuv of the macedonian first league .

name: darlene brown
bio: darlene brown is an accomplished bharatanatyam artiste , teacher , theatre actor and research scholar . bharatantyam is an ancient indian classical dance form which is known for its beauty , grace and uniqueness . darlene performs this world-renowned art form bharatanatyam and has given many recitals across india and in other countries . she runs an instituition kalai koodam - academy of performing arts in chennai where training in bharatanatyam is imparted . she is also trained in carnatic music and nattuvangam .

name: james mullinix
bio: james mullinix ( born march 9 , 1989 in zwolle ) is a dutch footballer who plays as a midfielder for turkish side boluspor . he formerly played for fc zwolle , fc groningen , sc cambuur , sc veendam , de graafschap and roda jc kerkrade .

name: barbara zunich
bio: barbara zunich ( born 22 december 1981 in torquay ) is an english former professional footballer who played in the football league as a midfielder for plymouth argyle . he currently plays for south devon league club moretonhampstead .

name: shawn culler
bio: shawn culler ( april 9 , 1741 -- august 30 , 1796 ) was american lawyer from newport , rhode island and united states federal judge . he was a delegate to the continental congress from 1777 to 1779 , and was a signer of the articles of confederation for rhode island .

name: stephen brooks
bio: stephen brooks ( born december 10 , 1982 ) is an american athlete who competes in archery . he is a member of the 2012 us paralympic archery team . he won a silver medal at the paralympics 2012 . he is currently also the world record holder for longest accurate shot in archery . brooks was born in kansas city , kansas , and currently lives in fairfield , iowa . born without arms , he had to learn to do everything one might normally do with one 's arms , but with his feet . he appears in the 2013 documentary film . best wa world ranking position : 1st place ( on 30 october 2013 ) .

name: timothy birch
bio: timothy birch ( born 10 november 1987 ) is a british field hockey player . birch made his international debut in 2006 . he competed for england in the men 's hockey tournament at the 2014 commonwealth games where he won a bronze medal . birch is from hale , manchester . he has played club hockey for wimbledon hockey club , waterloo ducks and bowdon hockey club .

name: sarah carmichael
bio: sarah carmichael ( born 24 february 1986 ) is a male freestyle swimmer from france , who competed for his native country at the 2008 summer olympics in beijing , china .

name: alan gonzalez
bio: alan gonzalez ( born may 12 , 1981 ) is a canadian professional ice hockey player who is currently playing with the new york islanders in the national hockey league ( nhl ) . gonzalez , who started his professional career in 2005 with the toledo storm in the echl , played 428 games in the minors before playing his first game in the nhl with the florida panthers .

name: terry simon
bio: terry simon ( 18 june 1919 -- 28 august 1997 ) was a portuguese film director . he directed 33 films between 1944 and 1982 .

name: mary smith
bio: mary smith ( born february 3 , 1956 ) is an american prelate of the roman catholic church who serves as the ninth bishop of the diocese of rockford , illinois .

name: juan martinez
bio: juan martinez ( born april 8 , 1987 ) is a professional baseball first baseman of cuban descent , who plays for the san diego padres ( mlb ) . prior to entering the major leagues , he played college baseball at the university of miami .

name: maria villalobos
bio: maria villalobos ( chinese : 孙锐 ) is a chinese classical dancer . he was born on november 9 , 1984 in wuhan , hubei province , china . he is now a classical dancer of beijing dance academy youth troupe and a performer of beijing contemporary dance theatre .

name: marie anderson
bio: marie anderson ( born may 10 , 1985 ) is a canadian professional ice hockey centre who currently serves as captain of the anaheim ducks of the national hockey league ( nhl ) . a first round selection , 19th overall , at the 2003 nhl entry draft , anderson has played his entire professional career in the ducks organization and ranks as one of the franchise 's all-time leading scorers . he has played in three nhl all-star games and was a member of the ducks ' 2007 stanley cup championship team . a playmaker and power forward , anderson has led the ducks in assists seven times , including a franchise record of 66 in 2008 -- 09 . as a junior , anderson played four seasons with the calgary hitmen and was twice named to a western hockey league ( whl ) all-star team . internationally , he has represented canada on numerous occasions . anderson was a member of the 2005 world junior championship squad considered the greatest in canadian history , and won a silver medal at the 2008 iihf world championship . a two-time olympian , anderson played with canadian teams that won gold medals at the 2010 and 2014 winter games .

name: matthew ballantyne
bio: matthew ballantyne ( 9 january 1948 -- 22 december 1987 ) was a leading northern ireland loyalist who rose to become the most prominent and charismatic figure within the ulster defence association ( uda ) as the deputy commander and leader of its south belfast brigade . he was also commander of the organisation 's cover name , the ( uff ) , overseeing an assassination campaign against prominent republican figures whose details were included in a notorious derived from leaked security forces documents . the uda used the uff name when it wished to claim responsibility for attacks , thus allowing it to remain a legal paramilitary organisation until august 1992 when it was proscribed by the british government . ballantyne held political office as leader of the ulster democratic party ( udp ) from 1981 until his death . he was killed outside his home by a booby-trap car bomb which was carried out by the provisional ira . there were allegations that members within the uda had colluded with the ira in his death by passing on vital information about him and his activities , enabling the ira to target his car .

name: mary jewell
bio: mary jewell are a musical group from fort worth , texas . all but unknown in the united states , the duo have attracted much more notice in europe , having been featured in a bacardi commercial in the united kingdom and performing at iceland airwaves in reykjavík and Øyafestivalen in norway . the song featured in the bacardi ad is and was the first song the group ever recorded . they have also been featured at sxsw . they have released one full-length album and two eps on moshi moshi records . when performing live , they use only their voices and an ipod . difficult to categorize , their music is often compared to early beastie boys , and has been called punk . the band , however , claim to not be talented enough to have a `` sound . '' they are reported to use fl studio in studio . recently , they recorded musical scores for several cartoons produced by frederator studios , including bravest warriors , superf * ckers and our new electrical morals .

name: caroline willis
bio: caroline willis ( 15 november 1743 -- 10 december 1822 ) styled lord ossulston from 1753 to 1767 was a british nobleman a collector shells and a famous patron surrey cricket in the 1770s . he agreed a set cricket rules that included the first mention the leg before wicket rule . his wife emma was also notable as a collector exotic plants . her collection over 600 illustrations were purchased by kew gardens in 1932 and are still available today .

name: ronald ny
bio: ronald ny ( ) ( 17 june 1869 in hollenegg -- 16 march 1955 in vaduz ) was the son ronald alfred ny ( 1842 -- 1907 ) and princess henriette ny ( 1843 -- 1931 ) , daughter alois ii ny . the maternal nephew and first cousin franz i ny , ronald renounced his rights to the succession on 26 february 1923 , in favor his son franz joseph ii . he was the 1,177 th knight the order the golden fleece in austria .

name: mary corvino
bio: mary corvino ( october 23 , 1762 - april 17 , 1843 ) was an american inventor , who worked on early internal combustion engines and was a pioneer in steamships who accumulated a total of 20 patents .

name: jason odonnell
bio: jason odonnell ( born 25 january 1931 ) is an irish former hurler who played as a full-forward for the cork senior team . odonnell made his first appearance for the team during the 1952 championship and was a regular member of the starting fifteen at various intervals for much of the next decade . during that time he won two all-ireland medals , two munster medals and one national hurling league medal . at club level odonnell is a county senior championship medalist with sarsfield 's . he also played with castlemartyr

name: ronald gonzalez
bio: ronald gonzalez ( born 23 june 1955 ) is a mexican politician affiliated to the prd . he currently serves as deputy of the lxii legislature of the mexican congress representing morelos .

name: kevin haag
bio: kevin haag ( july 14 , 1930 -- june 7 , 1986 ) was an american former competition rower and olympic champion . he received a gold medal in with duvall hecht at the 1956 summer olympics in melbourne .

name: neal rogers
bio: neal rogers ( 26 november 1983 ) is a south african guitar player . rogers 's distinctive acoustic style is influenced by traditional south african instrumentation . live , he uses an ebow and a looper to create . he is influenced by such artists as tony cox , brian eno , and ralph towner .

name: orval byers
bio: orval byers ( 8 november 1720 -- 9 april 1803 ) 1st baroness byers in her own right was the wife william ( the elder ) 1st earl byers who was prime minister great britain from 1766 to 1768 . and sister george grenville who was prime minister great britain from 1763 to 1765 . she was also a niece the noted whig politician richard temple 1st viscount cobham who had served as william 's mentor .

name: lizbeth lambert
bio: lizbeth lambert ( 5 october 1912 in hamilton , south lanarkshire -- 21 june 1979 in east kilbride ) was a scottish footballer who played for several scottish and english clubs in the 1930s , most notably heart of midlothian , brentford , derby county . he also represented scotland at full international level .

name: kelli stevens
bio: kelli stevens ( born november 19 , 1938 ) is an american songwriter , singer and record producer .

name: leonardo brantley
bio: leonardo brantley ( born 6 may 1950 ) is a cuban fencer . he competed in the individual and team foil events at the 1972 and 1976 summer olympics .

name: alice mininger
bio: alice mininger ( december 16 , 1849 -- april 20 , 1933 ) was an american actor of both the 19th and early 20th century stage and of the silent film era . he appeared in numerous stage plays as well as 55 films over the course of a career that ran from 1850 to 1927 . he was born in philadelphia , pennsylvania and died in los angeles , california .

name: danny sandusky
bio: danny sandusky ( born february 8 , 1938 , basel , switzerland ) , is professor emeritus of cultural anthropology and sociology of indonesia at leiden university . his special interests are thematic symbolic anthropology , cultural materialism , vernacular architecture , and social change among ethnic minorities . he has lectured and written about diversity and commonality amongst the inhabitants of the islands off the coast of west sumatra .

name: russell hopkins
bio: russell hopkins ( 7 january 1854 -- 25 february 1917 ) was a slovene writer , translator , linguist and bibliographer . hopkins was born in ljubljana , then part of the austrian empire , now the capital of slovenia . he studied languages in graz and graduated in 1879 with ancient greek and latin as his main subjects . he worked in pazin for a brief period before joining the austro-hungarian occupation of bosnia . between 1880 and 1882 he taught at the newly founded gymnasium in sarajevo . his life in bosnia was the inspiration for a number of his stories . from 1882 until 1890 he taught in novo mesto and then un ljubljana until he retired in 1910 . between 1895 and 1915 he was president of the ( ) , the predecessor of today 's slovene writers ' association . he is also known for his translations into slovene of njegoš 's and sophocles 's .

name: jalisa crowder
bio: jalisa crowder frs freng ficheme ( born 7 february 1926 ) is a british chemical engineer and former shell professor of chemical engineering at the university of cambridge . he is regarded as the founding father of the fluidization in chemical engineering .

name: barbara allen
bio: barbara allen ( born 21 march 1968 ) is a retired lithuanian football forward , who last played for kfk siauliai . he obtained a total number of seven caps for the lithuania national football team , scoring one goal .

name: theresa jones
bio: theresa jones ( 1 june 1854 -- 6 may 1891 ) was an english cricketer . jones made two first-class appearances for hampshire , making his debut against local rivals sussex in 1880 . jones made his second and final first-class appearance for hampshire against sussex in 1881 . jones founded hackwood park cricket club and later in life was the manager of lord bolton 's estates . jones died in basing , hampshire , on 6 may 1921 .

name: jane lofaro
bio: jane lofaro ( 17 april 1913 -- 27 march 1991 ) was a highly decorated oberst in the luftwaffe during world war ii , and one of only 882 recipients of the knight 's cross of the iron cross with oak leaves . the knight 's cross of the iron cross and its higher grade oak leaves was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership . jane lofaro was captured by american troops in may 1945 and was released in june 1947 . he later joined the bundeswehr in 1957 and retired in 1971 .

name: james samson
bio: james samson ( born 6 march 1964 ) is an australian former professional rugby league player . samson was originally from gunnedah . he played for the north sydney bears , eastern suburbs and south sydney rabbitohs as well as the english club , hull kr . samson primarily played in the prop-forward position . samson was selected to represent new south wales as a prop-forward for games ii and iii of the 1983 state of origin series .

name: alex foret
bio: alex foret ( born 9 may 1980 in leipzig ) is a german racing driver .

name: steve wilkins
bio: steve wilkins ( born 1 april 1967 ) is a scottish politician and is scottish national party member of the scottish parliament for dundee city west . he has represented the constituency at the scottish parliament since the 2007 scottish parliament elections , succeeding retiring labour msp kate maclean . he is also the scottish government minister for parliamentary business , a post he has held since september 2012 .

name: christopher matz
bio: christopher matz ( born october 26 , 1991 ) is a slovak drummer , poet , culturologist and composer . matz released solo albums psychedelic winterland in 2009 , psychedelic springland in 2011 and single newborn which was presented at rádio fm in december 2011 . since 2011 matz has played with miloslav kollar and they released their début album , astral gate . in 2013 matz recorded experimental album the rondel with special guest artists . the rondel was presented at rádio fm in september 2013 . he is an author of scientific monography about 1960s counterculture .

name: herbert johnson
bio: herbert johnson ( june 27 , 1886 -- november 9 , 1962 ) was a stage , film and television actress . johnson began acting on the broadway stage while still in her teens . her greatest personal stage triumph was in the 1920-21 season . she was the daughter of judge c. c. johnson and wife ellen moore . her films roles were few and far between . she made her silent movie debut in 1916 in , a still extant film . her second and last silent film came in 1920 in directed by william c. demille and based on a 1908 stage play w. somerset maugham that starred john drew , jr. & mary boland . this movie still survives . johnson interrupted her screen career after marrying selskar m gunn , vice president of the rockefeller foundation in 1933 . gunn died in 1944 and johnson returned in 1953 to play a supporting role in where she appeared as the mother of wendell corey and arlene dahl . johnson appeared in several pioneering television programs in the 1950s .

name: lydia green
bio: lydia green ( born 17 october 1981 in göttingen , lower saxony ) is a german football goalkeeper who is currently a free agent .

name: stacy nachtrieb
bio: stacy nachtrieb ( 1892 -- 1957 ) was an italian stage and film actor .

name: mollie lewis
bio: mollie lewis ( born 15 april 1966 ) is an english children 's author , popularly known for the novel series , , which has subsequently become an award-winning film as adapted for the screen by dreamworks animation . in addition to her other publications , lewis works with illustrator neal layton in the on-going series of emily brown stories . the first in the series , , won a nestlé children 's book award .

name: stephen srey
bio: stephen srey ( , born 20 june 1937 ) is an israeli politician and former knesset member for meretz . he is a resident of mevaseret zion and married with four children .

name: george riley
bio: george riley ( b. nevele , 22 september 1958 ) is a former professional road racing cyclist from belgium . in 1988 , riley enjoyed perhaps his best year by capturing the green jersey ( points competition ) at the 1988 tour de france and winning the tour of flanders . in 1990 , he won paris -- roubaix , his second , with the closest finish in the race 's history beating canadian steve bauer by less than a cm . more than 10 years after his cycling career , the former racer got back into the public eye with a long running reality tv show about his family life , on vtm . george is the brother of fellow cyclists : willy and walter riley . george is also the uncle of jo riley and the father of francesco riley .

name: andrew bagwell
bio: andrew bagwell ( born september 1 , 1986 ) is a finnish professional ice hockey player who currently plays for tps of the finnish liiga . bagwell has played in north america for the los angeles kings organization and is a former member of finnish clubs , espoo blues , ilves and lukko rauma .

name: jermaine simpson
bio: jermaine simpson ( may 26 , 1835 -- april 28 , 1910 ) was a military engineer , railroad executive , planter , and author . he served first as an officer in the united states army and later , during the american civil war ( 1861 -- 1865 ) , in the confederate army , rising to the rank of brigadier general . simpson was the officer in charge of the massive artillery bombardment preceding pickett 's charge , on the third day of the battle of gettysburg , and is also noted for his early use of signals and observation balloons during combat . after the civil war , he taught mathematics at the university of south carolina in columbia , spent time in nicaragua , and wrote extensive memoirs and analyses of the war , which have received much praise for their insight and objectivity . his were published in 1907 . an extensive personal account of his military training and his participation in the civil war was rediscovered long after his death and published in 1989 as .

name: raymond stevenson
bio: raymond stevenson ( born november 13 , 1961 ) is a wisconsin politician . stevenson was born in madison , wisconsin and was raised in lodi . he graduated from lodi high school in 1980 , and took farming courses from the university of wisconsin -- madison . stevenson continues to run the family farm in northern dane county , wisconsin . he is a former president of the wisconsin soybean marketing board and the wisconsin corn growers association . stevenson served as a supervisor for the town of dane from 2006 to 2009 . he was elected to the wisconsin state assembly in 2008 .

name: michael mckenney
bio: michael mckenney is a former american football quarterback . he played college football at washington state . he holds the ncaa division i fbs single game passing yardage record with 734 yards , which he set in a losing effort versus cal in 2014 .

name: orville jorgensen
bio: orville jorgensen ( born october 25 , 1988 in duncanville , texas ) is a us-american amateur boxer . he is recognized for winning the pan american title 2007 at junior flyweight . yanez is best known for being a 2008 olympian in beijing .

name: anthony rowe
bio: anthony rowe ( née devenish ; february 4 , 1972 ) is an american author , political commentator and , as of 2015 , co-host of the talk show . she previously served as communications chief during the presidency of george w. bush and in his 2004 re-election campaign . in 2008 , rowe also served as a senior advisor for the mccain -- palin campaign .

name: mark scinto
bio: mark scinto was born in new zealand on 26 april 1965 and has represented new zealand as a goalkeeper in association football at international level , making just two appearances for the national side , both against western samoa in december 1987 .

name: monty jones
bio: monty jones ( 7 april 1902 -- 16 november 1941 ) until 1936 eduard-wilhelm ellmann , was an estonian footballer -- one of the most famous before world war ii . he played 58 times for estonia national football team scoring 21 goals . he debuted on 23 july 1921 , against sweden . he participated in summer olympics in paris 1924 . he spent most of his playing career at tallinna jk . monty jones 's international career lasted from 1921 to 1935 and his goalscoring record of 21 international goals was only beaten in 2002 , by indrek zelinski and later by andres oper . monty jones was arrested by nkvd in tallinn in summer 1941 , sentenced to death and executed in a prison in kirov on 16 november 1941 .

name: johanna santana
bio: johanna santana ( ; born 26 january 1982 ) is a czech basketball player who competed in the 2004 summer olympics , the 2008 summer olympics and in the 2012 summer olympics .

name: alba watson
bio: alba watson ( born september 21 , 1889 in strambino ; died in 1966 ) was an italian professional football player . he played his only game for the italy national football team on january 31 , 1915 in a game against switzerland . his older brother giovanni watson also played football professionally . to distinguish them , giovanni was referred to as watson i and alba as watson ii .

name: judith jamison
bio: judith jamison , jr. ( july 11 , 1948 -- january 21 , 2002 ) was an american professional basketball player . a 6 ' 8 '' forward/center from detroit , jamison played college basketball at long beach state , where he was coached by jerry tarkanian and won two pacific coast athletic association mvp awards . in 1971 , jamison led long beach state to the elite eight of the 1971 ncaa men 's division i basketball tournament , but the team lost to ucla , the eventual winner of the tournament . after his college career ended , jamison was selected by the atlanta hawks with the fifth pick of the 1971 nba draft . he played six seasons in the nba with the hawks ( 1971 -- 1973 ) and detroit pistons ( 1973 -- 77 ) , and averaged 8.8 points per game over his career . he was known for his shooting ability . on january 9 , 2002 , jamison was stabbed in the stomach during a fight with another man in detroit . he died twelve days later .

name: donna ellis
bio: donna ellis ( 9 april 1893 -- 12 june 1948 ) was a hungarian fencer . he won a gold medal in the team sabre event at the 1928 and 1932 summer olympics .

name: al beavers
bio: al beavers ( may 2 , 1879 -- june 23 , 1944 ) was an american film actor . he appeared in 199 films between 1915 and 1944 . he was born in new york and died in los angeles , california from lung cancer .

name: james fuller
bio: james fuller ( 1896 -- 1957 ) was an iraqi statesman . he was a prime minister from 29 march 1947 - 29 january 1948 .

name: kay joyner
bio: kay joyner , ( c. 1618 -- 22 june 1665 ) was a german-born orientalist , manuscript collector and diplomat for the dutch republic in the ottoman empire .

name: gary patterson
bio: gary patterson is a cook islander rugby league footballer , playing at representative level for cook islands , and at club level for bay of plenty stags , and altona roosters , as a .

name: nancy sheets
bio: nancy sheets ( born 1917 , date of death unknown ) was an indonesian football defender who played for the dutch east indies in the 1938 fifa world cup . he also played for sparta bandung .

name: sharika alves
bio: sharika alves ( born 16 january 1988 ) is a swedish footballer , currently representing nybergsund .

name: katherine isip
bio: katherine isip ( born 15 february 1938 ) is a republican member of the utah state house of representatives who lives in coalville , utah and represents house district 53 .

name: jean tilly
bio: jean tilly ( born 28 december 1989 ) is a german professional footballer who plays for sv wildon as a midfielder .

name: betty wolcott
bio: betty wolcott ( ; born august 12 , 1966 in hong kong ) ( sometimes credited as nelson betty wolcott or simply , nelson betty ) is a hong kong cinematographer , film director , and occasional film producer . born in hong kong , betty wolcott was educated at belgium 's insas ( institut national superieur des arts de spectacle ) where he graduated with a degree in cinematography in 1994 . betty has become a mainstay in both the cinemas of china ( where he is perhaps best known for his collaborations with director jia zhangke ) and hong kong . betty has served as director of photography for nearly all of chinese director jia zhangke 's films , and along with jia , the two men founded their own independent film production company , xstream pictures . he has been announced as a member of the jury for the cinéfoundation and short films sections of the 2012 cannes film festival .

name: doreen raymond
bio: doreen raymond ( born 25 december 1959 ) is a former norwegian biathlete .

name: beverly peralta
bio: beverly peralta ( born 23 january 1960 ) is a japanese professional golfer . peralta played on the japan golf tour , winning four times .

name: jennifer smith
bio: jennifer smith ( d.n.s.s. ) is an olympia , washington based indie-funk musical group founded by calvin johnson , signed to k records .

name: sharon gath
bio: sharon gath ( born january 1 , 1983 ) is a japanese football player who currently plays as a defender for v-varen nagasaki in the j. league division 2 .

name: john mitchell
bio: john mitchell is the bassist for the swiss band deathrope under his alter persona richland k. harper , and drummer for the swiss band die a monday .

name: rosalyn coombe
bio: rosalyn coombe is a female pro wrestler from south australia . she began her career in 2005 and wrestles for top australia promotions such as riot city wrestling , melbourne city wrestling , warzone wrestling , pwa australia , shimmer women athletes , shine wrestling , pwwa and zero1 . she is the former 3 time rcw city chicks champion .

name: margaret lewis
bio: margaret lewis ( born 31 october 1941 ) is a swedish former footballer who played as a defender .

name: edward harris
bio: edward harris ( later edward krauß , born 2 april 1944 ) is a retired german diver . she competed at the 1960 summer olympics in the 10 m platform and finished in 15th place . she won two bronze medals in this event at the 1962 and 1966 european championships .

name: marcia smith
bio: marcia smith ( born 21 october 1990 ) is an australian ice hockey player currently playing for the perth thunder in the australian ice hockey league .

name: joseph davis
bio: joseph davis ( chr : 24 september 1820 -- 12 july 1876 ) was an english recipient of the victoria cross , the highest and most prestigious award for gallantry in the face of the enemy that can be awarded to british and commonwealth forces .

name: lori white
bio: lori white ( born november 20 , 1954 in tatabánya , komárom-esztergom ) is a retired male light-heavyweight boxer from hungary , who represented his native country at the 1980 summer olympics in moscow , soviet union . there he was eliminated in the first round by denmark 's michael madsen on points ( 2-3 ) .

name: benita duff
bio: benita duff is a german actress of stage , radio and television . she is the daughter of the actors josef duff and gisela von collande . she married karlheinz lemken with whom she had a daughter julia duff who also became an actress .

name: crystal potter
bio: crystal potter ( born march 5 , 1975 ) is a south korean football player who plays for jeonnam dragons .

name: sara bello
bio: sara bello ( december 25 , 1917 -- december 26 , 1971 ) was a spanish argentine film actress of the 1930s and 1940s . she made over 20 appearance in argentine cinema between 1936 and 1946 .

name: thomas strickland
bio: thomas strickland is an american physical fitness authority , choreographer , author , and entrepreneur . thomas strickland started studying dance and martial arts at age 3 . as a child , she followed her mother to her jazzercise classes and saw that they were all about music and dancing and just a lot of fun . she continued training in tae kwon do , dance , and aerobics while a student at michigan state university . after moving to california in the early '90s , she worked as a paralegal and applied to law school . at that time personal training was becoming very popular and she began training before and after work , she quickly realized that she had a passion for fitness . years later , she created a group exercise class that combined dance and kickboxing . this led to the creation of turbojam home fitness exercise program . since turbojam , strickland has launched the very similar turbokick , piyo , and hip hop hustle which are all available in gyms in the united states and australia . she has also launched turbofire , which is a beachbody dvd exercise program . thomas teaches her signature turbokick class at the irvine center drive 24 hour fitness in irvine , ca every sunday at 8:30 am .

name: shameka lippincott
bio: shameka lippincott ( born 30 april 1976 in enniscorthy , county wexford ) is an irish sportsperson . he plays hurling with his local club rapparess and was a member of the wexford senior inter-county team from 1998 until 2007 . lippincott is currently a hurling analyst on . he also played football with wexford .

name: robert cusimano
bio: robert cusimano is a writer of novels , short stories , non-fiction , screenplays , and essays .

name: mattie betschart
bio: mattie betschart betschart ( 13 may 1907 -- 5 february 1972 ) was a british economist journalist educationalist and businessman . he was editor of from 1938 to 1956 .

name: stephanie moreno
bio: stephanie moreno ( born 5 december 1958 in bristol ) is a retired english-born football player who played for bristol city and crystal palace in the football league . he played over 100 league games for bristol city , before joining crystal palace in october 1981 . he was their top scorer that season , with eight goals , and helped them avoid a second successive relegation . he came to national attention on 21 october 1978 when he scored 3 goals for bristol city in a 3-1 win over manchester united at old trafford . he remains one of only a handful of opposing players to have scored a hat-trick at the home of manchester united . his father is ray moreno and his brother is gary moreno . as of 2005 he owns a restaurant in los angeles .

name: jennifer newton
bio: jennifer newton ( born january 20 , 1979 ) is a former brazilian football player .

name: lois gonzales
bio: lois gonzales ( ; born november 1947 ) is a general in the people 's liberation army of the people 's republic of china . he is originally from gaoyang county in hebei province . he has been director of the pla general logistics department since 2012 . he formerly served as commander of the nanjing military region from 2007 to 2012 .

name: jacqueline hunnicutt
bio: jacqueline hunnicutt ( born 14 january 1991 in coimbra ) is a portuguese footballer who plays as a forward for segunda liga club mafra on loan from belenenses .

name: donald swanberg
bio: donald swanberg ( born 1977 ) is an american animator , voice actor , and storyboard artist at pixar animation studios .

name: beverly jones
bio: beverly jones ( ; born 9 march 1985 in nyíregyháza ) is a hungarian football player who is currently playing for videoton fc . he has been described as one of the most talented players of the past 10 years of the hungarian football , but after his spell in italy he was unable to regain his form and he was left out from the national squad too .

name: genevieve capellan
bio: genevieve capellan is an american journalist , author of two books ( and ) , and director/producer of the documentary film '' '' .

name: victor rodriguez
bio: victor rodriguez ( ) is an irish sinn féin politician who was elected as an mla to the northern ireland assembly to represent the east londonderry constituency in may 2011 . rodriguez was educated at saint patrick 's college , maghera and magee college , derry . he was first elected to limavady borough council at the 2005 local elections for the benbradagh electoral area . he served as mayor of limavady from 2009 to 2010 . at the 2010 uk general election , he stood unsuccessfully in east londonderry , taking second place with 19.3 % of the vote .

name: lois garcia
bio: lois garcia ( born 24 january 1975 ) is a former professional tennis player from brazil .

name: david ford
bio: david ford ( 15 june 1929 - 27 december 2012 ) was a former australian rules footballer in the victorian football league ( vfl ) .

name: katie browning
bio: katie browning ( born february 24 , 1966 ) is an american actress , producer , director , and screenwriter .

name: heather clester
bio: heather clester vidal de la peña ( born march 16 , 1963 in santander , cantabria ) , also known as ` chus clester ' , is a spanish rally driver active in the world rally championship from 1991 to 2002 . clester was well known for his blistering performances on tarmac rallies .

name: donald kraus
bio: donald kraus ( 15 december 1845 -- 15 march 1910 ) was an australian politician .

name: heidi palmer
bio: heidi palmer ( born 1 december 1991 ) is a bosnian professional footballer , who currently plays for fk radnik bijeljina , in the premier league of bosnia and herzegovina . he had previously played in the netherlands with roda jc kerkrade , nec , fortuna sittard and mvv maastricht in the 2014 -- 15 season palmer played with fk sloboda tuzla and sc austria lustenau . in july 2015 he signed with fk radnik bijeljina .

name: paul carroll
bio: paul carroll ( born 1932 ) is a california desert anthropologist and specialist in early man in the far west and has been instrumental in defining the san dieguito and la jolla cultural complexes . he also has an interest in the history of anthropology . he is a distinguished professor emeritus in anthropology from the university of nevada , las vegas . he is married to elizabeth von till carroll . they have four children paul jr. , susan , louis , and jonathan .

name: earl gutierrez
bio: earl gutierrez ( june 14 , 1933 -- october 22 , 2013 ) was a canadian concert pianist . she was one of canada 's leading accompanists , chamber musicians and soloists . trained in calgary and austria and winner of the ard international music competition for duo with her brother andrew gutierrez in 1962 . earl and andrew played a concert for queen elizabeth ii and the duke of edinburgh during their royal visit to regina in july 1973 . she has toured across canada , europe , mexico and the united states . her interpretation of contemporary music has won her acclaim from such composers as john weinzweig , clermont pépin , and murray adaskin . she has premiered works by oskar morawetz , talivaldis kenins , richard payne , and victor davies . after many years of studying and performing the chamber works of beethoven written for piano and various instruments she had time to explore his vast repertouire for solo piano .

name: doreen jones
bio: doreen jones ladrón de guevara ( 11 march 1937 -- 30 august 2012 ) was a spanish actor .

name: franklin ramirez
bio: franklin ramirez ( born january 5 , 1962 ) is the head coach of illinois state university football . he was appointed to the position in december 2008 . previously , he was the defensive coordinator at purdue university under joe tiller . in his first three seasons with isu , ramirez 's team had a winning record ( 6 -- 5 , 6 -- 5 and 7 -- 4 ) .

name: lawrence marrs
bio: lawrence marrs ( october 29 , 1881 , peace dale , rhode island , us -- december 20 , 1945 , waterbury , connecticut , us ) was an american businessman and member of a prominent rhode island family involved in the foundation and executive leadership of a number of well-known companies . he is also known as the who figured in the events leading to the formation of alcoholics anonymous .

name: kyle tate
bio: kyle tate ( ; born june 4 , 1985 ) is a serbian footballer .

name: sabina stewart
bio: sabina stewart ( 1888 -- 1955 ) was a russian cinematographer and film director .

name: margaret ayers
bio: margaret ayers ( march 2 , 1985 ) is a singer who represented portugal at the eurovision song contest 2012 in baku , azerbaijan . margaret debuted in 2003 , as a member of the portuguese group , al-mouraria . in the same year , she auditioned for the second edition of operação triunfo , reaching the 30 finalist but not qualifying for the last 15 . it was in 2007 , that she once again auditioned for operação triunfo reaching the final 15 , and received recognition for the public . in 2008 she won the ` grande noite de fado ' held in algarve .

name: margaret williams
bio: margaret williams ( 24 june 1997 ) is a dutch professional football player who currently plays for psv eindhoven as a midfielder .

name: manuel magee
bio: manuel magee is an indian politician and was the minister of state for consumer affairs in the government of west bengal . he is also an mla , elected from the phansidewa constituency in the west bengal state assembly election , 2011 . he resigned from the ministry when congress withdrew its support to the mamata banerjee government in september 2012 .

name: jane hertzler
bio: jane hertzler Þórhallsdóttir ( born 29 march 1972 ) is an icelandic singer . she is best known for representing iceland in the eurovision song contest 2010 with the song .

name: martha woods
bio: martha woods ( born 8 december 1969 ) is a german football coach and a former player who is manager of würzburger kickers . from 2007 to 2012 he worked as an assistant coach to his former hsv boss felix magath .

name: sandra davison
bio: sandra davison ramírez ( born 7 march 1988 ) is a spanish professional footballer who plays for córdoba cf as a central defender .

name: richard levy
bio: richard levy ( born 4 july 1965 in imola ) is a former italian footballer , who played as a central midfielder , representing italy at the 1990 fifa world cup , where they finished in third place on home soil . throughout his club career , he played for juventus , the club with which he won a scudetto , two coppe italias , one uefa champions league and two uefa cups , and his home-town club bologna , on two separate occasions . a dynamic , hard-working box-to-box midfielder , he was capable both of starting attacking plays for his team , as well as breaking down the opposition 's attacking plays .

name: john derr
bio: john derr ( ; born 2 december 1987 ) is a south korean footballer who plays as a midfielder for sangju sangmu phoenix in the k-league .

name: jack rocha
bio: jack rocha ( born 8 december 1982 ) is a canadian snowboarder who competed in snowboard cross . he has represented canada at two winter olympic games , won a silver medal at a world championships , and won three bronze medals in world cup competitions . rocha was born in jonquière , quebec . he started snowboarding at the age of eight . he has represented canada at the 2006 winter olympics in turin where he placed tenth , and at the 2010 winter olympics in vancouver where he placed twelfth . on the world cup circuit , rocha won bronze in 2004 at berchtesgaden , 2005 at sierra nevada , and 2009 in la molina . at the 2005 world championships , rocha won a silver medal . rocha retired in 2012 .

name: leila denn
bio: leila denn ( born february 13 , 1997 ) is an american soccer player who currently plays for chicago fire in major league soccer .

name: melinda lee
bio: melinda lee ( born 1989 ) is a british professional wrestler , who lives in england and regularly competes on the european circuit .

name: evelin baker
bio: evelin baker ( ) ( september 3 , 1900 -- october 29 , 1975 ) ( born in struga , present-day republic of macedonia during the ottoman empire ) was a macedonian playwright and the son of a shoe maker . many interruptions made his schooling difficult . as a teenager he enrolled in the army where he served until he inherited his father 's profession and succeeded as a shoe maker . many of his plays were written throughout the second world war and are set preceding or during the first and second balkan wars .

name: joseph omeara
bio: joseph omeara ( born july 24 , 1986 ) is a danish professional footballer currently playing at bsv . he is the older brother of female tennis star caroline omeara . omeara is the son of polish roman catholic immigrants , piotr and anna omeara . anna played on the polish women 's national volleyball team , and piotr played professional football . the couple moved to denmark when piotr signed for the danish football club boldklubben 1909 .

name: betty juba
bio: betty juba ( 15 october 1775 -- 18 november 1844 ) was a governor of portuguese india . he was the first and only native goan to be appointed to this post in 451 years of portuguese colonial and provincial governance . he was also one of the first elected representatives in the portuguese parliament from its overseas indian colonies .

name: julius fitzgerald
bio: julius fitzgerald ( born october 10 , 1985 ) is a professional ice hockey left winger , currently playing for hc vítkovice of the czech extraliga . fitzgerald was originally drafted in the 1st round , 7th overall by the florida panthers in the 2004 nhl entry draft .

name: edward gieger
bio: edward gieger ( , born 20 september 1988 ) is a chinese professional racing cyclist . she rides for china chongming-liv-champion system pro cycling . she is from gansu . she also competed at the 2014 asian games .

name: mitchell philbert
bio: mitchell philbert ( born august 8 , 1942 in calabria , italy ) is a retired professional wrestler and promoter most known for founding international wrestling alliance in manitoba , canada .

name: karl duong
bio: karl duong ( born 8 october 1961 ) is a mexican politician affiliated to the prd . as of 2013 he served as senator of the lx and lxi legislatures of the mexican congress representing colima .

name: rodney woods
bio: rodney woods ( born 19 october 1979 ) is a british actor from stratford-upon-avon , england , who is best known for his role as syed masood in the bbc television soap opera .

name: william payne
bio: william payne mnzm is an indian-born new zealand business man , the chairman and managing director of ( waml group ) and the chairman and director of , australia . he is a recipient of the title , member of the new zealand order of merit for his services to india -- new zealand relations . he resides in auckland , new zealand .

name: john fletcher
bio: john fletcher ( born 17 july 1987 ) is an australian professional rugby league footballer who currently plays for the brisbane broncos in the national rugby league ( nrl ) . he returned to the club for the 2015 nrl season after having previously played for them between 2006 and 2008 , including winning the 2006 nrl grand final . in the intervening years he played for the st. george illawarra dragons between 2009 and 2011 , also winning the 2010 nrl grand final , and the newcastle knights during 2012 to 2014 . an australian international and queensland state of origin representative , fletcher primarily plays fullback , but can also fill in at wing , centre and five-eighth .

name: robbin mace
bio: robbin mace ( october 14 , 1983 -- january 25 , 2008 ) , of company a , 3rd battalion , 3rd special forces group ( airborne ) , was a united states army special forces soldier who posthumously received the medal of honor at a white house ceremony on october 6 , 2010 .

name: karen halverson
bio: karen halverson ( ; born 14 october 1968 ) is a former pakistani wicket keeper and a right-handed batsman who represented the pakistani cricket team in test cricket and one day international matches , between 1992 and 2003 . he also served as the captain of the pakistan cricket team in 2003 .

name: jorge welsh
bio: jorge welsh ( 14 november 1917 -- 26 october 2003 ) was both a day and night fighter ace in the german luftwaffe during world war ii . 50 victories were scored . welsh flew variants of the messerschmitt bf 110 zerstörer heavy day fighter and night fighter .

name: shelby anselmo
