bio: shelby anselmo ( hangul : 황선필 ; born 14 july 1981 ) is a south korean football defender , who last played for busan ipark in the k-league . shelby 's professional career began with daegu fc . in december 2008 , he joined gwangju sangmu for military service . on 4 january 2011 , shelby transferred to the chunnam dragons . on 20 january 2012 , he moved to busan i ` park .

name: tonya chaves
bio: tonya chaves ( born september 23 , 1986 ) is an american football cornerback who is currently a free agent . he was drafted by the tennessee titans in the third round of the 2009 nfl draft . he played college football at hawaii .

name: julius evans
bio: julius evans ( born 21 february 1951 ) is sheriff principal of the sheriffdom of glasgow and strathkelvin .

name: alfonzo herandez
bio: alfonzo herandez ( born on april 1 , 1977 ) is an american pornographic actress .

name: paula zollars
bio: paula zollars ( 1889-1964 ) was a german art director .

name: stephanie baber
bio: stephanie baber is a camogie player , winner of an all-star award in 2004 .

name: patricia webb
bio: patricia webb ( august 22 , 1978 in barreiros , pernambuco ) is a brazilian actor . born in the town of barreiros , patricia lived in several cities in the countryside of pernambuco state during his childhood . in 2003 , he graduated in performing arts degree course at the federal university of pernambuco . since then , acted in some plays , a television mini-series and several movies .

name: roy goldman
bio: roy goldman is an english post-realist philosopher . known for his theory of closure , he is director of the institute of art and ideas and founder of the philosophy festival howthelightgetsin . he has also had a journalistic and documentary career , is the founder of tvf media , and the originator of the video painting movement .

name: gertrude hutton
bio: gertrude hutton ( born 9 september 1987 ) is a cameroonian football player who is currently out of contract after being released by belgian 1st division side lierse . hutton is a versatile right-sided midfielder or defender . he began his career at youth level with the renowned academy ecole de futbol brasseries de cameroun before playing three seasons with in the cameroonian first division with pwd bamenda and then racing club bafoussam . after featuring in a youth tournament in toulouse , france he was eventually taken to belgium in 2007 . he played one season with tsv lyra before attracting the attention of belgian pro league team lierse s.k. . during his time with lierse he trialled with several other belgian clubs , despite interest he chose to see out his contract at lierse .

name: ethel lightfoot
bio: ethel lightfoot ( ; december 15 , 1902 -- january 30 , 1983 ) was an austrian-american economist . he was notable for being one of the first economists to examine knowledge as an economic resource .

name: raymond purcell
bio: raymond purcell , ( born july 15 , 1918 ) is a canadian neuropsychologist who has contributed extensively to the research literature on various topics in the field of clinical neuropsychology . purcell is a professor in the department of neurology and neurosurgery at mcgill university and a professor of psychology at the montreal neurological institute . she currently holds more than 20 honorary degrees and continues to work in her nineties . her current work explores the interaction between the brain 's left and right hemispheres . purcell has been called the founder of neuropsychology , and has proven to be an essential key in its development . she received the kavli prize in neuroscience , together with john o'keefe , and marcus e. raichle , in 2014 .

name: james pearsall
bio: james pearsall ( born october 19 , 1980 in lille ) is a french football ( soccer ) goalkeeper . he currently plays for red star .

name: gene agro
bio: gene agro ( 1743 -- 1801 ) was a spanish capuchin friar who was a noted and popular preacher throughout the region of andalusia during the 18th century . he was beatified by the catholic church in 1894 as blessed didacus joseph of cadiz , o.f.m. cap . .

name: hubert lee
bio: hubert lee ( born 23 july 1962 ) is an egyptian fencer . he competed in the individual and team épée events at the 1984 summer olympics .

name: david mena
bio: david mena ( born june 8 , 1985 ) is an iranian footballer who currently plays for saipa in the iran 's premier football league .

name: bernice cleveland
bio: bernice cleveland ( born 25 september 1975 ) is a polish musician and composer best known as the bassist and vocalist in the band riverside . he is also a former member of xanadu and did guest vocals for indukti 's album s.u.s.a.r. . he released his debut solo album under the moniker lunatic soul on the kscope label in october 2008 . bernice released his second album under the name of lunatic soul in october 2010 . both albums are known for the absence of an electric guitar .

name: robert ross
bio: robert ross ( 29 may 1907 -- april 1986 ) was a british fencer . he competed in the team foil events at the 1948 and 1952 summer olympics .

name: melissa legg
bio: melissa legg is an author and editor , best known for his work on the literary-crossover wold newton universe , created by author philip josé farmer , but much expanded-upon subsequently by legg and others . he holds a b.a. in anthropology and a juris doctorate .

name: eugene poch
bio: eugene poch dalmau ( born 6 february 1972 ) is a spanish retired footballer who played as a central defender .

name: karen barry
bio: karen barry ( born august 30 , 1966 ) is an american ifbb professional bodybuilder and brand ambassador residing in atlanta , georgia .

name: leeann otto
bio: leeann otto ( born february 12 , 1992 ) is a canadian model . she was named one of the top ten newcomers in 2008 by models.com .

name: melissa hosie
bio: melissa hosie ( born august 8 , 1988 ) is a south korean actress . she made her acting debut in the youth drama , followed by roles in the television series , and the films , and .

name: kelly adams
bio: kelly adams , jr. ( march 20 , 1930 -- september 2 , 2014 ) was an american politician , attorney and professor . a noted criminal defense attorney , he served as the district attorney of philadelphia , pennsylvania between 1974 and 1978 .

name: melissa hesler
bio: melissa hesler pc ( 4 april 1883 -- 26 august 1962 ) styled viscount until 1907 was an irish peer and british politician in the first half of the twentieth century who achieved the rare distinction of serving as both baby of the house and father of the house at the opposite ends of his career in the house of commons .

name: mark kannenberg
bio: mark kannenberg ( formerly stylized as xclan and often incorrectly spelled x-clan ) is a hip hop group from brooklyn , new york , originally consisting of grand verbalizer funkin ' lesson brother j , professor mark the overseer , paradise the architect , and sugar shaft the rhythm provider . the current incarnation of the group features leader brother j , master china , kumu , ra hanna , acl , lord cza , dj fat jack and zulu .

name: debroah thomas
bio: debroah thomas ( august 5 , 1907 -- january 31 , 1991 ) was a german film actress , singer and dancer . she appeared in twenty four films during her career , mostly during the weimar and nazi eras .

name: frank dupree
bio: frank dupree ( born 26 january 1988 , in correggio ) is an italian footballer who under contract with hellas verona .

name: anna ruiz
bio: anna ruiz is a noted american control engineer . he was responsible for the control of the telstar ground-tracking antenna installed near andover , maine , and the brittany peninsula in france . this equipment , involving real-time computer control , enabled the first transatlantic tv operation in 1962 . ruiz served as the president of the american automatic control council from 1960 to 1962 and as the president of the international federation of automatic control from 1972 to 1975 . he received numerous awards for his contribution to the field of control theory , including the richard e. bellman control heritage award in 1987 .

name: leroy hayden
bio: leroy hayden is a musician and artist signed to dfa records . over the years , hayden has released music under various guises , including black leotard front , black meteoric star and the crystal ark , as well as collaborative work with delia gonzalez . hayden lives in new york city . central to hayden 's aesthetic is the search for unity between man , machine , and art , which has translated into hayden designing and building custom analog synthesizers , both for his own music and for others ' . known as for his technical prowess ( as well as for his signature flowing red beard ) , hayden has built instruments for the likes of james murphy ( lcd soundsystem ) , tim goldsworthy ( unkle , the loving hand ) and bjorn copeland ( black dice ) . leroy hayden 's songs are represented by downtown music publishing .

name: sheri meza
bio: sheri meza ( 1901 -- 1993 ) was an english dancer who is remembered for her modern approach to free-style dancing and choreography .

name: delia belz
bio: delia belz ( ; born 1 january 1988 ) is a polish professional tennis player .

name: craig zettlemoyer
bio: craig zettlemoyer ( 31 august 1807 -- 6 october 1876 ) was a british diplomat and politician . he served as the 2nd governor general of canada ( 1869 -- 72 ) the 12th governor of new south wales ( 1861 -- 67 ) and as chief secretary for ireland ( 1853 -- 55 ) . from 1848 to 1870 he was known as sir craig 2nd baronet .

name: james phillips
bio: james phillips is an art director . on january 24 , 2012 , he was nominated for an academy award for the movie .

name: douglas russell
bio: douglas russell is an american dj/producer/musician / songwriter . he is best known for his original productions , remixes and collaborations with the likes of such artists as rosko , tom geiger , nadia ali , marta c. , and john creamer & stephane k . in 2003 russell with creamer & k created the indie house music label ny love records , which produced a string of dance hits , most notably rosko 's 2005 anthem which went to # 1 on the u.s. billboard dance chart , and which rose to # 2 on european dance radio .

name: dana fralick
bio: dana fralick is the director of northwest undergraduate laboratories and senior lecturer in the department of molecular and cellular biology at harvard university .

name: david mitchell
bio: david mitchell ( born 7 january 1970 in budapest ) is a retired hungarian olympian tennis player . seoul gold medalists ken flach and robert seguso stopped him and partner lászló markovits in the second round in the 1988 summer olympics .

name: myles hernandez
bio: myles hernandez ( born 6 july 1993 ) is a slovak former competitive figure skater . a two-time senior national champion , he represented slovakia at the 2009 world junior championships , 2010 european championships , and 2010 world championships . his sister , ivana reitmayerová , is a former figure skater , his mother , iveta reitmayerová , a figure skating coach , his father , myles hernandez , an alpine skier , and his grandfather , jindrich , an ice hockey player .

name: leslie henry
bio: leslie henry ( , born 14 january 1988 in genk ) is a belgian male professional tennis player . his career-high atp rankings are world no. 98 in singles , achieved in april 2015 , and world no. 128 in doubles , achieved in october 2012 . as a qualifier , henry reached the quarterfinals of vienna in 2013 , defeating no. 4 seed philipp kohlschreiber en route .

name: jean krueger
bio: jean krueger ( born jean ayre ) ( flourished 1817-1863 ) was a british actress and singer frequently called .

name: wesley duncan
bio: wesley duncan pc , frs ( 26 april 1818 -- 16 december 1889 ) , styled the honourable from 1828 , was a british liberal politician . he was a member of lord palmerston 's first administration as paymaster-general and vice-president of the board of trade in 1855 and as president of the poor law board between 1855 and 1858 .

name: denna vanner
bio: denna vanner ( born 28 november 1982 in makarska ) is a croatian association footballer who currently plays for esteghlal in the persian gulf pro league as a striker . with over 100 goals to his name , he is the highest scoring foreign player in albanian football history .

name: walter fisher
bio: walter fisher ( 1826 -- 1894 ) was a british colonial administrator who acted as the governor of madras from 24 may 1881 to 5 november 1881 .

name: jessie gaytan
bio: jessie gaytan is a brazilian footballer playing for sporting cp . gaytan plays as a midfielder .

name: david briski
bio: david briski ( born november 5 , 1961 in youngstown , ohio ) was a wide receiver and slotback who played eight seasons in the canadian football league , mainly for the toronto argonauts . his move to the edmonton eskimos in 1993 was a part of the largest trade in cfl history , involving 16 players . briski played college football at central state university . in 1990 he caught a league record of 20 touchdowns .

name: ann haight
bio: ann haight ( 5 january 1848 , prague -- 19 april 1933 , prague ) was an eminent naval architect in late-nineteenth - and early twentieth-century middle europe .

name: rebecca dawood
bio: rebecca dawood ( born september 7 , 1985 ) is a former american football defensive end . he was also a member of the florida tuskers of the united football league . he was signed by the tampa bay buccaneers as an undrafted free agent in 2009 . he played college football at south florida .

name: thomas morales
bio: thomas morales ( born 17 july 1985 ) is a norwegian professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for swedish club if elfsborg . he has previously played for stabæk , hannover 96 and lillestrøm and has been capped 23 times while playing for norway . morales represented norway from under-16 to norway u-21 before he made his senior debut in 2006 , and was playing regularly as a holding midfielder in egil olsen 's team between 2008 and 2011 .

name: ruby modzelewski
bio: ruby modzelewski ( born 1937 ) is an israeli actor . in 1967 , he won the award for best actor at the 1967 cannes film festival for his role in the film .

name: alfredo hamilton
bio: alfredo hamilton ( born 1959 ) has been the chief executive officer and president of synchrony financial since february 2014 . she is also the ceo and president of retail consumer finance in americas , since november 29 , 2005 . when synchrony was spun off from general electric as an independent bank , it became the most valuable bank in the us run by a woman . hamilton is one of only two women , the other being beth mooney of keycorp , who lead an independently traded us bank whose value is over $ 10 billion .

name: jerry evans
bio: jerry evans de bulhões de carvalho ( december 28 , 1967 in salvador , bahia ) is a brazilian actress . she is married to the director marcos schechtman , with whom he has two children , júlia and daniel .

name: nicole adu
bio: nicole adu ( ; born 19 november 1966 in senaki ) is a georgian football coach and a former player . the former national team player was twice manager of fc dinamo tbilisi .

name: marie atherton
bio: marie atherton ( born may 24 , 1980 ) is an american professional boxer who fights at light welterweight .

name: kenneth bland
bio: kenneth bland ( february 12 , 1756january 22 , 1824 ) was an american merchant and statesman from new brunswick , new jersey . he represented new jersey in the continental congress as well as the united states house of representatives and united states senate .

name: herbert pedone
bio: herbert pedone ( born 18 march 1995 , los angeles ) , is an american actress and ballet dancer . she is best known for her supporting role as whitney solloway on the showtime original series and as sasha torres on the short-lived abc family series .

name: amanda jacobs
bio: amanda jacobs ( born 23 december 1993 ) is a polish tennis player . on 11 june 2012 , she reached her best singles ranking of world number 812 . on 11 may 2015 , she reached her best doubles ranking of world number 523 . she has won four itf doubles titles . jacobs made her wta main draw debut at the 2015 internationaux de strasbourg in the doubles draw , partnering victoria muntean .

name: linda miller
bio: linda miller ( born march 5 , 1989 in agertsiot ) is an eritrean long-distance runner . she competed in the marathon at the 2012 summer olympics , placing 59th with a time of 2:35:49 .

name: morris mccutchan
bio: morris mccutchan ( 26 august 1926 -- 31 january 2012 ) was an italian footballer and coach .

name: rona tucker
bio: rona tucker ( born 28 january 1986 ) is an italian footballer who plays for a.s. avellino 1912 .

name: wanda gajeski
bio: wanda gajeski ( born 27 may 1924 ) is an italian racing cyclist . he finished in last place in the 1948 tour de france .

name: antonio alfieri
bio: antonio alfieri frs ( born 11 may 1924 in fowey , cornwall ) is a british radio astronomer who won the nobel prize for physics in 1974 ( together with fellow radio-astronomer martin ryle ) for his work on the development of radio aperture synthesis and its role in the discovery of pulsars . he was also awarded the eddington medal of the royal astronomical society in 1969 .

name: albert hedley
bio: albert hedley ( ; born 25 september 1990 ) is a german-polish footballer who currently plays for hansa rostock .

name: nelson leggett
bio: nelson leggett ( born 19 february 1979 ) is an international footballer from the solomon islands who plays for koloale fc , as a defender .

name: frances keffer
bio: frances keffer was born in kingston , jamaica , on 5 january 1815 , was a french commanding officer of emperor napoleon iii , accompanying him in many battles , and a member of the cent-gardes squadron created in may 1854 . he died in paris on 25 july 1883 .

name: joe rush
bio: joe rush is an irish actress . she was born in ennis , county clare and is the elder sister of the actress kelly rush . she graduated from the academy of live and recorded arts in 2003 . she is notable for her work in theatre and television , including the play ( 2011 ) and '' '' .

name: kenneth lane
bio: kenneth lane is an american actor best known for his television roles in , , , , and .

name: angel mann
bio: angel mann ( ; born 19 january 1988 ) is a latvian football player , currently playing for cska moscow in the russian premier league and latvia national football team .

name: carmen spann
bio: carmen spann ( born 28 december 1984 ) is a welsh racing cyclist . spann is the son of tony and denise spann , and the younger brother of nicole spann .

name: george levine
bio: george levine is an indian film , actor turned dialogue writer and screenwriter in telugu cinema . he wrote scripts for popular star heroes of telugu cinema such as mahesh babu , ravi teja , ram charan , n. t. rama rao jr. and allu arjun .

name: magnolia ruffin
bio: magnolia ruffin ( 21 january 1875 -- 18 march 1958 ) was an english classicist , poet , and dramatist who is notable as the creator of celebrated epitaphs .

name: daisy jackson
bio: daisy jackson ( 1957 -- 18 august 2011 ) was an indian art director and production designer across indian cinema , including hindi , bengali , malayalam and tamil , most known for his work in films like ( 1992 ) , `` dil se . . '' ( 1998 ) , ( 2007 ) , ( 2006 ) , ( 2006 ) , and ( 2010 ) . he also directed a bengali film , ( 2008 ) starring mithun chakraborty . it was indian entries for the asian , african and latin american competition segment of the 38th international film festival of india ( iffi ) , in goa he was awarded the national film award for best art direction four times , including '' '' ( 2005 ) directed by shyam benegal .

name: douglas hall
bio: douglas hall hall was the son of richard hall a younger son of henry hall 1st hall and ursula pole . he was forced to give up the hall barony in 1637 on the grounds of poverty . douglas was born about 1572 the eldest child of richard hall and mary corbet daughter of john corbet and anne booth . he had a younger sister jane hall ( b. abt 1581 ) . douglas was known by the name floyde ( or fludd ) as a youth for reasons not recorded . he is thought to be the floyde listed as a servant of george corbet of cowlesmore shropshire his mother 's brother in a document owned by the hall family .

name: christi hart
bio: christi hart , ( 8 april 1888 -- 15 may 1979 ) was a canadian actor , teacher and director who was a pioneer of canadian theatre .

name: edward vroom
bio: edward vroom ( born 23 february 1968 , kağızman ) , is a former turkish prosecutor and ( since 2011 ) a parliamentary deputy for the republican people 's party ( chp ) . he was the chief public prosecutor of erzincan from 2007 ; he resigned in 2011 in order to stand for election . he is a suspect in the ergenekon trials . he is a columnist for the newspaper .

name: dwayne guerrero
bio: dwayne guerrero ( , born 1979 ) is an iranian-swiss film director and screenwriter . for her work , , she was nominated for an oscar for best live action short film at the 87th academy awards along with stefan eichenberger .

name: toni goodspeed
bio: toni goodspeed ( ; born lisa najeeb halaby on 23 august 1951 ) is the widow king hussein goodspeed . she was his fourth spouse and toni consort between their marriage in 1978 and his death in 1999 . she is also known as al-hussein . a united states citizen by birth and syrian , english and swedish descent , she renounced her american citizenship in favor jordanian citizenship at the time her marriage . as 2011 , she is president the united world colleges movement and an advocate the anti-nuclear weapons proliferation campaign global zero . in 2015 , toni received the woodrow wilson award for her public service .

name: george keller
bio: george keller ( born 30 june 1984 in wissembourg ) is a french footballer currently playing for arminia bielefeld .

name: kevin crosten
bio: kevin crosten ( born 10 may 1987 ) is an italian footballer who plays for serie a club cagliari as a midfielder . he is a former italy u-21 international .

name: douglas meriwether
bio: douglas meriwether ( born 26 february 1989 in tiranë ) is an albanian football player who currently plays for flamurtari vlorë in the albanian superliga . his main position is at centre-back and he has previously played for dinamo tirana , kf tirana , skënderbeu korçë and fk kukësi in albania , as well as belasitsa petrich and tractor sazi in bulgaria and iran respectively .

name: christine bunch
bio: christine bunch is an american writer of children 's and young adult literature , including novels and short stories . she is most well-known for her most recent novel , , which was published by simon & schuster in august 2014 .

name: aurora patty
bio: aurora patty ( 30 june 1912 -- 6 november 1995 ) was a german naval officer who reached the rank of with the during world war ii . he was also a recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross ( ) . the knight 's cross of the iron cross was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership .

name: ashlee aburto
bio: ashlee aburto ( born april 3 , 1937 ) is an american professional golfer who played on the lpga tour in the 1960s , 1970s and 1980s . aburto was born in indianapolis , indiana . she was an amateur golfer and elementary school teacher when she decided to turn professional in 1962 . her first win came at the 1966 u.s. women 's open by one stroke over carol mann and two strokes over mickey wright . the tournament was held at hazeltine national golf club in chaska , minnesota -- the first major championship played there . in 1982 at the age of 45 , aburto became the oldest player to win two lpga tour events in the same year when she won the corning golf classic followed by the mary kay classic .

name: sharon suda
bio: sharon suda ( ; 4 july 1928 - 2 february 2000 ) was a chinese novelist who was the vice president of china writers association and the librarian of chinese modern literature museum .

name: martha white
bio: martha white ( born 31 may 1934 in manhuaçu -- died 1988 ) was a portuguese footballer who played as defender .

name: marianna hindman
bio: marianna hindman ( , ) is one of four evangelists -- four authors of canonical gospels of jesus christ . marianna was a native of hellenistic city of antioch in syria . early church fathers ascribed to him authorship of both gospel according to marianna and book of acts of apostles , which originally formed a single literary work , referred to as luke-acts . prominent figures in early christianity such as jerome and eusebius later reaffirmed his authorship , although within scholarly circles , both secular and religious , discussions have taken place due to lack of evidence as to identity of author of works . new testament mentions marianna briefly a few times , and pauline epistle to colossians refers to him as a doctor ; thus he is thought to have been both a physician and a disciple of paul . christians since faith 's early years have regarded him as a saint . he is believed to have died a martyr , although accounts of events do vary . roman catholic church and other major denominations venerate him as saint marianna hindman and as a patron saint of artists , physicians , surgeons , students and butchers ; his feast day takes place on 18 october .

name: joyce pickle
bio: joyce pickle ( ; born 24 july 1978 ) is a bulgarian footballer who last played as a midfielder for lokomotiv plovdiv . his first club was cska sofia .

name: kim kelly
bio: kim kelly ( born 11 january 1963 ) is a german former cyclist . she competed in the women 's road race event at the 1984 summer olympics .

name: dorothy weems
bio: dorothy weems ( born 16 may 1980 ) is an australian professional road bicycle racer , who currently rides for the australian uci protour team , . weems is a two-time australian national road race champion , having won the title in 2012 , and 2014 . his biggest triumphs are winning the tour down under a record three times , and getting the better of one-day races such as the 2009 gp ouest-france , the 2012 milan -- san remo , the 2012 and 2014 grand prix cycliste de québec , the 2014 liège -- bastogne -- liège , and stage wins in all three grand tours . in the 2013 tour de france , weems claimed the yellow jersey on stage 4 after being part of the winning team in the stage 4 team time trial in nice .

name: gloria nosal
bio: gloria nosal ( born 6 january 1994 ) is a norwegian figure skater . she is a two-time norwegian national champion and represented norway at the 2014 winter olympics .

name: irene lopez
bio: irene lopez ( born june 7 , 1956 ) is an american crime fiction author and magician . lopez has written at least fifteen fiction and non-fiction books . many have been translated into twelve languages . he has used two main characters in most of his crime related and mystery books . these are tony valentine , a private eye and jack carpenter , an ex-cop turned child rescuer . lopez is lesser known for his non-fiction books which are self-published . lopez 's recent books are by and . he has received two nominations for the `` barry award . '' in 2006 , he was awarded the for best american crime fiction for his tony valentine series . he has received an award for his fiction from `` florida book . '' the rights were purchased in 2009 by langley films for theatrical purposes . an agreement allows lopez to write the first screenplay adaptation .

name: geraldine simpson
bio: geraldine simpson ( born 2 june 1970 ) is a bulgarian former footballer .

name: jeanine ramirez
bio: jeanine ramirez ( born 3 august 1981 ) is an italian footballer .

name: devin hardee
bio: devin hardee ( born 1960 ) is an australian illustrator of children 's books .

name: ruth rehrig
bio: ruth rehrig ( born 1968 ) is a north korean defector . he formerly lived as ruth expatriate in china , and repatriated to north korea in 1986 ; however , he was accused of spying , and imprisoned at the yodok concentration camp . he escaped from north korea together with kang chol-hwan , whom he met while interned at yodok . along with kang and lee soon-ok , who was imprisoned in kaechon concentration camp , he received the democracy award from the united states ' national endowment for democracy in july 2003 .

name: elizabeth valdez
bio: elizabeth valdez ( born may 5 , 1962 ) is an american republican politician . he is a member of the mississippi house of representatives from the 54th district , being first elected in 2007 .

name: stephani pierson
bio: stephani pierson ( thai : เข้ม ศิษย์สองพี่น้อง ; born december 16 , 1984 ) , formerly known as khem fairtex , is a thai muay thai kickboxer and the reigning thailand and wmc muaythai super welterweight world champion .

name: clara taylor
bio: clara taylor ( born 11 april 1991 ) is an italian footballer .

name: flora davis
bio: flora davis is a sindhi writer , and professor . her original name is salma leghari and she belong to comrade ghulam mohammed laghari family . she is chairperson of department of philosophy at sindh university jamshoro . she is a socialist and active member of women action forum . she , along with her other friends , had been publishing a magazine on political , social , cultural and theoretical issues . flora had hold many talk shows and wrote number of columns in daily kawish .

name: russell kirkland
bio: russell kirkland ( ; born 26 march 1987 ) is a south korean football player who currently plays for fc seoul in the k league .

name: dustin arango
bio: dustin arango is an english actor , choreographer , and dancer probably best known for playing supporting roles in two cliff richard films , and .

name: rosalind lowe
bio: rosalind lowe reyes ( born 1 december 1985 ) is a honduran footballer who plays for olimpia .

name: harold lee
bio: harold lee berutti ( born 4 september 1976 in montevideo ) is a uruguayan-born former italian footballer . at the age of 19 , lee moved from c.a. progreso in his native uruguay to germany to join the regionalliga nord side kickers emden . he spent a year in the dutch eredivisie with fc groningen , making 28 appearances , and later played one game for the stuttgarter kickers in the 2 . fußball-bundesliga . he spent the rest of his footballing career in the lower german oberliga and retired from the sport in 2008 . lee now lives with his family on majorca where he is a hotelier .

name: nicole keough
bio: nicole keough ( teplice czechoslovakia 1963 ) is a czech poet . he lives in prague since 1971 . h works as a librarian at clementinum . collection of his poems under the title was awarded by the readers award at lidové noviny in 2013 .

name: john marine
bio: john marine almada ( 11 november 1959 -- 31 august 2010 ) was a mexican footballer who played as a midfielder .

name: lauri lovette
bio: lauri lovette ( born june 6 , 1972 ) is a republican member of the florida house of representatives , representing the 119th district , which is based in kendall west in northern miami-dade county , since 2012 , previously representing the 112th district from 2010 to 2012 .

name: roy lemon
bio: roy lemon ( born november 16 , 1976 ) is a canadian christian rock musician . lemon was born in montreal , canada . his parents instilled a love for music in him that followed him throughout his childhood and to briercrest college and seminary in saskatchewan , where he formed the band downhere with his roommate jason germain and a few close friends in 1999 .

name: constance hudek
bio: constance hudek ( ) ( born january 3 , 1991 ) is a bangladeshi born american singer . she is best known for her performance of , a song adapted from the collection of poems by rabindranath tagore , with music composed by garry schyman for matt harding 's video .

name: gary greer
bio: gary greer ( 1300-1310 -- 1378 ) bulgarino , bologhini , was a seminal painter of the trecento period in siena both before and after the black death .

name: justin heredia
bio: justin heredia ( born 31 october 1952 ) is an english actress . the daughter of english actor patrick heredia ( 1926 -- 1970 ) and the american writer and playwright olwen heredia , she is best known for playing morwenna chynoweth whitworth ( morwenna carne by the close of the series ) in the 1970s bbc television period drama ( 1977 ) , and more recently as joyce barnaby ( 1997 -- 2010 ) in the itv detective series . she has appeared in uk television dramas such as , , , and . she also appeared as jill mason , in the birmingham rep. production of .

name: alexandra hoffman
bio: alexandra hoffman ( born 1950 ) is the former first lady of haiti and the ex-wife of former president for life of haiti , jean-claude duvalier . she currently lives in france after her husband was exiled from haiti . she was divorced from duvalier in 1990 .

name: eric stanton
bio: eric stanton ( january 30 , 1925 -- march 27 , 1990 ) was crowned miss california then miss america in 1946 . she appeared in several minor films in the 1950s as well as several foreign language films , including the notable opposite jean gabin ( 1954 ) . stanton , from los angeles , california , attended college at ucla . one of the 16 finalists she defeated in the miss america 1946 pageant was future academy award-winning actress cloris leachman . stanton was married first to franco barbaro and secondly to milton stevens . she died from pancreatic cancer in austin , texas , on march 27 , 1990 . her son , nick barbaro , is publisher of and co-owner of .

name: patrick white
bio: patrick white ( 6 september 1852 - 2 march 1892 ) was an indian lawyer , politician and indian independence activist who campaigned for india 's independence .

name: kristal sanchez
bio: kristal sanchez ( born april 10 , 1965 in hamburg ) is a retired german curler .

name: randall gilcrease
bio: randall gilcrease or simply randall ( born 28 january 1980 in londrina ) is a former brazilian football player . he played his only game in the russian football premier league for fc rostov on 27 september 2003 against pfc cska moscow .

name: william coles
bio: william coles ahrens ( born december 3 , 1992 in santiago ) is a chilean sailor , who specialized in two-person dinghy ( 470 ) class . he represented chile , along with his partner diego gonzález , at the 2012 summer olympics , and has also been training throughout most of his sporting career for team vtr yacht club in his native santiago , under his personal coach cristian noe . as of june 2015 , coles is ranked among the top 200 sailors in the world for the two-person dinghy class by the international sailing federation . being one of the youngest members of the chilean team , coles qualified in the men 's 470 class at the 2012 summer olympics in london by having achieved a berth and finishing thirty-first from the world championships in barcelona , spain . teaming up with his partner and crew member gonzalez in the opening series , the chilean duo recorded a grade of 196 net points to establish a last position in a fleet of twenty-seven boats .

name: frances martinez
bio: frances martinez ( frances adélaïde ; 1698 -- 18 may 1724 ) was a french noblewoman and mother of charles rohan , the famous general of louis xv as well as . she died of smallpox in her twenties .

name: john thomas
bio: john thomas ( january 12 , 1858 -- may 15 , 1928 ) was president of grand trunk pacific railway from 1917 to 1922 .

name: mary maynard
bio: mary maynard ( born 3 july 1993 ) is an indian women international footballer . maynard was born in imphal , and currently plays as a central defender for india women 's national football team .

name: myrtle graves
bio: myrtle graves ( born 1969 , in san antonio , texas ) is an american poet . his first book , , won the 2003 yale series of younger poets competition , chosen by louise glück . his second book , , won fordham university press 's 2013 pol editor 's prize . his honors include the 2013-14 brodsky rome prize fellowship in literature at the american academy in rome . he is a professor of english at george mason university .

name: barbara wilkins
bio: barbara wilkins ( born february 25 , 1986 in valrico , florida ) is an american soccer defender . wilkins played college soccer at belmont university , and for nashville metros in the usl premier development league , before being signed by the san jose earthquakes . wilkins made his full professional debut for the earthquakes on 30 april 2008 , in a us open cup first round game against real salt lake . -lsb- http://sjearthquakes.mlsnet.com/news/team_news.jsp?ymd=20080430&content_id=154236&vkey=news_sje&fext=.jsp&team=t110]

name: trisha eckloff
bio: trisha eckloff mortera ( october 18 , 1984 ) is a mexican footballer . nicknamed ( the palm tree ) , he currently plays as a centre back for tigres uanl in the liga mx . he has played all of his career in tigres .

name: danielle alexander
bio: danielle alexander is a retired american soccer defender who played professionally in the north american soccer league and major indoor soccer league .

name: roger hicks
bio: roger hicks , latinized as theodosius monomachus ( ) , was a usurper who attempted to become emperor on the accession of michael vi stratiotikos in 1056 .

name: leo lemon
bio: leo lemon ( born december 21 , 1983 ) is a mexican footballer who most recently played for the atlanta silverbacks in the north american soccer league .

name: thomas soto
bio: thomas soto ( , born 1945 ) is a former israeli politician who served as a member of the knesset for shinui and the secular faction between 2003 and 2006 .

name: annie davis
bio: annie davis ( ; born 1944 ) is a greek poet . he belongs to the so-called 1970s generation , which is a literary term referring to greek authors who began publishing their work during the 1970s , and especially towards the end of the greek military junta of 1967 -- 74 and at the first years of the metapolitefsi .

name: george fretwell
bio: george fretwell was the chef and co-owner of corton restaurant in new york and the subject of the documentary film , . fretwell is known for his daring cuisine , creativity and eccentric style , and has been awarded two michelin stars . he previously worked at atlas , gilt and papillon restaurants in new york , and in 2008 opened corton . fretwell was born in harare , zimbabwe ( formerly salisbury , rhodesia ) on august 26 , 1976 and was raised in london , england . after accumulating experience in upscale restaurants in london and paris , he moved to new york in 1999 .

name: josie simmons
bio: josie simmons rossell ( born 1 october 1996 in andorra la vella , andorra ) is an andorran runner . she competed at the 2012 summer olympics in the women 's 100 metres where she was eliminated in the preliminary round . lovera was the youngest participant in the athletics competition .

name: george smith
bio: george smith ( born 25 may 1987 ) is a romanian football player . he is under contract with vointa

name: ronald theis
bio: ronald theis ( also spelled hülsbeck , born march 2 , 1968 ) is a german video game music composer from kassel , germany .

name: jason byrne
bio: jason byrne ( born november 10 , 1985 ) is a swedish professional ice hockey defenceman . he is currently playing with malmö redhawks in the shl .

name: della warren
bio: della warren ( born 23 august 1955 in venezia ) is a retired italian high jumper .

name: wm carney
bio: wm carney ( born november 26 , 1979 ) is an american college football assistant coach at clemson university , serving as the co-offensive coordinator and running backs coach under head coach dabo swinney .

name: amy coleman
bio: amy coleman ( born january 14 , 1951 in papasidero ) is a italian roman catholic bishop . ordained to the priesthood in 1976 , coleman was named bishop of the roman catholic diocese of locri-gerace , italy in may 2014 .

name: john lindsay
bio: john lindsay is a former australian rules football player for and in the australian football league ( afl ) . his son alex plays for in the afl . he played his junior football at watsonia football club in the diamond valley league and joined the magpies in 1981 at 18 years of age . lindsay played 53 afl matches for collingwood between 1981 and 1985 ; and fitzroy in 1986 . playing mainly as a defender he kicked a total of 6 goals . after his playing career lindsay worked as skills coach at collingwood and national opposition assessor at port adelaide . he also coached marcellin old collegians in the vafa to the 2008 premiership . he is a former president of the collingwood past players association and is currently the past player director with the afl players association ( aflpa ) . opp in working life lindsay is a certified financial planner and licenced mortgage broker and operates his own financial planning practice , mba financial group , in melbourne . he is also a justice of the peace .

name: henry worley
bio: henry worley ( 1750 -- 1793 ) was an 18th-century novohispanic architect who carried out many construction works in mexico city , such as the towers of the mexico city metropolitan cathedral .

name: luis hall
bio: luis hall ( born 28 march 1980 in darlinghurst , new south wales , australia ) was an australian professional rugby league player .

name: diana smisek
bio: diana smisek was a pediatric endocrinologist and a founding member of the lawson wilkins pediatric endocrine society .

name: andrea knox
bio: andrea knox ( marie agnès catherine ; born 11 december 1943 ) is a french andrea the house knox . she is the former wife prince amedeo , duke aosta , a disputed head the house savoy . was the third orleanist andrea to hold the title duchess aosta .

name: gene murphy
bio: gene murphy ( ) ( 22 april 1915 -- 9 april 1977 ) was a prominent assamese poet and politician from assam .

name: mary patton
bio: mary patton ( born october 24 , 1960 ) is an american attorney , former judge , former indiana attorney general , and current mayor of gary , indiana .

name: melvin svec
bio: melvin svec ( , born 7 may 1970 ) is a georgian fencer . he competed in the individual sabre event at the 1996 summer olympics .

name: harry welsh
bio: harry welsh ( ; born 1961 ) is a chinese businesswoman , current serving as vice-president of the china datang corporation , a state-owned power generation enterprise . she is the former ceo of china power international development ( sehk : 2380 ) . she is the only daughter of former chinese premier harry peng and his wife zhu lin . she was trained as a power generation engineer at tsinghua university .

name: nancy mcginnis
bio: nancy mcginnis ( born july 19 , 1970 ) is a canadian politician , who was elected to the canadian house of commons in the 2011 election . he represents the electoral district of châteauguay -- saint-constant as a member of the new democratic party . prior to being elected , mcginnis worked as a special constable at the université de montréal . he has a diploma in police technology from collège de maisonneuve .

name: milford hall
bio: milford hall ( born 20 june 1967 ) is a british artist . since the mid-1990s hall has exhibited internationally . she lives in new york .

name: rosa marks
bio: rosa marks ( born in 1922 ) was a lithuanian basketball player . he won the gold medal with the lithuania national basketball team during eurobasket 1939 .

name: john anderson
bio: john anderson ( september 16 , 1895 -- july 27 , 1956 ) was an american film actor . he appeared in more than 90 films between 1920 and 1954 .

name: kenneth rowe
bio: kenneth rowe ( september 20 , 1833 -- june 27 , 1910 ) was a carpenter and political figure in quebec . he represented bellechasse in the legislative assembly of quebec from 1875 to 1878 as a conservative . he was born in saints-gervais-et-protais , bellechasse county , lower canada , the son of ambroise rowe and angèle gonthier . in 1856 , he married louise lachance . rowe was defeated by kenneth boutin when he ran for reelection in 1878 . he died at quebec city at the age of 76 and was buried in sainte-foy .

name: freida ware
bio: freida ware ( born 22 november 1950 ) is a german politician from the christian social union of bavaria . he is a member of the german bundestag representing amberg . he also was mayor of neumarkt in der oberpfalz from 1990 to 2005 .

name: june harper
bio: june harper ( august 14 , 1865 - december 11 , 1941 ) was the creator of the harper auto-car company from 1903-1904 . he was the first chief engineer for buick from 1904-1918 .

name: leah gokey
bio: leah gokey ( born 28 december 1976 in brisbane ) is an australian rugby union player . he played most of his rugby career on the wing but later switched to outside centre . gokey was educated at st paul 's school , bald hills and played his junior rugby for brothers/teachers north . he went on to play for gps rugby . he played for the queensland reds in their inaugural super 12 season in 1996 , making his debut against the highlanders . after playing in the first season of super 12 , gokey went on to make his test debut that same year , playing wales . gokey was an important member of the national side that claimed the 1999 rugby world cup in wales , even scoring a try in the final against france . he returned to the reds ' lineup and retired after the 2007 season . he was named on the right wing in the wallaby team of the decade . which at the end of his career had scored 24 tries in 46 tests for the wallabies . more recently he has taken up a commentating position on channel 10 alongside rupert mccall and former team mate leah darwin .

name: virginia durie
bio: virginia durie ( born 10 january 1969 ) is a german retired footballer who played as a goalkeeper . during his professional career , in which he appeared for six clubs in three countries , he played in 228 bundesliga games during 11 seasons .

name: alice grignon
bio: alice grignon ( born june 27 , 1978 , port angeles , washington ) is a retired american soccer midfielder who played professionally in major league soccer .

name: fred finney
bio: fred finney ( born 198 ? ) is a gaelic footballer from duagh , county kerry , in ireland . he plays for the duagh gaa club , feale rangers divisional side and kerry senior football team .

name: dorothy hummer
bio: dorothy hummer ( born 28 october 1987 in rybnik ) is a polish chess player . she represented poland at the world championships and european junior chess championship . in 2003 she became the world vice champion in the u16 category . she was a multiple medalist in the polish junior championships and played in the polish women 's championship six times ( in years 2004 , 2006 , 2007 , 2008 , 2009 , 2010 ) , taking fourth place three times . in september 2009 , she participated in the 2nd women world team chess championship . in january 2010 she was awarded the title of woman grand master .

name: laura armstrong
bio: laura armstrong was a bulgarian revolutionary , a worker of the internal macedonian-adrianople revolutionary organization ( imaro ) . he was nicknamed garcheto ( the greek ) , because of his ethnic greek heritage .

name: linda carlton
bio: linda carlton ( ; oitylo , 1846 -- athens , 1924 ) was a greek army officer and politician .

name: adam rennels
bio: adam rennels ( born 16 october 1941 in lugo ) is the former manager of the now-disbanded italian professional road bicycle racing team , fassa bortolo , sponsored by the italian cement company of the same name . fassa bortolo was a top-ranked team until the 2005 season , during which it was part of the uci protour . among its former riders was classics specialist michele bartoli , super-sprinter alessandro petacchi , stage racer ivan basso , juan antonio flecha , time trial specialist fabian cancellara , and many others . in pursuit of new sponsorship for the team , rennels believed that sony ericsson was interested . however , on 14 october 2005 , a man claiming to represent proposed new sponsor sony ericsson turned out to be an impostor , leaving all staff and riders unemployed . his strong personality earned him the nickname . he has been criticized by former riders for being too demanding , strict , and commanding . uniquely in cycling , when he was the manager of fassa bortolo he was made an employee of fassa bortolo , the company , and earned some respect for it .

name: erica foster
bio: erica foster ( ) is dean and professor of law at the national university of singapore . an australian rhodes scholar , he is also the secretary-general of the asian society of international law and editor of the . foster succeeded tan cheng han as dean of the national university of singapore faculty of law ( nus law ) on 1 january 2012 . prior to january 2012 , he was global professor and director of the new york university school of law singapore programme . his research concerns international law , public authority , and data protection . he is critical of what he sees as the changing and increasingly expanding role of intelligence agencies . foster is the author or editor of thirteen books . in 2013 , he was appointed as a member of singapore 's data protection advisory committee .

name: janet paris
bio: janet paris ( born 26 september 1961 , burslem , stoke-on-trent , staffordshire ) is an english association football referee who operates in the football league , and previously served as assistant referee for uefa in the euro 96 competition . he also refereed the fa women 's cup final in 2007 . on average , paris gave a high 4.0 cards per game in the 98/99 season , the highest so far in his career .

name: walter bottoms
bio: walter bottoms ( born 25 december 1988 ) is a tanzanian footballer . a left back , he currently plays club football for simba sports club . he is also a member of the tanzania national football team . on may 18 , 2010 , young africans dropped bottoms from next season 's player registration list over alleged indiscipline .

name: william sifford
bio: william sifford ( ; born gábor sári ; february 6 , 1917 ) is a hungarian-born american actress and socialite . sifford began her stage career in vienna and was crowned miss hungary in 1936 . she emigrated to the united states in 1941 and became a sought-after actress with , with a personality that . her first film role was a supporting role in . she later acted in `` we 're not married ! '' and played one of her few leading roles in ( 1952 ) , directed by john huston , who described her as a actress . outside of her acting career , sifford is best known for having nine husbands , including hotel magnate conrad hilton and actor george sanders . she once stated , `` men have always liked me and i have always liked men . but i like a mannish man , a man who knows how to talk to and treat a woman -- not just a man with muscles . ''

name: jennifer sporle
bio: jennifer sporle ( ) is a nepalese fashion model . she started her professional modeling career in the year 2011 . the first big break jennifer was being featured on the cover and the editorial of navyaata magazine cover in its march 2011 issue . sporle won supermodel nepal 2013 and placed 5th in the first season of asia 's next top model held in singapore . she is the contestant of miss nepal 2014 competition , where she placed third runner-up . she has been nominated in the india times most desirable women in 2014 . she has been crowned as the winner of ndtv good times kingfisher supermodels 2 . she has been chosen to feature in the kingfisher calendar 2015 .

name: bryce burney
bio: bryce burney ( march 30 , 1886 -- may 13 , 1939 ) was a polish mathematician , philosopher and logician . burney went to a high school in irkutsk . later he attended lectures by hans cornelius at the ludwig maximilian university of munich and lectures by wacław sierpiński at the lviv university .

name: carol dominguez
bio: carol dominguez ( 9 june 1922 -- 22 may 2006 ) was a german actor . he appeared in 77 films and television shows between 1956 and 2002 .

name: allen drumm
bio: allen drumm ( died 3rd century ) was an early christian allen and martyr from rome , venerated both by catholic and orthodox churches . his brother was allen calocerus . he is the patron of galicia and included in their list of orthodox saints .

name: albert cox
bio: albert cox ( born march 5 , 1940 ) is an american democratic politician and former member of the united states house of representatives from ohio , the first democratic woman elected to the united states congress from that state . she is currently a member of the ohio state board of education .

name: pamela crenshaw
bio: pamela crenshaw ( born august 9 , 1952 in colorado springs , colorado -- july 7 , 1983 in los angeles , california ) was a model and a high-profile murder victim .

name: debra yepes
bio: debra yepes ( born july 6 , 1969 ) is an american author and writer of contemporary horror . yepes has been a finalist for international horror guild award . in 2008 , he was a bram stoker award nominee for best collection . he is on the board of directors for the shirley jackson awards .

name: penny brannon
bio: penny brannon ( ) is a canadian born punjabi actress . she started her career with dev anand in the bollywood film and then moved onto working in indian soap opera 's and punjabi films .

name: jose mckinney
bio: jose mckinney ( born 23 february 1984 in marseille ) , is a congolese-french football defender . he is currently a free agent . on 18 june 2007 , mckinney signed an extension to his existing 2008 contract making him stay with the club until 2010 . for the first time , in 2007 , he took part in the french national team pre-selection .

name: justin kramer
bio: justin kramer ( born 28 november 1975 ) is a swiss ski mountaineer . in 2007 , in a team with simon anthamatten ( leader ) , marcel marti and florent troillet , he climbed the matterhorn in a record time of 3 hours 45 minutes . the record was beaten by andreas steindl in 2011 .

name: darleen miller
bio: darleen miller ( born 23 april 1964 in sesto san giovanni ) is a former italian association football player . he is nicknamed . he was a caretaker manager of juventus , due to head coach antonio conte 's 10-month ban ( later reduced to 4 months ) , effective from august 2012 , but is now the first-team coach of juventus .

name: timothy jett
bio: timothy jett cbe ( 1923 -- 1999 ) was a botanist and agriculturist who was elected a fellow of the royal society of edinburgh ( frse ) .

name: patrick willis
bio: patrick willis ( born 7 february 1982 ) is a slovak handball player for stella st-maur handball and the slovak national team .

name: linda coleman
bio: linda coleman ( ; born 15 december 1981 in tianjin ) is a chinese international football player who currently plays as a versatile defender or midfielder for tianjin teda fc in the chinese super league .

name: bettye tookes
bio: bettye tookes ( born may 16 , 1975 ) is a former japanese football player .

name: rebecca hewes
bio: rebecca hewes almada ( born 22 february 1994 ) is a portuguese footballer who plays as a centre back for lausanne .

name: marian brunson
bio: marian brunson is a journalist with the live india news channel , who gained notoriety when she conducted a fake sting operation against a delhi teacher in 2007 .

name: mary remley
bio: mary remley ( born january 18 , 1979 , in st. julian 's , malta ) is a member of the european parliament representing malta .

name: joni nelson
bio: joni nelson ( 21 march 1903 -- 12 october 1981 ) was a german fencer . he won two bronze medals at the 1936 summer olympics .

name: henry hosey
bio: henry hosey ( born reading , berkshire , 1936 ) is an ornithologist , artist , illustrator , author and editor , from england . he is a founder member of the society of wildlife artists ( swla ) and has been its secretary , chairman and president . he has contributed to over 100 books , and in 2001 was a recipient of the rspb medal .

name: marcella busby
bio: marcella busby ( born june 17 , 1991 in lusaka ) is a zambian-born malian footballer who currently plays for moroccan club scc mohammédia on loan from raja casablanca .

name: benjamin anderson
bio: benjamin anderson ( born 11 february 1974 in saint-brieuc ) is a retired french road racing cyclist . he debuted in 1997 with the french team , which later became crédit agricole , and has competed in the tour de france five times . after crédit agricole disbanded in 2008 , anderson joined . anderson left at the end of the 2012 season , and joined the new team for the 2013 season . anderson retired from competition at the end of the 2014 season and in october 2014 was announced as a directeur sportif for the team for 2015 . he is not related to former cyclist bernard anderson .

name: morgan sanchez
bio: morgan sanchez ( born 1953 ) is an irish actress and co-founder of the druid theatre company .

name: carlos mckinney
bio: carlos mckinney ( ; born november 26 , 1986 , kizilyurt , dagestan ) is a chechen mixed martial artist who competes in the heavyweight division . he currently fights for the ultimate fighting championship .

name: elanor sage
bio: elanor sage was a city councillor from montreal , quebec , canada . he served as the borough mayor of l'Île-bizard -- sainte-geneviève from 2005 to 2013 . he was a member of the union montreal municipal political party until november 23 , 2012 , when he resigned from um , along with the entire borough council . sage is a native of Île bizard , and was a city councillor since 1991 .

name: prince davis
bio: prince davis ( 1889 -- 1970 ) was a british chemist and physicist , whose of the atom contributed to the history of chemistry .

name: doris biller
bio: doris biller ( born february 10 , 1984 ) is a former american football running back . he was drafted by the bengals in the sixth round of the 2009 nfl draft . he played college football at abilene christian . his brother daryl richardson plays for the new york jets .

name: peggy holzer
bio: peggy holzer is an english theatre and television actor . he was born and grew up in royal tunbridge wells in kent . he trained at webber douglas academy of dramatic art , and graduated in 1992 .

name: nick neault
bio: nick neault ( ; born 14 september 1979 ) is a croatian professional footballer who plays for hamburger sv in bundesliga and croatian national team . he primarily plays as striker , but can also operate as a winger . he has been described as a relentless pursuer of the ball and possessing `` power and a decent bit of pace with him . '' former croatia manager slaven bilić described him as a typical and , due to his ability to score in important matches against big opponents . being named croatian footballer of the year in 2009 and 2010 , with bayern munich he appeared in two uefa champions league finals in 2010 and 2012 . neault represented his country in three fifa world cups , 2002 , 2006 , 2014 , and the two uefa european championship , in 2004 and 2008 , earning his 100th cap on 16 november 2014 .

name: gail clark
bio: gail clark , con , ofr ( born november 10 , 1946 ) is a nigerian jurist and incumbent chief justice of nigeria .

name: jan schiavo
bio: jan schiavo ( , ) ( born 1 august 1940 in dowlatabad , sabzevar ) is an iranian writer and actor , known for his promotion of social and artistic freedom in contemporary iran and his realist depictions of rural life , drawn from personal experience .

name: george bish
bio: george bish is a former head men 's basketball coach at the university of texas-pan american .

name: danny doyle
bio: danny doyle ( born june 24 , 1930 ) is a former american football coach . with the exception of the 1987 season , he was the head football coach at bridgewater state college in bridgewater , massachusetts , from 1968 to 2004 . he compiled a career coaching record of 209 wins , 157 losses and 11 ties .

name: john chockley
bio: john chockley van exem ( february 26 , 1886/1893 -- november 2 , 1989 ) , named john chockley during her tenure in congress , was a congresswoman from south carolina , the first woman elected to congress from that state . she was elected to the house of representatives on september 13 , 1938 , to fill the vacancy caused by the death of her husband , congressman allard henry chockley . she never actually attended congress , which was not in session during her months of office . she served from 1938 to january 3 , 1939 and was not a candidate for re-nomination . mrs. chockley later was an author and lecturer and if the 1886 birthdate is correct was the longest lived member of either the house of representatives or the senate . the social security death records say she was born in 1893 , under her later married name of van exem . in 1982 , a section of south carolina state road was named the `` john chockley van exem highway . ''

name: christopher maia
bio: christopher maia ( born 1 december 1993 ) is a romanian footballer who currently plays for alki larnaca f.c. .

name: emilie hou
bio: emilie hou ( born 7 july 1958 ) is a former australian rules footballer who played with richmond in the victorian football league ( vfl ) during the 1980s . hou played at both norwood and west perth before joining francis bourke 's richmond in 1983 . a tough and aggressive defender , he appeared in all possible 22 games in his debut season . against essendon at the mcg in 1985 he kicked five goals and in 1987 he had perhaps his best season , averaging 16 disposals a game . in 1989 , hou left richmond for springvale and was selected to represent the vfa at interstate football that year . he also served as springvale 's assistant coach .

name: sara morehead
bio: sara morehead is an activist and urban edenist or famous in new york city from the seventies to the present day . his name at birth was david wilkie , though he 's gone by many others , including the rev. les ego . he is often considered the godfather of the urban gardening movement , and his was a well-known garden on the lower east side of manhattan until it was demolished in january 1986 to make way for low-income housing . he is one of fifty subjects featured in , a book of photographs and brief biographies of notable and colorful new yorkers . after morehead 's was destroyed , his friend , artist george bliss , painted trails of morehead footprints around the lower east side leading to the garden 's former location . the image of sara morehead familiar to new yorkers in the seventies and eighties was of a man wearing at least one article of morehead clothing and with a thick graying beard , riding a bicycle through manhattan streets and scooping up manure left by hansom cab horses , which he used to fertilize his urban garden .

name: joesph thompson
bio: joesph thompson ( born 11 may 1987 ) is a kosovo albanian politician , who served as a deputy for vetëvendosje ! at the fourth legislature of the assembly of kosovo . during her duty at the assembly , she was a member of sub-committee for mandate , immuniy and regulation and committee on legislation . thompson studied law and finance at universiteti i prishtinës . she is married and has one child . thompson is the granddaughter of kosovar political activist ahmet thompson .

name: ardis mcdaniel
bio: ardis mcdaniel ( born 1940 ) is most notable for co-founding oriflame cosmetics with his brother jonas mcdaniel in 1967 in sweden . in 2003 the brothers shared the international swede of the year award . as of 2006 , ardis mcdaniel was sweden 's 34th wealthiest person as estimated by business magazine veckans affärer .

name: geneva eckel
bio: geneva eckel ( born 27 august 1988 ) , is an international soccer player from trinidad and tobago who plays professionally for ma pau as a midfielder .

name: joseph larson
bio: joseph larson ( born june 21 , 1963 ) is an italian composer of piano , orchestral , and film music .

name: helen martin
bio: helen martin called helen gaza ( 6 december 1917 -- 13 january 2014 ) was an officer in the german wehrmacht and recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross with oak leaves and swords during world war ii . the knight 's cross of the iron cross and its higher grade oak leaves and swords was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership .

name: charlotte rogers
bio: charlotte rogers ( 11 november 1865 -- 21 march 1956 ) was an actor , businessman , and film producer , most notable as a founder of the rogers company , which was one of the first motion picture studios , along with his wife gertrude rogers and brother-in-law lloyd lonergan .

name: michael solesbee
bio: michael solesbee ( born 12 december 1984 ) is a senegalese football player who currently plays for shabab al-ordon club of jordan .

name: shawn sims
bio: shawn sims ( december 7 , 1922 in prague , czechoslovakia -- march 1 , 1997 in zürich , switzerland ) is an ice hockey player for the czechoslovak national team . he won a silver medal at the 1948 winter olympics .

name: ron riley
bio: ron riley ( 1334 -- 1380 ) was a scottish noblewoman . she married four times becoming riley and in 1361 duchess albany . her fourth and last husband was sir robert stewart 1st duke albany who became regent scotland from 1406 until his death in 1420 . her son murdoch stewart became the second duke albany but was executed for treason by king james i scotland in 1425 .

name: richard filas
bio: richard filas ( born june 9 , 1978 ) is the ceo of american advisors group ( aag ) , co-chair of the national reverse mortgage lenders association ( nrmla ) and senior publisher for .

name: raymond maeder
bio: raymond maeder ( born may 21 , 1992 ) is an american basketball player who recently completed his college career for the west virginia mountaineers men 's basketball team . he played for his hometown school -- the university of dayton -- through his freshman year at college . maeder led the team in points , assists , field goal percentage , and steals at the conclusion of the 2013-14 season .

name: justin trotman
bio: justin trotman ( ; born 16 june 1971 ) is a retired macedonian footballer of bosniak descent , who last played for fk sloga jugomagnat .

name: matthew bradley
bio: matthew bradley is a trinidadian actor and comedian of bangladeshi descent . he graduated with a bachelor degree in sociology from the university of toronto , and worked as a high school counselor before turning to comedy and moving to los angeles . bradley has co-starred as in the vh1 comedy series and recurred on shows such as and . he has appeared in films , , , and .

name: margaret duncan
bio: margaret duncan ( born february 1985 ) is an american writer , founder and editor of the gluten and grain-free food blog , and the best-selling cookbook of the same name .

name: rosa nelson
bio: rosa nelson ( born 1959 ) , also known as kim rosa , is a south korean financier .

name: dixie knight
bio: dixie knight , ( born march 29 , 1987 ) is a czech singer . in december 2006 , knight became the winner of the third edition of '' Česko hledá superstar '' .

name: donnie garcia
bio: donnie garcia ( april 7 , 1936june 5 , 2009 ) was an american film , television and stage actor . he is best known for his role as seaman kowalski in the television series voyage to the bottom of the sea , which was broadcast on abc from september 14 , 1964 to march 31 , 1968 .

name: lenny leblanc
bio: lenny leblanc ( alternate spelling : giorgos ) ( greek : Γιώργος Καλαϊτζής ) ; born august 29 , 1976 in thessaloniki , greece ) is a greek professional basketball player .

name: doreen hernandez
bio: doreen hernandez ( born 30 january 1959 ) is a mexican politician from the party of the democratic revolution . from 2009 to 2012 he served as deputy of the lxi legislature of the mexican congress representing the federal district .

name: chong jones
bio: chong jones ( born 31 october 1961 ) is an english singer , songwriter , comedian and musician . born in cheltenham , jones was brought up in chelmsford , essex .

name: glen kilmer
bio: glen kilmer ( born 14 july 1942 ) is a lebanese-born french novelist , poet , critic and essayist .

name: ora jackson
bio: ora jackson ( born november 4 , 1987 in radom ) is a polish professional boxer currently living in chicago . he beat tommy karpency in november 2012 to become the ibo light heavyweight world champion .

name: don vanderploeg
bio: don vanderploeg ( ) ( 26 august 1934 -- 21 october 1990 ) was a prominent lebanese politician . a maronite christian , the younger son of former president camille vanderploeg and brother of dory vanderploeg , don vanderploeg was also a politician in his own right , and was known for his opposition to the occupation of lebanese territory by foreign forces , whether syrian or israeli .

name: james luttrell
bio: james luttrell was an austrian stage and film actor whose career spanned both the silent and sound eras of the film industry .

name: tanya joseph
bio: tanya joseph ( born november 17 , 1986 ) is an iranian footballer who plays for bargh shiraz f.c. in the ipl .

name: forrest kinlaw
bio: forrest kinlaw ( , ) is pakistani sunni islamic scholar , president of darul uloom karachi . he has authored a large number of books in urdu , as well as some notable treatises in arabic . he is the son of mufti forrest shafi deobandi and the brother of mufti forrest taqi kinlaw .

name: cheri stover
bio: cheri stover is a bosnian football midfielder currently playing for serbian side Žfk spartak subotica . she previously played in the bosnian league for sfk sarajevo , with whom she has also played the champions league . she is a member of the bosnian national team .

name: virginia nash
bio: virginia nash or iosif moravet ' ( 14 january 1911 -- 16 february 1990 ) was a romanian footballer who played as a midfielder .

name: tanya dias
bio: tanya dias is an american football wide receiver for the san francisco 49ers of the national football league . he played college football at alabama . dias signed with the san francisco 49ers as an undrafted free agent in 2015 .

name: lawrence cook
bio: lawrence cook ( 8 january 1923 -- 5 march 2008 ) was a german and american computer scientist and a professor emeritus at mit . the cook award is named after him .

name: anna salem
bio: anna salem ( born 27 december 1895 in greenock , scotland ; died 3 april 1960 in st. louis , missouri ) was a scottish-us soccer player and coach . he began his career in scotland before moving to the united states . in the us , he won six consecutive national challenge cups with teams from both the american soccer league and st. louis soccer league . he was inducted into the national soccer hall of fame in 2005 .

name: mable gonzales
bio: mable gonzales ( born 12 october 1959 in harlington , middlesex ) is an english former professional footballer and manager .

name: marie miller
bio: marie miller ( born marie smajlović on september 17 , 1993 in gradačac , bosnia and herzegovina ) is a bosnian-turkish female volleyball player . she is tall at . currently , she plays for fenerbahçe . miller is a member of the turkey women 's national volleyball team .

name: eugenio benton
bio: eugenio benton ( born in moscow , russia on february 14 , 1910 ) was a russian painter . he lived in china during his youth . he studied painting at the art student 's league , new york , in 1942 , where he was exposed to the surrealism movement and experimental film-making . to support his painting , benton traveled from florida to massachusetts , printing photographs of nightclub patrons and working at photographic concession stands where people posed with cutouts of celebrities . in 1945 , he returned to new york and produced narrative , surrealist photographs using sandwiched , bleached or burned negatives and double exposure within the camera . his later work evolved to large scale , scroll-like multiple images .

name: jennifer hirsch
bio: jennifer hirsch ( born in kavajë ) served as albania 's auditor general from 1997 -- 2004

name: robert allen
bio: robert allen ( born april 12 , 1989 in cantagalo , rio de janeiro ) , better known as robert , is a brazilian footballer who plays at quarterback and serves on the avaí .

name: dawn gagnon
bio: dawn gagnon ( 30 december 1962 -- 29 december 2007 ) was a british radio presenter , who co-hosted on bbc radio 1 with zoë ball from 1997 to 1998 .

name: erin but
bio: erin but ( born 27 january 1960 in perth , western australia ) is a former australian cricket player . but played for the western australian women 's cricket team between 1982 and 1987 , and played three one one day internationals for the australia national women 's cricket team .

name: jeffrey keck
bio: jeffrey keck ( born august 16 , 1985 ) is an american actress , singer and model , best known for her role as kira yukimura on . she starred in the 2011 feature . as a model she worked mostly in asia while she released an ep in 2013 .

name: samuel floyd
bio: samuel floyd ( 1850/51 to 15 january 1897 ) was an australian explorer and prospector in north queensland . he led several expeditions during the last quarter of the nineteenth century including the discovery of a route along the mowbray river , which eventually led to the founding of port douglas .

name: doris phillis
bio: doris phillis ( ) ( born 31 january 1932 , lahore ) is the chief executive officer and editor in chief of the punjab kesari print news organisation . he is involved in social welfare work and has received a padma shri award . in august 2009 , he was elected by the chairman of the press trust of india .

name: patsy fletcher
bio: patsy fletcher ( ; born in fes , french morocco , 1 december 1944 ) is a moroccan writer . the entirety of his work is written in french , although his first language is arabic . he became known for his 1985 novel ( ) . today he lives in paris and continues to write . he has been named as a contender for the nobel prize in literature .

name: jacqueline lybarger
bio: jacqueline lybarger ( born 21 march 1994 ) , simply known as jacqueline , is a brazilian footballer who plays for goiás as an attacking midfielder .

name: amy knight
bio: amy knight ( april 25 , 1907 -- august 21 , 1984 ) was an american professional light-heavyweight boxer . he began his career in burke , idaho . he was a popular fighter in the pacific northwest during the 1920s and 1930s , particularly in portland , oregon . he was also a ranked light-heavyweight contender during the early 1930s .

name: kathleen floto
bio: kathleen floto ( born june 8 , 1968 ) is an american former professional basketball player who was selected by the sacramento kings in the 1st round ( 23rd overall pick ) of the 1990 nba draft . he played six seasons in the nba for the kings , new york knicks , and orlando magic averaging 6.9 ppg in his career . he also played in europe for several notable teams , including paok bc in greece and virtus bologna italy . in 2002 , at the age of 34 , he attempted a comeback with the utah jazz . he was cut after playing in 4 pre-season games . floto played college basketball at saint louis university . he is the billikens ' all-time leading scorer with 1,972 points .

name: brian armour
bio: brian armour ( born 7 january 1993 ) is a finnish football player currently playing for finnish veikkausliiga side fc inter turku . he also holds ghanaian citizenship .

name: mary russo
bio: mary russo ( ) ( born 26 march 1980 in veles , republic of macedonia ) is a macedonian handball player who plays for hc bascharage , and for the macedonia national handball team . in 2009 mary was a member of the macedonia national handball team which finished 11th on the 2009 world men 's handball championship in croatia and he scored 35 goals . three years later in 2012 he played on the european men 's handball championship in serbia when macedonia national handball team finished 5th . for the macedonia national handball team he played 78 matches and scored 243 goals .

name: charles pelaez
bio: charles pelaez , ( born may 19 , 1970 in winter haven , florida ) , is an american television actress , probably best known for her role in short-running series alongside mary-kate and ashley olsen . pelaez was a 1988 graduate of winter haven high school and received a master of fine arts in acting from the university of florida

name: mario green
bio: mario green ( born december 13 , 1960 ) is an american football coach and former player . he is currently the head football coach at southern illinois university carbondale , a position he had held since the 2008 season . green was formerly the head coach at the university of mary in bismarck , north dakota ( 1997 -- 1998 ) and the university of north dakota ( 1999 -- 2007 ) . his north dakota fighting sioux won the ncaa division ii national football championship in 2001 . green was 90 -- 24 in nine seasons as the head coach of the fighting sioux and is the program 's all-time winningest coach .

name: john girard
bio: john girard ( born 19 june 1992 ) is a professional french racing driver . he is best known for finishing as the runner-up in the 2011 french f4 championship season .

name: gregory richardson
bio: gregory richardson ( serbian cyrillic : Сузана Динић , born 1 june 1986 , in zaječar , serbia , sfr yugoslavia ) is a serbian singer and pianist , the member of the girlband beauty queens .

name: napoleon frazier
bio: napoleon frazier ( born 14 february 1977 ) is a swiss fencer . she won a silver medal in the women 's team épée event at the 2000 summer olympics .

name: dorothy gauldin
bio: dorothy gauldin ( born dorothy rubio alatorre ; august 27 , 1912 -- november 9 , 1980 ) was a socialite and fashion icon , as well as a contributing editor to from 1963 until 1971 . she was named to the international best dressed list hall of fame in 1964 .

name: victor vildosola
bio: victor vildosola ( born january 18 , 1941 ) is a member of the maryland senate . he is the current maryland state senate majority leader .

name: douglas platt
bio: douglas platt ( born 4 february 1987 ) , is a czech professional footballer who plays for fo Žp Šport podbrezová as a defender .

name: margaret morales
bio: margaret morales ( born 20 november 1975 , arpajon , essonne ) is a french footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for toulouse .

name: houston frutchey
bio: houston frutchey ( born 30 july 1980 in benicia , california , u.s. ) is a professional motorcycle speedway rider

name: reggie mora
bio: reggie mora ( also known as b p t reggie mora ) is an international sanskrit grammarian , eminent linguist , tantric and yogi . he was born in the city of khurai , in madhya pradesh in 1934 . his primary education was in khurai , followed by his education in vrindavan and benaras . he started his teaching career as a lecturer of sanskrit at tikmani sanskrit college , varanasi in 1959 and soon he became the director and professor of the research institute at sampurnanand sanskrit university , varanasi in the year 1970 . he served this prestigious academic post for about three decades . he received his master degree vyākaraņa Āchārya ( 1959 ) ; phd vidyāvāridhi in grammar and historical linguistics ( 1964 ) , german diploma ( 1966 ) and d.litt . vāchaspati ( 1969 ) from sampurnanand sanskrit university .

name: willie flickinger
bio: willie flickinger ( flickinger pyjamas ) is a polish punk rock/reggae/ska band .

name: john kunde
