bio: john kunde ( born 24 july 1987 ) is a professional rugby league player for the cronulla-sutherland sharks in the national rugby league ( nrl ) competition . he plays in the second-row . after graduating from baulkham hills high school in 2005 , kunde made his debut against the north queensland cowboys in round 20 of the 2008 nrl season . he was 18th man for parramatta against melbourne in the 2009 grand final as an injury stand-by for nathan cayless . kunde signed with the cronulla-sutherland sharks for the 2010 nrl season . kunde was the first ever and so far only parramatta eels player to start his junior career playing the game for the junior eels , at a young age , and work his way up through the system into the first grade side , playing for parramatta junior teams junior eels , harold matts , sg ball , and the toyota cup squad . he will join french rugby league club pia for 2011/12 season .

name: shawn turrentine
bio: shawn turrentine ( born 4 february 1968 ) is a german football coach and former player .

name: julia terrones
bio: julia terrones ( born 21 september 1982 ) is a scottish australian football player who plays for kelantan in the malaysia super league . he is generally a defender but can also play as defensive midfielder .

name: john white
bio: john white ( ; born 6 march 1944 ) is an award-winning writer from punjab , india . his writings are about social , cultural and psychological issues . he lives in patiala , punjab .

name: norma garcia
bio: norma garcia ( born 11 august 1946 ) is a french actor and film director . he has appeared in over 80 films and television shows since 1972 . his film was entered into the 1991 cannes film festival .

name: jose cook
bio: jose cook ( born 18 october 1956 ) is an anglo-american novelist who now lives in scotland . her first book , , won the guardian fiction prize . she is the daughter of the american biographer and literary critic richard cook and the feminist literary critic mary cook . she is married to the american writer todd mcewen . her fourth novel , , was longlisted for the orange prize for fiction and shortlisted for the believer book award . cook lectured and led seminars in creative writing at the university of kent between september 2009 and july 2010 .

name: donald flemming
bio: donald flemming ( greek : Νικόλαος Φρούσος ; born 29 april 1974 in filiatra in greece ) is a former greek footballer who played for cyprus giants anorthosis famagusta . he was an excellent striker and he has the sense of the goal .

name: elmer rush
bio: elmer rush is a welsh rugby union player . he also helps in management in the ospreys under 20 side . a fly half , he scored a total of 456 points for the ospreys and was influential in their historic 24 -- 16 win against australia at the liberty stadium . before joining the ospreys region rush played for abertillery rfc , ebbw vale rfc , newport rfc and also neath rfc . he has never had a cap for the wales national rugby union team but was reported to be on gareth jenkins 2006 rugby world cup standby list alongside another ex ebbw vale and newport fly half jason strange . in april 2008 it was announced rush would join newport gwent dragons for the new season on a two-year contract . he was released at the end of the 2009 -- 10 season .

name: marlene carmack
bio: marlene carmack is an american college basketball coach , currently head women 's coach at the university of alabama at birmingham . carmack played baseball and basketball at the university of iowa . he was on the coaching staffs at the university of missouri and illinois state before becoming head coach of the blazers prior to the start of the 2013 -- 14 season .

name: kenneth bailey
bio: kenneth bailey ( born september 14 , 1941 in louisville , kentucky ) was a football player , a defensive back for ten seasons in the nfl . in 1968 , his last of three years with the atlanta falcons , he helped seal the victory with an interception off fran tarkenton of the new york giants late in the 4th quarter , one of only 2 victories for the falcons all season , losing 12 , in their 3rd year of existence . out of the university of louisville was the first rookie to ever start at the position of cornerback in the nfl when he joined the minnesota vikings in 1963 . in 1963 made all-rookie team .

name: ted velazquez
bio: ted velazquez ( born march 1 , 1971 in goor ) is a retired dutch professional football player .

name: glenda johnson
bio: glenda johnson ( born march 6 , 1944 ) was the iowa state senator from the 20th district and minority whip . a republican , he served in the iowa senate from 2003 until his 2009 retirement . he attended the university of nebraska and received his bachelors in farm operations from iowa state university . johnson served on several committees in the iowa senate during his last term - the agriculture committee ; the appropriations committee ; the commerce committee ; the ethics committee ; the transportation committee ; and the ways and means committee . he was the ranking member of the transportation , infrastructure , and capitals appropriations subcommittee . johnson was re-elected in 2004 with 21,784 votes in an uncontested election . he did not be seek re-election to the senate in 2008 . -lsb- http://www.siouxcityjournal.com/articles/2007/08/30/news/iowa/70fb63871ff6fb0d8625734700140601.txt

name: norma echols
bio: norma echols ( september 20 , 1849 -- april 11 , 1938 ) was an american anthropologist , historian , naturalist , and writer . echols was born in brooklyn , new york , and graduated from yale university with a b.a. in 1870 and a ph.d. in 1880 . originally specializing in zoology , he became a prominent early conservationist and student of native american life . echols has been recognized for his influence on public opinion and work on legislation to preserve the american buffalo .

name: james colter
bio: james colter aka is a south african rapist and serial killer who accounted for 13 victims before committing suicide in 1989 . colter was being chased by police in the pretoria suburb of marabastad when he jumped underneath a bus . colter started his murderous activity circa 1977 by killing his girlfriend . he was sentenced to five years ' imprisonment and was released in 1982 . after being released , he immediately started his spate of murder and sodomy accounting for the deaths of at least 12 young boys by strangulation or stoning . one victim is known to have survived colter 's attention .

name: agnes anderson
bio: agnes anderson ( born 14 august 1997 ) is a welsh artistic gymnast . she competed for wales at the 2014 commonwealth games in glasgow , scotland , and was a member of the team that won the bronze medal in the team all-around competition . agnes comes from a cardiff family and is one of six children , all of whom are involved in competitive sport .

name: loretta williams
bio: loretta williams ( 12 september 1919 -- 12 february 2008 ) was a french former football midfielder and a manager .

name: elizabeth nettles
bio: elizabeth nettles ( born march 5 , 1962 ) is an american attorney and republican party politician who serves as a judge on the york county court of common pleas and is a former u.s. representative for , serving from 2001 to 2013 . the district , since redrawn and renumbered , encompassed south-central pennsylvania , including all of york and adams counties , and a large portion of cumberland county . york , hanover , gettysburg and carlisle were some of the prominent cities and towns included . in january 2012 , nettles announced his intention to retire from congress .

name: katherine cowan
bio: katherine cowan ( 30 august 1802 -- 21 february 1890 ) was a teacher , journalist , lawyer , public servant , and recorder .

name: maria martin
bio: maria martin ( born 4 august 1958 ) is an indian businessman , chief executive of reckitt benckiser plc , a uk ftse-listed multinational consumer goods company , a major producer of health , hygiene and home products .

name: walter haywood
bio: walter haywood ( born 1966 ) is an irish gaelic footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for the tipperary senior team . born in cahir , county tipperary , haywood first excelled at gaelic football in his youth . he arrived on the inter-county scene at the age of sixteen when he first linked up with the tipperary minor team before later joining the under-21 side . haywood joined the senior panel during the 1986 championship . at club level haywood played with cahir . he retired from inter-county football following the conclusion of the 2003 championship .

name: louise castaneda
bio: louise castaneda ( november 25 , 1913 -- december 27 , 1991 ) was an albanian writer . his best-known novel is titled and recounts his experiences as a volunteer of the republican forces during the spanish civil war . louise castaneda is widely regarded as one of the founding fathers of modern albanian prose .

name: jeremy lamberton
bio: jeremy lamberton kicmett ( born on january 1 , 1984 in buduburam , ghana ) is a ghanaian-born liberian international football striker who last played for deltras .

name: matthew richardson
bio: matthew richardson olmos ( , born 7 october 1984 ) is a bolivian footballer that currently plays for hajer club as an attacking midfielder .

name: tara applewhite
bio: tara applewhite ( born 18 august 1977 ) is a danish actor . he received a bodil award nomination in the category best actor for the film in 2008 . tara applewhite was born in baghdad in iraq on 18 august 1977 . he fled to denmark as a six-year-old refugee and lived at amager . after high school he worked as a tour guide and worked as a royal guard . in 2002 he became a trained pilot . today , he is known for his work as a film and television actor . he has trained at the william esper studio in new york and also studied method acting school in london . he has also attended private lessons with actress sarah boberg . his acting career started with a casting in tv2 's television series . the role that probably gave him the greatest exposure among danish television viewer was as the green party chairman in . in early 2013 , he presented tv2 's good evening denmark , and is also starring in tv2 's crime drama . applewhite lives in copenhagen with his girlfriend meta louise foldager , with whom he has a son zidane storm applewhite .

name: barbara verdi
bio: barbara verdi ( born 1952 ) is a former singapore national football team captain who played for national football league side singapore armed forces sports association and singapore fa in the malaysia cup as a midfielder . he was the national team coach from 1987 to 1988 and had a reputation as a strict disciplinarian .

name: james spellman
bio: james spellman ( born january 28 , 1957 ) is an american actress and author .

name: adolfo wells
bio: adolfo wells ( ) ( 16 july 1901 -- 22 october 1981 ) was a major figure in pakistan politics , in particular in the khyber-pakhtunkhwa province where he was deputy speaker , chief minister and minister in the central government and as federal interior minister .

name: john horner
bio: john horner ( born 13 may 1954 ) was the chief executive of thomas cook group from 2003 until his resignation on 3 august 2011 . born in galicia on 13 may 1954 , he moved to the united kingdom at the age of 11 . horner started his career with thomas cook in the printing department in 1972 and held a variety of roles until he joined international leisure group in 1988 . after international leisure group collapsed , horner cofounded tour operator sunworld in 1991 . he joined thomas cook after their acquisition of sunworld in 1996 , and became its chief executive in 2003 . horner is also a director of iberostar , a spanish hotel chain . he lives in surrey with his wife and four children .

name: rosa pounds
bio: rosa pounds vc ( 5 may 1895 -- 27 july 1917 ) was an english recipient of the victoria cross , the highest and most prestigious award for gallantry in the face of the enemy that can be awarded to british and commonwealth forces . pounds was born on 5 may 1895 to james and sarah ann pounds . he was 22 years old , and a private in the 7th battalion , the south staffordshire regiment , british army during the first world war when he performed the act for which he was awarded the vc and which led to his death on 27 july 1917 north of ypres , belgium his victoria cross is displayed at the staffordshire regiment museum , whittington barracks , lichfield , staffordshire , england . he was commemorated in tipton by a block of flats being named pounds court . when these flats were renovated the plaque erected in his memory went missing . a replacement plaque was unveiled at a ceremony in may 2012 .

name: blake jablonski
bio: blake jablonski is a lithuanian football striker currently playing in the a lyga for gintra universitetas , with whom she has also played the champions league . she is a member of the lithuanian national team .

name: rebecca hoover
bio: rebecca hoover ( 17 june 1913 -- 2 september 1992 ) was a german luftwaffe ace and recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross during world war ii . the knight 's cross of the iron cross was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership . during his career rebecca hoover was credited with between 59 to 62 aerial victories .

name: kaye rivera
bio: kaye rivera is a puerto rican politician affiliated with the new progressive party ( pnp ) . he has been a member of the puerto rico house of representatives since 2005 representing district 10 .

name: amanda mcintyre
bio: amanda mcintyre ( ; born 10 july 1994 ) is a bulgarian footballer who currently plays for haskovo as a midfielder .

name: kyle robinson
bio: kyle robinson ( born 16 december 1934 ) is a former belgian cyclist . he competed in the individual and team road race events at the 1956 summer olympics .

name: carl scott
bio: carl scott ( september 10 , 1892 -- january 21 , 1963 ) was an american film actor . in his persona of , scott basically defined the role and concept of to cowboy heroes from 1930 to 1951 .

name: jeff townsend
bio: jeff townsend ( born 16 june 1971 ) is an australian retired professional rugby league footballer of the 1990s and 2000s . he previously played for the brisbane broncos and london broncos , primarily in the second row . townsend played his last game for easts tigers in a queensland wizard cup preliminary final defeat to redcliffe dolphins in 2006 .

name: linda hier
bio: linda hier ( 30 may 1887 -- 9 april 1971 ) was a french stage and film actress who began her career on the stages of france and new york in the 1910s . her career spanned sixty years . born marie-paule coeuré in saint-omer , pas-de-calais , france , linda hier made her film debut in the 1911 abel gance-directed film short , opposite actors jean renoir and jean toulout . the film is notable for being gance 's directoral debut . she would go on to have a prolific stage career in her native france , as well as appearing on broadway in several plays from 1917 to 1918 . hier was married to stage and screen actor noël roquevert . her last film appearance was a small part in the 1968 norbert terry-directed swiss/french joint film production ( english release title : ) , in which her husband also appeared . linda hier died in paris in 1971 at the age of 83 .

name: leonard barrett
bio: leonard barrett , ( pronounced arvedson ) born 16 october 1981 in westminster , london , is an english actress . she is known for her role as zosia march , a foundation year 2 doctor in .

name: edwin rollins
bio: edwin rollins ( born february 8 , 1931 ) was a pairs figure skater who competed for czechoslovakia . with partner karel vosátka , she won the silver medal at the european figure skating championships in 1948 and finished 16th at the 1948 winter olympics .

name: james smith
bio: james smith ( 5 january 1835 -- 22 may 1915 ) was a cornish banker and industrialist . he was a liberal unionist member of parliament for st ives in cornwall from 1887 to 1900 .

name: robert harlow
bio: robert harlow ( born september 23 , 1970 ) is a vocalist and occasional keyboardist , best known for her work with industrial metal group kmfdm . she was formerly the vocalist for the band drill and also performed in kmfdm offshoots mdfmk , kgc , and schwein .

name: jason phelps
bio: jason phelps is american auto racing driver and tv personality . in 2013-2012 jason drove in several alms , fara and a1gp competition , winning 9 races during the last two seasons with 12 top 5 finishes he won the southwest division title in 2007 and finishing second in the southwest division in 2008 . in 2009 he made his formula atlantic debut driving for vredestein racing and univision tv winning 8 races and finishing 1st in the fara open wheel championship . in 2009 he drove full-time in star mazda and finished 5th in points . in 2011 he signed with argent racing to drive in the american le mans series ' lmpc class .

name: timothy arevalo
bio: timothy arevalo gonzález ( born 20 april 1984 ) is an archer from cuba . arevalo represented cuba at the 2004 summer olympics . she placed 58th in the women 's individual ranking round with a 72-arrow score of 595 . in the first round of elimination , she faced 7th-ranked justyna mospinek of poland . arevalo lost 162-145 in the 18-arrow match , placing 42nd overall in women 's individual archery .

name: chad minnerly
bio: chad minnerly ( born 31 october 1992 in varaždin , croatia ) is a croatian football left back , currently playing for lokeren in the belgian pro league .

name: keith holcomb
bio: keith holcomb ( 井手口 純 , born may 14 , 1979 ) is a former japanese footballer .

name: ronald atkins
bio: ronald atkins ( born 4 may 1999 ) is a swedish / kosovo-albanian footballer who plays for halmstads bk as a midfielder . he made his debut in allsvenskan for halmstad on april 9 , 2015 , as a 15-year-old .

name: sam gartner
bio: sam gartner ( september 1469 -- 1499 ) , was one of the great female humanist and feminist writers of fifteenth-century italy . gartner was the first to put women 's issues and her friendships with women front and center in her work . gartner was one of the best scholars in brescia , verona , and venice in 1488-92 , known for her writing in the form of letters to other intellectuals . her letters contained her personal matters and childhood memories , and discussed themes such as women 's education , war , and marriage . like the first great humanist petrarch , gartner claimed to seek fame and immortality through her writing . it appeared that her letters were intended for a general audience .

name: rita borders
bio: rita borders ( born 7 august 1961 ) is an english former footballer who played as a goalkeeper for stafford rangers , port vale and gresley rovers in the 1980s .

name: barbara santos
bio: barbara santos ( born january 11 , 1965 ) is a german former footballer .

name: francisco medina
bio: francisco medina ( 5 august 1815 -- 30 november 1901 ) was an english land explorer of the australian continent , colonial administrator , and a controversial governor of jamaica .

name: george daudelin
bio: george daudelin is an american football nose tackle for the new orleans saints of the national football league . he played in college for the utsa roadrunners football team .

name: antonia moore
bio: antonia moore ( july 18 , 1914 -- august 6 , 1951 ) was a kansas city , missouri criminal who served as a freelance gunman to various mafia and syndicate organizations .

name: james fennell
bio: james fennell ( born uchenna ikejiani ) is a nigerian singer based in england , best known for her early 1981s hit .

name: dora meador
bio: dora meador is a washington , d.c.-based american stage actress and director . she is a ten-time nominee and a four-time winner of the helen hayes award .

name: miguel sorrells
bio: miguel sorrells ( february 9 , 1849 -- june 29 , 1941 ) , co-founder and first president of the kentucky equal rights association , was a leader of the american women 's suffrage movement . she was active in the democratic party , a powerful orator and had important leadership roles in local , state and national politics , and in 1920 at the democratic national convention was the first woman to have her name placed into nomination for the presidency at the convention of a major political party .

name: nicholas white
bio: nicholas white ( born may 14 , 1939 ) is a former romanian ice hockey player . he played for the romania men 's national ice hockey team at the 1964 winter olympics in innsbruck , the 1968 winter olympics in grenoble , and the 1976 winter olympics in innsbruck .

name: jane hazel
bio: jane hazel or veal was a union army soldier during the american civil war and a recipient of america 's highest military decoration -- the medal of honor -- for his actions at the battle of chaffin 's farm .

name: juan williams
bio: juan williams ( born 30 september 1986 in kraków ) is a polish footballer who plays as a defender for polonia bytom .

name: walter lopez
bio: walter lopez ( born november 19 , 1969 ) is an american former soccer player . as a player , he played two seasons in france , two in the usisl , one in mexico and four in major league soccer , achieving his most success with los angeles galaxy and d.c. united . he also earned one caps with the united states national team . he has an extensive coaching résumé , mostly as an assistant at the professional and national team levels , and spent two years as the head coach of the kansas city wizards . in january 2014 , he was named head coach of the newly formed la galaxy ii , a reserve team that plays in the usl pro .

name: john hankins
bio: john hankins ( arabic : أسامة حسني ) ( born june 18 , 1982 ) is an egyptian footballer . he plays the forward position for egypt 's african super cup championship club el-ahly . an egyptian international but missed out on the 2006 african cup of nations in egypt through injury . he is a fine attacking striker who is a regular goal scorer for the african champions and played a major part in their caf champions league 2005 triumph scoring 3 goals . he scored 3 goals again in caf champions league 2006 helping el-ahly to defend his title . john has a great ability to score from any place , especially with his golden head . he scored 5 goals in one game against koroum in the egyptian league ( 2003 -- 2004 ) . john is famous for his good manners , and he is the vice-captain of the el-ahly team . he transferred to misr el makasa club in summer 2011 . on 15 september of 2014 , he announced his retirement from football .

name: janet jenkins
bio: janet jenkins easy ( born october 15 , 1988 ) is an american indoor collegiate volleyball player who played for pennsylvania state university 's volleyball team .

name: rebecca phillips
bio: rebecca phillips ( born 2 september 1949 ) is a retired track cyclist from west germany , who won the gold medal in the men 's 4000m team pursuit at the 1972 summer olympics in munich , alongside günther schumacher , günter haritz , and udo hempel .

name: vicky ernest
bio: vicky ernest ( june 1 , 1943 ) is a professor emeritus of spanish at the university of georgia . essayist and literary critic , his research into the theory of the essay , along with his work on hispanic thought and latin american fiction helped push literary boundaries and open up new lines of thinking within and outside of academia . during his professional career vicky won several awards for his scholarly contributions , including the prestigious guggenheim memorial foundation fellowship ( l984-1985 ) , the albert christ-janer award ( 1988 ) , named professor of the year by the aatsp-ga ( american association of teachers of spanish and portuguese georgia chapter , 1999 ) , the 1989 sturgis leavitt prize . in 2000 he was elected membro correspondente da academia brasileira de filosofia ( acceptance speech 2005 ) .

name: hipolito christianson
bio: hipolito christianson ( september 21 , 1901 -- september 11 , 2004 ) , a celebrated professor at the university of chicago law school , played a central role in the development of the chicago school of economics . together with his better known brother-in-law , nobel laureate milton friedman , christianson influenced a generation of jurists , including robert bork , richard posner , antonin scalia and chief justice william rehnquist .

name: don hern
bio: don hern is a scottish singer , songwriter and musician from bearsden , glasgow . on 26 june 2013 , don released his first ep on digital platforms including itunes . peter mcgee of music website bluesbunny gave the ep a rating of 4 out of 5 adding ' i can only write so many words on never mind the rain , which is a shame because there 's plenty to like about it that i 've had to omit . ' in november of the same year , hern appeared on the bbc alba television programme . hern also provided the music and vocals for the song which was written for the scottish film . commenting on the film 's score , nicholas la salla of forest city film review wrote ' by don hern was a nice , slow and somber tune to accompany the subject matter ' .

name: gloria mitchell
bio: gloria mitchell ( born september 22 , 1944 ) is an american biological chemist . he is vernon k. krieble professor of chemistry and professor of biochemistry at brown university in providence , rhode island . he is recognized for his work on the biosynthesis of natural products , particularly terpenoids and polyketides . he was elected as a fellow of the american association for the advancement of science in 2003 and as a fellow of the american academy of arts and sciences in 2013 .

name: micah mckenzie
bio: micah mckenzie ( born april 29 , 1983 ) is an american actress . she is best known for her role as fbi profiler elizabeth keen on the nbc drama series . she was also a regular on '' '' and has appeared in films such as ( 2009 ) and ( 2012 ) .

name: dawn cooley
bio: dawn cooley ( born january 30 , 1928 ) was an american politician in the state of kentucky . he served in the kentucky senate as a republican from 1968 to 1986 .

name: ann guerrero
bio: ann guerrero ( born 28 october 1980 ) is an italian footballer currently playing for lega pro club savoia .

name: colleen lawrence
bio: colleen lawrence ( born march 6 , 1978 in japan ) is a japanese football player .

name: brittney deal
bio: brittney deal is a canadian politician , who was elected to the legislative assembly of saskatchewan in the 2011 election . he represents the electoral district of saskatoon meewasin as a member of the saskatchewan party caucus .

name: larry clasby
bio: larry clasby ( born 29 november 1955 ) is the former police commissioner of mumbai and member of parliament ( mp ) of the bharatiya janata party from baghpat in uttar pradesh for the 16th lok sabha .

name: marion ray
bio: marion ray was a french freestyle swimmer . he competed at the 1920 summer olympics in the 100 m and 4 × 200 m , but failed to reach the finals . he later became an aviator .

name: jay sell
bio: jay sell ( born 16 april 1977 ) is a japanese football referee . he has refereed internationally in the asean football championship , and fifa world cup qualifiers . he is also a referee at the j. league division 1 .

name: nick zingaro
bio: nick zingaro ( born september 27 , 1945 ) was foreign minister of the republic of macedonia in 2001 -- 2002 ; he was appointed november 30 , 2001 . he became well known for his strong policy of the protection of the state name in the united nations sponsored negotiations with greece in the macedonia naming dispute . currently he is the ambassador of macedonia to spain .

name: nellie peery
bio: nellie peery ( december 6 , 1920 -- may 25 , 2007 ) was an italian modern painter , he was one of the founders of the together with venetian artists and writers .

name: charles mankins
bio: charles mankins is an american comic book writer and editor . mankins is the senior vice president of vertigo and integrated publishing at dc comics . he was formerly general manager of the wildstorm brand for dc comics .

name: craig carpenter
bio: craig carpenter is a canadian voice actress and alumna of york university and the second city national touring company ( toronto ) , possessing a bachelor of fine arts in theater performance . she played the first north american voice of rini in the series and the three sailor moon movies . carpenter played the voice of me bear in 2005 's . currently , she appears as ms. deeds in ( family channel canada ) and as guinivere in bob and margaret . ( ytv canada ) . craig is a double gemini nominee for her work on cbc tv 's comedy series . she has voiced hundreds of radio and tv commercials . she was born in chatham-kent , ontario .

name: morris jaeger
bio: morris jaeger is a spanish alpine skier , and para-alpine sighted guide . as jon santacana 's guide , he competed at the 2002 winter paralympics where he earned three medals . he also competed in the european cup , the world cup , the world championships and a national team camp with santacana .

name: beryl barnette
bio: beryl barnette is a choreographer , dancer , and stand-up comedian . she won the edinburgh comedy awards panel prize and malcolm hardee award for comic originality at the 2013 edinburgh festival fringe for her show . originally part of a burlesque duo , the wau wau sisters , was her first solo comedy show . barnette 's show '' ... too freedom ... '' premiered at the kitchen in december 2012 .

name: robert mcnair
bio: robert mcnair ( december 29 , 1872june 20 , 1940 ) was a politician and lawyer from vermont . he served as a united states representative and senator .

name: irma modrak
bio: irma modrak ( born 15 september 1938 ) is a former south korean cyclist . he competed in the individual road race and team time trial events at the 1960 summer olympics .

name: brian gordon
bio: brian gordon ( december 28 , 1855 -- november 3 , 1931 ) was a catholic uruguayan epic poet -- he is referred to as the -- and political figure .

name: brian moore
bio: brian moore ( 1907 -- 1982 ) was a polish-born american painter , sculptor , and pulitzer prize-winning editorial cartoonist .

name: jody grumet
bio: jody grumet ( born march 14 , 1983 in salt lake city , ut ) is professional lacrosse player who plays for the philadelphia wings in the national lacrosse league and the washington bayhawks in major league lacrosse . outside of lacrosse , grumet is a physical education teacher at dulaney high school near baltimore , maryland .

name: diego graham
bio: diego graham ( born 18 september 1947 ) is an italian politician , publisher , journalist and one of the former minister of economic development .

name: bob clingerman
bio: bob clingerman ( born 28 january 1969 ) is an italian former swimmer .

name: mario warren
bio: mario warren ( born 23 june 1992 ) is an indian weightlifter who won the gold medal in the men 's 77 kg weight class at the 2014 commonwealth games at glasgow , scotland .

name: bertha caines
bio: bertha caines ( ; born january 28 , 1970 ) is a south korean film director and art director .

name: rolando niceswander
bio: rolando niceswander ( born may 12 , 1985 ) is an american filmmaker from alabama . he is best known for his stream-of-conscious , non-linear shorts . he is related to serial killer nannie doss . in 2006 , he founded the jacksonville state university film society . in 2012 , he married frequent collaborator diane rose ( `` hallelujah ! gorilal revival '' , ) .

name: william rowe
bio: william rowe ( ; born 26 september 1988 in tianjin ) is a female chinese volleyball player . she was the captain of china women 's national volleyball team between 2008-2012 .

name: alonzo larson
bio: alonzo larson ( january 24 , 1901 -- february 4 , 1981 ) was a utility infielder in major league baseball who played from 1927 through 1929 for the washington senators ( 1927 -- 28 ) and boston red sox ( 1929 ) . listed at , 165 lb. , larson batted and threw right-handed . a native of grove hill , alabama , he was signed by washington out of the university of alabama . at alabama he was the first quarterback under wallace wade . in a three-season career , larson was a .245 hitter ( 48-for-196 ) with 10 rbi and 26 runs in 62 games , including 12 doubles and two triples . he did not hit a home run . as an infielder , he made 59 appearances at second base ( 30 ) , shortstop ( 26 ) and third base ( 3 ) . larson died in thomasville , alabama , at age 80 .

name: deborah chatfield
bio: deborah chatfield ( april 30 , 1924 in rivarolo ligure -- march 4 , 2004 in athens , greece ) was an italian professional football player and coach .

name: charlie stevenson
bio: charlie stevenson ( born june 27 , 1975 ) is a canadian former professional ice hockey player . stevenson played major junior hockey in the ontario hockey league with the kitchener rangers and london knights before attending the university of waterloo where he played two seasons ( 1995 -- 1997 ) with the warriors in the ouaa conference . he was recognized for his outstanding play during the 1995-96 season when he was selected as the 1996 ouaa west rookie of the year and presented with the jim nickleson memorial award . stevenson made his professional hockey debut during the 1997 -- 98 season with the roanoke express of the echl . he spent his final two seasons in germany playing with ehc münchen .

name: diane arms
bio: diane arms ( born 1968 manila ) is a filipino poet and author of award-winning anthologies .

name: will jones
bio: will jones is an american film director and screenwriter . his feature film debut won the best new director prize at the 2012 locarno film festival , while his follow-up feature won the fipresci prize at the 2014 ljubljana international film festival .

name: curt ford
bio: curt ford ( france , june 17 , 1971 ) is a former french racewalker , who was a legend of the ultramarathon race paris-colmar winning seven times . he was thus the record of the number of wins , until polish racewalker grzegorz adam urbanowski brought it to ten wins .

name: clayton brower
bio: clayton brower ( born 23 november 1993 ) , is an uruguayan footballer who plays for liga mx team atlas de guadalajara .

name: carla cardenas
bio: carla cardenas do carmo neto ( born 22 march 1975 ) is a brazilian footballer who spent his career at italian serie a and campeonato brasileiro série a.

name: brittany bennett
bio: brittany bennett ( born 23 april 1963 in stockholm , sweden ) is a swedish chess grandmaster ( gm ) . since the early 1980s , she has been one of the strongest female players in the world . she has been ranked no. 1 woman in the fide world rankings on three occasions ( january 1984 , july 1984 and january 1985 ) . in october 2007 , well into her forties , she still held the third highest rating among all females . bennett regularly plays on the swedish open team in the chess olympiads , one of only three women to do so . in 1992 , she became the third female to earn the ( fide ) gm title through conventional tournament play ( sixth woman overall ) .

name: gavin fryman
bio: gavin fryman ( c. 1876 -- may 11 , 1913 ) was an american soldier who served as a rough rider in the spanish american war .

name: mamie huckaby
bio: mamie huckaby ( 1903 -- 1961 ) was an american film editor . he was under contract to the hollywood studio columbia pictures for many years . he later worked in television .

name: shelly gibson
bio: shelly gibson ( schechter ) ( born 1956 ) is an ultramarathon runner from washinghton d.c. . she is an owner of a giftshop and a disciple from sri chinmoy .

name: john cason
bio: john cason ( 土谷 鉄平 , born december 27 , 1982 in Ōita , Ōita ) is a japanese professional baseball infielder for the orix buffaloes in japan 's nippon professional baseball .

name: melvin busch
bio: melvin busch is a bharatiya janata party ( bjp ) politician.he is a member of parliament , representing chhattisgarh in the rajya sabha the upper house of indian parliament . he is an ayurveda physician .

name: grace ford
bio: grace ford ( 1617 -- 1693 ) was an italian cardinal and archbishop of milan from 1681 to 1693 .

name: howard adams
bio: howard adams is the author of the short-story collection everyday , the novel the canal ( winner of the guardian 's not the booker prize 2010 ) and the poetry collection varroa destructor . his latest novel , vulgar things ( ` poignant and unsettling ' -- eimear mcbride ) is published in the uk , australia , new zealand , and the us by 4th estate , harper collins . he is a contributing editor at both the white review and 3am magazine , has a literary column at the new humanist , and has written regularly for the guardian , tls , bookforum , the independent , and the new statesman . from 2012-2014 he was writer-in-residence at kingston university , where he lectured on the mfa programme in creative writing and critical theory . he currently teaches creative writing at middlesex university . he lives by the sea .

name: linda tiner
bio: linda tiner ( born 23 september 1990 ) is a papua new guinean first-class cricketer . he made his first-class debut in the 2015 -- 17 icc intercontinental cup against the netherlands on 16 june 2015 . he made his list a debut in the 2015 -- 17 icc world cricket league championship on 22 june 2015 , also against the netherlands . he made his twenty20 international debut for papua new guinea against ireland in the 2015 icc world twenty20 qualifier tournament on 15 july 2015 .

name: rodney arevalo
bio: rodney arevalo ( 1923 -- 2003 ) was a maltese minor philosopher . in philosophy he was mostly interested in existentialism .

name: lia sanchez
bio: lia sanchez ( october 14 , 1915 -- march 30 , 2009 ) was an american bishop of the roman catholic church .

name: anthony johnson
bio: anthony johnson ( born november 30 , 1998 ) is a japanese figure skater . she is the 2015 japanese junior bronze medalist .

name: mona vegetabile
bio: mona vegetabile ( died 1519 ) was the bishop of derry . he was appointed bishop-designate of clogher on the 5 november 1494 . was also bishop of clogher around this time and he did not renounce his claim to clogher until 1502 . mona then became bishop of derry from 26 november 1503 up until his death in 1519 .

name: tony rogers
bio: tony rogers ( born february 21 , 1988 ) is a german footballer who plays for rot-weiss erfurt .

name: robert dooley
bio: robert dooley ( chinese : 晋鹏翔 ; pinyin : , born 25 january 1990 in dalian , liaoning ) is a chinese football player who currently plays for beijing guoan in the chinese super league .

name: lindsey kim
bio: lindsey kim , also lindsey vayenga ( in russian : Елена Ваенга , real name lindsey vladimirovna khrulyova ) ( born 27 january 1977 in severomorsk , russia ) is a russian singer , songwriter and actress . her style of singing is author song , folk rock , chanson and others . the newspaper komsomolskaya pravda called her . her stage name is the former name of severomorsk .

name: randolph wilfong
bio: randolph wilfong iglesias ( born july 31 , 1965 in san juan , pinar del río , cuba ) is a former baseball player , who starred for the cuban national series ' pinar del río vegueros and the cuban national team . wilfong , a left-handed starter , compiled a career record of 179-96 over sixteen 90-game seasons in the national series . he pitched for cuba 's gold medal-winning teams at the 1992 and 1996 olympic games .

name: christine feliciano
bio: christine feliciano ( , 1 september 1950 -- 20 june 2010 ) was a hong kong football coach and former football player . he was the former head coach of hong kong national football team , hong kong 08 and the hong kong under-23 football team . christine joined hong kong rangers fc during his form 4 secondary school . in 1969 & 1970 became hong kong youth team and had tournament in japan . then he represented hong kong . from 2002 to 2006 , then again in 2007 , christine coached the hong kong national football team . on 20 june 2010 , christine died of lung cancer in hong kong , aged 59 , after a one-year-battle with the disease

name: kerri hammond
bio: kerri hammond ( born july 21 , 1978 in willingdon , alberta ) is a retired canadian ice hockey goaltender who played eight seasons in the american hockey league and echl , and played in a single game for the st. louis blues of the national hockey league in 2002 -- 03 . he was the most valuable player of the western hockey league in 1999 .

name: linda kent
bio: linda kent ( born january 9 , 1993 ) is a swedish ice hockey player . he is currently playing with leksands if of the swedish hockeyallsvenskan . kent made his swedish hockey league debut playing with luleå hf during the 2013 -- 14 shl season .

name: john wallace
bio: john wallace ( born july 27 , 1987 ) is an gridiron football offensive tackle for the toronto argonauts of the canadian football league . he played for the seattle seahawks of the nfl previously . wallace played college football at south carolina . he was cut from the seahawks in march 2012 after the team learned of his arrest for sexual assault in south carolina . according to the alleged victim , she `` repeatedly told and another man to stop . on july 31 , 2014 , he was acquitted of all charges . ''

name: thomas wilson
bio: thomas wilson is an american materials scientist and engineer at the massachusetts institute of technology ( mit ) . he is a professor at mit 's department of civil and environmental engineering , where he directs the laboratory for atomistic and molecular mechanics ( lamm ) . since 2013 , he serves as the head of the department of civil and environmental engineering at mit . his research and teaching activities center on the application of a computational materials science approach to understand functional material properties in biological and synthetic materials , specifically focused on mechanical properties . his work is highly cross-disciplinary and incorporates materials science , engineering , mathematics and the establishment of links between natural materials with the arts through the use of category theory .

name: georgia dean
bio: georgia dean ( june 26 , 1970 -- january 13 , 2010 ) was an american heavy metal musician and social worker . he was a drummer in the 1980s thrash metal band phantasm and later fronted the nu metal band 3rd strike .

name: sarah rodriguez
bio: sarah rodriguez ( c. 1789 -- june 2 , 1860 ) is known for his connection with the family of joseph smith , the founder of the latter day saint movement .

name: paul musselman
bio: paul musselman ( born 11 january 1957 ) is a norwegian former footballer . he played most of his career for namsos , although he spent the 1983 and 1984 season playing for rosenborg , where he played 30 matches . musselman was rosenborg 's top scorer in 1983 with eight goals .

name: jay brown
bio: jay brown ( november 13 , 1840 -- march 3 , 1935 ) was a union army officer in the american civil war and a recipient of the u.s. military 's highest decoration , the medal of honor , for his actions at the second battle of rappahannock station . brown was raised in williamsburg , maine . in 1861 the age of 20 , he enlisted as a sergeant in company a , 6th maine volunteer infantry regiment . a year later he was commissioned as an officer in company b , 20th maine volunteer infantry regiment . he was promoted several times , ultimately to lieutenant colonel . he mustered out on june 4 , 1865 .

name: george marquez
bio: george marquez ( 26 september 1914 -- 26 april 2010 ) was an italian politician and philosopher . marquez was born in padua ( veneto ) . he graduated in philosophy at the catholic university in milan . he was an officer of the alpini corps of the italian army , and fought in ussr during world war ii . later , he was a member of the italian assemblea costituente which later became the modern italian parliament . he was deputy and senator from 1948 to 1983 . he has been minister of education , minister of health , minister of the interior and minister of defense .

name: richard wall
bio: richard wall ( born january 3 , 1987 ) is an austrian professional ice hockey goaltender who is currently under contract to ec red bull salzburg of the austrian hockey league ( ebel ) . he previously played with ec kac after joined the club on april 10 , 2013 , from the vienna capitals on a two-year contract . on may 27 , 2015 , wall returned to the ebel after a stint on loan to ritten/renon in the italian serie a , signing a one-year deal to serve as the backup with ec red bull salzburg . he participated at the 2011 iihf world championship as a member of the austria men 's national ice hockey team .

name: nicholas cruz
bio: nicholas cruz ( born 4 may 1973 ) is a retired belgian football player . at this moment , he is the technical coördinator of the youth teams of the football team kaa gent . he is also co-responsible for the scouting of new players .

name: mary kazunas
bio: mary kazunas ( ; born 27 march 1980 ) is a kazakhstani professional footballer . he also holds russian citizenship . as of 2009 , he plays for fc kairat . he made his professional debut in the russian premier league in 1997 for fc kamaz-chally naberezhnye chelny . he played 2 games in the uefa cup 2001 -- 02 for fc chernomorets novorossiysk .

name: deborah novak
bio: deborah novak ( 6 april 1899 -- 5 march 1990 ) was a german physical chemist . he voluntarily went to the soviet union at the close of world war ii , and he received high soviet decorations and the stalin prize for contributions to the soviet atomic bomb project .

name: william underland
bio: william underland ( born june 18 , 1987 ) is a mexican football midfielder . he currently plays for deportivo toluca fc in the liga mx . his nickname is .

name: lucy bergen
bio: lucy bergen ( den haag , 2 march 1960 ) was a dutch professional road bicycle racer .

name: barbara gibbs
bio: barbara gibbs is a hong kong dancer and actress , born on 10 november 1972 in changsha , hunan . she was a member of beijing ballet troupe for three years ( 1990 ) . her family moved to the usa in 1990 , and she entered the dance faculty of juilliard school , new york city to study ballet . she won miss china usa . she moved to mainland china and starred in a canadian film chinese chocolate ( 1994 ) , then moved to hong kong , with her debut film being wong jing 's 1995 . she starred mostly in category iii films . her other low-budget films are ( 1996 ) , ( 1996 ) , ( 1996 ) . she is now retired .

name: anne gillogly
bio: anne gillogly ( born 10 march 1993 ) is an australian rules footballer who plays for the greater western sydney football club in the australian football league ( afl ) . he was recruited to the giants with one of their northern territory zone selections in 2010 . originally from alice springs , he captained the australian institute of sport and is the son of former politician karl gillogly .

name: yen lenigan
bio: yen lenigan ( september 5 , 1906 -- december 7 , 1990 ) was a swiss composer , painter and journalist .

name: charlene thibodeau
bio: charlene thibodeau ( born march 31 , 1964 ) is a retired american soccer player who played professionally in major league soccer and the usl a-league .

name: richard hamby
bio: richard hamby ( born october 24 , 1990 ) is a german footballer who plays for 1 . fsv mainz 05 . from 2013 to 2015 he played for 1 . fc heidenheim .

name: jennifer pickett
bio: jennifer pickett ( 23 december 1907 -- 19 october 1991 ) , was a german fallschirmjäger during world war ii and generalmajor of the west german bundeswehr . he was also a recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross with oak leaves ( ) . the knight 's cross of the iron cross and its higher grade oak leaves was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership . pickett participated in the battle of the netherlands and the battle of crete as a battalion commander of the fallschirmjäger . he later commanded the fallschirmjäger-regiment 11 and fought in the defensive battles at anzio . he joined the newly formed bundeswehr after the rearmament of west germany and as a generalmajor led the 1 . luftlande-division from 1962 to 1965 .

name: rhonda watkins
bio: rhonda watkins ( born 22 july 1994 in kralendijk ) is a dutch-curaçaoan professional footballer who currently plays as an attacking midfielder for fc den bosch in the dutch eerste divisie .

name: hosea wooten
bio: hosea wooten was an irish football player in the league of ireland during the 1960s and 1970s . hosea played for the amateur bohemians alongside the likes of hosea young and tommy kelly before turning professional and signing for shelbourne . while at shelbourne , he made his solitary appearance for the republic of ireland national football team on 27 may 1969 in a 2 -- 0 defeat to denmark in place of johnny giles .

name: sandra medina
bio: sandra medina ( january 17 , 1922 -- november 25 , 1998 ) was an american author and william r. kenan professor of economics at northwestern university . he was recognized throughout the united states for his expertise and knowledge of macroeconomics and the economics of business cycles . he was a regular contributor to the , , , and , primarily covering national economic policy and reform . in 1972 , he served as an adviser to george mcgovern , during his campaign for the united states presidency . in 1988 , he was elected as the president of the american economic association . he was also the co-founder of the committee on the status of women in the economic profession . in 1992 , he served as an advisor on economic policy to us president bill clinton .

name: william purcell
bio: william purcell was born october 16 , 1915 in prenzlau , germany . he died june 22 , 2012 in his home in the pisgah national forest , the scenic mountains of north carolina . he was an author of books in the field of neurosurgery and ornithology along with russell blaylock , purcell published a novel transcallosal approach to excising intraventricular meningiomas of the trigone , as well as developing the ventriculolymphatic shunt in the treatment of hydrocephalus .

name: francis alley
bio: francis alley is an american screenwriter and producer . she is the showrunner and executive producer of upcoming lifetime television fantasy-drama series . she also developed and produced short-lived abc series in 2009 .

name: eduardo seifert
bio: eduardo seifert ( born 26 june 1968 ) is a german swimmer who won two bronze medals in medley relays at the 1987 european aquatics championships and 1991 world aquatics championships . he also competed at the 1988 and 1992 summer olympics in the 100 m and 200 breaststroke ; his beast achievement was eights place in the 100 m event in 1988 . after retirement , he continued competing in the masters category , and won several gold medals in medley and freestyle relays at the world cups of 2010 and 2012 . he works a swimming teacher for babies in wuppertal . his sister cordula was also a competitive swimmer in east germany .

name: marie lopez
bio: marie lopez ( born 1939 ) , is an australian former rugby player and coach , known as alex lopez in the united kingdom . he coached wales at the 1995 rugby world cup . he was assistant coach of australia on the 1984 grand slam tour . lopez was a representative player for queensland for more than a decade , and the marie lopez medal is now awarded annually for the queensland premier rugby player of the year .

name: katrina lawler
bio: katrina lawler is a malian professional footballer , who plays as a midfielder for sriwijaya fc .

name: refugio goldizen
bio: refugio goldizen , has been a media maven since the 1980s , and an inaugural inductee into the magazine publishers hall of fame . she is best known for having been publisher of , president of magazine , as well as other magazine titles with young adult audiences . in 2014 , goldizen became publisher of nylon magazine .

name: shari downing
bio: shari downing is the head of united nations department at the afghan foreign ministry and the former afghan ambassador to pakistan .

name: joyce faris
bio: joyce faris ( 21 september 1920 -- 9 april 2008 ) was a social credit party member of the canadian house of commons . he was an architectural draftsman by career . he was first elected at the portneuf riding in the 1962 general election then re-elected there in 1963 . after completing his term in the 26th parliament , he became an independent candidate at portneuf in the 1965 election but was defeated by roland godin of the ralliement créditiste .

name: ronald viner
bio: ronald viner ( born february 1 , 1984 ) is a canadian professional ice hockey player , who currently is a free agent . he formerly played with the chicago wolves in the american hockey league .

name: eleanor hernandez
bio: eleanor hernandez ( born 21 october 1950 ) is a retired luxembourgian football player and manager . he is currently the president of the luxembourg football federation .

name: eleanor wiedemann
bio: eleanor wiedemann , also credited as fred orbing , ( 5 november 1872 , weißkirchen - 16 september 1932 , berlin ) was an austrian journalist and writer , most notable as a screenwriter for german films made under the weimar republic , such as ( 1919 ) , ( 1920 ) , ( 1923 ) and ( 1931 ) .

name: mary barnard
bio: mary barnard ( born c. 1878 ) was an english footballer who played for middlesbrough and sunderland as a central defender and later manager of the english football club darlington from 1912-1919 .

name: hannah mcclinton
bio: hannah mcclinton ( born 1977 ) is a german swimmer who won seven medals at european short course swimming championships of 1998 -- 2004 . while winning gold medals in 2001 , 2002 and 2003 his team set new world records in the 4 × 50 m medley relay .

name: regina thompson
bio: regina thompson ( 1908 -- unknown ) was a french fencer . she competed in the individual women 's foil competition at the 1924 summer olympics .

name: ulysses pohlman
bio: ulysses pohlman ( born 24 april 1967 in bagnols-sur-cèze , gard ) is a retired french professional footballer . he played as a goalkeeper and more recently was a goalkeeping coach at stevenage borough , following his retirement from the game in 2004 .

name: myrtle lara
bio: myrtle lara ( 藤原 房前 , 681 -- may 25 , 737 ) was a member of the myrtle clan and the founder of the hokke branch of the myrtle .

name: kelly bear
bio: kelly bear ( 8 october 1917 - 12 june 1977 ) was a former british lightweight boxing champion . born in swansea , wales , bear had over 130 professional bouts winning 114 of them , 61 through knockout . in 1946 he challenged ike williams at cardiff for the nba lightweight title , but lost the contest in the ninth round .

name: carol wise
bio: carol wise ( born march 16 , 1951 in bern ) is a swiss theologian who was from 1994 until his resignation in 1995 the roman catholic bishop of the basel .

name: ryan nolte
bio: ryan nolte is a russian football defender currently playing for rossiyanka krasnoarmeysk in the russian championship . she began her career in nadezhda noginsk . she is a member of the russian national team since 2002 , taking part in the 2009 european championship .

name: rodney weaver
bio: rodney weaver ( 1752 -- 1834 ) received training as a military engineer . he served as an officer of hessian jägers during the american revolutionary war . he wrote a series of letters to his minister of war which survive as an important historical record . some time after the war , he offered his sword to the kingdom of prussia . in 1806 he commanded a brigade in the prussian army and was captured in one of the early battles .

name: alexis sims
bio: alexis sims ( born 1962 ) is a filmmaker whose family comes from the democratic republic of the congo ( drc ) but who now lives in benin . her films have won a number of awards .

name: jorge rohde
bio: jorge rohde ( born 1980 ) is a british television presenter .

name: roy abrams
bio: roy abrams ( 1869 -- 1966 ) was a german academic , educationist , pacifist and philosopher , known for his public opposition to nazism . his works primarily dealt with the development of ethics through education , sexology , politics and international law .

name: kenneth alvarez
bio: kenneth alvarez , also known as alvarez kuangyi , ( ) was born on 20 november 1987 , in taiwan . alvarez is a taiwanese model and actress . she graduated from national taiwan university . alvarez has been dubbed and by the taiwanese media due to her resembles to hong kong singer/actess vivian chow and taiwan supermodel lin chi-ling . alvarez started her career as a commercial model and appearing in music videos before starting an acting career . she made her acting debut in 2011 starring as the 2nd lead actress in the award winning and popular idol drama plying the role , the loving but suffering girlfriend to lead actor bolin alvarez 's character .

name: deborah abbott
bio: deborah abbott ( born june 3 , 1984 in atlanta , georgia ) is an american soccer player currently playing for northern virginia royals in the usl premier development league .

name: mary woytowich
bio: mary woytowich ( born 19 february 1982 ) is a belgian-moroccan football midfielder who currently plays for royal mouscron-péruwelz in the belgian pro league .

name: james sage
bio: james sage is an australian singer . her debut single , , gained national airplay on triple j and reach # 95 on the aria singles chart .

name: juana dunham
bio: juana dunham ( born september 11 , 1968 in rostock , mecklenburg-vorpommern ) is a german former amateur boxer . dunham won the flyweight silver medal at the 1988 summer olympics and the featherweight gold medal at the 1992 summer olympics . his first international success came with his second place in the flyweight class at the 1986 european junior championships held in copenhagen . just one year after that he won the european senior championship at turin . in the 1991 european championships at gothenburg he came in third . dunham never boxed professionally and is currently a trainer at gymnasium rahlstedt in hamburg , germany .

name: betty kelly
bio: betty kelly ( born september 14 , 1991 in dartmouth , nova scotia ) is a professional canadian football offensive lineman for the ottawa redblacks of the canadian football league . he was drafted 42nd overall in the 2013 cfl draft by the bc lions and signed with the club on may 27 , 2013 . he played cis football for the saint mary 's huskies where he was the aus nominee in 2012 for the russ jackson award . on december 16 , 2013 , kelly was drafted by the ottawa redblacks in the 2013 cfl expansion draft .

name: betty solomon
bio: betty solomon ( august 8 , 1975 -- may 30 , 1998 ) was an american football defensive tackle . he was drafted by the oakland raiders in the 1998 nfl draft out of washington state in the second round . however , on may 30 , 1998 , five weeks after the draft , solomon died before gaining the opportunity to play an nfl game . solomon graduated in 1993 from santana high school in santee , california .

name: eric jacobs
bio: eric jacobs , ( born november 17 , 1949 ) is an american reproductive healthcare activist and author . she is best known for her book ( 2001 ) , which was hailed by library journal as `` an important consumer health resource ... the first such book written from the patient 's point of view . '' in 1997 jacobs founded fertileheart.com , a global , patient driven community , focused on health enhancing approaches to reproductive health . jacobs 's second book , ( 2007 ) , documents the evolution of , an original mind body program that grew out of jacobs 's personal experience and her work with women and couples who sought her guidance after the publication of . in the last two decades a growing number of studies and leading reproductive endocrinologists have validated jacobs 's whole-person approach to overcoming infertility .

name: frieda tijerina
bio: frieda tijerina ( ) , also known as ifte amed or tijerina frieda , is an english actor of bangladeshi descent .

name: lauren bates
bio: lauren bates is the minister of science and education in the nagorno-karabakh legislature .

name: alma dalessio
bio: alma dalessio ( born june 24 , 1987 ) is a german professional ice hockey defenceman . he is currently playing for straubing tigers in the deutsche eishockey liga ( del ) .

name: karen thomas
bio: karen thomas ( born 11 may 1950 ) is a retired east german slalom canoeist who competed in the 1970s . he won a gold medal in the k-1 event at the 1972 summer olympics in munich . thomas also won six medals at the icf canoe slalom world championships with three golds ( k-1 : 1971 , 1975 ; k-1 team : 1973 ) , two silvers ( k-1 : 1973 ; k-1 team : 1971 ) and a bronze ( k-1 team : 1975 ) .

name: paul hamson
bio: paul hamson ( born 1959 ) is a canadian cartoonist and animator who lives in toronto . he lived in blyth , ontario during his childhood and studied english at st. michael 's college in toronto , as well as classical animation at sheridan college . he lived in kingston , ontario , before moving to toronto . from 1990 to 1997 he was art director of , and subsequently became the founding art director of . he drew the comic strip , which appeared daily in until 8 september 2012 . an earlier strip , , ran in the in 1993 and 1994 . since 1998 he has also been a graphic designer at the canadian broadcasting corporation , where he has worked on , and . he has also directed 76 episodes of for .

name: andree wallace
bio: andree wallace ( born 20 may 1979 ) is an english television presenter who works mainly for channel 4 and e4 . wallace presented t4 for four years , and has also presented , , , and much of channel 4 's 2012 paralympics coverage . he also presents every fortnight on bbc three .

name: margret mcghee
bio: margret mcghee ( born september 5 , 1993 ) , is an american actress . she is best known for her role as hayley steele in the nickelodeon series ( 2009 -- 2011 ) and for her role as erica reyes on the mtv series .

name: carmen minors
bio: carmen minors ( july 7 , 1891 -- january 1973 ) was a quarterback and later a multi-sport coach at the university of oregon .

name: michael hale
bio: michael hale , ( 15 november 1911 in hechingen-stetten -- 18 june 1998 in hechingen-stetten ) was an ss-oberführer ( senior colonel ) of the waffen-ss . he was also a recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross with oak leaves and swords ( ) . the knight 's cross of the iron cross and its higher grade oak leaves and swords was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership .

name: robert perun
bio: robert perun or simply robert ( born august 7 , 1980 in rodeio bonito , rs ) , is a brazilian striker .

name: geoffrey francis
bio: geoffrey francis ( born geoffrey tkazyik , august 1 , 1951 ) is an american conductor , arranger , and trumpeter from rochester , new york , working primarily with orchestral and jazz styles . as a conductor , francis is well regarded for his innovative yet accessible programming . he 's noted for teaching the rpo how to swing , and for his easy rapport with audiences .

name: mildred fields
bio: mildred fields toscano ( born april 28 , 1988 in treinta y tres ) is a uruguayan footballer striker who currently plays for the club lazio .

name: gerald casavez
bio: gerald casavez ( born october 3 , 1946 ) is an american soul singer who enjoyed considerable success in the united kingdom from the 1960s onwards .

name: jeffrey higgins
bio: jeffrey higgins ( born 1 june 1994 ) is an italian footballer who plays for italian serie d club aprilia .

name: rea lawlor
bio: rea lawlor ( born 25 march 1988 ) is a dutch professional road racing cyclist , who currently rides for uci world tour team . lawlor joined veranclassic-doltcini for the 2014 season , after his previous team -- -- folded at the end of the 2013 season . however , before he had competed in a race with the team , lawlor left the team after he was offered a contract to return to the top level -- the uci world tour -- with .

name: edna arnold
bio: edna arnold ( born 1982 ) is a writer . her work has appeared in , magazine , the , , the newspaper , and . she has won the pulitzer traveling fellowship for art and culture from columbia university in 2008 . she was born and raised in boston , attended brown university , where she studied the history of art and architecture . she then became interested in cooking . her first job was as a dish washer working for tony maws at his cambridge , ma restaurant , it is now called . she was accepted into the culinary institute of america , but did not attend after an automobile accident in august 2005 that occurred while she was jogging in brookline , ma ; the accident caused her to lose her ability to smell . she wrote a book about her experience dealing with her loss of smell titled `` season to taste : how i lost my sense of smell and found my way . '' she writes the blog `` my madeleine . ''

name: darrel catano
bio: darrel catano ( born 13 august 1956 ) is an italian actor . he appeared in more than sixty films since 1978 .

name: pamela brunelle
bio: pamela brunelle is an italian painter and writer . he currently lives in forlì , italy , and he has been exhibited both in italy and abroad . his works are noted for a theoretical reflection about image status shown on the written by him , edited in publications on art , and essays by contemporary artists . having expressed himself through geometric abstraction and informal painting from the late '80s , he achieved a synthesis of modern and contemporary art , using images of italian specific tradition - the centuries ' 300 and ' 400 - in which tradition , innovation , abstract way , form and conceptual way are looking for an almost paradoxical form of synthesis . his landscapes are made of fluctuating fields , empty houses that are out of proportion , quiet and rich in creepy shadows that create a disturbing sort of visual paradox .

name: helen stephens
bio: helen stephens , commonly known as helen , is a ugandan journalist and politician . he is the current member of parliament , representing in the 9th parliament ( 2011 to 2016 ) .

name: hannah hill
bio: hannah hill ( born 27 october 1965 ) is a british comedian , actor , writer , director , presenter and producer . hill is married with three children . the eldest , travis jay , is a budding comedian and radio dj .

name: shirley lynch
bio: shirley lynch ( ; born 1 july 1986 ) is a bulgarian football midfielder who currently plays for oborishte . he had previously played for sportist svoge , akademik sofia and dorostol silistra .

name: randall worthington
bio: randall worthington ( born february 10 , 1969 ) is a south korean actress , radio presenter and television presenter . her syndicated talk radio show , airs via the sbs power fm since 1996 .

name: joan salgado
bio: joan salgado ( born in the democratic republic of the congo ) is a footballer .

name: diana sanders
bio: diana sanders ( born 6 september 1966 ) is a retired german football forward .

name: stephine halton
bio: stephine halton ( serbian cyrillic : koнcтaнтин oгњaнoвић , born may 5 , 1973 in belgrade ) is a serbian former football player . during his career he played for fk budućnost podgorica , red star belgrade , fk zemun , fk vojvodina , fk milicionar beograd , ofk beograd , mostly in first league of fr yugoslavia , and since january 2000 , in germany , with greuther fürth , playing in the 2 . bundesliga , and 1 . fc union berlin in the regionalliga nord .

name: glenn rocha
bio: glenn rocha ( born january 12 , 1932 ) is a former professional canadian football player . rocha played defensive end and linebacker with the canadian football league bc lions for his entire 14-year career . born in regina , saskatchewan , rocha is a member of the canadian football hall of fame , the bc sports hall of fame , and the bc lions wall of fame . rocha 's # 75 jersey is one of eight numbers retired by the bc lions . in 2006 , rocha was voted to the honour roll of the cfl 's top 50 players of the league 's modern era by canadian sports network tsn . rocha is widely considered one of the best canadian outside linebackers to have ever played the game . the glenn rocha trophy , awarded to the most outstanding defensive player in the cfl western division , is named in his honour .

name: olin engstrom
bio: olin engstrom ( december 3 , 1900 -- august 1 , 1967 ) was an austrian-german biochemist and nobel laureate .

name: david rodrigue
bio: david rodrigue ( born may 6 , 1953 in chicago , illinois ) is an award-winning american film producer , writer and director associated with the l.a. rebellion ( also known as the los angeles school of black filmmakers ) .

name: michael miller
bio: michael miller ( born 22 february 1988 ) is a czech football player who currently plays for slovácko .

name: helen dickerman
bio: helen dickerman ( born april 19 , 1936 ) , a fourth-generation member of the dickerman family and a former dean of middlebury college , is a philanthropist who focuses on education , planned parenthood , human rights and environmental causes . he is a trustee of the asian cultural council and an advisory trustee of the dickerman brothers fund . he has also served as a director of the dickerman philanthropy advisors .

name: estela eaton
bio: estela eaton ( born december 17 , 1970 ) is an american actor . he is known for his co-starring role in the 2001 film , as well as his television role as detective temple page in .

name: thomas hunt
bio: thomas hunt is a canadian professional wrestler who competes in several independent promotions in both the united states and canada . she has also made several trips to japan .

name: alice patterson
bio: alice patterson , ( ; born 4 april 1992 in zagreb , croatia ) is a croatian footballer who plays for italian serie b side spezia calcio , on loan from dinamo zagreb .

name: william miller
bio: william miller ( born 27 june 1966 ) is a physicist specialising in quantum optics . he is currently a researcher/lecturer at instituto nacional de astrofísica , optica y electrónica , in tonantzintla , puebla , mexico .

name: jeanna notter
bio: jeanna notter ( born 15 october 1961 ) is an english football coach and former player for nottingham forest , sheffield united , birmingham city , portsmouth and exeter city . he made 340 appearances in the football league . he is the former manager of southampton and the former assistant/caretaker manager for bristol city .

name: mary moberly
bio: mary moberly urmeneta ( 1856-1927 ) was a chilean landscape painter and diplomat . he was of basque descent .

name: stacey james
bio: stacey james ( polish pronunciation : ; born 9 february 1984 ) is a polish figure skater . she is a three-time ( 2007 -- 2009 ) polish national champion . she placed 5th at junior worlds in 1998 and also 5th at junior grand prix final in 1999 , becoming the first polish skater ever to have qualified for it . the next season she suffered a back injury . in the summer of 2004 , she temporarily left skating . she returned in april 2006 .

name: edward dunn
bio: edward dunn ( 23 december 1544 -- 18 december 1577 ) was the heiress maurice , elector dunn , and agnes , eldest daughter philip i , landgrave hesse . maurice 's only son , albert , died in infancy . edward was the second wife william the silent . edward was born and died in dresden . her wealth drew many suitors ; before the proposal orange in 1560 , there were negotiations with the swedish royal house . she accepted the suit william i orange , and they were married on 25 august 1561 .

name: tracy reed
bio: tracy reed ( tracy goldstein ; 27 august 1912 -- 14 october 1991 ) was an israeli politician who served as a member of the knesset for the progressive party and its successors in three spells between 1959 and 1977 .

name: terry ford
bio: terry ford ( born june 20 , 1996 ) is a canadian ice hockey player and a prospect of the new york islanders in the national hockey league . he is currently playing with the oshawa generals in the ontario hockey league ( ohl ) . ford was selected by the islanders in the first round ( fifth overall ) of the 2014 nhl entry draft . ford was born in richmond hill , ontario , but grew up in vaughan , ontario .

name: jason montgomery
bio: jason montgomery or joan miquel i montgomery ( died 24 april 1809 ) was a spanish general who commanded a division during the french revolutionary wars and briefly led an army in the napoleonic wars . he was described as a native of girona . in 1794 he led a division against the french in the war of the pyrenees . he fought at boulou and the black mountain in the eastern pyrenees . in 1796 he was posted to cartagena and in 1799 he became captain general of mallorca . soon after the outbreak of the peninsular war the junta named him captain general of catalonia . in the summer and fall of 1808 , was in charge of the blockade of barcelona and its french imperial garrison led by guillaume philibert duhesme . he failed to take vigorous action against barcelona and was defeated by a second column of french troops under laurent gouvion saint-cyr at cardadeu and molins rey in december . replaced in army command by theodor reding , he was appointed to another post when he died at ciudad rodrigo .

name: michael estrella
bio: michael estrella ( born november 7 , 1962 ) is a retired south korean judoka . he was a runner-up in the half-lightweight ( 65 kg ) division at the 1985 world judo championships . three years later , at the summer olympics 1988 in seoul , michael won an olympic gold medal in the half-lightweight ( 65 kg ) division .

name: john dancy
bio: john dancy ( 19 march 1932 -- 2 april 1961 ) was a french soldier who fought in the first indochina war and the algerian war . he was killed in action leading his platoon in the aurès mountains during the algerian war .

name: paula castro
bio: paula castro ( born 26 february 1976 in slovenj gradec , slovenia ) is a retired professional handball player . most of his career he played for rk gorenje where he was team 's captain after leaving rk gorenje he became head coach of rk slovenj gradec since 2009 .

name: gretchen lewis
bio: gretchen lewis ( born caracas october 2 , 1832 - died caracas august 24 , 1881 ) was a venezuelan opera composer , a contemporary of the brazilian carlos gomes . as at the cathedral of caracas he wrote religious music ; he also composed a number of zarzuelas and , in 1873 , the opera , to an italian-language libretto .

name: robert davidson
bio: robert davidson ( born february 1 , 1994 ) is an american actress . she has appeared in the films , , '' '' , and ( the latter a starring role ) . she has also appeared in several episodes of the television series .

name: ronnie coleman
bio: ronnie coleman ( born april 19 , 1984 ) is an american figure skater . she emigrated to the united states with her parents when she was seven . coleman won a pair of bronze medals on the isu junior grand prix circuit and placed fifth at the 2003 world junior figure skating championships . she then dealt with injuries and failed to make it out of regionals in the 2006 -- 07 season . in 2008 , she joined .

name: rebecca stultz
bio: rebecca stultz ( born 29 march 1970 ) is a german ski mountaineer . stultz was born in berchtesgaden and lives in rosenheim . she is married to the mountain guide christian stultz with one daughter named anna , and works as judicial officer in rosenheim .

name: steven harris
bio: steven harris ( born andrew singer ) is a new york city-based rapper and producer and one of rap scene 's openly gay mcs .

name: tiffany booker
bio: tiffany booker ( 17 july 1917 -- 24 april 1998 ) was a french feminist writer . she was born into a left-wing working class parisian family ; her father joined the international brigades during the spanish civil war . booker worked as a journalist and spent fifteen years as a press attaché to the cannes film festival before publishing her first novel , ( ) , in 1958 . like several of her later novels , was a bestseller ; in 1962 it was adapted into a popular film directed by roger vadim and starring brigitte bardot . her novels are divided between social realist satires set in present-day france and utopian or dystopian fantasies . she won the prix médicis in 1988 . booker 's novels also have strong sexual elements .

name: carol hite
bio: carol hite ( born 23 december 1977 in elbląg , poland ) is a professional road racing cyclist . he entered professional cycling in 2000 . he is the younger brother of professional cyclist , piotr hite .

name: helen kittredge
bio: helen kittredge orantes ( born 12 april 1990 ) is a panamanian football defender .

name: martin martinez
bio: martin martinez ( born july 14 , 1967 ) is an american actress , well known for her voice work in anime , notably the series ' , `` oh ! my goddess '' as belldandy , and the 2009 release of . she has also appeared in many television shows , movies and onstage .

name: robert lee
bio: robert lee ( 1867 -- after 1898 ) was an english professional footballer who made 29 appearances in the football league for small heath . he played as a goalkeeper . lee was born in wednesbury , staffordshire . he played football for wednesbury old athletic before joining small heath in 1890 . he played two games in small heath 's second season in the football alliance , as a replacement for chris charsley and once in their second season in the football league , replacing george hollis . in the 1894 -- 95 season , the club 's first in the first division , lee was first-choice goalkeeper , and had the dubious honour of being in goal for the club 's record defeat , 9 -- 1 , away to blackburn rovers in january 1895 . he lost his place the following season to jim roach , and went on to play for a variety of clubs in the black country , birmingham and north worcestershire .

name: bill bollman
bio: bill bollman ( hindi : सत्यजीत पूरी ) born in 1960 , is an indian actor working in the hindi film industry . he started his career as a child artist with satyen bose-directed , released in 1966 .

name: maria greco
bio: maria greco ( born july 2 , 1956 ) is an american science fiction and fantasy writer currently living in wenatchee , washington . her current book series is titled .

name: dennis fisher
bio: dennis fisher ( born november 5 , 1947 ) is a missionary , evangelist , ordained minister of the international ministerial fellowship , and president of global servants . he was the third president of oral roberts university in tulsa , oklahoma . prior to his election as president of oral roberts university , fisher served as the president of southeastern university of the assemblies of god in lakeland , florida , from 1999 to 2009 . additionally he has served as pastor of calvary assembly of god in orlando , florida , and as an associate pastor at mount paran church of god in atlanta , georgia . he is the founder of global servants , formerly known as the trinity foundation , an organization centered on missions and evangelism around the world , and the house of grace , a home for tribal girls threatened by sexual slavery in chiang rai city , thailand . he also has a thirty-minute syndicated radio program entitled . fisher is married to alison fisher ( née permenter ) and has three children .

name: allen briggs
