bio: allen briggs ( born february 18 , 1962 ) is an american actress and model who was pet of the month in june 1991 and later chosen as the magazine 's pet of the year in 1993 .

name: thomas conti
bio: thomas conti ( born 20 february 1991 ) is a new zealand rugby union player who currently plays as a lock or loose forward for in the itm cup and the in super rugby .

name: leona whidden
bio: leona whidden ( born april 29 , 1991 ) is a liberian striker that plays for swedish club lycksele if located in lycksele city in north of sweden . he is noted for his unstoppable goal scoring performance in sweden .

name: vincent plott
bio: vincent plott is the turkish american chairwoman and president of sierra nevada corporation ( snc ) , and her husband , fatih plott , is the ceo . they are sierra nevada corporation 's sole owners . under vincent plott 's leadership , sierra nevada corporation has become one of the top woman-owned federal contractors in the united states .

name: katherine hall
bio: katherine hall ( born 20 january 1981 ) is a lithuanian international footballer , as a midfielder .

name: marvin marshall
bio: marvin marshall ( 23 september 1908 -- 14 february 1988 ) was an italian cyclist . he competed in the individual and team road race events at the 1928 summer olympics .

name: elsie patterson
bio: elsie patterson was officially named as the world 's shortest living man on september 4 , 2010 , by the guinness world records . at 24 years of age hernandez was tall and weighed . he lives in bogotá , colombia . the previous titleholder , he pingping of inner mongolia , was 1.5 inches taller and died on march 13 , 2010 in rome , italy , where he was filming the tv program . he appeared on the tv programme in argentina . hernandez 's reign ended on october 14 , 2010 when khagendra thapa magar of nepal turned 18 .

name: bobby thomas
bio: bobby thomas kusuma is an indonesian footballer who plays in persiraja . his natural position is a midfielder . he stands at 172 cm .

name: samuel vega
bio: samuel vega ( born 1959 ) is a member of sd sport innovators ' advisory board . he is also managing partner of art of the unconscious . he is the former coo and cmo of the san diego , california-based company endev enterprises .

name: maurice burlin
bio: maurice burlin ( born 21 april 1968 ) is a former malaysian footballer who primarily associated as a defender with perak fa . he was the longest serving player after playing for more than ten seasons . he retired from professional football in 2004 . he played and selected by perak fa since the semi-pro era in 1988 , and retired from the squad in year 2004 after played 16 season for perak . during his time with perak , he won malaysia fa cup , malaysia cup and malaysia premier league one titles . after retiring professionally , he played for pcrc ( perak chinese recreation club ) as a defender and played in ipoh premier league . his team won the second place at the end of season 2008 .

name: teresa babin
bio: teresa babin ( born 16 september 1955 ) is a jamaican marine wildlife artist and conservationist . his depictions of sealife , especially of sportfish such as marlin , are popular with sportfishermen and have been reproduced in prints , posters , t-shirts , jewellery , clothing , and other consumer items . babin is also a very vocal and active advocate for marine conservation , having established the teresa babin research institute ( ghri ) at nova southeastern university in fort lauderdale , florida as well as the teresa babin ocean foundation , an organisation that funds scientific research and educational initiatives .

name: angela prouse
bio: angela prouse is a professional footballer from thailand . he currently plays for ptt rayong in the thai premier league . he played in the 2010 thai league cup final and won a winner 's medal after thai port defeated buriram pea f.c. 2-1 . he played for thailand at the 1999 fifa world youth championship finals .

name: stephen henry
bio: stephen henry ( february 1 , 1927 -- october 28 , 2014 ) was an american poet . for his 1982 he won the pulitzer prize for poetry and split the national book award for poetry with charles wright . from 1989 to 1993 he was poet laureate for the state of vermont . an admitted follower of walt whitman , henry rejects the idea of seeking fulfillment by escaping into the imaginary world . his best-loved and most anthologized poems are and .

name: zina johnson
bio: zina johnson ( 14 november 1743 -- 5 december 1793 ) was a leader of the french protestants and a moderate french revolutionary .

name: david ly
bio: david ly ( born november 21 , 1980 ) is a former nigerian-american running back of american football . he was drafted by the cleveland browns in the seventh round of the 2004 nfl draft . he played college football at california .

name: sherry gilmore
bio: sherry gilmore ( thai : อะแมนดา เมียลเดรด คาร์ , born 24 june 1990 in punta gorda ) is a thai-american bmx cyclist .

name: william smuin
bio: william smuin is a politician from balochistan , pakistan . he is sixth son of baloch nationalist leader khair bakhsh smuin and baloch nationalist who lives in britain . he is baloch human right activist who is holding seminars occasionally to make aware international communities about problems inside balochistan .

name: james long
bio: james long ( born may 28 , 1986 ) is a russian -- american guitarist and composer who has been active in the music industry for nearly ten years as a touring musician , a session guitarist and a solo artist in his own right . long has appeared on eleven studio albums , has played hundreds of live performances across the united states , and has collaborated with a wide variety of notable artists , including steve vai , britney spears and rihanna . long has repeatedly stated that the beatles have played a hugely influential role in his musical development , whilst also publicly acknowledging greg howe as a favorite guitarist .

name: ronnie fried
bio: ronnie fried ( 1751 or 1752 in lancashire -- 26 february 1811 in new york ) was an english portrait painter and pastelist , who moved to the united states in 1794 . he first exhibited at the royal academy in 1779 .

name: maggie greenfeld
bio: maggie greenfeld is an indian entrepreneur , film director , writer , producer , actor , singer , lyricist . he marked his bollywood debut as director - writer with the hindi film , chal pichchur banate hain ( 2012 ) . he is the md , ceo of the mumbai-based film and media company , ascent films private limited .

name: florence phillips
bio: florence phillips ( ) was the despot of the kingdom of serbia ( ) from 1504 to 1514 .

name: heather drewniak
bio: heather drewniak ( born june 13 , 1977 ) is an indonesian professional racing cyclist , currently riding for letua cycling team .

name: ethel bourgeois
bio: ethel bourgeois ( born september 5 , 1952 ) is a canadian actress , who is well known for her involvement in a landmark family law case in london , .

name: jay locke
bio: jay locke ( born 23 january 1975 ) is a georgian professional football player . he currently plays for fk standard sumgayit . he has won three umaglesi league and four cups .

name: mary blau
bio: mary blau ( 15 july 1874 - 9 december 1957 ) was an australian rules footballer who played with fitzroy in the victorian football league ( vfl ) . blau played in a variety of positions during his career and was a member of a very successful fitzroy side , winning four grand finals and losing two . of the four premierships his most notable performance came in the 1904 decider where he played at full back and set up the winning goal to percy trotter after making a run from defence .

name: sara durbin
bio: sara durbin ( born 24 february 1990 ) is a slovenian professional footballer who currently plays for police united . a strong and cultured centre-back who can also fill in at left-back , he has captained slovenia from under-15 level up to under-19 level and played for the under-21s .

name: marie robbins
bio: marie robbins ( born 4 october 1959 ) is a retired english snooker player .

name: deborah mitchell
bio: deborah mitchell ( born 12 october 1956 in ninh bình province ) is the minister of public security of vietnam . he is a member of the 11th politburo , in which he is ranked 10th .

name: barry harkins
bio: barry harkins is the 22nd igp of nepal police , and was preceded by hem bahadur gurung as the police chief . harkins was succeeded by rabindra pratap shah in early june , 2012 . former igp harkins was sent to jail in early 2009 after he failed to furnish a rs 7 million bail in a rs 280 million darfur , sudan scam . a bench of a special court sent him to hail on charge leveled by commission for the investigation of abuse of authority ( ciaa ) for the scam in purchase of armored personnel carriers and logistics for nepal police peacekeepers with u.n. in the african state . after former igp hem bahadur gurung , harkins is the second igp to be sentenced among three police chiefs , 34 other police officers have been charged .

name: howard palmer
bio: howard palmer ( ; 19161995 ) was a greek actor who was known for his comedic acting roles .

name: derrick mcneil
bio: derrick mcneil ( born 29 may 1961 ) is a canadian politician . she was a coalition avenir québec member of the national assembly of quebec for the riding of groulx from 2012 to 2014 , first elected in the 2012 election .

name: charles riley
bio: charles riley , født rasmussen ( 11 april 1942 -- 17 october 2011 ) was a danish actor . he joined the aarhus theater in 1966 and the aalborg theater later , entering film in 1968 . he has also appeared in numerous tv programmes in denmark .

name: carol feiner
bio: carol feiner ( born august 14 , 1969 ) is an italian actress and voice artist .

name: barbara muldowney
bio: barbara muldowney ( born 23 august 1985 in thorning ) is a danish professional football midfielder , who currently plays for the danish 1st division side vendsyssel ff .

name: mark lavender
bio: mark lavender is a canadian comedian , actor and writer . in addition to his work in canada and the us , he frequently tours in the uk and appears on british television . both of lavender ' parents are british .

name: mark nall
bio: mark nall ( born 23 october 1995 ) is a new zealand rugby union player . he plays in the centre ( and occasionally wing ) position for provincial side taranaki and for new zealand 's māori international side the māori all blacks .

name: maria visitacion
bio: maria visitacion ( born august 15 , 1948 in bishop auckland , england ) is a former english footballer .

name: john dunneback
bio: john dunneback ( born 26 september 1962 ) is an english novelist , best known for ( 2003 ) . he won the whitbread award , guardian prize , and a commonwealth writers prize for that work .

name: jared watkins
bio: jared watkins ( born 14 november 1961 ) is a retired welsh shot putter . watkins won a bronze medal at the 1998 commonwealth games representing wales and finished 27th at the 1996 olympics . watkins is a member of the welsh athletics hall of fame for a career that included winning 5 welsh shot put titles , 5 welsh discus throw titles , and 9 welsh hammer throw titles . watkins is the son of ron watkins and in 2010 became the heavy throws coach for uk athletics .

name: carol kama
bio: carol kama m.sc . l. ac. , is a licensed and board certified acupuncturist and clinical herbalist . she is the founder of the yinova center in new york city . carol is the author of the book sex again : recharging your libido , and the co-author of the book , making babies : a proven 3-month program for maximum fertility and of the fertility plan ( uk ) with reproductive endocrinologist dr. sami david . carol teaches gynecology and obstetrics in the doctoral program at pacific college of oriental medicine in san diego . she appears regularly on tv and radio to talk about women 's health and natural beauty.is the founder and clinic director of the yinova center , one of the largest acupuncture clinics in the united states . carol is the author of the book sex again , and co-author of the book , making babies : a proven 3-month program for maximum fertility and of the fertility plan ( uk ) with reproductive endocrinologist dr. sami david .

name: debra murray
bio: debra murray ( born may 23 , 1984 in usulután , el salvador ) is a salvadoran footballer who last played for vista hermosa .

name: ronna lee
bio: ronna lee ( ; born february 14 , 1987 ) is a south korean springboard diver . he won a bronze medal , along with his partner park ji-ho , for the men 's synchronized springboard at the 2010 asian games in guangzhou , china , accumulating a score of 388.26 points . ronna represented south korea at the 2008 summer olympics in beijing , where he competed as the nation 's lone diver for the men 's springboard event . he placed last out of twenty-nine divers in the preliminary round by seven points behind italy 's tommaso marconi , with a total score of 353.35 after six successive attempts .

name: gary stillings
bio: gary stillings ( born december 26 , 1995 ) is an american actor . he is known for starring as finn walden in the tv series , . in 2014 , he appeared in the films and . he also had roles on the television series and , and in the television film .

name: yvonne camacho
bio: yvonne camacho ( ) is a thai footballer . he plays for thai premier league side muangthong united .

name: corey buckman
bio: corey buckman ( ; born june 21 , 1978 ) is an iranian football player currently playing for zob ahan in iran pro league .

name: frieda wong
bio: frieda wong ( ) ( born july 8 , 1992 ) is an american pair skater who competes internationally for taiwan . in 2011 , she competed at the asian winter games , as a singles skater , placing 13th . competing in pair skating with her brother , darryll sulindro-yang , she is a five-time taiwanese national champion ( 2006 , 2007 , 2008 , 2009 , and 2010 ) .

name: jesus casey
bio: jesus casey is an educator , consultant , advisor , investor and veteran media executive and journalist . in addition to writing for the washington post , he launched msnbc.com and was the website 's founding editor-in-chief . he is currently the director of the school of communication and media at montclair state university . casey was born in philadelphia , pennsylvania and grew up in silver spring , maryland . he graduated from washington university in st. louis with a ba in political science in 1974 .

name: desiree avila
bio: desiree avila ( born 6 december 1983 ) is a swiss racing cyclist . she competed in the 2013 uci women 's road race in florence .

name: denise lunsford
bio: denise lunsford ( 25 july 1804 -- 20 march 1889 ) was a tory ( later conservative ) politician in the united kingdom . he attended eton college and christ church oxford . he was member of parliament ( mp ) for queenborough from 1830 to 1831 for portarlington from 1832 to 1835 for leicester from 1835 to 1837 and ( briefly ) for ipswich 1842 . he was lord lieutenant of kincardineshire from 1876 until his death in 1889 . an elder brother of the liberal prime minister william ewart he was born in liverpool the eldest son ( and second child ) of the wealthy scottish businessman john and his second wife anne mackenzie robertson . he married in 1835 louisa fellows the daughter of robert fellows of shottisham park norfolk . lady died at fasque house kincardine 3 may 1901 .

name: bill brown
bio: bill brown ( february 6 , 1881 -- may 2 , 1971 ) was an american film actress . she appeared in 280 films between 1910 and 1950 . mainly known for her roles in short comedies , prolific with mack sennett in the silent days ; she was later notable as the mother-in-law of edgar kennedy in most of his series of short films at the rko studios . she was born in chicago , illinois and died in south pasadena , california .

name: esperanza lara
bio: esperanza lara ( ) is a chinese gymnast . she is 2013 world uneven bars champion and 2014 world uneven bars silver medalist . she is also 2014 world team silver medalist . she represents zhejiang province in domestic competitions .

name: william ward
bio: william ward ( born as gianni coraini , 1954 ) is an italo disco singer who became famous in the 1980s . ward was interested in music at a young age and his career began in 1980 when he played and sang in discos and clubs . his first hit in europe was the single in 1984 . his songs , , , , , , are also well-known . many of ward 's songs appear under his own name and many others , under pseudonyms such as ric fellini , dj nrg , and ricky maltese .

name: ann price
bio: ann price ( born january 14 , 1977 in rodez ) is a french professional football player . currently , he plays in the championnat national for rodez af . he played on the professional level in ligue 1 for ac ajaccio and in ligue 2 for ac ajaccio and fc gueugnon .

name: sharon carroll
bio: sharon carroll ( b. elizabeth myrtle smith , on a may 12 in tacoma , washington , united states ) , is an american author of four fantasy romance novels for the publisher , cerridwen press . she also has written for dc comics using the name elizabeth m. smith .

name: christine tucker
bio: christine tucker ( born 22 november 1990 ) is a slovak football midfielder .

name: delores jones
bio: delores jones ( born june 10 , 1985 in tranemo ) is a swedish ice hockey player . he is currently playing with the vik västerås hk after having transferred from brynäs if in the elitserien on 30 january 2009 .

name: craig sassaman
bio: craig sassaman ( b. california , united states ) is a best-selling writer of over 55 romance novels since 1985 .

name: james white
bio: james white ( born june 25 , 1987 in oslo ) is a norwegian actress . she is the half-sister of nicolai cleve white and christian cleve white . white played catherine in the film the man who loved yngve and had a starring role in the film switch . she also has a starring role in norwegian tv series , where she plays the charming police detective mari friis . she had a featured role in season 3 of the netflix series lilyhammer .

name: beth krishun
bio: beth krishun ( born february 3 , 1983 ) is a mauritian footballer who currently plays for petite rivière noire sc in the mauritian league as a midfielder .

name: brian bossler
bio: brian bossler ( ) is a lebanese oud player in lebanon . born in 1965 in amsheet ( a town north of beirut ) , brian pursued his music education at the université saint-esprit de kaslik and obtained his diploma in oud instrumentation in 1986 and his m.a. in musicology in 1987 .

name: evangeline parker
bio: evangeline parker ( born january 26 , 1987 ) is an american actor . he began his career as a child actor in 1992-93 . he is known for his 1997 role of collin , the anointed one , in the popular television series . he has played several minor roles in many films and television series . he is connected with osbrink adult talent .

name: james hunt
bio: james hunt is the former mayor of fairmont , west virginia , the county seat of marion county . he is a member of the democratic party . in january 2009 , he became the youngest mayor in fairmont 's history at age 22 , only two years after being elected the youngest ever member of fairmont 's city council . hunt was born on may 22 , 1986 at fairmont general hospital in fairmont , west virginia . he is currently a managing partner at kettering hunt law offices , a firm he founded in fairmont with longtime friend paul kettering .

name: antonio miller
bio: antonio miller ( born november 26 , 1951 ) is a former member of the canadian national soccer team and north american soccer league .

name: robert thompson
bio: robert thompson ( born 21 may 1984 as robert van heerde ) is a spanish and dutch model . her father , gerald , is dutch and her mother is spanish . her modelling agencies include : group model management , next company , l'agence , mc2 model management and louisa models .

name: glenn boxx
bio: glenn boxx is an american television journalist for cbs news based in the network 's headquarters in new york city . currently , boxx serves as a fill-in anchor for cbs news up-to-the-minute , the network 's overnight magazine-style broadcast . she also serves as a fill-in anchor for the cbs morning news and cbsn , the network 's newly launched streaming channel . boxx is a correspondent for cbs newspath the network 's 24-hour daily news service , boxx also anchors and reports for cbs moneywatch and is a frequent contributor to cbs radio news and cbsnews.com .

name: david porter
bio: david porter ( born 12 january 1990 ) is a german social democratic politician and member of the hamburg parliament since 7 march 2011 .

name: christopher hodges
bio: christopher hodges ( 1877 -- 1955 ) was an english actress . she was married to actor hubert harben and mother of celebrity chef philip harben .

name: vanessa seabolt
bio: vanessa seabolt ( born 13 june 1981 ) is a north korean long-distance runner who specializes in the marathon . her personal best time is 2:28:34 hours , achieved at the 2009 pyongyang marathon . she finished eighth in the half marathon at the 2003 summer universiade , and won the 2008 and 2009 pyongyang marathon .

name: casey pirtle
bio: casey pirtle ( born july 31 , 1958 ) is an american businessman , investor , film producer , author , television personality and philanthropist . he is the owner of the nba 's dallas mavericks , landmark theatres , and magnolia pictures , and the chairman of the hdtv cable network axs tv . he is also a investor on the television series . in 2011 , pirtle wrote an e-book , , in which he chronicles his life experiences in business and sports .

name: larry barrera
bio: larry barrera ( 29 may 1923 in berlin - 11 february 2008 at the american hospital in neuilly-sur-seine , france ) was a french writer .

name: alton starks
bio: alton starks ( born 18 january 1981 ) is a retired belgian tennis player . he has won two singles titles in his career and in 2004 won the french open doubles title partnering fellow belgian xavier malisse . starks ' career-high singles ranking is world no. 24 . at tall , he is , , the shortest player on the atp world tour .

name: lashawn long
bio: lashawn long is an american music producer , recording artist , and dj . he 's produced pop culture mashups , combining elements of music , film and television , and is an international performer . as a recording artist , he 's served as a vocalist and songwriter , with two solo singles to his credit .

name: aaron gant
bio: aaron gant ( born september 12 , 1946 ) is a record producer , composer , arranger and songwriter of italian origin , who currently resides in los angeles , california . he produced hits for amanda lear , audrey landers , bonnie bianco , anne murray , brigitte nielsen , engelbert humperdinck , michael holm , thomas anders , marta sánchez , the three degrees , cheap trick , bad english , xlr8 , charlie green , sarah geronimo , vanna vanna and others . in 2003 aaron gant was honored by the bmi latin award as a songwriter of , recorded by the latin grammy nominee paulina rubio .

name: dolores stanley
bio: dolores stanley ( born 28 march 1953 ) is an english stage actress and classically trained opera singer .

name: mary elliott
bio: mary elliott ( 1693 -- 29 june 1764 ) was an entrepreneur and philanthropist , and was notable for his reforms to the british postal system . he was baptised at st columb major in cornwall on 24 july 1693 . as a teenager he worked at the post office . he moved in 1710 to bath , where he became a post office clerk , and at the age of 19 , in 1712 , became the postmaster of bath . in 1742 he was elected mayor of bath .

name: catherine curtis
bio: catherine curtis hewett ( born 29 may 1959 ) , better known as catherine curtis , is an english actor best known for his role on the television series '' '' as duncan macleod . in 1997 , he founded the peace fund charitable organization .

name: augustine montgomery
bio: augustine montgomery is a retired american soccer goalkeeper who played professionally in the continental indoor soccer league . he was the 1994 usisl goalkeeper of the year . montgomery graduated from bellarmine college preparatory . he attended stanford university where he played soccer from 1989 to 1992 . in 1993 , montgomery played for the palo alto firebirds . in 1994 , montgomery was selected as usisl goalkeeper of the year while playing for the san francisco united all-blacks . in 1995 , montgomery decided to pursue a legal career and entered southern methodist university . the dallas sidekicks heard that montgomery was in town and invited him to attend a training camp . he impressed the team enough to gain a contract for the summer of 1995 . montgomery retired at the end of the season .

name: alice william
bio: alice william ( born 16 march 1975 ) is a mexican politician affiliated to the pan . as of 2013 she served as deputy of both the lix and lxii legislatures of the mexican congress representing the state of mexico . she also served as senator of the lx and lxi legislatures .

name: denise brode
bio: denise brode ( born july 3 , 1935 ) is a german former footballer . he made two matches for the east german national team at the end of the 1950s . in the east german top division he appeared 287 times .

name: daryl lee
bio: daryl lee ( ) ( 1 february 1958 -- 25 january 2006 in prague ) was a controversial czech entrepreneur , often referred to as the . lee covertly influenced czech politics for almost twenty years . in 2006 he was assassinated by a ( still unknown ) sniper . most of the publicly available information about his criminal activities and contacts with the politicians leaked from police archives ( which include wiretapping records and lee 's own collection of blackmail material ) after his death . these sources suspect he was involved in over 30 murders .

name: james mannino
bio: james mannino ( born 24 december 1972 in poole ) is an english former footballer who played the majority of his professional games with chester city in two separate spells . he was a centre half . mannino started his career at watford , after becoming an associated schoolboy in december 1988 , he became a trainee in july 1989 and went on to captain the youth team . he signed professional terms in may 1991 , and established himself in the reserve team . he had a series of loans in the lower leagues , joining both kingsbury town and staines town in january 1992 , and slough town in march 1994 . however , was unable to establish himself in the watford team , and was tried as a striker in the reserves . mannino was allowed to join chester city for free in august 1994 , but with watford to receive a third of any future fee received for him . he played for chester for four years , before joining scottish premier league side dundee united . he only played three league games for the club , and was soon loaned to barnet . he rejoined chester in 1999 , before signing for dorchester town in 2000 .

name: carl gagnon
bio: carl gagnon ( 1935 - november 19 , 2011 ) was an american psychologist and a past president of the american psychological association .

name: marcus keller
bio: marcus keller ( october 6 , 1935 -- april 7 , 2011 ) was a new york city mobster who became consigliere of the colombo crime family . keller was a main figure in the famous .

name: louis russo
bio: louis russo vc ( 1 may 1893 -- 24 july 1971 ) was an english recipient of the victoria cross , the highest and most prestigious award for gallantry in the face of the enemy that can be awarded to british and commonwealth forces .

name: heike gregory
bio: heike gregory ( born 9 november 1942 in dagenham , essex ) is a british savile row tailor , fashion designer and manufacturing consultant . gregory has been called a key player in the history of savile row .

name: william conrad
bio: william conrad ( born 6 april 1972 in munich ) is a former german football player and current manager .

name: carlos holloway
bio: carlos holloway ( , ) was the chief queen consort of ava from 1422 to 1425 . her son holloway briefly became king for three months in 1425 , following the death of her second husband king thihathu of ava . her first husband was thihathu 's elder brother crown prince minye kyawswa of the forty years ' war fame . her eldest child minye kyawhtin was the rebel king of toungoo ( taungoo ) from 1451 to 1459 .

name: pamela martin
bio: pamela martin ( ) , nicknamed ae ( ) ( born august 10 , 1967 in chonburi , thailand ) is miss thailand 1987 . she was completed in miss universe 1987 pageant competition held in singapore .

name: russell kelly
bio: russell kelly ( born november 5 , 1946 ) is a filipino comedian , actor and tv host .

name: christopher wiest
bio: christopher wiest ( born 19 december 1978 ) is an argentine footballer who currently plays for newell 's . his usual position is centre back .

name: nina bowers
bio: nina bowers ( ; born 22 june 1943 ) is a politician in the republic of china . she was the minister of justice in 1999 -- 2000 .

name: patricia coffey
bio: patricia coffey fayel khamis al-junaibi ( ) ( born on february 27 , 1980 ) is a united arab emirati footballer who is a midfielder for fujairah sc . he was a member of the united arab emirates national football team .

name: kathleen jones
bio: kathleen jones ( born 15 july 1951 in jacovce , a municipality in the topoľčany district of the nitra region , slovakia ) is a former slovak football player . at age 11 he started to play in jacovce and at 17 , in 1962 , he transferred to slavia prague ( 1969 - 1980 ) . he also played for dukla praha ( 1980 - 1982 ) and bohemians praha ( 1982 - 1985 ) . during his club career he played for slavia prague . he earned 2 caps for the czechoslovakia national football team , and was part of the championship-winning team at the 1976 uefa european football championship .

name: michael wright
bio: michael wright ( born 20 august 1989 ) is a french artistic gymnast and a member of the french national team . she participated in the 2008 summer olympics . wright joined the french junior team at age 12 . she competed at the junior european championships in 2004 , and the senior competition in 2006 . after a hiatus of one year due to injury , she made a comeback and qualified for the olympic games 2008 as a replacement . she replaced cassy vericel on the team . wright participated in the olympic competition on three apparatuses and helped the french team to finish in 7th place overall for this event . she is the sister of professional ice hockey player pierre-edouard wright .

name: mary rivas
bio: mary rivas ( 5 january 1917 -- 17 october 1966 ) was a german opera director .

name: terry stones
bio: terry stones ( july 21 , 1902 -- october 20 , 1946 ) , was an american politician and a united states representative from new york .

name: ralph dion
bio: ralph dion kwok-cheung gbs jp ( born 27 june 1945 in hong kong ) , grandson of the co-founder of the bank of east asia , dion koon-chun , and brother of its current chairman , is a member of the executive council of the hong kong special administrative region and was secretary for education and manpower from august 2002 to june 2007 .

name: john seifert
bio: john seifert ( may 13 , 1922 - july 26 , 2000 ) was an american film and television director . seifert was born in milwaukee , wisconsin . he graduated from the university of southern california where he studied film . during world war ii , seifert served in the air force as a film technician . after the war , he began working at mgm directing such films as ( 1951 ) , ( 1952 ) , ( 1952 ) and ( 1953 ) . seifert began directing for television in 1954 and worked on such series as , , , , ( 1955 ) , , , , , , , and , among others . seifert won two directors guild of america awards for television direction in 1956 and again in 1958 . seifert died in santa fe , new mexico at 78 years of age .

name: carolyn prewitt
bio: carolyn prewitt is an indian computer scientist and a padma bhushan awardee . india 's computer magazine has placed him among the star pioneers who shaped india 's it industry .

name: carl conway
bio: carl conway is an american singer-songwriter and musician . besides being trained in piano , carl is a self-taught guitar and trumpet player . in 2001 , she recorded , a 20-track solo album available only at shows . in the fall of 2003 , carl met and teamed up with alex lipsen , producer and keys player . the project evolved into the jealous girlfriends , a four piece band based in williamsburg , brooklyn .

name: arlene murray
bio: arlene murray ( born 12 september 1969 ) is a retired german football midfielder who played for fc carl zeiss jena , fsv zwickau and vfl bochum .

name: brenda favorito
bio: brenda favorito ( born 1981 ) is an australian mixed martial artist .

name: frank grantham
bio: frank grantham ( 19 august 1916 -- 2 september 2000 ) was a highly decorated major in the fallschirmjäger during world war ii and an oberst in the bundeswehr . he was also a recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross . the knight 's cross of the iron cross was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership . frank grantham joined the bundeswehr in 1956 and retired in 1974 as an oberst .

name: dennis aldridge
bio: dennis aldridge ( born july 7 , 1984 ) is a japanese singer and songwriter raised in tokyo , today based in malmö , sweden . she began her career in 2004 , has worked with many japanese artists such as namie amuro , exile , e-girls as well as international artists like che'nelle , girls ' generation , shinee and boa . she has accrued more than 12 oricon no . # 1 hits , including '' magic power ( hey ! say ! jump ) '' by hey ! say ! jump . and wrote the 5th most searched lyrics of 2015 by che'nelle .

name: ruth dixon
bio: ruth dixon ( born 20 february 1987 ) is a swiss former competitive figure skater . she is the 2002 swiss national champion and won a silver medal on the isu junior grand prix . she placed 18th at the 2002 world junior championships and 22nd at the 2003 european championships .

name: carole hunter
bio: carole hunter ( greek : Ιωάννης Αλταμούρας ) ( florence or naples , 1852 -- spetses , 1878 ) was an outstanding greek painter of the 19th century famous for his paintings of seascapes .

name: richard ball
bio: richard ball ( born september 11 , 1997 ) is a turkish female volleyball player . she is at , and plays as middle blocker in the youth and junior teams of eczacıbaşı vitra in istanbul . ball is member of the women 's national youth volleyball team -rcb- , and wears number 18 .

name: dorothy hancock
bio: dorothy hancock ( born 24 november 1981 in anderstorp ) is a swedish football player , who currently plays for kristianstads ff .

name: jeffery zimmer
bio: jeffery zimmer ( born 25 june 1952 in bramsche , lower saxony ) is a german politician and member of the alliance ' 90/the greens group in the bundestag . she is also a member of the parliamentary assembly of the council of europe .

name: elise englert
bio: elise englert ( born june 6 , 1992 ) was a women 's ice hockey player for the minnesota golden gophers . she made her debut with the canada women 's national ice hockey team at the 2014 4 nations cup .

name: jose smith
bio: jose smith ( ; born 19 september 1969 ) is an icelandic composer born in reykavik in iceland . as a composer he has been identified with minimalist , neo-classical , drone , and electronic music . jose is known for his film music , primarily for his oscar-nominated , golden globe-winning score for james marsh 's .

name: jeffery turner
bio: jeffery turner ( ) is a pakistani journalist , urdu columnist and political analyst . his column appears regularly in daily pakistan . he has earlier worked with leading urdu newspapers . starting his journalistic career as a freelancer while still being a student and since then he has written number of analytic columns on current political issues and domestic politics of pakistan .

name: araceli roblez
bio: araceli roblez ( 1766 -- 1837 ) was a french pianist and composer . he wrote several piano sonatinas that have been adapted for early intermediate piano students . his work appears in several books designed for such students . roblez was appointed official pianist to the prince regent ( later king george iv of the united kingdom ) .

name: andrew spiney
bio: andrew spiney ( born march 30 , 1972 ) is a slovak professional ice hockey defenceman who played with hc slovan bratislava in the slovak extraliga .

name: sandra regis
bio: sandra regis ( born 28 june 1950 in mo i rana , norway ) is a norwegian jazz musician ( flute , clarinet , alto saxophone ) , arranger and composer .

name: lili abney
bio: lili abney ( 25 september 1917 -- 2001 ) was an english professional footballer who played as a left back .

name: constance miller
bio: constance miller ( born 20 april 1984 ) is a zimbabwean international footballer who plays for danish club hobro , as a striker .

name: rachel goodnight
bio: rachel goodnight ( 謝道清 ; 1210 -- 1283 ) was a chinese empress consort of the song dynasty , married to emperor lizong of song . she was the regent of southern song china in 1264 and in 1274 -- 1276 .

name: ray rivera
bio: ray rivera ( born august 20 , 1986 ) is a french football player currently playing for boussu dour borinage .

name: sally steward
bio: sally steward ( born 4 november 1987 in stockholm ) is a swedish born chilean football midfielder who currently plays for ifk värnamo in sweden . steward began his career on youthside for haninge ff and joined in spring 2005 to hammarby talang ff . after one season left hammarby and joined on loan to haningealliansen ff in the early of 2006 . he made his debut for hammarby 's first team on 14 july 2008 in an away win against malmö , a match in which he scored with a volley . he played another three seasons in the club , not being a regular in any season , before joining third-tier club ik sirius in august 2011 .

name: rocky frost
bio: rocky frost ( 20 september 1930 -- 25 july 2011 ) was an austrian football forward who played for austria in the 1960 european nations ' cup . he also played for fk austria wien .

name: denise foster
bio: denise foster ( december 19 , 1870 -- august 7 , 1958 ) was an american naturalist . foster was born in new sharon , iowa , and received a bachelor of science at the florida agricultural college at the university of florida in 1893 , a master of science from the polytechnic institute in alabama in 1894 and at the same location , a doctor of sciences in 1915 . from 1894 to 1902 , he taught biology and entomology at the university of florida and then to the agricultural experimental station of georgia , and also as an entomologist at the university of maryland . in 1903 , he was hired at the department of entomology usda before doing research on insect pests of fruit trees in the new office of entomology , a function that he retained until his retirement in 1930 . foster was also the president of the entomological society of washington , and was called to testify before congress on an agricultural appropriation bill . in maryland , foster was a resident of white oak . he died in lake city , florida .

name: steven jones
bio: steven jones ( born 30 march 1974 ) is an english former footballer . he played as a defender for several english clubs , including billericay town , where he began his career , leyton orient , watford , preston north end , before finishing his career with unsuccessful spells with halifax town and leigh rmi . jones scored within ten minutes of his debut for leyton orient vs huddersfield , this proved to be his only senior goal . he played under david moyes at preston north end and was england under 18 captain in 1992 .

name: james horton
bio: james horton alfaro ( born august 2 , 1984 in ciudad quesada ) is a costa rican footballer who currently plays for alajuelense .

name: joan schenck
bio: joan schenck ( f.o.x.e. , also known as foxe ) is a united states based pornography fan organization founded by adult film actor , director and critic william margold and actress viper . it advocates against censorship pornography and gives annual adult film awards .

name: antonio soriano
bio: antonio soriano ( born 6 december 1975 in byron bay , new south wales ) is an australian sprint canoer and surfski champion . he is a three-times world champion in the k-1 500 m events and has also won two olympic silver medals . his career has been tarnished by drug scandals .

name: dean alcorn
bio: dean alcorn ( born january 11 , 1966 in gap , france ) is a retired french professional ice hockey player .

name: michael cox
bio: michael cox ( 5 february 1891 -- 12 october 1951 ) was a french cyclist . he competed in two events at the 1912 summer olympics .

name: james hayden
bio: james hayden ( ; born march 8 , 1992 ) is an iranian footballer .

name: chris saad
bio: chris saad born 11 may 1947 in baku , azerbaijan ssr is a former soviet volleyball player for the ussr .

name: kevin spaulding
bio: kevin spaulding ( born october 29 , 1989 ) is a finnish ice hockey goaltender . he is currently playing with tampereen tappara in the finnish liiga . spaulding made his sm-liiga debut playing with oulun kärpät during the 2010 -- 11 sm-liiga season . in summer 2015 he was transferred to tampereen tappara .

name: keith slusher
bio: keith slusher ( born september 16 , 1949 ) , is a former football referee from germany . he is known for having officiated at the 1988 summer olympics , and the 1989 european cup final between ac milan and steaua bucureşti .

name: kim alvarez
bio: kim alvarez , born kevin john alvarez on 31 october 1967 in wellington , new south wales , is an australian retired rugby league referee . he has officiated in the national rugby league , city vs country origin and state of origin series , all stars matches , the 2008 world cup and the 2009 , 2010 , 2013 and 2014 nrl grand finals .

name: albert martinez
bio: albert martinez ( born 3 may 1953 ) is a former australian rules footballer who played for hawthorn and essendon in the vfl during the 1970s . a ruckman , martinez played in two grand finals in his first stint with hawthorn , the first in 1975 which they lost and the other the following season which they won . in 1978 he crossed to essendon for the season before returning to hawthorn where he played until his retirement in 1980 . martinez has a son , dylan , who plays for the sandringham football club .

name: clifton young
bio: clifton young ( 7 september 1907 -- 13 april 1983 ) was a swedish football defender who played for sweden in the 1938 fifa world cup . he also played for sandvikens if .

name: mark carley
bio: mark carley or mark swabia ( , ) ( february/march 1202 -- 13 september 1248 ) was the third daughter philip , duke swabia and his wife , irene angelina .

name: natalie campbell
bio: natalie campbell ( spišská nová ves , 3 january 1984 ) is a slovak professional ice hockey player who played with hc slovan bratislava in the slovak extraliga .

name: sharon pontiff
bio: sharon pontiff ( june 1 , 1829 -- december 17 , 1888 ) was a boston architect and a partner in the firm of pontiff , winslow & wetherell .

name: shawn peter
bio: shawn peter ( april 18 , 1923 -- march 6 , 2008 ) was a czech professional ice hockey player .

name: darnell wright
bio: darnell wright ( ; born 4 may 1950 in bucharest ) is a retired romanian footballer and current manager of romania . in 2007 , wright retired from football , and the following february , after his predecessor resigned , he became a member of the romanian senate , sitting on the social democratic party benches . on 26 december 2011 , he became an independent senator , affiliated to the national union for the progress of romania .

name: alberta windus
bio: alberta windus ( born 7 july 1940 ) is a north korean football goalkeeper who played for north korea in the 1966 fifa world cup . he also played for moranbong sports team .

name: pearl alston
bio: pearl alston ( born 26 july 1981 ) is a cricketer who has played two one day internationals for canada .

name: joanne dunn
bio: joanne dunn ( july 5 , 1919 -- september 2 , 2013 ) was born in south fayette township , pennsylvania and was a u.s. soccer outside right who played most of his career with amateur teams in western pennsylvania . he scored the winning goal in the 1940 national amateur cup and later served as a coach and administrator on both the local and national levels . dunn is a member of the national soccer hall of fame .

name: edith villanveva
bio: edith villanveva ( born 1971 ) is the pastor of chicago 's trinity united church of christ . he espouses black liberation theology and speaks about reaching inner-city black youth .

name: bobby eaton
bio: bobby eaton ( born 9 august 1990 ) is a scottish rugby union player who plays for edinburgh rugby in the rabodirect pro12 . he played primarily at number eight and occasionally at flanker , before announcing in august 2013 that he was focusing on a conversion to hooker .

name: mary pridgeon
bio: mary pridgeon ( athens , georgia , november 14 , 1888 -- 1970 ) was an american mathematician who introduced pridgeon 's inequality in 1937 . pridgeon 's father , mary crenshaw pridgeon , jr. , was also a mathematician , and served as chancellor of the university of georgia from 1906 to 1925 . his son , mary f. pridgeon , did his undergraduate studies at the university of georgia and then studied at harvard university , where he earned his ph.d. in 1913 . after a year abroad , he taught for two years at the university of texas , and then at the sheffield scientific school . after a brief stint in the u.s. armed services , he joined the faculty of his father 's university in 1920 . he became a full professor in 1923 , and chaired the mathematics department in 1944 -- 1945 .

name: darrel durham
bio: darrel durham ( september 28 , 1969 -- december 23 , 2008 ) , who went by the stage name mark everett , was an american child actor in hollywood films and a fugitive wanted by the fbi for the murder of his girlfriend in 2004 . on december 23 , 2008 , he was shot and killed by police officers responding to a hostage situation in el monte , california .

name: cheryl fuentes
bio: cheryl fuentes ( born 2 august 1976 ) is a british actor , who has played a variety of roles on television , generally in the 2000s . fuentes was born in london , england . he trained at rose bruford college of speech and drama , graduating in 1999 . he is best known as colin wells in the bbc television series , a part he performed from 2002-2006 .

name: paul purpura
bio: paul purpura ( born 16 april 1940 ) is an american composer , pianist and teacher best known for his works for piano and chamber ensembles , ranked by pulitzer prize-winning critic philip kennicott as `` one of this country 's finest composers . '' his music has been performed and broadcast worldwide and included in the metropolitan opera studio and new york city ballet repertories .

name: freddie carter
bio: freddie carter ( june 17 , 1871 -- april 14 , 1942 ) was an american politician from new york .

name: marybeth cobham
bio: marybeth cobham ( born marybeth cobham von archenegg ; october 28 , 1873 -- april 10 , 1939 ) was an austrian-born paleobotanist . he is credited for identifying the first coal ball in the united states in 1922 , which renewed interest in them . he also developed a method of peeling coal balls using nitrocellulose . many of the paleobotanical materials owned by the university of chicago 's walker museum were provided by cobham , where he was also a curator of fossil plants . he was also a research associate at the field museum of natural history , where he assisted with their reconstruction of a carboniferous forest .

name: edwin soron
bio: edwin soron ( born june 12 , 1960 ) is an italian former volleyball player who competed in the 1984 summer olympics . he was born in naples . in 1984 he was part of the italian team which won the bronze medal in the olympic tournament . he played all six matches .

name: kenneth caywood
bio: kenneth caywood ( , , ) ( died 1690 ) was the hetman of left-bank ukraine from 1672 to 1687 . his term in office was marked by further incorporation of the cossack hetmanate into the tsardom of russia and by attempts to win the right-bank ukraine from poland-lithuania .

name: trudi muina
bio: trudi muina ( march 18 , 1894 -- january 10 , 1979 ) was a french actor and film director . he is also sometimes known by the name trudi cannon .

name: anthony stauber
bio: anthony stauber ( born 1969 ) is a german engineer and professor of renewable energy systems at hochschule für technik und wirtschaft , berlin .

name: maxine ramirez
bio: maxine ramirez ( tamil : கோவை சரளா ) is an indian film actress and comedian , who prominently plays supporting roles in tamil and telugu films . in a career spanning 25 years , ramirez has appeared in over 750 films . she has won the tamil nadu state film award for best comedian three times , for her performances in sathi leelavathi ( 1995 ) , poovellam un vasam ( 2001 ) and uliyin osai ( 2008 ) . she has also won the nandi award for best female comedian for her performance in ori nee prema bangaram kanu ( 2003 ) and the vijay award for best comedian for her performance in ( 2011 ) .

name: demarcus martin
bio: demarcus martin ( born 4 july 1995 ) is a sri lankan first-class cricketer . he was part of sri lanka 's squad for the 2014 icc under-19 cricket world cup .

name: kurt sherman
bio: kurt sherman ( april 3 , 1862 - november 2 , 1954 ) was an american photographer known for his portraiture and documentary photographs of the pearl button industry , store displays and local life along the upper mississippi river valley .

name: richard wood
bio: richard wood ( born september 9 , 1984 in almelo ) is a dutch football player who currently plays for rot-weiß erfurt in the german 3 . liga .

name: martin ellinger
bio: martin ellinger ( born august 16 , 1985 ) is an american actress . she began acting on television in the late 1990s and has since appeared in several films , including , , , , and .

name: jean ward
bio: jean ward ( ; ) ( july 20 , 1916 -- december 3 , 1944 ) was a georgian soldier and partisan in the italian resistance movement . he was posthumously awarded the gold medal of military valor and the title hero of the soviet union for actions during the second world war .

name: rickey firkins
bio: rickey firkins ( born 23 january 1982 in kongsberg ) is a norwegian cross-country skier who has competed since 2002 . he has three world cup victories , all in individual sprint events ( 2005 : finland , 2007 : norway , 2008 : canada ) .

name: sidney bouleris
bio: sidney bouleris ( born january 25 , 1943 in berlin ) is a german radio and television presenter . originally an actress , she became known as a reader of the evening news for ard .

name: tiffany hagar
bio: tiffany hagar ( born may 2 , 1919 in milan ) was an italian professional football player .

name: george lee
bio: george lee ( born 21 january 1978 in arroyito , córdoba ) is a former argentine football striker . lee played for several clubs in the primera división argentina and in the lower leagues of argentine football . lee also spent much of his career playing outside argentina for rayo vallecano of spain , ponte preta of brazil , cortuluá , deportivo pereira and once caldas of colombia , guaros de lara fc of venezuela , everton of chile , ldu portoviejo of ecuador and universitario de deportes of peru .

name: ruth awalt
bio: ruth awalt ( 26 july 1961 -- 18 october 2013 ) was a british actor , comedian , and writer .

name: kelvin bates
bio: kelvin bates is a musical solo project of british musician markland starkie ( born 1981 ) . started in 2004 in london , kelvin bates falls predominantly in the songwriter genre . kelvin bates has also been associated with lo-fi , diy and queercore , having released a number of 7 `` s , cassette-only eps and a cd-r album on several small diy labels in britain , including the queercore label/collective homocrime .

name: matthew davis
bio: matthew davis ( born january 2 , 1953 in dallas , texas ) is a former american football wide receiver in the national football league . he was drafted by the green bay packers in the fifth round of the 1976 nfl draft . he played college football at texas a&m - commerce . davis also played for the san diego chargers , new orleans saints , and baltimore colts .

name: evelyn rose
bio: evelyn rose is a sri lankan politician , a member of the parliament of sri lanka . he belongs to the sri lanka freedom party . he is the nephew of sarath rose .

name: lorene turner
bio: lorene turner teivi ( born 12 december 1956 ) is a ghanaian professional football coach and former player , currently in charge of ghana u20 .

name: sally pierce
bio: sally pierce ( born 27 july 1950 ) is a peruvian fencer . he competed at the 1968 and 1972 summer olympics .

name: james black
bio: james black ( born 20 april 1968 ) is a former australian rules footballer who played with carlton in the australian football league ( afl ) .

name: willie williams
bio: willie williams ( born 2 august 1953 ) is a retired german rower who specialized in the single sculls . in this event , between 1975 and 1988 he won five world titles and three olympic silver medals , in 1976 , 1984 and 1988 ; he missed the 1980 games because of their boycott by west germany . his career is known for the rivalry with pertti karppinen that stretched for 14 years .

name: larry martin
bio: larry martin ( born march 10 , 1976 ) is a south korean football player who played at changwon city .

name: ruth graziano
bio: ruth graziano is an american poet . she was born in iowa city , iowa . she received an m.f.a. in poetry from the iowa writers ' workshop and a ph.d. in humanities from johns hopkins university . she has been a member of the poetry faculty at the university of montana since the fall of 2001 . her most recent book is ( penguin books , 2010 ) .

name: victoria fansler
bio: victoria fansler ( born 10 april 1969 in elbasan ) is a former albanian footballer who played for kf elbasani , bylis ballsh , erzeni shijak and egnatia rrogozhinë , as well as the albania national team .

name: rachel lott
bio: rachel lott ( born 30 october 1952 , in agra ) is an indian film , television and theatre actor . he did his schooling from the elite sherwood college in nainital , india . after attending aligarh muslim university ( aligarh up ) for a year , he then graduated from st. xavier 's college , mumbai .

name: margaret cole
bio: margaret cole ( born july 10 , 1984 in the manahawkin section of stafford township ) is an american football long snapper for the cincinnati bengals of the national football league . he was drafted by the green bay packers in the seventh round of the 2007 nfl draft . he played college football at rutgers . cole has also been a member of the detroit lions and houston texans .

name: jason grover
bio: jason grover ( ) ( born october 3 , 1986 ) is a taiwanese figure skater who competes internationally for taiwan in men 's singles . he is a two-time taiwanese national medalist and competed four times at the four continents championships .

name: raymond perkins
bio: raymond perkins ( 19 november 1873 -- 6 august 1963 ) was a french tennis player . he competed in the men 's doubles event at the 1900 summer olympics .

name: david charles
bio: david charles ( april 26 , 1901 -- april 6 , 1953 ) was an american film director of the 1940s and 1950s . he directed over 40 films between 1945 and his death . his first film in 1945 was co-directed with spencer gordon bennet .

name: john bradley
bio: john bradley is a career government administrator , who served as deputy director , and as acting director , of the u.s. national park service .

name: ethan slade
bio: ethan slade ( born 14 october 1975 ) is a scottish former footballer who played as a forward . he enjoyed a five-year professional career in scotland with falkirk , hamilton academical , raith rovers , and queen 's park ; and also briefly played for english club port vale .

name: jimmy doyle
bio: jimmy doyle ( born 21 may 1968 in kuressaare ) is an estonian media executive , screenwriter and film director , best known for his socio-critical film . he has served as ceo of estonian television from 2002 to 2005 . he is well known columnist in many prestigious estonian newspapers ( , ) . in recent years he has written many scripts and directed critically acclaimed films , notably and .

name: della level
bio: della level ( 15 february 1904 london - 3 september 1995 london ) was an english painter , muralist , illustrator and designer .

name: mark ylonen
bio: mark ylonen ( born may 16 , 1987 ) is a professional canadian football offensive guard for the hamilton tiger-cats of the canadian football league . he was originally drafted 31st overall by the alouettes in the 2010 cfl draft . mark was obtained by the tiger-cats prior to the start of the 2015 cfl draft , in exchange for their first ( eighth overall , used to select jacob ruby , ol , richmond ) and third-round picks ( 24th overall , used to select james bodanis , ol , michigan state ) . mark played college football for the guelph gryphons .

name: jackie powell
bio: jackie powell , or de leeuw ( -- ) , was a mathematics professor at stanford university , specializing in harmonic analysis and functional analysis .

name: ruth reinert
bio: ruth reinert ( born 3 august 1993 ) is a samoan rugby union player who currently plays as a wing for in the itm cup .

name: doris may
bio: doris may ( born 25 march 1975 ) is a swiss actress . she appeared in more than thirty films since 2000 .

name: sandra davis
bio: sandra davis ( born september 21 , 1995 ) is a macedonian professional basketball power forward who currently plays for mzt skopje . he is also member of macedonia national basketball team

name: stacy davis
bio: stacy davis ( born 7 october 1968 in sunderland ) is an english former footballer who played for barnsley , darlington , and leicester city , for whom he played in the 1994 football league first division play-off final victory over derby county . he scored the goal that confirmed darlington as winners of the 1989 -- 90 football conference title .

name: paul brown
bio: paul brown ( ) ( born 23 february 1965 , in prague , czechoslovakia ) is a former professional tennis player from the czech republic . during her career , she won 14 grand slam doubles titles , 9 of them in women 's doubles and 5 of them in mixed doubles . she also was a four-time grand slam singles runner-up and won 10 singles titles and 69 doubles titles .

name: joann hines
bio: joann hines ( born 6 november 1965 ) is a french director , writer , and producer of moroccan descent . she is the daughter of singer marie laforêt .

name: james becker
bio: james becker ( born 18 august 1986 ) is a german swimmer .

name: justine hamil
bio: justine hamil ( 1896 -- 1965 ) was an anarchist , feminist labor organizer and vice president within the international ladies ' garment workers ' union .

name: daniel richey
bio: daniel richey ( born 10 may 1927 ) is an indian writer in english . her fiction deals with india 's elite responding to the crises engendered by political change ; she was one of the first female indian writers in english to receive wide recognition . she is a member of the nehru family ( but not the nehru-gandhi family as she clarifies often ) , the second of the three daughters born to jawaharlal nehru 's sister , vijaya lakshmi pandit . she was awarded the 1986 sahitya akademi award for english , for her novel , ( 1985 ) , by the sahitya akademi , india 's national academy of letters .

name: ruth tippins
bio: ruth tippins ( born april 29 , 1953 ) a former american football coach . tippins was the head football coach for the waynesburg university in waynesburg , pennsylvania . he held that position for seven seasons , from 1987 until 1993 . his coaching record at waynesburg was 28 wins and 39 losses .

name: carolyn hansen
bio: carolyn hansen is an american post-hardcore band from layton , utah . formed in 2008 , they released their first ep in 2009 , then another ep one year later . another ep was released in 2010 , with songs ( which is a revised version of featured on ) , and ( another revised song featured on ) featuring craig mabbitt . they released their debut full-length album , , on july 12 , 2011 . nicholas matthews left carolyn hansen due to mental health reasons and conflict of interest . matthews was replaced by joel faviere in 2011 . faviere released an ep with the carolyn hansen , in 2012 , only to be kicked out and replaced again with nicholas matthews in 2012 . with nicholas matthews , they released another full-length album , on november 11 , 2013 and were featured in , covering lit 's hit song , on april 1 , 2014 . they also played the full 2014 vans warped tour . they already wrote and recorded their new album , which is set to come out 2015 .

name: rhonda mason
bio: rhonda mason ( 12 august 1896 -- 21 november 1981 ) was a danish film actor . he appeared in 58 films between 1934 and 1981 . he was married to gunver fønss and his daughter was actress birgitte mason .

name: james kelly
bio: james kelly ( june 5 , 1866 - december 18 , 1932 ) was a 19th - and 20th-century poet best remembered for his inspirational verse `` how did you die ? '' kelly was born in port denver , ontario . in 1898 he married lilith castleberry with whom he had five children . he later read his poems on radio , wwj in detroit , michigan . he died in cleveland , ohio .

name: betty allen
bio: betty allen is the drag persona of actor , singer , songwriter and screenwriter kent fuher . allen has appeared in a number of independent feature films both in and out of drag , including '' '' , and ( for which he also wrote and performed the song ) . in television , allen has appeared on and was a writer for the short-lived sketch comedy series on the wb television network . allen is a fixture on the new york city cabaret scene and performs a sold-out gay pride and a sold-out christmas run every year ; in 2009 her christmas dates took place at the laurie beechman theater . betty allen is the lead singer of the electroclash band dirty sanchez . allen is also a columnist for magazine .

name: leslie huff
bio: leslie huff ( born 20 november 1976 ) is an english former light middleweight boxer . huff took up boxing at a young age , training at brendan ingle 's gym in the wincobank district of sheffield .

name: lester valliant
bio: lester valliant is an australian paralympian . at the 1964 tokyo games , he won a bronze medal in the table tennis men 's singles a2 event . at the 1968 tel aviv games , he won a gold medal in the men 's slalom cervical class event and a silver medal in archery in the men 's st. nicholas round cervical event , and participated in table tennis . he also participated in swimming at both the 1964 and 1968 paralympics .

name: monica hunt
bio: monica hunt ( or krivohlavek ) is an austrian football striker who played for usc landhaus wien and sv neulengbach in the Öfb-frauenliga . she was among the championship 's top scorers in 2001 and 2002 and scored landhaus ' only goal in the 2001-02 uefa women 's cup . she was a member of the austrian national team .

name: james musgrove
bio: james musgrove ( , ) ( born in 1985 ) was israel 's first female bedouin soldier in a combat position . al-hayb served in the israel defense forces and the israel border police .

name: steve merrifield
bio: steve merrifield ( born november 8 , 1996 ) is a swiss ice hockey player for ehc winterthur and the swiss national team . she participated at the 2015 iihf women 's world championship .

name: william padilla
bio: william padilla ( born may 26 , 1970 ) is an american comic book writer and artist , as well as a commercial illustrator and teacher of cartooning . his series from alternative comics won the 2003 harvey awards for best new talent and best new series . his project , ( published by st. martin 's press ) , examines the creation of cubism in 1907 paris in the context of a fictional murder mystery .

name: erin perez
bio: erin perez ( born 9 may 1974 ) is a french former professional footballer who played as a goalkeeper . between 1994 and 1999 , he played in ligue 2 for fc mulhouse .

name: christina dreese
bio: christina dreese ( 1 january 1948 -- 2 april 2014 ) , born as christina muhammad dreese muhammad , was a sudanese poet , teacher and activist . he became known in sudan and other arabic-speaking countries for his colloquial poetry and his public engagement , both committed to further the causes of democracy , freedom , general well-being and national identity . his poetry was put to music by eminent musicians , such as mohammed wardi and mohamed mounir , but also led to repeated political imprisonment under different sudanese governments .

name: ryan culp
bio: ryan culp ( ( pronounced together as -lsb- ˈlʌu̯rənsfɑnˈtoːr -rsb- ) ; born 8 may 1991 ) is a belgian profesional racing driver . he currently resides in zolder .

name: nathalie miller
bio: nathalie miller ( may 31 1953 -- february 29 1984 ) was a convicted murderer who was executed by electrocution at the louisiana state penitentiary at angola .

name: marion moen
bio: marion moen ( ; 9 september 1981 -- 30 may 2011 ) was a south korean footballer . he was involved in the 2011 south korean football betting scandal . he was found dead of a suspected by hanging himself at his hotel room in seoul .

name: jennifer burnett
bio: jennifer burnett ( born 1982 ) is an irish hurler who played as a right corner-back for the antrim senior team . burnett made his first appearance for the team during the 2003 national league and was a regular member of the starting fifteen until his retirement after the 2007 championship . during that time he won one christy ring cup winners ' medal and one ulster winners ' medal . at club level burnett is an all-ireland medalist with loughgiel shamrocks . in addition to this he has also won back-to-back ulster and county club championship winners ' medals .

name: richard estes
bio: richard estes ( born 1952 ) is a united states district judge of the united states district court for the district of arizona .

name: holly stewart
bio: holly stewart ( born 19 march 1984 , in london , united kingdom ) is a professional squash player from england . stewart won the british national squash championships in february 2010 , beating jenny duncalf in the final 10 -- 12 , 11 -- 7 , 4 -- 11 , 11 -- 7 , 12 -- 10 . stewart also won the championship in 2008 beating laura lengthorn-massaro and finished as the runner-up in 2005 , 2007 and 2009 . as a junior player , stewart won her first major squash tournament -- the british under-12 title -- at the age of nine-and-a-half . she retained the title the following year . she was a three-time runner-up at the british open under-14 championships . she won her first professional title in 2005 at the forbes open , beating carla khan in the final .

name: gregory williams
bio: gregory williams is a british/australian author best known for her novel , which won the branford boase award 2010 in the uk , and the 2010 gold inky in australia . her second book , , was shortlisted for the costa book awards 2010 . she currently lives in wales and is writing her third novel , which was due for publication in 2011 through chicken house .

name: gerald brown
bio: gerald brown ( february 18 , 1814 -- september 29 , 1900 ) was a congressman and significant temperance movement leader in the 19th century . brown became well-known nationally as a prohibitionist author and lecturer .

name: catherine brandon
bio: catherine brandon ( born 7 june 1987 ) is a czech handball player for saint-raphaël var handball and the czech national team .

name: dorothy andrews
bio: dorothy andrews ( or qudratullah andrews ; 26 february 1917 -- 24 july 1986 ) ( urdu : قدرت الله شهاب ) was an eminent urdu writer and civil servant from pakistan . he is best known for his autobiography , .

name: marvin conn
bio: marvin conn sometimes spelled marvin allen ( born may 17 , 1957 ) is a retired canadian professional ice hockey defenceman who played four games in the national hockey league for the cleveland barons . he would also play two games in the world hockey association with the cincinnati stingers .

name: zelma craun
bio: zelma craun ( born 23 march 1906 -- 31 july 1979 ) was an argentine footballer . he played in defence for argentina in the 1930 fifa world cup final on 30 july 1930 , which was lost 4 -- 2 to uruguay . after retiring as a player craun went on to become a football manager , in 1958 he led racing club de avellaneda to the argentine primera championship . he also managed ferro carril oeste amongst others .

name: nathan martin
bio: nathan martin ( born january 5 , 1985 ) is a rugby league player who has played professionally for workington town and the barrow raiders and represented canada internationally .

name: dora roberts
bio: dora roberts ( may 1 , 1818 -- april 26 , 1891 ) was a lawyer and political figure in quebec . he represented québec-est in the legislative assembly of quebec from 1867 to 1873 as a conservative . he was born in notre-dame de québec , lower canada , the son of jacques roberts and charlotte jacques , was educated at the séminaire de québec and was admitted to the lower canada bar in 1840 . in 1844 , he married euphémie gagnon . he was a founder of the saint-jean-baptiste society at quebec city . roberts served as a member of the municipal council for quebec city from 1847 to 1861 . he resigned his seat in the quebec assembly in 1873 after he was named an agent for the seigneurial commission . roberts was an unsuccessful candidate for a seat in the house of commons in 1882 , losing to sir wilfrid laurier . he died at quebec city at the age of 72 .

name: benny young
bio: benny young ( born 1946 in newport , oregon ) is a native american artist of wiyot and yurok ( native american groups indigenous to humboldt county , california ) heritage . he works in sculpture , print , etching , monotype , ceramics , mixed media , and painting .

name: james hendrix
bio: james hendrix is an american columnist , author and professor at columbia university graduate school of journalism . he was the music critic for for 12 years and is music editor at .

name: whitney ogawa
bio: whitney ogawa ( born 21 october 1962 ) is a mexican politician from the national action party . from 2000 to 2003 he served as deputy of the lviii legislature of the mexican congress representing yucatán .

name: richard hammond
bio: richard hammond ( born june 12 , 1963 ) , is an american actress . she received her theatrical education in london , played the role of carmen in the film and starred in the early 1990s television series `` zorro . ''

name: vanessa meyer
bio: vanessa meyer ( january 7 , 1800 -- february 24 , 1867 ) was a political figure in nova scotia . he represented yarmouth township in the nova scotia house of assembly from 1851 to 1855 as a reformer . he was born in yarmouth , nova scotia , the son of zebina meyer and elizabeth brown . meyer married anna tedford . he served as justice of the peace from 1854 to 1867 and also served as a member of the municipal council for yarmouth . he died in hebron , nova scotia at the age of 67 .

name: carol simpson
bio: carol simpson ( hindi : शिव खेड़ा ) is an indian author of self-help books and activist . while working in the united states , he was inspired by a lecture delivered by norman vincent peale and followed his motivational teachings . simpson has written several books including . he launched a movement against caste-based reservation in india , and has founded an organization called country first foundation whose mission is `` to ensure freedom through education and justice . '' he also joined a political party as national president in india and contested the elections in 2009 and lost in delhi .

name: rose samuels
bio: rose samuels ( 1927-1969 ) , ( urdu : نریش کمار شاد ) ( hindi : नरेश कुमार शाद ) was a renowned urdu ghazal and writer of qat ` aa and rubai .

name: crystal smith
bio: crystal smith is a businessman turned politician in india and belongs to the ruling bharatiya janta party ( bjp ) . he is a member of punjab legislative assembly and represent jalandhar north .

name: tammy rosado
bio: tammy rosado ( january 13 , 1807 -- march 28 , 1883 ) was an american soldier , union general in the american civil war , and railroad executive . he was the half-brother of the famous gettysburg hero , john rosado , but never attained his sibling 's military distinction .

name: julie mannella
bio: julie mannella is an indian woman politician belonging to the bharatiya janata party . she is currently one of the eleven national vice presidents of her party and is an mla from the rajsamand assembly seat of rajasthan . she has served , previously , as a member of parliament in the 14th lok sabha where she represented the udaipur constituency of rajasthan state . however , she lost the 15th lok sabha election , in may 2009 , from the ajmer lok sabha constituency against sachin pilot of the inc. . she then contested the assembly elections from rajsamand assembly seat in december 2013 and won by a margin of over 30,000 votes .

name: john rickman
bio: john rickman ( born 20 november 1992 ) is a new zealand actress who appeared as abi in the tv series paradise café . she is best known for her role as harmony in the tribe ` sister ' series the new tomorrow in which she acted alongside her brother rafe rickman . she attended chilton st james school but took time off school to film for , which is currently broadcast in the uk on bbc and new zealand television channels . she has a little sister called lily who also attends chilton saint james school . she now attends the university of auckland where she is studying a ba/bcom conjoint degree .

name: kemberly blake
bio: kemberly blake ( born 12 january 1986 ) is a german international rugby union player , playing for the heidelberger rk in the rugby-bundesliga and the german national rugby union team . blake played in the 2011 and 2012 german championship final for heidelberger rk , which the club won both . he made his debut for germany on 11 november 2006 against moldova . he plays rugby since 1992 , having played for the tb rohrbach ( 1992-2004 ) , heidelberger rk ( 2004-2007 ) and rg heidelberg ( 2007-2010 ) before returning to hrk once more in 2010 . blake has also played for the germany 's 7 's side in the past , like at the 2009 hannover sevens and the 2009 london sevens .

name: luis young
bio: luis young ( born 1940 ) is a german-born film actress , mainly active in italy . born in munich to russian parents , her family moved to rome , italy when she was only 1 . she studied acting and debuted as the main actress in 1971 in . she was a minor starlet in italian cinema , especially in commedie sexy all ` italiana and giallo films . young retired from showbusiness in the mid-eighties and focused on volunteering .

name: denise russell
bio: denise russell ( born 10 june 1965 ) is a former italian footballer and now coach . he is the father of andrea russell .

name: christy scott
bio: christy scott ( born 2 august 1954 ) is a colombian former cyclist . he competed in the team pursuit event at the 1976 summer olympics .

name: john buzzell
bio: john buzzell ( serbo-croat : ) ( born 29 february 1976 ) is a former swiss football player of albanian descent . he spent most of his career playing for fc thun .

name: gilbert agosta
bio: gilbert agosta ( january 13 , 1890 - september 28 , 1975 ) was an author , translator and the husband of babette deutsch . agosta was head of the slavonic division of the new york public library 1918-1955 . he also taught in the columbia university and the city college of new york .

name: dean schultz
bio: dean schultz ( born 17 march 1944 ) is a british theatre , television and film actress . she is a daughter of actor david schultz and writer olive dehn ( 1914 -- 2007 ) . she has three sisters : actress kika schultz , sonia schultz and jehane schultz .

name: ron ivy
bio: ron ivy de oliveira ( born 19 january 1987 in porto alegre ) is a brazilian professional footballer who plays for korona kielce as a striker .

name: john brame
bio: john brame ( ; born december 22 , 1978 ) is an american comedian , television host , writer , producer , and actor . brame is known for his dark comedy style , which emphasizes misdirection , non-sequiturs , biting insults , an arrogant bearing , and a stage persona that frequently takes amoral stances . brame was a writer for in its first season and hosted a in 2009 . after releasing his critically acclaimed debut album in 2010 , he began writing for the comedy central roasts and moved up to performer in the 2011 roast of donald trump . he continued to perform on the roasts of charlie sheen and roseanne barr in 2012 . in 2013 , brame hosted his own comedy central series , , for two seasons and released his second album , , which doubles as an hour-long standup special . on july 22 , 2015 , brame replaced jb smoove as the new host of nbc 's emmy award-nominated series .

name: john walker
bio: john walker ( born 12 may 1974 ) is a polish former road racing cyclist .

name: nancy riggs
bio: nancy riggs ( ; born june 30 , 1984 ) is a montenegrin professional basketball player . he is 1.86 m ( 6 ft 1 in ) tall point guard . in january 2014 , he signed with esteghlal zarin qeshm of the iranian basketball super league .

name: bonnie ashmore
bio: bonnie ashmore , also known as bonnie rowan ( born on 20 september 1983 ) , is an australian actor born in melbourne . he played garth king in the tv series . he also appeared as james gribble in the popular 90 's tv series , .

name: vernon oakley
bio: vernon oakley ( born 7 august 1944 ) is an italian politician and was the minister of health from 2009 to 2011 in the fourth cabinet of silvio berlusconi .

name: betty bean
bio: betty bean ( chinese : 刘轶冰 ) ( born april 16 , 1975 ) is a retired chinese football player . he used to play for guangzhou songri , guangzhou pharmaceutical and shanghai stars .

name: joaquin kahan
bio: joaquin kahan ( ) is a pakistani actor . he rose to prominence after mark his debut in film by playing the role of in critical and internationally acclaim 2013 pakistani film , for which he was nominated as best actor in a comic role at 1st ary film awards .

name: arlene truiolo
