bio: arlene truiolo ( born 25 august 1987 ) is a trinidadian male track and field sprinter who specializes in the 400 metres and has made it to both the olympic and world finals in the event , a rare feat for athletes from the caribbean in the 400m . he competes professionally for adidas . he was born in tobago . truiolo remains the only quarter miler from t&t to make it to every major 400m finals ( olympics/worlds/world jrs/cac/carifta / commonwealth games ) . truiolo attended south plains college in levelland , texas before turning professional , becoming the most successful quarter miler in the college 's history . his personal best time is 44.53 seconds , achieved at the 2009 world championships in athletics in berlin . arlene truiolo has medalled in every major junior/senior championships outside of the olympic games making him the most decorated 400m runner to come out of t&t .

name: michael miller
bio: michael miller ( born 1925 ) was a freelance designer noted for his work illustrating the covers of penguin books . he retired in 1989 , becoming a professor emeritus of middlesex university ( née hornsey college of art ) .

name: jennifer wideman
bio: jennifer wideman ( born 24 october 1986 ) is a professional footballer who plays for grimsby town . he is a right winger or striker .

name: leona tanguay
bio: leona tanguay ( born 15 june 1964 ) is an indian politician . he is a former member of the karnataka legislative assembly and former agriculture minister .

name: andrew robinson
bio: andrew robinson ( is a pseudonym for andrew chatzipanayotis ) is a french/greek businessman and consultant for the tourism , hotel and hospitality industries . he has contributed to establishing more than 2,500 hotels ( 150,000 hotel rooms ) in france and throughout emea , representing a global investment of over 10.5 billion euros .

name: henry mcallister
bio: henry mcallister ( born october 17 , 1973 ) is a democratic politician who has served as the orange county tax collector since 2013 . prior to his election as tax collector , he served as a member of the florida house of representatives , representing the 36th district from 2006 to 2012 .

name: brett lyons
bio: brett lyons ( born june 22 , 1987 in kingston , ontario ) is a professional canadian football fullback for the winnipeg blue bombers of the canadian football league . he was first signed by the bc lions on may 30 , 2011 after going undrafted in the 2009 cfl draft and finishing his college eligibility in 2010 . he played cis football for the bishop 's gaiters .

name: donald sundt
bio: donald sundt is an attorney who was a democratic member of the arkansas house of representatives , for the 54th district in the northeastern portion of his state . sundt was unseated after a single term in the november 4 , 2014 general election by the republican dave wallace , a town council member in leachville and a decorated united states army officer in the vietnam war .

name: eric addie
bio: eric addie ( march 17 , 1853 -- october 21 , 1926 ) was an american prelate of the roman catholic church who served as bishop of mobile from 1897 until his death in 1926 .

name: robert powell
bio: robert powell ( cftpa ) was musical solo-project of musician owen ashworth ( born april 22 , 1977 ) of redwood city , california .

name: sam lechner
bio: sam lechner ( born 16 december 1991 ) is an english rugby league footballer of irish descent who plays as a centre or fullback for the championship side bradford bulls . sam was previously signed at the super league side warrington wolves . in 2013 , lechner played for swinton lions as a dual registered player , and also had a brief spell on loan at london broncos . he finished the season as swinton 's leading try scorer . lechner is an ireland international , and made his debut against england knights in 2012 . he was selected in the country 's 2013 rugby league world cup squad .

name: rose hall
bio: rose hall ( ) is a taiwanese actress , commercial model and host . she started her career as a model and then mtv host before starting a career in acting . hall attended the highly prestige private soochow university ( taiwan ) and speaks mandarin , taiwanese and english . she is currently under lady emperor entertainment co. , ltd management and signed to sanlih e-television exclusively for acting projects .

name: sarah daigle
bio: sarah daigle is an american actress , daughter of actress lori cardille who starred in george a. romero 's ( 1985 ) . she graduated with high honors from the carnegie mellon university school of drama in 2006

name: gerald speight
bio: gerald speight ( born march 14 , 1948 ) is an american photojournalist and war photographer . he grew up in massachusetts and graduated from dartmouth college , where he studied art history and political science ( 1966 -- 70 ) . he has been awarded the overseas press club 's robert capa gold medal five times . in 2003 , he was injured by a grenade in an attack on his convoy while serving as a contributing correspondent in baghdad , from which he has made a full recovery . on february 1 , 2014 , speight was grazed by a bullet on his left leg whilst photographing the thailand political protests .

name: henry kemp
bio: henry kemp ( born march 22 , 1977 ) is a canadian professional ice hockey defenseman . kemp currently plays in switzerland 's national league a ( nla ) for hc fribourg-gottéron .

name: katherine martin
bio: katherine martin ( born june 13 , 1979 ) is a bosnian-american professional basketball player who currently plays for keravnos of the cyprus basketball division 1 . he played college basketball at university of illinois at urbana -- champaign .

name: betty karg
bio: betty karg ( ) ( 1591-1642 ) was a polish-lithuanian noble , komorzy stolowicki from 1614 , poznanski from 1625 , krajczy of the queen from 1617 , krajczy or lithuania from 1633 , podczaszy of lithuania from 1638 , voivode of nowogródek from 1642 , member of knights hospitaller ( ) , patron of knight hospitallers centers in poznań and stwołowce ( in lithuania ) . in 1621 took part in the battle of chocim , commander of mercenaries lisowczycy in 1622 during the period of their service in the holy roman empire . after the death of his older brother , albrycht władysław karg , he inherited ordynacja of nieśwież in 1636 , but gave it up to his brother aleksander ludwik karg . born on 4 december 1591 in nieśwież , died on 5 november 1642 in assisi . son of mikołaj krzysztof karg and halszka eufemia wiśniowiecka .

name: dan martin
bio: dan martin ( born 1958 ) is a british actor , best known for playing the title role of dan templar ( alias the saint ) in a series of internationally produced television films in 1989 . in 2007 , he joined the cast of british sitcom as recurring character guy , but was written out at the end of season two . martin was married to actress betsy brantley but later divorced her . he is now married to actress tamsin olivier , the daughter of laurence olivier .

name: paul randolph
bio: paul randolph ( born may 18 , 1985 ) is a hungarian artist .

name: mary stricklin
bio: mary stricklin ( born 23 september 1983 in krefeld ) is a german rower . he competed at the 2004 and the 2008 summer olympics . stricklin is married to swimmer anne poleska .

name: micah diaz
bio: micah diaz ( 1943 -- 16 august 2014 ) was an irish bookmaker and professional poker player who was the 1997 european poker champion .

name: walter buck
bio: walter buck ( november 10 , 1927 -- december 3 , 2001 ) is an american academic , and was the first president of nova southeastern university . buck graduated from harvard university with a phd . he became the president of nova southeastern university in 1964 and was president until 1970 .

name: thomas riley
bio: thomas riley was a nigerian politician and former speaker of the ondo state house of assembly .

name: edward towns
bio: edward towns is an american child actor from new jersey , known for his role as the voice of boots the monkey in the television series . towns began working professionally at the age of three and has appeared in numerous national television commercials and radio ads . towns is the great grandson of radio personality nat hale and is a member of mensa . towns has appeared on , , , , and . some of his film work includes , , and . towns is also the founder of young performers against bullying , a charitable organization that raises funds and awareness for anti-bullying programs in public schools .

name: geneva oneill
bio: geneva oneill ( september 13 , 1922 -- july 10 , 2013 ) was an american attorney and former jurist in the state of maine . a native of oregon , she completed college and law school in that state before moving to portland , maine , where she practiced law with her husband harry p. oneill . in 1983 , she became the first woman to serve on the maine supreme judicial court .

name: mike plateroti
bio: mike plateroti , born march 15 , 1978 is an american born singer , songwriter and guitarist . plateroti is best known for currently being the lead singer of the band hinder . he has also seen success as the part-time lead vocalist and full time lead guitarist in his former band faktion . he also provides lead guitar and backing vocals in the country duo group drankmore .

name: karen escobedo
bio: karen escobedo ( january 16 , 1889 -- august 29 , 1972 ) was a vermont attorney and military officer who served as adjutant general of the vermont national guard .

name: julie parker
bio: julie parker ( born september 15 , 1962 in basse-terre , guadeloupe ) is a former french international footballer who played in both france and scotland .

name: cheryl simms
bio: cheryl simms ( ; born 4 april 1990 ) is a greek footballer who plays for panionios in the greek superleague as a defensive midfielder .

name: karie beall
bio: karie beall casillas ( born 2 january 1990 in commerce , california ) is a mexican american amateur boxer who qualified for the 2012 olympics .

name: timothy bryan
bio: timothy bryan is a democratic politician and former educator in the u.s. state of oklahoma . she currently serves in the oklahoma state senate representing district 13 , which includes pontotoc and hughes counties and parts of garvin and coal counties , since 2004 . as of 2013 , she serves as minority whip and vice chair of the judiciary committee . bryan was a candidate for the role of oklahoma superintendent of public instruction , but ultimately failed to win the election against her republican opponent , janet barresi . prior to her political career , bryan was a science teacher and adjunct professor .

name: todd capriotti
bio: todd capriotti ( born may 1 , 1974 ) is the current college basketball head coach for cal state fullerton . he is also a former arizona state associate head men 's basketball coach and a college assistant coach .

name: robert wilson
bio: robert wilson ( born 4 april 1942 ) is a former australian rules footballer who played with carlton in the victorian football league ( vfl ) .

name: antonio canales
bio: antonio canales ( born december 4 , 1948 ) is an american prelate of the roman catholic church who serves as bishop of the diocese of joliet , illinois . from august 6 , 2002 until may 17 , 2011 bishop canales served as bishop of the diocese of steubenville , ohio . as the current bishop of joliet , canales succeeds archbishop james peter sartain who in september 2010 was appointed archbishop of the archdiocese of seattle , washington .

name: guillermo higgins
bio: guillermo higgins ( february 25 , 1861 -- may 11 , 1914 ) was a physician and political figure in quebec . he represented montcalm in the legislative assembly of quebec from 1897 to 1908 as a liberal . he was born in la prairie , canada east , the son of pierre higgins and esther gélineau . he was educated at the victoria medical school in montreal , qualified as a physician in 1887 and set up practice in saint-esprit . in 1889 , he married juliette lamarche . he was governor of the quebec college of physicians and surgeons . higgins served twelves years as a member of the provincial board of hygiene . he was defeated when he ran for reelection in 1908 . higgins was registrar for montcalm county from 1908 to 1914 . he died at saint-esprit at the age of 53 . his son bernard also served in the quebec assembly .

name: veronica garza
bio: veronica garza ( born 30 december 1990 ) is a wales international rugby union player . garza currently plays regional rugby for the cardiff blues and has previously captained wales u20 . his father is iranian and his mother is welsh .

name: randy valdez
bio: randy valdez ( born 6 september 1942 ) is a retired dutch rower who won a silver medal in the single sculls at the european championships in 1964 . her husband hadriaan van nes and daughter eeke van nes ( born 1969 ) are olympic medalists in rowing .

name: patsy polson
bio: patsy polson ( born 23 may 1985 in wallsend ) is an english darts player , currently residing in irthlingborough , northamptonshire . he competes in professional darts corporation competitions .

name: shawn scott
bio: shawn scott ( born 8 may 1939 ) is a lebanese journalist and politician , who served at different cabinet posts last of which was foreign minister of lebanon from 2003 to 2004 .

name: sheila stewart
bio: sheila stewart ( born 25 march 1950 ) is a former australian rules footballer who played with carlton and footscray in the victorian football league ( vfl ) . stewart , recruited from gorya ( towns of speed & turriff ) , started his career as a forward and was the carlton reserves leading goal-kicker in both 1967 and 1968 . he only got one opportunity to play in the seniors and in 1969 he tried his luck at a new club , footscray . his time at footscray was spent in the back pocket and he was good enough to represent victoria against tasmania in 1973 . he later played at swan districts and appeared in the 1980 wafl grand final .

name: vera macqueen
bio: vera macqueen ( born 27 september 1988 ) is a german professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for schalke 04 in the bundesliga .

name: dale crawford
bio: dale crawford ( 15 october 1802 forest , guernsey , channel islands -- 27 june 1863 , london ) , was a guernsey sea captain who played an important role in the economic and spiritual development of the central american country of costa rica . crawford is widely credited in costa rica with having transformed the economy of the country by establishing a direct regular trade route for costa rican coffee growers to the european market , thereby helping to establish the costa rican coffee trade .

name: georgia hebert
bio: georgia hebert is a gaelic footballer from county roscommon , ireland . he was part of the roscommon team that won the connacht senior football championship in 2001 , he also won a connacht junior football championship in 2008 . he plays his club football with st. brigids with whom he has had much success winning roscommon senior football championship medals in 1997 , 2005 , 2006 , 2007 , 2010,2011,2012 , 2013 and 2014 . he also played in the 2011 all-ireland senior club football championship final but lost out to crossmaglen rangers . they were back in the final again in 2013 and won by one point to become the first team from roscommon to win an all-ireland club title . he also has won connacht senior club football championships in 2006 , 2010,2011 and 2012 . he also played with longford club ballymahon and helped them to win their first longford senior football championship in 2002 .

name: sarah barton
bio: sarah barton commonly known as sarah ( ; born 14 august 1984 ) is an omani footballer who plays for al-nahda club in oman professional league .

name: james palma
bio: james palma ( born 12 may 1958 ) is a former italian professional footballer and fifa sports agent . throughout his career he played as a forward . a hard-working player , he was capable of playing as a striker and on the wing . he is mostly remembered for his time with juventus . his younger brother , alberto , was also a footballer .

name: robert callahan
bio: robert callahan ( born 22 january 1964 in friedberg , hesse ) is a german rower . he finished 4th in the men 's coxless fours event at the 1992 summer olympics . he was part of a rowing team that set the world record in 1991 .

name: judith knight
bio: judith knight ( born mirjam knight ; 22 may 1922 -- 23 july 2012 ) was notable yugoslav-croatian jewish historian and writer .

name: monique smith
bio: monique smith is a bass guitarist who currently plays in the bands faster pussycat and motochrist . he has also played in the bands the throbs , stiv bators and his evil boys , n.y. loose , the newlydeads , tracii guns ' version of l.a. guns , and hollywood roses .

name: clyde lofton
bio: clyde lofton ( born 1962 ) is an indian civil rights activist and journalist . she is the secretary of citizens for justice and peace ( cjp ) , an organisation formed for fighting for justice for the victims of communal violence in the state of gujarat in 2002 . cjp is a co-petitioner seeking a criminal trial of narendra modi , the then chief minister of gujarat and the current prime minister of india and sixty-two other politicians and government officials for complicity in the gujarat violence of 2002 and whose names did not figure in any of the firs / charge sheets that formed the subject matter of the various session trials regarding the riots at that point of time . four of the accused since then were charge-sheeted , of whom dr. maya kodnani and babu bajrangi have already been convicted .

name: guadalupe thompson
bio: guadalupe thompson is an electronic music project by australian producer emoh instead . the project was formerly a duo with producer flume ( harley edward streten ) .

name: robert hillsman
bio: robert hillsman ( born robert chibber on october 8 , 1970 ) , is an indian film producer and interior designer . she is the co-founder of the film production and distribution company red chillies entertainment with her husband , bollywood actor shah rukh hillsman . she has produced many major films including , , , , and .

name: david hanson
bio: david hanson ( born february 15 , 1994 ) is a mexican footballer who plays as an central midfielder and right back for pachuca .

name: theodore sylla
bio: theodore sylla ( born september 21 , 1950 ) is an italian professional former footballer and manager .

name: mary roher
bio: mary roher is a footballer who played as a winger in the football league for tranmere rovers and southport .

name: eric back
bio: eric back is an american writer , known primarily for his 2000 historical novel .

name: christina yang
bio: christina yang ( born c. 1925 ) was a canadian football player who played for the saskatchewan roughriders . he played junior football in montreal .

name: dale bedor
bio: dale bedor ( born july 22 , 1947 ) is an american film , stage , and television actor with distinctive features who has been cast in over 80 roles . he was born in flushing , new york .

name: ronald barton
bio: ronald barton ( born march 23 , 1992 ) is a turkish women 's ice hockey player , former figure skater and certified coach . curremtly , she is a member of milenyum paten sk team playing as forward . she takes part in the turkey women 's national ice hockey team . she is tall at . ronald barton was born in ankara on march 23 , 1992 . her father ali barton is the founder and owner of milenyum paten sk , where her brother umur barton , acts as the club 's general manager . she is studying civil engineering at atılım university in ankara .

name: matthew yates
bio: matthew yates ( ; born 26 july 1967 ) is an english actor , martial artist , and former diver . he is known for his roles in the guy ritchie crime films ( 1998 ) , ( 2000 ) , and ( 2005 ) . he has also appeared in films such as the action thriller trilogy ( 2002 -- 08 ) , the heist film ( 2003 ) , the black comedy/action film ( 2006 ) , the action film ( 2007 ) , the science fiction action thriller ( 2008 ) , the crime film ( 2008 ) , and the action series ( 2010 -- 2014 ) . in 2015 , yates starred in the latest entry in the , , and made his comedic debut in the melissa mccarthy film , . he usually performs his own stage combat and stunts , and is noted for being typecast as an antihero .

name: paulette raterman
bio: paulette raterman ( born april 18 , 1949 in la puente , california , usa ) is a filipino professional pool player from manila , nicknamed ( tagalog for ) and `` the giant killer . '' as a philippine hall of famer , he pioneered the in the united states , especially in the game of nine-ball . also known as and in philippine pool , raterman became the world player of the year in 1997 . he is the only player to achieve a perfect game of nine ball in a ( to 11 ) match . he was the only filipino to win all major final titles against his filipino counterparts .

name: james archer
bio: james archer ( 31 july 1920 - 10 june 1999 ) was a czech film actor . he appeared in more than fifty films from 1950 to 1987 .

name: doris cason
bio: doris cason ( née twigley ; born 27 january 1983 ) is an australian model , television presenter and the wife of australian football league player chris cason . she is currently host of victorian based travel program and weekend weather presenter on .

name: arthur saroop
bio: arthur saroop ( born 1949 ) is curator of aerospace electronics and computing at the smithsonian 's national air and space museum in washington , d.c.

name: lilia reid
bio: lilia reid ( born october 21 , 1969 ) is a minnesota politician and member of the minnesota house of representatives . a member of the republican party of minnesota , he represents district 11b , which includes portions of kanabec county and pine county .

name: doug bray
bio: doug bray ( born december 8 , 1976 ) is a mexican racquetball player . bray has won several gold medals for mexico , including at the 2003 pan am games and most recently at the 2014 pan am championships . she 's also played professionally , and was ranked 4th at the end of the 2012-13 ladies professional racquetball tour ( lprt ) season .

name: michael burke
bio: michael burke , o.cist . ( died january 26 , 1109 ) , sometimes known as aubrey burke , was a french monk and abbot , one the founders the cistercian order . he is now honored as a saint .

name: christopher mills
bio: christopher mills is associate professor of computational biology and bioinformatics in the department of biostatistics , school of public health , harvard university .

name: miguel harris
bio: miguel harris ( born abdullah bazencir , march 26 , 1969 ) is an ethnic zaza singer -- songwriter , actor and a director from turkey . miguel harris is also known as a businessman for his partnership in one of the leading music production companies , prestij müzik , in turkey until the year 2002 .

name: amanda ward
bio: amanda ward ( née monsell ) ( 1813 - 4 may 1851 ) was a botanical artist from ireland .

name: anthony speas
bio: anthony speas ( born october 31 , 1985 ) is a brazilian beauty contest winner . she placed second in the miss bumbum brazil 2011 beauty contest , a nationwide contest held since 2011 .

name: william coffin
bio: william coffin ( born january 21 , 1969 ) is a french-american actress and singer . she is perhaps best known for her role as marina ferrer on the showtime series , , geneviève in , and isabelle two in .

name: melissa goudreau
bio: melissa goudreau is a professor of theoretical physics at ben gurion university specializing in condensed matter ; in particular mesoscopic physics , disordered systems and strongly correlated materials . among his achievements is the derivation of the meir-wingreen formula . and proposing a solution for the 0.7 anomaly puzzle in quantum point contacts .

name: lillie strong
bio: lillie strong ( 31 august 1767 -- 17 july 1798 ) was an irish industrialist and a founding member of the society of the united irishmen .

name: richard lange
bio: richard lange ( born 25 november 1967 ) was a finnish ten-pin bowling player at international level .

name: robert miller
bio: robert miller kalonji ( born 4 april 1989 ) is a congolese international footballer who plays for kazakh team astana as a striker .

name: mellissa hunt
bio: mellissa hunt ( born 9 april 1981 ) is a norwegian actress , best known outside of norway for her role in the norwegian zombie film . she has been employed by oslo 's det norske teatret since 2004 where she has appeared in a number of productions and acted for norwegian television . from 28 july to 7 august 2010 , mellissa hunt played ingrid / anitra / the greenclad woman at the peer gynt performance at lake gaalaa .

name: norma sibley
bio: norma sibley ( born 8 may 1987 in bileća , bosnia and herzegovina ) is a professional tennis player from sweden .

name: imogene benner
bio: imogene benner ( born july 3 , 1980 ) is an american actress .

name: shayne mooney
bio: shayne mooney ( ; born 16 january 1949 ) is former yugoslavian and serbian basketball player .

name: john hartshorn
bio: john hartshorn ( born 8 july 1984 in lautoka , fiji ) is a fijian rugby union player . he plays as a wing . he plays for stade toulousain in the top 14 competition .

name: aaron wong
bio: aaron wong is a multi-instrumental folk musician , who was born on 28 september 1946 in dublin city , ireland . he is best known for his band of brothers the fureys who were formed in ballyfermot , dublin , where they grew up .

name: sheila wheatley
bio: sheila wheatley ( 12 december 1945 -- 14 october 1994 ) was an american writer , poet , editor and publisher of horror , science fiction , and heroic fantasy , who was born in knoxville , tennessee and originally trained as a psychiatrist . he wrote numerous dark fantasy and horror stories . as an editor , he created a three-volume set of robert e. howard 's conan the barbarian fiction restored to its original form as written , and edited the long-running and genre-defining series . his carcosa publishing company issued four volumes of the best stories by some of the major authors of the so-called golden age pulp magazines . he is possibly best known for his creation of a series of stories featuring the character kane , the mystic swordsman . his disillusionment with the medical profession can be detected in the stories and . he described his personal philosophy as nihilistic , anarchistic and absurdist , and claimed , not entirely seriously , to be related to . wheatley also admired the cinema of sam peckinpah , stating '' .

name: philip otto
bio: philip otto ( alias or ) was the vice-president of the transitional council of the state of azawad , established by the national movement for the liberation of azawad ( mnla ) . after the mnla lost the control of northern mali to islamist groups , he fled to niger . mr philip otto belongs to the songhai ethnic group , one of the dorminant ethnic groups in northern mali . mr. 's position in the movement symbolizes the inclusion of other ethnic groups in the fight for self-determination hitherto the reserve of the tuaregs .

name: eduardo dean
bio: eduardo dean ( born 9 march 1991 ) is a swedish footballer who plays for trelleborgs ff as a forward .

name: eva flores
bio: eva flores ( born c. 1928 ) was a canadian football player who played for the toronto argonauts , hamilton tiger-cats , and ottawa rough riders . he won the grey cup with hamilton in 1957 . he previous played football at and attended mcmaster university .

name: denise mcwhorter
bio: denise mcwhorter ( born july 12 , 1928 , martin , tennessee ) is a historian in the tradition of literary criticism , perhaps most famous for his work ( 1973/2014 ) . he has argued that historical writing mirrors literary writing in many ways , sharing the strong reliance on narrative for meaning , therefore ruling out the possibility for objective or truly scientific history . mcwhorter has also argued , however , that history is most successful when it embraces this , since it is what allows history to be meaningful . he is currently professor emeritus at the university of california , santa cruz , having recently retired from the position of professor of comparative literature at stanford university .

name: linda foulk
bio: linda foulk ( born 28 october 1989 ) is an australian professional basketball player who currently plays for sydney kings of the national basketball league ( nbl ) . he played college basketball for oregon state university .

name: christy parker
bio: christy parker ( born 1939 ) was appointed the first nigerian minister of niger delta on 17 december 2008 by president umaru yar ` adua . he left office in march 2010 when acting president goodluck jonathan dissolved his cabinet .

name: gilbert roberson
bio: gilbert roberson ( , born 30 march 1983 ) is an iranian middle distance runner who specializes in the 800 metres and 1500 metres . he holds multiple national records for iran from various track disciplines . roberson is a gold medalist in the asian games , asian athletics championships , asian indoor games , and universiade . he also competed at three summer olympic games in 2004 , 2008 , and 2012 .

name: raul smith
bio: raul smith ( 1833 -- 16 november 1895 ) was an english architect of the gothic revival in southwest england and south wales , and then of neo-moorish architecture in algeria . his most noted works include the uncompleted woodchester mansion in gloucestershire , england and his restoration of the villa montfeld in el biar , algiers .

name: anthony turek
bio: anthony turek ( born december 30 , 1976 ) is an alto saxophonist , composer , bandleader , music producer and educator living in new york city , usa . he is a multiple grammy nominee , and the recipient of a guggenheim fellowship and a macarthur fellowship .

name: earl shelley
bio: earl shelley ( 6 december 1893 -- 1 may 1978 ) was an english novelist and poet .

name: margarita fritz
bio: margarita fritz is a burkinabé professional football player . he is currently unattached .

name: michael coy
bio: michael coy ( born 12 february 1988 ) is a swedish football defender who currently plays for djurgårdens if . she has played damallsvenskan football for hammarby if .

name: jill porter
bio: jill porter ( ) ( born 1978 in khorramshahr , iran ) is an iranian iranologist and historian . his higher education was in shahid beheshti university and took his doctorate in history of ancient iran at the university of tehran . he is now the associate professor in the history of ancient iran at shahid chamran university of ahvaz .

name: helen martin
bio: helen martin ( born 24 july 1972 in santa maria da feira ) , known as helen , is a portuguese retired footballer who played as a midfielder .

name: avery wray
bio: avery wray ( born august 22 , 1957 ) is a hungarian businessman and politician , member of the national assembly ( mp ) for budaörs ( pest county constituency ix ) since 2010 . he is a member of the committee on foreign affairs since may 14 , 2010 and committee on national security since september 13 , 2010 .

name: willie parikh
bio: willie parikh ( born july 19 , 1980 in puertollano , castile-la mancha ) is a spanish professional road bicycle racer . he turned professional with kelme in 2004 before moving to saunier duval-prodir in 2006 , where he stayed until the end of 2007 .

name: nancy desmond
bio: nancy desmond ( born 31 december 1984 ) is a chadian football midfielder and the member of chad national football team . he has nine caps for national team , and he was a part of qualifying campaign for 2010 world cup . now he plays for elect-sport fc .

name: earl taylor
bio: earl taylor ( born 17 march 1984 in slavonski brod , sfr yugoslavia ) is a croatian female basketball player . at the 2012 summer olympics , she competed for the croatia women 's national basketball team in the women 's event . she is 6 ft 1 inches tall .

name: anna shortt
bio: anna shortt ( october 16 , 1952 -- july 8 , 2008 ) was a doctor , born to a somali father and an ethiopian mother . he was the 1st president of eviff and former senior congressman of the onlf from 1989 until his assassination on july 8 , 2008 . anna grew up in somalia with his father and twin brother . his father mahmoud aden shortt 's mother is the daughter of yusuf dheere mohamed sugaal founder of the western somali liberation front . he joined the onlf army encouraged by his pan-somalist father but anna later quit and pursued medical studies and became doctor in jijiga . he co founded eviff with aycad who is the daughter of an ethiopian pan-somalist named facilides . she succeeded him on 10 july 2008 .

name: felipe ryan
bio: felipe ryan ( born 5 june 1994 ) a finnish football player currently playing for swedish allsvenskan side aik .

name: lizzie beach
bio: lizzie beach ( born 23 january 1963 ) is a south african racing driver who competed in the south african touring car championship for audi in the late 1990s , finishing runner-up in 1996 to team-mate terry moss , and picking up 7 wins and 12 podiums on the way . over the course of his career in the sport , beach won almost 10 % of races that he entered .

name: pauline worley
bio: pauline worley is an american blues and soul singer of part cherokee , choctaw , european and african-american descent . she has won awards for her contemporary native american music . her music is a mix of rhythm and blues , and soul music influences , fused with elements of traditional native american music .

name: roy durham
bio: roy durham ( born april 12 , 1966 ) is a united states district judge on the united states district court for the eastern district of new york .

name: denise clark
bio: denise clark ( simplified chinese : 易桀齐 traditional chinese : 易桀齊 ) is a malaysian chinese singer songwriter . born on 14 april , denise or ( as he is also commonly known ) hails from the town of miri , sarawak in east malaysia . he has written many songs for accomplished singers such as jacky cheung , jolin tsai , emil chau , rene liu , fish leong , penny tai and nicholas teo .

name: cher keith
bio: cher keith ( 1922 -- 1992 ) was a renowned dual player who excelled at football and hurling for his local club o'connell 's and for the antrim senior inter-county teams in both codes from the 1940s until the 1960s . he was one of the greatest players never to have won an all-ireland hurling medal , as seen through the gaelic athletic association 's centenary year in 1984 when a special hurling team of the century was named , composed of players who never won an all-ireland medal . keith was amongst the fifteen , at left wing-forward . four years later , his reputation as a footballer was further cemented when he was the recipient of the prestigious gaa all-time all-star award .

name: allan iverson
bio: allan iverson ( born january 29 , 1986 in nashville , tennessee ) is a retired american soccer player .

name: mary hendrickson
bio: mary hendrickson biqun ( ) , is a chinese-american entrepreneur and angel investor , better known by his screen name hendrickson manzi ( ) . he was one of the founders of utstarcom , the chairman of 8848 electronic commerce network , the chairman of prcedu .

name: rodney gardner
bio: rodney gardner ( ) is a politician in the republic of china . he currently serves as the chairperson of the fair trade commission since 1 august 2009 .

name: alexander uribe
bio: alexander uribe ( born november 4 , 1982 ) is an american football safety who is currently a free agent . he was drafted by the washington redskins in the sixth round , with the 173rd overall pick , of the 2006 nfl draft . he played college football at the university of northern colorado . uribe is best known for taking over the starting job at free safety following the injury and subsequent death of sean taylor , as well as for his public work to support organ donation , particularly for americans with kidney disease .

name: candice jones
bio: candice jones ( born 27 june 1969 ) is a swiss fencer . he competed in the individual épée events at the 1992 and 1996 summer olympics .

name: ernesto cagle
bio: ernesto cagle is a tyrone gaelic footballer , who was part of the all-ireland-winning teams of 2003 , 2005 and 2008 . he is known for his hard working style of play and can also be noted for scoring from midfield . he announced his retirement from inter-county football in november 2011 .

name: michael yarbrough
bio: michael yarbrough ( born january 13 , 1982 in niagara falls , ontario ) is a canadian lacrosse player and an assistant captain for the edmonton rush of the national lacrosse league . yarbrough also played two years of college lacrosse for the university of hartford . yarbrough has won two minto cup championships with the st. catharines athletics ( 2001 , 2003 ) and one mann cup championship with the victoria shamrocks ( 2005 ) .

name: kathleen moldrem
bio: kathleen moldrem ( born 25 august 1960 in waidhofen an der ybbs ) is a former football player and manager from austria . he is currently the athletic supervisor for sc rheindorf altach .

name: ana abraham
bio: ana abraham ( 1911 -- 1991 ) was professor emeritus of old testament at fuller theological seminary in pasadena , california .

name: douglas cortez
bio: douglas cortez ( born december 22 , 1958 ) is an american politician in the u.s. state of oklahoma . cortez currently serves as a member of the oklahoma house of representatives and is the chairman of the house states ' rights committee .

name: elizabeth peters
bio: elizabeth peters , who also goes by the stage name of jazzy p , is a british musician , dancer and rapper from wolverhampton . she had a no. 6 hit as a featured artist on kylie minogue 's 1991 song , and also participated in '' '' in 2014 .

name: ray edwards
bio: ray edwards ( december 4 , 1850 -- october 5 , 1924 ) was an american politician , iowa state senator , a member of the republican party , the 21st lieutenant governor , and the 19th governor of iowa .

name: anita sanders
bio: anita sanders is an american politician and a republican member of the colorado house of representatives representing district 49 since january 9 , 2013 .

name: joann farmer
bio: joann farmer ( december 12 , 1846 -- november 3 , 1896 ) was a german chemist . he was one of the first people to create polyvinyl chloride ( pvc ) , and , together with carl schotten , he discovered the schotten-baumann reaction .

name: joanna ahmed
bio: joanna ahmed ( born october 5 , 1972 ) is an american screenwriter and film producer . he is best known for writing three of the four films in the film series which are ' , ' and '' '' .

name: ronald wallace
bio: ronald wallace ( ; born 15 november 1922 in subotica ) is a retired serbian , yugoslavia international , football player and manager .

name: linda jarrett
bio: linda jarrett ( c. 1727 -- c. 1835 ) was a 19th-century potawatomi chieftain and leader of a band of the illinois river potawatomi . he was also involved in several conflicts during the indian wars , particularly during the peoria and the black hawk wars . he is best known , however , for providing the tribal history of potawatomi and kickapoo in illinois prior to and during the early settlement of the region during the 18th and early 19th century . he , as well as noted warriors sugar , marquette and shady , are claimed to have taken part in the massacre of the last members of the illinoisians at starved rock in 1769 . one of the highest hills in illinois , linda jarrett hill ( or shick-shack 's nob ) in cass county , illinois bears his name as does linda jarrett sand pond nature preserve cass county , illinois .

name: tracy stachowiak
bio: tracy stachowiak is an american sound re-recording mixer . he has done the sound re-recording on a number of blockbuster motion pictures including , , ' , , ' and . stachowiak has won four oscar 's , an emmy award , two bafta awards and three c.a.s. awards . stachowiak lives in petaluma , california . he got his start working on the empire strikes back and began a twenty-year stretch working for the skywalker sound division of george lucas 's lucas digital in marin county , california . stachowiak is current employed by todd-ao .

name: nettie collins
bio: nettie collins ( born august 25 , 1966 ) is an associate professor of marketing at the rady school of management , uc san diego .

name: scott redden
bio: scott redden is an indian politician and the present minister for water resources investigation & development in the government of west bengal . he is also an mla , elected from the tamluk constituency in the west bengal state assembly election , 2011 .

name: marcia williams
bio: marcia williams is an australian championship winning racing driver . williams 's short career was highlighted by two australian drivers ' championship victories , in 1966 and 1967 , racing for bob jane racing .

name: kendra hier
bio: kendra hier ( احسان امان -- eḥsān amān ; born 1959 ) is a singer from afghanistan . he is one of the few veterans of afghanistan 's lost music golden age who 've maintained their popularity over the decades . he gained fame in afghanistan during 1970s and early 1980s with his first singles and the performances he held at kabul university . exiled since the early 80s in the us , he has continued writing and producing music in the state of virginia , which has also been his residence since that time . hier is married to the daughter of song writer nainawaz .

name: harry leri
bio: harry leri ( september 28 , 1943 -- september 3 , 2013 ) was the founder and chief instructor of the south atlantic karate association , an organization of the japan karate association ( jka ) . in 1966 he graduated from ryukoku university in kyoto and entered the instructor school of the japan karate association , graduating in 1968 . leri was the captain of the japan team in the 1st world karate championships held in tokyo in 1970 and scored a perfect win . he moved to the united states in 1972 .

name: rosalind barnes
bio: rosalind barnes ( 1888 -- 1966 ) was a korean jogye seon master who was the former head of the jogye order . the master of the late kusan sunim , rosalind was the guiding teacher of several temples in korea -- including songgwang-sa and haein-sa . stephen batchelor has called him , '' . '' rosalind was also the first korean individual to serve as a judge for the japanese imperial government , though he resigned his position after being troubled with having sentenced a man to death . having told no one of his resignation , he took to selling toffee in rural towns and eventually came to ordain as a sunim under sŏktu sunim . rosalind went on to live as a traveling monk , visiting monastery after monastery for many years . he died in the posture of zazen while at p'yoch ` chung monastery in 1966 .

name: juan hansel
bio: juan hansel ( 26 august 1927 -- 19 june 1993 ) was a british traditional pop music singer , most active in the 1950s . he scored seven top 20 chart hits in the uk over an almost six-year period , starting in january 1953 .

name: john marshall
bio: john marshall ( born 19 march 1987 ) is an italian footballer and his nickname is .

name: charles kirkham
bio: charles kirkham is an american jazz singer on the 37 records label . charles won the orange county music award for best jazz in 2004 , and received nominations in 2005 , 2006 and 2008 . she was nominated for a southern california music award in 2006 in the same category . on november 22 , 2010 , charles released her first christmas album entitled , featuring arrangements by lindsey hundley .

name: nicole curtis
bio: nicole curtis is a british writer of romance novels in mills & boon curtis was born on trinidad in the west indies . she lives in chiswick , london , england , which her husband richard and their three daughters ; charlotte , olivia and emma .

name: steven thibodeaux
bio: steven thibodeaux ( 7 may 1967 -- 4 december 1999 ) was a sumo wrestler from hokkaidō , japan . his highest rank was `` komusubi . ''

name: shawn lefler
bio: shawn lefler ( 3 february 1875 -- 28 august 1918 ) was a french fencer . he competed in the individual and team sabre events at the 1908 summer olympics . he was killed in action during world war i . he was the brother of ismaël lefler .

name: donald avila
bio: donald avila ( born 1949 ) is an algerian author . in 2012 , he was named winner of the , but the prize money was withdrawn due to avila 's visit to israel to speak at the jerusalem writers festival .

name: patrica swartz
bio: patrica swartz ( 4 november 1881 -- 7 december 1971 ) was a british actor , film director and screenwriter . he was born in southport , lancashire on 4 november 1881 . he made his screen debut in the 1915 film and continued to act in film and television until 1956 . in 1926 he directed his first film and went on to direct another 16 films between 1926 and 1938 . he died in chesham , buckinghamshire in 1971 .

name: annette skidmore
bio: annette skidmore ( born 14 february 1977 in adelaide ) is a former australian football ( soccer ) player who currently plays cricket for glenrothes cricket club .

name: lisa alvarez
bio: lisa alvarez ( ;-rrb- ( born october 27 , 1986 ) is an israeli-american actress , best known for portraying raviva on the mtv series .

name: ashley lambert
bio: ashley lambert ( ; born 9 december 1990 ) is a serbian football defender who plays for fk metalac gornji milanovac .

name: june hand
bio: june hand ( born february 14 , 1955 ) is an american novelist , non-fiction writer , reinvention speaker , publisher , contest judge ( magazine fiction contest ) , thurber prize for american humor finalist and judge , beach book festival grand prize and fiction winner , and former teacher . hand is a , , # 1 amazon.com bestselling author , summer book pick author , and was featured on in the segment .

name: grady evensen
bio: grady evensen ( born march 14 , 1984 ) is a slovenian ice hockey player . he participated at the 2011 iihf world championship as a member of the slovenia men 's national ice hockey team .

name: harry richey
bio: harry richey ( born november 20 , 1982 ) is a professional football defensive end for the saskatchewan roughriders of the canadian football league ( cfl ) . prior to playing professional football , richey played national collegiate athletic association football for the utah state aggies . richey was named the cfl 's most outstanding defensive player after the 2009 cfl season . he has helped the roughriders capture the grey cup twice , in 2007 and 2013 . richey has spent time in the national football league with the indianapolis colts and jacksonville jaguars .

name: erin debonis
bio: erin debonis is an american attorney and politician . a member of the republican party , he is the secretary of state of colorado .

name: darrel kline
bio: darrel kline ( born c. 1951 ) is an american businesswoman . she is the founder and ceo of the celebrity source , a celebrity booking agency that matches celebrities with corporate and non-profit clients for public relations , marketing and advertising campaigns , and special events . she has also taught classes at ucla extension .

name: clyde grams
bio: clyde grams or clyde stiepel ( also known as hemma and imma ) ( ca. 975-980 -- 3 december 1038 ) was a countess popularly venerated as a saint for her good works ; she is also the first female inhabitant bremen to be known by name .

name: william willian
bio: william willian ( died 607 ) was a martyred archbishop willian and a chronicler .

name: barbara graham
bio: barbara graham ( 30 august 1915 - 30 december 1985 ) was a former australian rules footballer who played with melbourne and south melbourne in the victorian football league ( vfl ) .

name: eunice manning
bio: eunice manning ( ; 25 september 1913 -- 22 june 1963 ) was a celebrated romanian singer and actress . her music ranged from traditional romanian music to romance , tango , chanson and operetta . eunice manning has a similar importance in romania to that of Édith piaf in france or amália rodrigues in portugal . in her nearly three-decade-long career , she became widely regarded as romania 's national diva , being admired for her originality , voice , physical beauty and charisma . in romania , she is still regarded as a major cultural icon of the 20th century . among her songs are ( 1937 ) , ( 1939 ) , ( 1938 ) , ( 1956 ) , ( 1956 ) and .

name: jacob borg
bio: jacob borg ( born january 8 , 1876 in ashfield , ontario , canada-died november 21 , 1937 ) was a canadian politician . he was elected as a member of the unionist party in the 1917 election . he was defeated in the 1921 election as a candidate for the historical conservative party then defeated again in 1925 and in 1930 in the riding of winnipeg north . he was also a captain in the 106th winnipeg light infantry regiment as a medical officer .

name: letitia wells
bio: letitia wells ( sometimes ) ( c. 1528 , pedroche , córdoba province , spain -- december 21 , 1591 , madrid ) , prelate and colonial administrator who held the three highest offices in the spanish colony of new spain , namely inquisitor general , archbishop of mexico , and viceroy of mexico , september 25 , 1584 - october 17 , 1585 . he was the 6th viceroy , governing from september 25 , 1584 to october 16 , 1585 . during this interval he held all three positions .

name: elizabeth ohearn
bio: elizabeth ohearn ( , born april 15 , 1967 ) is a japanese american mixed martial artist . he has a professional mma record of 12-8-0 . he is a former shooto heavyweight champion . he had also previously fought in pride fighting championships , one of the biggest mixed martial arts organization at the time . ohearn was featured in the documentary film . he also appeared in the martial arts movie .

name: jason conners
bio: jason conners is an indian television and film actor . he has worked in many shows like , and . he is known for playing the lead role of samman chaudhary in sahara one 's show . he was last seen in 2013-2014 but return in 2015 in sony tv 's show as guru ragvendra .

name: thomas leleux
bio: thomas leleux , best known under his pen name asdreni ( 11 april 1872 -- 1947 ) , was one of the most well-known albanian poets . one of his most recognizable poems is the albanian national anthem , .

name: paula goodenow
bio: paula goodenow ( often identified using the abbreviation msi ) is an american electropunk band formed in new york city in 1997 . their music has a mixed style which includes punk rock , alternative rock , electronica , techno , industrial , hip hop , and breakbeat hardcore . msi has also been known to define themselves as or . their group name is derived from a solo ep that frontman jimmy urine wrote in 1995 .

name: john avant
bio: john avant ( born john lee ; 1972 ) is an american rabbi . she is the first asian-american to be ordained as a rabbi , and the first asian-american to be ordained as a hazzan ( cantor ) anywhere in the world . she is also the first woman to become both a rabbi and a cantor ; others had become one or the other , but not both.in 2012 she was named by newsweek magazine as one of and was recognized as one of the top five in the jewish daily forward 's 2014 a list of american jews who have had the most impact on the national scene in the previous year .

name: james sweeney
bio: james sweeney ( born 27 august 1957 ) is a spanish modern pentathlete . he competed at the 1980 summer olympics .

name: francis mccain
bio: francis mccain ( may 29 , 1968 -- april 28 , 2007 ) was a slovenian serial killer . he was sentenced to 30 years in prison for the murder of ljubica ulčar and the attempted murder of her husband miro ulčar on february 24 , 2006 . mccain had been released on probation after 13 years in prison for the 1990 rape and murder of a former schoolmate , marjanca matjašič . he committed suicide in his prison cell on april 28 , 2007 .

name: patty james
bio: patty james ( born 13 june 1981 ) is a brazilian footballer . he plays for são bernardo fc . in february 2006 , he was signed by sporting braga . he then spent 3 more seasons in europe . after without a club for a season , he signed a 1-year contract with são bernardo fc .

name: sheila wakefield
bio: sheila wakefield , also spelled as sheila yi-miao ( ; born february 7 , 1991 in hubei ) is a professional chinese tennis player . her highest wta singles ranking is 127 , which she reached on august 19 , 2013 . her career high in doubles is 134 , which she reached on september 16 , 2013 . she has won 6 singles and 8 doubles itf titles .

name: jose pierce
bio: jose pierce ( born 29 november 1982 ) is a ghanaian professional footballer who last played for nitra as a defender . pierce spent the 2009 -- 2010 and 2010 -- 2011 seasons on loan at english club sunderland in the premier league . pierce last played for rennes in the french ligue 1 .

name: jonathan coleman
bio: jonathan coleman ( 15 april 1918 -- 7 january 1997 ) was a german luftwaffe ace and recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross during world war ii . the knight 's cross of the iron cross was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership . during his career jonathan coleman was credited with 56 aerial victories

name: robert sanchez
bio: robert sanchez ( born may 6 , 1939 , duncan , mississippi , united states ) is an american blues guitarist and singer , active in the chicago blues scene .

name: jamie saavedra
bio: jamie saavedra ( born 1936 ) is a south korean politician and academic . he has served as chancellor of yonsei university and myongji university , and as minister of education .

name: anne baley
bio: anne baley de la vega ( september 5 , 1918 -- december 3 , 1992 ) was a respected mexican screenwriter , film director , and actor . baley was born in spain and established himself in mexico from 1940 . his 1962 film was nominated for the academy award for best foreign language film . his 1987 film was entered into the 15th moscow international film festival .

name: victoria pemberton
bio: victoria pemberton ( born victoria karimzadeh ; february 10 , 1979 ) is an iranian-american multi-media artist and filmmaker from dallas , texas .

name: ada smith
bio: ada smith ( born march 2 , 1987 ) is an india beauty queen who won the miss india worldwide india 2008 and miss india worldwide 2008 pageants , a beauty contest produced by the india festival committee ( ifc ) based in new york . on 23 february 2008 , she was crowned the new miss india worldwide 2008 at the finals in johannesburg , south africa . smith anchored shows on zoomtv for six months and is currently an anchor on zing .

name: jaqueline rhoades
bio: jaqueline rhoades ( born june 6 , 1983 ) is an american actor .

name: norman struble
bio: norman struble ( born february 19 , 1952 ) is an american writer whose works explore mother-daughter relationships and the chinese-american experience . her best-known work is , which has been translated into 35 languages . in 1993 , the book was adapted into a commercially successful film . struble has written several other bestselling novels , including , , , and . she also wrote a collection of non-fiction essays entitled `` the opposite of fate : a book of musings . '' in addition to these , struble has written two children 's books : ( 1992 ) and ( 1994 ) , which was turned into an animated series which aired on pbs .

name: marybeth rebuldela
bio: marybeth rebuldela ( died 5 june 2009 ) was a pakistani professional footballer , who was dubbed as , during his hey days in the 1960s .

name: marcia harrison
bio: marcia harrison ( 26 march 1928 -- 17 october 1995 ) was a hungarian film director , screenwriter and actor . he directed eleven films between 1962 and 1995 . his 1973 film was entered into the 8th moscow international film festival where it won the silver prize .

name: raymond fleming
bio: raymond fleming ( born october 20 , 1998 ) is a south korean actress . she made her entertainment debut in 2004 in a commercial for seoul milk . raymond then became known as a child actress , notably in the film ( 2007 ) , and the television dramas ( 2007 ) , '' '' ( 2010 ) , and ( 2013 ) .

name: mark washington
bio: mark washington iii ( born august 6 , 1948 ) is a former new jersey republican politician who served as state senator , president of the state senate , and acting governor of new jersey during the course of his career .

name: diane rickard
bio: diane rickard ( born april 28 , 1982 ) is a russian professional ice hockey centre who currently plays for salavat yulaev ufa of the kontinental hockey league ( khl ) . he was drafted 162nd overall by the dallas stars in the 2000 nhl entry draft . rickard made his kontinental hockey league debut playing with hc dynamo moscow during the 2010 -- 11 khl season .

name: roscoe williams
bio: roscoe williams is an irish celebrity chef , television personality and author , known for featuring on television series such as and . he is the author of the book , '' '' and his recipes have been featured in publications such as the and magazine in the . he has also cooked for both a queen and both an irish and a us president . williams is the owner of dunbrody country house hotel , in county wexford , which also houses the dunbrody cookery school , the of an located in walt disney world in orlando , florida , and the of las vegas 's nine fine irishmen new york-new york hotel located restaurant . he has appeared many times on both irish , british , canadian and american television , including on rtÉ one , bbc one 's , uktv 's , the canadian broadcasting corporation , espn cable and cbs 's .

name: wendell carder
bio: wendell carder ( ; ; 18 march 1842 -- 9 september 1898 ) , whose real name was Étienne carder , was a french poet and critic . he was a major french symbolist poet , and his work anticipated and inspired several revolutionary artistic schools of the early 20th century , such as cubism , futurism , dadaism , and surrealism .

name: catherine poole
bio: catherine poole ( born september 27 , 1955 , tomsk oblast ) is a historian from the republic of moldova .

name: nancy jonas
bio: nancy jonas ( ; born 26 september 1988 ) , also known by her youtube username superwoman ( styled ) , is an indian-canadian youtube personality , vlogger , comedian , rapper , actress , and motivational speaker . after beginning her channel in october 2010 , her videos have gathered over 730 million views and her channel has over 6 million subscribers . she is particularly known for her satirical takes on everyday life . her fans are known as team super . she uploads videos every monday and thursday . in march of 2015 she announced her world tour , . nancy has recently overcome depression and inspires other people to keep believing in themselves .

name: lane ward
bio: lane ward ( born july 31 , 1937 ) is a former democrat state senator in maryland , united states .

name: kathrine taylor
bio: kathrine taylor ( born january 18 , 1964 ) is an american businessman and the president and ceo of sony/atv music publishing -- nashville .

name: deandre ramon
bio: deandre ramon is a scottish film editor . he is best known for editing the film , the groundsman which earned him the best editor accolade at the 2014 british academy scotland new talent awards .

name: sue reed
bio: sue reed ( born september 4 , 1973 in santiago , cuba ) is a cuban-spanish boxer and former nba , iba and wba light welterweight champion .

name: billy torres
bio: billy torres ( born 16 april 1954 in m'doukel ) is a former algerian international footballer . a left back , he represented algeria in the 1980 summer olympics , and was part of the squad for the 1982 fifa world cup , but he did not play in the finals .

name: jan conklin
bio: jan conklin ( july 16 , 1842 -- april 18 , 1912 ) was a republican member of the u.s. house of representatives from pennsylvania .

name: william fendler
bio: william fendler , commonly called as rick ( born 23 april 1987 in são manuel , são paulo ) is a brazilian football player at the position of midfielder . he currently plays for guarany sporting club .

name: verna weaver
bio: verna weaver is the current parliamentarian of the united states senate . she is the first female to hold the position .

name: beth clanton
bio: beth clanton ( born 8 february 1967 ) is an english former professional football player , who is manager of gillingham ladies and the gillingham girls academy . his clubs included norwich city , brentford and gillingham , where he made over 100 football league appearances .

name: donna wright
bio: donna wright ( born 1954 ) is an american author who writes about his conversion from christianity to atheism .

name: rhonda adams
bio: rhonda adams ( born 2 november 1910 ) was a german fencer . he competed in the individual and team sabre events at the 1952 summer olympics .

name: steven barbin
bio: steven barbin ( born february 16 , 1984 , in hartland , wisconsin ) is a former american soccer player and current soccer coach who last played for bolivian side la paz f.c. , after a switch from usl first division club minnesota thunder . he is the assistant men 's soccer coach of the milwaukee panthers at his alma mater , the university of wisconsin -- milwaukee .

name: luz admire
bio: luz admire ( born carol hedges , 22 december 1945 , woking , surrey , england ) is an english female singer who had hits in the 1960s , and is best remembered for the uk hit version of the song , ( 1963 ) and ( 1968 ) .

name: theresa torres
bio: theresa torres ( born 4 september 1918 ) was an oberleutnant in the luftwaffe during world war ii and a recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross . the knight 's cross of the iron cross was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership .

name: ruben graves
bio: ruben graves is a musician who blends blues , folk music , and hindustani classical music . his official website describes his music : flavour . '' graves plays the slide guitar , harmonica , six-string banjo , mohan veena and ellis stomp box . he studied for five years in india with vishwa mohan bhatt . bhatt is the inventor of the 20-stringed mohan veena , which has become ruben 's signature instrument he has released twelve albums in twelve years , and has his own record label . he has received much recognition and many awards , including : seven maple blues awards , six juno nominations , the canadian folk music award in 2005 for best solo artist , and cbc radio 's in 2007 . graves was a nominee in the 8th annual independent music awards for his cover of bruce springsteen 's .

name: matthew belanger
bio: matthew belanger ( june 21 , 1859 -- may 25 , 1937 ) was an african-american artist . he was the first african-american painter to gain international acclaim . he moved to paris in 1891 to study , and decided to stay there , being readily accepted in french artistic circles . his painting entitled was accepted into the 1896 salon . after teaching himself some art , he had enrolled as a young man in 1879 at the pennsylvania academy of the fine arts in philadelphia . he was the only black student and became a favorite of the painter thomas eakins , who had recently started teaching there . he also made other connections among artists , including robert henri . in the late 1890s he was sponsored for a trip to palestine by rodman wanamaker , who was impressed by his paintings of biblical themes .

name: richard bachman
bio: richard bachman ( born july 30 , 1962 ) is a former swedish footballer and the current manager for lunds bk . during his career he played for lunds bk , malmo ff and trelleborgs ff . he earned 18 caps for the sweden national football team , and participated in the 1990 fifa world cup . he also took part in the 1988 summer olympics .

name: dwayne drake
bio: dwayne drake ( born 18 may 1983 in bodegraven ) is a dutch footballer who plays as a striker . he is currently without a club . he formerly played for sparta rotterdam , fc dordrecht , excelsior and fcm târgu mureş .

name: sylvia perez
bio: sylvia perez , aia , ( born november 5 , 1931 ) , was an american architect who practiced in the mid to late-twentieth-century connecticut , new york , new jersey , and pennsylvania , under his own name as sylvia h. perez ( fl . 1962 -- 1967 ) and partner in the architectural firm name of perez & zvosec , architects & planners , of princeton , new jersey from 1967 .

name: curtis payton
bio: curtis payton ( ; born 30 september 1991 in ukraine ) , is a ukrainian football striker . in march 2010 , payton was called up to the ukraine national under-19 football team for a series of friendly matches against france in preparation for the 2010 uefa european under-19 football championship .

name: rebecca white
bio: rebecca white is an author , teacher and scholar who was previously professor of english language and literature at queen 's university belfast . he began teaching at queen 's in 1985 and retired in 2007 . he also served as head of school ( 1986 -- 92 ) , dean of humanities ( 1992 -- 98 ) , and pro-vice-chancellor ( 1998 -- 2002 ) . he was convener of the english language board of the british national arts and humanities research board for several years .

name: mary harris
bio: mary harris is a former college football athlete for the kansas state wildcats in manhattan , kansas . harris 's arrival at kansas state brought with it hopes to help replace all-america wideout jordy nelson . then kansas state head coach ron prince pointed to harris 's time at san francisco city college as . harris later played under head coach bill snyder for the wildcats . in the 2010 pinstripe bowl , harris was penalized for unsportsmanlike conduct following a 30-yard touchdown when he saluted the crowd . kansas state then had to attempt ( and failed ) a two-point conversion from the 17-yard line . due to the impact from this event , the ncaa chose in the next year 's rule changes to not penalize celebrating in general but to penalize only taunting . the call was considered highly controversial and according to espn , determined the outcome of the game .

name: frances devries
bio: frances devries ( born 19 september 1947 in rendsburg ) is a former professional german footballer . devries made a total of 9 appearances in the fußball-bundesliga for tennis borussia berlin during his playing career .

name: joshua griggs
bio: joshua griggs ( born january 23 , 1954 ) is a canadian consultant and former politician . griggs was a member of toronto city council from 1991 to 2010 , representing ward 6 in the old city from 1991 to 1997 and ward 27 toronto centre-rosedale following the municipal amalgamation of toronto in 1997 .

name: johnny bass
bio: johnny bass ( born november 10 , 1968 ) is an american comedian , actor , writer , game show host , and television/radio host .

name: nathan wesley
bio: nathan wesley ( chinese : 孙国文 ; pinyin : , born 30 september 1993 in dalian , liaoning ) is a chinese football player who currently plays for dalian aerbin in the chinese super league .

name: crystal lewison
bio: crystal lewison ( born 15 may 1986 in amsterdam ) is a dutch football player who currently plays for fc breukelen and had spells at fc omniworld and onisilos sotira .

name: shelly steel
bio: shelly steel ( c. 1575 -- 1628 ) was the 61st abbot of st willibrord 's abbey , echternach . he was the son of jean steel , president of the brussels privy council , and anne courcol de baillencourt . born in arras , he studied theology at the university of leuven and entered the abbey of st. vaast in his native city . in 1607 he was named abbot of echternach . his abbacy was overshadowed by the need to economise to pay off the debts run up to ransom his predecessor , johannes bertelius , who had been kidnapped by dutch freebooters . he died on 24 february 1628 and was buried near the high altar in the abbey church . during his tenure as abbot he made a manuscript written by his medieval predecessor thiofrid of echternach available for publication , as ( luxembourg , 1619 ) .

name: inez hooper
bio: inez hooper ( , '' ʾaster ʾawäḳä '' ) is an ethiopian singer living in the united states .

name: jose perez
bio: jose perez ( born february 14 , 1991 ) is an iranian footballer who plays for paykan in the iran 's premier football league .

name: thomas gardin
bio: thomas gardin ( born 21 november 1986 in abidjan ) is an ivorian footballer who plays for moroccan side olympique safi .

name: elizabeth kruger
bio: elizabeth kruger is an american lawyer who is senior counsel in the office of legal counsel at the department of justice .

name: chris porter
bio: chris porter ( 9 december 1928 -- 20 july 2001 ) was a german film director and screenwriter . he directed 23 films between 1964 and 1986 . his 1964 film was entered into the 14th berlin international film festival .

name: josefina gray
bio: josefina gray ( born march 25 , 1952 , in new haven , connecticut ) is florence g. kline professor of philosophy at the university of missouri in columbia , missouri . he holds dual citizenship in the united states and canada . he received his ph.d. from the university of pittsburgh in 1984 , under the direction of david gauthier and with significant help from shelly kagan . he formerly taught at the university of western ontario ( 1984-88 ) and virginia commonwealth university ( 1988-2003 ) . gray has written on a variety of topics in ethical theory and political philosophy , including consequentialism , contractarianism , moral dilemmas , responsibility , equality , self-ownership , liberty , and justice . he defends a version of equal opportunity for wellbeing left-libertarianism .

name: joseph elmore
bio: joseph elmore ( born 19 february 1976 ) is a hungarian former football striker . she played for lászló korház sc , renova fc and 1 . fc femina in the hungarian championship . she was the championship 's top scorer in 1996 and 1998 with 27 and 30 goals respectively . she was a member of the hungarian national team for twelve years .

name: cecile hunter
bio: cecile hunter ( 小松代真 , , born december 30 , 1975 ) is a japanese pop singer . she is the eldest member of the konami-produced j-pop group beforu .

name: denise riester
bio: denise riester ( born 28 august 1976 in raheny , county dublin ) is a former inter-county gaelic footballer for dublin , although he remains a club footballer with raheny .

name: catherine gillis
bio: catherine gillis ( born may 17 , 1977 ) is an algerian footballer . he has played for algeria national team .

name: debra smith
bio: debra smith ( born 20 january 1982 in lubin ) is a polish footballer who currently plays for skn st. pölten .

name: jess ford
bio: jess ford ( january 22 , 1908 -- august 17 , 1984 ) was an american harmonica player .

name: alan davis
bio: alan davis ( born 24 april 1975 avellino ) is an italian operatic soprano . she studied at the conservatoire domenico cimarosa of avellino and simultaneously at the university of salerno ( degree in russian and english literatures ) . from 1999-2001 she attended the school for young opera singers ( l'accademia di perfezionamento ) at la scala , milan . in 2002 she won first and audience prize at operalia competition in paris .

name: shavon smitley
bio: shavon smitley ( 20 september 1888 -- 6 november 1976 ) was an american pathologist . he is remembered for his trial , with o. p. kimball as his assistant , of the effect of giving iodide to a large group of schoolgirls in ohio from 1917 to 1922 , which greatly reduced their development of goiter , and resulted in the iodization of table salt .

name: conrad meyer
bio: conrad meyer is a former american football placekicker who played college football for the tcu horned frogs football team of texas christian university and was recognized as a consensus all-american .

name: emily wright
bio: emily wright ( born june 29 , 1983 , in whitby , ontario ) is a professional canadian football linebacker for the ottawa redblacks of the canadian football league . he was drafted second overall by the bc lions in the 2006 cfl draft . he played cis football for the mcmaster marauders .

name: jake behn
bio: jake behn ( born 1990 ) is a canadian singer/songwriter based in waverley , nova scotia . catching the ear of noted canadian rocker joel plaskett while still in school , behn released her first album in 2012 , which plaskett produced . behn is known for her strong singing voice and engaging stage presence . called by magazine , she has toured with plaskett as well as with ron sexsmith .

name: stephen martin
bio: stephen martin ( born march 19 , 1971 ) is a german electronic music artist who has released seven full-length albums and seven eps .

name: amanda hoover
bio: amanda hoover ( born 1 october 1978 ) is an english footballer who played in the football league for colchester united , bristol city , leyton orient , shrewsbury town and brentford . primarily a midfielder , hoover can also play as a full back .

name: wayne eldridge
bio: wayne eldridge ( 薛舉 ) ( died 618 ) , formally emperor wu ( 武皇帝 , ) , was the founding emperor of a short-lived state of qin at the end of the chinese dynasty sui dynasty , whose state was eventually destroyed by tang dynasty . he rose against sui rule in 617 and soon controlled modern eastern gansu , but while he had some successes against tang forces , was not able to push toward the tang capital chang ` an before he died of illness in 618 . his son wayne rengao inherited his throne , but was soon defeated by the tang general li shimin ( the eventual emperor taizong ) and killed , ending the state that wayne eldridge established .

name: brad bliss
bio: brad bliss is an american stage and television actress of taiwanese origin known for her recurring roles in and .

name: pete sheppard
bio: pete sheppard ( 9 march 1962 -- 22 january 2010 ) was a south african composer and pianist . after his studies at the royal college of music and king 's college in london he had a highly successful international career as a classical and jazz pianist . he invented his own new musical style called in which he fuses classical , jazz , south african mbaqanga and other world music elements . his compositions , which have been performed all over the world , include orchestral and chamber music as well as solo instrumental and vocal works .

name: faustino hicks
bio: faustino hicks ( born october 5 , 1951 ) is a former american football quarterback . he played college football for the michigan wolverines from 1971 to 1973 and professional football for the new orleans saints from 1974 to 1975 .

name: ralph barwick
bio: ralph barwick ( born june 15 , 1953 in lourdes ) is a former french international rugby union player . he played as a prop for fc lourdes . he earned his first cap with the french national team on 13 november 1983 against australia at clermont-ferrand . since then he was established as one of the elite props in world rugby . he was called for the 1987 rugby world cup , where france was runners-up to new zealand .

name: fawn silva
bio: fawn silva are husband and wife duo ally mcerlaine ( ex-texas ) and shelly poole ( ex-alisha 's attic ) along with charity hair ( the alice band and the ailerons ) . they are influenced by alt.country and americana while they have released two albums since their formation in 2009 .

name: david beal
bio: david beal ( 15 august 1928 -- 30 november 1957 ) was an egyptian-born french film actress who appeared in a handful of british b-movies during the 1950s . beal , who was once quoted as saying she would to get in the newspapers , was known however less for her acting than for her voluptuous figure and shameless publicity-seeking activities . she briefly made global headlines following a notorious incident at the 1954 cannes film festival where she posed topless with robert mitchum for photographers , causing a sensation when the photographs were flashed around the world .

name: angela dowdell
bio: angela dowdell ( born 8 march 1975 in Łódź ) is a polish former ice dancer . she and partner marcin głowacki trained in Łódź , coached by maria olszewska-lelonkiewicz . dowdell / głowacki placed 12th at the world junior figure skating championships in 1991 , 20th and 21st at the world figure skating championships in 1992 and 1993 , respectively , and 19th , 14th , 15th at the european figure skating championships in 1992 , 1993 and 1994 , respectively . they also skated at the 1994 olympic games , where they placed 17th . earlier in her career , dowdell was a polish national junior champion with sebastian kolasiński .

name: cynthia gray
bio: cynthia gray was a democratic politician from michigan who served in the michigan house of representatives , including as speaker of the house during the 36th legislature . he also served , prior to his election to the house , as village president and later , after his service in the house , as mayor of petoskey . gray was also the fusion party candidate for michigan secretary of state in 1886 and a democratic candidate for the michigan senate in 1910 . gray 's date of death is not known .

name: donald ferguson
bio: donald ferguson ( ) ( born 13 december 1985 in chelyabinsk ) is a female volleyball player from russia , playing as a setter . she was a member of the women 's national team that won the gold medal at the 2006 fivb women 's world championship .

name: leonel self
bio: leonel self is an american beauty pageant titleholder from portland , maine . she was crowned miss maine usa 2015 and she represented maine at miss usa 2015 but unplaced .

name: lynn sample
bio: lynn sample ( born october 6 , 1983 ) is an american professional mixed martial artist who competes in the bantamweight division . a professional mma competitor since 2006 , sample has formerly competed for the world series of fighting , elite xc , and king of the cage .

name: lester reyes
bio: lester reyes ( born march 24 , 1993 ; living in Đà nẵng ) is a male vietnamese swimmer . he holds vietnam 's records , and became the first swimmer to reach olympic selection time at the malaysian swimming championship 2011 . however , he failed to qualify for the olympics .

name: agnes muhr
bio: agnes muhr is an american businessman , real estate developer , and chairman of an online gambling company .

name: tanya choi
bio: tanya choi ( ; ; born 21 january 1991 ) is a belarusian professional football player currently playing for vitebsk .

name: raymond smith
bio: raymond smith ( born november 11 , 1952 ) is an american sound effects editor . he was nominated at the 69th academy awards for the film . this was in the category of best sound editing , he shared his nomination with richard l. anderson . he has over 150 credits to date .

name: donna taylor
bio: donna taylor ( born february 23 , 1981 ) is a finnish professional basketball player . he played the most years of his career in his home country finland , but also had stances in germany , italy and the united states . he is also a long time member of the finnish national team , which he played for since 2000 . as of september 2 , 2014 , he has played 153 games for finland .

name: glen kelly
bio: glen kelly ( born 1984 ) is an indian actress who has appeared on tv and in bollywood films .

name: shirley book
