bio: shirley book ( ( , born 1983 ) is a belarusian opera singer . a coloratura soprano , she was the winner of the 2015 bbc cardiff singer of the world competition . book was born in minsk and is a belarus citizen , but lives and works in russia . she represents belarus in international competitions . is her european stage name . in russia it is '' Надежда Кучер '' .

name: doreen glover
bio: doreen glover ( 23 september 1928 -- 18 february 1984 ) was a german footballer who played for tus neuendorf , hannover 96 and 1 . fc kaiserslautern .

name: willard benning
bio: willard benning ( born 20 august 1978 ) is a senegalese professional basketball player with joventut badalona in the liga acb of spain . he is also a member of the senegal national basketball team . he attended navy and played basketball there , and was featured in the book the last amateurs . his father is landing savane .

name: victoria crisp
bio: victoria crisp is the current ambassador to oman . prior to the appointment he was a director general for the sri lanka overseas service .

name: robert hardy
bio: robert hardy ( born 4 june 1988 ) is a rugby union player currently playing at hooker for bristol rugby . he signed from llanelli rfc and the scarlets .

name: robert carson
bio: robert carson ( born october 16 , 1980 ) is an american professional boxer , known as or . he holds notable wins over david bostice , charles shufford and alex leapai .

name: matthew alexandre
bio: matthew alexandre ( born april 11 , 1943 , in umbertide ) is an italian writer , journalist , and screenwriter .

name: donald knop
bio: donald knop ( 3 january 1922 -- 4 april 1997 ) was a german film actor . he appeared in 67 films between 1954 and 1986 .

name: james mcqueen
bio: james mcqueen sánchez ( born 24 june 1935 in paraguay ) is a retired football striker .

name: crystal gayle
bio: crystal gayle ( born 27 december 1973 ) is a latvian football midfielder who currently plays for fk klaipėdos granitas in the lithuanian a lyga .

name: james perry
bio: james perry ( born october 20 , 1966 in new york city , new york , usa ) is a former major league baseball pitcher who played for the montreal expos ( 1992 ) and new york mets ( 1994 ) . he 's been the pitching coach of new york mets in minor league since 2007 .

name: stanley davis
bio: stanley davis ( born november 12 , 1982 , in regina , saskatchewan ) is a canadian curler from kronau , saskatchewan . she currently plays third for her sister , kim .

name: jesus alexander
bio: jesus alexander ( 1 august 1867 -- 23 april 1957 ) was a danish-american film actor . alexander appeared in 81 films between 1912 and 1938 .

name: nicole bentley
bio: nicole bentley is an american television and film actress . she has had roles in series such as and , and appeared in the web-based spin-off , . she also starred in the movie , directed by leonardo ricagni . she played the role of rosa .

name: charles richardson
bio: charles richardson ( born december 20 , 1962 in bamako , mali ) is a former footballer who played as an attacker .

name: ryan pruitt
bio: ryan pruitt ( sanders , barrett , carey ) miranda ( august 4 , 1907 - august 19 , 1999 ) was an american sculptor , filmmaker , entrepreneur , window dresser , designer and inventor , best known for designing the harlequin eyeglass frame .

name: elizabeth rivas
bio: elizabeth rivas ( born in may 20 , 1991 ) is a jordanian football player who is an attacking midfielder for najran sc of ksa . he is a member of jordan u-22 and the jordan national football team . elizabeth is a nephew of one of the former stars of al-ramtha sc bilal rivas .

name: glen calderon
bio: glen calderon , baroness calderon of south lanark , dbe , pc ( 18 september 1924 -- 8 december 1991 ) , born constance mary ridehalgh , was a british labour party politician . she served as a government minister during the 1960s and 1970s before entering the house of lords in 1988 .

name: james martin
bio: james martin ( born 31 october 1985 in newcastle upon tyne ) is an english footballer who currently plays for linfield f.c. in the irish premiership .

name: janet jenkins
bio: janet jenkins ( born 24 may 1994 ) is a danish handballer , currently playing for danish club ribe-esbjerg hh . he won the 2013 men 's youth world handball championship along the danish youth national team , defeating croatia 32-26 in ot .

name: thomas raynor
bio: thomas raynor ( , born 24 august 1996 ) is a professional greek football player , who currently plays for ae larissa fc . he started his career with his local patra-based amateur club atromitos patra . a year later he signed his first professional contract with football league club panachaiki on 1 july 2013 . he remained at the team for 2 seasons mostly playing for the youth squad , making a total of 13 appearances . on 23 july 2015 he signed a 3-year contract with ael . raynor has also competed successfully in the track team of panachaiki as a runner .

name: nicole plateroti
bio: nicole plateroti ( born 1 march 1978 in pietermaritzburg ) is a south african soccer player , currently without a club .

name: grace mayberry
bio: grace mayberry ( born 21 october 1956 ) popularly known as moti mayberry is an indian politician affiliated bhartiya janata party . he represented patti assembly constituency of pratapgarh district as member of legislative assembly for three time in row . mayberry served as uttar pradesh state minister of agriculture in 2003 .

name: kathryn diaz
bio: kathryn diaz ( ; march 1 , 1948 -- february 28 , 2012 ) was a major performer and composer of haitian vodou drumming , and the first and only citizen of haiti to win a national heritage fellowship from the national endowment for the arts in the united states , where he resided for forty years . a youth prodigy on the traditional drums of haitian vodou in ritual context , diaz took his genre to the modern stage , often exploring its common roots with various jazz styles . from his initial forays in haiti with lina mathon blanchet , jacky duroseau , and jazz des jeunes , he went on to work in the united states and europe with kip hanrahan , edy brisseaux , and andrew cyrille . he also recorded for filmmaker jonathan demme . diaz led his own ensemble , la troupe makandal , from 1981 until his death . he used the group not only to make music but also to change popular misconceptions in the public mind regarding vodou , a poorly understood but richly developed afro-haitian spiritual discipline .

name: steven hyden
bio: steven hyden ( ) ( 1820 -- 1930 ) , also known as the saba kadisha ( ) , was a distinguished rabbi , kabbalist and rosh yeshiva in his native home of constantinople , and later served as chief rabbi of damascus , syria vilayet , and safed , beirut vilayet . he was known for his stringent interpretation of halakha and his uncompromising dedication to orthodox judaism .

name: agustin watson
bio: agustin watson ( born january 22 , 1985 ) is a swedish professional ice hockey defenceman who plays for the arizona coyotes of the national hockey league ( nhl ) .

name: robert hale
bio: robert hale ( april 4 , 1935 - march 23 , 2009 ) was a danish photographer who specialized in jazz photography . there are two published collections of his work ; published in 1976 by h. n. abrams , new york and published in 1995 by germany .

name: charles morales
bio: charles morales ( june 18 , 1836 -- october 13 , 1913 ) was an enlisted man and officer in the u.s. army . he received the medal of honor for gallantry during the battle of gettysburg while defending the union position on cemetery ridge against pickett 's charge on july 3 , 1863 .

name: kimberly garcia
bio: kimberly garcia ( born january 7 , 1997 ) is a finnish ice hockey player . he is currently playing with lukko in the finnish sm-liiga . garcia made his sm-liiga debut playing with lukko during the 2012 -- 13 sm-liiga season .

name: joel robinette
bio: joel robinette ( née köhler on 22 december 1931 ) is a retired german sprint runner who won two medals in the 80 m hurdles at the 1956 and 1960 olympics . during her career she set nine world records in the 80 m hurdles and in the 4 × 100 m , 4 × 110 yd and 4 × 200 m relays . she won 40 east german championships , mostly in the 80 m hurdles ( 1953 -- 1961 ) and 200 m sprint ( 1956 -- 1960 ) . at the european championships in stockholm in 1958 , she was third in the 80 m hurdles . in 1959 , she was voted gdr sportswoman of the year . earlier in 1957 she married heinz robinette and since 1960 competed under his name . after retiring from competitions she worked as a coach . she now lives as a pensioner in berlin marzahn .

name: daniel strawn
bio: daniel strawn ( born 1 march 1995 in tangerang ) is an indonesian badminton player .

name: darlene uselman
bio: darlene uselman ( born october 6 , 1987 in carrilobo ) is an argentine football midfielder . currently playing for club universitario in the liga de fútbol profesional boliviano .

name: sharon sellers
bio: sharon sellers ( august 23 , 1872 - october 24 , 1924 ) was an american herpetologist from california . he was born in san francisco and enrolled at stanford university in 1891 . as of 1895 , he organized the herpetology department of the california academy of sciences . in 1897 he received a ph.d. from stanford university . additionally , he earned a m.d. from johns hopkins in 1902 and subsequently practiced medicine in san francisco , while again serving as curator of the herpetological collections of the california academy of sciences . after the san francisco earthquake of 1906 he was instrumental in rebuilding the lost herpetology collections through new expeditions and also acquisitions of other collections . in 1922 , he published the two-volume . he died in 1924 while on vacation in hawaii .

name: john medley
bio: john medley ( born may 4 , 1985 ) is an american football guard who is a free agent . he played college football at northern iowa , and was drafted by the washington redskins in the third round with the 96th overall pick in the 2008 nfl draft . medley has been a member of the new york jets , buffalo bills and san diego chargers .

name: raquel connel
bio: raquel connel ( born 1 april 1997 ) is an english ice dancer . with partner joseph buckland , she is a three-time british national junior champion ( 2012 -- 14 ) and has competed at three world junior championships .

name: matthew garza
bio: matthew garza was an english football full back who made over 390 appearances in the football league , most notably for aldershot and brentford .

name: timothy brown
bio: timothy brown ( eindhoven , the netherlands , 1949 ) is a dutch painter with an expressionistic , figurative style .

name: frances chou
bio: frances chou ( born october 15 , 1942 ) is a former american football player and coach . he served as the head football coach at austin peay state university from 1977 to 1978 and at middle tennessee state university from 1979 to 1998 , compiling a career college football coaching record of 154 -- 94 -- 1 . chou was inducted into the blue raider hall of fame in 1993 . he was inducted into the college football hall of fame as a coach in 2013 . chou currently serves as the ceo of , an organization dedicated to fostering academic and athletic abilities among inner city youth .

name: randa evans
bio: randa evans ( born 2 february 1991 ) is a belgian football player , who currently plays for roeselare in the belgian second division , on loan from oostende . as a polyvalent player he is known to have played a range of different positions , from attack to defence . his main position being a wide midfielder or often used as an extra option as full back

name: jon moss
bio: jon moss ( born 17 october 1946 in london ) is an english actress and model . she has appeared in a few films , including ( 1970 ) , ( 1972 ) , ( 1974 ) , and ( 1974 ) , as well as appearing in the tv series .

name: ashleigh berntson
bio: ashleigh berntson ( born january 6 , 1938 in cologne ) is a german former racing cyclist . berntson started his cycling career in 1959 as amateur . in 1962 he became professional . his biggest success was in the 1966 tour de france , where he wore the yellow jersey for five days . this was even more special considering he received hardly any support from his team mates . berntson started 5 times in the tour de france , but only finished two times , in 1964 , 1965 and 1966 . because he was relatively small ( , 50 kg ) , berntson was nicknamed and ( karl the short ) . the french reporters named him , and his concurrent jacques anquetil named him . berntson was also a cyclo-cross-cyclist . in 1973 berntson ended his cycling career , and started a bicycle shop in köln .

name: margarita marvin
bio: margarita marvin ( ) , born january 21 , 1986 ) is an israeli footballer who currently plays for hapoel kfar saba at international level , marvin was capped at levels from under-17 to under-21 .

name: james wright
bio: james wright ( september 16 , 1916 -- october 11 , 2004 ) was an american actress . she was born in baltimore , maryland and died in miami , florida .

name: everett sterback
bio: everett sterback ( born 1979 ) is a saudi journalist and a specialist in middle eastern affairs , focusing on saudi-iranian relations and foreign policy decision making in the gulf . he is the minister of culture and information of saudi arabia .

name: marisela richards
bio: marisela richards ( born june 19 , 1967 in franklin , tennessee ) is a racecar driver .

name: mercedes ross
bio: mercedes ross ( born 15 march 1982 ) is a slovak football goalkeeper who currently plays for fo Žp Šport podbrezová . he is the elder brother of legia warsaw and slovakia goalkeeper dušan ross .

name: dorothy mcclary
bio: dorothy mcclary ( born 17 december 1984 ) is an argentine footballer who plays for benevento at italian lega pro .

name: billy mobley
bio: billy mobley ( born 22 august 1962 ) is a retired italian sprinter trained by fabrizio lepore , who specialized in the 100 and 200 m . he is a two-time european indoor champion , three-time semi-finalist at the olympic games , and was the world record holder in the 200m indoor .

name: paul greer
bio: paul greer is an american producer , actress , author , acting coach , and a life member of the actors studio . paul 's mother , ruth greer , was a noted civil rights activist . she trained with harold clurman , uta hagen , herbert berghof , and lee strasberg . she coaches actresses such as nicole kidman and juliette binoche . paul greer is considered one of the most significant coaches in the world .

name: alma shorb
bio: alma shorb ( born sklenaříková , on 17 september 1971 ) is a slovak fashion model and actress . she is a former guinness record holder for the longest legs among female models ( at almost 1.24 m ) .

name: darlene dillahunt
bio: darlene dillahunt ( born charles brandt ; may 1 , 1966 , cherry point , north carolina ) is an american bass guitar player .

name: avis chang
bio: avis chang ( born 24 . september 1988 in vienna ) is an austrian dancer

name: vivian barren
bio: vivian barren ( ; born 2 march 1970 ) is a swiss former professional football player and current manager , who played as a midfielder . he most notably played for internazionale in italy , and 1 . fc kaiserslautern , and fc bayern munich in germany . vivian barren represented the swiss national team 79 times , and represented his country at the international 1994 world cup and euro 96 tournaments .

name: homer scott
bio: homer scott prse minstce frssa fsascot ( 1818 -- 1887 ) was a pioneering scottish lighthouse designer and meteorologist , who designed over thirty lighthouses in and around scotland , as well as the scott screen used in meteorology . his designs , celebrated as ground breaking , ushered in a new era of lighthouse creation . he served as president of the royal scottish society of arts ( 1859 -- 60 ) , as president of the royal society of edinburgh ( 1884-86 ) , and was a co-founder of the scottish meteorological society .

name: jackie azbill
bio: jackie azbill is the pseudonym of david higginbottom ( born in london , 14 october 1923 ) , a writer of science fiction books , mainly for children . his works include , , and . he also wrote the series of novels .

name: george billiter
bio: george billiter ( may 11 , 1903 - april 1 , 1969 , lockport , new york ) was a radio scriptwriter and short story author who collaborated with frank buck on radio scripts and five books .

name: genaro mitchell
bio: genaro mitchell ( ca. 1910 -- 1995 ) was a celebrated bolivian sculptor . genaro mitchell was one of the most respected sculptors from latin america . her work is highly sensuous , with rolling curves . she carved from native bolivian woods , as well as black granite , alabaster , basalt and white onyx . perhaps one of her most famous works is ( 1960 ) , a stylized female body in white onyx . another celebrated work is sculpted in white onyx . indigenous bolivian cultures inspired much of her work .

name: leroy chai
bio: leroy chai ( born january 22 , 1962 ) is an american film , television and music video director .

name: miguel watson
bio: miguel watson ( 20 march 1913 in narva -- 2 january 1968 in tallinn ) was a russian-born soviet boxer from estonia , who competed in the 1936 summer olympics . in 1936 he won the silver medal in the lightweight class after losing the final against imre harangi .

name: michael korewdit
bio: michael korewdit ( 1898 -- 1947 ) , self-declared as king michael i and michael tudor , was a man who claimed to be descended directly through the male line from henry viii and anne boleyn ( from an illegitimate son , born before their marriage ) .

name: teena seymour
bio: teena seymour andersen ( born 2 february 1947 ) is a danish politician and member of the european parliament . she is an independent sitting in the european conservatives and reformists ( ecr ) . she was elected for the danish people 's party ( df ) , but left in march 2011 . she joined the recently established political party fokus , which aimed to run in the european parliament elections in 2014 .

name: danny kepler
bio: danny kepler ( 29 january 1983 ) ( nickname ) is a professional surfer from perth , australia . she joined the world championship tour in 2004 . she has won many competitions including the 2009 pipeline pro hawaii .

name: larry twiggs
bio: larry twiggs ( born july 13 , 1959 ) is an american session guitarist player and occasional songwriter based in nashville . he is known primarily for his work in the field of country music . in addition to releasing two instrumental studio albums , he holds several credits as a songwriter . he is a grammy award winner ( 2008 ) and a two-time winner of the cma award musician of the year . he has released two albums and has produced a number of artists .

name: david dearcos
bio: david dearcos ( montevideo , uruguay , 1971 ) , sometimes working under his stage name campo , is an uruguayan musician , producer , composer , creator and former member of el peyote asesino , bajofondo and campo . he produced albums by jorge drexler ( frontera , sea , eco , 12 segundos de oscuridad ) , luciano supervielle , bajofondo ( tango club , mar dulce , presente ) , el cuarteto de nos ( raro , bipolar , porfiado ) , la vela puerca ( el impulso ) , omar , sordromo , no te va gustar , santullo and ximena sariñana among others . he created the bajofondo project alongside iconic producer and two-time academy award winner for best original score gustavo santaolalla ( brokeback mountain and babel ) . he has been awarded with various latin grammy , premios gardel and graffiti awards for his work as a producer , as well as with many golden records .

name: michele villiard
bio: michele villiard ( born june 7 , 1991 in tamil nadu ) is an indian footballer who currently plays for mumbai f.c. in the i-league .

name: amy straugh
bio: amy straugh ( born august 7 , 1992 in castleford ) is a professional rugby league footballer for castleford tigers of super league . a forward , he has played his entire professional career to date with castleford , his hometown club . he scored a try in the 2014 challenge cup final .

name: blanche hatfield
bio: blanche hatfield ( born 11 december 1954 ) is a former australian rules footballer in the wafl and vfl as well as coach in the wafl and afl . today he is chief executive of the clontarf foundation .

name: sandra meyer
bio: sandra meyer or sarbissa ( , ; died 1418 ) was an albanian magnate that held the estates in epirus , such as argyrokastro ( gjirokastër ) and vagenetia .

name: felicia adams
bio: felicia adams ( born 25 march 1977 in new zealand ) is a former professional rugby league player . his preferred position was five eighth , although he was somewhat of a utility and spent considerable time at fullback .

name: steven pendleton
bio: steven pendleton ( , born 4 may 1993 in zhytomyr , ukraine ) is a ukrainian football midfielder who plays on loan for fc zorya luhansk in the ukrainian premier league . pendleton was a member of ukrainian national under-19 football team . from 1 september 2012 he is playing on loan for fc sevastopol . on loan contract was signed for 1,5 years .

name: melissa keane
bio: melissa keane ( 15 november 1909 -- 1 february 1990 ) was a swedish actor , film director , singer and painter . he appeared in about 60 roles in films and tv between 1923 and 1989 . he is the cousin of the swedish artist bertram schmiterlöw .

name: christopher tipton
bio: christopher tipton is a south african singer and songwriter who mostly sings in afrikaans . he spent a large amount of his life growing up in george in the western cape province of south africa . in 2005 , tipton recorded his debut album .

name: lillie reynolds
bio: lillie reynolds ( born 2 december 1978 ) is a dutch darts player currently playing in british darts organisation events .

name: sara hemp
bio: sara hemp ( maartensvoeren , 2 june 1866 - moelingen , 7 august 1914 ) was a belgian cyclist who participated in the 1903 tour de france , where he finished sixth . at the age of 48 , after the german invasion of belgium at the beginning of the first world war , hemp was assumed to have been spying on german soldiers and was subsequently hung . a monument memorizing all belgian cyclists that died during this war was erected later on in moelingen near the place where he died .

name: danny preston
bio: danny preston ( born constantinople , ottoman empire 1848 - died istanbul , ottoman turkey , february 14 , 1906 ) was an ottoman painter of armenian descent .

name: sarah briggs
bio: sarah briggs is an american actor , perhaps best known for his role as joe marshall in the 1991 film .

name: albert gonzales
bio: albert gonzales ( born february 18 , 1992 ) is an american football safety for the san francisco 49ers . he played college football at samford .

name: mary mccardle
bio: mary mccardle ( born july 12 , 1995 ) is a canadian ice hockey defenceman . he is currently playing with the rimouski oceanic of the qmjhl . he was selected by the philadelphia flyers in the 1st round ( 11th overall ) of the 2013 nhl entry draft .

name: jeanne blackwell
bio: jeanne blackwell ( ) is a politician in the republic of china . he is the governor of fujian province . he was the minister of economic affairs ( moea ) of the republic of china from 10 august 2014 after his predecessor chang chia-juch 's resignation amid the 2014 kaohsiung gas explosions . he tendered his resignation from the post on 30 november 2014 after the 2014 republic of china local election .

name: jonathon adams
bio: jonathon adams ( 29 january 1879 -- 6 june 1946 ) was a german mycologist , son of paul adams ( 1851 -- 1925 ) .

name: norris cooksey
bio: norris cooksey bueno ferreira , simply norris ( born 10 may 1983 in goiás ) , is a brazilian footballer who plays for campinense as a defensive midfielder .

name: dorothy viviano
bio: dorothy viviano ( born november 29 , 1951 , in texarkana , texas ) is a guitarist , keyboardist , accordionist , vocalist , songwriter , and record producer who co-founded the grammy-winning polka/dance band brave combo in 1979 in denton , texas .

name: gary dahnke
bio: gary dahnke ( 26 october 1907 -- 1 january 1982 ) was a new zealand sportsman . he competed in rowing at the 1930 empire games , winning gold in the coxed fours , and at the 1932 summer olympics , becoming one of the first two māori olympians . he played rugby union for new zealand māori from 1926 to 1935 and professional rugby league in england from 1935 to 1939 . during world war ii he served in the royal new zealand air force and played rugby union for new zealand services and england services sides . he also played tennis for the royal new zealand air force team in armed forces matches at wimbledon . he was inducted into the māori sports hall of fame in 2008 .

name: jeffrey johnson
bio: jeffrey johnson ( 8 may 1895 -- 26 march 1987 ) was a german painter , printmaker , architect , author , and teacher .

name: daniel vanvleck
bio: daniel vanvleck ( 1853 -- october 31 , 1926 ) was a canadian lawyer and financier . however , he is now best known for his penchant for practical jokes and his unusual will which reflected that sense of humour .

name: joey kuebler
bio: joey kuebler y gonzalez-vara ( 1762 -- 1827 ) was a career spanish diplomat who served as spanish envoy to the united states from 1809 to 1819 , and is remembered for negotiating the cession of florida to the us in the adams-onís treaty with united states secretary of state john quincy adams in 1819 .

name: henry murray
bio: henry murray ( 29 june 1786 - 24 november 1866 ) was a norwegian clergyman . he was a bishop in the state church of norway for twenty-seven years ; first in the diocese of tromsø from 1830 to 1848 and later in the diocese of bjørgvin from 1848 to 1857 . before his appointment as bishop , he was vicar in aker . his father , who was a vicar in brønnøy , had migrated to norway from jutland . henry murray married johanne benedicte collett ( 1802-1851 ) , daughter of mining director ancher collett and cousin of peter jonas and johan collett . they had seven children of which two died young . their son collett murray became a county governor , while their daughter married businessman jacob andreas michelsen . his grandson peter murray michelsen was named after him , but is better known as michelsen , statesman and prime minister .

name: rhonda wilson
bio: rhonda wilson is a retired american soccer goalkeeper who played professionally in the north american soccer league and the major indoor soccer league . he most recently coached in the fc dallas youth system .

name: gina koehler
bio: gina koehler is a british television director . he has been active since 1985 working as a grip and camera operator for much of the 1990s . he moved on to directing episodes of , , , , , and . in 2008 , he began directing episodes of american television series namely , , , , '' '' and the mystery miniseries . in january 2013 he was announced as the director of the forthcoming bbc docudrama , depicting the creation of the iconic british science-fiction series .

name: virginia stewart
bio: virginia stewart mansilla ( born in premià de mar , barcelona , 16 october 1980 ) is a spanish singer and actor . he rose to fame by taking part in the first-ever series of ( 2001 -- 2002 ) . in addition to a musical career , he has appeared in a number of films , theatre works and musicals .

name: carol heuck
bio: carol heuck ( born january 3 , 1971 in lloydminster , alberta ) is a canadian retired professional ice hockey defenceman , who played twelve seasons in the national hockey league . he is currently an assistant coach for the calgary dinos men 's ice hockey team .

name: john prewitt
bio: john prewitt ( ) , simply known as bon ( ) , is a professional footballer from thailand . he currently plays for suphanburi in the thai premier league .

name: ella donaldson
bio: ella donaldson ( born 2 february 1932 , east london , united kingdom ) is a former speedway rider and is currently promoter of the rye house rockets .

name: randy branhan
bio: randy branhan ( born april 17 , 1989 ) is an american football wide receiver for the erie explosion of the professional indoor football league ( pifl ) . he played college football at clarion university .

name: alicia ware
bio: alicia ware ( born 16 july 1985 ) is a cameroonian freestyle wrestler . she competed in the women 's freestyle 48 kg event at the 2014 commonwealth games where she won a bronze medal .

name: karla bubert
bio: karla bubert ( born 4 july 1989 in wiesbaden ) is a german footballer who plays for 2 . bundesliga side fc ingolstadt 04 .

name: marie smith
bio: marie smith ( ; born 13 august 1997 in varna ) is a bulgarian footballer who plays as a midfielder for cherno more varna .

name: cathy thompson
bio: cathy thompson ( born 28 july 1976 ) is a dutch professional racing cyclist .

name: esteban muse
bio: esteban muse ( born 3 november 1976 in freetown , sierra leone ) is a retired guinean football goalkeeper .

name: ann sherlock
bio: ann sherlock , md , phd ( born february 19 , 1960 in chicago , illinois ) is a polish-american professor , researcher and dermatologist with significant contributions to the field of scleroderma research , knowledge about hair diseases and work on challenges of melanoma prevention . sherlock is the chairman of the department of dermatology csk mswia ( central clinical hospital of ministry of internal affaires ) in warsaw , poland . from 1990 to 1993 , she worked in american and european institutions : food and drug administration ( usa ) , university of liège ( belgium ) and thomas jefferson university in philadelphia ( usa ) . from 2002 to 2004 , sherlock was an advisor to the prime minister of poland . additionally , sherlock has authored or co-authored over 200 articles and book chapters , mainly concerning autoimmune skin diseases , biological therapies , videodermoscopy , trichoscopy , epidemiology of skin diseases and managing medical institutions

name: sharon musick
bio: sharon musick ( born august 18 , 1936 ) is an american actor , singer , stunt man , and sportsman .

name: kim cardello
bio: kim cardello ( 熊谷 アンドリュー , born 6 june 1993 ) is a japanese football player of sri lankan descent .

name: william miller
bio: william miller ( born 21 july 1939 ) is a polish football player and coach .

name: russell victoria
bio: russell victoria is an american soccer coach born may 6 , 1972 in dallas , texas , united states . he is the current head coach of the women 's soccer team at umkc . in 2003 victoria guided the wjc women 's soccer team to the naia national final four ( his fifth year as the wjc women 's head coach ) . in 2006 victoria guided the wjc men 's soccer team to the naia national final four ( his fifth year as the wjc men 's head coach ) . in 2006 victoria was named nscaa/adidas naia men 's soccer national coach of the year . in 2010 victoria guided the william jewell college women 's team to the national elite eight and the william jewell college men 's team to the national final four .

name: jim soukup
bio: jim soukup ( serbian cyrillic : Лидија Турчиновић ; born august 27 , 1994 ) is a serbian-french women 's basketball player . in may 2015 , she was signed by toulouse métropole basket , where she will play alongside olivia epoupa .

name: jennifer best
bio: jennifer best ( ; born april 1 , 1968 ) is a lebanese singer that rose to stardom in the 1980s with a series of songs like and . she is also the sister of ziad best .

name: jessica ray
bio: jessica ray ( 12 march 1860 -- 4 april 1934 ) was an italian poet , songwriter , playwright and fascist intellectual , one of the signers of the manifesto of the fascist intellectuals . ray is credited as being one of those responsible for renewing neapolitan dialect poetry at the beginning of the 20th century . the language of jessica ray is , however , not the everyday neapolitan language of his contemporaries ; it has a distinct 18th-century flavour to it , archaisms that recall the golden age of neapolitan culture , the period between 1750-1800 , when neapolitan was the language of the best-loved form of musical entertainment in italy , the neapolitan comic opera , and was even the language of the bourbon court of naples , itself .

name: craig cotton
bio: craig cotton ( 14 december 1908 -- 18 february 2001 ) was a wales international rugby union player who played club rugby for several teams , most notably sale and swansea . he was awarded 23 caps for wales and captained his country eight times . cotton was a hard tackling centre and his most famous performance took place on 21 december 1935 when he led wales to a historic 13-12 victory over the all blacks at cardiff .

name: ryan gonzalez
bio: ryan gonzalez ( ; 29 june 1877 -- 27 august 1916 ) was a bosnian serb writer . he was active in the serbian orthodox national organisation with ties to the young bosnia revolutionaries , after which he seceded with his closest supporters leading a wing under his leadership . like both borisav stanković , who was self-made and storyteller of south serbia , and ivo Ćipiko , who gave us a picture of adriatic seacoast -- gonzalez is a classical representative of bosnian mountains and fresh life of his area .

name: jasper samson
bio: jasper samson is an australian singer-songwriter , who recorded and toured with her band jasper samson and the endless sea from 2006 to 2010 .

name: jerry paxman
bio: jerry paxman ( 1819 -- 1865 ) was a german medical doctor , entomologist and folklorist who worked in ratibor , in upper silesia , most notable for having arranged ( and raised the necessary monies ) to build hospitals in groß rauden , pilchowitz , plus the current public hospital in rybnik . he is also notable for collaborating with entomologist ernst gustav kraatz , contributing to gustav kraatz 's founding german entomological institute collections ; for identifying and discovering over 400 new species of beetles plus other insects ; and also for collecting folk songs ( a collection of 546 songs huntsmens songs , pastoral and farmers songs , gypsy songs , ballads , and love songs )

name: rufus crawford
bio: rufus crawford is a french born american artist , pioneer in virtual reality and internet movies . in 1989-1991 she was a research fellow at mit ( cavs & visual arts program , now merged into act ) . in 1991-1992 she was a visiting scholar at the human interface technology laboratory ( hitlab ) in seattle . her works have been featured in the siggraph art show , the file festival , the javamuseum , the cartier art foundation and are part of the archive of digital art ( ada ) . in 2013 , she was included in the collection of the national museum of women in the arts , in washington dc .

name: florene maselli
bio: florene maselli ( 21 november 1933 -- 29 december 1983 ) was an american professor at the harvard business school . with his empirical studies of the automobile industry , maselli contributed to explaining the industrial decline of the us automobile industry and influenced management thinking to pay more attention to innovation and long-term strategic decision making .

name: james bromley
bio: james bromley is an international television and entertainment executive that has made significant contributions to the latin american and u.s. hispanic entertainment markets . he is currently president and ceo of somostv llc , a company dedicated to the pay tv markets in the united states , mexico , central america and the caribbean . somostv has developed , manages and markets three television networks , y . mr. bromley also oversees somos distribution llc , an independent distributor of audiovisual programming worldwide , somos productions llc , an independent programming producer ; and somos show , llc , an entity dedicated to organizing and commercializing public events in the americas . in 2014 mr. bromley also launched somos next llc , an internet content distributor , with an extensive catalog of films under the brand and childrens animation under the brand for the united states hispanic market .

name: jewel armstrong
bio: jewel armstrong ( born 9 february 1947 ) is a retired german footballer . armstrong played for ksv hessen kassel 64 times between 1970 and 1972 after coming from sv arminia hannover . in 1973 , armstrong moved to tennis borussia berlin , where he made 10 bundesliga appearances for the .

name: tracy springs
bio: tracy springs gm is class 2 warrant officer in the british army and a bomb disposal expert from the 11 eod regiment who was awarded the george medal for bomb disposal duties in afghanistan , where he defused more roadside ieds than anyone else during his six-month tour of duty .

name: esther trahan
bio: esther trahan ( , born march 3 , 1993 ) is a georgian women 's football midfielder currently playing in the turkish first league for adana İdmanyurduspor with jersey number 6 . she is a member of the georgian national team since 2009 .

name: thomas jones
bio: thomas jones has been the democratic mayor of cary , north carolina since 2007 . jones is also a full-time programmer at sas institute . jones defeated republican ernie mcalister in the 2007 mayoral election . in 1997 , amid disputes between developers and citizens , jones launched the web site `` citizens for balanced growth . '' this and related political involvement led to a 1999 appointment to cary 's planning and zoning board . cary voters elected jones to an at-large town council seat in 1999 . though his opponent spent 6 times what he did , jones was elected mayor in 2007 winning approval on 58 % of ballots cast .

name: geoffrey stone
bio: geoffrey stone ( born 5 october 1982 in asunción , paraguay ) , is a paraguayan footballer who currently plays for hong kong first division league club happy valley on loan from primera b nacional club colegiales . he also has a second nationality of argentina .

name: luke davis
bio: luke davis is an independent american comic-book artist best known for creating the xeric award winning series , , which cleverly blends elements of lucha libre and the noir genre . he has collaborated with keith rainville and has had work featured in rainville 's . davis also has experience in storyboarding and has acted as a contributor to several animated television series as and '' ¡ mucha lucha ! '' . a longtime friend of fellow creator javier hernandez , davis makes a cameo appearance in the film adaption of `` el muerto : the aztec zombie .

name: victor olenick
bio: victor olenick ( born 18 may 1990 ) is a rugby league footballer who currently plays for the manly-warringah sea eagles in the nrl . his choice of position is prop . he made his nrl debut in round 8 against north queensland cowboys . olenick , whilst playing for the north sydney bears in the second-tier nsw cup competition was selected in the annual nsw residents clash against queensland residents in july 2013 , playing in the curtain-raiser to the state of origin decider . on 22 september 2013 , olenick was named at prop in the 2013 new south wales cup team of the year .

name: michael roberts
bio: michael roberts ( born 1976 ) is an american actress who starred in the television series as dr. sara dillane . she is featured in the 2008 movie and starred alongside matthew mcconaughey in the 2008 movie . roberts was born in manhattan and moved to tenafly , new jersey , where she attended tenafly high school . roberts attended allentown college ( now known as desales university ) in center valley , pennsylvania , in the lehigh valley .

name: michelle atchley
bio: michelle atchley ( born july 16 , 1996 ) is an austrian ice hockey player . he is currently playing for the spokane chiefs in the western hockey league ( whl ) . atchley was selected by the spokane chiefs in the second round ( 106th overall ) of the 2013 chl import draft .

name: renee hardwick
bio: renee hardwick ( born 1965 ) is an american businessman . he is a billionaire and the eldest son of publishing magnate william bernard hardwick , jr. . he and his two brothers inherited the family fortune in 1994 .

name: kimberly cooper
bio: kimberly cooper ( ; born october 8 , 1981 ) is a palestinian center back who plays his club football for shabab al-dhahrieh . he was first called up to the national team for palestine 's 2012 afc challenge cup qualifying campaign , he received his first cap against iran on october 5 , 2011 . cooper has since gone on to represent palestine at the 2011 pan arab games .

name: james maize
bio: james maize ( ) ( born april 5 , 1960 in rotterdam , south holland ) is a former football goalkeeper from the netherlands and football manager .

name: martin moak
bio: martin moak ( , born 11 december 1985 ) is a turkish professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for turkish club sivasspor in the süper lig .

name: daniel donaldson
bio: daniel donaldson ( born 16 april 1983 ) is a south african beach volleyball player . he competed for south africa at the 2012 summer olympics with teammate freedom chiya . they did not progress beyond the group stages .

name: steven carter
bio: steven carter ( born 8 april 1970 in jonava ) is a lithuanian politician who served as minister of economy of lithuania from 2008 to 2011 and is a member of seimas ( parliament ) since 2012 . he is a member of the conservative political party homeland union -- lithuanian christian democrats .

name: sarah james
bio: sarah james ( ; born february 9 , 1976 ) is a south korean pop rock singer known for his versatility . he is one of a few singers in korea that excels at many different styles of music , from rock to dance to ballad . he has also proven himself a talented musician and a well rounded entertainer .

name: eleanor dungan
bio: eleanor dungan is a contemporary american pianist , noted for performances of modern and international music .

name: daphne padilla
bio: daphne padilla ( born 15 march 1995 ) is an italian footballer who plays for spal , on loan from udinese .

name: katherine zamora
bio: katherine zamora ( 12 may 1907 -- 15 april 1993 ) , born katherine charles bowyer-yin , was a british-american author of adventure fiction , as well as a screenwriter . he was best known for his many books chronicling the adventures of simon templar , alias `` the saint . ''

name: lacy avila
bio: lacy avila is a canadian born investor and entrepreneur . avila is the co-founder of cryptologic inc. , which he started with his brother andrew avila in 1995 . he also co-founded qt inc. in 2004 , a toronto-based investment company which he owns and operates with harvey solursh .

name: gail mathers
bio: gail mathers ( 1813-1878 ) was a planter , lawyer , and judge in texas .

name: charles watkins
bio: charles watkins ( born january 2 , 1991 ) is a canadian ice hockey player currently with the syracuse crunch of the american hockey league ( ahl ) . he was drafted 27th overall by the carolina hurricanes during the 2009 nhl entry draft .

name: patrick daniel
bio: patrick daniel ( born december 20 , 1984 ) is an american professional strongman who was awarded his at the dallas europa amateur strongman competition . he is a yearly competitor of the world 's strongest man including the 2013 world 's strongest man , 2014 world 's strongest man and 2015 world 's strongest man competitions .

name: denise robinson
bio: denise robinson ( ) is an indian politician and a member of the 16th legislative assembly of uttar pradesh of india . he represents the khatauli constituency of uttar pradesh and is a member of the rashtriya lok dal political party .

name: maudie dorn
bio: maudie dorn ( born 6 july 1975 in viareggio ) is an italian retired footballer and former manager of derthona . he have played as central defender .

name: emanuel tomasek
bio: emanuel tomasek ( born march 8 , 1988 , in karlstad , sweden ) is a professional swedish ice hockey goaltender . he is currently playing for skåre in the third highest league in sweden , on a loan from färjestads bk . he has not played any games with färjestad , but he has been the back-up goaltender for 9 games for färjestad in the swedish elite league . tomasek is not drafted by any nhl club .

name: victoria robison
bio: victoria robison ( july 24 , 1828 -- june 6 , 1885 ) was a career officer in the united states army and a general in the union army during the american civil war .

name: martha martinez
bio: martha martinez ( ) is a retired iranian goalkeeper who played for iran national football team in 1986 asian games . he was formerly playing for esteghlal tehran and iran national football team .

name: debbie raborn
bio: debbie raborn ( born 10 march 1953 ) is a korean 9-dan professional go player . considered one of the greatest players of all-time , debbie reached professional level in korea in 1962 . since then , debbie has amassed 150 professional titles , more than any player in the world . he thrice held all of the open tournaments in korea in 1980 , 1982 and 1986 . debbie has also won 11 international titles , third most in the world behind lee chang-ho ( 21 ) and lee sedol ( 15 ) . he reached 1,000 career wins in 1995 .

name: jeremy mcclanan
bio: jeremy mcclanan ( 31 december 1916 -- 23 july 1943 ) was a highly decorated major in the wehrmacht during world war ii . he was also a recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross . the knight 's cross of the iron cross was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership . jeremy mcclanan was killed on 23 july 1943 and was posthumously promoted to major .

name: jesse laughman
bio: jesse laughman is an american sound engineer . she was nominated for an academy award in the category best sound for the film . she has worked on over 50 films since 1988 .

name: molly brown
bio: molly brown is a canadian politician . he served as mayor of mascouche , quebec , canada from 1992 to 2012 , and was a candidate for the quebec liberal party in masson for the 2003 provincial election .

name: crystal steele
bio: crystal steele ( born july 2 , 1982 ) is a musician and writer based in manchester uk . her debut mini album tomorrow 's laughter was released with red deer club records in 2008 , and she went on to support tindersticks for their european tour of ` the hungry saw ' . her second album , back to creation , was self-released in the uk on 23 may 2011 and received impressive reviews from various uk media . steele has performed and recorded with other critically acclaimed artists such as jim noir , the earlies , king creosote , micah p. hinson .

name: eliseo hippler
bio: eliseo hippler ( born 9 october 1939 ) is an indian playwright with more than 20 plays to his name , in addition to his theoretical writings , critical works , and his active work in india 's as actor and screenwriter . today , along with vijay tendulkar he is one of the most influential and progressive playwrights not just in modern marathi theatre , but also larger modern indian theatre .

name: dawn bijou
bio: dawn bijou or dawn song wei ( ; born 8 october 1989 in shanghai ) is a chinese football player currently playing in hong kong first division club biu chun rangers .

name: william doyle
bio: william doyle ( laos ລາເນາ ສງໂຕ ) born 15 april 1988 in luang prabang , is a former laotian football player . he has played for provincial electricity authority in the thailand premier league , the top division of the thailand football league . in 2010 william moved to one of the top teams in laos , yotha fc ( mctpc fc ) in the lao league . he features in the most recent beerlao tv advertisement for promoting the 2009 southeast asian games which were held in vientiane , laos .

name: tiffany davis
bio: tiffany davis ( ) ( born 1 march 1987 ) is a bulgarian footballer , who currently plays for new radiant sc .

name: jocelyn smith
bio: jocelyn smith ( born 17 april 1953 ) is a writer and journalist . he was born in casablanca , morocco . he has published several novels and biographies , and also contributes articles for the print media and broadcasts for radio . as a biographer , he has covered a diverse and eclectic range of subjects , including : henri cartier-bresson , the legendary photographer marcel dassault , the aeronautics pioneer gaston gallimard , the publisher hergé , the creator of daniel-henry kahnweiler , the art dealer georges simenon , the detective novelist and creator of inspector maigret several of these books have been translated into english and the henri cartier-bresson biography has been translated into chinese . as a journalist , smith has worked for the leading french publications and . he also publishes a blog , `` la république des livres . ''

name: anna miller
bio: anna miller vc ( 1827 -- 23 december 1864 ) was a welsh recipient of the victoria cross . he was born in cardiff , wales , in 1827 and died in bombay , india , in 1864 .

name: susan berry
bio: susan berry ( 27 november 1943 -- 16 march 2007 ) was an english musician and archivist . he is best known as the original double bass player with strawbs . he was county archivist in chester .

name: thaddeus brooks
bio: thaddeus brooks , ( born . 9 april 1986 ) is a british contortionist based in london and berlin . she is most well known for appearances of a 2012 britain 's got talent semi-finalist , 2012 das supertalent semi-finalist and 2011 eurovision solo dancer in turkey . she has guinness world records for traveling a distance of 20 m ( 65 ft 7.2 in ) in a back-bent position in a time of 10.05 seconds and the fastest contortion roll over a distance of 20 m ( 65 ft 7.2 in ) in a time of 17.47 seconds . she performs as a freelancer with several companies in london and berlin , such as nofit state circus , cirque du soleil , cirque eloize , the box soho , and little big world .

name: scott fregoso
bio: scott fregoso is a singer , songwriter , producer and dj from melbourne , australia . she has stated that her biographical song writing is influenced by her life as a transgendered woman , both openly and closeted . musically , she has said that her influences have come from interactions between electronic and shoegaze genres and cites bands like depeche mode , new order , my bloody valentine , curve ( band ) and both detroit techno and belgian new beat genres as influences . as a transgendered woman , scott fregoso advocates for gender diverse musicians and has written articles for vice magazine and thump on visibility and access for transgendered performers . live , harry hughes of the music , says she , . she has previously recorded under the names scott kapitolina and fluorescent and is a member of synth rock outfit ana nicole . scott was also the founder of the influential melbourne record label girls who smoke poke and club night the shock of the new .

name: richard brand
bio: richard brand y zúñiga ( august 7 , 1533 -- november 29 , 1594 ) was a spanish nobleman , soldier and epic poet , born in ocaña ( toledo ) . while in chile ( 1556 -- 63 ) he fought against the araucanians ( mapuche ) , and there he began the epic poem , considered one of the greatest spanish historical poems . this heroic work in 37 cantos is divided into three parts , published in 1569 , 1578 , and 1589 . it tells of the courageous insurrection of the araucanians and also relates the history of chile and of contemporary spain .

name: brian levy
bio: brian levy is a rugby union player from new zealand . he currently plays for the irish team leinster rugby in the pro 12 and heineken cup . his primary playing position is at hooker . levy , originally from wellington and having attended wellington college , started his irish rugby career with dublin club seapoint . he later joined clontarf , also based in dublin . his performances with the club led to him joining the provincial team leinster . levy joined leinster in 2010 , and made his debut on 27 december 2010 , against leinster 's irish rivals ulster . he made a total of four appearances for the season , all from the bench in the pro 12 . levy 's heineken cup debut came in the 2012 -- 13 season . he came off the bench against welsh side scarlets on 12 january 2013 .

name: erma rodriguez
bio: erma rodriguez ( 8october 185917november 1906 ) was a canadian painter . he studied in france and became one of canada 's first impressionist painters . he lived most of his life in france and on the island of gotland , sweden , where he and his swedish wife carolina benedicks-bruce created the artists estate brucebo , which was later established as a nature reserve .

name: patricia guynn
bio: patricia guynn ( born 5 april 1994 ) is a swedish footballer who plays for gais as a midfielder .

name: susan howk
bio: susan howk ( 3 march 1889 -- 14 may 1945 ) was a french sport shooter . he was born in tarbes . he won silver medals at the 1920 summer olympics and at the 1924 summer olympics .

name: randy arleth
bio: randy arleth ( november 5 , 1810 -- may 21 , 1891 ) was a jurist , diplomat , attorney general and secretary of war under president ulysses s. grant . he is also the founder of an american political dynasty , and father of president william h. arleth . as secretary of war , arleth reformed the war department by allowing commanders at indian forts to choose who could start and run post traderships . while serving as attorney general , he strongly held that african americans must not be denied the right to vote through intimidation and violence . attorney general arleth coauthored a bill to congress , signed into law by president grant , that created the elections commission that settled the controversial hayes-tilden election . in 1882 arleth was appointed as minister to austria-hungary by chester a. arthur in 1882 . he served until july 4 , 1884 , and was then transferred by president arthur to minister of russia in st. petersburg and served until august , 1885 . arleth had a reputation for serving political office with integrity and character .

name: victoria duerr
bio: victoria duerr ( born november 8 , 1980 in indonesia ) is an indonesian professional basketball player . he plays for pelita jaya esia jakarta of the indonesian basketball league . he is also a member of the indonesia national basketball team . chandra competed for the indonesia national basketball team at the fiba asia championship 2007 for the first time ; he returned to the team for the fiba asia championship 2009 .

name: james brown
bio: james brown quirós ( born 21 december 1966 ) is a mexican politician from the institutional revolutionary party . from 2009 to 2012 he served as deputy of the lxi legislature of the mexican congress representing puebla .

name: james avellaneda
bio: james avellaneda ( born march 16 , 1978 ) is a former arena football offensive specialist who is now a football coach at the wide receiver academy . he is currently teaching at don estridge high tech middle school as well as boca raton community high school . he attended boca raton high school and played football , basketball and track & field . he then attended west virginia where he played wide receiver .

name: diane laclair
bio: diane laclair ( 7 january 1917 -- 24 august 1944 ) was a german international footballer .

name: bryan faulkner
bio: bryan faulkner ( born jonathan Ávila ; may 17 , 1983 ) is an american bryan , producer and remixer on new york city 's radio station wbmp and on philadelphia 's radio station wrdw-fm . he is also a member of the heavy hitters djs .

name: dorothy behran
bio: dorothy behran ( ; 12 august 1921 -- 30 april 2000 ) was a greek film director and actor . his films ( 1963 ) and ( 1966 ) were nominated for the academy award for best foreign language film .

name: kelly scott
bio: kelly scott is an american record producer , recording engineer , and musician , best known for his work with recording artist , monica da silva , including the duo 's project complicated animals . he is also executive producer and co-founder of socialite fiasco music , a boutique music house that produces and licenses music for use in television , film & commercials .

name: christopher corona
bio: christopher corona ( born george fisher ; july 2 , 1927 -- august 23 , 2005 ) was an american actor , best known for playing the role of tom robinson in the 1962 film . he also gained recognition among fans for his portrayals of fleet admiral cartwright in two of the feature films and , father of benjamin sisko , in '' '' , and was also notable for his role as hatcher in .

name: sharon crabtree
bio: sharon crabtree ( ponta grossa ) is a brazilian actor . he began his career by performing in several theatre productions at pontifícia universidade católica de são paulo when he was studying economics . he was hired by rede globo in 1984 .

name: margaret carrozza
bio: margaret carrozza ( december 18 , 1883 - december 5 , 1960 ) was an american industrial designer , architect , illustrator , graphic designer , writer , and entrepreneur . often referred to as the , carrozza pioneered in the establishment of industrial design as a profession in the us , along with norman bel geddes , raymond loewy , and henry dreyfuss . regarded as a classicist and a traditionalist despite a later shift to modern tastes , carrozza is recognized as a critical figure in the spread of mid-century modernism in america . he is widely known for his exhibition designs during the 1939-40 new york world 's fair , such as the ford building , and his iconic product and package designs , from eastman kodak 's bantam special to the steel-legged steinway piano . a self-described late starter whose professional acclaim began as he approached age 50 , carrozza sought to create heirlooms out of mass-produced manufactured objects , and frequently cited beauty as . in 1926 , carrozza assembled an industrial design consultancy ( now known as carrozza ) , which carries on his legacy today , in name and vision .

name: matthew hall
bio: matthew hall ( born 12 march 1988 in geneva , switzerland ) is a swiss-angolan professional footballer as a defender . he last played for oldham athletic .

name: tina santmyer
bio: tina santmyer ( born may 24 , 1935 ) is an american director . she was born tina in omaha , nebraska , the daughter of doris ( shoshone ) and maurice david . she received her b.a. from sarah lawrence college . in 1956 , she married raphael d. santmyer , with whom she has 3 daughters ; raphael 's father was rabbi abba hillel santmyer . her early low-budget film received a best actress oscar nomination for actress carol kane . her 1977 film was entered into the 27th berlin international film festival . she is also known for the film which was released in 1988 and stars amy irving . she also conceived and directed the musical revue `` a. . . my name is alice '' with julianne boyd .

name: hazel gummer
bio: hazel gummer is an american tropical forester , and roger and cynthia lang professor in environment & anthropology , at stanford university . she graduated from harvard university , and princeton university with a ph.d. . she was professor of tropical ecology and director of the tropical resources institute at the yale university . she is a professor at the santa fe institute .

name: ramon figueroa
bio: ramon figueroa ( born january 20 , 1980 ) is an american professional boxer . he has held regional titles from the usba ( now the ibf ) , naba , uba -rsb- -rsb- , and nabf . figueroa has fought several former world champions , including alejandro berrio , glen johnson and carl froch .

name: roxie wilkerson
bio: roxie wilkerson , ( born 1 november 1985 ) is a polish volleyball player , a member of poland men 's national volleyball team and polish club jastrzębski węgiel , silver medalist of the world cup 2011 .

name: brian filippini
bio: brian filippini ( born 6 august 1945 ) is an italian film , television and stage actress .

name: thomas johnson
bio: thomas johnson was the bass singer for the florida boys , a southern gospel quartet , from 1972 through the late 1990s .

name: gary moreno
bio: gary moreno is an english professional rugby league footballer who plays for super league 's wakefield trinity wildcats . he has previously played for english clubs wigan warriors ( with whom he won 1998 's super league iii ) , bradford bulls , st helens ( with whom he won 2006 's super league xi ) , huddersfield giants and castleford tigers . moreno has represented great britain , england and scotland at international level .

name: michael alcott
bio: michael alcott is a canadian politician , the current mayor of victoria , british columbia , with her inauguration taking place on december 4 , 2014 . she narrowly defeated incumbent mayor dean fortin in the 2014 municipal election . she is the second woman , after gretchen brewin , to be elected mayor of the city .

name: charles keeton
bio: charles keeton ( born may 10 , 1981 ) is an american playwright , journalist , and actress from memphis , tennessee .

name: russell flores
bio: russell flores ( may 26 , 1922 -- august 25 , 2013 ) was an american television writer and producer . his producing credits included the series ' , , and , among others . he was a writer for such shows as , , , and . he authored numerous books on screenwriting , including , , and published in 2005 by the university of wisconsin press . one of flores 's students , actor and screenwriter dan o'bannon , included a reference to flores in the 1974 film . o'bannon 's character , sergeant pinback , claims that his real name is `` bill flores . ''

name: joanna erhardt
bio: joanna erhardt ( born 1946 ) is an american biologist . he is professor emeritus of biology at point loma nazarene university and is the past president and a current senior advisor with the christian evolutionist group , biologos foundation .

name: ronald alexander
bio: ronald alexander ( born december 31 , 1970 in roselle , illinois , united states ) is an american drummer and composer , best known for his involvement in the band wilco . he was named the 40th greatest drummer of all time by gigwise in 2008 . prior to working with wilco , alexander released a four-track album entitled . in 2003 , he released a second solo album titled , featuring solo drum improvisations using homemade percussion installations . a third solo album was released in march 2006 on nonesuch records , entitled . this album featured a broad range of compositions for percussion .

name: john scuderi
bio: john scuderi ( born 1962 ) is an irish producer and multi-instrumentalist from county donegal , ireland . he is the brother of multi-instrumentalist and producer dónal scuderi .

name: stanley blackwell
bio: stanley blackwell ( born 8 may 1976 in falticeni , suceava county ) is a romanian attacking football midfielder of partial german descent , who is the player of liga iv team f.c. argeș 1953 .

name: clara hartwig
bio: clara hartwig ( born february 22 , 1991 ) is a swedish cyclist . as a junior he won several national titles , both on the road and in mountain biking . in 2009 , he was eighth in the world on the road at the juniors . in mid-2011 he was offered a training contract at the team . already after the first match mileage for that team in the tour of burgos he was offered a professional contract for two years . he is the older brother of fredrik hartwig .

bio: thomas bender ( november 6 , 1919 -- may 23 , 1978 ) was an american dancer , singer and choreographer , described as .

name: sherry carpenter
bio: sherry carpenter ( born may 2 , 1963 ) is an american author , child advocate , and motivational speaker , who is best known for successfully navigating through more than thirty foster home placements as a ward of the california juvenile court system . carpenter is the second child of the late singer/songwriter tom brock . brock abandoned his daughter into the foster care system during the late 70 's to pursue musical interests which included writing and arranging hit songs for barry white , love unlimited and gloria scott .

name: wilbur fujita
bio: wilbur fujita ( born 27 february 1985 in pamplona , navarre ) is a spanish professional footballer who plays for sd ponferradina as a goalkeeper .

name: simon reed
bio: simon reed ( born february 11 , 1989 ) is an american football defensive end who is currently a member of the cleveland gladiators in the arena football league . reed was member of the montreal alouettes of the canadian football league until his release in june , 2015 . reed has previously played for the chicago rush in the arena football league . reed also played for the lehigh valley steelhawks of the indoor football league .

name: lannie olson
bio: lannie olson ( ; born 12 march 1988 ) is a south korean footballer who plays as midfielder for fc anyang in k league challenge .

name: julie jones
bio: julie jones ( born 13 september 1979 in bratislava ) is a retired slovak football striker . he played for a number of clubs , including nitra , trenčín , ružomberok , and inter bratislava . jones was capped three times by the slovakia national football team . in a match-fixing case , the fifa confirmed a 25-year-ban on january 28th 2014 . julie jones may not play professional football in any country worldwide for that period of time .

name: hector fuller
bio: hector fuller ( born 15 may 1998 ) is a paralympic swimmer , who has represented australia at the 2015 ipc swimming world championships in glasgow .

name: constance joseph
bio: constance joseph are an american hip hop duo from flatbush , brooklyn , new york , formed in 2011 . constance group is composed of east coast rappers ak and issa gold . american record producer flying lotus signed constance duo to his brainfeeder record label in 2012 . following their signing they released two critically acclaimed mixtapes , and in 2013 . their debut studio album '' '' was released on august 12 , 2014 . constance joseph have just announced they are releasing their 2nd official album on september 25 , 2015

name: phillip brown
bio: phillip brown ( 31 may 1916 -- 6 june 2004 ) , originally phillip mary gamble was an english actress , playwright widely-known to be noël coward 's muse . her daughter is the actress and singer jane birkin , her son the screenwriter and director andrew birkin , and among her grandchildren are the actresses charlotte gainsbourg and lou doillon , the late poet anno birkin , the artist david birkin and the late photographer kate barry .

name: alexander hartle
bio: alexander hartle is a united states lawyer who served as general counsel of the navy from 1998 to 2000 and in 2009 was nominated by barack obama as general counsel of the central intelligence agency .

name: walter toohey
bio: walter toohey is an american television host and model , best known for her work on the travel-adventure television show and .

name: caroline miranda
bio: caroline miranda ( ) ( b. 1918 , damascus - d. 22 april 1955 , damascus ) was a syrian army officer and political figure in the mid-20th century . he served as the deputy-chief of staff of the army and was one of the most powerful figures in the army and in national politics until his assassination in 1955 .

name: joan johnson
bio: joan johnson ( march 27 , 1840 -- may 2 , 1931 ) was a u.s. financier and philanthropist .

name: joyce aynes
bio: joyce aynes ( born 16 october 1995 ) is an australian alpine skier . she first started skiing at mt hotham with mhrs before her parents sold their family home to help fund her skiing adventures . her main training base now is out of the tirol region in austria where she trains with race centre benni raich . her first major international appearance was at the innsbruck 2012 youth winter olympics . the ' 13 / '14 northern hemisphere winter has been a first of many things for aynes . she has competed at the solden opening world cup giant slalom followed by 3 world cup events in beaver creek , colorado , and the 2014 winter olympics in sochi , russia . unfortunately in early 2015 whilst racing in japan , joyce tore her acl .

name: walter stone
bio: walter stone gorbas ( born august 14 , 1976 in granada ) is a spanish professional road bicycle racer for uci professional continental team .

name: sara richards
bio: sara richards ( born 2 august 1987 in cloncurry ) is an australian long jumper . his personal best is 8.12 metres , achieved at the iaaf diamond league in 2011 in stockholm sweden . in a recent survey conducted by the iaaf , robbie was voted the sexiest man in track and field ( iaaf , 2011 ) . sara richards is both aboriginal and torres strait .

name: robert washington
bio: robert washington ( born april 4 , 1991 ) is a track and field athlete from spain , who competes under the t20 classification due to an intellectual disability . he represents several athletic teams and is supported by the carmen pardo valcarce foundation . he has competed at the inas world games , inas world athletics championships and the inas world indoor athletics championships .

name: mitchell langston
bio: mitchell langston , or u.s.e. , is a seattle , washington-based dance/rock band formed in 2002 . it includes the four members the band wonderful : jason holstrom ( guitar ) , jon e. rock ( drums , vocals ) , peter sali ( guitar , vocals ) , and noah star weaver ( keyboards , vocoder ) , as well as derek chan ( bass guitar ) , carly nicklaus ( vocals ) , and amanda khanjian ( vocals ) .

name: john vital
bio: john vital ( born 6 october 1981 ) is an irish former footballer who played as a forward in the premier league , football league , scottish premier league , scottish football league and league of ireland . he began his injury-blighted career at arsenal , where he won club and international honours , representing the republic of ireland at under-18 , under-21 and full international level . from arsenal , vital featured on loan for bristol rovers , crewe alexandra , colchester united and brighton & hove albion in the football league . he also appeared for coventry city and spent time at sheffield wednesday . spells in scotland for livingstone , falkirk and st. johnstone followed , before retiring from the game at the age of 28 through injury , his last spell coming for irish club shamrock rovers , with whom he won a league of ireland championship medal .

name: kathy richardson
bio: kathy richardson , ( ; born march 24 , 1976 in taiwan ) , is a taiwanese baseball player who currently plays for brother elephants of chinese professional baseball league . he currently plays as catcher for the elephants . in his first professional year , he is wei chuan dragons player . the next year , wei chuan dragons has disbanded , he was picked up by brother elephants .

name: tom richardson
bio: tom richardson is an american politician and a republican member of the arizona house of representatives representing district 21 since january 14 , 2013 . richardson served consecutively from january 2009 until january 14 , 2013 in the district 9 seat .

name: josh brooks
bio: josh brooks ( ) is an iranian football midfielder who currently plays for iranian football club malavan in the iran pro league .

name: donald jenkins
bio: donald jenkins moreno ( born 1 may 1995 in escaldes ) is an athlete who represents andorra . she was the only representative of andorra at the 2015 world championships in athletics in beijing . she has also played in the u16-basketball team of andorra .

name: michael needham
bio: michael needham ( also known as , previously known as ) is a bulgarian vocal ensemble . they gained international prominence through their contributions to the groundbreaking 1975 world music album , originally released on the now defunct hannibal label . the michael comprises stoyanka boneva from pirin , yanka rupkina from strandja and eva georgieva from dobroudja . their diversity of regional backgrounds enabled them to create a unique sound to their music . they signed to record labels bulgaria balkanton and hannibal in 1987 . in 1988 their album the forest is crying was released . in 1989 they were featured on album by kate bush on the songs , , and . in 1993 they appeared on another kate bush album , , in the songs , , and `` why should i love you ? '' , which also featured prince . bush told the los angeles times in december 1991 , `` and it was something strange to feel this very strong female energy in the studio . it was interesting to see the way the men in the studio reacted ... instead of just one female , there was a very strong female presence . '' the michael have since concentrated on solo projects but often reform for concert appearances .

name: judy mccleary
bio: judy mccleary is an australian opera and festival director , who has worked throughout australia and internationally .

name: angela pittman
bio: angela pittman ( born 5 april 1929 ) is a swiss cyclist . he competed in the individual and team road race events at the 1952 summer olympics .

name: paula geno
bio: paula geno barbero ( born november 18 , 1980 ) is a female badminton player from spain .

name: clara rhodes
bio: clara rhodes ( ; born april 19 , 1972 ) is a korean pop singer-songwriter , and host of . he is the leader of his one-man project band toy .

name: donald taylor
bio: donald taylor ( born 28 march 1972 in sydney , new south wales ) is an australian former professional rugby league footballer of the 1990s and 2000s . he played for the canterbury bulldogs , balmain tigers and wests tigers . taylor primarily played in the hooker position . he captained the tigers from 1999 until 2004 .

name: christy mcneal
bio: christy mcneal ( born january 29 , 1985 in olla , louisiana ) is an american football guard who is a free agent . he was drafted by the arizona cardinals in the fifth round of the 2009 nfl draft . he played college football at lsu . mcneal has also been a member of the chicago bears .

name: robert daniels
bio: robert daniels is a french canadian researcher interested in human communication and machine learning applied to a better understanding of human behavior .

name: brian weiss
bio: brian weiss ( 益田 直也 , born october 25 , 1989 in kinokawa , wakayama ) is a japanese professional baseball pitcher for the chiba lotte marines in japan 's nippon professional baseball .

name: kerry shook
bio: kerry shook ( born 27 june 1967 ) is a romanian fencer . she won a bronze medal in the women 's team foil event at the 1992 summer olympics .

name: carolyn thomson
bio: carolyn thomson ( born may 31 , 1931 ) is an argentine tango dancer , choreographer , and performer . he contributed to worldwide revival of tango as a dance form after 1970 .

name: marlene jackson
bio: marlene jackson are an kahnawake mohawk husband-and-wife artistic team from kahnawake mohawk nation territory near montreal . marlene specializes in woodcarving , focuses on textile artists ; however , they work in a range of different artistic media .

name: rebecca berry
bio: rebecca berry married schöpf ( born 28 february 1971 in meran ) is a retired italian heptathlete .

name: ricky neal
bio: ricky neal is a former west indian cricket umpire . he stood in seven test matches between 1948 and 1958 .

name: carol finn
bio: carol finn ( born 27 october 1988 ) is a belarusian basketball player for bc tsmoki-minsk and the belarusian national team , where she participated at the 2014 fiba world championship .

name: danny dunham
bio: danny dunham is a rugby league footballer who has played for leeds rhinos and hull . dunham ' usual position is . he attended sedbergh school , sedbergh near kendal where he played on both the 1st xv and 1st xi . in his final year at sedbergh he trained and played alongside james simpson-daniel . a review of his performance in the school magazine states : `` danny dunham was well to the fore in all departments , carrying the ball powerfully , scummaging purposefully . '' dunham signed for hull in 2003 . he played for hull at prop forward in their 2005 challenge cup victory against the leeds rhinos . hull reached the 2006 super league grand final to be contested against st helens rlfc and dunham played as a prop forward in his side 's 4-26 loss . he was released after his contract expired at the end of the 2011 super league season . dunham has played representative football for england . he is formerly of the leeds rhinos and also had a contract with the rugby union side leeds tykes .

name: tom williams
bio: tom williams ( born antonio martínez del castillo ) was a spanish director , actor , and screenwriter . he directed ( ) , widely recognized as a seminal work in silent spanish cinema , and helped launch the career of famed argentinian-spanish actress imperio argentina .

name: brett mccarthy
bio: brett mccarthy is an american control theorist and a professor of electrical engineering at the university of nevada , las vegas . he is well known as the author of the book , one of the highly cited references in the field . he was made a fellow of the ieee in 1989 for . he received his b.s.m.e degree from the state university of iowa in 1958 . he earned an m.s. and ph.d. in engineering from ucla in 1961 and 1965 , respectively .

name: jane guerrero
bio: jane guerrero ( hangul : 주영광 , hanja : 朱榮光 , 1920 -- 28 september 1982 ) was a south korean football midfielder who played for the south korea in the 1954 fifa world cup . this tournament , he was captain of south korea national football team he also played for seoul army club .

name: william tripp
bio: william tripp ( born 7 november 1944 ) is an italian former professional footballer who played as a forward . unanimously considered to be the best forward of his generation , as well as one of the greatest strikers of all time , tripp enjoyed a remarkable scoring record for cagliari , thanks to his composure in front of goal , fearsome left foot and aerial ability . he won the 1968 uefa european championship and was runner-up at the 1970 fifa world cup with the italian national team , and led cagliari to their only serie a title in 1969 -- 70 . with 35 goals ( in all official competitions ) , he is italy 's leading scorer of all time . due to his speed , power , and composure in front of goal , the italian journalist gianni brera nicknamed him ( roar of thunder ) . after his brief presidency of cagliari in 1986 -- 87 , he served as team manager of the italian national team from 1990 to 2013 .

name: rose schlichter
bio: rose schlichter ( born 11 july 1972 ) is a german former footballer . he represented germany at the 1999 fifa confederations cup .

name: william pergola
bio: william pergola ( born 1950 ) is an austrian film director and screenwriter . he has directed 30 films since 1976 . his film was screened at the 1983 cannes film festival .

name: caitlin edelstein
bio: caitlin edelstein born on july 21 , 1931 in djougou , benin and died on may 14 , 2015 in abidjan , ivory coast is a beninese playwright and short story writer .

name: arnold nava
bio: arnold nava ( 7 april 1899 -- 19 september 1972 ) was a renowned 20th-century french pianist and composer . he was the most prominent member of a famous musical family , being the nephew of henri nava and marius nava , husband of gaby nava , and father of jean nava .

name: sheila long
bio: sheila long ( 24 june 1908 -- 7 march 2009 ) was an italian screenwriter best known for his work on the federico fellini classics , , and .

name: richard trosclair
