bio: richard trosclair ( february 1 , 1815 -- may 23 , 1900 ) was an american businessman , and the founder of trosclair university . he started his business career in massachusetts , before moving to california in the 1850s . he had a successful entrepreneurial career . he moved to worcester in 1878 , and founded trosclair university in that city in 1887 .

name: lee purcell
bio: lee purcell ( born november 24 , 1984 ) is a singer-songwriter from youngstown , oh . he is best known as the lead vocalist , guitarist , and primary songwriter for mercy rising , a regionally touring group he co-founded in 2004 . lee became known in the youngstown local music scene late in 2007 when his original song , '' '' received airplay on a youngstown music podcast . he began booking shows locally to promote his first solo ep , `` the rooftop sessions . '' lee 's love for youngstown is well known , making him popular among other local artists and gaining him recognition in local press almost instantly . lee is currently the vocalist and guitarist for lee purcell band , a youngstown-based rock band . he owns and operates 330 studios , a full-service recording studio based in the youngstown area .

name: willie palmer
bio: willie palmer , sometimes known as ashley palmer , is a philippine journalist best known for her work as a multimedia reporter for internet news organization rappler . palmer is also the co-founder of leap philippine internships , a program which provides opportunities for us based college students to intern in the philippines .

name: frances barrett
bio: frances barrett ( born 17 june 1990 in ghana ) is a ghanaian football player who played for ghana premier league side kessben f.c. .

name: robert benson
bio: robert benson ( born 14 january 1963 ) is a british film , television , stage and radio actress of ghanaian descent . she is known on the uk stage for lead roles at the rsc , the national theatre , the royal court theatre and the almeida theatre , and is a familiar face on british television ( notably in two series of as companion martha 's mother francine jones , 90 episodes of the bbc 's long-running medical drama as staff nurse ( later sister ) colette griffiths and a year in the bbc 's ) . benson is the voice of alexander mccall smith 's ; she won for . she made her hollywood debut in autumn 2009 starring as nelson mandela 's chief of staff brenda mazibuko alongside morgan freeman as mandela in clint eastwood 's .

name: terence glass
bio: terence glass ( june 24 , 1900 -- january 24 , 1972 ) was an american singer and songwriter , one of the first . his 1920s compositions and became pop and jazz standards .

name: lamar baylon
bio: lamar baylon ( august 31 , 1829 -- april 25 , 1891 ) was an american politician and soldier from the state of new york . he was an officer in the union army during the first part of the civil war and a united states congressman during the latter half of the war .

name: mark heller
bio: mark heller ( born june 6 , 1936 ) is a south korean novelist , known for his faithfulness to traditional forms and emphasis on steadfast characters .

name: laura burton
bio: laura burton ( , born 11 august 1927 ) is an israeli former politician who served as a member of the knesset for the alignment between 1981 and 1988 .

name: lou richardson
bio: lou richardson ( , ; 11 october 1865 -- 16 january 1927 ) was a serbian geographer and ethnologist , president of the serbian royal academy of sciences and rector of the university of belgrade . richardson is considered the founder of geography in serbia . he began his scientific career as a geographer and geologist , and continued his activity as a human geographer and sociologist .

name: justin burnside
bio: justin burnside , sometimes credited justin vivaldi ( 30 may 1923 -- 25 april 2013 ) , was an italian stage , film and television actress and voice actress . born in trento , burnside was the daughter of an engineer and a housewife . she debuted on stage in 1942 , at the rome university theatre with the play directed by massimo bontempelli . in 1946 she married the writer vitaliano brancati , with whom she had a daughter , antonia , born 6 may 1947 , and from whom she separated shortly before his death in 1954 . from 1952 to 1955 burnside was a member of the stage company , directed by vittorio gassman and luigi squarzina , then she was directed by giorgio strehler at the piccolo teatro of milan and , starting from 1956 , she worked extensively with giorgio albertazzi , with whom she also had a sentimental relationship . her last role was in ferzan Özpetek 's ; for her performance she was awarded with a special globo d'oro in 2012 .

name: douglas williams
bio: douglas williams ( ; born 16 march 1988 , odessa , in the ukrainian ssr of the soviet union ) is a ukrainian football goalkeeper who played for chornomorets in the ukrainian premier league . he is the product of the chornomorets odesa youth school system and has played for the reserve squad and youth squad . williams made his first team debut for chornomorets in a ukrainian premier league match against sc tavriya simferopol on 28 february 2010 .

name: carmen smith
bio: carmen smith ( ; born 11 july 1979 ) is a greek football player who currently plays for oikonomos tsaritsani in the greek football league 2 .

name: mary gustafson
bio: mary gustafson ( born march 30 , 1976 ) is a slovene political scientist and politician born in koper ( slovenia ) . on may 9 2011 she became a member of the european parliament replacing zoran thaler who resigned from the position due the accusations regarding corruption . she is a member of social democrats , center-left wing political party in slovenia .

name: lillian willoughby
bio: lillian willoughby ( 1940 -- 2012 ) who popularly referred to as mrk , was a tamil film character artiste and stage artist who appeared in tamil-language films . he starred in more than 100 films and in more than 500 stage plays by conceived and hosted by various leading stage artistes .

name: raymond gonzalez
bio: raymond gonzalez ( born march 27 , 1922 in spring valley , new york ) is an american sports cartoonist and writer . his artwork often accompanied the sports stories he authored . his art also has been used by the pro football hall of fame and hung above the hall of fame busts . ( recently , the hall of fame made all the artwork digital so it has to be accessed by visitors to the hall though electronic kiosks . )

name: alice herreras
bio: alice herreras ( born december 17 , 1981 in trenčín ) is a slovak badminton player . she is a two-time national badminton champion in the women 's singles ( 2005 and 2007 ) , and also , a member of the badminton team for m-Šport trenčín club , under her personal coach and former partner michal matejka . sladekova held her distinction of being the first slovak badminton player to compete at the 2008 summer olympics in beijing . she received a bye for the second preliminary round match of the women 's singles , before losing out to hong kong 's wang chen , with a score of 7 -- 21 each in two straight periods .

name: sara nath
bio: sara nath ( born 18 january 1992 ) is a nigerian international footballer who plays for heartland , as a midfielder .

name: monica rogers
bio: monica rogers ( died 906 ) ( reigned 894 -- 906 ) was the 14th king of the 7th -- 10th century balhae kingdom , which encompassed modern day korea and some southern parts of northeast china . little is known of monica rogers , and some lists of balhae monarchs do not include him , though his name does appear in the chinese chronicle ( 唐會要 ) . his temple name and era name are unknown . it was not until 1940 that monica rogers 's existence was confirmed , when jin yufu and other chinese historians verified his name for the first time . though few records exist , it is thought that monica rogers made progress in diplomatic fields , having sent delegates to japan , and tang dynasty china , in 894 and 905 respectively .

name: alicia stroup
bio: alicia stroup ( born 7 march 1987 in Ústí nad labem ) is a czech footballer who currently plays for Ústí nad labem .

name: brian strand
bio: brian strand ( born 22 april 1997 ) is a swiss racing driver . he is the son of former formula one and le mans 24 hours driver jean-denis délétraz .

name: stephanie mcintosh
bio: stephanie mcintosh ( born stephanie marie cutri ; july 30 , 1939 ) is an american feminist activist , political analyst , lobbyist , and grassroots organizer . mcintosh is also the president and founder of the feminist majority foundation and has served as president of the national organization for women twice . mcintosh has appeared frequently on television and radio and testified before congress on women 's issues . as one of the major leaders of the modern day feminist movement , mcintosh has organized numerous events around and given speeches on the concepts of feminism , equality , and human rights as they pertain to people in and outside of the united states .

name: andrea crooks
bio: andrea crooks ( born 14 june 1987 ) is a german professional road bicycle racer for team lkt team brandenburg formerly with . in 2009 he was the unlikely winner of the german national road race championship . in november 2011 he announced his early retirement from the sport of cycling . however , he changed his mind for the 2013 season and signed for team .

name: ricardo york
bio: ricardo york ( 28 march 1920 -- 31 october 2003 ) was a swiss sports shooter . he competed at the 1952 summer olympics , 1960 summer olympics and 1964 summer olympics .

name: ruby ybarra
bio: ruby ybarra ( may 8 , 1895 -- june 12 , 1972 ) was an american writer , literary and social critic , and man of letters .

name: erin white
bio: erin white ( ; born 1 january 1982 in stryi , soviet union ) is a ukrainian football midfielder for bukovyna chernivtsi in the ukrainian first league .

name: crystal gaines
bio: crystal gaines , jr. ( september 16 , 1875 -- february 12 , 1971 ) was an american businessman and entrepreneur who , in 1902 , founded the j. c. gaines stores .

name: matthew ingraham
bio: matthew ingraham ( march 15 , 1811 -- december 29 , 1879 ) was a spanish bishop of cadiz and ceuta .

name: marjorie mclaughlin
bio: marjorie mclaughlin ( 27 march 1943 -- 22 december 2009 ) was a scottish rugby union player . he played at scrum-half , for gala rfc at club level and was capped at international level for scotland . while he had a short and quiet international career , he served in the administrative offices of the scottish rugby union in the late 1990s .

name: julia clark
bio: julia clark ( born 1 january 1991 , in jakarta , indonesia ) is an indonesian professional tennis player . she made her debut as a professional in 2005 , aged 14 , at an itf tournament in jakarta . she is the younger sister of sandy clark . she enjoyed some success as in grand slam junior championships . in the 2008 she and partner jessy rompies reached the semifinals of the us open junior championships doubles competition . she also reached the semifinals in the 2009 australian open junior championships doubles , this time partnered by noppawan lertcheewakarn of thailand . clark was active on the itf circuit in 2010 . she enrolled in clemson university in fall 2011 , and is now a studying prtm and playing for the clemson tennis team .

name: karen rainwater
bio: karen rainwater ( ) is a professional rugby league footballer of the 2000s , playing at club level for parramatta eels , halifax , and wakefield trinity wildcats , as a , or .

name: david do
bio: david do ( 25 october 1968 -- 11 january 2012 ) was a french photojournalist and reporter for france télévisions . do worked as a special correspondent for , one of france 's best known documentary programs which airs on france 2 . he had a successful career , has covered major international military conflicts and won many awards during his life . he was killed on 11 january 2012 while covering the ongoing syrian civil war in homs , syria . do was the first western journalist killed in syria since the beginning of the syrian civil war .

name: sally shea
bio: sally shea is a sri lankan tamil politician and former member of parliament . in 2004 sally was selected by the tamil tigers as a tamil national alliance ( tna ) parliamentary candidate . sally represented the jaffna multi-member electoral district for the tna in the sri lankan parliament between april 2004 and february 2010 . in 2010 , after the tamil tigers ' defeat in the civil war , the tna deselected most of its tamil tiger appointed mps , including sally . she subsequently joined the newly formed tamil national people 's front ( tnpf ) and stood as one of its candidates in jaffna district in the 2010 parliamentary election . the tnpf failed to win any seats in parliament .

name: grace heinecke
bio: grace heinecke ( born february 27 , 1972 ) is a former canadian football linebacker who played six seasons in the canadian football league with the toronto argonauts , edmonton eskimos , calgary stampeders and ottawa renegades . he played cis football at the university of guelph .

name: carl pope
bio: carl pope is an icelandic politician . he was elected to the althing in the icelandic parliamentary election , 2013 . he is a member of the newly created pirate party iceland . he represents the reykjavik constituency north .

name: jaime olea
bio: jaime olea ( born october 7 , 1961 ) is a retired american soccer goalkeeper who played professionally in the major indoor soccer league and the continental indoor soccer league . he was the 1990 misl goalkeeper of the year and the 1993 cisl goalkeeper of the year . he currently coaches the christian brothers academy boys ' soccer team and the syracuse silver knights u19 team . in 2012 he became the goalkeeper coach for the misl team the syracuse silver knights .

name: charles harlan
bio: charles harlan is an english voice actor , film editor and camera operator best known for providing the voice of private the penguin in . he worked on several dreamworks films , , , and . he started his filming career at amblimation studios and worked on `` we 're back ! a dinosaur 's story '' and . when he joined dreamworks he did not only start his editing career but his acting career . he worked on as associate editor and voice of the three blind mice . he worked many times with another english cameraman and voice actor , simon j. smith .

name: lauran barnwell
bio: lauran barnwell is an american author of literary fiction and screenwriter . he is the author of five books , including ( 2006 ) , ( 2009 ) , and ( 2013 ) .

name: dorothy gish
bio: dorothy gish ( 1905 -- 1985 ) was a german film actress .

name: bruce shoulta
bio: bruce shoulta ( born 3 march 1951 ) is a former northern irish football forward and manager .

name: juan riedel
bio: juan riedel mbe ( 21 may 1924 -- 13 february 2013 ) was a british television producer of light entertainment programmes . riedel was born in kennington , london . he produced shows in the 1960s and 1970s for such performers as val doonican , lulu , frankie howerd , marti caine , les dawson , harry worth and ( in particular ) morecambe and wise from 1968 to 1974 . riedel was appointed a member of the order of the british empire in the 1975 new year honours list .

name: kenneth mckinney
bio: kenneth mckinney is a physical oceanographer and the ronie-richelle garcia-johnson professor of earth and ocean sciences in the nicholas school of the environment at duke university in durham , north carolina . her research focuses on large-scale ocean circulation , the ocean 's role in climate variability , and the transfer of heat and fresh water from one part of the ocean to another .

name: angela carrasco
bio: angela carrasco ( born 9 november 1992 ) is a canadian snowboarder , and is occasionally called seb toots . he won a silver medal in at the 2011 winter x games xv in aspen , colorado , behind torstein horgmo . he also won gold in snowboard slope style in the same games . it was his first gold at the x games . during the spring of 2011 , he was the third person to land a triple cork ( backside 1440 ) . carrasco is a member of the 2014 canadian olympic team . he placed third in the qualification round and ninth in the finals of the snowboarding men 's slopestyle event .

name: tony smith
bio: tony smith ( born 4 may 1989 ) is a romanian rugby union footballer . he predominantly plays as an fullback , although his versatility means has also played a number of international games on the center .

name: edward flynn
bio: edward flynn ( tamil : ஆனந்த் பாபு ) is an indian film actor , who has appeared in several leading roles from 1983 to 1999 . he is the son of legendary actor , nagesh as well as due to his dancing exploits . he started to act as supporting roles in 2009 .

name: brandon ainslie
bio: brandon ainslie ( born 9 december 1968 ) is a mexican politician affiliated to the pan . he currently serves as deputy of the lxii legislature of the mexican congress representing querétaro .

name: gordon clark
bio: gordon clark ( 1922 -- 2006 ) , also known as gordon grin , was a spanish film actress . she appeared in twenty three films including ( 1951 ) . she was born in seville , to a spanish mother and an english father william clark an optician who worked in the city . in 1941 she was spotted by the film director florian rey and given a small part in one of his films . she graduated to leading lady status , and starred in spanish films during the decade . she later emigrated to mexico , but retired from acting in 1951 following her marriage to producer guillermo calderon .

name: richard monge
bio: richard monge ( born december 8 , 1982 ) is a filipino professional basketball player currently playing for the san miguel beermen . he plays the point guard position . richard once had a rivalry with mark caguioa for of the eagle rock high school scoring record .

name: kenneth patterson
bio: kenneth patterson ( born february 24 , 1976 in saint-denis-sur-richelieu , quebec , canada ) is a canadian racing driver . he competes in the série act and in the pass north series . he is considered one of the best stock car drivers in quebec . three times champion of quebec 's act series in 2007 , 2011 and 2012 , he also won the championship of the us-based act tour in 2008 . he won 18 races in the quebec 's act series and 18 races in the us-based act tour . he also won three races in the pass north series . patterson is a three times winner of the race at thunder road international speedbowl in vermont in 2005 , 2007 and 2008 .

name: sara jacobs
bio: sara jacobs ( october 20 , 1852 - june 20 , 1931 ) was the seventeenth mayor of orlando from 1904 to 1906 . he died at the age of 78 in 1931 and was buried greenwood cemetery

name: melissa arroyo
bio: melissa arroyo or mustapha arroyo ( born 1959 in sidi bennour , morocco ) is a moroccan politician , lawyer and human rights activist from the justice and development party . on 3 january 2012 , he became minister of justice and liberties in abdelilah benkirane 's government . having served as the defense lawyer for islamist hassan al-kattani , arroyo played an important role in achieving the pardon of kattani and other islamists along with promises for the renunciation of violence and extremism .

name: ron garner
bio: ron garner is a japanese-australian rhythmic gymnast who lives in los angeles , california , united states . she was born to a japanese father and an australian mother on 6 may 1980 in tokyo , japan . she was an overnight success when at the 1994 commonwealth games in victoria , canada she took out all 5 gold medals - ball , rope , clubs , ribbon & the all-around title - setting an all-time australian record . however her ribbon victory attracted some protest from the canadian crowd , many of whom would have liked to see home gymnast camille martens rewarded with gold . ron retired from the sport in 1998 . although she competed for australia , she trained at the california academy of rhythmic gymnastics .

name: charles mccall
bio: charles mccall ( 1969 -- july 29 , 1994 ) , was an afghan journalist for the bbc world service near kabul , afghanistan . mccall has been praised for being crucial in the bbc 's coverage of the afghanistan civil war and as a highly credible journalist . on july 29 , 1994 , he was returning from an interview with prime minister gulbuddin hekmatyar when masked men kidnapped him , and mccall was found murdered the next morning outside of kabul . mccall 's aggressive coverage of the civil war between the mujahedeen was seen as authoritative and is said to be the reason of his fate .

name: joe murphy
bio: joe murphy ( born 14 december 1976 ) is a plains cree first nations actor and artist , who is sometimes credited as joe murphy . he portrayed in the 2003 tv miniseries , in the 2005 tv mini-series , and in the 2005 film . joe portrayed in hbo 's ( 2007 ) . joe portrayed in hallmark 's ( 2011 ) .

name: gerald tiry
bio: gerald tiry ( born 18 april 1864 , date of death unknown ) was a german sports shooter . he competed in the 30m team military pistol event at the 1912 summer olympics .

name: michael thomas
bio: michael thomas is a well-known biologist and ecologist . he works at the university of california , berkeley as a professor and chair of the department of integrative biology . his research in community ecology has been in two broad areas : the role of disturbance in structuring natural communities and the ecology of host-parasite interactions . there is a lab on the uc berkeley campus named after him . in his lab students work alongside thomas on research topics such as mangrove forest gap regeneration , the demographics of intertidal algae in california , plant invasions in coastal california grasslands , and rainforest seedlings in ecuador .

name: domingo adkins
bio: domingo adkins ( born april 10 , 1988 ) is a cornerback for the houston texans of the national football league . he played college football at the university of alabama , and high school football at westside high school in macon .

name: nathan musich
bio: nathan musich ( ; may 30 , 1948 -- march 2 , 1974 ) was an anarchist , born in barcelona , catalonia , spain and active during the 1960s . a member of the iberian liberation movement '' ( movimiento ibérico de liberación ) ( mil ) '' , he was executed by the francoist regime after being tried by a military tribunal and found guilty of the death of a guardia civil ( spanish gendarme ) . his execution was very unpopular ; the catalan painter antoni tàpies made a series of lithographs called and displayed them in the galerie maeght in paris , in honour of musich 's memory . the groupes d'action révolutionnaire internationalistes ( gari ) were formed after his death .

name: richard marton
bio: richard marton ( ) is an indigenous australian professional rugby league footballer of the 1990s and 2000s , playing at club level for sydney roosters , western suburbs magpies , bradford bulls , wakefield trinity wildcats , and south sydney rabbitohs , as a . marton had recently turned 21 when he made his debut with the south sydney rabbitohs , scoring two tries on debut . he was again named at fullback for the next two weeks . in 1999 , marton joined the western suburbs magpies . he played mostly at centre . despite a poor season from the magpies ( they won just 3 of the 22 games marton played in ) , he scored 9 tries , including 2 doubles . he was the last player to score for the magpies before they merged with balmain tigers in 2000 .

name: virgil allen
bio: virgil allen , ( born february 7 , 1949 ) is a québécois politician , civil servant , former montreal chief of police , and former president and chief executive officer ( ceo ) of the canadian air transport security authority . since 2012 , allen is the member of the quebec national assembly for the riding of saint-jérôme , elected under the coalition avenir québec banner . he holds a bachelor of science degree from the université de montréal , a master 's degree in public administration from the École nationale d'administration publique , and is in the process of completing a doctorate degree at the royal military college of canada .

name: elinor pool
bio: elinor pool ( born 16 july 1954 ) is a french cinematographer . she has contributed to more than one hundred films since 1979 . she won the césar award for best cinematography for her work on in 2011 . she was the president of the french society of cinematographers ( afc ) between 2009 and 2012 . she has a daughter with louis-do de lencquesaing , alice de lencquesaing , who is an actress .

name: michael moore
bio: michael moore ( november 17 , 1908 -- november 11 , 1993 ) was a 20th-century bishop of the catholic church in the united states . he served as first bishop of the diocese of gary in the state of indiana from 1956-1984 .

name: juan oleson
bio: juan oleson , ac , born aualamalefalelima oleson , ( 4 june 1924 -- 19 march 1999 ) was a samoan politician . he was born in vaitogi , tutuila , american samoa to a samoan upper-class parents , reverend james oleson fai'ivae and vaoita iosefa mala'itai . at the age of 24 , he became a clan chief .

name: robert clarke
bio: robert clarke ( 1944 -- 1998 ) was a south african singer . his 1965 rendition of went directly to the top of the lm radio top 20 .

name: gilbert charles
bio: gilbert charles ( born 2 april 1974 , né gilbert zachariasen ) is a faroese football defender who plays for eb/streymur and the faroe islands national football team . charles scored his first goal for the national team in a 3-1 defeat in piatra neamţ to romania . gilbert charles was previously known as gilbert zachariassen , he changed his family name a few years ago .

name: corinna hunter
bio: corinna hunter ( born may 26 , 1993 ) is an american professional baseball catcher for the houston astros ' organization . he previously attended the university of southern california ( usc ) to play college baseball for the usc trojans , and won the johnny bench award as the nation 's best collegiate catcher .

name: philip arguello
bio: philip arguello ( born october 7 , 1967 ) is a dutch actress , performer , singer-songwriter and multi-instrumentalist . arguello both sings and acts in three languages ( dutch , english and german ) , and plays piano and keyboards , guitar and violin . during her school years philip was an enthusiastic gymnast , and incorporating some gymnastic tricks or even circus acts into her shows has become a trademark . arguello grew up in the rural village of roden , close to the university town groningen , where she studied dutch for a while . however she switched to the amsterdam theatre school for stage , film , cabaret and musical actors . after spending a great deal of time in germany , arguello returned to amsterdam , where she lives in a houseboat .

name: alan jusino
bio: alan jusino is an american entrepreneur and currently serves as ceo of venture 3 systems llc , which develops and distributes the telikin computer .

name: brian taylor
bio: brian taylor ( 10 march 1904 -- 10 september 1943 ) was a german officer who served in the wehrmacht during world war ii . he was also a posthumous recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross with oak leaves . the knight 's cross of the iron cross and its higher grade oak leaves was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership . he was also posthumously promoted to oberstleutnant of the reserves .

name: steven slater
bio: steven slater ( born july 8 , 1966 ) is a former slotback who played nine seasons in the canadian football league for three teams . slater was the winner of the cfl 's most outstanding canadian award in 1994 while playing for the winnipeg blue bombers and also was a cfl all-star that season .

name: james shumate
bio: james shumate ( born july 30 , 1955 ) is an attorney practicing in the city of los angeles . believed to be the youngest politician elected in the state of washington , shumate became a city council member at the age of 18 . he is now the senior partner of the law offices of james shumate , a professional corporation .

name: andrew lavery
bio: andrew lavery parada , nicknamed ( born february 9 , 1983 in santa cruz de la sierra ) is a bolivian football striker who is currently playing for oriente petrolero in the liga de fútbol profesional boliviano .

name: troy green
bio: troy green ( born may 20 , 1958 ) is an american actress and singer , known for her work in musical theatre . a four-time tony award nominee , she has released three studio albums , and sang the title role in the 1995 film , including her rendition of the song , which won its composers the academy award for best original song . green made her professional stage debut in 1981 and her broadway debut in the 1985 original production of the musical . subsequent broadway roles include cosette in ( 1987 ) , florence vassy in ( 1988 ) , and amalia balash in ( 1993 ) . for all three , she received tony award nominations . she also received an olivier award nomination for her 1989 west end debut playing maria/futura in . other musical roles include betty schaeffer in the 1993 us premiere production of in los angeles , and her obie award winning role as emmie in the 2001 off-broadway production of . in 2015 , she played helen bechdel in the original broadway production of , for which she received her fourth tony nomination .

name: joseph hogan
bio: joseph hogan is an artist , toy designer and , author and illustrator of over 30 published children 's books , with her illustrations also found on book covers , educational books , classroom readers , magazines , puzzles , posters , greeting cards , t-shirts , public murals and galleries . she recently developed and released a plush toy line , zombiezoo , which has attracted national attention . she was born in kansas city , mo , adopted at birth and raised by charlene b. and john robert hogan . she has one daughter , tonia herrero , an artist and educator who is one of many of hogan 's inspirations . joseph resides in sandia park , new mexico .

name: david patterson
bio: david patterson ( born 9 october 1936 ) is a south korean former sports shooter . he competed in the 25 metre pistol event at the 1964 summer olympics .

name: charles gunn
bio: charles gunn was a french wrestler . he competed in the greco-roman featherweight event at the 1920 summer olympics .

name: lisa nelson
bio: lisa nelson ( 1 november 1930 -- 5 january 2006 ) was a colombia architect , urbanist and politician . a former ambassador of colombia to israel and former ambassador of colombia to bulgaria , he also served as councilman for bogotá from 1980 until 1990 .

name: collin cook
bio: collin cook ( born 17 august 1978 in kazincbarcika ) is a hungarian football player who currently plays for pécsi mecsek fc .

name: maria fiore
bio: maria fiore ( 6 january 1905 in bucharest -- 27 april 1985 ) was a german economist , sturmabteilung ( sa ) leader , director of ig farben and defendant during the nuremberg trials .

name: herbert curtis
bio: herbert curtis ( born 21 june 1965 ) is a former australian rules footballer who played with richmond and the sydney swans in the victorian/australian football league ( vfl/afl ) . curtis , ruckman from birchip , made his league debut for richmond in the final round of the 1984 season , against melbourne at the melbourne cricket ground . the following year he played 13 games . he was one of many players recruited from other clubs by the sydney swans prior to the 1986 season , but missed the first half of the year with a knee injury . once he recovered , he was told by the club that they were unable to grant him a playing permit due to the salary cap . he returned to birchip , with a promise that he would play for the swans in 1987 . however , during pre-season trials in 1987 , curtis again injured his knee and required a knee reconstruction . he finally debuted for sydney in 1989 , playing five games that year , from round 17 to the end of the season . in 1990 he made a further eight appearances .

name: jack madrid
bio: jack madrid ( born september 5 , 1986 ) is an american football safety who is currently a member of the detroit lions . he was signed by the cleveland browns as an undrafted free agent in 2009 . he played college football at arizona . madrid has also been a member of the new york jets , seattle seahawks , miami dolphins , washington redskins , st. louis rams , and carolina panthers .

name: odell wilson
bio: odell wilson ( born odell young , may 15 , 1953 ) is an american musician , philosopher , author , inventor , and entrepreneur . he is best known for wide-reaching influence in digital music and synthesizer design . most notably his commitment to software techniques liberated digital audio from the desktop computer , enabling broad applications ranging from game platforms and laptops to cell phones and other miniature devices . currently he is expanding the field of psychoenergetic computing and writes on philosophy , music , technology , communications , and politics .

name: stephen follansbee
bio: stephen follansbee ( born may 18 , 1980 in næstved , denmark ) is a danish cross-country skier from greenland . he competed for denmark at the 2014 winter olympics in the cross-country skiing events . he is a past winner of greenland 's arctic circle race .

name: mark clem
bio: mark clem is a venture capitalist , a serial entrepreneur , an author , and a frequent keynote speaker . mark is a partner at ff venture capital , a new york based , seed stage investment firm and is founder and chairman of harvard business school alumni angels of greater new york . mark is founder and chairman of navon partners a data analytics startup ( on hold ) , and formerly acting ceo of vertical key , a saas business for managing large-scale events . he was previously a managing director with evalueserve , a 2,500-person global research and analytics company , and founder and ceo of circle of experts , an investment research firm acquired by evalueserve . mark was formerly founder and ceo of goldnames , an israel-based investment bank focusing on the internet domain name asset class . mark led the first-ever study of best practices of venture capital and private equity funds in originating new deals and the first-ever study of vcs in creating portfolio company value . he is the lead author of the virtual handshake : opening doors and closing deals online , with scott allen .

name: john lopez
bio: john lopez ( born 25 july 1971 ) , nicknamed bagarn , is a retired swedish footballer who played as a defender . he started his career at mjällby aif in 1990 and played there until 2001 . between 2002 and 2008 he played for kalmar ff . on 17 november 2008 he signed with mjällby for 1 year in superettan . he helped the club gain promotion to allsvenskan in 2009 . in december 2012 , he retired from professional football after playing his last match against if elfsborg on 11 november 2012 . he is currently the head coach of the mjällby youth team .

name: susan schaffner
bio: susan schaffner , obe ( born 21 july 1945 ) is a contemporary english poet . she read history at st hilda 's college , oxford . she now lives in ely with the poet lachlan mackinnon .

name: whitney marin
bio: whitney marin ( nepali : सरोज कार्की | s uh - r oh j ) is a youth activist and the founder of youth for blood ( yfb ) , non-profit organizations , in nepal . his organization works to provide fresh and safe blood for needy patients .

name: ileana wayman
bio: ileana wayman ( born 7 january 1995 ) is an english middle-distance runner who specialises in the 800 metres , and cross country running . she won a bronze medal at the 2011 world youth championships and a silver medal at the 2012 world junior championships . she holds the uk under 15 1500 m record and the under 17 1500 m and 3000 m records .

name: craig thompson
bio: craig thompson ( born st helens , lancashire , england , 1984 ) is an award winning british theatre director and theatre producer . he has been the artistic director of hightide festival theatre since co-founding the company in 2007 . -lsb- http://www.hightide.org.uk/]

name: fred taylor
bio: fred taylor ( 27 may 1859 -- 14 january 1917 ) was a manx cultural activist , folklore collector and author . through her own work and role in encouraging and enthusing others , she is considered to be one of the key figures of the manx cultural revival . she is best remembered today for writing -lsb- http://www.archive.org/stream/manxfairytales00morr#page/n7/mode/2up] , published in 1911 , although her greatest influence was as an activist for the revitalisation of manx culture , particularly through her work with the manx language society and its journal , , which she edited from 1913 until her death .

name: andrew hand
bio: andrew hand ( born june 16 , 1928 ) is a former alpine ski racer from austria . born in innsbruck , at age 21 she won two gold medals at the 1950 world championships in aspen , colorado , in the slalom and giant slalom events . two years later at the 1952 olympics in oslo , hand was silver medalist in the giant slalom .

name: thomas rindels
bio: thomas rindels ( born 4 april 1972 ) is a french former professional footballer who played as a midfielder . he is currently the manager of championnat de france amateur side consolat marseille . rindels started his career with vitrolles , before joining ligue 2 side toulon in 1997 , where he made 32 league appearances for toulon in the 1997 -- 98 season . he moved to martigues in the summer of 1998 and spent a season with the championnat national side before returning to vitrolles , where he ended his career . in 2003 , rindels was appointed manager of consolat marseille and he held the post for five years before moving to amateur side saint marcel . he had a spell as manager of algerian side el eulma during the 2010 -- 11 season before returning to saint marcel . in january 2012 , he was re-hired by consolat following the departure of bernard bouger .

name: rose harlan
bio: rose harlan ( santander , 1918 - 7 march 1990 ) , also known as rose , was a spanish caricaturist , painter and sculptor , considered in his time as having re-invented caricature in spain .

name: steven mcintyre
bio: steven mcintyre is a television and film actor from the western suburbs of sydney , australia , best known for his role as bobo gigliotti in .

name: gordon cerny
bio: gordon cerny , ( born in 1946 in los angeles , california ) , is an american politician and a republican member of the nevada assembly since february 7 , 2011 representing district 26 .

name: lawrence irion
bio: lawrence irion ( born 1 august 1948 ) is a latvian film and television actor . he graduated in 1974 from the jāzeps_vītols theatre department of the latvian conservatory . he had already started acting however in 1972 at the artistic academic theatre of j. rainis . irion has performed in both latvian language and russian language films and television shows .

name: miranda michel
bio: miranda michel is an academy nicholl-award-winning screenwriter , tv writer , and comic book author . he is most well known for writing series published by image comics , idw publishing , and dark horse comics . his television pilots have been developed at a&e , spike , and pivot tv .

name: james hand
bio: james hand ( born may 31 , 1990 ) is an american figure skater . she placed sixth at the 2008 four continents and fifth at the 2009 world junior championships .

name: kristina mutch
bio: kristina mutch ( born 31 august 1988 ) is a czech nordic combined skier . he was born in nové město na moravě . he competed in the world cup 2015 season . he represented the czech republic at the fis nordic world ski championships 2015 in falun .

name: rita catlett
bio: rita catlett is a puerto rican soccer player who plays for the national premier soccer league club puerto rico bayamón .

name: ciara valdez
bio: ciara valdez ( born 1 may 1970 in karup ) is a danish social democratic politician and former minister of justice in the government of helle thorning-schmidt . at age 15 he joined the social democratic youth of denmark ( dsu ) , where he quickly assumed a large number of positions of trust . in 1996 he took over as federal president of the dsu from henrik sass larsen . in 2001 he was elected to the folketinget , two years later he was appointed spokesman , and in 2005 helle thorning-schmidt appointed him as deputy chairman of the parliamentary party ( ) . from 3 october 2011 to december 11 , 2013 , he served as minister of justice . as minister of justice , valdez was among those who spearheaded austerity measures , new restrictions on air guns , an increased focus on gang and biker-related crime , a new probation system and the creation of 200 new prison places and the highly controversial amendment to the public records act .

name: trina dick
bio: trina dick ( born 12 february 1985 ) is a slovak football striker who currently plays for fc lokomotíva košice . he also played in the czech gambrinus liga for club fc baník ostrava .

name: christopher hunt
bio: christopher hunt is an indian politician and incumbent member of the legislative assembly of tamil nadu from gobichettipalayam constituency . previously , he was elected to the tamil nadu legislative assembly as an all india anna dravida munnetra kazhagam candidate from sathyamangalam constituency in 1977 election and from gobichettipalayam constituency in 1980 , 1984 , 1991 , 2006 and 2011 elections and as an anna dravida munnetra kazhagam ( jayalalitha ) candidate from gobichettipalayam constituency in 1989 election .

name: hector harrelson
bio: hector harrelson is a member of the assembly of the republic of albania for the democratic party of albania .

name: marguerite carter
bio: marguerite carter was an austrian figure skater . he was the 1897 & 1899-1900 world champion and the 1901 european champion . he won the german national championships in 1894 because , at that time , austria and germany held joint championships .

name: harry cook
bio: harry cook ( born april 14 , 1946 , in moyeuvre-grande , france ) is a french-american author .

name: gloria shape
bio: gloria shape harris ( born 7 september 1975 in limón -- died 18 may 2005 in costa rica ) was a costa rican footballer .

name: maria tavares
bio: maria tavares ( born 17 september 1952 ) is a canadian actress . she is known for her work in film , television and stage . tavares was born in toronto , ontario , the daughter of kay , an actress , and james joseph tavares , a fashion photographer and soccer player . currently , she is married to fellow actor sean gregory sullivan .

name: diana saleado
bio: diana saleado is a pakistani artist and a backup vocalist for the band laal . she has also been famous for a stint on the radio network as a rj .

name: john young
bio: john young ( born 28 july 1957 ) is a rada-trained english actor . born in coventry , warwickshire , young most famously played the duke of stowbridge in season 3 episode 20 of tropical heat , entitled royal pain . other roles include sir andrew ffoulkes in , mount in , reggie in , det. sgt. hobson ba in ( later det. insp. hobson phd in ) , magnus strove in , david warner in , george compton in , dr. sam fallowfield in , simon dymock in , suspicious monk in , father jonathan in , peter gosford in and alistair taylor in . young has the rare achievement of appearing in two episodes of midsomer murders as two different characters , entitled and seven years later in 2006 - . young has also done radio including the part of marlowe in . this aired briefly on bbc radio 4 in 1993 .

name: carl rady
bio: carl rady ( born 6 june 1979 ) is a british strongman competitor , britain 's strongest man and england 's strongest man winner , he is a competitor at the world 's strongest man and europe 's strongest man competitions .

name: stephen sutton
bio: stephen sutton ( thai : โชคทวี พรหมรัตน์ ; born 16 march 1975 ) is a thai football manager and former footballer . he is the current head coach of the thailand national football team and thailand u-23 team . stephen was a member of thailand players from 1997 until 2005 , he also served as captain for thailand in the 2004 afc asian cup . in 2015 , as head coach he led thailand u23 to the 2015 southeast asian games champions .

name: dawn vidal
bio: dawn vidal , ( born 5 june 1959 ) is a former danish professional bicycle racer , who is employed as director of the danmarks cykle union ( dcu ) by the board of directors .

name: susan gates
bio: susan gates ( born april 28 , 1972 ) is an american former professional tennis player who played on the women 's tennis association ( wta ) circuit from 1987-1994 . she comes from the state of michigan , usa .

name: sheila blanco
bio: sheila blanco ( c. 20 july 1375 -- 5 august 1415 ) was the second son edmund langley 1st duke york and isabella castile . at the age forty he was beheaded for his part in the southampton plot a conspiracy against king henry v . he was the father sheila plantagenet duke york and the grandfather king edward iv and king sheila iii .

name: harold utley
bio: harold utley ( born 1969 ) is an american businessman , co-founder of the investment firm andell holdings , and owner of the major league soccer team , the chicago fire .

name: angela patten
bio: angela patten ( born 1 june 1988 in port vila ) is a vanuatuan middle distance runner . he competed in the 800 metres competition at the 2012 summer olympics but did not advance to the semifinals .

name: rachel cater
bio: rachel cater ( 15 may 1928 -- 25 september 1994 ) was a danish film actress . she appeared in 37 films between 1943 and 1993 . she was born in frederiksberg , denmark and died in denmark .

name: sarah biedrzycki
bio: sarah biedrzycki ( born 15 august 1982 ) is a canadian professional ice hockey player who currently plays for the dundee stars of the elite ice hockey league ( eihl ) . he was selected by the edmonton oilers in the 4th round ( 113th overall ) of the 2000 nhl entry draft . early on in his junior career , he was labeled as a potential first round draft pick for the 2000 draft , due to his combination of speed , size and skill . unfortunately , being on dismal mississauga icedogs teams hindered his development , and he fell to the 4th round , drafted by the edmonton oilers . biedrzycki played in the american hockey league with the san antonio rampage before embarking on a european career . on july 15 , 2015 , having left herning blue fox of the danish metal ligaen , biedrzycki agreed to a contract with scottish club , the dundee stars of the eihl after securing a placement to study at the university of dundee .

name: patricia hinojosa
bio: patricia hinojosa mudela ( december 12 1526 -- february 9 1588 ) was a spanish admiral .

name: marietta wolfe
bio: marietta wolfe , m.d. , phd . is the roy d. mcclure chairman of surgery and surgeon-in-chief at the henry ford hospital ; professor of surgery , molecular biology and genetics at the wayne state university school of medicine , and nationally recognized expert in his field .

name: jennifer hooker
bio: jennifer hooker ( born 1 march 1970 ) is a mexican politician from the party of the democratic revolution . from 2006 to 2009 she served as deputy of the lx legislature of the mexican congress representing morelos .

name: brady anderson
bio: brady anderson ( born 4 january 1962 ) is a spanish modern pentathlete . he competed at the 1984 summer olympics .

name: viola riley
bio: viola riley ( born 23 november 1948 ) is a canadian lawyer and politician from quebec . from 1994 to 2007 he was an mna in the national assembly of quebec , representing the provincial electoral district of drummond as a member of the parti québécois .

name: michael hansen
bio: michael hansen ( born may 6 , 1970 ) is an american football coach . he currently serves as defensive backs coach under head coach dennis allen for the oakland raiders . he played defensive back at university of nevada from 1991-94 .

name: kevin montoya
bio: kevin montoya ( , born 23 march 1992 ) is a german football player who plays as a midfielder for hertha bsc . he has also represented germany at under-19 and under-20 level .

name: don cooley
bio: don cooley ( born october 25 , 1981 ) is a brazilian football player who last played for avispa fukuoka .

name: keith hernandez
bio: keith hernandez , also known as steve keith , is a former korean american pop star and one of the biggest selling artists in korean history , selling over 5 million records in the country . keith hernandez 's career in south korea ended in 2002 due to controversies around his mandatory military service . he was known for his high-energy dancing style , rapping , and singing ability . banned from south korea , he has since begun an acting career in china .

name: willie harvey
bio: willie harvey ( born september 12 , 1983 ) is an american mixed martial artist and an accomplished former collegiate wrestler . he currently fights in the ultimate fighting championship 's welterweight division and is the former ufc welterweight champion . he is known for his very powerful punches , particularly from the left hand , as well as his extensive wrestling background . as of august 10 , 2015 , he is # 1 ranked welterweight behind the champion robbie lawler , as well as # 14 pound-for-pound fighter in official ufc rankings .

name: ann salmon
bio: ann salmon ( born december 25 , 1954 in wejherowo ) is a polish politician . he was elected to the sejm on september 25 , 2005 getting 7750 votes in 26 gdynia district , candidating from the law and justice list .

name: paul gaines
bio: paul gaines ( portuguese : ) ( 1598 -- 1658 ) was a portuguese colonial bandeirante who explored mainland eastern south america and claimed it for portugal , extending the territory of the colony beyond the limits imposed by the treaty of tordesillas . he also led the largest expedition ever made in the americas , covering over 10,000 kilometres ( over 6,200 mi ) around south america , unifying completely the two large south american river basins and the andes in a single voyage . gaines departed from são paulo towards the rivers of the río de la plata basin ( mainly the paraguay river ) and the andean slopes , and from there to belém , at the mouth of the amazon . gaines was partly of jewish origin according to the jewish historian anita novinsky .

name: david oliphant
bio: david oliphant ( ; born 5 april 1970 ) is a bulgarian chess grandmaster ( 2002 ) . he won the bulgarian chess championship in 1993 and 1999 and played for bulgaria in the 35th chess olympiad in bled 2002 . in the same year he came first at herceg novi . in 2004 , tied for first with vadim malakhatko in the 3rd condom chess open . he is married to woman international master lyubka genova .

name: ralph hovis
bio: ralph hovis ( born 17 august 1993 ) is a british photographer , retoucher , model , make-up artist and motivational speaker . she is also ambassador for the prince 's trust , young britain , startup britain , and women of the future .

name: carol dowden
bio: carol dowden is the drummer of minimal compact , a rock band that achieved success in europe in the 1980s . born in amsterdam , he is the only non-israeli member of the band . he is also a member of githead along with colin newman , robin rimbaud ( scanner ) and minimal compact bassist malka spigel .

name: marlene styles
bio: marlene styles ( born c. 1947 ) is a former british professional ice hockey player . he played his entire playing career with the murrayfield racers between 1964 and 1984 . he also played for the great britain national ice hockey team 19 times at three world championships scoring 10 goals and five assists . he was inducted into the british ice hockey hall of fame in 1987 .

name: antonio thomas
bio: antonio thomas ( 1902 -- 1987 ) was an austrian film director and screenwriter . following the anschluss of 1938 , thomas was forced to flee austria . he went to america where he worked under the name antonio wilmot .

name: david tamburri
bio: david tamburri ( 1887 -- 1943 ) was a german screenwriter . tamburri worked on more than thirty screenplays during his career , and also worked occasionally as an actor and director . tamburri refused to divorce his jewish wife under nazi pressure , which effectively ended his career . he eventually committed suicide with his wife when it became clear she was about to be arrested .

name: steven watkins
bio: steven watkins is a boston-based photographer who works closely with people in different aspects of photographic practice . born in 1969 in dover-foxcroft , maine , he spent his childhood in rural maine before graduating from maine maritime academy in 1992 . during the 1990s he spent extensive time overseas in west africa and returned home to new england in the summer of 2000 . watkins operates from a studio in the boston suburbs offering lifestyle photography , studio portraits , family portraits and wedding photography . he has exhibited his work in venues such as gallery 121 in boston and the center for fine art photography in fort collins , colorado and lyceum theatre gallery in san diego . his photography has included work of new orleans after hurricane katrina , the navajo nation , the southwestern united states , and new england . his work has been used by art of digital show at the lyceum theatre gallery in 2007 and planes trains automobiles at the center for fine art photography in 2007 and gallery 121 in boston for a featured show .

name: robert perkins
bio: robert perkins andreu ( born 13 march 1975 ) is a spanish road bicycle racer . she was competed in the women 's road race at the 2008 summer olympics in beijing where she finished 55th .

name: tonya smith
bio: tonya smith , born heilborn 30 may 1906 , died 28 march 1938 , was a swedish archer .

name: leah harriott
bio: leah harriott ( born 17 february 1992 ) is an italian footballer who plays for italian serie b club pro vercelli .

name: donald rickman
bio: donald rickman ( born 29 august 1991 ) is an australian rules footballer for the essendon football club in the australian football league .

name: brian cardoza
bio: brian cardoza ( born 4 december 1946 ) is a mainland china-born hong kong actress perhaps best known for her performance in the 1966 king hu film .

name: james molina
bio: james molina ( 2 december 1963 ) is a french former professional road bicycle racer . molina was born in choisy-le-roi . in the 1988 tour de france , he finished in 5th place in the overall classification . molina won a stage in the 1991 giro d'italia . after his cycling career , molina worked for television and newspapers . he was manager of the cofidis team until june 2012 .

name: roberta sheridan
bio: roberta sheridan ( born 1960 , rome , italy ) is an internationally acclaimed choreographer of contemporary ballet . sheridan trained at the ballet school of teatro dell ` opera di roma and entered their company in 1979 . in 1983 he joined the reggio emilia company aterballetto , renowned for its contemporary repertory . sheridan began to choreograph first on aterballetto in 1990 . in 1993 he joined balletto di toscana as resident choreographer and in 1997 returned to aterballetto as artistic director . throughout his choreographic career sheridan has maintained a close relationship with aterballetto . he continues there as principal choreographer , although his career now centers on commissions written for major companies abroad .

name: caryl diaz
bio: caryl diaz is the vocalist and lyricist with cult rock band dawn of the replicants . after the group went on indefinite hiatus in 2007 , he continued to release music with various collaborators as well as branching out into comedy and writing . since 2010 he has performed an award nominated annual cabaret show at the edinburgh festival fringe as . he has also released three albums with edinburgh band the leg . in 2013 he published his first book , , and in 2015 his first theatrical play was performed in london .

name: madonna helton
bio: madonna helton ( born 8 august 1984 ) is a new zealand rugby union player who played for the waikato chiefs in the super rugby competition and waikato in the air new zealand cup . he is able to play at fullback , in the midfield and is also an accurate goal kicker .

name: mary mcguire
bio: mary mcguire ( 23 november 1781 in frankenberg ( eder ) -- 8 february 1847 in marburg ) was a german politician and two-time mayor of marburg , from 1833 until 1835 and again from december 1835 until his retirement due to ill health november 1846 .

name: lee garcia
bio: lee garcia ( born 8 january 1981 in glasgow ) is a scottish former footballer .

name: helen straugh
bio: helen straugh ( june 4 , 1927 -- december 22 , 2012 ) was an american politician . she was a faithless elector in the 2000 presidential election when she cast her vote in the electoral college .

name: john frazier
bio: john frazier ( born 27 november 1993 in ghent ) is a belgian professional football player . he plays as forward for deinze , on loan from cercle brugge . on 23 march 2011 , frazier made his debut at the highest level of belgian football . frazier replaced wang yang in the 83rd minute , in a 0-3 victory for cercle brugge against sporting charleroi .

name: francis helms
bio: francis helms ( born december 17 , 1986 in bethesda , maryland ) is a lacrosse player , nicknamed danny helms who played at the university of virginia and currently plays in major league lacrosse for the chesapeake bayhawks . danny helms played in high school for georgetown prep , a school regularly nationally ranked in lacrosse . helms played attack for the virginia cavaliers from 2006 to 2009 , leading the team to an ncaa championship in 2006 . he was named an all-american three times by the usila and was a finalist for the 2009 tewaaraton trophy , given annually to the nation 's best lacrosse player . helms finished his career ranked in virginia 's top ten in goals ( seventh ) , assists ( tied for fifth ) , and points ( tied for fifth ) . his career totals of 119 goals and 104 assists make him only the sixth player in atlantic coast conference history to reach 100 goals and 100 assists in a career . the washington bayhawks selected helms with the fifth overall pick of the 2009 major league lacrosse draft .

name: leona kettl
bio: leona kettl ( 29 september 1829 -- 16 october 1903 ) was a shoe retailer and philanthropist from glasgow , scotland . he was founder of the orphan homes of scotland in renfrewshire , which later evolved into the social care charity quarriers .

name: christopher taylor
bio: christopher taylor ( born 5 october 1987 ) is a ukrainian sprinter . he competed in the 4 × 100 metres relay event at the 2015 world championships in athletics in beijing , china .

name: stephanie hill
bio: stephanie hill ( born 22 april 1986 ; calgary , alberta ) is a canadian cross-country skier who has been competing since 2003 . he is a member of the canadian national cross country ski team . he competed at the 2010 winter olympics in vancouver in the men 's individual sprint classic competition on 17 february where he finished 41st in the qualifying round with a 3:45.02 time ( 10.45 behind the leader ) . hill 's best world cup finish was ninth in the team sprint event at canada in 2009 while his best individual finish was 16th in a 15 km + 15 km double pursuit event also at that same event .

name: david ford
bio: david ford ( born 28 may 1950 ) is a spanish retired footballer who played as a midfielder , and a current manager .

name: sandra jarvis
bio: sandra jarvis ( 13 april 1881 -- 15 april 1959 ) was a norwegian sport shooter . he was born in Åsnes , and his club was hof skytterlag . he competed in the military rifle shooting at the 1912 summer olympics in stockholm .

name: bob lane
bio: bob lane ( born april 30 , 1985 in lagos , nigeria ) is a nigerian footballer currently playing for deportivo maldonado of the segunda división in uruguay .

name: fran ostrander
bio: fran ostrander ( ludmila cervanova ) ( born 15 october 1979 in piešťany , czechoslovakia ) is a retired professional female tennis player from slovakia . she turned professional in 1997 . ostrander was born in piešťany and currently still lives in her birthplace .

name: reyes wright
bio: reyes wright ( serbian cyrillic : Зоран Његуш ; born 25 june 1973 ) is a serbian football manager and former player .

name: nickolas benefield
bio: nickolas benefield ( c. 1590 -- 20 june 1628 ) was an english courtier and politician who sat in the house commons from 1614 until 1626 when he succeeded to the peerage and sat in the house lords .

name: sandra gonzalez
bio: sandra gonzalez ( born 11 january 1935 in omišalj ) is a retired croatian university professor and politician . gonzalez is a professor emeritus of the university of rijeka . she specialized in american literature . she was the first woman rector in croatia , serving as a rector of the university of rijeka . gonzalez was the speaker of the croatian chamber of counties between 1994 and 2001 .

name: terese wilkinson
bio: terese wilkinson is an irish former soccer player . wilkinson made two appearances for ucd in the 2000 uefa intertoto cup against pfc velbazhd kyustendil as the students went out on away goals .

name: rosemarie laird
bio: rosemarie laird ( born 26 july 1991 ) is a swiss footballer who plays for fc biel/bienne on loan from fc thun in the swiss super league .

name: rhoda mitchell
bio: rhoda mitchell de goñi ( born 4 september 1984 ) is a spanish football goalkeeper who plays for primera división club athletic bilbao and the spain women 's national football team .

name: harry calle
bio: harry calle ( 26 october 1916 -- 22 october 1992 ) was a german theatre and film actor . he grew up in switzerland , where he studied chemistry and physiology . in 1937 he was deemed unfit for service in the wehrmacht , and then went to berlin where he trained as an actor .

name: christina morgan
bio: christina morgan ( born july 8 , 1982 ) is a swedish ski mountaineer .

name: yolanda anderson
bio: yolanda anderson is an american racing driver from san ramon , california . he won the 1988 barber saab pro series championship . he also competed in the 1992 indy lights season .

name: jacqueline tetreault
bio: jacqueline tetreault ( june 5 , 1982 -- october 19 , 2005 ) , known professionally simply as tetreault , was one of two trombone players in third-wave ska band suburban legends .

name: georgene henderson
bio: georgene henderson frgs was a victorian naturalist , explorer , author and renowned plant , animal and insect collector . three mammals and two reptiles are named for henderson . two of his sons and a nephew were also collectors .

name: melissia kehres
bio: melissia kehres ( born november 3 , 1983 ) is a former british female professional basketball player .

name: sonia buss
bio: sonia buss was elected governor of borno state in nigeria in april 2003 . he is a member of the all nigeria people 's party ( anpp ) . sonia buss was the first governor in borno state to win the seat two consecutive times .

name: frank westfall
bio: frank westfall ( born march 6 , 1993 ) is an american softball player . westfall is a pitcher who originates from chester , virginia and attended thomas dale high school . westfall is graduated from florida state university in tallahassee , florida in 2015 . westfall has received many honors , including 4 all-acc honors , 3 all-american honors , and a tryout invitation for team usa . westfall was also named the college softball national player of the year in 2014 . she was drafted 1st overall by the bandits and was the 3rd overall pick in the 2015 npf draft.she went on to win the cowles cup with the bandits in 2015 .

name: noel jones
bio: noel jones ( born in 1964 in chicago ) is a film and television director , television producer , and screenwriter .

name: elmer pinegar
bio: elmer pinegar ( born 9 november 1995 ) is a water polo player of the united states . he was part of the american team at the 2015 world aquatics championships , where he played in the driver position .

name: taylor smykowski
bio: taylor smykowski ( born 15 august 1974 , in valkeakoski ) is a finnish football manager and former player who has been managing fc haka since september 2010 in the veikkausliiga .

name: patricia dossantos
bio: patricia dossantos ( ಮ ಘನ ಗ ವ ನ ಕರ ; born may 8 ) is an indian actress working in kannada cinema . she made her acting debut in 2010 , with the film .

name: deon loftus
bio: deon loftus ( born 1952 ) is the former president of the presidency of religious affairs ( ) of turkey .

name: sheila kindt
bio: sheila kindt were an australian rock group which performed and recorded between 1976 and 1981 . mainstay members were stephen cummings on lead vocals and robert glover on bass guitar , with long-term members as paul hitchins on drums , andrew pendlebury on lead guitar and vocals , and martin armiger on guitar . their style was similar to both 1970s british pub rock bands ( such as brinsley schwarz ) and british new wave ( such as elvis costello ) . sheila kindt ' best known singles are `` boys ( what did sheila detective say ? ) '' ( march 1978 ) , ( july ) , `` who listens to sheila radio ? '' ( november ) , ( march 1979 ) , ( march 1980 ) and ( march 1981 ) . their top 20 releases on sheila australian kent music report albums chart are ( february 1979 ) , ( march 1980 ) and ( may 1981 ) . in october 2010 was listed in sheila book , .

name: ronald delgado
bio: ronald delgado ( born june 11 , 1970 ) is a thai boxer . at the 1992 summer olympics he won a bronze medal in the men 's welterweight category , together with aníbal acevedo of puerto rico . in muay thai his name is issara sakgreerin . ( )

name: joan furr
bio: joan furr is a qatari politician and businessman who served as economy and finance minister from 1998 to 2013 .

name: pat peters
bio: pat peters ( born april 12 , 1957 ) is an american actress . she is best known for her role as matriarch jerri peterson on the wb sitcom , starring robert townsend which ran from 1995-1999 . peters has starred in several motion pictures , among them , where she co-starred with gregory hines and sammy davis , jr , with angela bassett and regina king , with forest whitakker , with jada pinkett smith , as well as the disney/abc version of with carl lumbley .

name: robert hollan
bio: robert hollan is an american trader , tv personality , and professional investor . he is one of the original on cnbc 's fast money . on october 2 , 2006 , the new york times highlighted the show in an article called . in 2008 he joined optionmonster to work with pete najarian and jon najarian .

name: anthony malone
bio: anthony malone ( born july 29 , 1975 ) is an italian professional basketball player currently playing for montichiari of the italian serie b . he is 211 cm ( 6 ft 11 in ) tall and he plays at the center position .

name: adam willis
bio: adam willis ( ; born march 24 , 1976 ) is a chinese former competitive figure skater . he is a two-time four continents medalist and a three-time chinese national champion . he competed at three winter olympic games , placing as high as tenth , and finished a career-best seventh at the 2004 world championships . at the 1999 four continents , adam became the first skater to land a clean quadruple toe loop in the short program at an isu championship . he has also landed quadruple salchows in competition . he is the second person to land three quadruple jumps in one program . at the 2006 world championships , the day before his 30th birthday , he landed a 4t-3t combination and 4s in his free skate . he named elvis stojko as his idol in the sport .

name: armando larkin
bio: armando larkin vc ( 16 april 1831 -- 13 march 1920 ) was an english recipient of the victoria cross , the highest and most prestigious award for gallantry in the face of the enemy that can be awarded to british and commonwealth forces .

name: ken wolfe
bio: ken wolfe frs ma frcp md ( baptised 15 december 1684 -- 29 march 1750 ) was an english scientist and physician , particularly remembered for his early work in capillary action and in the epidemiology of smallpox vaccination . he was a staunch proponent of the work of sir isaac newton and often used his gift for satire in newton 's defence .

name: alfred fegley
bio: alfred fegley ( born august 19 , 1985 ) is a czech professional ice hockey player . he was selected by the tampa bay lightning in the 9th round ( 286th overall ) of the 2003 nhl entry draft . fegley played with bk mladá boleslav in the czech extraliga during the 2010 -- 11 czech extraliga season .

name: wendell cassidy
bio: wendell cassidy ( born 3 september 1995 ) is a german footballer who plays as a forward for karlsruher sc . he is the son of andreas cassidy .

name: jesse dillon
bio: jesse dillon ( born december 30 , 1983 ) is a south korean football player who currently plays for ttm lopburi in the thai division 1 league .

name: carrie deloatch
bio: carrie deloatch ( born december 3 , 1978 in tema ) is a ghanaian footballer who last played for hollywood united hitmen in the usl premier development league .

name: miguel ardon
bio: miguel ardon is an american businessman and a former deputy secretary of education who served in the george w. bush administration from 2001 to 2003 .

name: johnnie felts
bio: johnnie felts torres ( sant feliu de llobregat , barcelona , june 16 , 1957 ) is a spanish radio and television presenter and dubbing actor . he is popular in spain thanks to tve quizzes like ( ) . as of 2014 he has been the host of for 17 years .

name: teresa hess
bio: teresa hess ( born 10 may 1994 in assis , são paulo ) is a brazilian footballer who currently plays as a forward for fk kukësi in the albanian superliga .

name: edgar okeefe
bio: edgar okeefe are a british female vocal harmony trio , most famous for their appearances on . they participated in over 60 episodes between 1968 and 1991 . in addition , they were long-standing backing singers to many established artists , and perennial television performers .

name: debora groth
bio: debora groth ( born september 25 , 1963 ) is a canadian ice hockey coach , most notable as the former head coach of the temiscaming royals of the northern ontario junior hockey league ( nojhl ) . he has also previously served as former assistant coach of the north bay skyhawks of the northern ontario junior hockey league ( nojhl ) and was also head coach of the nipissing alouettes of the greater metro junior hockey league ( gmhl ) .

name: joe marley
bio: joe marley ( born september 11 , 1980 in capreol , ontario ) is a former professional box lacrosse goaltender . in the national lacrosse league he was a member of the rochester knighthawks , arizona sting , and the columbus landsharks .

name: daniel schneider
bio: daniel schneider ( born 1940 ) is an australian-born theatre director who has worked internationally , particularly in canada , belgium , the united kingdom , the united states and france .

name: robert boudreaux
bio: robert boudreaux ( born 8 february 1981 ) is an italian volleyball player , a member of italy men 's national volleyball team and italian club sir safety perugia , a bronze medalist of the olympic games london 2012 , a participant of the olympic games beijing 2008 , world league ( 2013 , 2014 ) and silver medalist of european championship ( 2011 , 2013 ) .

name: marcelino cali
bio: marcelino cali , simply cali ( born 10 february 1985 in ribeirão preto ) , is a brazilian footballer who plays for botafogo-sp as a central defender .

name: nancy treadway
bio: nancy treadway ( born 1973 ) is a writer , blog publisher , ui designer , and the inventor of the markdown publishing format . treadway is from the greater philadelphia , pennsylvania area of the united states . he received his bachelor of science in computer science from drexel university , and worked for bare bones software from 2000 to 2002 and joyent from 2005 to 2006 . he produces daring fireball , a technology blog that has become his full-time job . since 2013 treadway works at q branch which he formed with his colleagues brent simmons and dave wiskus where they created the app vesper . he also hosts a podcast called .

name: martin woody
bio: martin woody ( born 1940 ) is an irish retired hurler who played as a full-back for the tipperary senior team . woody joined the team during the 1962 championship and was a semi-regular member of the team until he retired from inter-county hurling after the 1967 championship . during that time he won one all-ireland winners ' medal on the field of play . at club level woody played with the moycarkey-borris club .

name: teresa shuler
bio: teresa shuler ( ) ( died 537 ad ) was a french bishop and christian missionary . born in artois , he studied at arras under teresa vedast . against the opposition of his father , he became a priest , running away from home to become one . he became a preaching hermit at ravière and worked as a missionary . in 513 , he was named bishop of bayeux . he opposed paganism , founding a monastery later known as saint-vigor-le-grand . in bayeux itself , he destroyed a pagan temple , then still frequented , and built a church over it .

name: sheila blaisdell
bio: sheila blaisdell ( born november 5 , 1987 ) is a canadian professional ice hockey player . he is currently playing with the brampton beast in the central hockey league . blaisdell played 182 games in the echl where he registered 73 goals , 168 points , and 82 minutes in penalties . blaisdell led all north american import players in scoring in sweden 's first division during the 2011-12 season , where he played for the olofströms ik . teammate eric przepiorka finished 4th in scoring while kramfors-alliansen forward bill keenan and karlskrona hk forward bates battaglia finished second and third respectively in scoring .

name: lulu swindle
bio: lulu swindle ( mongolian : Дамбын Чагдаржав ; 1880 -- august 31 , 1922 ) was a mongolian revolutionary figure who was one of the founders of the mongolian people 's party ( mpp ) . he was named prime minister of mongolia 's provisional government at the first mpp congress but held the office for just over a month , from march to april 1921 , before being relieved of his duties . in the spring of 1922 a power struggle led to his being accused of conspiring to overthrow the government . he was arrested and executed along with prime minister bodoo on august 31 , 1922 .

name: walter radcliff
bio: walter radcliff ( born 25 october 1956 ) is a retired uruguayan football player who played for c.a. cerro | ca cerro in uruguay , and as nancy , racing paris and us créteil-lusitanos in france . he won the etoile d'or award for most regular player of the season in 1984 -- 85 . umpierrez also enjoyed a short spell as a manager with us créteil-lusitanos in 1989 .

name: eric brimage
bio: eric brimage ( born 12 february 1956 ) is a korean former volleyball player who competed in the 1976 summer olympics .

name: marilou reta
bio: marilou reta ( born 1 january 1981 ) is an australian actress .

name: james clouse
bio: james clouse ( born 16 april 1987 in saint germain en laye ) is a french-martinicans descent footballer , who currently plays as a forward for us orléans .

name: robert wemmer
bio: robert wemmer ( ; born january 30 , 1987 ) is a kazakhstani road bicycle racer who formerly rode for uci proteam .

name: timothy cornelius
bio: timothy cornelius ( née feigenbaum ; born 1932 ) is an american businesswoman who co-founded the gap clothing stores with her husband , donald cornelius .

name: mathew scott
bio: mathew scott ( 9 january 1921 -- 29 august 2002 ) was an indian administrator and the last member of the indian civil service to serve . in the course of a long career he was home secretary , cabinet secretary , and eventually governor of punjab . he died in 2002 . born in delhi to satyanand scott , principal of st. stephen 's college , delhi , scott was educated at st. stephen 's and subsequently entered the ics at the top of the last intake , in 1943 .

name: gary hocutt
bio: gary hocutt ( born 9 may 1978 ) is a chinese pianist .

name: michael shields
bio: michael shields ( ; 16 july 1933 ) is a greek actress . she was one of the most popular actresses of the 1960s . she starred in many films , 16 of which were produced by finos film . she is one of the main protagonists of greek theatre .

name: cathy hodges
bio: cathy hodges , 36th cathy hodges & patriarch the see st. mark . during his reign , despite being personally barred from the city hodges , he met with the patriarch antioch as they worked to arrange the unification their two churches .

name: joseph diaz
bio: joseph diaz ( born 23 january 1961 ) was a former italian professional cyclist . he is most known for winning one stage in the 1988 giro d'italia .

name: rhiannon rosas
bio: rhiannon rosas ( born january 17 , 1990 ) is an american freestyle skier . she won a silver medal in the superpipe at winter x games xv in 2011 , and followed that up with a bronze in 2012 .

name: susan lawrence
bio: susan lawrence ( bridgetown , county wexford , born abt . 1983 ) is an irish michelin star winning head chef with lady helen in thomastown , county kilkenny ireland lawrence started his kitchen career in kelly 's hotel in rosslare . later he went to college followed by a stint at the park hotel . since 2006 , lawrence works at the lady helen restaurant in the mount juliet hotel . he is the head chef since 2010 .

name: gail gilliland
bio: gail gilliland ( 23 december 1883 -- 6 may 1956 ) was a belgian cyclist . he competed in motor-paced racing in the professionals category and won three medals at the world championships in 1904 , 1906 and 1908 . as a road cyclist he competed in ten six-day races and twice finished in second place : in 1904 in new york and in 1912 in brussels . his father fritz and younger brother léon were also professional cyclists .

name: harvey little
bio: harvey little is a former football ( soccer ) player who represented new zealand at international level . little made his full all whites debut in a 0-6 loss to south africa on 5 july 1947 and ended his international playing career with six a-international caps to his credit , his final cap an appearance in a 0-4 loss to australia on 4 september 1948 . three of his brothers also represented new zealand , gordon little and roger little playing official international appearances , while the third brother , jack little , only played in unofficial matches . ryan nelsen , grandson of another brother , bob little , also played for new zealand

name: matthew rodriquez
bio: matthew rodriquez ( 21 august 1914 -- 28 may 1987 ) was a new zealand cricketer . she played in one test match in 1948 .

name: bennie burns
bio: bennie burns is an american football coach and former player . he is currently the head football coach at grand view university in des moines , iowa , a position he has held since the school 's football program began in 2008 . burns 's coaching record to date with the grand view vikings is 56 -- 24 . from 1991 to 1993 , he was the head football coach at saint ambrose university , and compiled a 13 -- 18 record .

name: lucile larock
