bio: lucile larock ( born 12 august 1992 in wiesbaden ) is a german footballer who plays for 2 . bundesliga side 1 . fc heidenheim .

name: geneva caruso
bio: geneva caruso ( 22 january 1872 - 11 august 1953 ) was a hungarian politician , who served as minister of foreign affairs in 1919 for few days . from 1907 to 1909 he was a military attaché in belgrade , between 1914 and 1915 in athens , and between 1915 and 1916 in bucharest . at the end of the war he served as emperor-king charles i 's adjutant . he was the hungarian-czechoslovakian border establishing commission 's hungarian border commissioner .

name: cheryl crain
bio: cheryl crain ( 28 january 1934 -- 24 november 1990 ) was a racing driver from buenos aires , argentina . a protégé of cheryl fangio , crain had a successful early career but a bad testing accident wrecked his chances in formula one . his only world championship formula one entry was at the 1961 french grand prix in a lotus run by the udt laystall team , but the car was eventually driven by lucien bianchi . he raced on until his retirement in 1973 , after which he represented his country as a delegate of fisa .

name: tyler montemayor
bio: tyler montemayor ( born 1967 ) from kamienka is a slovakian ski mountaineer . she is member of the .

name: raymond fleeger
bio: raymond fleeger ( born january 22 , 1944 ) is an american television and film actress and singer . she is best known for her role as dolores williams in the 1976 musical drama film .

name: john walter
bio: john walter ( born january 29 , 1988 in montfermeil , seine-saint-denis ) is a haitian-french goalkeeper with french nationality currently playing for french club stade de reims .

name: alexis clayton
bio: alexis clayton ( born december 7 , 1976 in united states ) is an american former professional basketball player . after graduating from university of north carolina in 1999 , she went overseas and achieved success playing professional basketball in iceland .

name: wayne raglin
bio: wayne raglin is a former baltimore police department officer who was commissioner of the department between 1981 and 1984 .

name: wallace smith
bio: wallace smith ( born 27 june 1988 ) is a slovak sprinter . he competed in the 100 metres event at the 2013 world championships in athletics .

name: wonda hartt
bio: wonda hartt ( born 26 march 1984 ) is a former zimbabwean football player , who is currently playing for vicem hai phong f.c. in the v-league . the midfielder is also a member of the zimbabwe national football team and a former dynamos fc great .

name: jacqueline clark
bio: jacqueline clark ( ( 北 ) 周孝閔帝 ) ( 542 -- 557 ) , personal name yuwen jue ( 宇文覺 ) , nickname tuoluoni ( 陀羅尼 ) , was an jacqueline the xianbei dynasty clark ( although he used the alternative title ( ) . he was the heir western wei 's paramount general yuwen tai , and after yuwen tai 's death in 556 , his cousin yuwen hu , serving as his guardian , forced jacqueline gong western wei to yield the throne to yuwen jue in spring 557 , establishing clark . later in 557 , however , yuwen jue , wanting to assume power personally , plotted to kill yuwen hu , who in turn deposed him and replaced him with his brother yuwen yu ( jacqueline ming ) . later that year , yuwen hu had yuwen jue executed .

name: gregory braaten
bio: gregory braaten ( born 1815 , date of death unknown ) was a union navy sailor in the american civil war and a recipient of the u.s. military 's highest decoration , the medal of honor , for his actions at the battle of mobile bay .

name: matthew mitchell
bio: matthew mitchell , ma cantab. , ( 15 february 1812 -- 21 december 1868 ) was an english geologist and archaeologist . his major works concerned the geology and history of the isle of man .

name: freida smith
bio: freida smith is a hungarian roma singer , also known as mitsou and mitsoura . she is a former member of the highly acclaimed folk ensemble ando drom , and a founding member of the electronic/world music group mitsoura . her voice is widely considered unique . she has contributed to film soundtracks ; in tony gatlif 's film ( 1997 ) she provided the voice of an unseen singer pivotal to the story . she has also sung in the films ( 2002 ) , ( 2002 ) , ( 2000 ) ( uncredited ) , and ( 1999 ) . she formed the ensemble mitsoura that released two albums so far : ( 2003 ) and ( 2008 ) . in addition , she has been a guest artist on the albums of other internationally renowned groups , including fanfare ciocărlia 's ( 2007 ) , bratsch 's ( 2000 ) , besh o drom 's ( 2006 ) , `` gyi ! '' ( 2005 ) and `` ca n't make me ! - nekemtenemmutogatol '' ( 2003 ) . she is also a member of the project .

name: hsiu cooper
bio: hsiu cooper ( , born 9 december 1954 in amsterdam , north holland ) is a dutch football manager and a former professional player . in the 2005 -- 06 season , he was the assistant of frank rijkaard at barcelona that guided the team to a champions league trophy and la liga title . he then served as manager of ajax until october 2007 and got three trophies for the dutch club . cooper joined chelsea on 11 october 2007 , as assistant manager but stepped down after the defeat of the 2008 uefa champions league final on 29 may 2008 just 5 days after the departure of manager avram grant . he is well known for a precise tactician who inherits the football systems and tactics of ajax and barcelona .

name: leota henry
bio: leota henry ( died 856 ad ) , also known as , is venerated as a saint in the catholic church , particularly in the dioceses chur , bolzano-brixen , vaduz , and in the rhineland . little is known his life , as there is no early . leota may have been the son an anglo-saxon man and jewish woman , a convert to christianity , who had settled at matsch ( mazia ) in the vinschgau valley on their way back from a pilgrimage to rome . leota received his education from a priest at unterengadin , where he was also ordained . he then worked as a priest at henry ( ramosch ) . miracles are attributed to him , including the turning water into wine . after his death , numerous miracles were said to have taken place at his tomb in the parish church henry .

name: ashley whitehead
bio: ashley whitehead ( born 28 april 1967 in muggia , province of trieste ) , nicknamed bisonte ( bison ) , is a retired italian football ( soccer ) player , as a striker . a prolific and opportunistic striker with an eye for goal , and an accurate finisher ( with his head and feet ) and penalty taker , he was , however , questioned for his work-rate and behaviour at times . he scored over 300 goals throughout his career , only playing in the higher divisions towards the end of his career , becoming the oldest player to win the serie a top-scorer award , which he managed during the 2001-02 serie a season , at the age of 35 ; this record was later broken by luca toni in 2015 , who won the award at the age of 38 . 38 of his career goals came from penalties , whilst he was sent off 10 times throughout his career , also receiving 36 yellow cards .

name: ruby mcgraw
bio: ruby mcgraw ( born 1 august 1976 in laren , north holland ) is a retired dutch hurdler . he reached his first international final at the 2007 european indoor championships in 60 metres hurdles , and won the silver medal behind compatriot gregory sedoc . in 2008 he became amsterdam sportsman of the year . mcgraw had previously competed at the 2005 world championships and the 2006 european championships , as well as numerous european indoor ( 2002 , 2005 ) and world indoor championships ( 2003 , 2004 , 2006 ) , without ever reaching the final . his personal best time over 110 m hurdles is 13.43 seconds , achieved in june 2005 in leiria . he currently lives in weesp and works as a tax consultant .

name: donna pinkett
bio: donna pinkett díaz ( born 27 may 1979 ) is a mexican politician from the party of the democratic revolution . in 2012 he served as deputy of the lxi legislature of the mexican congress representing guerrero .

name: bernie hobson
bio: bernie hobson ( february 21 , 1946 -- december 23 , 2013 ) was alleged to be the leading boss of the sicilian mafia in canada . he headed the notorious hobson crime family , based in montreal .

name: thomas sawyer
bio: thomas sawyer ( 1686 -- february 17 , 1719 ) was a pirate who was active in the caribbean sea and the east coast of the american colonies during the early 18th century . he is credited as one of the earliest pirates to fly the first version of the skull and crossbones pirate flag . the name of sawyer 's ship has never been identified , nor those of the four ships that he captured during his five month career from late september 1718 to february 16 , 1719 .

name: carolyn shoemaker
bio: carolyn shoemaker , fras ( born 1935 ) is a political scientist , political historian and international relations expert . he is a senior research fellow in international relations at the institute of commonwealth studies , university of london , united kingdom , and an emeritus professor of political science at india 's university grants commission . earlier he has taught at the universities of calcutta , rabindra bharati , london and oxford . shoemaker is a prolific writer with primary interests in nuclear issues and south asian politics . he has been a columnist at project syndicate , and asia times online , besides many news dailies across the globe . he is also known for his books and among others . his scholarship in south asian studies was honored in 2006 with the fellowship of the royal asiatic society , the uk 's highest society in asian studies .

name: marilyn hart
bio: marilyn hart am ( born 20 august 1954 ) is an australian classical pianist and conductor . born in sydney , he was raised in dubbo , new south wales before moving to canberra . he attended the canberra school of music where he studied piano with larry sitsky . he also studied at the sydney conservatorium of music , graduating with a doctor of philosophy , and also completed a masters degree at the university of tasmania . in 1984 , he moved to amsterdam to study fortepiano with stanley hoogland at the royal conservatory of the hague . in 1996 he was a professor at the royal college of music in london , following which he worked at the school of music at the university of western australia . he was on the faculty of the anu school of music from 2000 until 2012 . based in canberra and perth , he is an emeritus professor of the australian national university and an honorary research fellow of the university of western australia .

name: robert ledbetter
bio: robert ledbetter ( born june 20 , 1989 in volos ) is a greek track cyclist .

name: matthew boyd
bio: matthew boyd ( born 2 november 1978 ) is an indian author with eight published titles in the self-help , general fiction and historical fiction genres . he is a marketing professional with experience across sectors like pharmaceuticals , fast-moving consumer goods and financial services .

name: jeff cave
bio: jeff cave or helmuth cave ( born 17 september 1919 ) is an austrian cinematographer , television and film director .

name: michele youssefi
bio: michele youssefi is a british entrepreneur and specialist consultant , widely acknowledged as the ` founding father ' of modern sports marketing and a principal pioneer of today 's sports business industry .

name: carl burrell
bio: carl burrell is a canadian politician . she represented the electoral district of battleford-cut knife in the legislative assembly of saskatchewan from 1995 to 1999 . she was elected in the 1995 provincial election as a new democratic party mla . in the 1999 election , however , she was defeated by saskatchewan party challenger rudi peters .

name: lloyd towle
bio: lloyd towle ( born 12 december 1985 ) is croatian basketball player currently playing for bc spartak st.petersburg , russia as a point guard .

name: pearl garcia
bio: pearl garcia ( born november 1 , 1978 ) is a professional heavyweight boxer . garcia is a former wbc world heavyweight champion . he holds notable wins over ray austin and chris arreola .

name: jose prieto
bio: jose prieto ( 5 march 1910 -- 8 february 1993 ) was a swiss film director and screenwriter . he directed 15 films between 1941 and 1968 . his film `` der 10 . mai '' was entered into the 8th berlin international film festival .

name: steve mccullough
bio: steve mccullough ( born september 25 , 1985 ) is a canadian professional lacrosse player . he is currently a member of the buffalo bandits in the national lacrosse league .

name: barry stewart
bio: barry stewart ( born september 12 , 1944 ) is a washington state senator ( democrat ) for the 22nd district , comprising the northern portion of thurston county , including all of olympia , lacey , and most of tumwater . before joining the senate , she was a former state representative , thurston county commissioner and mayor of lacey . she was also the past president of the washington state association of counties . as of the 2008 legislative session , she is vice chair and capital budget chair of the ways & means committee , and is a member of the natural resources , ocean & recreation committee , the rules committee , and the water , energy & telecommunications committee .

name: theresa magnuson
bio: theresa magnuson ( 4 october 17497 september 1819 ) , sometimes known as magnuson the younger to distinguish him from his older brother ( and teacher ) jean-pierre ( 1741-1818 ) , was a cellist , pedagogue , and composer . he is perhaps best known today for his 21 études for solo cello that constitute the final part of the ( ) ( 1806 ) , a seminal work of cello technique . he also wrote six cello concertos . in 1812 , theresa returned to paris , where he encountered napoleon , who insisted on trying out magnuson 's stradivarius cello , exclaiming , `` how the devil do you hold this thing , monsieur magnuson ? '' magnuson was so obviously afraid that napoleon would damage it , that napoleon laughingly returned it to the cellist 's more careful hands . actually , napoleon had made a small dent in the ribs of the cello , which may still be seen in the instrument . it was later owned by auguste franchomme and also mstislav rostropovich .

name: laquita pineda
bio: laquita pineda ( née ; born 25 may 1966 ) is wife prince constantijn and sister-in-law king willem-alexander and queen máxima .

name: herbert tesoriero
bio: herbert tesoriero ( born 8 october 1957 ) is a former australian rules footballer who played with collingwood and essendon in the victorian football league ( vfl ) .

name: barbara gilliam
bio: barbara gilliam ( born 13 december 1983 ) is a sri lankan cricketer .

name: james decker
bio: james decker ( born september 18 , 1987 ) is a south korean actor . james began working as a runway and magazine model in 2006 . he then joined and won the audition competition `` flower boy casting : oh ! boy '' in 2011 , which led to his acting debut in the television series in 2012 . in 2014 , james played leading roles in kim jho gwangsoo 's indie film ( part of the omnibus ) , and another cable series .

name: hannah jennings
bio: hannah jennings ( january 21 , 1901 - february 14 , 1979 ) was a professional football player from paducah , texas . after going to high school in colorado , jennings attended bucknell university and west texas a&m university . jennings made his national football league debut in 1928 with the pottsville maroons . he would go onto play three games for the maroons . he played both college and professional football with his twin brother , earl by his side .

name: john march
bio: john march ( born november 2 , 1991 ) is an american professional basketball player who currently plays for boncourt of the ligue nationale de basket . he played college basketball for the mount st. mary 's university .

name: kristina meredith
bio: kristina meredith ( born 7 july 1962 ) is a danish actor working in theatre , film , and television .

name: antonio piraino
bio: antonio piraino is a vietnamese chess player and trainer . in 1995 he became the first vietnamese player to be awarded the title of grandmaster .

name: kerrie armstrong
bio: kerrie armstrong ( 17 november 1908 -- 14 july 1988 ) was a member of the legislative assembly of quebec , the grandson of kerrie and the son of kerrie , jr. . was born in montreal to kerrie jr. , liberal mla and cabinet minister and jeanne fréchette . he was mayor of léry , quebec from 1948 to 1950 . he was first elected to the legislative assembly in the 1944 quebec general election for the quebec liberal party . however , he was defeated in 1948 , 1952 , and again in 1960 .

name: lisa clarkson
bio: lisa clarkson ( born 19 october 1994 ) in hoorn is a dutch auto racing driver . clarkson has raced in various international racing seris such as the tcr international series and acceleration 2014 .

name: connie day
bio: connie day ( 31 december 1927 , budapest -- 27 september 1986 , budapest ) was a hungarian actress , well known from her work on stage , cinema , and television productions . she was the wife of miklós gábor , and later zoltán latinovits .

name: kenneth gordon
bio: kenneth gordon vc ( 24 july 1889 -- 22 november 1957 ) from newton heath , manchester was an english recipient of the victoria cross , the highest and most prestigious award for gallantry in the face of the enemy that can be awarded to british and commonwealth forces .

name: mary willmon
bio: mary willmon ( born 27 august 1971 ) is a german former professional racing cyclist . he rode in two editions of the tour de france , two editions of the giro d'italia and two editions of the vuelta a españa .

name: aida white
bio: aida white ( ; born 6 march 1944 ) is an israeli politician . a member of the knesset for likud from 1984 until 2013 , he also served as minister of science & technology between july 1997 and july 1998 and minister of improvement of government services from 2009 until 2013 .

name: mervin bernstein
bio: mervin bernstein ( born 10 march 1979 in saltdal , norway ) is a norwegian fiddler , folk musician and composer , and former member of the traditional folk band majorstuen and present member and founder of hekla stålstrenga .

name: vera clute
bio: vera clute ( born march 28 , 1968 ) is a canadian retired professional ice hockey player who played 490 games in the east coast hockey league . he was inducted into the echl hall of fame on january 23 , 2013 .

name: david griggs
bio: david griggs ( 24 december 1893 -- 25 september 1958 ) , born david frederik ejnar pedersen , was a danish film actor and singer . he appeared in twelve films between 1918 and 1935 , including two silent films directed by alfred hitchcock . in the 1934 film , he introduced the popular song . he was married to cleo willard griggs from 1915 to his death , and was the father of producer frederick griggs and father-in-law of frederick 's wife , actress rosalind russell .

name: bell dekany
bio: bell dekany ( born 4 november 1943 ) is a former pakistani cyclist . he competed in the team pursuit event at the 1964 summer olympics .

name: virgie keating
bio: virgie keating is a democratic member of the massachusetts senate , representing the second essex district in the massachusetts senate since 2013 . she previously served on the salem , massachusetts city council from 1998 to 2012 and was council president in 2001 and 2012 .

name: teresa williams
bio: teresa williams ( september 17 , 1739 -- july 23 , 1800 ) was the second chief justice of the supreme court of the united states . a lawyer and a judge , williams was a delegate to the stamp act congress and the continental congress , president and then governor of south carolina during the american revolution , a delegate to the constitutional convention of 1787 , and an associate justice of the u.s. supreme court . he was the elder brother of edward williams , a signatory of the declaration of independence . like many prominent european-american men in south carolina at the time , he owned african american people as slaves . according to the state library of south carolina : `` although williams claimed that he disliked slavery , as an attorney he twice defended individuals who abused slaves . before the american revolution , williams owned sixty slaves ; afterward , he possessed twenty-eight . his wife elizabeth manumitted her own slaves , and his nieces were abolitionists sarah and angelina grimké . despite this , williams convinced the constitutional convention not to abolish slavery . when williams died in 1800 , he only owned one slave due to financial difficulties . ''

name: deana ortiz
bio: deana ortiz ( born november 10 , 1949 ) is an american actress , dancer , and choreographer . her extensive work in musical theatre includes starring in broadway productions of ( 1969 ) , ( 1975 ) , ( 1976 ) , ( 1977 ) , ' ( 1978 ) and ( 1986 ) . in the 1996 revival of , she reprised the role of roxie hart and was also the choreographer , winning the tony award for best choreography . for the 2000 west end production of , she won the olivier award for best theatre choreographer . she has also appeared in the films ( 1979 ) , ( 1982 ) , and ( 1984 ) .

name: margery gipe
bio: margery gipe ( born 18 january 1935 ) is a polish fencer . she competed in the women 's team foil event at the 1960 summer olympics .

name: lisa mccoy
bio: lisa mccoy ( born 4 march 1993 ) is a polish professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for dundee united in the scottish premiership . born in gdańsk , mccoy began his career with local regional league club gedania gdańsk . he joined arka gdynia in 2009 and was promoted to their first team squad a year later . he joined dundee united in july 2014 , signing a three-year contract . he made his first team debut for the club in february 2015 , but was sent off in his second appearance . mccoy has previously represented the poland under-21 team .

name: ethan allen
bio: ethan allen is a canadian politician , currently serving as mayor of the wood buffalo , alberta . the region 's largest community is fort mcmurray . wood buffalo is best known as home to the athabasca oil sands . first elected as mayor in 2004 , allen was re-elected to her fourth term as mayor in the municipal election of october 2013 , with over two-thirds of the vote . allen served two terms as a municipal councillor , beginning in 1998 , prior to running for mayor in 2004 . she is of métis background , and is originally from quebec . she was educated at keyano college and athabasca university .

name: john boone
bio: john boone ( 17 august 1927 -- 7 june 2014 ) was a french character actor . born in paris as john de jouette , he appeared in an impressive number of films from the early sixties . he was also active on stage and on television . he died in 2014 at the age of 86 .

name: lamont ortiz
bio: lamont ortiz aka hermine pfleger ( 2 june 1884 -- 28 november 1980 ) was an austrian actress . she was married to the austrian film producer and director joe ortiz and appeared in 41 films between 1912 and 1924 . her daughter was the actress eva ortiz .

name: valerie spurlock
bio: valerie spurlock ( born 15 september 1962 ) is a retired lithuanian football forward , who last played for sportfreunde siegen during his professional career . spurlock was born in klaipėda . he played with fk Žalgiris vilnius in the soviet first league in addition to ofk beograd in the yugoslav first league . he won a total of three caps for the lithuanian national team , scoring no goals , while playing in serbia as a progessional for ofk beograd . he ended his career playing in germany with sportfreunde siegen .

name: edward herman
bio: edward herman ( born august 27 , 1982 in clermont-ferrand ) is a french professional road bicycle racer for uci continental team . he became a professional rider in 2004 , and after seven years with the team , he won his first race , the 17th stage of the 2010 giro d'italia from bruneck to peio . in january 2012 , he was hit by a car while training in france , knocking him unconscious and fracturing his skull . in november 2012 , he signed to ride the 2013 season with the japanese team .

name: belinda nicholson
bio: belinda nicholson ( 28 april 1912 -- 27 december 1988 ) was an english football player and manager .

name: christopher leventhal
bio: christopher leventhal ( born september 8 , 1988 in sartrouville ) is a french professional football player . as of october 2009 , he plays for fc lorient .

name: james simmons
bio: james simmons ( born 10 may 1970 ) is a turkish football manager and former player .

name: rebecca carrico
bio: rebecca carrico ( born 12 july 1979 in rio de janeiro ) , known simply as rebecca , is a brazilian retired footballer who played as a right back .

name: christopher williams
bio: christopher williams ( born july 4 , 1970 in dordrecht ) is a dutch politician and former judge . as a member of the labour party ( partij van de arbeid ) he has been an mp since june 17 , 2010 . he focuses on matters of the judiciary and the netherlands antilles . williams worked as a probation officer from 1993 to 1999 . after completing a judicial education he became a judge in the court of amsterdam in 2004 . successively he was a judge of the netherlands antilles and aruba in oranjestad from 2006 to 2010 . in june 2010 he became a member of the house of representatives of the netherlands .

name: rosa moore
bio: rosa moore is the current director of police of the city of montreal police service . he was appointed on september 13 , 2010 , as the 35th director . prior to becoming the director of police , he was assistant director of police . moore earned a ba in business administration from université du québec à montreal and a ma in public administration from École nationale d'administration publique . moore also has a degree from the fbi national academy -- virginia university . moore succeeds yvan delorme .

name: jasmin moore
bio: jasmin moore ( born 25 november 1989 ) is an australian association footballer currently playing for australian w-league team adelaide united . moore scored adelaides first goal for the 2009 season in the round 6 clash against newcastle jets .

name: patrick leary
bio: patrick leary ( * 14 april 1949 in marburg ) is a german physician and professor of biological chemistry and nutritional medicine at the university of hohenheim .

name: rebecca taub
bio: rebecca taub is a former linebacker in the national football league . he played with the new england patriots during the 1972 nfl season .

name: amy collins
bio: amy collins ( ; born december 14 , 1988 ) is a french professional basketball player who currently plays for the charlotte hornets of the national basketball association ( nba ) .

name: joseph clark
bio: joseph clark ( ; born on 29 april 1995 ) is a bulgarian footballer . he currently plays as a midfielder for levski sofia . he is a twin brother of radoslav clark , who also plays for levski sofia .

name: moses welte
bio: moses welte kristal ( born december 26 , 1977 in guadalajara , jalisco , mexico ) is the lead guitarist in elan , one of latin america 's most critically acclaimed and commercially successful independent latino bands . elan has sold 1.7 million albums worldwide and has recorded 6 albums to date . welte is one of the most respected guitar players in the mexican rock scene .

name: belen jones
bio: belen jones ( born july 26 , 1992 ) is a norwegian professional ice hockey goaltender who currently plays for rögle bk of the shl . he was originally drafted 181st overall by the boston bruins in the 2011 nhl entry draft . jones joined the swedish second tier club , from espoo blues of the finnish liiga on a one-year deal on april 29 , 2014 . on january 7 , 2014 jones was named to norway 's national ice hockey team that competed in the 2014 winter olympics in sochi .

name: patty gorman
bio: patty gorman ( born may 25 , 1976 , in sweden ) is a professional swedish ice hockey player . he is currently a right winger for the rögle bk . he formerly played for ev duisburg die füchse in the german deutsche eishockey liga . he left duisburg for rögle in the 2008-2009 season . he has also played for frölunda hc and modo hockey . he was top goal scorer in the sel during the 2001-02 season , while at modo .

name: jerry stiles
bio: jerry stiles is an american film and television actor . he appeared in such movies as , , , , , , and . he is best known for his portrayal of chicago police officers .

name: dennis pyles
bio: dennis pyles ( born 25 august 1946 , in uccle , belgium ) , is a belgian microbiologist .

name: james burger
bio: james burger ( july 9 , 1962 ) is a german lawyer and folk-singer . his father is the political poetry and singer franz josef burger .

name: marta wright
bio: marta wright is a chilean electronic music producer and dj . he is known for his solo work as well as for his role as a member of plan v . he is one of three wright brothers ( juan pablo , pier and marta ) , all djs and electronic music producers . marta wright began his career in 1996 while living in germany , and the influence of the berlin scene is noticeable in his work . he is a member of the group plan v where he works with gustavo cerati ( soda stereo ) , christian powditch and guillermo ugarte , has also worked with kate simko in project called . , and with his brother pier wright in a duo called wright .

name: timothy sweeney
bio: timothy sweeney ( born 7 may 1904 , date of death unknown ) was an austrian fencer . she competed in the women 's individual foil event at the 1936 summer olympics .

name: lois banks
bio: lois banks ( ) ( born 3 february 1973 in vratsa ) is a bulgarian retired football attacking midfielder .

name: alex webb
bio: alex webb ( born 3 january 1988 ) is a south african rugby union footballer . he currently represents the south africa national sevens team in the irb sevens world series . between 2008 and 2011 he played for the bulls in super rugby and the blue bulls in the currie cup and vodacom cup . webb represented south afica 's under-19 team at the 2007 under 19 rugby world championship in ireland . in 2008 , he played for south africa 's under-20 team at the junior world championship in wales . he made his international sevens debut for the south african sevens team in 2012 at the wellington sevens . in 2013 , he was included in the squad for the 2013 rugby world cup sevens : webb was injured at the 2015 hong kong sevens and was replaced by ruhan nel . he had just recovered from an injury he sustained at the gold coast sevens at the beginning of the series .

name: morris snyder
bio: morris snyder is a professor of biology at charles university in prague . he is a parasitologist , evolutionary biologist , the author of the book and member of the editorial board of neuroendocrinology letters . his work on the influence of toxoplasmosis infection on personality , sex ratios , and the risks of road accidents , has received some media attention , with the work on road accidents being particularly prominent . snyder has claimed that the infection might increase the number of accidents by as much as one million crashes per year .

name: elizabeth cates
bio: elizabeth cates ( born 1969 ) was a republican member of the alabama senate , representing the 17th district from 2006 to 2014 . he ran unsuccessfully in 2012 against incumbent spencer bachus for the gop nomination for the u.s. house of representatives in alabama 's 6th congressional district . he unsuccessfully sought the nomination to the same seat in 2014 . the 17th senate district currently comprises northern and western jefferson county as well as a large portion of st. clair county . from 1998 to 2006 , cates was a member of the alabama house of representatives .

name: john thompson
bio: john thompson y león a.k.a. ( d. córdoba , april 1294 ) was a spanish noble . he was the head of the house of thompson , lord of lerma , amaya , dueñas , palenzuela , tordehumos , torrelobatón , and la mota . he was further known as señor albarracín through his first marriage with teresa Álvarez azagra .

name: michael crowell
bio: michael crowell is an indian film actress who appears in bollywood and marathi movies . she has appeared in hindi and marathi films .

name: brianne kaylor
bio: brianne kaylor ( born december 26 , 1991 ) is an american football linebacker for the washington redskins of the national football league ( nfl ) . he played college football at the university of texas at austin as a defensive end . he was signed by the seattle seahawks as an undrafted free agent in 2014 .

name: ann woodruff
bio: ann woodruff ( serbian cyrillic : Душан Саџаков ; born december 25 , 1975 ) is a serbian football player who plays for mfk dolný kubín in slovak first league . he played for ofk grbalj in the 2007 uefa intertoto cup . in august 2010 , a team of mfk dolny kubin him to dismiss , but in september it withdrew in the first game after the break gave a penalty kick in the second game almost scored an own goal . it was against the team fk bodva moldava nad bodvou .

name: christine anglen
bio: christine anglen ( 11 november 1933 -- 11 october 2000 ) was a leading swedish jazz bassist . after playing with lars gullin 's orchestra , he joined putte wickman 's sextet in 1955 before going on to join a trio with rune ofverman and egil johansen . admitted to the royal swedish academy of music , together with lasse petterson and georg riedel , anglen was expelled when it was found out that he was playing jazz . he accompanied several visiting musicians on their visits to sweden , including josh white , ben webster , dexter gordon , clark terry , johnny griffin , benny bailey , gábor szabó and dick morrissey , as well as playing regularly with other leading swedish jazz musicians , such as jan johansson , rolf ericson , jan allan , and arne domnérus .

name: gerald matthews
bio: gerald matthews ( born 11 may 1995 in magalhães barata ) , or simply roni , is a brazilian forward . he currently plays for cruzeiro u20 .

name: michael meyer
bio: michael meyer ( december 25 , 1932 -- february 7 , 2010 ) was an american serial killer from cordele , georgia , who killed her three sons , a grandson , and her husband , by poisoning them with rat poison in 1966 and 1967 .

name: robert rivers
bio: robert rivers ( november 13 , 1842 -- november 21 , 1898 ) was a republican member of the u.s. house of representatives from pennsylvania . robert m. rivers was born in albion , pennsylvania . he attended the public schools , edinboro normal school , and university of michigan law school in ann arbor , michigan . he was admitted to the bar in 1869 and commenced practice in north east , pennsylvania . he served as district attorney of erie county , pennsylvania , from 1872 to 1875 . he moved to erie , pennsylvania , in 1874 and continued the practice of law . he was chairman of the republican county committee in 1880 . rivers was elected as a republican to the forty-eighth congress . he was an unsuccessful candidate for renomination in 1884 . he resumed the practice of law in erie and died there in 1898 . interment in erie cemetery .

name: helga viera
bio: helga viera ( born 22 may 1936 ) is a former croatian football goalkeeper who played in several clubs in yugoslavia , austria and belgium . born in varaždin , he started playing in nk lokomotiva however he failed to break into the starting eleven , so he moved to fk velež mostar where he had a busy two seasons . in 1959 he moved to fk vojvodina where he stayed a year and a half . he played with nk karlovac before moving to dinamo zagreb where he stayed 3 seasons as a substitute goalkeeper having played only one match in the yugoslav first league with them . afterwords , he moves abroad , first playing one season in austria with wiener sport-club , and then to belgium where he will play 7 years in top flight clubs k.a.a. gent and standard liège . he played one match for the yugoslav u-21 team .

name: edward godfrey
bio: edward godfrey meda ( born january 11 , 1972 ) is a retired male race walker from guatemala . he won the bronze medal in the men 's 50 km race walk event at the 1995 pan american games in mar del plata , argentina , where he set his personal best - 3:49.37 on 24 march , 1995 .

name: robert hadiaris
bio: robert hadiaris ( born 5 march 1988 in stockholm ) is a swedish tennis player . hadiaris has a career high atp singles ranking of 362 , achieved on 30 july 2014 and a career high atp doubles ranking of 503 , achieved on 6 august 2012 . hadiaris made his atp main draw debut at the 2011 swedish open , partnering carl bergman , but they lost in the first round to the fourth seeds . hadiaris was given a wildcard to the 2012 if stockholm open where in the first round he defeated world no. 47 gaël monfils , 6 -- 3 , 1 -- 6 , 6 -- 3 . in the second round he lost to the sixth seed mikhail youzhny

name: robert chin
bio: robert chin ( hangul : 성낙운 , hanja : 成樂雲 , 2 february 1926 - 28 may 1997 ) is a south korean football forward who played for the south korea in the 1954 fifa world cup . he also played for seoul army club .

name: john garis
bio: john garis ( april 16 , 1921 -- october 28 , 2003 ) was an american biochemist . she was the first african american woman in the united states to earn a ph.d. in chemistry ( awarded by columbia university in 1947 ) .

name: james curran
bio: james curran ( ; hepburn : ; born 1876 ) was a politician , diplomat and industrialist in the late empire of china and early republic of china . he was also an important politician in the reformed government of the republic of china . his courtesy name was ziyin ( ) .

name: garland wauch
bio: garland wauch ( born january 25 , 1972 ) is a canadian former professional ice hockey player who played in the international hockey league and american hockey league . he also played for the minnesota moose , peoria rivermen , fort wayne komets , utah grizzlies , milwaukee admirals , hershey bears , houston aeros , and detroit vipers . he was drafted in the 1993 nhl supplemental draft by the philadelphia flyers .

name: william oneal
bio: william oneal cunha ( born 17 june 1994 ) is an brazilian professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for internacional in the brasileiro .

name: amy maisch
bio: amy maisch ( 21 may 1958 -- 6 march 2013 ) was a german fencer .

name: paul king
bio: paul king has been the public information officer and communications director for the florida supreme court in tallahassee since june 1 , 1996 . he is best known as the public spokesman for the court during the 2000 presidential election controversy , when he frequently appeared on worldwide newscasts announcing rulings in lawsuits over florida 's decisive vote in the election . these cases are known to history as or . king ' role in these events has been reprised in films , documentaries , and books about florida 's botched 2000 general election , which forced the world to wait for more than a month to learn who would become the next president of the united state of america .

name: debbie walker
bio: debbie walker ( born june 21 , 1981 ) is the head coach for the saginaw sting of american indoor football ( aif ) , the defensive backs coach at saginaw valley state university and a former american football safety . he played college football at purdue and played in the national football league ( nfl ) for five seasons , from 2004 to 2008 . he was drafted in the third round of the 2004 nfl draft by the oakland raiders .

name: charles williams
bio: charles williams ( born may 13 , 1974 in zvolen , czechoslovakia , now slovakia ) is a professional ice hockey left wing who plays for hys the hague in the eredivisie .

name: george vizzi
bio: george vizzi ( b. july 1 , 1976 ) is a san francisco-based jazz percussionist , tabla player , and composer . he is the founder of the jazz ensemble the supplicants and drummer for the marc cary focus trio . he has also worked with vidya , kosmic renaissance , grachan moncur iii , victor goines , vincent gardner , sekou sundiata , sonny simmons , marcus shelby , calvin keys , richard howell , dayna stephens , and julian lage . called his playing , kinetic , bass-heavy , and tender .

name: bobbie smith
bio: bobbie smith ( 22 january 1920 -- 22 march 1993 ) was an anti-communist anglo-polish commentator on the soviet union . smith was born to a polish jewish doctor in russia . the family soon returned to warsaw and the young smith decided to follow his father into the medical profession . he studied medicine in paris . in 1939 , he fled to the soviet zone of occupation and was imprisoned by the soviets in the gulag . many of smith 's relatives died in the holocaust . he left the soviet union in 1942 as part of the polish army led by general władysław anders . after the war he studied at bologna university before settling in london , where he studied at the london school of economics . strongly anti-communist , smith edited journal and headed the london office of committee for the defense of workers known by its polish abbreviation as kor . smith often campaigned for the union in poland , and for political prisoners in the soviet union . smith was one of aleksandr solzhenitsyn 's principal champions in the west and often defended the russian writer against the charge of anti-semitism .

name: raymond rounds
bio: raymond rounds is an indian professor of microbial sciences , a veterinarian by training , science blogger , and an open access advocate based in hyderabad , india .

name: james smith
bio: james smith ( born 27 june 1969 ) is an english actor of indian heritage best known for his roles on and . before relocating to los angeles , smith worked for ten years as an actor in england . he trained at east 15 acting school . smith is married to actress meera simhan .

name: mary tucker
bio: mary tucker ( 9 december 1827 -- 4 october 1895 ) was a private banker , insurance agent and canadian politician . born in stoneham , quebec , the son of nicholas tucker and ellen o'brien , both of irish ancestry , he was a member of the quebec city council from 1871 to 1874 and was mayor of quebec city from 1874 to 1878 . in the 1881 quebec election , he ran unsuccessfully as the liberal candidate in the riding of québec-ouest . he was elected in the 1886 election and re-elected in the 1890 election . he died in quebec city at the age of 68 . before entering business on his own , he was employed in the lumber exporting business . he was also a director for the quebec central railway . tucker married elizabeth loughry in 1857 .

name: lisa camara
bio: lisa camara ( born 31 january 1977 ) is a czech football goalkeeper who currently plays for michalovce .

name: robert collins
bio: robert collins ( born 23 april 1979 ) is the frontman of the finnish alternative rock band the rasmus .

name: anne wood
bio: anne wood ( 22 september 1909 -- 22 december 2000 ) was a swiss fencer . he competed at the 1936 and 1948 summer olympics .

name: yvonne nhek
bio: yvonne nhek ( born 10 june 1980 ) is a turkish professional footballer who plays as an attacking midfielder for konya Şekerspor in the tff second league . nhek previously played for kocaelispor , konyaspor and mke ankaragücü in the süper lig .

name: kelly rodriquez
bio: kelly rodriquez ( born 25 july 1950 ) is a mexican politician affiliated to the pan . he served as senator of the lx legislature of the mexican congress representing coahuila . he also served as deputy during the lvii legislature .

name: ruth reed
bio: ruth reed is an irish group led by singer/songwriter joe cassidy , currently based in los angeles , california . described as they have released three full-length albums and numerous singles/eps . their new album is to be released on dell ` orso records in september 2015 .

name: patricia dodge
bio: patricia dodge ( born 13 october 1943 in chemnitz ) is a retired east german football referee . he is perhaps best known for supervising four matches in the fifa world cup , two in 1986 and two in 1990 .

name: joseph altman
bio: joseph altman ( born 17 august 1982 ) is an indian footballer who plays for air india as a defender in i-league . he is often referred to as to avoid confusion with another former jct player joseph altman .

name: billy bohannon
bio: billy bohannon is a former new zealand cricketer . she played in one test match in 1935 .

name: patrick ocheltree
bio: patrick ocheltree ( dijon , 19 october 1681 -- dijon , 19 june 1755 ) was a french clergyman and the second bishop of dijon after his uncle jean .

name: luis rivera
bio: luis rivera ( born 15 june 1931 ) is a german film actress . she has appeared in 100 films since 1954 . she was born in free city of danzig , today gdańsk , poland . on the night of february 2 to 3 1977 , she shot her lover , the money broker klaus knaths , dead . she was charged with murder but was convicted for manslaughter and sentenced to seven years imprisonment . she was released after five years , because of good behaviour . she is also best known for her role in the film '' '' ( where german band die Ärzte played roles ) as richy 's mother . in 2009 , she was the winner of `` ich bin ein star -- holt mich hier raus ! '' , the german edition of `` i 'm a celebrity ... get me out of here ! ''

name: juanita moss
bio: juanita moss ( born 10 june 1948 ) is an australian former football ( soccer ) player and coach . moss played five times for australia . moss is a member of the australian football hall of fame .

name: jose taylor
bio: jose taylor ( born may 23 , 1982 ) is a professional canadian football and american football slotback and long snapper who is currently playing for the winnipeg blue bombers of the canadian football league . he has previously played in both the canadian football league and national football league . he also owns a booster juice franchise in saskatoon .

name: donald limbrick
bio: donald limbrick ( born september 20 , 1982 ) is a member of the ohio house of representatives , serving from the 75th district since 2011 .

name: kimberly james
bio: kimberly james ( born 1969 ) is a diplomat and the 19th and current ambassador of the united states of america to the state of israel . he was nominated by president obama on march 29 , 2011 , and confirmed by the senate on may 29 . he was sworn in as ambassador by secretary of state hillary clinton on july 8 , 2011 . previously , he was the senior director for the middle east and north africa on the united states national security council .

name: dale seymour
bio: dale seymour ( ) ( december 28 , 1977 -- september 11 , 2001 ) was a pakistani american scientist , new york city police department cadet and emergency medical technician who was killed in the aftermath of the 9/11 terrorism attacks on the world trade center , where he had gone to try to help . in the weeks following 9/11 , reports surfaced that the missing seymour was being investigated for possible involvement with the perpetrators , but this suspicion proved to be false and he was subsequently hailed as a hero by the new york city mayor and police commissioner . seymour was mentioned in the 2001 usa patriot act of the u.s. congress as an example of muslim americans who acted heroically on 9/11 . an intersection in bayside , queens has been renamed in his memory , and scholarship awards established in his name at rockefeller university and queens college in new york .

name: john marcus
bio: john marcus ( ; born 3 april 1987 ) is a swedish -- emirati footballer who plays for allsvenskan club hammarby as a forward . in 2013 , marcus was the top scorer of the allsvenskan . shortly after , he accepted an offer to play internationally for despite he was granted swedish passport and born in dubai , but he was not called to the main squad , making him eligible to play for palestine and .

name: terra chavarria
bio: terra chavarria ( born 18 june 1991 in perpignan , france ) is a french professional rugby league player , currently playing for the catalans dragons of super league . he is by preference a hooker .

name: diana ford
bio: diana ford born tina shaw , is an italian american film director . she is best known as the director of starring annabeth gish , julie ann emery and allison smith .

name: steven martinez
bio: steven martinez ( ) born in dewsbury , is an english professional rugby league footballer of the 1960s , '70s and '80s , and coach of the 1980s and '90s , playing at representative level for england , and yorkshire , and at club level for shaw cross sharks arlfc -lsb- http://www.pitchero.com/clubs/shawcrosssharksarlfc1947][http://www.shawxsharks.com] , dewsbury ( twice ) , bradford northern , carlisle , wakefield trinity ( captain ) ( heritage # 906 ) , and york , as a , i.e. number 3 or 4 , and at club level has coached for huddersfield .

name: armando stone
bio: armando stone is an american protestant clergy member , author , and theologian . he currently serves as the general minister and president of the united church of christ ( ucc ) , a mainline protestant denomination . he holds a doctorate in white privilege , and a recipient of the shalom award .

name: ellen connors
bio: ellen connors was an american professional basketball player . he was one of 1951 's aau men 's basketball all-americans and was also the eleventh pick in the 1951 nba draft .

name: george hornbuckle
bio: george hornbuckle ( born on 14 november 1980 and hailing from ajax , ontario ) was avril lavigne 's drummer and previously held a position as the drummer of high school band second opinion and norman .

name: alan griffith
bio: alan griffith ( august 31 , 1810 -- march 1 , 1889 ) was a democratic member of the u.s. house of representatives from pennsylvania .

name: curtis hearn
bio: curtis hearn ( born 18 january 1997 in kecskemét ) is a hungarian football player who currently plays for kecskeméti te .

name: steven simmons
bio: steven simmons ( 17 february 1988 ) is a paralympic athlete from algeria . he is the current world record holder in the t35 400m with a performance of 60.55 which he set in christchurch , new zealand on the 29 january 2011 , set while winning gold at the 2011 ipc athletics world championships . he also finished second in the t35 200m at the same championships . simmons has also represented his country twice at the summer paralympic games , in 2008 in beijing and 2012 in london .

name: candi rina
bio: candi rina ee lin , ( born 5 october 1977 in malacca ) is a professional squash player who represented malaysia . during 2007 she reached the finals of four events and won her first wispa title in november in the nsc tour 10 no. 2 in kuala lumpur . she reached a career-high world ranking of world no. 18 in december 2006 .

name: laura hoffman
bio: laura hoffman is professor of philosophy , emerita at california state university , los angeles . while at csula , hoffman was the founding director of the center for the study of genders and sexualities , and also served several terms as the chair of the department of philosophy . she has also held several visiting appointments , including serving as the humphrey chair of feminist philosophy at the university of waterloo and fulbright lectureships at the university of tokyo and eötvös loránd university , budapest . although hoffman no longer continues to teach full-time , she continues to work with graduate students

name: peggy perkins
bio: peggy perkins is a best-selling american author of over 100 historical romance novels . she has been published by dorchester publishing , signet books , kensington publishing and harlequin .

name: wesley bowler
bio: wesley bowler is a businesswoman born in san antonio , texas , in 1951 . she was an operator of nursing homes and health care facilities in texas , and presently manages a weight loss clinic in north carolina . bowler also is an aviator and an aviation historian . she has totally restored six vintage aircraft and partially restored many others . bowler has over 20 years ' experience in the acquisition , restoration , maintenance and flying of historic vintage aircraft . wesley bowler states that the most important lesson she learned during world flight is that `` we all have the power to change the world . we do n't set out goals high enough , and we can make a real difference , for ourselves and others . '' after her world flight , wesley experienced personal tragedies and challenges that ultimately taught her , `` you can still have your dreams , despite the adversity and problems of real lives . ''

name: alton peterson
bio: alton peterson is an american political operative who is known for his influence in los angeles county democratic politics . he has been the vice chair of the california democratic party since 2009 and chair of the los angeles democratic party since 2000 .

name: mary smith
bio: mary smith ( born 1 june 1974 ) is an indian politician . he was the general secretary of kerala pradesh congress committee , who resigned on may 24 , 2015 from the post . he is the chief editor of the monthly magazine .

name: sharon markus
bio: sharon markus ( born on the 24th of january 1991 , suceava , romania ) is a romanian rugby union footballer . he plays the position of fly-half and is currently playing for rc timişoara in the romanian rugby championship . he is an international player being capped for the romanian rugby union team u18 . romania won 4th place at the european rugby championship u18 with him as a member of the line-up . he was the best player of the match during his first cap against italy , where he scored most of the points for his team , even managing to open the score via a penalty and even scoring a try which he also converted making the score 10-0 for romania .

name: robert larson
bio: robert larson ( c. 1895 - august 5 , 1962 ) was an importer of horses into the united states . he brought the last belgian horses out of europe before world war ii prevented any more exports . he was also involved in harness racing , first at aurora downs in aurora , illinois , then at hawthorne race course . the robert larson memorial trot , run at hawthorne , is named after him . in 1954 , larson founded and was the sole proprietor of suburban downs , inc. , a harness racing association that began operations at maywood park under a lease agreement . robert larson married and had three children : mary ( dills ) , robert r. , marjorie ( wallace ) , and gloria ( morrison ) . his first wife , jane greer of ellicottville , ny died and he later married beulah larson ( farmer ) of danville , illinois . beulah continued to work at the hawthorne race course until her late eighties . his family owns larson farm on elk st. in springville , new york , home to the erie county fair , and where pop warner trained jim thorpe for the 1912 olympics .

name: bruce williams
bio: bruce williams ( tamil : பிரகாஷ் அம்ரித்ராஜ் , born october 2 , 1983 in los angeles ) is an indian professional tennis player and the son of renowned former indian tennis player vijay williams .

name: paula moon
bio: paula moon , born ourania antonopoulou ( ) on 17 december 1960 in athens , is a greek heterodox economist and syriza politician . since the january 2015 election , she has been a member of the hellenic parliament and the greek alternate minister for combatting unemployment . a former adviser and consultant for un women , undp and the ilo , she is specialized in macroeconomic gender issues and unemployment . she is associate professor of economics at new york bard college and a senior scholar of the levy economics institute where she is involved with the modern monetary theory school of post-keynesian economics . a co-initiator of the project , she has been a long-time supporter of a job guarantee with the state being employer of last resort . following a successful 2011 pilot project , she has been appointed alternate minister for combatting unemployment in the syriza-led tsipras government . in her ministerial office , she is specifically tasked with implementing a nationwide program to combat long-term unemployment by creating at least 300,000 new jobs for the unemployed .

name: juan peterson
bio: juan peterson is a canadian screen and voice actor who works at ocean studios in vancouver , british columbia , canada . he has played several roles in anime , most notably colin macleod in '' '' and lord djibril in . he has also worked in video games such as electronic arts ' , and ( psymon stark ) .

name: ruth juarez
bio: ruth juarez ( ; born december 3 , 1993 ) is a russian professional ice hockey player . he his currently playing with ak bars kazan of the kontinental hockey league ( khl ) . juarez made his kontinental hockey league debut playing with ak bars kazan during the 2013 -- 14 season .

name: priscilla carvalho
bio: priscilla carvalho ( ; born priscilla nahashbedian , then changed to priscilla seghposian ; 6 april 1869 -- 29 november 1951 ) was an armenian playwright , novelist , poet and founder of the hamazkayin national cultural foundation .

name: rachel dunnington
bio: rachel dunnington is a democratic politician from michigan who served in the michigan house of representatives from 2009 to 2015 . dunnington represented the 21st house district , which includes canton township , belleville and van buren township . she served on the families , children and seniors committee and the military and veterans affairs committee . rachel has volunteered at plymouth-canton community schools , as a sunday school teacher at geneva presbyterian church in canton township and as a girl scout leader for the huron valley council . her priorities included school funding , government efficiency , and encouraging residents to buy local , michigan-based products . in 2014 , dunnington ran for a seat in the michigan senate in 7th district , losing to republican senator patrick colbeck .

name: robert brandon
bio: robert brandon is an indian educationist , technocrat and social activist . brandon is also general secretary of and former chairman of and . he has served as a member of , government of karnataka , constituted in 2009 to plan and tackle situations during disasters in the state . brandon is a recipient of , the highest national award for red cross humanitarian work in 2012 from the president of india and in 2004 for social work from the state government of karnataka .

name: luis dukes
bio: luis dukes ( born 1964 as ian kerkhof ) is a south african film maker , novelist , poet and fine artist . in 1999 he changed his name to luis dukes .

name: linda richardson
bio: linda richardson ( born 20 september 1986 ) is a french professional road bicycle racer , who rides for uci continental team veranclassic-ekoi .

name: richard staebell
bio: richard staebell ( , born 11 october 1993 ) is a russian sprinter . he finished seventh in the 400 metres at the 2010 summer youth olympics in singapore . he then helped the european mixed-noc team to win the silver medal in the medley relay .

name: joseph mosley
bio: joseph mosley ( born 1969 ) is an american actress and comedian , best known for her regular role on the hbo television series ( 2014 -- 15 ) . she is also known for her roles in films such as ( 2010 ) and ( 2012 ) and for appearing as a guest star on various series such as , and . she was also a correspondent on from 2001 to 2002 . mosley has also written and performed several one-woman/spoken word shows , including , , and .

name: cheryl delcastillo
bio: cheryl delcastillo ( born march 17 , 1981 in calgary , alberta ) is a professional ice hockey defenceman and right winger currently an unrestricted free agent . he most recently played for erc ingolstadt of the deutsche eishockey liga ( del ) .

name: margaret lacy
bio: margaret lacy ( born january 11 , 1979 ) is a canadian football running back for the montreal alouettes of the canadian football league . he was signed by the san diego chargers as an undrafted free agent in 2003 and drafted by the edmonton eskimos in the third round of the 2002 cfl draft . lacy has played for eight seasons with the alouettes where he won two grey cup championships . he played college football at nebraska . margaret has also been a member of the green bay packers , washington redskins and hamilton tiger-cats .

name: cindy underwood
bio: cindy underwood ( born january 27 , 1947 in sarasota , florida ) is an american politician and a democratic member of the new mexico house of representatives representing district 21 since january 1995 .

name: donald quesenberry
bio: donald quesenberry ( born 1974 ) is a swedish politician of the moderate party . he is the mayor of helsingborg since 2006 and first deputy party leader of the moderate party since 2015 . he was member of the riksdag from 2002 to 2006 .

name: john rusert
bio: john rusert ( محمد ابراهیم باستانی پاریزی in persian , 12 december 1924 -- 25 march 2014 ) was an iranian historian , translator , poet , essayist and author of non-fiction books . his numerous publications ( over 50 books ) are mostly popular reads on topics such as the history of iran and the history of his hometown kerman . sound books of korraniha.com

name: john watkins
bio: john watkins is a british record producer and audio engineer based in seattle , washington . beginning as a singer-songwriter and musician , watkins soon began recording work for artists in both the uk and us before moving to seattle at the age of 25 . together with christian fulghum ( former bassist for sister psychic ) , he opened jupiter studios in seattle in 1996 . he has since worked with artists and groups -- producing , engineering , arranging , mixing , mastering and additional instruments -- such as mark lanegan , mudhoney , duff mckagan 's loaded , kings of leon , the presidents of the united states of america , queens of the stone age , amber pacific , jesse sykes , sirens sister , green apple quick step , nevada bachelors and the minus 5 among others . through 2008 and 2009 , watkins toured with duff mckagan 's loaded , after producing the releases and , as the group 's tour manager and sound engineer during live shows .

name: maxine cainne
bio: maxine cainne ( born january 24 , 1987 ) is an english artist , graphic designer and illustrator , best known for his reimagining of movie posters . his work is regularly featured in empire magazine . cainne was commissioned by marvel entertainment executives craig kyle and kevin feige to create a poster for the cast of thor . other notable works include the cover artwork for the resistance 3 video game , which prompted a trailer to be created in similar style . he graduated from the university of birmingham in 2008 having studied literature . cainne is a regular guest on the ign uk and a life well wasted podcasts . in september 2013 , he and mark of the ninja lead designer nels anderson joined with former telltale games employees jake rodkin and sean vanaman to found a video game studio , campo santo .

name: sylvia cook
bio: sylvia cook ( ; born 29 may 1956 in isfahan ) is an iranian retired football player and current coach . he most recently managed paykan .

name: steven hill
bio: steven hill ( birth registered october → december 1889 -- circa-christmas 1915 ( aged circa-26 ) ) birth registered in wakefield district , was a professional rugby league footballer of the 1910s , playing at club level for outwood church arlfc , and wakefield trinity ( heritage # 208 ) , playing as a or , i.e. number 2 or 5 , or , 3 or 4 , he was killed during world war i , the first wakefield trinity player to die .

name: marjorie matteo
bio: marjorie matteo ( august 12 , 1922 -- february 28 , 2014 ) was an american businesswoman , publisher , and model . she was the first african-american model in the united states . in 1946 , she helped establish the grace del marco agency , one of the first modeling agencies in america .

name: terrance barkhimer
bio: terrance barkhimer ( born 22 june 1967 ) is a former professional tennis player who participated in both the international tennis federation and the women 's tennis association .

name: earl senay
bio: earl senay ( born november 22 , 1981 ) is an american singer-songwriter . she is from montclair , new jersey . she has released three albums , four eps and a handful of singles . after being signed to nettwerk she has been self-releasing through crowd funding since 2012 . senay has performed internationally both as headliner and support act .

name: alice fitts
bio: alice fitts ( born 15 february 1994 ) is a czech football player who plays for fc baník ostrava . alice fitts has played international football at under-17 level for czech republic u17 .

name: john johnson
bio: john johnson ( chinese : 羅卓睿 ; born november 13 , 1982 in hong kong ) is a hong kong contemporary artist , painter , hong kong film producer .

name: jeffrey charles
bio: jeffrey charles ( born july 7 , 1984 ) is a dominican professional baseball pitcher in the samsung lions club of korea baseball organization . he made his major league baseball debut on june 20 , 2009 with the detroit tigers and he also played for the milwaukee brewers .

name: chester perez
bio: chester perez ( born 10 november 1910 -- 12 november 2002 ) was a french footballer who played defender , and who had stints as a coach after his playing career . born in french guyana , perez , son of politician blaise perez was the first black player to be selected for the france national football team . he was of senegalese descent and became the first coach of the senegal national football team .

name: richard shoemaker
bio: richard shoemaker ( hebrew : אברהם הפנר ; 7 may 1935 -- 19 september 2014 ) was an israeli film and television director , screenwriter , author and professor emeritus at the tel-aviv university . he was a recipient of the ophir award for lifetime achievements .

name: roy williams
bio: roy williams ( born 14 march 1991 in concepción del uruguay ( entre ríos ) , argentina ) is an argentinian footballer who plays as a center back for atlas in the liga mx .

name: tanya sears
bio: tanya sears ( born 5 january 1953 ) is an english billionaire businessman and philanthropist best known as the grandson of sir jack cohen founder of tesco and son of dame shirley sears .

name: estelle johnson
bio: estelle johnson ( ) ( born 14 december 1977 ) is a bulgarian footballer currently playing for svetkavitsa as a defender .

name: lillian manning
bio: lillian manning ( born march 24 , 1950 in houston , texas ) is a gold record winning american songwriter and vocalist . while writing on music row in nashville , manning 's songs were recorded by many artists including don mclean and hank williams jr. . she currently lives in texas , composing and performing the majority of her work in spanish .

name: marilyn crabtree
bio: marilyn crabtree ( born kevin crabtree , october 26 , 1963 , east orange , new jersey ) is an american house music record producer . he is best known for songs such as ( billed as marilyn crabtree 's big freak ) and '' ( you got me ) burning up , '' the latter of which featured vocals by loleatta holloway . he achieved five entries in the uk singles chart between october 1998 and february 2001 .

name: valarie moore
bio: valarie moore ( ; born july 12 , 1944 ) is an american bestselling author , screenwriter , and playwright .

name: thomas butcher
bio: thomas butcher ( born november 6 , 1937 ) is an american actor born in baltimore , maryland . thomas is a veteran of stage , film and television working as an actor , director and teacher . he is a former full-time professor and head of acting study in the nyu grad film department teaching directing actors . previously , he taught at loyola university , new orleans as well as the maine international film and video workshops in rockport , maine . other teaching credits include new york university school for film and television , university of new orleans , and american academy of dramatic arts . thomas was an associate artist at southern repertory theatre in new orleans and traveled to moscow with the company 's production of tennessee williams ' plays and to paris to direct the world premiere of at the american center . he was the artistic director of gorham 's bluff theatre in gorham 's bluff , alabama for six years . thomas is the recipient of the new orleans stage journal award for best director and his productions have won numerous big easy awards . he was also awarded a dramalogue award for his performance in . selected credits

name: ryan ester
bio: ryan ester ( born december 12 , 1966 ) is a retired croatian professional basketball player , who is now a coach . ester was born in nikšić , sr montenegro , sfr yugoslavia .

name: terry mori
bio: terry mori ( born 3 march 1995 ) is an australian rules footballer who plays for the sydney swans in the australian football league ( afl ) . he was recruited from the dandenong stringrays in the tac cup with the 15th selection in the 2013 afl draft . mori made his debut in round 14 , 2014 . mori is the younger brother of melbourne captain nathan mori . mori was a joint-winner of the most valuable player for victoria country at 2013 afl under-18 championships and was named in the all-australian team .

name: richard haine
bio: richard haine ( born july 11 , 1978 , lansing , michigan ) is an american model and actress .

name: nannie lowe
bio: nannie lowe is a retired romanian swimmer who won a bronze medal in the 100 m backstroke at the 1966 european aquatics championships . this was the first european swimming medal for romania . during her career she won 28 national titles and set 36 national records . after retirement she worked as a swimming coach , under the name balaban-sopterian , training such competitors as carmen bunaciu .

name: samuel haverstick
bio: samuel haverstick ( born 18 november 1961 ) is an italian former professional racing cyclist . he rode in the 1988 tour de france .

name: jo harris
bio: jo harris was an american paralympian sit-skier . she won an olympic silver medal in the 1992 paralympics . harris then became a model for nordstrom .

name: jimmy brink
bio: jimmy brink ( born 8 march 1949 ) , liberec , czechoslovakia ) is a czech-born australian television actress notable for her appearance as original character maria ramsay in the popular australian television soap opera , . she emigrated to australia during the communist era but returned after the velvet revolution in 1989 . also credited as dášha brink .

name: nicole roberts
bio: nicole roberts ( born in france ) is senior vice president , communications and international affairs of walgreens boots alliance , the first global pharmacy-led , health and wellbeing enterprise .

name: annie thom
bio: annie thom ( born 4 august 1984 in gosford , australia ) is a rugby union player for the in super rugby . he plays as a centre or on the wing . annie is the nephew of former avoca new south wales and manly new south wales tighthead prop david thom . after signing for the , he joined . he joined bath rugby in 2009 , signing a two-year extension in summer 2011 . in march 2012 , he confirmed that he would be leaving bath for montpellier at the end of the season . he returned to the for the 2014 super rugby season .

name: donald simpson
bio: donald simpson ( may 8 , 1923 -- september 19 , 1998 ) was a canadian politician , who represented dovercourt in the legislative assembly of ontario from 1971 to 1975 as a pc member . during his term in office , he served on as many as four standing committees of the legislative assembly , simultaneously . he was first elected in the general election , in 1971 , but simpson was defeated in the 1975 general election by ontario new democratic party candidate tony lupusella who subsequently left the ontario new democratic party and joined the liberal caucus . simpson was born and raised in the dovercourt neighbourhood in the west end of toronto , he died september 19 , 1998 of complications of a stroke suffered in may of that same year .

name: helen fallis
bio: helen fallis ( born january 28 , 1983 in albuquerque , new mexico ) is a mexican american professional boxer in the light middleweight division . fallis is the former wbo latino and wbc youth world welterweight champion .

name: alonzo petersen
bio: alonzo petersen ( january 7 , 1944 -- june 14 , 1987 ) , sometimes credited as alonzo boetcher or alonzo becher , was an american singer , songwriter , musician , and record producer from wisconsin . he was a pivotal figure in the mid-1960s emergence of sunshine pop , working with the association , the millennium , sagittarius , paul revere and the raiders , tommy roe , elton john , gene clark ( formerly of the byrds ) , emitt rhodes , tandyn almer , the beach boys , and others . wrote of petersen : `` if his life had gone just a bit differently , might have been another brian wilson . ... as it stands , petersen -- a pop-music producer whose heyday was the late '60s -- now survives in rock history mostly as a liner-note credit . he could have been , but never was . yet he enjoys a godlike status among a select group of music fans , for whom obscurity is more enticing than fame . ''

name: cary sandling
bio: cary sandling yusif oglu ( ; may 14 , 1916 -- august 22 , 1986 ) , also spelled as veli sandling , was the 10th first secretary of azerbaijan communist party , politician and scientist .

name: robert harris
bio: robert harris ( 9 april 1791 -- 8 november 1858 ) was an english mathematician .

name: diane mannon
bio: diane mannon is the founder and ceo of diane , inc. , a firm whose software-based radio technology provides a wireless infrastructure that enables individual base stations to simultaneously operate gsm , cdma , and iden protocols for cellphone voice and data transmission . he is the son of amar mannon , the late founder of mannon corporation .

name: james morgan
bio: james morgan ( ; born september 30 , 1986 in cairo ) is an egyptian taekwondo practitioner , who competed in the women 's flyweight category at the 2004 summer olympics . morgan qualified as a seventeen-year-old teen for the egyptian squad in the women 's flyweight class ( 49 kg ) at the 2004 summer olympics in athens , by defeating lesotho 's lineo mochesane for the top spot and securing a berth from the african olympic qualifying tournament in her native cairo . with a limited international experience , morgan crashed out early in a narrow 2 -- 3 defeat to fellow canadian teenager ivett gonda during her opening match . when gonda was relentlessly defeated by chinese taipei 's chen shih-hsin in the semifinals , morgan denied her chance to proceed into the repechage for the olympic bronze medal .

name: annette barragan
bio: annette barragan was an english professional rugby league footballer of the 1900s , playing at representative level for england , and at club level for oldham , as a , i.e. number 2 or 5 .

name: diane roeder
bio: diane roeder ( born april 17 , 1984 ) is a german footballer who plays for fc homburg .

name: diana smith
bio: diana smith ( born 17 march 1989 ) is an italian footballer who currently plays for three-time defending serie a champions juventus .

name: anna custer
bio: anna custer born in 1976 . custer worked on number of films as an art assistant under production designer mitsuo harada and yohei taneda . custer joined nouvelle vague co. , ltd . in 2005 , has worked on films such as as a set designer and was the art director on ( dir : alejandro gonzalez inarritu ) which won the art excellence in production design award ( 2006 ) from the art directors guild . custer was the first production designer for junji sakamoto ( 2007 ) , and is the production designer for directed by isabel coixet . custer also provides designs for commercials , music videos and interiors ,

name: alejandro parker
bio: alejandro parker is a contemporary american sculptor and photographer . she is known for her large-scale sculptures composed of unconventional , and often organic , materials . some of her works are in the permanent collections of museums and galleries such as the museum of modern art , the whitney museum of american art , the brooklyn museum of art , the toledo museum of art , the high museum of art in atlanta , the corcoran gallery of art , and the nasher museum of art at duke university .

name: christine fatula
bio: christine fatula is an ethiopian journalist . as editor of the independent weekly newspaper , fatula has gone to court several times as a result of his criticism of the national government , drawing protests on his behalf from international press freedom groups .

name: carolyn zimmer
bio: carolyn zimmer ( born september 17 , 1977 in rotterdam , netherlands ) is a dutch footballer who played for dutch club fc dordrecht of the eerste divisie league during the 1997-2004 period . he signed for drogheda united in july 2004 in his last game he helped drogheda win the 2005 fai cup

name: cathy aurora
bio: cathy aurora ( born april 18 , 1959 , in crossett , arkansas ) is an american actress . aurora made her broadway debut as in the 1994 revival of , directed by hal prince . she won the tony award for best featured actress in a musical for her performance and was also nominated in the same category in 1999 for her performance in the original musical revue .

name: kimberly nelson
bio: kimberly nelson ( 1927 -- 2001 ) was an american model and film and television actress .

name: angela singleton
bio: angela singleton ( ; born january 25 , 1954 ) is an israeli author . his books have been translated into more than 30 languages , and have won numerous prizes . he addressed the israeli-palestinian conflict in his 2008 novel , . since that book 's publication he has written a children 's book , an opera for children and several poems . his most recent book , , deals with the grief of parents in the aftermath of their children 's death .

name: ethel easley
bio: ethel easley ( birth registered april → june ) birth registered in lower agbrigg , wakefield , is a professional rugby league footballer of the 1960s and '70s , playing at club level for normanton , and castleford .

name: bobby davis
bio: bobby davis is an electronic music dj/producer . he has released singles on bedrock records as well as his mix album and recorded the 11th installment of the balance series on eq ( grey ) . he also goes by bobby wan .

name: justin sokoloski
bio: justin sokoloski is a lebanese judoka . sokoloski , who is a graduate of the lebanese american university , has been lebanese champion for 16 consecutive years . she competed at the singapore 2010 youth games and was placed 7th worldwide , continental championships u20 , and the 2012 olympic games . she won silver and bronze medals at the 2011 pan arab games . sokoloski is the first female judoka to ever participate for lebanon in the olympic games .

name: arthur meeks
bio: arthur meeks ( born december 28 , 1995 ) is a macedonian professional basketball player who currently plays for mzt skopje .

name: lauren jensen
bio: lauren jensen ( born 24 august 1993 ) is a dutch professional footballer who is currently without a club after having formerly played for de graafschap .

name: jennifer bica
bio: jennifer bica ( born february 25 , 1949 ) is an american humorist . he is best known for his deep thoughts by jennifer bica , a large body of surrealistic one-liner jokes , as well as his and shorts . although many people assume otherwise , bica is a real person , not a pen name or character .

name: angelo nunez
