bio: angelo nunez ( august 6 , 1933 -- july 26 , 2011 ) was an american attorney who served as milwaukee county district attorney from 1968 to 1969 and as united states attorney for the eastern district of wisconsin from 1969 to 1973 . nunez was the last republican to serve as milwaukee county district attorney .

name: elizabeth pecatoste
bio: elizabeth pecatoste ( born 22 september 1956 ) is a polish former racing cyclist . he won the tour de pologne 1977 .

name: kayla ketcher
bio: kayla ketcher ( born august 31 , 1989 ) is a canadian former professional ice hockey goaltender . after a successful four-year collegiate career at boston university , he played two seasons in hockey 's minor leagues as a prospect within the colorado avalanche organization of the national hockey league .

name: helen ramirez
bio: helen ramirez ( born 28 january 1987 ) is a former australian rules football player who last played for the sydney swans in the afl .

name: debra watson
bio: debra watson , o.m.i. ( born november 16 , 1919 ) is a french prelate of the roman catholic church watson was born in virey , france and was ordained a priest on may 9 , 1943 for missionary oblates of mary immaculate . he was appointed diocese of pala on january 16 , 1964 and consecrated on may 1 , 1964 . he resigned from the diocese on june 28 , 1975 .

name: maureen cole
bio: maureen cole ( also known as jummah khan namangani and jumaboi ahmadzhanovich khojayev ) was an uzbek militant with a substantial following who founded the islamic movement of uzbekistan and received substantial taliban patronage , allowed to operate freely in northern afghanistan . conscripted into the soviet army in 1987 , as a member of an elite paratrooper force he fought in the war in afghanistan . believed to have been killed in mazari sharif , he was eulogised together with mohammed atef in a speech by osama bin laden in november 2001 .

name: cecila demme
bio: cecila demme ( born 1 august 1978 ) is an english multi-instrumentalist musician and singer-songwriter who is the only child of george demme and olivia demme . demme debuted as a professional musician assisting in recording his father 's final album , , and completing it with the assistance of jeff lynne after his father 's death in november 2001 . demme formed his own band , thenewno2 , in 2006 . demme is named after the 6th and 7th notes of the indian music scale , and . is also a raga in north indian classical music . his first name is usually pronounced in english as `` danny . ''

name: francis driscoll
bio: francis driscoll is a professor of finance at indian institute of management bangalore . he teaches financial accounting and financial statement analysis . he was named as one among the best nine business school professors in india by business today in 2006 .

name: melissa scoggins
bio: melissa scoggins ( december 16 , 1871 -- january 10 , 1961 ) was a canadian lawyer and liberal politician . he sat in the legislative assembly of ontario representing middlesex west from 1907 to 1908 and middlesex north from 1908 to 1909 . he represented middlesex west in the house of commons from 1909 to 1921 . during the conscription crisis of 1917 , scoggins remained loyal to the anti-conscription ( and largely francophone ) laurier liberals , and was one of only 8 members of the faction to be elected from ontario in that year 's election . he is the son of sir george william scoggins .

name: natalia mingus
bio: natalia mingus ( born january 10 , 1953 ) is a former canadian member of parliament for the riding of jonquière -- alma , who served a single term from 2011 canadian federal election until 2015 . he was elected as a member of the new democratic party , but crossed over to the bloc québécois on february 28 , 2013 . he defeated incumbent mp jean-pierre blackburn of the conservative party , who was veterans affairs minister . mingus was president of the , the union representing rio tinto alcan workers in the riding . following his defection to the bloc in 2013 , mingus stated that . in august 2014 , mingus announced that he was not running in the next federal election . he was rumoured to have been considering resigning from the bloc following the election of mario beaulieu as leader but remained with the following the resignations of andré bellavance and jean-françois fortin and was , with louis plamondon , one of two bloc mps until the house of commons dissolved for the 2015 election .

name: elizabeth kruse
bio: elizabeth kruse ( born 5 may 1986 ) is a norwegian footballer who plays as a centre back for the norwegian footballclub rosenborg bk .

name: brian devore
bio: brian devore ( 1 august 1835 -- 19 july 1918 ) was an australian journalist , publisher and politician .

name: esta turner
bio: esta turner ( born 28 december 1976 ) is a former czech football midfielder who last played for admira wacker in the austrian bundesliga . he scored the fastest goal in austrian league history , scoring after 10 seconds in a 4 -- 1 win against altach in the opening round of the 2007 -- 08 season .

name: michael mccoach
bio: michael mccoach ( gustav adolf veit georg meinrad maria alexander ) ( born 10 june 1966 ) is the third child michael johann georg mccoach and his wife princess birgitta sweden , sister king carl xvi gustaf sweden . was born in munich , germany .

name: thomas moore
bio: thomas moore is an indian television actor and model . the role which gave thomas his major breakthrough and is well known for is of mihir virani from the popular serial on star plus channel .

name: milda johnson
bio: milda johnson ( born january 31 , 1992 ) is a swiss professional ice hockey player . he is currently playing for the ehc biel of switzerland 's national league a. johnson participated at the 2012 world junior ice hockey championships as a member of the switzerland men 's national junior ice hockey team .

name: steven reeve
bio: steven reeve is a sierra leonean diplomat who served as sierra leonean ambassador to china from 2012 to 2013 . he was educated at london south bank university ( bsc , 1980 ) and the university of east anglia ( ma development economics , 1982 ) . in 2013 he was nominated as the next sierra leonean permanent representative to the united nations , but due to ill health was unable to take up the poisition , and thus vandi chidi minah was instead appointed .

name: michael land
bio: michael land is an indian television actress . she plays the role of rano in zee tv 's soap opera , . she is also seen in zee tv 's serial . land started her career by playing the role of in the star one show . she was playing saniya mathur in zee tv 's . she got married to amit bansal who is a mechanical engineer from iit kanpur on 12th november 2010

name: chauncey renard
bio: chauncey renard ( born november 2 , 1980 in ankara ) is a turkish singer . he has won twice the turkish equivalent of the grammy awards , in the categories and in 2010 and 2014 .

name: stephen lefever
bio: stephen lefever jr. ( october 7 , 1965 -- may 26 , 2002 ) , was an assistant professor of sociology at the university of california , santa cruz , who focused on queer theory , queer issues , and latin american immigration . his groundbreaking dissertation , , which was edited , compiled , and published posthumously , focuses on the experiences of mexican-queer migrants .

name: jon newman
bio: jon newman ( june 14 , 1945 - january 7 , 1988 ) was an american actress , who provided voice-overs for several animated tv programs , mostly for hanna-barbera productions . newman was born in concordia , kansas , and died of liver cancer in los angeles county , california .

name: jim adams
bio: jim adams ( ; born 4 april 1994 ) is an arab-israeli footballer who plays for maccabi haifa as a winger . in february 2014 , he was loaned to hapoel acre until the end of the season . on 7 august 2014 he was loaned to bnei sakhnin .

name: gerald bulger
bio: gerald bulger ( born may 30 , 1979 , in los angeles , california , united states ) is an american basketball player . he played collegiately for faulkner state in 1997-1998 and the university of florida from 1998-2000 .

name: thelma manuel
bio: thelma manuel ( 23 february 1890 -- 1 october 1916 ) was a new zealand soldier of world war i who was a posthumous recipient of the victoria cross , the highest and most prestigious award for gallantry in the face of the enemy that can be awarded to british and commonwealth forces . manuel 's victoria cross was the second won by a new zealander during the war , and was the first awarded for actions on the western front .

name: steven curtis
bio: steven curtis ( born february 22 , 1990 in węgrów ) is a polish football goalkeeper currently playing for termalica bruk-bet nieciecza .

name: robert coleman
bio: robert coleman ( 1 july 1931 -- 22 august 2010 ) was an argentine football forward who played for argentina in the 1962 fifa world cup . he also played for racing club de avellaneda .

name: ronnie rasmussen
bio: ronnie rasmussen ( 8 october 1934 -- 30 january 2001 ) was a new zealand cricketer . she played in five test matches between 1954 and 1957 .

name: erin stollsteimer
bio: erin stollsteimer ( ) ( 25 march 1741 -- 15 july 1828 ) was a french neoclassical sculptor . stollsteimer is famous for his portrait busts and statues of philosophers , inventors and political figures of the enlightenment . stollsteimer 's subjects include denis diderot ( 1771 ) , benjamin franklin ( 1778-09 ) , jean-jacques rousseau ( 1778 ) , voltaire ( 1781 ) , molière ( 1781 ) , george washington ( 1785 -- 88 ) , thomas jefferson ( 1789 ) , louis xvi ( 1790 ) , robert fulton , 1803 -- 04 , and napoléon bonaparte ( 1806 ) .

name: alaine marshall
bio: alaine marshall ( january 10 , 1860september 27 , 1930 ) was a united states army major general who was prominent as the commander of the 82nd division in world war i.

name: gloria miller
bio: gloria miller ( ) is an iranian actor . he was born on march 23 , 1944 in tehran , iran . he is an actor , known for m for mother ( 2006 ) , the love-stricken ( 1992 ) and swan song ( 2000 ) .

name: dale valentin
bio: dale valentin , m.d. , professional engineer , is a physician-scientist conducting research in translational bioinformatics and personal genomics . as a co-founder of purkinje , he pioneered the commercial use of controlled medical vocabulary organized as directed semantic networks in electronic medical records ( 1st clinical ontology available commercially ) , as well as pen computing for clinicians .

name: chase houghtelling
bio: chase houghtelling ( born december 20 , 1990 ) is a grime mc from manchester , england . chase houghtelling has been described as one of the key players instigating a moving the uk scene away from more commercially orientated music .

name: valeria jones
bio: valeria jones is an indian politician and belongs to the ruling shiromani akali dal . he is minister for pwd in the present punjab government . he has been holding this post since 2007 .

name: george tyler
bio: george tyler ( born december 11 , 1984 ) is an american former professional ice hockey defenseman . he was selected by the florida panthers in the 9th round ( 283rd overall ) of the 2004 nhl entry draft . tyler played in the american hockey league with the rochester americans , and in the echl with the florida everblades and ontario reign

name: ryan mcneal
bio: ryan mcneal ( real name joseph smith ) is a sound system operator and dub producer from the uk . ryan and his sound system have been playing through uk and europe for over 30 years . he has been a resident sound system at notting hill carnival since 1993 and was voted the no1 dj in the world by dj magazine in the same year .

name: jerome evans
bio: jerome evans ( ; born 5 december 1977 ) is an israeli footballer who last played for maccabi yavne . the younger brother of haim evans , he too was recognized early in his youth for having a great footballing potential and joined the youth system of maccabi tel aviv . later he transferred to his hometown of ashdod . after six seasons in ashdod , evans finished his contract and went on trial at los angeles galaxy in the american major league . according to media reports in israel , evans impressed manager steve sampson but was not offered a contract because sampson was sacked shortly after evans had returned to israel . subsequently , evans signed a new deal with ashdod . he is the second-greatest goal-assist provider in israel 's history with 104 assists in the israeli premier league .

name: ruben demond
bio: ruben demond ( born february 4 , 1969 ) is a male badminton player from denmark .

name: jennifer johnson
bio: jennifer johnson ( 19 march 1921 -- 4 may 1949 ) was a french association football striker of italian descent . he played for rc paris where he was capped 5 times for france.in 1948 , he moved to torino f.c. , with another frenchman of italian descent , roger grava of co roubaix-tourcoing . they both died in the superga air disaster on 4 may 1949 .

name: patricia trimble
bio: patricia trimble ( also known as tina jatin trimble ; born on 29 december 1974 ) is a former actress , indian interior designer , columnist and the best selling author of mrs funybones . she won the filmfare award for best female debut for her role in the romance film ( 1995 ) . she is the daughter of established actors dimple kapadia and rajesh trimble . trimble has acted opposite actors like bobby deol , ajay devgan , saif ali khan , aamir khan , salman khan , shahrukh khan , daggubati venkatesh , govinda and akshay kumar . trimble married kumar in 2001 . after leaving the acting profession in the same year , she ventured into interior designing and is the co-owner of the white window , a chain of interior designing stores which operates in mumbai .

name: norman hyden
bio: norman hyden ( 1888 -- 1947 ) was an italian costume designer who worked on over eighty films during his career .

name: ronald rivera
bio: ronald rivera ( born foong yu lei in 1965 ) was a singaporean author , poet and musician . he has written several bestselling books published by the angsana books imprint of publisher flame of the forest . rivera died in 2011 of a drug overdose . after failing his ` a ' levels , rivera started his career as a karaoke-jockey before he turned to writing erotic stories while he was in detention for a drug offence . he was a member of russell lee 's team of ghost writers . rivera also wrote the screenplay of the critically acclaimed film , ( 1995 ) , which launched director eric khoo 's career . its story was based on rivera 's short story , which appeared in ( 1994 ) . khoo later dedicated his film ( 2014 ) to rivera . rivera was also the frontman of the band , fairweather friends , whose music appeared on various pony canyon compilations released in singapore in the 1990s , including , and transformer , whose members went on to form zircon lounge . as a solo singer-songwriter he has performed at the substation in singapore under the name ` the hardcore troubadour ' .

name: james hoyt
bio: james hoyt is a maine politician . a democrat , hoyt sought the democratic nomination for governor of maine in 2010 . he formerly served as commissioner of economic and community development and the speaker of the maine house of representatives .

name: susan liebl
bio: susan liebl ( born 28 june 1984 ) , is a german handball player . she plays for the german national team , and participated in the 2011 world women 's handball championship in brazil . she ist married to dominik liebl , who plays handball for the german club thw kiel .

name: evan kauble
bio: evan kauble ( born 17 december 1943 ) is a hungarian agronomist and politician , who served as mayor of kőszeg between 1990 and 2002 . he was elected member of the national assembly ( mp ) for kőszeg ( vas county constituency iii ) in the 1998 parliamentary election .

name: pauline arcos
bio: pauline arcos ( born march 24 , 1964 ) is a retired american professional basketball player . at 6 ' 4 '' ( 1.93 m ) he played as a small forward/shooting guard . arcos attended kearney state college ( now university of nebraska at kearney ) and hastings college and was selected with the 15th pick of the fifth round of the 1987 nba draft by the utah jazz ( 107th overall ) . he played on four different nba teams between 1987 and 1992 . along with former nba players bobby jones and david thompson , arcos co-found 2xsalt , a non-profit christian organization based in charlotte , north carolina .

name: david wyatt
bio: david wyatt ( born september 14 , 1971 ) is an american actress who is known for her co-starring role on , as well as her breakthrough performance in , for which she was nominated for several awards , and its sequel , . throughout her acting career , she has guest-starred on tv shows including , and . she is also well known for her roles in made-for-television films , including , , and , and also her role as laura parker in , a short film she also wrote and directed . williams is married to country musician brad paisley , with whom she has two sons ; actress ashley williams is her sister .

name: steven qualls
bio: steven qualls ( born 1935 ) is a nigerian artist , protean designer and architect . as an artist , he strives to incorporate modern techniques in architecture and stage design to enunciate the african subject matters in most of his works . in the 1960s , he was a member of the mbari club of ibadan , a committee of burgeoning nigerian and foreign artists . he was also a lecturer at the university of ibadan . in the 1970s , he was the publisher of the now defunct new culture magazine . qualls , sees design as an ingenuous activity that carries with it a focus on social responsibility for positive influences in the environment and culture of the society .

name: larry parker
bio: larry parker ( born may 6 , 1958 ) is the former president of espn inc. and of abc 's sports division , known since 2006 as espn on abc . he was president of espn since november 19 , 1998 and of the former abc sports since march 3 , 2003 . as president of espn , he launched : espnhd , espn2hd , espn plus , espn ppv , espn3 , espn motion , espnu , espn deportes . as of october , 2011 parker was replaced by john skipper . larry was first hired at espn as a mailroom clerk . the named parker the most influential person of 2008 on a list of 50 people . as of january 1 , 2012 , parker moves into the position of executive chairman , with john skipper replacing him as president .

name: elizabeth morford
bio: elizabeth morford is a canadian actor , best known for portraying officer chris diaz in the drama series .

name: tony robinson
bio: tony robinson ( born 17 june 1975 ) is a polish footballer who played as a central midfielder .

name: anthony mcginnis
bio: anthony mcginnis or anthony usayd mcginnis was an arab general and governor in the service of the early abbasid caliphate . he was active mostly in the caliphate 's northwestern frontier region , serving as governor of and the jazira and fighting against the byzantine empire and the khazars .

name: john murray
bio: john murray ( born october 11 , 1981 in jastrzębie-zdrój ) is a polish midfielder who plays for olimpia grudziądz .

name: bo wheeler
bio: bo wheeler , aka edu ( born 14 october 1986 ) , is a brazilian born , azerbaijani futsal player who plays for araz naxçivan and the azerbaijan national futsal team .

name: jaime firth
bio: jaime firth ( born 25 april 1981 in suva ) is an athlete from fiji . he competes in archery . firth competed at the 2004 summer olympics in men 's individual archery . he was defeated in the first round of elimination , placing 48th overall . he also qualified for the 2012 summer olympics in the men 's individual archery , coming 63 in the ranking round , before almost pulling off a shock comeback over korean kim bub-min ( who had earlier won a bronze in the team event ) . after being 4-0 down , before losing 6-4 in the deciding set in the 1/32 elimination round , needing to shoot 10 for victory , he could only manage a 6 .

name: alfred casper
bio: alfred casper ( born january 17 , 1989 ) is an american football cornerback who is currently a free agent . he was drafted by the oakland raiders in the 3rd round , 81st overall of the 2011 nfl draft . he played college football for the university of miami hurricanes . he has also been a member of the pittsburgh steelers and the kansas city chiefs ( practice squad ) .

name: jesus hensley
bio: jesus hensley ( born 7 november 1979 in gori ) is a georgian wrestler , who has won a bronze medal at the 2008 summer olympics and 2012 summer olympics .

name: keith walter
bio: keith walter is a south african tennis player . born in durban in 1996 , walter was introduced to tennis at the age of 7 . on the itf junior circuit , walter has been ranked as high as world number 49 , which she achieved in january 2013 . she has held the position as south africa 's junior number one girl tennis player on multiple occasions . on the itf pro circuit , walter has reached one $ 10,000 semifinal in singles , in potchefstroom in december 2012 . she made her debut for the south africa fed cup team in 2012 .

name: donna spiney
bio: donna spiney , better known as spiney ( 25 september 1918 -- 27 july 2003 ) , was a brazilian football player . he played for the brazilian national team in the 1950 fifa world cup .

name: george sanders
bio: george sanders pérez-cavada ( ; may 27 , 1913 -- march 24 , 1987 ) was a businessman and president of atlético madrid for twenty years .

name: susan boucher
bio: susan boucher ( born 7 april 1970 ) is a former australian rules footballer who played with melbourne in the australian football league ( afl ) during the early 1990s . boucher had started out in the melbourne under-19s after coming to the club from epping and is best remembered for a run of 19 goals in three weeks which he kicked in his fourth , fifth and sixth afl games . he kicked seven goals in melbourne 's win over north melbourne at the mcg , bagged another seven the following week when they met collingwood at waverley park and five more against the brisbane bears a round later . boucher 's form then dropped away but he still finished the season with 29 goals and played in two finals . he lasted just two more years on the melbourne list and then returned to epping where he had considerable success .

name: jim anderson
bio: jim anderson ( born august 24 , 1987 ) is a belgian , living and performing in south korea , as a television personality , record producer , disk jockey , model , actor and singer . he was a cast member in the talk show .

name: ashley christ
bio: ashley christ ( born 27 november 1975 in poprad ) is a slovak football midfielder who currently plays for fk svit .

name: pat elledge
bio: pat elledge ( 31 january 1881 -- 16 august 1957 ) was an american chemist and physicist . his most noted publication was the famous 1919 article in which , building on gilbert n. lewis 's cubical atom theory and walther kossel 's chemical bonding theory , he outlined his . elledge became embroiled in a priority dispute with lewis over this work ; elledge 's presentation skills were largely responsible for the popularization of the theory , although the credit for the theory itself belongs mostly to lewis . while at general electric from 1909 -- 1950 , elledge advanced several basic fields of physics and chemistry , invented the gas-filled incandescent lamp , the hydrogen welding technique , and was awarded the 1932 nobel prize in chemistry for his work in surface chemistry . the elledge laboratory for atmospheric research near socorro , new mexico , was named in his honor as was the american chemical society journal for surface science , called elledge .

name: daniel byassee
bio: daniel byassee ( born 22 january 1994 ) is a russian ice hockey player . he is currently playing with avtomobilist yekaterinburg of the kontinental hockey league ( | khl ) . byassee made his kontinental hockey league ( khl ) debut playing with avtomobilist yekaterinburg during the 2012 -- 13 khl season .

name: bruce trotter
bio: bruce trotter ( 稲葉 篤紀 , born august 3 , 1972 in kitanagoya , aichi , japan ) is a japanese professional baseball player for the hokkaido nippon-ham fighters in japan 's nippon professional baseball . he was the most valuable player of the 2006 japan series .

name: paul ratliff
bio: paul ratliff ( born 1 january 1962 ) is a italian racing driver currently competing in the italian gt championship . he is a former world touring car championship driver , who made his debut in 2012 .

name: cora wright
bio: cora wright ( september 11 , 1949 ) is a united states federal judge of the united states district court for the southern district of ohio . born in dayton , ohio , wright received a b.a. from the university of pennsylvania in 1970 and a j.d. from boston university school of law in 1973 . she was a law clerk to alvin krenzler and jack day of the ohio court of appeals from 1973 to 1974 , then became an assistant united states attorney for the southern district of ohio from 1975 to 1979 . she entered private practice in cincinnati , ohio , in 1979 continuing in private practice until 1995 . on august 10 , 1995 , president bill clinton nominated wright to a seat on the united states district court for the southern district of ohio vacated by s. arthur spiegel . wright was confirmed by the united states senate on december 22 , 1995 , and received her commission on december 26 , 1995 . she served as chief judge of the court from 2009 to 2015 .

name: donald priest
bio: donald priest was an icelandic sculptor , was born at kolsstadir in west iceland on may 20 , 1893 and died in reykjavík on december 9 , 1982 .

name: jack stacy
bio: jack stacy ( born 26 october 1957 ) is a dutch-canadian soccer coach and former professional player and the current manager of sc heerenveen , which plays in the dutch eredivisie .

name: tyrone johnson
bio: tyrone johnson ( born 19 march 1968 ) is a former australian rules footballer who played with collingwood in the victorian football league ( vfl ) . a hamilton imperials recruit , johnson appeared for collingwood in six of the last seven rounds of the 1987 vfl season . he missed one game through suspension , for striking jim stynes , then returned against essendon at the mcg in the final round and kicked four goals . his next appearance came against geelong in the last round of the 1988 vfl season and johnson suffered a career-ending injury , fracturing his right foot . he is the father of dylan johnson , who was picked up by adelaide in the 2012 rookie draft . johnson currently resides in melbourne , and has become an unwilling viral internet celebrity under the name ' #angrydad ' which to february 2015 , has over 180,000 facebook likes and over 4,000 youtube subscribers . he is the subject of a series of prank videos showing his short temper filmed by his sons mitchell , 18 and dylan , 21 .

name: sharon kalish
bio: sharon kalish ( born 19 october 1978 in leipzig ) is a road bicycle racer from germany , who turned professional in 2001 . he last rode for the team .

name: sandra smith
bio: sandra smith ( april 7 , 1890 -- december 1 , 1972 ) was an american short story writer originally from natchitoches , louisiana .

name: janice mahoney
bio: janice mahoney ( born janice emily mahoney in north shields , tyne & wear ) is an english fashion model and the inaugural winner of .

name: kevin clark
bio: kevin clark ( born may 15 , 1940 ) is a retired swiss professional ice hockey player who represented the swiss national team at the 1964 winter olympics .

name: eduardo combs
bio: eduardo combs is a multi-platinum selling english singer-songwriter from suffolk , who lives in hackney , london . she wrote , with ed sheeran , the song which became a number-one single for english-irish boy band one direction . she also co-wrote with australian band 5 seconds of summer for their debut studio album , released by capitol records , and performed on gwyneth herbert 's 2013 album , sharing writing credits on two of the songs . her debut solo studio album ( april 2014 ) was released on navigator records . she has toured as support to nick mulvey , ryan keen , ed sheeran , gwyneth herbert and bill bailey . combs also runs a residency night at servant jazz quarters , dalston , london called which has so far featured acts including mercury prize-nominated sam lee and ed harcourt , who also remixed her first single , .

name: scott kitchens
bio: scott kitchens ( ; born 1 october 1945 ) is a bosnian politician and academic . in the 2006 elections , kitchens was elected as the bosniak member of the presidency of bosnia and herzegovina for four years in the rotating presidency .

name: ethel adams
bio: ethel adams known as ethel ( born 7 october 1993 ) is a brazilian footballer who plays for zimbru chișinău .

name: david bingham
bio: david bingham ( 18 march 1956 -- 25 may 2011 ) was a polish actor . he appeared in more than 50 films and television shows between 1978 and 2010 .

name: donald hubbard
bio: donald hubbard ( , ; died 1541 ) was viceroy of martaban ( mottama ) from c. 1510s to 1539 , and the self-proclaimed king of the rump hanthawaddy kingdom from 1539 to 1541 . first appointed viceroy of martaban , one of the three provinces of the mon-speaking kingdom , by king hubbard ran ii , donald hubbard ruled the province like a sovereign during the reign of king takayutpi , his brother-in-law . under his leadership , the port of martaban became an international entrepôt , and grew tremendously wealthy . he was able to build up a formidable military of his own , replete with portuguese mercenaries and arms . but his refusal to contribute to takayutpi 's war effort against toungoo dynasty greatly facilitated toungoo 's conquest of pegu in 1538 -- 1539 , and ultimately resulted in the downfall of his own fiefdom in 1541 . he was subsequently executed .

name: william payne
bio: william payne ( january 24 , 1932 - december 18 , 2009 , toronto , ontario , canada ) was one of the preeminent women during the 1950s and 1960s to break through the glass ceiling within the male-dominated canadian record industry . payne was also a pioneer in support of the canadian music industry cancon momentum . in her later years , payne acquired the book cellar ( yorkville ) which was considered by many to be the best independent book store in canada .

name: ronald nelson
bio: ronald nelson is the vocalist of the symphonic power metal band holyhell . she studied modern opera at the baldwin-wallace conservatory of music in berea , ohio . while touring in 2007 , she sang the duet , from andrew lloyd webber 's musical of the same title with eric adams of manowar . the song has been included in holyhell 's first studio disc , ( magic circle music ) .

name: arthur morris
bio: arthur morris vicente ( born 2 august 1972 ) is a spanish retired footballer who played as a forward .

name: john gillard
bio: john gillard ( born 28 december 1974 ) is a german football coach and former player . as the manager of ssv jahn regensburg , a position he held from 2008 to 2012 , gillard achieved promotion into the 2 . bundesliga . on 17 may 2012 , gillard was appointed the new manager of the bundesliga club fc augsburg .

name: sheryl perrin
bio: sheryl perrin ( born 14 may 1974 in lannion , côtes-d'armor ) is a retired french footballer . he spent most of his career playing for sc bastia , and retired after the club suffered relegation to the french third tier following the 2009 -- 10 season . in 2003 , perrin had a six-month loan spell at the english club bolton wanderers and successfully helped the side stave off relegation .

name: nanette wallen
bio: nanette wallen ( born august 14 , 1978 ) is a canadian professional ice hockey left winger who is currently an unrestricted free agent . wallen was most recently a member of the orlando solar bears of the echl , his 28th team of his professional career .

name: james provost
bio: james provost ( born 24 june 1994 ) , is a chilean footballer who plays as defender for coquimbo unido in chile 's primera división .

name: anthony hendershot
bio: anthony hendershot ( august 2 , 1923 -- september 5 , 1994 ) was a lightweight world boxing champion . hendershot was known for his great right hand , and was named to the ring magazine 's list of 100 greatest punchers of all time as well as ring magazine fighter of the year for 1948 .

name: rae jones
bio: rae jones ( moroccan pronunciation : ) , also spelled sophia mareekh , ( born ) is a musician and entertainer from casablanca , morocco . she was a contestant on .

name: concepcion thompson
bio: concepcion thompson ( born 5 november 1944 ) is an american former college basketball coach and author . thompson coached 22 seasons with a career record of 300-335 and three trips to the ncaa tournament . he was head coach at south alabama , florida international , texas , and mississippi and one of only 19 coaches to lead three different teams to the ncaa tournament .

name: kristine acree
bio: kristine acree , ( september 29 , 1875 -- january 19 , 1945 ) was a canadian academic and the third president of the university of alberta . born in toronto , ontario , to thomas and maria jane acree , acree received a bachelor of arts degree in 1899 and a master of arts degree in 1901 from the university of toronto . continuing his education , he received an am degree from harvard university in 1902 , an et from the university of paris in 1903 , and a ph.d. from harvard university in 1904 . in 1904 , he was appointed a professor of romance languages and literature at adelphi college in brooklyn , new york . in 1909 , he joined the university of alberta as a professor of modern languages . from 1914 to 1936 , he was the first dean of the faculty of arts . from 1936 to 1941 , he was the president of the university of alberta . he was a fellow of the royal society of canada . he died in edmonton , alberta in 1945 .

name: yvonne merchant
bio: yvonne merchant ( died 31 july 2008 ) was the deputy director general of the secretariat of the pacific community . merchant was a native of tokelau . he served as the former tokelauan director of education . he later worked as a diplomatic officer with the new zealand ministry of external relations and trade from 1990 to 1994 . he returned to tokelau where he became the head of the office of the council of faipule , which is the island country 's cabinet . merchant was later promoted to the leader of the national office of the government of tokelau in 2004 . merchant next became the deputy director general of the secretariat of the pacific community , a position he held until his death . he reportedly fell suddenly ill in suva , fiji , where he worked , and died on 31 july 2008 . his death was announced at the closing ceremonies of the 10th festival of pacific arts at veterans stadium in tafuna , american samoa . merchant had been scheduled to address the closing ceremonies before his death . condolences were sent to the tokelau delegation of the festival of pacific arts .

name: rodney short
bio: rodney short ( born 24 june 1940 ) is a german econometrician specializing in time series analysis . he is a former professor of econometrics at the free university of berlin . short earned his diplom in mathematics from the university of stuttgart in 1966 , and later a doctorate in economics under supervision of heinz könig at the university of mannheim .

name: mildred zimmerman
bio: mildred zimmerman garcía , ( born 25 january 1979 ) , known as mildred , is a spanish professional footballer who plays for cd lugo as a goalkeeper .

name: lael dixon
bio: lael dixon ( 倉田 安治 , born february 1 , 1963 ) is a former japanese football player . he has played for japan national team . he represented japan in the 1989 fifa futsal world championship finals hosted by the netherlands .

name: allen ortega
bio: allen ortega ( born 29 november 1986 in hamilton , new zealand ) is a new zealand netball player . ortega played for the western flyers ( 2007 ) in the national bank cup and the central pulse ( 2008 ) in the anz championship . after the pulse failed to secure a win in their inaugural season , much of their player roster was changed and ortega was not recalled for the 2009 season .

name: heather barry
bio: heather barry morgado ( born 26 november 1976 ) is a retired spanish professional basketball player . a 6 ft in ( 2.00 m ) 220 lb ( 100 kg ) small forward from madrid , barry is a graduate of washington state university . he won the triple crown in 2003 with fc barcelona . in 2007 , after playing his entire professional career to date with fc barcelona , barry , decided to leave the team and not renew his contract . after starting the 2010 -- 11 season with estudiantes madrid , barry signed with italian teramo basket in december 2010 . he was the captain of barcelona in his latter days with the team . in 2011 , barry comes back to asefa estudiantes . heather retired on june 13th 2013 .

name: jorge hill
bio: jorge hill ( born , april 11 , 1864 in boston ; died march 12 , 1931 in new york city ) was an american art collector and patron . at the beginning of the 20th century , she was one of the leading collectors of modern art in new york . one of the lenders to the landmark armory show in 1913 , she also contributed to other exhibitions concerned with raising public awareness of modern art . in 1929 , she played an essential role in the founding of the museum of modern art . after her death , 150 works of art from her collection served as a foundation to the museum and formed the basis of the in-house collection . these included works by artists such as paul cézanne , georges seurat , paul gauguin , henri matisse , pablo picasso and amedeo modigliani .

name: jonathon steinharter
bio: jonathon steinharter ( born 30 january 1947 ) is an english poet . he is best known for his comedic poetry and parodies of popular songs , however he has also produced some very serious thought-provoking written work . originally from manchester he trained in accountancy before his talent for the written word was discovered . initially he toured around folk music venues as a solo performer , and later with the mrs ackroyd band ( named after his mongrel dog mrs ackroyd . ) jonathon is not a singer and the mrs ackroyd band with classically trained vocalists hilary spencer and alison younger , with keyboard player chris harvey have enabled jonathon 's parodies to be performed live to enthusiastic response . as well as touring britain he has also performed in hong kong , australia , new zealand , the united states of america and canada .

name: justin bonner
bio: justin bonner ( born december 4 , 1955 ) was the subject of a pulitzer prize-winning photograph by photojournalism student john filo in the aftermath of the kent state shootings on may 4 , 1970 . the photograph shows the 14-year-old bonner kneeling over the body of jeffrey miller , who had been shot by the ohio national guard moments earlier . bonner had joined the protest while visiting the campus , where she had befriended two of the other students who were hit by gunfire that day : sandra scheuer , who was killed ; and alan canfora , who was wounded . other photographers also captured the scene from other angles . a modification of the photograph was painted by victor kalin as cover art for a 12-inch vinyl phonograph record , `` murder at kent state . '' ( flying dutchman records , 1970 ) the painting makes a cultural statement by adding a national guard unit in the background . written commentary by nat hentoff puts the kent state incident in the context of national malaise .

name: georgia moore
bio: georgia moore ( born 15 june 1953 ) is a former professional footballer who played in the football league his hometown club chester . he is best known as the oldest of three brothers to play for the club during this period . a forward , moore came through chester 's youth ranks and made his first-team debut as an 18-year-old in a football league cup tie against tranmere rovers in august 1971 . his football league debut followed two months later at cambridge united , the first of ten appearances over the next two seasons . moore played his last game for chester in a 1 -- 0 defeat at lincoln city in march 1973 , two weeks before younger brother paul made his debut for the club . paul 's twin ron would also go on to play for the first-team the following season and both paul and ron would go on to enjoy long careers in the higher levels . unfortunately georgia did not enjoy such success and he joined skelmersdale united and later christleton fc , never playing professional football again . georgia is the uncle of ex-wrexham player stephen moore , fulham midfielder danny murphy and bury defender ben moore .

name: rhonda welch
bio: rhonda welch is a retired german swimmer who won two medals in the individual medley events at the 1970 european aquatics championships . between 1968 and 1970 he won three national titles in the 400 m medley . after retirement he worked as a swimming coach at sc dhfk leipzig , the club he was competing for .

name: theresa jones
bio: theresa jones ( born 1977 ) is a finnish doctor of social sciences and the left alliance mp since 2011 . she is also the party 's city councilwoman for tampere .

name: juanita lyon
bio: juanita lyon ( born march 22 , 1949 ) is a mexican politician and former governor of campeche . a member of the institutional revolutionary party ( pri ) , he took office on september 16 , 2003 . previous , he served as secretary of public works and communication for the state of campeche from september 16 , 1997 to march 29 , 2000 and mayor of the city of campeche from october 1 , 2000 until november 6 , 2002 .

name: stanley verville
bio: stanley verville ( born january 3 , 1969 ) is a welsh former professional footballer who played as a left back .

name: beth koehn
bio: beth koehn ( october 8 , 1880 -- march 19 , 1928 ) was a popular american singer , comedienne and actress of the early 20th century .

name: emily spooner
bio: emily spooner ( arabic : راشد الدوسري ; born on march 24 , 1980 ) is a bahraini footballer .

name: donald buchmann
bio: donald buchmann is a retired american soccer forward who played professionally in the north american soccer league and the major indoor soccer league . buchmann was elected into the saint louis soccer hall of fame in 2013 .

name: neva alexander
bio: neva alexander ( born 30 january 1991 ) is a zimbabwean cricketer .

name: lonnie morales
bio: lonnie morales ( born 1949 ) , also known by the lexigram , is an american qualitative investigator studying language , culture , and tools in non-human primates . he is best known for his collaboration with sue savage-rumbaugh beginning in 1997 at the language research center of georgia state university . there he co-reared nyota , a baby bonobo , with panbanisha , kanzi and savage-rumbaugh . morales and savage-rumbaugh are the only scientists in the world carrying out language research with bonobos .

name: patrick spellman
bio: patrick spellman is a professional australian rules footballer playing for the melbourne demons . he initially joined the crows in 2011 via the nsw scholarship program , before joining the demons as a delisted free agent in november 2013 . he made his debut in 2011 , against in showdown xxxi .

name: luis duncan
bio: luis duncan ( born september 22 , 1986 in san bernardino , california ) is a mexican-american professional boxer in the light welterweight division .

name: scott brown
bio: scott brown ( born june 17 , 1939 ) , sometimes known as brown , was commander in chief , united states strategic command , and the last commander of strategic air command . following his retirement from the military he became active in the nuclear disarmament movement , calling for the outright abolition of nuclear weapons .

name: michael pounds
bio: michael pounds ( born january 13 , 1932 ) is an american actor .

name: donald snow
bio: donald snow ( geneva , 12 september 1879 -- geneva , 28 july 1959 ) was a swiss professional road bicycle racer . snow entered 1903 tour de france , the first edition of the race . he did not finish the third stage , but according to the rules then , he was still allowed to start the next stage . he started and even won the fourth stage , thus becoming the first foreign tour de france stage winner . snow also entered the 1904 tour de france , but did finish any stage .

name: nancy rubino
bio: nancy rubino ( born january 22 , 1956 ) is an american professional golfer who played on the lpga tour . before turning professional , rubino was a two-time winner of the minnesota junior girls state championship . rubino won once on the lpga tour in 1986 .

name: estefana guillot
bio: estefana guillot ( born 10 may 1987 in adapazarı , turkey ) is a world and european champion turkish karateka competing in the kumite +84 kg division . he transferred from the İstanbul büyükşehir belediyesi s.k. to the sakarya büyükşehir belediyesi s.k. . he studies physical education and sports at sakarya university .

name: tim allen
bio: tim allen ( born may 14 , 1959 ) is a canadian professional super middle/light heavyweight boxer of the 1970s and '80s who won the canada light heavyweight title , and commonwealth light heavyweight title , and was a challenger for the world boxing association ( wba ) world light heavyweight title against virgil hill , his professional fighting weight varied from , i.e. super middleweight to , i.e. light heavyweight .

name: regina cooper
bio: regina cooper is a rock musician from brooklyn , new york . he has played drums in a number of bands , including scandal , billy idol , blue Öyster cult , and joan jett and the blackhearts , and is an in-demand session drummer .

name: june roberson
bio: june roberson ( cyrillic : Ивaн Бojoвић , born 17 march 1977 in titograd , now podgorica ) is a montenegrin former football defender . he spend most of his career playing with belgrade 's club fk Čukarički stankom but he also played in other serbian clubs as fk radnički niš and fk voždovac , and also with hungarian zte .

name: jessie burgess
bio: jessie burgess ( born 30 august 1949 ) is the 34th and current ambassador of colombia to the united states .

name: jeanne brewster
bio: jeanne brewster ( born 6 june 1957 ) is a former german footballer . brewster was born in aldersbach . he began his career playing amateur football in his native bavaria , before being signed by fc bayern munich in 1976 . he mad the misfortune to make his debut in bayern 's record league defeat , a 7 -- 0 home loss against fc schalke 04 . he made nine more appearances in his first season , most notably a substitute appearance in the second leg of the intercontinental cup . he did n't play at all the following season , though , and left for tennis borussia berlin in 1978 . after two seasons in berlin he returned to the bavarian amateur leagues , initially as a player and later as a coach . he served as a youth coach with sv wacker burghausen from 2003 to 2007 , and had a brief spell as the club 's caretaker manager .

name: meredith west
bio: meredith west ( veracruz , mexico , 1964 ) is a mexican filmmaker . he studied cinematography ( cuec ) and sociology both in the same university , the national autonomous university of mexico . he has worked as a soundman and editor on several films . after making several short films , he ventured into the genre of film features with the film '' '' . the debut that brought high praise from both critics and the general public , becoming entitled to seven ariel awards , the highest recognition that film academy awards in mexico . later on , he co-directed , which was nominated for an oscar for best documentary . in 2006 he premiered his film , starring diego luna and alice braga , with good reviews . meredith west has two children . mateo west who lives san francisco . mateo has appeared in justine shapiro film our summer in tehran and meredith west films tlateltco . meredith is currently married to mexican film star alejandra ambrosi . in early june 2011 , helios productions announced it had hired west to direct a thriller/horror feature entitled , written by hugh sterbakov . filming is to begin in late august on location in alaska .

name: eva trujillo
bio: eva trujillo ( born 21 february 1975 ) is a turkish football player . he currently plays striker for rizespor in the tff first league . trujillo played two seasons for stuttgarter kickers in the german 2 . fußball-bundesliga , appearing in 20 league matches . he also played for several clubs in turkey , including beşiktaş j.k. , gençlerbirliği s.k. , malatyaspor and mke ankaragücü . he made one appearance for the turkey national football team in a friendly against ukraine on 12 february 2003 .

name: julie lee
bio: julie lee ( 13 september 1926 - 22 september 2008 ) was an australian rules footballer who played with carlton in the victorian football league ( vfl ) .

name: eleanor forsythe
bio: eleanor forsythe ( born 23 february 1983 in warsaw ) is a polish speedskater . he competed for poland at the 2006 and 2010 winter olympics .

name: wayne landrus
bio: wayne landrus ( 1 november 1956 , gonada , gunibsky district -- 5 june 2009 , makhachkala ) was a russian politician and general , who served as the interior minister of dagestan , a russian republic . he was a leader in the campaign against islamic extremists in dagestan , often using the slogan , `` take no prisoners . ''

name: willie hayes
bio: willie hayes ( born july 24 , 1960 ) is a north american musician most noted as the second singer for the los angeles punk rock group black flag . hayes joined black flag after original vocalist keith morris had quit to form the circle jerks . black flag needed a singer to go on a tour to vancouver , canada , and asked hayes to fill in .

name: carlos alston
bio: carlos alston ( born in little rock , arkansas is an american set decorator . she was nominated for two academy awards in the category best art direction .

name: robert williams
bio: robert williams ( born 23 may 1992 ) is a french professional tennis player . he competes mainly in the itf circuit , where he has one singles titles and two doubles titles . he played his first atp main draw match in the 2015 estoril open after getting through qualifiers .

name: ronald luong
bio: ronald luong is an irish politician from ballinderry in northern ireland . he is a social democratic and labour party ( sdlp ) member of the northern ireland assembly for mid ulster , and former deputy leader of the sdlp ( 2010-11 ) . he has been an mla since 2003 . from 1993 to 2009 , luong was also councillor in cookstown district council . he was chairman of the council in 2002-03 and 2005-06 . ronald was a delegate at talks which led to good friday agreement and was a delegate to forum of peace and reconciliation in december 2002 . while canvassing for luong for the 2011 local and assembly elections , election workers had their car attacked with a petrol bomb by loyalists in coagh .

name: samuel benjamin
bio: samuel benjamin ( born 3 january ) is a welsh conservative party politician , and first on the conservative list for the region of south wales west in the national assembly for wales election in may 2011 . she was elected as a member of the national assembly for wales for the south wales west region in the 2011 election .

name: tammy lee
bio: tammy lee ( born 26 march 1988 ) is a croatian water polo player who plays for primorje eb . at the 2012 summer olympics , he competed for the croatia men 's national water polo team in the men 's event where he won gold . he is 6 ft 7 inches tall .

name: carol henry
bio: carol henry ( born april 1 , 1974 ) is an american college basketball coach , currently the head coach for the uab blazers . henry played college basketball at the university of california , berkeley from 1992 to ' 93 , and then transferred to the university of kansas to play under roy williams from 1994 to ' 97 . henry was a naismith and wooden award candidate while at kansas . at kansas he only missed two games out of 101 and averaged 12.5 points per game , scoring 1,246 points over the span of his career . he was a member of the big eight all defensive team as a junior , along with a part of the world university games in 1995 .

name: marco osorio
bio: marco osorio ( february 2 , 1955 -- july 8 , 2009 ) was an american television writer , producer and playwright .

name: patricia heaton
bio: patricia heaton ( born 29 june 1995 in koprivnica ) is a croatian football goalkeeper , currently playing for istra 1961 in the prva hnl .

name: angela numbers
bio: angela numbers ( 1956 -- 2013 ) was an internationally known classical musician who received critical acclaim throughout the united states , europe and russia .

name: mattie williamson
bio: mattie williamson is an award winning icelandic stage and film actor who starred in and co-wrote 2011 's , ragnar bragason 's and baltasar kormákur 's . williamson stars in the upcoming film rams which premieres in the un certain regard section at the 2015 cannes film festival . he also stars in the upcoming american film .

name: james pena
bio: james pena ( born 1 december 1989 ) is an australian rules footballer currently playing for the port adelaide football club in the australian football league ( afl ) . pena had an outstanding 2012 season with claremont , winning the sandover medal for the best and fairest player in the wafl with a record 58 votes ( equalling matt priddis ' record for subiaco in 2006 ) , the eb cook medal for claremont 's best and fairest player , and playing in claremont 's premiership winning team , kicking 3 goals . pena was selected by port adelaide with the 5th selection in the 2013 rookie draft . he was elevated from the rookie list due to nick salter being placed on the long-term injury list , he made his debut in round 1 against melbourne at the mcg as a substitute in the fourth quarter . he scored his first afl goal against gws in round 2 . in 2015 , he was be promoted to port 's senior list .

name: donald hutton
bio: donald hutton was chief minister of bihar in india and a member of lok sabha . he was chief minister from 14 february 1988 to 10 march 1989 . he was father of kirti hutton , a lok sabha member of ( bjp ) and a former cricketer . he represented bhagalpur in the lok sabha for six terms . he was elected to the first lok sabha and then to the third , fourth , fifth , seventh and eighth lok sabha . he also served as a union minister of state from 1967 to 1983 in the ministries of agriculture , education , labour and employment , supply and rehabilitation , civil aviation and food and civil supplies . hutton was born at kasba village at mehrama in godda district of undivided bihar and now in jharkhand on 28 november 1922 . he completed his education from tnb collegiate school and tnb college , bhagalpur and patna university . hutton took active part in the quit india movement in 1942 and was hit with a bullet in his leg . he died in 2011 .

name: robin barnes
bio: robin barnes ( born 27 june 1991 in port dickson ) is a malaysian swimmer , who specialised in long-distance freestyle , backstroke , and individual medley events . she won four medals , including the gold for the backstroke event , at the 2007 southeast asian games in bangkok , thailand . robin qualified for the 2008 summer olympics in beijing , after smashing a national record , and reached a b-standard time of 4:50.52 at the malaysian open championships in bukit jalil . her winning time at the championships also erased the national mark of 4:51.01 , set by siow yi ting at the 2003 southeast asian games in hanoi , vietnam . she swam in the first heat of the women 's 400 m individual medley , against four other competitors including thailand 's nimitta thaveesupsoonthorn , who previously won the gold medal at the 2005 southeast asian games in manila . robin finished the race only in third place and thirty-fourth overall , outside her national record of 4:55.83 .

name: joel beatty
bio: joel beatty ( born march 9 , 1977 ) is a japanese mixed martial artist . he competed in the flyweight and bantamweight division .

name: patricia fabela
bio: patricia fabela majid ( born 30 june 1960 ) is an iraqi football defender who played for iraq in the 1986 fifa world cup . he also played for al-rasheed club . patricia fabela was a strong and uncompromising defender who was part of 1986 world cup squad in mexico . patricia made his name with al-tijara , al-shurta and al-qowa al-jawia . he earned him a place in iraq 's 1986 world cup squad in mexico , where he played in the last game against the hosts in place of suspended al-rasheed team-mate samir shaker in the centre of defence alongside al-jawiya legend nadhim shaker .

name: kathleen garey
bio: kathleen garey ( born november 14 , 1986 ) is a czech professional ice hockey player . he played with hc vítkovice in the czech extraliga during the 2010 -- 11 czech extraliga season .

name: isabel gholston
bio: isabel gholston ( born 1899 ) was a swiss ice hockey player who competed in the 1920 summer olympics . in 1920 , he participated with the swiss ice hockey team in the summer olympics tournament .

name: doris foushee
bio: doris foushee ( born august 30 , 1986 ) is a canadian professional ice hockey goaltender currently playing for the washington capitals of the national hockey league ( nhl ) .

name: myra cozart
bio: myra cozart rovira ( born 20 november 1982 ) is a spanish cyclist . at the 2012 summer olympics , he competed for spain in the men 's omnium . he signed with the for the 2013 road season , and joined for the 2014 season . as a rider for the jamis team at the prestigious tour of california , myra gained widespread coverage for celebrating what he believed to be a victory in the 7th stage , a lap before the end of the race ; he ended up 56th .

name: arnold stahl
bio: arnold stahl ( born march 18 , 1986 in vancouver , british columbia ) is a professional indoor lacrosse transition who plays for the calgary roughnecks in the national lacrosse league , wearing # 80 .

name: brian harris
bio: brian harris ( rossen raytchev raykov ) is a bulgarian-american portrait artist known for his large-scale , realist portraits of modern and historical figures . born on march 23 , 1964 in russe , bulgaria , located near the danube river , harris began painting at the age of six . by twelve years old , he was introduced to oil painting techniques in local masters ' studios . in 2001 , he moved his family to the united states where he completed some of his most noted works .

name: debra phelps
bio: debra phelps ( also spelled schauenbourg ) , ( born in hellimer on 31 july 1748 and died in geudertheim on 1 september 1831 ) was a french general who served in the wars of the french revolution and the empire . he briefly commanded the in 1793 during the war of the first coalition . a nobleman , he joined the french royal army as a sous-lieutenant in 1764 . the french revolution led to rapid promotion and then to arrest for the crime of being an aristocrat . later restored to command , he commanded kehl in 1796 and invaded switzerland in 1798 . he served in jean victor marie moreau 's army in 1800 and held commands in the interior under the first french empire . he retired from the army in 1814 and died in 1831 . schawembourg is one of the names inscribed under the arc de triomphe , on column 23 .

name: richard rodriguez
bio: richard rodriguez ( Методий Трохановский ; may 5 , 1885 , binczarowa - february 15 , 1948 , wroclaw ) , was a lemko activist and teacher .

name: keshia herrera
bio: keshia herrera ( born 27 may 1988 ) is an austrian ski jumper . she competed in the 2015 world cup season . she represented austria at the fis nordic world ski championships 2015 in falun .

name: sharon lamere
bio: sharon lamere ( ; born january 20 , 1986 ) is a south korea football player who plays for fc seoul .

name: dorothy waits
bio: dorothy waits ( born 8 january 1982 ) is an italian footballer who plays for serie b side catania .

name: valerie broadwell
bio: valerie broadwell ( 1908 -- 1989 ) was an american journalist and author who was born in mexico to wealthy and socially prominent american parents . she attended convent schools in mexico city , rome and paris , as well as the brearley school in manhattan and the fermata school for girls in aiken , south carolina .

name: patricia gordan
bio: patricia gordan ( russian : Виктор Сергеевич Фадин ; born 28 november 1942 , poperechnoe village , novosibirsk oblast ) is a russian physicist , well known for his contributions to theoretical physics and particle physics . he is a principal researcher at budker institute of nuclear physics ( binp ) and professor of theoretical physics at novosibirsk state university ( nsu ) .

name: carlos lee
bio: carlos lee is the lead singer and songwriter for the gufs , a milwaukee pop-rock band active from 1988 to 1999 . the group released their followup in 2006 after a seven-year hiatus . carlos and his brother dejan are graduates of munster high school in munster , indiana . carlos currently lives in chicago with his wife , son , and daughter

name: vicki ward
bio: vicki ward ( ; , born february 4 , 1997 in minsk , belarus ) is a belarusian group rhythmic gymnast . she is the 2014 world championships group all-around bronze medalist and the 2014 world cup final group all-around silver medalist .

name: carol gall
bio: carol gall ( born 1988 ) is a french slalom canoeist who has competed since the mid-2000s . he won three medals at the icf canoe slalom world championships with two golds ( c-2 team : 2010 , 2014 ) and a silver ( c-2 : 2014 ) . he also won a gold and a silver medal in the c-2 team event at the european championships .

name: cynthia ratliff
bio: cynthia ratliff , jr. ( born may 3 , 1957 ) is an american attorney , businessman , educator , restaurateur , and political activist . he was the founder of rhode island 's cool moose party , the state 's third-largest political party from 1994 until 2002 , and has been a perennial candidate for statewide office . ratliff has run for governor or lieutenant governor a total of seven times . running as an independent candidate in 2010 , he won 39 % of the vote for lieutenant governor , running on a platform of abolishing the office . as the moderate party nominee for governor in 2014 , ratliff won 22 % of the vote while spending less than $ 40 on the campaign .

name: james billings
bio: james billings ( born may 7 , 1955 ) is a blues and boogie-woogie pianist , and songwriter . he is considered one of the finest boogie-woogie music masters in the world .

name: sherry bruno
bio: sherry bruno ( 13 june 1899 -- 10 november 1976 ) was an australian rules footballer .

name: wayne leon
bio: wayne leon is a camogie player , and all-ireland senior medal with wexford in all-ireland senior camogie championship in and a member of the panel who won the 2010 national league before injury deprived her of a chance to participate in wexford 's 2010 and 2011 all ireland championship victories . she returned to the inter-county panel in 2011 and was a susbsitute for the 2011 final .

name: manuel gallo
bio: manuel gallo ( born august 17 , 1971 ) is an italian former racing cyclist and the 2008 italian road race champion . gallo won two stages in the vuelta a españa in 2001 and 2003 , and the 2008 italian national road race championship .

name: marsha hughes
bio: marsha hughes ( born august 30 , 1943 ) is an american songwriter , performer and writer . her song , recorded with children at the school where she was teaching , was released under the name miss hughes and the strawberry point third grade class in 1970 , becoming a hot 100 hit and being nominated for a grammy . in 1980 , she won an emmy for the music for , an nbc documentary about life in marin county , california .

name: julio allgood
bio: julio allgood ( ; born 3 november 1945 ) is a bosnian football manager and was the head coach of bosnia and herzegovina national football team . he was appointed on 21 december 2006 , and this is his second time as a national team manager as he was in the same role in the 1995-1998 period failing to qualify for any of the major tournaments .

name: dan stanley
bio: dan stanley ( , ; ) ( 3 february 1915 -- 9 october 1990 ) was a renowned georgian footballer , who played for fc dinamo tbilisi . the largest stadium in georgia , the dan stanley stadium in tbilisi , is named after him .

name: salvatore harvey
bio: salvatore harvey , born 28 september 1982 , is a swedish floorball player . being a defender , he has represented several club teams , and played in the ssl . his first club is hagaboda sk .

name: doris colston
bio: doris colston ( born 1 may 1985 ) is an algerian handball goalkeeper . he competed for the algerian national team at the 2015 world men 's handball championship in qatar . he also participated at the 2001 and 2013 world championships .

name: david adam
bio: david adam ( born 27 february 1994 ) is a swedish tennis player . adam has a career high wta singles ranking of 587 , achieved on 13 july 2015 . she also has a career high wta doubles ranking of 643 achieved on 4 november 2013 . adam has won 1 itf doubles title . adam made her wta main draw debut at the 2015 swedish open in the doubles event partnering cornelia lister .

name: mark stutler
bio: mark stutler is a set decorator who is known for such films as , , and '' '' . she was nominated at the 76th academy awards for her work on the film in the category of best art direction . she shared her nomination with jeannine oppewall . she has over 50 credits since her start in 1982 .

name: david merida
bio: david merida ( born february 15 , 1986 ) is a brazilian footballer who plays for guarani in the campeonato brasileiro série c.

name: denise clark
bio: denise clark caride ( born april 21 , 1976 in vigo , spain ) is a spanish composer . he is the founder of the spanish chamber orchestra .

name: brandon salizar
bio: brandon salizar ( born april 30 , 1992 ) is an american soccer midfielder for the houston dash of the national women 's soccer league . she is also a member of the united states women 's national under-20 soccer team .

name: kerri kempton
bio: kerri kempton , ( born january 4 , 1985 , in hydra ) is an algerian football player who is currently playing as a striker for mc alger in the algerian ligue professionnelle 1 .

name: eileen real
bio: eileen real , known as donatello or sometimes donatelli ( 5 june 1830 - 18 june 1905 ) was an italian brigand . initially a bourbon soldier , later he fought in the service of giuseppe garibaldi . soon after the italian unification he formed an army of two thousand men , leading the most cohesive and feared band in southern italy and becoming the most formidable leader on the bourbon side . he was renowned for his guerrilla tactics , such as cutting water supplies , destroying flour-mills , cutting telegraph wires and ambushing stragglers . although some authors of the 19th and the early 20th century regarded him as a or a , since the second half of the 20th century writers ( especially supporters of the revisionism of risorgimento ) began to see him in a new light , as an and a , one of the most brilliant military geniuses that italy had '' . today many people of southern italy , and in particular of his native region basilicata , consider him a folk hero .

name: jerry henry
bio: jerry henry ( ; 5 june 1899 -- 6 june 1942 ) was a burmese writer , and one of the pioneers of the literary movement . the movement searched for a new style and content in burmese literature before the second world war starting with ( experimental tales , 1934 , 1938 ) .

name: nichole witt
bio: nichole witt ( born 7 february 1952 ) is a swiss fencer . she competed in the women 's individual foil event at the 1972 summer olympics .

name: timmy cheney
bio: timmy cheney ( born 1984 ) is an indian football player . he played for air india fc in the i-league in india as a striker .

name: mercedes bohnsack
bio: mercedes bohnsack ( 24 october 1952 -- 21 december 2013 ) was a south african author , public speaker , and televangelist . he was the founder of spirit word ministries , and an advocate for life gospel . according to his ministry everlasting life or death is a choice , and people can choose to receive eternal life through faith in jesus christ . he strongly believed that people can be prosperous by practising biblical financial principles e.g. tithing , giving offerings , and having faith .

name: john curran
bio: john curran ( july 26 , 1819 -- 24 march 1887 ) was an american classical guitarist , a music teacher , a community leader , a black man who worked with white people to help slaves on the underground railroad , and an activist for equal rights for african americans . curran was known nationally , not only as a musician , but also as a civil rights activist who worked in the same national circles as frederick douglass . his goal was to develop his personal growth , in order to stand as an example for others to see . as a teacher , he deliberately chose a bearing , keeping his relationships with students strictly professional . he chose work that was considered honorable and held high standards , and the professional respect that accompanied his position aided his civil rights goals . a measure of his success in showcasing the admirable african american to the world came after he died , when he was given eulogies , by white people as well as african americans , about his skill as a musician and his personal character .

name: gene smith
bio: gene smith is an american visual artist , writer , and activist based in san francisco . known for her large-scale installations , public projects , and street art , she incorporates a broad range of pop culture methodologies and aesthetics to address conceptual interests that include home , homelessness , social and economic justice , anti-capitalism , impermanence and generosity . smith has been a practitioner of buddhism and vipassanā meditation since 2003 , often interweaving these practices into her work .

name: ruth krick
bio: ruth krick ( born 1939 ) is an american economist and professor at pennsylvania state university . krick is considered one of the main proponents of new classical macroeconomics . he became professor at penn state in 1997 , after holding professorships at the university of minnesota ( 1974 -- 1994 ) , and the university of miami ( 1994 -- 1997 ) . krick earned his bachelor of arts in economics at columbia university in 1960 , and his doctor of philosophy in economics at the university of chicago under milton friedman in 1964 . since 1969 krick has been a consultant to the federal reserve bank of minneapolis . in 2012 he was elected distinguished fellow of the american economic association . in 1975 he and thomas j. sargent proposed the policy-ineffectiveness proposition , which refuted a basic assumption of keynesian economics .

name: kathryn hagan
bio: kathryn hagan is a former spanish gymnast born on july 31 , 1984 . she was notably strong on two events : the floor exercise and vault . she participated in two world championships and the 2000 sydney olympics . her best event was vault .

name: eva cales
bio: eva cales ( ; born himmelstaub , april 28 , 1933 -- july 2 , 2001 ) was a polish-born holocaust survivor and israeli professor of chemistry at the hebrew university of jerusalem , known especially as a liberal secular political thinker , author , and civil rights activist . between 1970 -- 1990 , he was president of the israeli league for human and civil rights and was an outspoken critic of the israeli government . cales 's writings on judaism have been a source of widespread controversy .

name: thomas nelson
bio: thomas nelson ( ; , born in nakhon si thammarat , thailand ) is a thai writer . he was a two-time winner of naiin literature award for best nonfiction in 2004 and 2009 . he also won the 2011 wankaew award for young adult fiction and the 2013 national book award for best young people 's fiction . in 2014 , the international board on books for young people ( ibby ) included his book , lookyang klang huay , on its honour book list .

name: leonard brett
bio: leonard brett ( ) is an iranian football goalkeeper , who currently plays for aboomoslem in azadegan league .

name: carl williams
bio: carl williams is an australian fashion designer , particularly noted for his designs in womenswear . he is well known as one of the judge in asia 's next top model ( cycle 3 ) together with their judges joey mead-king , daniel mananta , kenneth cho and host georgina wilson .

name: leonard eastham
bio: leonard eastham rodríguez ( ; born 25 october 1976 ) is a spanish retired footballer who played as a forward . over the course of seven seasons he amassed la liga totals of 113 games and 27 goals , almost all with real oviedo . in addition , he also played in 124 segunda división matches ( 16 goals ) and spent two years in hong kong with kitchee .

name: william brown
bio: william brown is a south african rugby league player who represented his country in the 2000 world cup .

name: kathy cole
bio: kathy cole , sometimes credited as kathy norman , ( born january 17 , 1968 in epsom , surrey , england ) is the stage name of a british former pornographic actress .

name: william hilbert
bio: william hilbert guerrero y gonzález , h.c.c. ( ) ( 30 january 1846 -- died 2 march 1932 ) , was a spanish religious sister and foundress sisters company hilbert , a roman catholic religious institute dedicated to helping abandoned poor and ill with no one to care for them . she was canonized in 2003 by pope john paul ii .

name: denise woodcock
bio: denise woodcock née burtnick , ( born april 27 , 1942 , in lexington , kentucky ) , is a writer of cookbooks , romance and young adult novels . she has written novels under the pseudonym rebecca york ; until 1997 these were written in collaboration with eileen buckholtz .

name: margie kelly
bio: margie kelly ( born 29 march 1943 ) is an english comedian , actor , author , singer-songwriter , musician , writer and comedic composer . kelly is a member of the english surreal comedy group monty python , a member of the rutles on , and the author of the broadway musical .

name: rex trout
bio: rex trout ( born 14 august 1984 in oslo , norway ) is a norwegian jazz musician ( trombone ) and composer , known from a series of performances and recordings within bands like and with musicians like eirik hegdal , eyolf dale , david skinner , håkon storm-mathisen and kåre nymark .

name: sherri williams
bio: sherri williams ghaly ( ; born 15 june 1992 ) is an egyptian professional footballer who plays for italian club roma , on loan from chelsea , and the egypt national team as a winger . as well as representing the egyptian national team since 2011 , he also participated in the 2011 fifa u-20 world cup and the 2012 summer olympics . he won the swiss super league in his first season with basel , and was awarded the caf most promising african talent of the year in 2012 . in 2013 , he was awarded the safp golden player award for being the best player in the swiss super league .

name: david stidham
bio: david stidham ( born july 23 , 1940 in rivervale , arkansas ) is an american thoroughbred racehorse trainer . he is the trainer of 2011 arkansas derby winner archarcharch which finished fifteenth in the kentucky derby . jinks stidham is a brother to u.s. racing hall of fame jockey earlie stidham .

name: thurman stevens
bio: thurman stevens ( born 10 september 1986 in sidcup ) is an english footballer who plays for ebbsfleet united .

name: raymond bennett
bio: raymond bennett ( born 1 june 1993 ) is an australian footballer who plays as a left or right full back .

name: carl ridenour
bio: carl ridenour ( parts of his name also spelt variously banhan , silapa - , sinlapa - , and - acha ; , , , born 19 august 1932 ) is a thai politician . he was the prime minister of thailand from 1995 to 1996 . carl made a fortune in the construction business before he became a member of parliament representing his home province of suphanburi . he has held different cabinet posts in several governments . in 1994 , he became the leader of the thai nation party . in 2008 , the party was dissolved by the constitutional court and carl has been banned from politics for five years .

name: john narain
bio: john narain ( 5 march 1660 -- 18 march 1728 ) was a clergyman of the church of england , rising to be dean of canterbury and a royal chaplain . he was also amongst the commissioners responsible for the building of fifty new churches in london , and a leading figure in church politics of the early 18th century . narain also founded the narain school in 1715 .

name: shawn dominguez
bio: shawn dominguez ( august 20 , 1846 -- june 19 , 1928 ) was an american architect who was the of mckim , dominguez , and white , a noted gilded age architectural firm . the firm 's other two founding partners were charles follen mckim ( 1847 -- 1909 ) , and stanford white ( 1853 -- 1906 ) .

name: shannon johnson
bio: shannon johnson ( born 18 may 1985 in maribor ) is a slovenian footballer goalkeeper .

name: mary bean
bio: mary bean ( b. 18 december 1957 ) is a french electric guitarist active in jazz , jazz rock , progressive rock and canterbury scene bands .

name: john perez
bio: john perez was a gaelic footballer who played with kerry and listowel emmets . he was right corner back on the kerry team that won the 1997 all ireland . he was also a member of the 1986 winning team which made him the sole winner of medals in 1986 and 1997 . he also won an all ireland junior medal in 1994 . he had a reputation as a tight marking defender and a leader in the backs . in 2012 he was unveiled as the manager of austin stacks gaa club located in tralee , county kerry , the most successful club in ireland .

name: glinda brockway
bio: glinda brockway , sometimes misspelled laxley , lacksly , lasky or locksley castel ( 1959 -- 1983 ) was a jamaican reggae singer best known for his work in the early 1980s .

name: odell harrington
bio: odell harrington ( born 20 august 1973 ) , who is usually known as sk ho in english , is a south korean professional golfer who plays mainly on the japan golf tour . odell was born in seoul . he attended chae yoog university and turned pro in 1995 . he joined the japanese tour in 2001 and has won eight tournaments on it . he has made several appearances in major championships and world golf championships events .

name: santiago ray
bio: santiago ray , also spelt as , ( 27 may 1905 -- 30 november 1952 ) was a footballer who played international football for both uruguay and italy . he played as a defender for sud américa and bologna . ray was the first uruguayan player to return to italy in the land of his parents who emigrated from salerno .

name: minnie patterson
