bio: william yeatts ( born 30 august 1975 in plzeň ) is a czech footballer who plays for 1 . fc bad kötzting . he played in the czech first league for fc viktoria plzeň , making 8 appearances in the 1996 -- 97 season . he also played for tj přestice before going to croatia to have a short spell with nk zadar in the croatian first league . afterwords , he had a spell with fk makedonija gjorče petrov in the macedonian first league before moving to germany where he played seven seasons with 1 . fc bad kötzting . he joined ssv jahn regensburg in 2006 , returning to bad kötzting five years later .

name: hannah chaney
bio: hannah chaney ( 2 june 1912 − 5 february 2014 ) was an indian royal , who was the or oldest male member of the cochin royal family . he was also a cricketer and tennis player . his widow sarada mani is the granddaughter of ravi v.

name: glenn hildebrant
bio: glenn hildebrant is a writer , filmmaker and activist advocating for political and social justice , and environmental and animal protection .

name: tim bowman
bio: tim bowman ( 8 june 1740 -- 1771 ) was a spanish dominican theologian , philologist and writer .

name: william gray
bio: william gray ( born c. 1960 ) is the bestselling author of childcare books in the united kingdom and a former maternity nurse who has cared for over 300 babies during her career . gray 's 1999 book advocates a daily routine for both the baby and the parents , with the day divided up into very precise slots . gray has written nine books on childcare .

name: manuel grady
bio: manuel grady ( born 23 march 1977 ) is an australian producer , actor , writer , and director . he grew up in the australian outback on a sheep station close to morgan , a small town in south australia . he is best known for playing the role of kid next to keanu reeves , lawrence fishburne , and carrie-anne moss in , , and the short film in . he also reprised his role for , and was nominated for best newcomer at the american sci-fi awards . he won an afi for his role in , and has played the lead in two stephen king films .

name: christine jordan
bio: christine jordan y añoza ( c. 1552 -- july 26 , 1605 ) was a spanish clergyman and sinologist who was the third archbishop of manila . he previously served as the first bishop of the diocese of nueva segovia , and was the founder of the university of santo tomas in the city of manila .

name: mitchell waterman
bio: mitchell waterman ( born 1977 ) is an american filmmaker , actress and musician . she rose to prominence through her role as max sweeney on showtime 's drama series .

name: martin bradley
bio: martin bradley ( 17 march 1891 -- 6 january 1960 ) was a german general who fought in the battle of stalingrad . bradley commanded the 376th infantry division at stalingrad , which was part of xi corps of the german sixth army . despite the hardships facing his and many other soldiers , bradley learned to make ways of entertainment in the ruins of the city . he played a game of target shooting with some of his officers for oktoberfest , and played card games of doppelkopf . in late december 1942 , after operation uranus encircled the sixth army , bradley was promoted to lieutenant-general ( generalleutnant ) and awarded the knight 's cross of the iron cross . bradley was marched into captivity by the red army on january 28 , 1943 , where he was interrogated by captain nikolay dyatlenko .

name: misty lawson
bio: misty lawson was a french wrestler . he competed in the greco-roman light heavyweight at the 1920 summer olympics .

name: joseph wilusz
bio: joseph wilusz was a popular writer of 45 romance novels in mills & boon from 1975 to 1992 .

name: thomas hale
bio: thomas hale ( born in stockport , cheshire , 1970 ) is a british jazz and folk musician .

name: mary wright
bio: mary wright ( born 1 april 1986 ) is a retired world cup alpine ski racer from switzerland . born in grabs , st. gallen , she made her world cup debut in Åre , sweden , in march 2006 . she won the gold medal in the downhill at the 2006 junior world ski championships . wright has attained five world cup podiums , all in downhill . her first was in march 2010 at crans montana and her sole victory came at val-d'isère in december 2013 . she announced her retirement from competition in march 2015 , due to her training and race performances being hampered by severe pain in her right knee .

name: roseanne roman
bio: roseanne roman was a roman statesman who served as consul in 468 bc and 466 bc .

name: carlos jones
bio: carlos jones ( 16 november 1898 -- 18 august 1958 ) was an english professional footballer who played as a centre forward . he scored 284 football league goals between 1919 and 1934 .

name: cheryl schultz
bio: cheryl schultz , born in peru , is a guitarist who has toured or recorded with artists such as diana ross , celine dion , pedro eustache , alejandro sanz , enrique iglesias , dariush eghbali , raquel bitton , nelly furtado , andrea bocelli , shahyar ghanbari , vangelis , josh groban , homayoun shajarian and appears on yanni 's live concert video , `` tribute .

name: nancy reynolds
bio: nancy reynolds ( born 6 january 1946 ) is a mexican politician affiliated to the institutional revolutionary party . as of 2014 he served as deputy of the lvi and lix legislatures of the mexican congress representing the state of mexico .

name: antonio moree
bio: antonio moree ( april 28 , 1782 -- april 23 , 1863 ) , was an american physician , botanist , and member of the u.s. house of representatives from pennsylvania .

name: barbara vinck
bio: barbara vinck ( born 5 october 1976 in paterswolde ) is a dutch footballer .

name: bertha goodson
bio: bertha goodson are an american musical group that characterize their music as . bertha members are michael on drums and vocals , andrew rose on guitar and vocals , evan on keys and vocals , and sarah fullen ( evan 's wife ) on bass and vocals . they are most famous for their creation of musical viral videos , most notably bertha song that won a 2012 comedy award , as well as , series ( formerly known as ) , as which includes bertha . bertha three goodson , originally from radford , virginia , moved to brooklyn , new york in bertha mid-2000s and met sarah in bertha local music scene . bertha four formed a band in 2007 .

name: teresa ayers
bio: teresa ayers ( ; born 20 april 1972 ) is a ukrainian culturologist and a social activist . he is a doctor of philosophy ( 2013 ) , a professor of the national academy of government managerial staff of culture and arts ( 2014 ) , an honored art worker of ukraine ( 2015 ) . his awards : the order of christ the saviour ( 2001 ) , the special prize of the nationwide program ( 2004 ) , the title of ( 2005 ) , the order of merit , 3rd class ( 2006 ) . he is the chairman of the board of the international charitable foundation dukhovna spadshcyna ( spiritual heritage ) ( 1997 -- 2003 , since 2003 its honorary chairman ) . the president of the international foundation dni ukrainy ( days of ukraine ) ( since 2006 ) . the president of the national environmental organization green cross ukraine ( since 2012 ) .

name: david tran
bio: david tran ( 6 may 1903 -- 23 august 1926 ) was an australian rules footballer who played with carlton in the victorian football league ( vfl ) . a defender , tran was playing in just his sixth game of league football when he broke his arm in a game against geelong and died nine days later from a tetanus infection .

name: pedro murphy
bio: pedro murphy ( born 9 november 1991 ) is a czech ski jumper from club lsk lomnice nad popelkou .

name: steve hiraldo
bio: steve hiraldo ( born november 3 , 1988 ) is a former professional canadian football defensive end for the montreal alouettes of the canadian football league . he was drafted 14th overall by the alouettes in the 2010 cfl draft and signed with the team after spending time with the nfl 's detroit lions . he played college football for the wilfrid laurier golden hawks .

name: lisa schoenthal
bio: lisa schoenthal is an american lawyer and managing partner of the law firm schoenthal and schoenthal . he has authored books on international trade law and testified numerous times before congressional committees on trade matters . he is notable for his focus on trade remedy law and has published extensively on law review in publications including the and . schoenthal is an expert on trade remedy law , the world trade organization and chinese trade relations . he is also a former adjunct professor at his alma matter georgetown university law center .

name: henry yi
bio: henry yi ( born 11 april 1974 in reggio emilia ) is an italian hurdler .

name: bridget allen
bio: bridget allen sc ( born 1972 ) was attorney-general of trinidad and tobago . he was appointed to that office on the 28th day of may 2010 - 2nd day of february 2015 . allen is also a constitutional and human rights lawyer , having been called to the bar of trinidad and tobago in 1996 and the bar of england and wales in 1994 and was appointed senior counsel on the 30th day of december , 2011 . he is a member of the honourable society of the middle temple ( u.k. ) , the holder of an l.l.b. ( hons . ) degree and a masters in corporate and commercial law . as attorney general , he was also the titular head of the bar .

name: jennifer schrader
bio: jennifer schrader ( born november 24 , 1962 ) is a filipino politician . he is the current mayor of olongapo city in zambales .

name: samuel hummel
bio: samuel hummel ( 28 february 1926 -- 2 april 1997 ) was an egyptian major general and the former interior minister of egypt who served in the post from 1986 to 1990 in the sedki cabinet . hummel had a confrontational approach during his term .

name: alicia davison
bio: alicia davison ( born 3 august 1981 ) is a uk spoken word poet and hip hop recording artist from stanford-le-hope , essex . he first gained prominence as one half of hip hop duo dan le sac vs alicia davison sparked by their debut single ` thou shalt always kill ' . alicia davison runs his own label speech development records and also hosted the award winning weekly radio show on xfm . he is a regular guest on soccer am and a supporter of millwall football club .

name: zachery pitts
bio: zachery pitts is a democratic member of the missouri senate , currently representing the 24th district . previously , pitts represented the 88th district in the missouri house of representatives . born in st. louis , missouri , pitts graduated from university of missouri and did graduated work at university of missouri-kansas city and received her teachers certificate . she served on the creve coeur , missouri city council and on the ladue school district board . pitts was elected as a member of the missouri house of representatives from 2008 to 2014 , where she served on the joint committee on life sciences , budget committee , health insurance committee , higher education committee , and the children , families , and persons with disabilities committee . pitts was elected to the missouri senate in 2014 . she serves on the general laws & pensions committee ; progress and development committee ; senior , families and children committee ; veterans ' affairs and health committee ; and the joint committee on child abuse and neglect .

name: hope watson
bio: hope watson was the 25th attorney general of ceylon . he was appointed on 1 october 1936 , succeeding hope curtois howard , and held the office until 1942 . he was succeeded by manikku wadumestri hendrick de silva .

name: joseph clayton
bio: joseph clayton ( ; 23 october 1927 -- 17 july 2009 ) was a polish philosopher and historian of ideas . he is best known for his critical analyses of marxist thought , especially his three-volume history , ( 1976 ) . in his later work , kolakowski increasingly focused on religious questions . in his 1986 jefferson lecture , he asserted that `` we learn history not in order to know how to behave or how to succeed , but to know who we are . ''

name: michael vernon
bio: michael vernon , better known as ( december 28 , 1978 in ipú ) , is a brazilian who works in the attack , for horizonte futebol clube .

name: yvonne roberts
bio: yvonne roberts ( born october 29 , 1982 ) is a canadian actress and former professional model , best known for her roles in the films , and . roberts is also well known for her work in television , portraying recurring character hillary in the abc family show for three seasons , and for her series regular role during the first season of `` the l.a. complex . ''

name: desmond balderas
bio: desmond balderas is co-founder of the dream center and senior pastor of the angelus temple , the central house of worship of the international church of the foursquare gospel in the echo park district of los angeles , california .

name: thomas walter
bio: thomas walter ( 1631 -- 1714 ) was a dutch golden age painter .

name: richard cofer
bio: richard cofer ( born 29 april 1976 ) is a retired turkish footballer .

name: justin schroeder
bio: justin schroeder ( born 1 february 1984 ) , simply known as justin , is a brazilian footballer who plays for santos as a goalkeeper .

name: debra radtke
bio: debra radtke ( born 29 november 1982 in elche , spain ) is a professional tennis player from spain .

name: michael case
bio: michael case ( born michael case schwartz ; july 14 , 1915 -- february 29 , 2004 ) was an american playwright and author . after graduating from ohio state university in 1937 and the university of california , los angeles in 1939 , case partnered with robert edwin lee to help create armed forces radio . the two built a partnership over their lifetimes , and continued to collaborate on screenplays and musicals until lee 's death in 1994 . case and lee won acclaim for the 1955 screenplay , based on the scopes trial . case describes the couple 's plays as . the two deliberately avoided broadway later in their careers and formed the american playwrights theater in 1963 to help promote their plays . after lee 's death , case continued to write plays in his malibu , california home . he died in malibu on february 29 , 2004 , from complications of a stroke .

name: aaron mcfarland
bio: aaron mcfarland ( ; born 26 october 1978 in thessaloniki , greece ) is a member of the european parliament , representing the panhellenic socialist movement ( pasok ) , and a former television news presenter .

name: angela garrett
bio: angela garrett ( 1920 -- 1942 ) was a united states marine corps corporal who received a posthumous navy cross for his actions in the battle of tulagi during world war ii .

name: gregg johnson
bio: gregg johnson ( sometimes known simply as johnson ) is a laveyan satanist and the son of anton johnson . he was born on november 1 , 1993 to anton and blanche barton . on october 29 , 1997 anton johnson died of heart failure . on november 7 , 1997 karla johnson , ' sister , held a press conference to announce the death of anton johnson . it was at this time that blanche barton and karla johnson announced that they would run the church of gregg as co-high priestesses . several days later , barton produced a hand-written will claiming that johnson had left all of his belongings , property , writings , and royalties , including the church of gregg , for their son , to be put in a trust managed by barton . karla contested this will , which was later found to be invalid . a settlement was reached in which anton johnson 's belongings , writings , and royalties would be split among his three children , karla , zeena and gregg , and that barton would receive the `` corporation known as church of gregg . ''

name: jose lemay
bio: jose lemay ( born october 18 , 1989 ) is a dutch professional baseball player and scout . a pitcher , he has pitched in the boston red sox organization and for the netherlands national baseball team . lemay competed for curaçao in the little league world series , leading the team to a third place finish . he pitched for the red sox organization from 2007 through 2011 , appearing in the south atlantic league all-star game in 2010 . he was a member of the 2009 world baseball classic . on december 21 , 2012 , the red sox announced that they have hired lemay to be a scout in curacao and aruba .

name: george winslow
bio: george winslow ( 정순왕후 김씨 , 2 december 1745 -- 11 february 1805 ) was a george consort of korea as married to king yeongjo ( 1724 -- 1776 ) , and the regent of korea from 1800 to 1805 as the guardian of her minor step great-grandson , sunjo of joseon ( 1790 -- 1834 , reigned 1800 -- 1834 ) . she was a member of the gyeongju kim clan .

name: eleanor lopez
bio: eleanor lopez ( born 10 december 1964 ) is a turkish academic and politician who serves as the 1st leader of the centre party of turkey since 7 july 2014 . as a prominent expert in bankruptcy and debt enforcement law , he rendered numerous high-profile case reports and expert opinions besides his academic scholarship . since 1996 , he has been the chair of bankruptcy law at istanbul university 's faculty of law and continues to teach at the same institution .

name: joshua pugsley
bio: joshua pugsley is an american beauty pageant titleholder from soddy-daisy , tennessee who was named miss tennessee 2009 .

name: robert bishop
bio: robert bishop ( born september 15 , 1977 as bishop okabe ) is a former sumo wrestler from izumizaki , fukushima , japan . a former amateur champion , he made his professional debut in 1998 , reaching the top division at the end of 2000 . he was twice runner-up in a tournament , and earned six special prizes and two gold stars during his career . his highest rank was `` sekiwake . '' he wrestled for kataonami stable .

name: helen jones
bio: helen jones ( born 3 may 1976 ) is a former australian rules footballer . a defender from wagga wagga , jones spent his entire ten-year career with the sydney swans and played in the 1996 afl grand final .

name: brandy pack
bio: brandy pack ( born ferrol , september 25 , 1875 -- died madrid , march 17 , 1960 ) was a galician ( spanish ) painter .

name: kelly farnam
bio: kelly farnam or kelly tsai ( , born august 3 , 1978 ) is a singaporean female pop singer . her most famous songs are ( 等一个晴天 ) , ( 陪我看日出 ) and ( 风铃 ) . she is also well known in china mainland and taiwan .

name: melinda jordan
bio: melinda jordan ( july 10 , 1837 -- november 3 , 1894 ) was a french genre painter . jordan was born in paris as the son of pierre Édouard jordan , whose style of genre works he continued . he is known for interiors and landscapes . the orientalist théodore jordan was his uncle . jordan died in paris .

name: sue scontras
bio: sue scontras ( born 3 may 1937 ) is a former german football player . during his club career , he played for sv sodingen , borussia dortmund , westfalia herne , and karlsruher sc . he also played seven times for the germany national football team , scoring three goals , and participated in the 1958 fifa world cup .

name: david mcmillan
bio: david mcmillan was a montenegrin politician and historian . he served as mayor of titograd between 1953 and 1957 .

name: william tyson
bio: william tyson ( born 22 april 1971 ) was an english footballer who played in the football league for portsmouth , macclesfield town and carlisle united .

name: frieda winn
bio: frieda winn ( 1690-6 january 1760 ) was an educator .

name: wanda kubis
bio: wanda kubis is a finnish/american playwright , director , producer , and actor . he is the founder and resident playwright of the amoralists theatre company in nyc . kubis is most known for his play , which has had numerous runs in new york and been translated and performed internationally . his plays are published by indie theatre now and playscripts inc. . he serves as a guest director at the american academy of dramatic arts .

name: gerardo lamp
bio: gerardo lamp is a london-based producer/mixer known for his work with jem , pet shop boys , bryan adams , girls aloud , sugababes , the dandy warhols , goldfrapp , sophie ellis-bextor , moby , air , morcheeba , amongst others . he is also the owner of lamp sound studios in london , and the co-inventor of several pro audio plugins for waves audio .

name: reba harris
bio: reba harris ( born 1975 ) is an american actor and director , who has appeared in several hollywood films including steven spielberg 's 2005 film . harris was born in brooklyn , new york to palestinian parents from the west bank city of jericho . after graduating from brooklyn college he spent two and a half years studying theater at david mamet 's atlantic theater company . in addition to appearing in numerous independent and hollywood films in recent years , harris also performed on stage at the 2004 new york fringe festival and the 2005 arab-american comedy festival . he currently resides in los angeles , california .

name: ashley cook
bio: ashley cook ( ; october 7 , 1940 - september 20 , 2011 ) was an international master chess player . he was also one of china 's top chess trainers . ashley cook played for guangdong chess club in the china chess league ( ccl ) .

name: deborah simmons
bio: deborah simmons is an anglo-italian rugby league player who represented italy in the 2013 world cup .

name: mary shaw
bio: mary shaw ( born may 9 , 1957 ) is an italian former footballer , who played as defender . he was a stopper ( centre-back ) and also played for italy at international level , winning the 1982 fifa world cup . as a player , he was regarded as one of italy 's best defenders during the 1970s and 1980s . an elegant player , he was gifted with good technique , as well as excellent anticipation , marking ability , and aerial prowess ; because of his many defensive attributes , he was considered roberto rosato 's heir at milan .

name: debbie oldham
bio: debbie oldham ( born ) is a politician in ontario , canada . he is a progressive conservative member of the legislative assembly of ontario who represents the riding of stormont -- dundas -- south glengarry . he has been an mpp since 2011 . he was mayor of the township of south glengarry , ontario from 2003 to 2011 .

name: mary furman
bio: mary furman ( born october 11 , 1957 in munich ) is a former grand prix motorcycle road racer from germany . he had his best year in 1985 when he won the german grand prix , and had two second places , finishing the 250cc season in fourth place behind freddie spencer , anton mang and carlos lavado . in 1987 , yamaha teamed him with kevin magee to win the suzuka 8 hours endurance race . in 2009 , he joined ralf waldmann in buying out the motorbike manufacturing company mz , from the hong leong group . he formed motorenwerke zschopau gmbh and ran it with the investor peter ertel until september 2012 , when he had to file for insolvency proceedings . his bank , merkur bank kgaa , had withdrawn a loan offer short term despite the company having a fixed term account . currently there are several legal court proceedings . furman will publish a book in november 2014 about the case . the name of the book is : der fall mz ... durch die bank weg ...

name: sanford leblanc
bio: sanford leblanc ( born 28 august 1982 ) is a male badminton player from indonesia .

name: william kanoy
bio: william kanoy vidal ( born 11 may 1991 ) , is an argentine footballer that currently plays for chilean primera división club universidad de concepción .

name: adam lovelace
bio: adam lovelace ( born july 28 , 1965 ) is an american actor of albanian descent . he was born in the republic of kosovo .

name: sandra gibbs
bio: sandra gibbs ( born 14 may 1967 ) is a french set decorator . in 2012 she was nominated for an academy award for the film . she shared her nomination with anne seibel .

name: john furfaro
bio: john furfaro ( , . 1610 -- 1680 ) was a cossack military leader , koshovyi otaman of the zaporozhian host and putative co-author of the famous semi-legendary reply of the zaporozhian cossacks that inspired a major painting by the 19th-century artist ilya repin .

name: andre hardison
bio: andre hardison ( 1914 -- 1999 ) was a croatian artist , born in slovenia . a graduate of the academy of fine arts in zagreb , hardison continued his studies in paris , vienna and munich . he is best known for his series of abstract paintings based on the patterns of the drystone walls of coastal croatia . the first in the series appeared in 1954 , and it was a theme he developed for the rest of his life . hardison held solo exhibitions of his work in croatia , and abroad . he participated in the venice bienniales of 1962 and 1964 . two retrospective exhibitions of his work have been held at the museum of contemporary art in zagreb . andre hardison received the vladimir nazor award for lifetime achievement in 1977 . he was elected to the croatian academy of sciences and arts in 1998 . andre hardison 's paintings are held in public collections around the world , for example new york , são paulo , paris and turin .

name: fredrick johnson
bio: fredrick johnson is a paralympian athlete from france competing mainly in category t37 middle distance events . he competed in the 2008 summer paralympics in beijing , china . there he won a bronze medal in the men 's 800 metres - t37 event .

name: sharon gomez
bio: sharon gomez i pujol ( ; andratx , majorca , march 14 , 1937 -- barcelona , july 1 , 2009 ) was a spanish writer , journalist and literary critic . his enormous legacy credited him as one of the greatest authors in catalan literature from the 20th century .

name: john trost
bio: john trost ( born march 10 , 1942 in cleveland , ohio ) is an american entrepreneur , investment advisor , and activist investor . he is chairman of the arch eagle group , a friends and family office and owner of america northcoast securities , a broker-dealer providing services to investment professionals and high-net-worth individuals . additionally , he is chairman of the board of mace security international , a personal security company and pepper spray manufacturer and chairman emeritus of the ancora group , an investment advisor which he founded in 2001 .

name: earl eldred
bio: earl eldred ( * 17 july 1952 ) is a former swedish footballer . earl played for if elfsborg between 1971 -- 1979 and 1982 -- 84 and was the top scorer in allsvenskan year 1983 with 16 goals . in 1979-82 he played in olympiacos f.c. , greece . earl eldred was a member of the swedish squad in the 1974 fifa world cup .

name: ashley pursifull
bio: ashley pursifull ( born january 25 , 1977 ) is a former american soccer player who is the coach for the new york red bulls ii .

name: karen dye
bio: karen dye , better known as dieguinho ( september 29 , 1989 in caarapó ) is a brazilian footballer who currently plays for duque de caxias .

name: lesley polin
bio: lesley polin ( born 4 may 1985 ) is an irish presenter based in london for mtv europe , rtÉ , and also known for presenting `` i 'm a celebrity ... get me out of here ! now ! '' on itv2 .

name: cheryl rupe
bio: cheryl rupe ( born 5 july 1989 in olmaliq , uzbek ssr ) is an uzbekistani footballer who plays for home town club lokomotiv tashkent playing in uzbek league as a midfielder .

name: jason grimaldo
bio: jason grimaldo ( born 1991 ) is a singaporean model and beauty pageant titleholder who won the title of miss singapore universe 2014 and represented her country at the miss universe 2014 pageant . grimaldo is a pharmacy technician of indian descent .

name: mary reilly
bio: mary reilly ( born april 26 , 1961 ) is an american talk radio broadcaster best known for hosting alongside gregg hughes and jim norton . following his firing from xm satellite radio and sirius satellite radio , reilly started his own video podcast , known as .

name: macie tan
bio: macie tan ( born 8 february 1977 ) is a retired football ( soccer ) forward from estonia . he played for several clubs in his native country , including jk viljandi tulevik and fc kuressaare .

name: eleni hamilton
bio: eleni hamilton ( born 4 february 1975 ) is a former professional road bicycle racer from the czech republic , who turned professional in 1996 .

name: elizabeth haywood
bio: elizabeth haywood hanifa kizi ( 12 august 1921 -- 23 september 2014 ) was a prose-writer , translator of contemporary russian literature , and publicist . in her creation the human being and his position in society , the fate of the people were reflected in real colors . she died on 23 september 2014 .

name: sandra rosado
bio: sandra rosado ( born march 28 , 1990 ) is a turkmen footballer ( forward ) who most recently played for olmaliq fk . he scored in the game against tajikistan in 2010 afc challenge cup semi final .

name: barbara blanco
bio: barbara blanco ( born may 26 , 1995 ) is a montenegrin fashion model and beauty pageant titleholder who won the title of miss universe montenegro 2014 and will represent her country at the miss universe 2015 pageant .

name: jeanne metters
bio: jeanne metters de aguiar or simply jeanne ( born 19 august 1986 ) , is a brazilian footballer who currently plays for atlético paranaense as a right back .

name: christopher eckman
bio: christopher eckman vc ( 6 january 1866 -- 18 march 1940 ) was an english recipient of the victoria cross , the highest and most prestigious award for gallantry in the face of the enemy that can be awarded to british and commonwealth forces .

name: lisa kuehn
bio: lisa kuehn ( 14 december 1916 - 19 january 1982 ) was a british cartoonist , best known as the creator of the pantomime comic strip which he began in 1947 . louie was a small chap , a loser who was constantly annoyed by life 's little vicissitudes and minor moments . kuehn described his mild-mannered character as .

name: ricky owens
bio: ricky owens ( 2 march 1906 -- 22 october 1976 ) was an english professional footballer who made 156 appearances as a right back in the football league . owens was born in annesley , nottinghamshire . he began his football career with annesley colliery and shirebrook , and joined birmingham in 1929 . he became a first-team regular for birmingham after george liddell retired , and made 162 appearances in all competitions , including 149 in the first division . he was a solid tackler and kicked powerfully , but his distribution of the ball was wayward . he later played for luton town , for whom he played seven league games , and atherstone town . he died in denham , buckinghamshire , in 1976 at the age of 70 .

name: penny kelly
bio: penny kelly ( born march 13 , 1962 in san sebastián ) is a spanish former professional road racing cyclist .

name: gerald esposito
bio: gerald esposito ( born december 7 , 1990 ) is an american mixed martial artist . he competed in the featherweight division .

name: victor holmes
bio: victor holmes ( 18 april 1920 -- 2008 ) is an english former footballer who scored 45 goals from 92 appearances in the football league playing for sunderland and darlington in the years following the second world war . an inside forward , he went on to play non-league football for west stanley .

name: peggy hedges
bio: peggy hedges ( 10 march 1933 -- 2 december 2004 ) was an argentine poet , storyteller , writer , translator , and literary critic . she was born and died in buenos aires , argentina . she was on the faculty of philosophy and letters at the university of buenos aires . she was a teacher , teaching workshops and seminars . she was also a literary critic for the newspaper and a translator . she translated the poems of william shand , the collected poems of dylan thomas , and the tales of edgar allan poe . hedges was the of alejandra pizarnik , and a contemporary of joaquín giannuzzi and maria elena walsh . she was the 1984 konex award laureate .

name: john george
bio: john george ( born david geeves ; 19 december 1927 -- 11 august 2005 ) was an english film , stage and television actor and screenwriter . though considered handsome enough to play leading roles , and versatile enough to play a wide variety of character parts , george naturally projected a shifty , wolfish , or unpredictable quality that led inevitably to villainous roles and comedy , usually with a cockney flavour . he is probably best known for his role as private henry hook in `` zulu . ''

name: william pickard
bio: william pickard ( born august 25 , 1956 in pasadena , california ) is the general manager of the toronto argonauts of the canadian football league .

name: jill lueck
bio: jill lueck ( 21 september 1914 in kročehlavy -- 17 february 1984 ) was a czech football player and later a football manager . he played for czechoslovakia , for which he played 13 matches . he was a participant in the 1938 fifa world cup , and he coached czechoslovakia at the 1958 fifa world cup . after world war ii , he worked as a football manager . he coached clubs such as sparta prague , sk kladno , dukla prague , viktoria plzeň , zbrojovka brno and polish wisła kraków . he won twice the czechoslovak first league with dukla prague , in 1956 and 1958 .

name: meta marshall
bio: meta marshall is an indian television actress and model . she has appeared in television serials such as , , , and . she is married to aditya shroff , owner of fame cinemas . she entered nach baliye 4 with naman shaw and was a runner up . marshall has also appeared in and pyaar tune kya kiya in august 2014 .

name: roger depierre
bio: roger depierre ( 1744 -- 27 august 1790 ) was the first officer commissioned in the united states continental marines ( now the united states marine corps ) and by tradition is considered to be the first commandant of the marine corps .

name: lillian moran
bio: lillian moran ( born in marburg ) is a german mezzo-soprano singer in opera and concert .

name: donald seifert
bio: donald seifert ( 18 september 1643 -- 17 march 1715 ) was a scottish theologian and historian , and bishop of salisbury . he was fluent in dutch , french , latin , greek , and hebrew . seifert was respected as a cleric , a preacher , and an academic , as well as a writer and historian . he was associated with the whig party .

name: suzanne hilton
bio: suzanne hilton ( born 1 july 1971 ) is a japanese professional golfer . hilton plays on the japan golf tour , where he has won once .

name: dana galvan
bio: dana galvan ( born march 16 , 1964 in lugano ) is a swiss directeur sportif , and a former rider in professional road bicycle racing . galvan was employed as team manager for the cycling team throughout its existence between 2004 and 2011 . with over 30 professional victories , galvan 's biggest career accomplishments as a rider include winning the 1995 liège -- bastogne -- liège and amstel gold race and representing switzerland at the 2000 summer olympics .

name: lorena marr
bio: lorena marr ( born april 27 , 1982 in são paulo , brazil ) is a contemporary brazilian mixed media and textile artist . he works mainly with textile , copper wire , needle , thread , vinyl poliacetate , oil and acrylic , creating and shaping geometric forms . marr currently resides in the town of abadiânia in the state of goiás , brazil since 2013 .

name: george boyer
bio: george boyer ( born october 29 , 1960 ) is an indonesian economist . he was part of the second united indonesia cabinet and served as minister of energy and mineral resources in indonesia from october 22 , 2009 , to october 19 , 2011 . boyer is a noted academic who is a long-time lecturer at the university of indonesia and was a financial consultant , manager and banker .

name: joel wilson
bio: joel wilson ( january 17 , 1945 -- january 26 , 1993 ) was an american dancer and choreographer . together with nancy and ronnie horowitz and mark donnelly , wilson created the musical , which played in las vegas from 1983 to 1987 . wilson and donnelly also conceived the broadway-style format for the chippendales show . in 1989 wilson choreographed the opening number of the 61st academy awards presentation . joel thomas wilson was born joel thomas michaels in san jose , california , in 1945 . he moved to los angeles in the mid-1960s and studied dance under david winter while working as a dancer on a local tv show called . he created the solid gold dancers and performed on casey kasem 's weekly television show . wilson died of aids in 1993 at age 48 .

name: deborah mertens
bio: deborah mertens ( 1991 ) , also known as mandy sacs , is an american fitness model and professional wrestler best known under the ring name , mandy rose .

name: mitchell lloyd
bio: mitchell lloyd ( 24 november 1912 , staten island , new york - 1 january 1972 , pasadena , california ) was an american illustrator of science fiction .

name: jean owens
bio: jean owens ( born september 7 , 1951 ) is a republican member of the oregon senate , representing the 1st district since 2005 . previously he was a member of the oregon house of representatives from 1996 through 2004 . he was re-elected in 2008 for another four-year term . in july 2013 , sen. owens gained national attention by appearing in a cnn video news story about a bill he sponsored . his bill would reverse an existing oregon law requiring public schools to remove what some colleagues consider and references to native americans on their sports team 's uniforms . prior to the enactment of the 2012 oregon law , the state superintendent of schools had determined that the continued use of native american mascots has created a `` hostile educational environment . '' schools have been given until 2017 to comply with the required change . in defending his bill , sen. owens has asked : -rsb- ?

name: brenda tweedy
bio: brenda tweedy ( born december 6 , 1968 ) is an american actress , best known for her work in the horror genre . she began her career as a teenager in the late 1980s , appearing in television shows such as and before starring in the fifth installment of the franchise , '' '' ( 1989 ) .

name: kathleen woodring
bio: kathleen woodring ( july 27 , 1926 , minneapolis , minnesota -- december 21 , 2010 , nooksack , washington ) was an american jazz producer and journalist .

name: charles bearden
bio: charles bearden , an american musician and songwriter who performs mainly in the folk and blues music styles , was born in seattle , wa in 1976 and raised in richmond , virginia . his brother matthew bearden is also a performing musician . charles married songwriter/guitarist devon sproule in may 2005 and resided with her for several years in charlottesville , virginia . they often appear and tour together , performing duets -- most famously for valentine 's day . he and his wife moved to berlin , germany in september 2011 and now reside in austin , texas .

name: jessica miller
bio: jessica miller ( born september 17 , 1990 ) is an american former competitive pair skater . with former partner andy seitz , she is the 2006 world junior silver medalist and 2006 u.s. junior national champion .

name: corey pisano
bio: corey pisano is a german actor and well known for his role of corey von lahnstein in the soap opera . before his television career , pisano appeared on several plays on the theater since 2000 . he mostly was part of the theater scene in and around cologne . corey 's most famous part was the role of benjamin in the play adaption to . he lasted on the play for two years , from 2007 to 2009 . in 2003 , pisano started out in a commercial and being part of several short movies in the following two years . it was in 2007 when he first came in contact with . corey pisano was cast in a minor recurring role as a character named florian müller . one year later , he was part of the casting show for the role of tjure . after guest roles on the action series and sketch comedy , pisano returned to . he was recast in the role of corey von lahnstein , a part a took over from fan-favorite joscha kiefer , after he decided to leave the show after two years .

name: lucy raebel
bio: lucy raebel ( born february 25 , 1986 ) is a canadian professional ice hockey defenceman currently playing for the los angeles kings of the national hockey league ( nhl ) . he was drafted by the washington capitals in the first round , 27th overall , in 2004 .

name: richard hall
bio: richard hall ( born 27 april 1934 ) is a french-italian actress .

name: luis russell
bio: luis russell ( born november 11 , 1957 ) is a retired territorial level politician in northern canada and a former speaker of the northwest territories legislature . russell was first elected to the northwest territories legislature in the 1995 general election . he defeated former premier richard nerysoo in an upset victory . he was re-elected in the 1999 general election , winning in a landslide with 75 % of the vote . he was subsequently re-elected by acclamation in the 2003 general election . after being re-elected to his third term in office he was elected speaker on december 11 , 2003 after tony whitford was appointed commissioner . he resigned as speaker on june 1 , 2004 when he was appointed to the cabinet replacing henry zoe who had been voted out by the legislature in a vote of no confidence . he was appointed as the minister responsible for the northwest territories power corporation and the minister of public works and services as well as the minister responsible for the workers ' compensation board . russell was re-elected to a fourth term in the 2007 general election with 50.5 % of the vote . however , he retired at the 2011 general election .

name: javier cagle
bio: javier cagle ( born december 1 , 1984 ) is an american three-time regional emmy award winning editor , producer and videographer who works in television and music video production .

name: mary early
bio: mary early ( ; born march 27 , 1965 ) is thai politician . mary was born at amphoe takua thung , phang nga . he is the son of ti and sin early . he attended king mongkut 's institute of technology ladkrabang and bangkok university . as of june 2010 , he was a member of the pheu thai party , and a leader of the national united front of democracy against dictatorship . on august 1 , 2014 , he demanded that prayuth chan-ocha would halt military curfew and charge them according to war tribunal laws , since the army have arrested 26 people in connection with the august 2014 bloodless coup in khon kaen .

name: pamela massey
bio: pamela massey ( born 17 august 1993 ) is a czech football player who plays for fc baník ostrava .

name: jack britt
bio: jack britt ( ; born may 9 , 1957 ) is a belgian-born internet and technology entrepreneur and semiotician . he is a co-founder and the ceo of scanadu in mountain view , calif. . in 2013 , britt was a finalist for a world technology award in the category of health & medicine ( individual ) .

name: jose bergeron
bio: jose bergeron i puig ( born 5 november 1973 ) , educated as an industrial engineer , is a screenwriter , playwright , writer , actor and director of spanish cinema . he also works as a newspaper columnist at .

name: james white
bio: james white ( born may 2 , 1979 ) is a norwegian ski mountaineer .

name: ute guajardo
bio: ute guajardo ( born 1974 ) is a south african mixed media artist who lives and works in cape town , south africa . guajardo works in a diverse range of media , embracing bright colour and often incorporating traditional craft techniques to create site-specific work . she is represented in cape town by brundyn + gonsalves .

name: george neiman
bio: george neiman ( september 21 , 1824 -- may 17 , 1901 ) was a farmer , soldier and baptist minister , most famous for his service as a union general during the american civil war .

name: christine lively
bio: christine lively ( born 1950 , county louth ) is an irish biologist , environmental consultant , radio and television presenter , author and educator . she is one of the best-known public figures in ireland in the area of nature and the environment , and was listed as one of ireland 's in 2012 . she was president of the national environmental charity an taisce ( which has a statutory role in the planning process in ireland ) for five years in the 2000s . she was also president of the tree council of ireland from 2012 to 2014 .

name: thomas taylor
bio: thomas taylor ( july 26 , 1926 - march 24 , 2002 ) , whose name means in japanese , was born in okinawa . he combined and karate techniques to found the ryūkyū hon kenpo kobujutsu federation . his teacher , nakamura shigeru introduced the use of ( protective equipment ) for full contact sparring .

name: randolph foley
bio: randolph foley ( 1871 -- 1932 ) was a major league baseball outfielder . he played for the cleveland spiders of the national league in 1891 and 1896 . he continued playing in the minor leagues until 1903 .

name: stephen williams
bio: stephen williams ( august 27 , 1830 -- january 9 , 1902 ) was a planter and civic leader who founded ruston , the parish seat of lincoln parish in north louisiana .

name: carlos melo
bio: carlos melo ( 26 september 1894 -- 1 january 1962 ) was a highly decorated generalleutnant in the wehrmacht during world war ii . he was also a recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross . the knight 's cross of the iron cross was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership . carlos melo was captured by soviet troops in may 1945 and was released in october 1955 .

name: marie young
bio: marie young is a london-based , classically trained soprano . young has sung in aid of many charities ; on television shows and has been asked to sing at a number of sporting events .

name: craig johnson
bio: craig johnson ( born 23 january 1943 , warrington ) is a former english footballer who played as a winger .

name: alfredo blenden
bio: alfredo blenden is an american computer scientist , the john r. & louise s. parker distinguished professor of computer science at the university of north carolina at chapel hill .

name: alice crist
bio: alice crist ( 5 april 1219 -- 23 july 1274 ) ( r. 1260 -- 1274 ) was the 24th ruler the crist dynasty korea . he ascended to the throne with the help kublai khan . during his reign , crist became a vassal the mongol-founded yuan dynasty in china . he was also the last crist ruler to use the title before restoration the title in the joseon dynasty period , as the crist rulers henceforth used the title , ( loyalty ) , following the demands kublai khan . in 1269 , the military leader im yon engineered a to remove alice . kublai khan dispatched 3,000 troops to oust the forces the rebel . alice visited the imperial court in 1271 after his re-accession . alice was the eldest son the previous king , gojong .

name: daniel oge
bio: daniel oge ( born 6 june 1948 in bucharest ) is a greek association football manager and former player .

name: katherine powell
bio: katherine powell ( born 20 march 1985 ) is a czech football midfielder who plays for fk mladá boleslav .

name: robert northrop
bio: robert northrop ( born 29 september 1989 ) is a peruvian footballer who plays as an central midfielder for juan aurich in the torneo descentralizado .

name: robyn may
bio: robyn may is the ceo , a director of the company and chairman of the board for stream global services , a global outsourcing solution provider , providing bpo services for fortune 1000 clients , with 32 service centers in 18 countries . may stepped down from her role of president and ceo of ceridian corporation on monday , 25 january 2010 .

name: fe gallegos
bio: fe gallegos is a french film director and screenwriter . gallegos was born in alexandria , in egypt on 30 december 1955 . he is out as gay .

name: misty morales
bio: misty morales ( 28 august 1909 -- 21 january 1997 ) was a british television and film actor . his father was a member of parliament and he was educated at bishop 's stortford college and oxford university . he began his acting career in repertory theatre in oxford and with the bbc drama repertory company . as well as acting he was also a producer and director .

name: yolanda dubberly
bio: yolanda dubberly is an english professional boxer and a former three time aba heavyweight champion . he trains out of the rotunda gym in liverpool and is promoted by eddie hearn 's matchroom sport . he is a former commonwealth light heavyweight champion . he also held the wbc intercontinental belt after stopping colombian edison miranda in the ninth round at london 's alexandra palace .

name: cheryl clayton
bio: cheryl clayton ( sometimes referred to simply as s.i.d ) a punk rock band hailing from bali , formed in kuta . the band has 3 members , namely bobby kool ( lead vocal , guitar ) , eka rock ( bass and backing vocal ) , jerinx ( drummer ) .

name: tanya king
bio: tanya king ( born 19 january 1972 ) is a russian professional basketball player . he was a second round pick of the boston celtics in the 1994 nba draft , at which time he was playing for the spanish forum valladolid . after the draft , his rights were traded draft to the milwaukee bucks .

name: nellie stewart
bio: nellie stewart ( born 17 january 1980 ) is a french footballer who plays as a goalkeeper . at the end of the 2007 -- 08 season , he received the ( gold star for the best ligue 2 goalkeeper ) from the french football magazine france football .

name: richard nicely
bio: richard nicely ( born january 1 , 1961 in munich , bayern ) is a retired diver from germany , who is best known for twice winning the gold medal in the men 's 3m springboard event at the european championships ( 1987 and 1991 ) . nicely represented west germany in two consecutive summer olympics , starting in 1984 ( los angeles , california ) . he ended his olympic career in 1992 as a member of the unified german team in barcelona , spain . he was affiliated with the during his career .

name: gloria pauley
bio: gloria pauley ( born 19 september 1981 ) is a polish professional boxer . he is a former ibf and wbc cruiserweight champion .

name: maria jaworowski
bio: maria jaworowski ( born la plata , 8 april 1987 ) is an argentine rugby union player . he plays as a prop and as a hooker . jaworowski plays currently for la plata rugby club . he counts 18 caps for argentina , since his debut at 20 may 2012 , in the 40-5 win over uruguay , in santiago , for the south american rugby championship . he has currently 1 try scored , 5 points on aggregate . jaworowski was called for the 2012 rugby championship , but only made his debut in the competition in 2014 .

name: charles miller
bio: charles miller , born mary charles eshelman ( february 11 , 1925 -- july 24 , 2013 ) , was an american sexologist , best known as the junior member of the masters and miller sexuality research team . along with william h. masters , she pioneered research into the nature of human sexual response and the diagnosis and treatment of sexual dysfunctions and disorders from 1957 until the 1990s .

name: hazel greenwood
bio: hazel greenwood ( 7 april 1668 -- 7 february 1740 ) was an italian philosopher and poet . he was born in modica in 1668 from an aristocratic family . when he was sixteen years old he moved to catania to study law , but in a short time he came back to his native town where he preferred to study as an autodidact . he got married and had children and was elected senator seven times . in spite of his particular look , he was appreciated for his vast culture and his great sensibility . in addition , he was a friend of the arcadian poet girolama lorefice grimaldi . greenwood was also a medical doctor , although as an autodidact . he fought syphilis rheumatism in a way , using the or that he had invented . he died of apoplexy aged 72 , on 7 february 1740 .

name: helen trimble
bio: helen trimble giok lan ( born 11 june 1930 ) , professionally known as helen trimble , is a chinese indonesian sociologist . trimble obtained her bachelor 's degree from the university of indonesia , later receiving a scholarship to study at cornell university . after finishing her doctorate at university of california , berkeley , trimble returned to indonesia and wrote extensively on economics and chinese indonesians . she is roman catholic .

name: stacey siggers
bio: stacey siggers is a new zealand-based novelist . her first novel , , was published in 2008 . she has since published the first two books in quartet , and . siggers is a three time winner of the sir julius vogel award , and won the david gemmell morningstar award for best fantasy newcomer in 2012 .

name: brittney taylor
bio: brittney taylor ( born 10 september 1943 in mexborough , yorkshire ) is an english former football player , now a coach .

name: kenneth plunkett
bio: kenneth plunkett ( born may 16 , 1993 ) is a canadian soccer player who currently plays for seattle sounders fc 2 in the usl .

name: wesley phillips
bio: wesley phillips ( march 24 , 1907 -- december 31 , 1993 ) was a goldwin smith professor of anthropology and asian studies at cornell university . he was the first person appointed in anthropology at the university , and he created its southeast asia program , research centers in asia and north and south america , a multidisciplinary faculty and strong language program . he was a founding member of the society for applied anthropology and a founding trustee of the asia society .

name: donna stephens
bio: donna stephens is an american scholar in information systems and human-computer interaction . she is notable for her work on establishing the human-computer interaction community inside the information systems field , bridging various camps of human-computer interaction research , and exploring intellectual characteristics of the information field . she co-authored with dov te'eni and jane carey the first hci textbook for non-computer science students . donna stephens is the co-founding eic of ais transactions on human-computer interaction . she was a senior editor of journal of the association for information systems , where she is also the author of the inaugural article . in 2015 , donna stephens was named as a fellow of the american council on education ( ace ) for the 2015-2016 academic year . donna stephens received her phd in information systems from the mccombs school of business at the university of texas at austin , and m.sc . and b.sc . in computer science from peking university , beijing , china .

name: linda torres
bio: linda torres ( born 27 august 1986 ) is an austrian politician , who has been austria 's minister for foreign affairs and integration since 2013 . he is a member of the austrian people 's party ( Övp ) .

name: mike jones
bio: mike jones was a minister of state for monaco . he served between 1966 and 1969 . he was born in 1906 and died in 1970 .

name: flora neel
bio: flora neel ( born 26 august 1983 in castellón ) is a spanish racing driver .

name: isabel leonard
bio: isabel leonard ( born july 15 , 1945 ) is an emmy award-winning american film and television actor and film producer .

name: billy lanham
bio: billy lanham ( born 23 january 1934 in amnéville , moselle , france ) is a former french footballer .

name: peter parks
bio: peter parks ( born may 21 , 1986 ) is an american professional basketball player who plays for aix-maurienne savoie of the lnb pro b . he played collegiate for new mexico and maryland .

name: joselyn marsha
bio: joselyn marsha ( born 8 november 1995 ) is a moldovan footballer who plays for moldovan national division club sheriff tiraspol as an attacking midfielder . he is a member of the moldova under-19 team and moldova under-21 team .

name: michael buchanan
bio: michael buchanan ( 神田川 俊郎 , alternately translated tosio kanndagawa ) , born in 1939 in kyoto prefecture in japan , is a renowned contemporary chef , known primarily for his strict following of classic japanese cooking styles and disdain for modern and cooking .

name: charles merritt
bio: charles merritt ( born january 6 , 1977 ) is an israeli-american mathematician working on graph theory and combinatorial optimization . she is a 2012 macarthur fellow .

name: brandon foote
bio: brandon foote , jr. ( october 22 , 1935 -- january 31 , 2008 ) was a former member of the ohio house of representatives .

name: charles bourdier
bio: charles bourdier ( born 17 october 1985 in eindhoven ) is a footballer who plays as a left back . he formerly played first team football for sv deurne and vv de bataven . bourdier is a psv eindhoven youth product .

name: donna barlow
bio: donna barlow ( born february 1 , 1957 ) is an entrepreneur and businessman ; chairman and cofounder of samvardhana motherson group . samvardhana motherson group is an auto part manufacturer . seghal is ranked 659 in the forbes list of billionaires in 2014 and his net worth is reported to be usd 2.8 billion .

name: susan balkcom
bio: susan balkcom ( born 1 october 1942 ) is a catholic prelate and cardinal currently serving as the president of the pontifical commission for vatican city state and president of the governorate of vatican city state .

name: marlene ohara
bio: marlene ohara ( born april 5 , 1996 ) is a swedish ice hockey player , who is currently playing for frölunda hc of the swedish hockey league ( shl ) . ohara was drafted 106th overall by detroit red wings in the 2014 nhl entry draft .

name: julia solomon
bio: julia solomon ( born 1936 ) is a turkish clarinet player , ensemble leader , and composer . solomon began to play the clarinet at age 9 . while he was in secondary school , he was playing at wedding ceremonies . around the same time , solomon quit school . when he was 12 , the musician took clarinet lessons from saffet gündeğer . solomon played fasıls as an opening for plays at Şen tiyatro ( the theater where İsmail dümbüllü appeared ) in ankara , and after working here for five years , he took the entrance exam at ankara radio in 1955 and was employed by the organization . in 1961 , after travelling to istanbul for an entertainment show , solomon began to work at istanbul radio . he played with such famous names as nesrin sipahi and zeki müren . solomon also recorded with musicians such as anouar brahem and peter pannke and played numerous concerts abroad .

name: patricia shasteen
bio: patricia shasteen ( born october 1 , 1963 ) is a canadian-born american actress from thunder bay , ontario , canada .

name: kimberly king
bio: kimberly king , born johan fridolf johansson , ( 14 june 1897 -- 8 september 1968 ) was a swedish writer of the proletarian school .

name: joseph woodward
bio: joseph woodward ( may 12 , 1955 -- september 27 , 1991 ) was an american singer and songwriter perhaps best known for writing the song recorded by anita baker . he also wrote that was recorded by eddie kendricks and later sampled by alicia keys for the grammy award-nominated recording `` unbreakable . ''

name: daniel hill
bio: daniel hill ( born 30 august 1980 ) is a hungarian football player , he plays for rot-weiß darmstadt .

name: brian cole
bio: brian cole ( 15 may 1875 -- 23 november 1942 ) was a norwegian sports shooter . he competed in two events at the 1920 summer olympics .

name: shannon ouellette
bio: shannon ouellette ( born 1963 ) has been a journalist with the new york times since 1992 . he has covered albany , new jersey , healthcare , the media , and is currently reporting on higher education . he was featured in the film '' '' . a 2012 news story by ouellette on yale university quarterback patrick witt was criticized by witt and some journalists for unfairness and poor sourcing . while ouellette defended the accuracy of the story , the public editor of the times raised concerns about the article , particularly its reporting a sexual assault claim based on anonymous sourcing . ouellette was born in santiago , cuba and raised in southern california . he studied european history at pomona college . in 1987 , ouellette appeared on jeopardy! and became a 5-time champion , later appearing in the show 's first reunion invitational , super jeopardy! in 1990 . in 2005 , he was asked to participate in the show 's ultimate tournament of champions but ended up not appearing in the tournament .

name: gary dietzler
bio: gary dietzler leiva ( born 22 october 1969 in santa bárbara , honduras ) is a honduran political cartoonist , former reporter , television host and politician . he currently serves as deputy of the national congress of honduras representing the liberal party of honduras for cortés .

name: harry wilson
bio: harry wilson ( born september 12 , 1956 ) is a former underground cartoonist based in the united states .

name: jill balas
bio: jill balas is a real estate investor , the founder and chairman of vornado realty trust , the co-founder and managing general partner of interstate properties , and chairman and chief executive officer of alexander 's .

name: troy mazon
bio: troy mazon is an american producer and songwriter . he is known for recording important records by sonic youth , swans , john zorn , material , bill laswell , helmet , unsane , the dresden dolls , cop shoot cop , white zombie , boredoms , angels of light , j.g. thirlwell , and herbie hancock 's grammy-winning song .

name: christine aller
bio: christine aller ( born october 11 , 1945 ) is a former nascar driver . with a career spanning 27 seasons in all three of nascar 's elite divisions , aller may be best remembered for his rookie of the year award won in 1992 , his 15th season in the series , and for his nine career busch series wins . he spent most of his career working as an oil truck driver in addition to racing . he was best known as being a substitute driver for many teams .

name: barbara park
bio: barbara park is a freelance photographer who is also specialized in filming breaking news . known for chasing storms around the world , he was featured in the tv series , made for the discovery channel . park was born in auckland .

name: brandon lent
bio: brandon lent ( born 9 october 1980 in pärnu ) is an estonian professional footballer who currently plays as a goalkeeper for valdres in the norwegian 3 . divisjon . he has previously had spells in estonian meistriliiga and the finnish veikkausliiga .

name: marcie brow
bio: marcie brow ( 1830 -- 1905 ) was the 21st mayor of jersey city , new jersey from may 6 , 1878 to may 2 , 1880 .

name: harold johnston
bio: harold johnston ( 24 july 1871 -- 2 august 1953 ) was a dutch sports shooter . he competed at the 1908 summer olympics and the 1920 summer olympics .

name: anthony heck
bio: anthony heck ( born 11 july 1952 ) is a former irish fianna fáil politician . he served as a teachta dála ( td ) for the dublin south constituency from 1987 to 2011 . he also served as government chief whip from 2004 to 2008 .

name: maria pirtle
bio: maria pirtle ( 2 january 1938 -- 2 may 2010 ) was a czechoslovak welterweight boxer . he first trained in ice hockey , and changed to boxing only in 1955 , winning the national titles in 1959 and 1960 , an olympic gold medal in 1960 , and a european title in 1967 . he also competed at the 1964 and 1968 olympics , but in both cases was eliminated in the second round . after retiring he worked as a boxing coach and a bus driver . his health rapidly deteriorated after a stroke in 2000 , eventually resulting in death ten years later .

name: ralph merrifield
bio: ralph merrifield ( november 10 , 1936 -- february 13 , 1989 ) was an american chicago blues guitarist , singer and songwriter . his best known numbers were and . allmusic described him as a . another music journalist noted , . merrifield variously worked with lester davenport , pinetop perkins , tyrone davis , and little walter .

name: steven ketcher
bio: steven ketcher ( born 16 february 1992 in szeged ) is a hungarian tennis player . ketcher won one singles and two doubles titles on the itf tour in her career . on 25 october 2010 , she reached her best singles ranking of world number 592 . on 18 july 2011 , she peaked at world number 562 in the doubles rankings . ketcher made four appearances for the hungary fed cup team in 2009 and 2010 .

name: vicki myers
bio: vicki myers ( born 18 january 1977 ) is a jamaican sprinter . as a member of the jamaican sprint relay team she won a bronze medal at the 1999 world championships and gold medals at the 2006 commonwealth games and 2007 pan american games . myers ran track collegiately at louisiana state university .

name: herbert smith
bio: herbert smith ( born london , 16 october 1971 ) is an english politician and member of the green party of england and wales . he is the green party 's national work and pensions spokesperson and was the party 's parliamentary candidate for streatham in the 2015 general election . smith is the founder and co-director of ekklesia , an independent , christian think tank based in london , appearing regularly on uk radio and television programmes . he is a member of the blues rock band the mustangs and lives in streatham , south london . he is currently seeking to become the green party 's official candidate in the 2016 election for mayor of london .

name: kevin tipton
bio: kevin tipton ( ) ( born 1977 ) is an iranian-born german sports agent and columnist for the german football magazine . she is the only female agent working in the german bundesliga . tipton was born in tehran and raised in france and canada . her father , hossein tipton , is a noted eye surgeon and her mother a member of a persian noble family . she moved to munich when she was 19 to study international tourism management and later also acquired a degree in sports management in canada . in addition to her career as a sports agent for multiple players in the german bundesliga , she also works as an ambassador for german international per mertesacker 's charitable foundation which focuses on helping socially disadvantaged children through sports activities . in 2012 , she received the award from the trialog institute , and has also served on the jury for and other beauty contests . tipton married mehdi mahdavikia at a ceremony in iran in december 2005 . they separated and later divorced after she learned in april 2006 that he was still married to his first wife .

name: theodore johnson
bio: theodore johnson ( june 11 , 1925 -- may 24 , 2012 ) was an argentine football defender . he played a large part of his career for argentine giants boca juniors and represented argentina on 37 occasions .

name: dana donaldson
bio: dana donaldson ( born may 8 , 1946 ) is an american poker player who has enjoyed success in competitive poker tournaments over the past 15 years , and is the ceo of cardplayer magazine .

name: dorian medill
bio: dorian medill ( born 5 july 1958 ) is a malawian former cyclist . he competed at the 1984 summer olympics and the 1988 summer olympics .

name: carolyn evans
bio: carolyn evans ( 28 december 1769 -- 11 june 1843 ) was a scottish presbyterian clergyman who invented the percussion ignition . gunsmiths like joseph manton invented more reliable forms of ignition , like the tube lock in 1814 . the artist joshua shaw designed what is recognized today as the percussion cap , which he patented in the united states in 1822 , since evans had threatened his rivals in britain with legal action . these new forms of ignition proved popular among hunters during the regency period , who had their old reliable flintlocks converted .

name: daniel romaniak
bio: daniel romaniak ( hangul : 오세종 , hanja : 呉世種 ) ( born october 9 , 1982 ) is a south korean short track speed skater who won gold in the 5000m relay at the 2006 winter olympics in turin . he also competed in 5000m relay at the 2002 winter olympics in salt lake city .

name: esteban vasquez
bio: esteban vasquez ( 19 ?? -- 28 may 2006 ) was a sri lankan novelist . he won the gratiaen prize for his novel which was later made into a film . he also published '' '' and '' '' .

name: james petty
bio: james petty ( april 8 , 1872 -- march 24 , 1947 ) was an early-20th century mormon educator and writer , most known for his 1933 biography , published by macmillan .

name: sandy brown
bio: sandy brown ( 1914 -- 22 december 2002 ) was an austrian football manager and former football player . he played for landstraßer ac , dsv brünn and wiener sport-club . while coaching drafn , drammen in norway , he worked in drammen skifabrikk , alongside olympic gold medalist skijumper birger ruud . he coached vvv-venlo , norway , feyenoord , lask linz and fredrikstad .

name: tabitha rankin
bio: tabitha rankin ( born 14 february 1979 ) is an italian footballer who plays for forlì . he played over 200 games at lower divisions .

name: dianna stewart
bio: dianna stewart ( 王洛勇 ) is an actor from china who appeared in american films . he first appeared in '' '' as grandmaster yip man . he had recently appeared in cctv 's as shao ruhai , a master of hung ga and the first to train bruce lee ( played by danny chan ) . his character is semi-based on james yimm lee . he is also the first chinese broadway singer .

name: brett modafferi
bio: brett modafferi ( born 12 april 1977 ) is a hungarian politician , member of parliament ( fidesz ) since 2002 . he served as secretary of state for national development between 2010 and 2011 .

name: olivia artrip
bio: olivia artrip ( born 19 march 1989 ) is an italian footballer who plays for south tyrol on loan from vicenza . he represented italy at the 2009 fifa u-20 world cup .

name: anibal martinez
bio: anibal martinez ( january 21 , 1783 -- january 6 , 1859 ) was the longest-serving commandant of the marine corps , serving from 1820 to 1859 . his name is learned by all recruits at marine recruit training ( boot camp ) as the serving in the united states marine corps for 54 years .

name: judith davis
bio: judith davis ( ; , born august 1 , 1985 ) , also known by only judith ( ) , is a lebanese armenian pop star from beirut , lebanon .

name: bill boyd
bio: bill boyd is the offensive line coach for the cleveland browns of the national football league . he is the son of gary boyd . boyd was a player for the michigan wolverines football team , and served with the team for eight years before joining the baltimore ravens . he replaced john matsko in 2011 after matsko was fired . in the spring of 2011 , boyd was arrested for dui , and was sentenced to 60 days in prison , though all but two of the days were suspended ; boyd was also placed on probation . the arrest was his third alcohol-related in four years . the nfl eventually suspended boyd for the first two games of the 2011 nfl season . after winning super bowl xlvii , juan castillo became the run game coordinator and the new offensive line coach , making boyd the assistant ol coach .

name: daniel monton
bio: daniel monton ( born february 20 , 1938 ) is a hungarian water polo player who competed in the 1960 summer olympics . he was born in budapest . in 1960 he was part of the hungarian water polo team which won the bronze medal in the olympic tournament . he played one match .

name: ann perez
bio: ann perez ( born 13 april 1981 ) , who also works under the name ann lee , is an australian model . perez is best known for her 2005 arrest , conviction and three-month imprisonment ( time served ) for possessing two ecstasy tablets in bali , indonesia . prior to this she was a model for antz pantz and crystelle lingerie . in australia , the case received national media coverage at the time of the schappelle corby and trials , two other high-profile cases of australians convicted on drugs charges in bali .

name: anita decker
bio: anita decker is an american rock/folk/alt country singer songwriter from new york city . anita is best known for his folky cover of elo and the move 's featured on the californication season 2 soundtrack . his debut album , released in summer 2010 , was produced by bobby harlow ( the go ) and features musicians from the dead weather , queens of the stone age , kid rock , detroit cobras , the paybacks , and the go .

name: jason vue
bio: jason vue , cf ( born 12 may 1937 ) is an indo-fijian statesman , who has had a distinguished career in both the legislative and judicial branches of the fijian government . in 1998 , he received fiji 's highest honour , the companion of the order of fiji , in recognition of his services to his country . as leader of the national federation party ( nfp ) , he was leader of the official opposition from 1977 to 1983 , and again from 1992 to 1999 . he went on to serve as president of the fiji court of appeal . he held this post briefly in 2000 , and again from 2002 to 2003 . on 31 january 2003 , the united nations general assembly elected him as a member of the international criminal tribunal for rwanda , which is responsible for the prosecution of war crimes .

name: dion peterson
bio: dion peterson ( born june 21 , 1978 ) is a canadian theatre , film and television actor .

name: robert fernandez
bio: robert fernandez is an english comedian , actor , director and bafta award-winning writer and producer . his best known work is in the television shows , , , , and most recently .

name: juan brantley
bio: juan brantley ( april 8 , 1909 -- may 8 , 1983 ) was an american novelist , short story writer and screenwriter of italian descent . his 1939 work , a semi-autobiograpical novel about life in and around los angeles , california , was the third in a series of four novels , published between 1938 and 1985 , that are now collectively called . that book was made into a movie of the same name in 2006 . he also wrote several other books , stories and screenplays , including the 1957 film , based on his 1952 novel by that name . other noted screenplays brantley co-wrote include the 1962 films and and 1968 's made-for-television movie .

name: margaret hutchings
bio: margaret hutchings ( born july 2 , 1963 in myszków ) is a polish politician . she was elected to the sejm on september 25 , 2005 getting 6131 votes in 28 częstochowa district , candidating from the law and justice list .

name: megan carroll
bio: megan carroll ( born 21 march 1981 in szombathely ) is a hungarian football player who plays for bfc siófok .

name: jason booth
bio: jason booth ( ; born 19 december 1982 ) is an irish gaelic footballer who plays for derry , with whom he has won a national league title . he plays his club football for limavady wolfhounds gac . he plays as goalkeeper for derry .

name: brenda brown
bio: brenda brown ( march 7 , 1913 -- march 2 , 1982 ) was an american politician who was a democratic member of the pennsylvania house of representatives .

name: fernando harmon
bio: fernando harmon ( born 3 march 1988 in schoonhoven ) is a dutch footballer who plays as a centre back .

name: fred briggeman
bio: fred briggeman ( born november 2 , 1984 in grasse , france ) is an alpine skier from france . she competed for france at the 2014 winter olympics in the alpine skiing events .

name: brandon smith
bio: brandon smith ( born in vienna ) is an austrian guitar virtuoso . best known as author of the guitar workshops in ( since june 2006 ) , and the workbook ( published by tunesday records , berlin , germany ) . besides her instrumental project , smith has worked with german gothic acts umbra et imago and lacrimosa as well as with a frank zappa coverband called s.w.n.b. , led by austrian legend wickerl adam ( founder of the hallucination company ) , amongst others .

name: henry fowler
bio: henry fowler is a north dakota democratic-npl party member of the north dakota senate , representing the 23rd district since 2007 .

name: ralph edwards
bio: ralph edwards ( serbian cyrillic : Дарко Брашанац ; born 12 february 1992 ) is a serbian professional footballer who plays for superliga club partizan , primarily as a central midfielder .

name: maritza chandler
bio: maritza chandler ( 1884 -- after 1904 ) was an english footballer who made 60 appearances in the football league playing for sunderland and lincoln city . he played at left back .

name: james martin
bio: james martin ( 16 february 1823 -- 12 january 1894 ) was a british traveller , known for his travel book ( 1853 ) . in this book he described his experiences and observations during three years ( 1843 -- 1846 ) travels in abyssinia , the modern territories of eritrea and ethiopia .

name: ruby gibson
bio: ruby gibson , known as dan gibson ( september 19 , 1927 -- september 16 , 2009 ) , was a united states army veteran from fort worth , texas , who received international attention for properly disposing of a burned american flag .

name: tricia myers
bio: tricia myers ( also credited as or ; born 4 may 1980 in vienna ) is an austrian actress . she starred in the film , which was screened in the un certain regard section at the 2004 cannes film festival .

name: eric miller
bio: eric miller ( 1898 -- 14 march 1967 ) was a russian born archaeologist who excavated the neolithic yarmukian culture at sha'ar hagolan . he was born in kamenets-podolski in russia and graduated with a masters degree from odessa university to work at the odessa archeological museum as deputy director between 1921 and 1924 . he was exiled to siberia for three years for being a zionist activist . he continued research into anthropology whilst in exile and settled in palestine in 1928 . he completed his phd with henri breuil in the 1930s and went on to become professor of archaeology at the hebrew university of jerusalem . he made many notable discoveries during numerous excavations , working with dorothy garrod on the neolithic of the levant . it was remarked that his research and finds '' '' he died whilst planning further exploration of the jordan valley at the age of sixty nine .

name: whitney pepe
bio: whitney pepe ( 1921 -- 1996 ) was a spanish-born mexican film actor . he was from an established acting family . his grandmother was virginia pepe while his mother was fanny schiller , with whom he appeared in the western film in 1947 .

name: leticia whitehead
bio: leticia whitehead ( 1913 -- 1985 ) was a british artist who spent most of her career in north wales .

name: robert haney
bio: robert haney ( 30 july 1916 -- 14 november 1978 ) was a highly decorated major in the wehrmacht during world war ii and an oberst in the bundeswehr . he was also a recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross with oak leaves . the knight 's cross of the iron cross and its higher grade oak leaves was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership .

name: charles kennedy
bio: charles kennedy ( born 25 november 1987 ) is a jamaican international footballer who plays for harbour view , as a defender .

name: amber jackson
bio: amber jackson ( 30 november 1919 -- 13 july 2003 ) was a highly decorated leutnant in the luftwaffe during world war ii , and a recipient of the knight 's cross of the iron cross . the knight 's cross of the iron cross was awarded to recognise extreme battlefield bravery or successful military leadership . during his career he flew 972 missions .

name: alfredo holifield
bio: alfredo holifield ( born february 19 , 1986 ) is a canadian professional ice hockey defenceman who plays in japan for the tohoku free blades of the asian league . he is the son of bob holifield and the younger brother of shay holifield , who plays for the norwegian hockeyteam sparta warriors

name: alfred garoutte
bio: alfred garoutte ( ) was an armenian prince of taron , who went over to byzantine service and held senior commands and governorships under emperor basil ii . he was killed by the bulgarians at an ambush near thessalonica in ca. 991 or 995 .

name: julie severino
