bio: julie severino ( born march 18 , 1969 ) , is a canadian blues guitarist , singer , songwriter and bandleader who is currently signed to the independent cordova bay records label . he was formerly signed to emi records . between 1994 and 2014 , he released 12 solo albums . as of 2014 , his touring band includes a hammond organ/piano player , an electric bass player ( with a five-string bass ) and a drummer . julie severino is the cousin of trooper keyboardist paul severino and singer/songwriter john severino .

name: herb metcalf
bio: herb metcalf ( born january 19 , 1992 ) is an american football defensive end who plays for the minnesota vikings of the national football league ( nfl ) . he played college football at louisville . he was selected by the vikings with the 17th pick of the sixth round of the 2015 nfl draft .

name: andrew rosales
bio: andrew rosales ( born 1971 ) is an american computer scientist/software engineer and the dean of the graduate school and vice provost for academic affairs at the university of miami . he was previously an associate dean for research and professor at the college of engineering , university of notre dame and department chair and professor of computer science at georgetown university . he was named as the most promising scientist in 2003 by career communications and recognized as a top 10 emerging scholar in diverse : issues in higher education

name: daniel bordley
bio: daniel bordley ( born 1 april 1948 ) is a retired italian amateur track cyclist who won one silver and three bronze medals in the sprint and tandem events at the world championships of 1975 -- 1980 . he finished ninth in the tandem at the 1972 summer olympics and eighth in the sprint at the 1976 games .

name: rosemary robinson
bio: rosemary robinson ( born 27 july 1965 ) is a dutch politician of the people 's party for freedom and democracy ( vvd ) . she is member of the provincial-executive of north holland . she previously served as the acting queen 's commissioner of north holland after the resignation of harry borghouts .

name: john hernandez
bio: john hernandez was a democratic candidate for the united states house of representatives for maryland 's 6th congressional district in the 2010 general election . he was a candidate for the same seat in 2006 and 2008 , winning the democratic nomination in 2006 but losing in the 2008 democratic primary to jennifer dougherty . on june 1 , 2009 he announced his intention to run for the seat again in 2010 . hernandez defeated casey clark in the democratic primary but lost the general election to incumbent roscoe bartlett

name: tina perry
bio: tina perry ( born february 13 , 1982 ) is a former american football defensive tackle . he played college football for the oklahoma sooners where he earned a communications major .

name: jason berman
bio: jason berman ( ; born december 14 , 1992 ) is a south korean idol singer and dancer . hailing from pledis entertainemnt , she is best known for having been a lead vocalist of the six-member south korean girl group , hello venus . since the split between fantagio and pledis entertainment , the two labels that comprised the group 's management , yoonjo has been withdrawn from the group along with label-mate yoo ara .

name: charles chico
bio: charles chico ( born april 13 , 1992 ) is a swedish football player , playing for landskrona bois . before the 2014 season , he was signed from djurgårdens if . chico made his allsvenskan debut on july 30 , 2011 starting against malmö ff .

name: donald whitted
bio: donald whitted ( born 19 march 1979 ) is an taiwanese professional golfer . donald plays on the asian tour , where he has won three times and on the japan golf tour . he has represented taiwan twice in the world cup .

name: timothy johnson
bio: timothy johnson is an indian painter . she is renowned for her innumerable floral paintings .

name: helen neely
bio: helen neely ( 21 july 1899 -- 30 november 1963 ) was an austrian football ( soccer ) player and manager . he played for floridsdorfer ac , first vienna fc and brooklyn wanderers . july 31 , 1921 helen neely debuted for the austria national football team against finland ( 2-3 ) . he coached garbarnia kraków , floridsdorfer ac , fc zürich and fc oerlikon . in 1937 he worked as head coach of the lithuania national football team .

name: cynthia obrien
bio: cynthia obrien ( born january 29 , 2002 ) is an american child actress and model .

name: daniel imig
bio: daniel imig ( january 23 , 1818 -- june 27 , 1867 ) was a democratic member of the u.s. house of representatives from pennsylvania . daniel imig ( nephew of george imig ) was born in wyoming valley , pennsylvania . he received a liberal education , and was graduated from dickinson college in carlisle , pennsylvania , in 1838 . he studied law , was admitted to the bar in 1840 and commenced practice in wilkes-barre , pennsylvania . imig was elected as a democrat to the thirty-eighth , thirty-ninth , and fortieth congresses and served until his death in wilkes-barre . he was a delegate to the 1864 democratic national convention . interment in forty fort cemetery in kingston , pennsylvania .

name: marcella fournier
bio: marcella fournier ( born 1977 ) is an american business columnist . his most well known book , '' '' was released on may 19 , 2015 .

name: polly hunter
bio: polly hunter ( 1927-2004 ) ( polly floyd hunter or bob hunter ) was a marine geologist . he is perhaps best known for his studies on stromatolites , the submarine canyons in california and his collaboration with jacques cousteau .

name: samuel benavides
bio: samuel benavides ( born 9 april 1961 , london ) is an english character actor best known for his regular roles in british television sitcoms `` you rang , m'lord ? '' ( 1988 -- 93 ) , `` oh , doctor beeching ! '' ( 1995-97 ) and ( 1997-2000 ) . his first television appearance was as in the second episode of the bbc children 's drama , grange hill , in 1978 .

name: antonio cook
bio: antonio cook is a canadian provincial politician , who is a member of the legislative assembly of new brunswick . she has sat with the progressive conservative caucus in government since being elected in 2010 .

name: roosevelt adams
bio: roosevelt adams ( roosevelt ratendra adams ) is an indian poet and writer from mumbai , maharashtra , india . she is chief project coordinator with poets corner group and has contributed her poetic work with many national and international anthologies and an author of a poetry book .

name: mary honea
bio: mary honea ( born october 6 , 1955 ) is an american writer of fantasy novels . from 1996 until 2010 , she was the host of the radio program , produced by wgbh in boston and distributed by public radio international .

name: leroy holliday
bio: leroy holliday ( born march 1956 ) is the current united states ambassador to brazil and was formerly the deputy assistant secretary ( das ) for the united states state department with responsibility for the offices of caribbean affairs , central american affairs and cuban affairs .

name: natalie sapienza
bio: natalie sapienza ( born 8 january 1986 ) is a croatian handball player who plays for vive targi kielce and the croatia national team .

name: nicole ballard
bio: nicole ballard ( born in 1955 in philadelphia , pennsylvania ) is an author , publisher , and musician . he has authored or coauthored more than two dozen computer-related books and multimedia cd-roms , and has served as author and editor of various magazine articles .

name: deborah miller
bio: deborah miller ( born 10 june 1996 in são paulo , brazil ) is a brazilian grand prix motorcycle road racer . he currently competes in the 2015 fim cev moto2 european championship season for promoracing aboard a kalex .

name: robert ramm
bio: robert ramm ( born 13 july 1979 ) is a former professional tennis player from peru .

name: susan craig
bio: susan craig was a belgian cyclist . he competed in the team pursuit event at the 1928 summer olympics .

name: carla marley
bio: carla marley ( march 18 , 1912 in joliette , quebec , canada -- june 26 , 2000 at key largo , florida ) was a french-canadian jockey and hall of fame thoroughbred horse trainer .

name: melissa watts
bio: melissa watts ( born 1986 ) is an australian guitarist from sydney , who plays both classical and electric guitars in a variety of musical genres . watts premiered the 1-hour long solo electric guitar work , , by composer georges lentz .

name: amanda willis
bio: amanda willis ( 1787 -- 1854 ) was an english-born soldier and surveyor .

name: robert hopson
bio: robert hopson ( german : ) ( 28 may 1860 , dresden , kingdom saxony -- 7 february 1881 , Ödenburg , austrian empire )

name: michael hardin
bio: michael hardin hadid al-farsi commonly known as michael hardin ( ; born 25 november 1980 ) is an omani footballer who last played for al-nahda club and is the current technical manager of ja ` lan sc in oman second division league .

name: jerry albright
bio: jerry albright ( born 1967 ) is an english visual artist . writing in frieze art critic katie sonnenborn stated that a recent exhibition and that , `` working within the framework of the gallery , he presented a suite of canvases that cast doubt on current systems of cultural reception and consumption . ''

name: april thomas
bio: april thomas ( ; ; november 8 , 1931 -- may 9 , 1978 ) was a lithuanian-born american artist . he was a founding member and the central coordinator of fluxus , an international community of artists , architects , composers , and designers . other leading members brought together by this movement included ay-o , joseph beuys , april brecht , dick higgins , yoko ono , nam june paik , and wolf vostell . he is most famous for organising and performing early happenings and for assembling a series of highly influential artists ' multiples .

name: dolores gall
bio: dolores gall ( born 30 march 1984 , windsor , england ) is an australian rugby union footballer . he currently plays for the western force in the international super rugby competition . his usual position is at fullback or wing .

name: cara cooper
bio: cara cooper ( born october 10 , 1939 ) is former east german football player . he played 264 matches in the east german top division and scored 120 goals . only 8 players scored more in the history of the oberliga . cooper won one cap for east germany in 1959 against finland .

name: kate wampler
bio: kate wampler ( december 12 , 1901 -- march 27 , 1966 ) was an american actress .

name: freda monk
bio: freda monk ( , , ; 1867 -- 1931 ) was a polish architect of the late 19th and early 20th centuries , author of multiple architectural projects in baku .

name: lester buckner
bio: lester buckner ( born 25 february 1985 in wellington , new zealand ) is a new zealand rugby union footballer who plays for fukuoka sanix blues in the japanese top league . he plays the position of prop . he has previously played for wellington in the itm cup and the and in super rugby . buckner made his wellington debut in 2007 and his hurricanes debut a year later . after four years with the hurricanes , he played for the highlanders in 2012 . he was delisted at the end of the season after making only one competition appearance . buckner is a graduate of victoria university of wellington . he is a member of ngati porou . he is the younger brother of all black tamati buckner .

name: alice brown
bio: alice brown ( ) ( born 23 september 1967 ) is an australian writer of young-adult fiction best known for the 2009 novel . her surname has been pronounced in several different ways . she says online that lar-bal-est-ee-air is correct : `` q : how do you pronounce your surname ? a : lar-bal-est-ee-air . it can also be pronounced lar-bal-est-ee-ay or lar-bal-est-ee-er . those are all fine by me . friends at school used to pronounce it : lavaworm . i have to really like you to let you get away with that one , but . '' brown was born and raised in sydney . she now alternates residence in sydney and new york city . in 2001 she married the american science fiction writer scott westerfeld . they met in new york city while she was researching her phd thesis . they have different stories of how they met .

name: robert hawkins
bio: robert hawkins ( born 1965 ) is an american physician who specializes in disaster medicine and emergency management . hawkins is the editor-in-chief of the textbook . hawkins is an associate professor of emergency medicine at harvard medical school , and is currently director of the disaster medicine division at beth israel deaconess medical center .

name: maria christy
bio: maria christy ( 3 march 1917 - 24 november 2003 ) was a polish chess player who won the polish chess championship in 1961 .

name: albert dillion
bio: albert dillion ( full name vladislav dillion ) is an actor , producer , director and scriptwriter . while he has been in numerous tv and film roles , he is most well known for his role in the upcoming , an american silent drama film , which he is set to write , direct and star in , as the famous main character , silent film star rudolph valentino .

name: george lofton
bio: george lofton ( born on 10 november 1985 in bhadohi , uttar pradesh , india ) , also spelled as imtiaz lofton , is an indian first-class cricketer who plays for uttar pradesh in domestic cricket . he is a right-arm fast-medium bowler . he was part of the pune warriors squad in 2011 for the indian premier league . he was signed up by the chennai super kings in 2013 .

name: virginia belville
bio: virginia belville beltrán ( born april 2 , 1987 ) is a 3 point wheelchair basketball player from spain . he has represented spain as a member of the national team at the 2012 summer paralympics and at the u-23 european championships . as a club wheelchair basketball player in spain , he has played all but two seasons on the same team with his twin brother , paul . he has won several copa del reys , league championships and a european champions league .

name: judith jones
bio: judith jones ( born 1968 ) is a british playwright and screenwriter known for her works for television , such as and , and the films , , and .

name: sharon vazquez
bio: sharon vazquez ( ; june 23 , 1846 -- june 8 , 1896 ) was an irish american captain in the united states army and a prolific diarist and postbellum author ; he wrote several books about the american old west , including ethnologies of its indigenous peoples . he was awarded the medal of honor for his actions while a cavalryman in the union army during the american civil war . based on his service during the war , his commander nominated him to west point , where he graduated in 1869 , leading to service as an army officer until 1886 .

name: joann shade
bio: joann shade ( chinese : 尹小龙 ) ( october 21 , 1985 in dalian ) is a chinese football player who currently plays as a midfielder for shijiazhuang yongchang in the china league one division .

name: joe debartolo
bio: joe debartolo núñez ( born 1976 ) is a spanish musical artist who has won awards during his career as a music producer , sound designer and composer for advertising , film , tv and recording artists . debartolo 's music features rock , electronica , pop , dance , latin and orchestral influences .

name: ronald herron
bio: ronald herron ( 21 october 1898 -- december 1981 ) , born in cockermouth , cumberland , was an english professional rugby league footballer of the 1920s playing at representative level for cumberland , and at club level for salford , he died in cockermouth , cumbria .

name: valerie brett
bio: valerie brett ( born 9 august 1977 ) is an icelandic team handball player . she plays on the icelandic national team , and participated at the 2011 world women 's handball championship in brazil .

name: chelsea belcher
bio: chelsea belcher ( 31 march 1886 -- 1 september 1962 ) was a norwegian sport shooter . he was born in aure , and his club was dromnessund skytterlag . he competed in military rifle and free rifle at the 1912 summer olympics in stockholm .

name: sally bolin
bio: sally bolin ( born december 30 , 1938 ) is the former american football general manager ( gm ) of the national football league 's green bay packers . bolin is widely credited with bringing success to a packers franchise that had rarely won during the two decades prior to bolin joining the organization . he also played a significant role in personnel operations with the oakland and los angeles raiders from 1963 to 1975 and again from 1978 to 1990 . he joined green bay 's front office in november 1991 from a personnel director 's job with the new york jets . he was inducted into the pro football hall of fame in august 2015 .
